NK117(she)001:1: // sa rba sa m+aa dza bi d+y+aa d+ai pam n+aa
NK117(she)001:2: ma d+ha rma ma h+aa ni d+hi ko sha bi
NK117(she)001:4: chos kyi gter mdzod chen po kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK117(she)001:5: dpal kun tu bzang po rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:6: rgyu yis stsol sgrub las 'das kun bzang bde ba che //
NK117(she)001:7: mngon gyur sems nyid sems las ma byung rig pa'i gshis //
NK117(she)001:8: lung las ma byung man ngag zab mos mngon sum du //
NK117(she)001:9: bstan mdzad dpal ldan bla ma mchog zhabs spyi bos mchod //
NK117(she)001:10: chos dbyings gnas lugs phyogs bral byang chub snying po'i ngang //
NK117(she)001:11: gdod nas bcing grol med la rkyen gyis 'khrul ma myong //
NK117(she)001:12: rgyu rtsol lam gyi rtogs las shin tu khyad 'phags pa'i //
NK117(she)001:13: rang byung ston pa rgyal ba kun gyi myes chen po //
NK117(she)001:14: sku lnga lhun rdzogs phyogs bral mkhyen mchog gsum ldan pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15: yon tan rgya mtsho rdzogs shing thugs rjes mkha' ltar khyab //
NK117(she)001:16: rlabs chen mdzad pas kun grol dpal mgon mchog gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:17: rang byung kun tu bzang la chos dbyings dbyer med 'dud //
NK117(she)001:18: ci bzhin lam gyis rtogs pa mngon gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:19: spang thob gnyis med skyon bral yon tan rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:20: mkhyen pa'i ye shes sgrib med mngon sum gzigs //
NK117(she)001:21: brtse ba'i thugs rjes srid mtha' ma lus 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:22: mdzad pa'i phrin las bde legs kun 'byung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:23: rgyal ba sku lnga ye shes mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK117(she)001:24: phyogs dus sangs rgyas ma lus 'khor bcas la //
NK117(she)001:25: rang snang dbyer med gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:26: rgyal ba'i zhal nas legs gsung bka' rgyud rnams //
NK117(she)001:27: sems kyi nam mkha' phyogs ris kun bral la //
NK117(she)001:28: ye shes nyi mas ma rig mun sel zhing //
NK117(she)001:29: dri med bdud rtsis 'khor ba'i gcong 'byin pa'i //
NK117(she)001:30: rim dang cig char rnam grol yang dag lam //
NK117(she)001:31: dam pa'i chos la mi 'bral spro bas 'dud //
NK117(she)001:32: rig pa mchog la mnga' brnyes sems dpa'i tshul //
NK117(she)001:33: sangs rgyas gnyis pa rgyal sras 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK117(she)001:34: rgyal ba'i dbang bskur bstan pa'i sgron me mdzad //
NK117(she)001:35: thugs rje thabs mkhas mdzad pa bsam yas kyis //
NK117(she)001:36: lha srin dbang sdud gdul bya kun sgrol ba'i //
NK117(she)001:37: rig 'dzin byang sems rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:38: bod kyi mun sel gdul bya skal ldan phyir //
NK117(she)001:39: thugs rjes ltar snang dka' ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK117(she)001:40: sangs rgyas bstan pa ma lus thugs la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:41: bod khams chos kyi nyi shar gdul bya smin //
NK117(she)001:42: rnam snang la sogs sgra bsgyur sprul pa la //
NK117(she)001:43: rang bzhin rnam dag dbyer med ngang phyag 'tshal //
NK117(she)001:44: bka' brgyud gdams pa'i mdzod la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK117(she)001:45: dbang dang byin brlabs nyams myong rtogs par ldan //
NK117(she)001:46: chu bo bzhi rdzogs yon tan gter mdzod kyis //
NK117(she)001:47: gdul bya'i re skongs thar pa'i lam 'dren pa'i //
NK117(she)001:48: rgyal sras mi mchog 'gro mgon dge ba'i bshes //
NK117(she)001:49: bka' rgyud bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:50: dkon mchog gsum bdag chos rje gtsug gis rgyan //
NK117(she)001:51: dam pa'i mdzod mnga' rnal 'byor dbang phyug che //
NK117(she)001:52: lung rig man ngag rang rig sgron ma yis //
NK117(she)001:53: ma rig mun sel yang dag lam ston pa'i //
NK117(she)001:54: bla ma 'gro ba'i mgon po lha rje la //
NK117(she)001:55: gnyis med rang snang ngang du phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:56: dus gsum rgyal ba ma lus thugs kyi bcud //
NK117(she)001:57: bstan pa'i snying po ma nor nges pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:58: theg pa'i yang rtse nye lam bde rdzogs shing //
NK117(she)001:59: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kun 'byung rin chen mdzod //
NK117(she)001:60: gsang sngags khog dbub gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don //
NK117(she)001:61: gol sa'i dmigs bsal theg pa'i shan phye la //
NK117(she)001:62: don gyi la bzla dgongs pa'i bcud blangs te //
NK117(she)001:63: rang grol mngon bstan don chen lhun grub phyir //
NK117(she)001:64: bla ma'i gsung dang lung rig man ngag gi //
NK117(she)001:65: dgongs pa'i bcud bsdus legs dpyad don dril nas //
NK117(she)001:66: 'di mos 'ga' la phan srid sems bskyed dang //
NK117(she)001:67: bskul don brtse bas gsal byed yi ger bkod //
NK117(she)001:68: sprul sku thub dbang sgron ma'i bstan pa la //
NK117(she)001:69: bstan pa'i gzhi ma sde snod rnam gsum dang //
NK117(she)001:70: chos dbyings bde chen 'og min gnas mchog tu //
NK117(she)001:71: rgyal ba sku bzhi'i dgongs pa mngon phyungs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:72: bstan pa'i snying po theg mchog gsang sngags ni //
NK117(she)001:73: sku lnga brgyud nas 'dzam gling dbus su byung //
NK117(she)001:74: rgyal sras rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' yis //
NK117(she)001:75: de don mngon byas zab mo'i bcud bsdus shing //
NK117(she)001:76: dgongs pa'i don bkrol thugs rje'i 'od zer spros //
NK117(she)001:77: rgya gar chos kyi 'byung gnas bstan pa rgyas //
NK117(she)001:78: bod kyi mun sel sgra bsgyur sprul pa yis //
NK117(she)001:79: bod khams chos kyi nyi shar dkar por bsgyur //
NK117(she)001:80: rim par brgyud nas rje yi bka' drin gyis //
NK117(she)001:81: snying po'i 'od kyis bdag blo'i mun bsal nas //
NK117(she)001:82: rtogs pa'i nor mchog shes rab sgron ma yis //
NK117(she)001:83: chos kun bcud bsdus gter mdzod man ngag 'di //
NK117(she)001:84: bka' rnams gsal ston bstan pa'i spyi 'grel zhing //
NK117(she)001:85: shan 'byed la zlos theg pa'i spyi mdo ste //
NK117(she)001:86: lta phug kun ston dgongs pa'i spyi mdzod do //
NK117(she)001:87: rgyu 'bras kun gsal chos kyi me long yin //
NK117(she)001:88: mngon sum ngo sprod nyams myong man ngag la //
NK117(she)001:89: sa lam rtogs tshad kun gsal sgron ma ste //
NK117(she)001:90: 'khor ba'i gcong 'byin dri med bdud rtsi'i mchog /
NK117(she)001:91: chos dbyings mdzod brtul bcud bsdus gsal byed pas //
NK117(she)001:92: chos gter kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me'o //
NK117(she)001:93: nyi 'od 'bum pas shin tu gsal gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:94: mun sel rig pa'i nyi ma 'di gson cig /
NK117(she)001:95: sman mchog ma gi tas kyang bskrun med pa'i //
NK117(she)001:96: nyon mongs nad 'joms sman mchog 'di gson cig /'dod 'byung yid bzhin nor gyis mtshungs med pa'i //
NK117(she)001:97: chos dbyings mi mdzad gter chen 'di gson cig /
NK117(she)001:98: ro brgya ldan pa'i zas bas bcud lhag pa'i //
NK117(she)001:99: zag med bdud rtsi'i zas mchog 'di gson cig /
NK117(she)001:100: mi 'jigs rdo rje'i rdzong bas btsan gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:101: skye med rdo rje'i rdzong chen 'di gson cig /
NK117(she)001:102: gnas lugs phyogs bral rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ni //
NK117(she)001:103: thun mong ma yin shin tu dpag dka' bas //
NK117(she)001:104: dad tsam la brten gang zag rjes 'brang ba'i //
NK117(she)001:105: rang blo phyogs 'dzin dri ma kun bsal te //
NK117(she)001:106: bsregs bcad bdar bas sa gser nges rtogs ltar //
NK117(she)001:107: chos kyi rjes 'brang tshad ma rnam gsum gyis //
NK117(she)001:108: legs par brtag dpyad shes rab mig ldan pas //
NK117(she)001:109: 'di don phug rtogs dgongs pa'i bcud longs shig /
NK117(she)001:110: de la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa /
NK117(she)001:111: bstan pa thams cad kyi snying po /
NK117(she)001:112: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK117(she)001:113: gsang ba bas kyang ches gsang ba /
NK117(she)001:114: yang gsang rmad du byung ba pa /
NK117(she)001:115: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i don gyi khog dbub cing /
NK117(she)001:118: 'bras bu mngon du bya ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:121: don ma nor bar la bzlas te /
NK117(she)001:122: rang grol mngon sum du ston pas 'di la nan
NK117(she)001:123: tan du byas la dgongs pa'i bcud blang bar bya'o
NK117(she)001:124: // de ltar mtshon cing gtan la 'bebs pa la spyi don gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:125: khog dbub pa'i stong thun dang /
NK117(she)001:126: don snang ba rnam pa bzhi'am /
NK117(she)001:127: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du dril te bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:129: chos spyi'i ngos bzung 'brel ka dang bcas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:130: bye brag tu rgyud dam man ngag tu khog dbub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:132: gzhi shes bya gshis kyi gnas lugs ci ltar yin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:133: de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:134: 'khrul gyis mi bde ste sdug bsngal zhing nyam thag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:135: de la thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis gzigs tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:136: gzigs nas thugs rje skyes tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:137: skyes nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:139: spyir thegs pa re la 'dod lugs re yod kyang /
NK117(she)001:142: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:144: sangs rgyas pa'i go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:145: sangs rgyas pa'i rgyas lugs dang /
NK117(she)001:146: de ngo sprad cing the tshom gyi geg bsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:148: chos kun rang byung ye shes yin la /
NK117(she)001:149: de nyid mtha' gang du yang ma lhung bas sangs /
NK117(she)001:150: mtha' thams cad du ma 'gags par rang snang bas rgyas pa zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:153: nyon mongs dug lnga dug gsum kyang //
NK117(she)001:154: rang byung ye shes mngon du phyung //
NK117(she)001:156: rig pa mngon du phyungs bas na //
NK117(she)001:158: gang la mi gnas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK117(she)001:159: mngon sum pa ru ye sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:161: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:162: 'khor 'das gzhi la gnas pa'i lhun grub de //
NK117(she)001:163: rang sems snying po byang chub chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:164: kun la rang chas yod phyir ye sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:165: rtogs dang ma rtogs med par kun gyi gzhi //
NK117(she)001:169: thams cad ye shes chos skur shar //
NK117(she)001:172: dngos po med sangs kun khyab rgyas //
NK117(she)001:173: de shes de bzhin nyid du chub //
NK117(she)001:176: rang byung chos sku spros dang bral bas sangs //
NK117(she)001:177: spros bral rtogs pa gdeng du gyur pas rgyas //
NK117(she)001:180: sangs rgyas sangs rgyas bya ba'i nges tshig ni //
NK117(she)001:181: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin las //
NK117(she)001:182: spros bral dbyibs dang dbang po'i spyod yul sangs //
NK117(she)001:183: nam mkha' bzhin du kun la khyab pas rgyas //
NK117(she)001:184: sangs rgyas ming du btag pa nga yis med //
NK117(she)001:187: ma h+aa yo ga bden pa rnam gsum sku gsum du sangs rgyas lugs dang /
NK117(she)001:188: a nu yo ga yab yum dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde ba chen po dang /
NK117(she)001:189: mdo dgongs 'dus nyid kyi dkyil 'khor gsum sku gsum du dang /
NK117(she)001:190: a ti 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes ye nas che ba lngar sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:192: bden pa gsum gyi go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:193: de sku gsum du sangs rgyas lugs so //
NK117(she)001:194: snga ma ni chos thams cad spros bral skye ba med cing /
NK117(she)001:195: rang rig pa'i ye shes las g.yos pa med pas don dam zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:197: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK117(she)001:198: dmigs med tshul du der snang ngo //
NK117(she)001:199: dbyings dang dbyings kyi ye shes kyang //
NK117(she)001:200: rang rig kho na tsam du zad //
NK117(she)001:202: la shan gyi ma h+aa'i skabs nas /
NK117(she)001:203: rang rig nyi ma'i ye shes nyid //
NK117(she)001:204: dngos gnyis la sogs byed po'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:206: de nyid rig pa sgyu ma'i ngo bor cir yang snang bas kun rdzob ste /
NK117(she)001:208: rgyal ba'i sku yang ma bskyed par //
NK117(she)001:209: rig pa'i ye shes sgyu mar shar //
NK117(she)001:210: khams gsum pa yang de bzhin pas //
NK117(she)001:211: thabs chen sgyu ma kun ngo bo //
NK117(she)001:214: cho 'phrul yul sems tshul nyid kyang //
NK117(she)001:215: thabs dang shes rab mtshan nyid do //
NK117(she)001:217: de gnyis su med pa ni bden pa dbyer med do //
NK117(she)001:219: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK117(she)001:220: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtogs //
NK117(she)001:223: gnyis med byang sems ngo bo las //
NK117(she)001:224: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin ngang gis med //
NK117(she)001:227: ngo bo thams cad sems yin te //
NK117(she)001:228: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med //
NK117(she)001:229: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:231: de nyid spros bral skye ba med pas chos skur dang /
NK117(she)001:232: ma 'gag pa cir yang snang bas sprul skur dang /
NK117(she)001:233: de gnyis su med pa rang rig pa'i ye shes su longs spyod pas longs skur sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:235: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:236: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK117(she)001:237: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK117(she)001:239: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK117(she)001:240: gzhi rdzogs phyag rgyar ma 'dres gsal //
NK117(she)001:243: thams cad ma lus chos so chog /
NK117(she)001:244: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK117(she)001:245: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:246: yang a nu yab yum dbyings dang ye shes gnyis
NK117(she)001:247: su med pa'i sras bde ba chen por sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:248: pa ni / yul du snang ba thams cad dbyings su mtha' med pas yum kun tu bzang mo /
NK117(she)001:249: rig pa rang gsal ba thams cad ye shes sgrib pa med pas yab kun tu bzang po /
NK117(she)001:250: de gnyis 'du 'bral med pas sras bde ba chen por sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:252: rang snang rol pa bsam yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:253: b+ha ga'i klong las g.yos pa med //
NK117(she)001:255: sangs ma rgyas gcig med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:257: de yang dbyings skye ba med par chos skur dang /
NK117(she)001:258: ye shes rol pa rang snang bas sprul skur dang /
NK117(she)001:259: 'du 'bral med pas longs skur sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:261: dkyil 'khor gsum sku gsum du sangs rgyas lugs ni /
NK117(she)001:262: dal gsum gyi go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:263: sangs rgyas pa'i rgyas lugs so //
NK117(she)001:265: ye ji bzhin pa'i dal ni /
NK117(she)001:267: sems kyi rang bzhin ma bcos ma bslad skye ba med cing /
NK117(she)001:268: ye nas gnas pa la bya ste /
NK117(she)001:270: ma bcos ma bslad ma bung ma skyes ci bzhin pa de kho na nyid /
NK117(she)001:271: ye ci bzhin pa'i dal du mthong lags so //
NK117(she)001:273: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dal ni /
NK117(she)001:274: sems nyid rtsol ba med par thams cad du rang shar zhing chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:275: thams cad de bzhin nyid du sangs rgyas te /
NK117(she)001:276: kun la khyab pa'i slad du /
NK117(she)001:277: rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i dal du mthong lags so //
NK117(she)001:279: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dal ni /
NK117(she)001:280: thams cad sems su 'dus shing gnyis su med pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:281: thams cad rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dal du mthong lags so //
NK117(she)001:284: ye ci bzhin pa bcos bslad med par chos kyi skur sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:285: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa /
NK117(she)001:286: rtsol ba med par rang snang bas /
NK117(she)001:288: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dal gnyis su med
NK117(she)001:289: par longs spyod pas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur sangs
NK117(she)001:291: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK117(she)001:292: skye 'gag med pa'i snying po ste //
NK117(she)001:293: bya ba med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK117(she)001:294: ye nas grub zin lhun gyi grub //
NK117(she)001:296: de'ang gdul bya rnams la sna tshogs zhen bcas kyi rtog pa yod pas /
NK117(she)001:298: sems can thams cad dang ye ci bzhin pa'i dal du ngo sprad /
NK117(she)001:299: sangs rgyas bya ba bzang po gcig log na yod par 'dzin pa'i rtog pa yod pas /
NK117(she)001:301: sangs rgyas dang rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dal du ngo sprad /
NK117(she)001:302: sna tshogs gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa yod pas de dgrol ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:303: sems can dang rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dal du ngo sprod do //
NK117(she)001:305: a ti 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes che ba lngar sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK117(she)001:307: ma spangs mi gnas mi ltos rag ma lus //
NK117(she)001:308: tha snyad kun dang bral ba'i 'bras bu ste //
NK117(she)001:309: rang bzhin lhun grub 'dus ma byas pas na //
NK117(she)001:310: 'bras bu'i rgyal po khyad par dpag ste che //
NK117(she)001:312: chos kun sems nyid rang snang ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:313: de nyid spangs gar yang ma spangs mngon sum par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:314: skye bo mu stegs dang nyan thos rang rgyal las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:315: ltos ci la yang ma ltos te de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:316: dbu ma sems tsam dang kri yog sde gsum las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:317: rag gar yang ma lus bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:318: ma h+aa yo ga las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:319: gnas ci la yang mi gnas dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:320: a nu yo ga las grol zhing dpag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:321: thams cad nas thams cad du sangs rgyas pas sangs rgyas las med pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:322: a ti'i rgyud lung man ngag las rol zhing dpag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:324: che ba lnga'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:325: sems nyid che ba lngas 'phags te //
NK117(she)001:327: mngon par sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK117(she)001:328: 'dus ma byas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:329: snang srid thams cad khyar par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:330: rdzogs pa chen po'i che bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:332: de yin sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK117(she)001:333: ma nor ba yi byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:334: gtan tshigs kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:335: yo ga dag gi che bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:337: bdag nyid sangs rgya che ba ni //
NK117(she)001:338: lhun gyis grub pa'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:339: rtsol zhing bsgrub las khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:340: ma h+aa yo ga'i che bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:342: chos dbyings sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK117(she)001:343: thams cad 'byung ba'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:345: a nu yo ga'i che bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:347: thams cad sangs rgyas che ba ni //
NK117(she)001:348: sgro skur 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:349: bsam dpyod kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:350: la zlos pa yi che bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:353: sems nyid klong chen yangs pa ru //
NK117(she)001:355: che ba lnga ru mngon sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:357: de yang sngar ma grub pa gcig bsgrub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:358: ma yin pa gcig yin par byas pa ma yin te /
NK117(she)001:360: gnyis med bde chen lhun grub sangs rgyas te //
NK117(she)001:361: sngar 'das sangs rgyas sgam pos 'di ma mdzad //
NK117(she)001:362: slad kyi sems can sgrin pos 'di ma bsgyur //
NK117(she)001:363: ma mdzad mi bsgyur snying po'i don 'di la //
NK117(she)001:366: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:367: ye'am ngang gis sangs rgyas la //
NK117(she)001:368: min la yin par gyur ma yin //
NK117(she)001:370: man ngag rtsa ba bsdus pa'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:371: byang chub sems kyi ngo bo de /
NK117(she)001:372: rang bzhin gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK117(she)001:373: sangs rgyas sgam pos 'di ma mdzad //
NK117(she)001:374: sems can sgrin pos 'di ma bcos //
NK117(she)001:375: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:376: de yang ye ci bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK117(she)001:377: 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas dang /
NK117(she)001:378: rgyud dag pa rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:380: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas shing /
NK117(she)001:381: bcos bslad med par snying po byang chub tu gnas pa la bya ste /
NK117(she)001:383: rnam par kun ldan stong chen po //
NK117(she)001:384: sangs rgyas bas kyang sngar sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:387: chos rnams kyi chos nyid ma bcos ma bslad snying
NK117(she)001:388: po byang chub tu ye nas gnas pa de la
NK117(she)001:389: / ye ji bzhin pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes gdags so //
NK117(she)001:390: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:392: gzhi rang byung gi ston pa kun tu bzang po /
NK117(she)001:393: 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas yin te /
NK117(she)001:394: chos kun gdod nas rang byung gi ye shes su sangs rgyas pas /
NK117(she)001:395: de nyid 'khrul yang ma myong la lam bgrod kyang ma myong ste /
NK117(she)001:396: gnas lugs rang sa zin nas /
NK117(she)001:397: ye shes dang che ba'i yon tan thams cad gdod ma nas rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:398: de nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yang myes yin shing /
NK117(she)001:399: sangs rgyas thams cad de las byung bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:400: de yang lung man ngag rigs pa gsum gyis nges par bya ste /
NK117(she)001:403: rang byung ston pa 'od gsal thugs //
NK117(she)001:404: phyogs med rig pa'i nyi ma shar //
NK117(she)001:405: me shel 'od ltar byin rlabs 'khrig /'od gsal rig pa'i bstan pa sgrogs //
NK117(she)001:408: dang po'i sangs rgyas rgyu med pas //
NK117(she)001:409: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
NK117(she)001:411: nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:413: nga rtogs kun tu bzang po byung //
NK117(she)001:416: gang yang med pa'i sngon rol tu //
NK117(she)001:417: rang byung ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK117(she)001:418: lung las ma bstan man ngag chos //
NK117(she)001:419: rang gi rig pas rang rtogs phyir //
NK117(she)001:420: 'khrul ma myong la rtogs ma myong //
NK117(she)001:422: gzhi shes rang byung rig pa la //
NK117(she)001:423: gzhi gnas ma rig med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:424: rkyen gyis sngar 'khrul ma myong bas //
NK117(she)001:425: lung bstan gyis ni bstan mi dgos //
NK117(she)001:426: de phyir lung las ma byung chos //
NK117(she)001:427: ya mtshan rmad du byung ba'i bka' //
NK117(she)001:428: sangs rgyas thams cad de las bskyed //
NK117(she)001:430: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:431: sems can ma 'khrul sangs rgyas med pa'i gong //
NK117(she)001:432: ngo bo nyid kyi sku la rang byung sems //
NK117(she)001:433: de nyid ma 'khrul gnas lugs yin pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:434: de rtogs chos sku mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:435: kun tu bzang po ye shes rang byung thugs //
NK117(she)001:436: rang sems rang gis rig pas chos kyi rje //
NK117(she)001:439: sangs rgyas thog ma gcad pa'i man ngag las //
NK117(she)001:440: rang byung ngo bo kun gyi gzhi //
NK117(she)001:442: ye nas ye shes rnam drug gis //
NK117(she)001:443: gzhi gnas ma rig med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:444: rkyen gyis sngar 'khrul med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:445: lung bstan gyis ni bstan ma dgos //
NK117(she)001:446: lung las ma bstan chos de yis //
NK117(she)001:447: sangs rgyas kun gyi chos skur shes //
NK117(she)001:448: de la kun tu bzang por bya //
NK117(she)001:451: rang byung ston pa kun bzang rgyal ba'i yab //
NK117(she)001:452: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:454: 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas med na gzhi 'khor ba'i mtha' thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:455: dang po ston mkhan gyi sangs rgyas med pas /
NK117(she)001:456: rtogs pa'i thabs lam med pa la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:458: de ltar 'khrul ma myong gi sangs rgyas yod pas /
NK117(she)001:459: des dang po ngo ma shes pa'i 'khrul pa rnams la /
NK117(she)001:460: grol ba'i thabs lam rgya cher bstan nas /
NK117(she)001:461: rtogs shing grol ba rnams ni /
NK117(she)001:464: zhal nas nges par brgyud pa yi //
NK117(she)001:465: man ngag snying po 'di rtogs nas //
NK117(she)001:466: rtogs pa mngon gyur sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:469: ye nas yin pa'i don de rab rtogs nas //
NK117(she)001:470: rtogs pa brtan pa de la 'bras bur gdags //
NK117(she)001:473: gzung 'dzin bag chags ma lus kun sangs nas //
NK117(she)001:474: ye shes mkha' la nyi shar bzhin du rgyas //
NK117(she)001:475: sangs rgyas zhes kyang de la btags pa yin //
NK117(she)001:478: sems can rnams kyi chos nyid gang mthong ba'i gnas skabs la ni /
NK117(she)001:479: rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' zhes gdags so //
NK117(she)001:481: ngo sprod cing the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba ni /
NK117(she)001:482: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de /
NK117(she)001:485: rigs pa gsum gyis ngo sprad cing bsgrub ste /
NK117(she)001:488: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki //
NK117(she)001:489: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK117(she)001:490: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK117(she)001:491: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK117(she)001:494: bcing med rnam par grol med pas //
NK117(she)001:495: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK117(she)001:498: thams cad de bzhin nyid dbyings su //
NK117(she)001:499: ye nas rnam rtog med sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:500: gdod sangs rgyas ru ga la yod //
NK117(she)001:503: 'gro kun ye nas sangs rgyas nyid //
NK117(she)001:504: nyon mongs ye nas ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:505: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:506: dug gsum sku gsum gtan sprug pas //
NK117(she)001:509: dmyal ba'i tsha grang sdug bsngal yang //
NK117(she)001:510: chos nyid rang gi klong na 'byams //
NK117(she)001:511: rang las tha dad med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:512: sku gsum klong na ye sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:513: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:515: srid gsum lam lnga'i chos lnga yang //
NK117(she)001:516: byang chub sems su mngon sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:520: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK117(she)001:521: de min lta ba bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:524: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK117(she)001:525: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:528: mtha' yas 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:529: rgyal ba'i ye shes rang chas ldan //
NK117(she)001:530: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:532: lung man ngag gi rjes su 'jug cing /
NK117(she)001:533: lung man ngag dang mthun par bsgrubs te /
NK117(she)001:534: rigs pa spyi'i go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:537: shes bya ma shes pa shes par byed pa /
NK117(she)001:538: shes bya bden pa dang 'brel pa gcig yin gsungs /
NK117(she)001:541: shes bya ma shes pa shes par byed pa la yang 'dod /
NK117(she)001:543: 'khrul ba'i gnyen po tshad mar gyur phyir rigs //
NK117(she)001:546: bden pa'i tshad mas don gyi mtshan nyid rtogs par byed pa gcig la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:558: snang grags byang chub sems su lhun grub pas //
NK117(she)001:559: rigs pa bzhi yis sgro skur the tshom bsal /
NK117(she)001:560: bsregs bcad bdar bas sa gser nges rtogs ltar /
NK117(she)001:561: chos nyid bya byed ltos pa de 'thad bsgrubs //
NK117(she)001:563: chos nyid kyi rigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:567: dang po la go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:568: bye brag phye ste bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:570: nyid kyi rang bzhin nyid las mi 'gyur zhing 'da' ba'o //
NK117(she)001:572: nam mkha' sa chu me dang rlung //
NK117(she)001:573: rang rang don las mi 'da' zhing //
NK117(she)001:574: snang grags chos rnams ma lus pa //
NK117(she)001:575: bde chen ngang las 'da' mi srid //
NK117(she)001:578: rang gi rang bzhin mi 'gyur spros pa gcod //
NK117(she)001:581: gzhi rtsa gcig pa'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:582: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:583: rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:586: mthar thug chos nyid kyi rigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:587: gnas skabs chos nyid kyi rigs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:589: chos kun ci ltar snang yang chos nyid rang snang bas /
NK117(she)001:590: de nyid ma bcos ma bslad snying po byang chub tu ye nas sangs rgyas shing /
NK117(she)001:591: cir snang yang chos nyid las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK117(she)001:593: chos kun rang rig rang snang bas //
NK117(she)001:594: spang bya med cing gnyen po med //
NK117(she)001:595: nyid las gzhan pa'i chos med pas //
NK117(she)001:596: ngan song gnas kyang skye med rang //
NK117(she)001:597: snang srid snod bcud chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:602: gang du yang ma bcos pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:605: 'dre ldog spyi tsug gar gyur kyang //
NK117(she)001:606: snying po'i don las mi 'da' bas //
NK117(she)001:609: thams cad thams cad ji snyed pa //
NK117(she)001:610: tshig gi tha snyad tsam dag las //
NK117(she)001:611: 'di la bya ba ci yang med //
NK117(she)001:612: rang bzhin nyid de ye sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:615: phyi nang gi chos kun mtshan nyid gang ma 'dres par gsal zhing 'dzin pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:617: gnas skabs chos nyid 'khrul snang rang mtshan nyid /
NK117(she)001:618: sa sra chu gsher me tsha rlung yang g.yo //
NK117(she)001:619: zhe sdang kun nas mnar sems la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:620: kun nas ma 'dres ye nas so sor shar //
NK117(she)001:622: bya ba byed pa'i rigs pa yang /
NK117(she)001:624: bye brag phye ste bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:626: don byed nus shing de'i bya ba byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:628: mes btso bsreg gi bya ba byed pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:629: rgyu rkyen 'dzom nas gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu bskyed pa'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:630: blo dang chos su 'dzom nas rang rang gi 'bras
NK117(she)001:631: bu mngon du thob par byed pa la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:632: / gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi bya ba byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:634: gnas skabs bya byed rgyu rkyen de 'tshogs pas //
NK117(she)001:635: 'bras bu tha dad mngon par bsgrub pa'ang rigs //
NK117(she)001:637: ltos pa'i rigs pa la yang gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:639: chos gang zhig gang la ltos te btags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:644: theg pa mtho dman la sogs pa gnas skabs dang /
NK117(she)001:645: mthar thug la sogs pa thams cad gcig la gcig ltos te brtags pa shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:647: gnas skabs mthar thug rgyu 'bras la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:648: gcig la gcig ltos ltos nas brtags pa yin //
NK117(she)001:650: 'thad pa bsgrub pa'i rigs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:652: de yi 'thad pa bsgrub pa sgra tshad chos //
NK117(she)001:654: sgras mtshon te rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:655: don gyis tshad mas gtan la dbab ste rtogs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:657: de yang don la dmigs shing sgra las byung //
NK117(she)001:658: mthun par snang la thun mong du grags shing //
NK117(she)001:659: mngon par zhen nas de yis de 'thad 'grub //
NK117(she)001:665: de'i don la mngon par zhen pa gcig dgos /
NK117(she)001:666: de'ang don la ma dmigs na don gyi dmigs mi shes pas don la dmigs pa gcig dgos /
NK117(she)001:667: sgra las ma byung na don mi mtshon pas /
NK117(she)001:668: sgra las byung ba gcig dgos /
NK117(she)001:669: snang tshul mi mthun na gtan la dbab tu mi btub pas /
NK117(she)001:670: mthun par snang ba gcig dgos /
NK117(she)001:671: thun mong du grags pa gcig med na ci la zer cha med cing /
NK117(she)001:673: thun mong du grags pa gcig dgos /
NK117(she)001:674: mngon par ma zhen na don mthar mi phyin pas /
NK117(she)001:675: don la 'dris shing zhen pa gcig dgos /
NK117(she)001:676: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi don gang mtshon kyang /
NK117(she)001:677: bzhi po des mtshon zhing rtogs par bya ste /
NK117(she)001:678: rang rang gi skabs dang sbyar te rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:679: don gyi tshad mas gtan la dbab pa la yang /
NK117(she)001:681: bye brag phye ste bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:683: rtags la brten nas don gyi mtshan nyid bsgrub pa'am /
NK117(she)001:686: tshad ma mngon sum rjes su dpag pas kyang /
NK117(she)001:687: rang mtshan spyi yi rnam pa de 'thad bsgrub //
NK117(she)001:689: mngon sum gyi rtags la brten nas don rang gi mtshan nyid rtogs par byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:690: rjes dpag gi rtags la brten nas don spyi'i mtshan nyid bsgrub par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:692: mngon sum spyi'i go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:693: bye brag phye ste don rang gi mtshan nyid rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:695: mtshan nyid pa'i lugs kyis gzung yul la ma 'khrul ba'am /
NK117(she)001:696: rtog bral ma 'khrul ba la 'dod de /
NK117(she)001:697: de'i don kyang go ba blang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:699: gsal ba mthar thug pa la mdzad gsung ngo //
NK117(she)001:701: snang la mi rtog don la ma 'khrul bar //
NK117(she)001:704: snang la ma 'khrul ba la bya ste /
NK117(she)001:705: de gnyis kyi go ba yang shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:707: thun mong spyi'i mngon sum dang /
NK117(she)001:708: khyad par gsang sngags mngon sum gyi tshad mas chos
NK117(she)001:709: kun ye nas sangs rgyas pa de rtogs par byed
NK117(she)001:712: rang rig rnal 'byor bzhi ste bgrang /
NK117(she)001:713: de la dbang po'i mngon sum ni /
NK117(she)001:714: 'jig rten grags tshod kyi dbang po skyon med kyi ngo la snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:716: yid kyi yul du snang zhing grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:717: rang rig pa'i mngon sum ni /
NK117(she)001:718: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rtogs shing gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:720: stong zhing bdag med kyi don nyams su myong ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:721: lam pas rang gi grub matha'i don nyams su myong
NK117(she)001:722: zhing chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid shes pa'o
NK117(she)001:723: // slob dpon klu sgrub kyi dbu ma las /
NK117(she)001:724: gnod pa med pa'i dbang po drug rnams kyis //
NK117(she)001:725: gzung ba gang zhig 'jig rten gyis rtogs te //
NK117(she)001:726: 'jig rten nyid la bden yin lhag ma ni //
NK117(she)001:727: 'jig rten nyid las log par rnam par bzhag /
NK117(she)001:730: gsang sngags mngon sum gyi tshad mas rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:731: rjes dpag gis gsang don mngon sum du mi rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:735: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:736: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK117(she)001:739: rig pa mchog ldan bde gshegs bka' //
NK117(she)001:740: rang byung tshad mas mngon sum gsal //
NK117(she)001:744: thog bab car phog shugs 'byung dang //
NK117(she)001:745: klong rdol rang shar rang lugs kyis //
NK117(she)001:746: 'gro drug grong khyer gtan nas bcom //
NK117(she)001:748: rang rig pa'i tshad mas mngon sum du ngo sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:749: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste mngon sum du rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:751: mngon sum bzhi la sogs pas dngos su ngo sprod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:752: de la dbang po'i mngon sum gyis sgo lnga gnyis med rang gsal rig pa gcer mthong du dang /
NK117(she)001:753: yid kyi mngon sum gyis 'gyu byed mtshan ma rang grol du dang /
NK117(she)001:754: rang rig pa'i mngon sum gyis phyi nang gnyis med rig pa rang snang du dang /
NK117(she)001:755: rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum gyis chos kun ma 'dres
NK117(she)001:756: yongs rdzogs mnyam nyid rang grol du ngo sprad pa'o
NK117(she)001:757: // de nyid 'gags med sprul pa'i sku dang /
NK117(she)001:758: skye med chos kyi sku dang /
NK117(she)001:759: gnyis med longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK117(she)001:760: sku lnga lhun grub tu ngo sprad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:763: dbang po cer mthong chos nyid gsal //
NK117(she)001:764: snang ba rgya yan rig pa'i klong //
NK117(she)001:766: ma 'gags thugs rje'i sprul pa ni //
NK117(she)001:767: nges med sku ste cir yang snang //
NK117(she)001:770: rang shar rang grol chos nyid kyis //
NK117(she)001:771: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK117(she)001:774: skye med chos kyi dbyings na gsal //
NK117(she)001:777: ye shes rang shar chos nyid klong //
NK117(she)001:778: ma bsgribs phyi nang med par gsal //
NK117(she)001:780: nyid kyi rol pa longs spyod rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:781: longs spyod rdzogs sku nyid kyis bstan //
NK117(she)001:784: nyon mongs ye shes dbyer mi phyed //
NK117(she)001:785: ma shes pa la khams gsum ste //
NK117(she)001:786: de shes pa la sku gsum klong //
NK117(she)001:787: ye nas yin pas btsal mi dgos //
NK117(she)001:789: sku gsum rgyun chad med pa yis //
NK117(she)001:790: mtha' yi zhen pa rang sar grol //
NK117(she)001:793: rang byung ye shes nam mkha' che //
NK117(she)001:794: thams cad de ru 'dus pas na //
NK117(she)001:795: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs theg pa'i rgyan //
NK117(she)001:796: snang ba sna tshogs cir shar yang //
NK117(she)001:797: sku lnga'i klong las g.yos pa med //
NK117(she)001:799: de rnams rang rang gi rgyud lung man ngag dang ngo sprod pa ni /
NK117(she)001:800: bla ma'i zhal gyi gdams pa las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:801: gzhan yang nyon mongs ye shes su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:803: sems can sangs rgyas su ngo sprad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:805: ye shes pas kyang nyon mongs gtso //
NK117(she)001:806: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i zhags pa yis //
NK117(she)001:807: rang byung ye shes gtan la 'bebs //
NK117(she)001:808: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:809: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:810: bde chen bas kyang sdug bsngal gtso //
NK117(she)001:811: sdug bsngal zhen chags mtshan ma yis //
NK117(she)001:812: chags med bde chen gtan la 'bebs //
NK117(she)001:813: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:814: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:815: sems can dngos por snang ba yis //
NK117(she)001:816: dngos med sangs rgyas gtan la 'bebs //
NK117(she)001:817: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:818: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:820: de la sogs te snang ba sku'i dkyil 'khor /
NK117(she)001:822: dran rig thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du ngo sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:823: bden pa gsum sku gsum du dang /
NK117(she)001:825: che ba lngar sangs rgyas pa la sogs pas gang
NK117(she)001:826: zag las dang skal par ldan pa dbang po mchog
NK117(she)001:828: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mngon sum du ngo sprad pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:830: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK117(she)001:831: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:832: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK117(she)001:833: gzhan du sangs rgyas ma tshol cig /
NK117(she)001:836: kun 'dus gsang ba'i dgongs spyod zab mo ni //
NK117(she)001:837: rang byung rang rig mngon sum snang dus na //
NK117(she)001:838: rang byung ye shes de nyid mthong zhes bya //
NK117(she)001:841: ci ltar snang ba de bzhin nyid du gcig /'di la su yang 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK117(she)001:842: ma bcos mnyam pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK117(she)001:843: mi rtog chos sku'i dgongs pa de la gnas //
NK117(she)001:845: kun bzang rig pa rtsal shar ba'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:846: ma lus chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK117(she)001:847: shes pa chos sku rang gsal bas //
NK117(she)001:848: kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa las //
NK117(she)001:849: gar yang ma g.yos chos nyid yin //
NK117(she)001:852: snang zhing grags pa'i chos rnams dang //
NK117(she)001:853: mthong thos sgo lngar ci shar yang //
NK117(she)001:854: rang zhal rang gis mthong bas na //
NK117(she)001:855: gnyis su lta ba'i yul gzhan med //
NK117(she)001:856: gnyis su med do mnyam pa che //
NK117(she)001:857: yul sems mnyam pa'i klong du grol //
NK117(she)001:861: mchog gi rang rig mngon sum du //
NK117(she)001:862: rang gsal grol thob gnyis las 'das //
NK117(she)001:865: don nyid spros bral mngon sum las //
NK117(she)001:866: ma mthong cha gzhan yul med pas //
NK117(she)001:867: rtags la brten nas dbab tu med //
NK117(she)001:870: de bas gser lta gser bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:871: bdag phyir bya byed mi dmigs pas //
NK117(she)001:872: rtog dpyod gnyis 'dzin mi tshor bar //
NK117(she)001:873: de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mthong //
NK117(she)001:875: gtan tshigs kyis dngos su rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK117(she)001:876: rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:877: de ltar lung man ngag mngon sum gyi tshad ma
NK117(she)001:878: dang gtan tshigs kyis chos kun khong du chud cing
NK117(she)001:879: rang sems sangs rgyas su rtogs pas 'gyur med don
NK117(she)001:880: dang ldan zhing / lung rigs kyis log rtog rtsad nas gcod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:882: rang byung ye shes gcig tu gnas pa la //
NK117(she)001:883: rtogs pa'i ye shes gcig tu rtogs nas ni //
NK117(she)001:884: gnyis med gnad du chud pas sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:887: rang sems tshad ma'i gdengs ldan pas //
NK117(she)001:888: mi 'gyur don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK117(she)001:889: lung rig don gyi bya ra bas //
NK117(she)001:890: leg rtogs rkun po rdul du brlag /
NK117(she)001:892: de bzhin du chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK117(she)001:893: rang byung ye shes mngon sum du rtogs shing thag chod pa ni lus dman par gnas kyang /
NK117(she)001:894: sems dgongs pa sangs rgyas yin te /
NK117(she)001:896: de nyid de la zhen nges blo brtan zhing //
NK117(she)001:897: gang yang 'brel ba lta ba thag chod na //
NK117(she)001:898: dman pa'i lus la dam pa'i go 'phang can //
NK117(she)001:899: dbang phyug chen po yin pas de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK117(she)001:902: rnal 'byor dman pa las can gyis //
NK117(she)001:903: yid kyi don rtogs ngo shes pas //
NK117(she)001:904: kun bzang chos sku da lta nga //
NK117(she)001:905: dman pa'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:908: rang byung ye shes spros dang bral bas sangs //
NK117(she)001:909: spros bral rtogs pa gdeng du gyur pas rgyas //
NK117(she)001:910: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud lung man ngag du ma las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:911: de ltar chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas shing /
NK117(she)001:912: gsang sngags mngon sum gyi lam pa yin par lung man ngag du ma las gsungs shing 'grub bo //
NK117(she)001:913: rjes dpag gis mi rtogs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:914: chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas shing cir snang 'dus
NK117(she)001:915: ma byas kyi ye shes mngon sum du gsal ba
NK117(she)001:916: la / rjes dpag gi tshad mas mi rtogs shing de nyid log rtog yin par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:918: dape'am tshad ma gtan tshigs sam //
NK117(she)001:919: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK117(she)001:920: rtogs par nus pa ma yin te //
NK117(she)001:924: rig pa rang gsal mngon sum la //
NK117(she)001:925: rjes dpag tshad mas rdzun gyis bslus //
NK117(she)001:929: tshad mas gzhal du med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:930: dpag dka' gting ring sgo yangs pas //
NK117(she)001:931: 'khrul pa rtog ge'i spyod yul min //
NK117(she)001:933: gzhal bya 'jal byed tshig gi mtha' //
NK117(she)001:934: dmigs pa'i yul la rtog dpyod byed //
NK117(she)001:935: yid dpyod shes pa'i don du 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:936: bskal pa bye ba brgyar bgrangs kyang //
NK117(she)001:940: thams cad ci bzhin pa yi chos yin pas //
NK117(she)001:941: ji bzhin pa la 'chos par byed pa ni //
NK117(she)001:942: rdzun gyis bden pa bslus pa sdig re che //
NK117(she)001:945: 'jal bya'i yul la bdag gis ni //
NK117(she)001:947: yin min 'du shes nyon mongs skye //
NK117(she)001:948: skyon yon gnyis kyi 'du shes kyis //
NK117(she)001:950: de nyid 'khor ba'i rgyu yin mod //
NK117(she)001:952: snying po don gyi rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:953: kye 'dus pa chen po'i rnal 'byor la //
NK117(she)001:954: rang sems rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin gsal //
NK117(she)001:955: sgra dang tshad ma gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:956: brjod bral gtan la phebs pa med //
NK117(she)001:957: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud lung du ma las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:958: de ltar rtogs pa'i skal ba dang mi ldan zhing
NK117(she)001:959: blo chung ba rnams kyi log rtog bsal ba'i phyir
NK117(she)001:960: / rjes dpag gi tshad mas don spyi'i mtshan nyid bsgrub pa ni /
NK117(she)001:961: thun mong gi rjes dpag dang /
NK117(she)001:962: thun mong ma yin pa'i rjes dpag gis chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas pa de bsgrub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:963: snga ma ni dper na me chos can me yod de dam bca'/
NK117(she)001:964: gtan tshigs du ba 'dug pa'i phyir zhes pa lta bu la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:965: don ni rtog ge dang dbu ma'i gtan tshigs bzhi
NK117(she)001:966: la sogs pa theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyi
NK117(she)001:967: rang rang gi grub matha'i don gtan la 'bebs pa'i
NK117(she)001:968: rjes dpag gi gtan tshigs rnams yin te rang rang
NK117(she)001:969: gi gzhung bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:970: de rnams kyang don la ltos na kun brtags yin te /
NK117(she)001:972: gtan tshigs bzhi sogs rim bkod pas //
NK117(she)001:973: dngos de nyid shes kun smra yang //
NK117(she)001:974: rtsol bral byar med don rigs na //
NK117(she)001:975: rjes dpag ltos brtags kho nar snang //
NK117(she)001:977: thun min gyi rjes dpag gis chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas par bsgrub pa ni /
NK117(she)001:978: sems can rnams lam sa gang yang rung ba gcig gi sems rgyud chos can /
NK117(she)001:979: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:980: gang gis rtogs pa mngon du sangs rgyas pa yin pa'i phyir zhes pa /
NK117(she)001:981: phyir gyi gtan tshigs ma grub ce na /
NK117(she)001:982: ye nas sangs rgyas pa min /
NK117(she)001:983: rtogs pas kyang sangs mi rgyas /
NK117(she)001:984: sangs rgyas gtan mi 'byung bar thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:987: sems rtogs na ye shes yin pas sangs rgyas gzhan
NK117(she)001:988: nas mi btsal ba'i 'du shes rab tu bsgom par
NK117(she)001:991: shes rab kyis ni chos kyi rang bzhin yongs shes nas //
NK117(she)001:992: khams gsum ma lus pa las yang dag 'da' bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:995: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes sku //
NK117(she)001:996: rang byung ye shes rtogs las 'byung //
NK117(she)001:1000: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK117(she)001:1001: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK117(she)001:1002: sems nyid rtogs pa sangs rgyas te //
NK117(she)001:1003: de las gzhan du yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:1006: ye nas sangs rgyas ma yin pa ci sto ste /
NK117(she)001:1007: khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK117(she)001:1008: ye nas sangs rgyas min pa la yin par rtogs na /
NK117(she)001:1010: log shes su thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1011: yang rtogs pas sangs rgya ba yin pa'i phyir gyi gtan tshig ma grub ste /
NK117(she)001:1012: sangs rgyas rgyu rkyen las byung ngo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1013: rgyu rkyen las byung na sangs rgyas 'dus byas su thal lo //
NK117(she)001:1015: sangs rgyas kyang mi rtag par 'jig par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:1016: rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed kyang 'dus ma byas yin no ce na /
NK117(she)001:1017: rang gi tshig gis gsal la shin tu yang 'gal te /
NK117(she)001:1018: nga'i a ma mo gsham yin zer ba lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:1019: yang gzugs sku rnam gnyis gnas skabs gdul bya'i ngor snang 'dus byas yin la /
NK117(she)001:1020: sangs rgyas zhes ni mthar thug chos sku la bya /
NK117(she)001:1022: mthar thug ni ngo bo nyid kyi sku'am /
NK117(she)001:1023: chos sku dag pa gnyis kyi bdag nyid 'dus ma byas yin zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1024: gzugs sku gnyis 'dus byas gnas skabs yin na /
NK117(she)001:1025: mi rtag skye 'jig 'khor ba'i mtha' las ma 'das shing /
NK117(she)001:1026: mthar thug gi sangs rgyas ma yin par thal /
NK117(she)001:1028: gnas skabs gdul bya'i ngor snang yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1030: mdo rgyud gsung pa'ang dri ma can du thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1031: ngo bo nyid kyi sku dang chos sku gnad gcig par shes par bya ste /
NK117(she)001:1032: mthar thug chos sku rgyu rkyen las ma byung bar thal /
NK117(she)001:1033: 'dod na sangs rgyas rgyu rkyen las byung ba nyams so //
NK117(she)001:1035: chos sku 'dus ma byas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1036: rgyu rkyen las byung yang 'dus byas te /
NK117(she)001:1037: de 'dus ma byas yin par thal de gong gi skyon las ma 'das so //
NK117(she)001:1039: dang po rgyu rkyen las byung yang /
NK117(she)001:1040: chos sku thob tsam na rgyu rkyen las grol bas /
NK117(she)001:1041: 'dus ma byas ma yin no zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1042: bum pa lta bu yang dang po rgyu rkyen las byung yang /
NK117(she)001:1043: phyis rgyu rkyen las grol bas /
NK117(she)001:1044: 'dus ma byas su thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1045: bum pa dngos po yin la /
NK117(she)001:1046: chos sku dngos po las grol bas 'dus ma byas yin no zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1047: dngos med yin na rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed par thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1051: dang po nas dngos med yin na rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed par thal /
NK117(she)001:1052: phyis yin na rkyen gyis bshig pa la sogs pa'i skyon du ma 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1053: 'o na rgyu lam du byed pa nor ram zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1054: dgos ched dang dgongs gzhi drang don du gsung pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1055: dgos ched phyin ci log gi gdul bya rim gyis yang dag pa'i don la zhugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1057: ma rtogs sdug bsngal zhing dngos por zhen pa'i sems rgyud la /
NK117(she)001:1058: rtogs pas sdug bsngal las grol zhing /
NK117(she)001:1059: rang la yod pa'i yon tan mngon du 'char ba la 'bras bur dgongs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1060: des na rgyu lam du byed pa'ang drang don du zad cing /
NK117(she)001:1061: gang la gang 'dul du gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1063: rgyu rkyen 'bras bur brtags pa yang //
NK117(she)001:1064: bkri drang don gyis bstan pa zad //
NK117(she)001:1066: 'o na gsang sngags pa'i lugs kyis /
NK117(she)001:1067: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin na /
NK117(she)001:1069: sangs rgyas yin pa la skyon brjod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1070: 'bras bu lam du byed pa la skyon brjod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1072: snang ba 'di sangs rgyas yin na /
NK117(she)001:1073: sangs rgyas 'dus byas su thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1076: skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal dang bcas par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1078: 'dus byas dang skye 'jig la sogs pa'i snang ba ma 'gag par thal zer ram /
NK117(she)001:1081: ngo bo skye 'gag med par rang snang bas so //
NK117(she)001:1082: phyi ma ltar na gtan tshigs ma grub bo //
NK117(she)001:1083: mngon sum gyis gsal lo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1085: yang sangs rgyas ni gong ltar gsum las /
NK117(she)001:1086: sems can rnams ni ye ji bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK117(she)001:1087: gshis yin tshul nas thal zer ram /
NK117(she)001:1088: 'khrul pa'i snang ngo la 'dug pa'i phyir zer /
NK117(she)001:1089: snga ma ltar na gtan tshigs ma grub bo //
NK117(she)001:1090: mngon sum gyis gsal lo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1091: mngon sum 'khrul lam ma 'khrul gyi brtag pa bya'o //
NK117(she)001:1092: phyi ma ltar na 'khrul snang la skye 'jig la sogs pa 'dug bkas /
NK117(she)001:1093: gshis la med pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1097: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK117(she)001:1098: yin phyiir ngo bo tha dad med //
NK117(she)001:1100: yang yul snang sangs rgyas yin na /
NK117(she)001:1101: lam dgos med du thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1102: yin kyang dgos na lam thug med du thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1103: lan 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin gdab bo //
NK117(she)001:1106: smin pa lam du byed dam /
NK117(she)001:1107: ma smin pa lam du byed /
NK117(she)001:1108: snga ma ltar na lam la thug pa med pa'i skyon 'ong la /
NK117(she)001:1109: phyi ma ltar na 'bras bu'i nges tshigs med do zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1110: ngo bo smin cing bgrong du med pas smin pa lam du byed de /
NK117(she)001:1111: de ma rtog pa rtogs par byed pa'i tshul gyis lam du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1113: rtogs nas 'dres par gang byed pa //
NK117(she)001:1114: lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:1116: de ltar na 'bras bu smin kyang lam dgos na /
NK117(she)001:1117: thug pa med par thal lo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1118: ngo bo thug med du thal zer ram /
NK117(she)001:1119: rtogs byed lam thug med du thal zer /
NK117(she)001:1122: mtha' la thug pa med cing dbyings la bri ba med //
NK117(she)001:1124: phyi ma ltar na he ru ma grub ste /
NK117(she)001:1125: rtogs byed lam mthar phyin pas de nyid kyis phyis lam dang rtogs par mi dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1127: 'bras bu'i ma sangs rgyas yin na /
NK117(she)001:1128: lam dgos pa med par thal lo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1129: yin pa'i ngos nas thal zer ram /
NK117(she)001:1130: ma rtog pa rtogs par byed pa la dgos med du thal zer /
NK117(she)001:1133: phyi dang nang dang chos kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:1134: rnam par dag pa'i spyod yul la //
NK117(she)001:1135: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK117(she)001:1136: lam gyis bcos su ga la yod //
NK117(she)001:1138: phyi ma ltar na phyir gyi gtan tshig ma grub ste /
NK117(she)001:1139: yin don ma rtog pa rtogs par byed pas dgos pa shin tu che'o //
NK117(she)001:1140: de skad du byas pa la /
NK117(she)001:1141: yin pa rang gis chog la /
NK117(she)001:1142: yin kyang dgos na lam thug med dang dgos pa med do //
NK117(she)001:1144: shin tu yang mi rigs te /
NK117(she)001:1145: yin pa rang gis chog na /
NK117(she)001:1146: ma rtog pa dang log shes gtan mi 'byung bar thal ba'i skyon dang /
NK117(she)001:1147: yang kho rang gi lugs kyis kyang /
NK117(she)001:1150: spros bral la sogs pa gang 'dod kyang /
NK117(she)001:1151: de nyid kyang yin pas chog la rtogs mi dgos par thal ba'i skyon 'ong bas 'agre'o //
NK117(she)001:1152: yang 'bras bu mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lam du byed dam mi ldan pa lam du byed /
NK117(she)001:1153: phyi ma ltar na nges tshig med la /
NK117(she)001:1154: snga ma ltar na 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid smin cing bgrod du med pa yin pa la /
NK117(she)001:1155: lam 'jug cing bgrod pa yin pas lam du byed pa 'gal zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1157: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu yang //
NK117(she)001:1158: mi rigs rigs par bshad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:1161: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu yin //
NK117(she)001:1163: rgyu yis bskyed pa'i 'bras bu min la /
NK117(she)001:1164: sems kyi ngo bo ye nas smin cing /
NK117(she)001:1165: sems las gzhan du bgrod du med pas /
NK117(she)001:1166: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lam du byed de /
NK117(she)001:1167: skyon sel ni gong bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:1169: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK117(she)001:1170: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK117(she)001:1171: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK117(she)001:1172: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK117(she)001:1174: de ltar ma shes te 'bras bu rang thad du bzung ba la /
NK117(she)001:1175: a tis skyon brjod pa ni /
NK117(she)001:1176: sems 'bras bu yin na rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed par thal ba'i skyon 'ong la /
NK117(she)001:1177: ma bskyed na 'bras bu'i nges tshig med do //
NK117(she)001:1178: des na chos kun 'dus ma byas la rgyu 'bras gnyis su lta bas don mthar mi phyin te /
NK117(she)001:1180: rgyu 'bras gnyis su gang lta ba //
NK117(she)001:1181: 'dus ma byas la rgyab kyis phyogs //
NK117(she)001:1182: yang dag don la sgro skur btab //
NK117(she)001:1185: rgyu 'bras dbyer med de nyid de //
NK117(she)001:1186: mi g.yo mi rtog yul 'das la //
NK117(she)001:1188: thams cad sgyu ma 'khrul pas bcing //
NK117(she)001:1191: rang byung rgyu 'bras 'das pa ma rtogs par //
NK117(she)001:1192: 'jig rten mtshan ma'i chos la tshod bcug nas //
NK117(she)001:1193: rgyu las btsal bas 'bras bu 'byung zer ba //
NK117(she)001:1194: de ni rgyu 'bras theg pa drang lung yin //
NK117(she)001:1196: des na 'bras bu lam du byed pa'ang /
NK117(she)001:1197: dgos ched dgongs gzhi drang don du gsungs pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1198: dgos ched rang la yod pa la /
NK117(she)001:1199: 'bras bu gzhan nas tshol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1200: dus nam zhig na thob par 'dod pa'i gol sa bcad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1201: dgongs gzhi sems nyid 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes
NK117(she)001:1202: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de smin cing bgrod par
NK117(she)001:1203: byar med pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1204: des na 'bras bu lam du byed pa yang drang don yin zhing shin tu zab bo //
NK117(she)001:1205: ye nas sangs rgyas shing 'dus ma byas kyi ye
NK117(she)001:1206: shes rang chas su yod pas skyon de dag las
NK117(she)001:1210: gcig pa'i don la snga phyi med //
NK117(she)001:1212: gnyis med don la sgrib pa med //
NK117(she)001:1215: rgyu 'bras rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK117(she)001:1216: rgyu med ye nas chos nyid klong //
NK117(she)001:1217: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:1220: kun bzang rig pa rtsal gyi rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:1221: phyogs med lhun grub 'bras bu ni //
NK117(she)001:1222: rang byung ye shes nyid la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:1225: sems nyid rang byung ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:1226: ye nas btsal zhing bsgrub med pas //
NK117(she)001:1227: rtsol bsgrub gnyis kyi spros dang bral //
NK117(she)001:1228: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'bras bu yin //
NK117(she)001:1230: de yang hril gyis dril na /
NK117(she)001:1232: rkyen la mi ltos pa'i grogs can /
NK117(she)001:1233: bde ba la 'bad pa med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1235: chos kun 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes ye nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1237: lung man ngag rigs pas dngos su ngo sprad cing rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1239: 'khor ba rang grol rtsol med bde ba chen por rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1240: de ltar chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas kyang /
NK117(she)001:1242: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de 'khrul par 'char bar mi rig pa la /
NK117(she)001:1246: gong ltar chos kun ye nas sangs rgyas shing /
NK117(she)001:1247: rig pa rten med yul med de 'khor bar 'khyams pa mi rigs so zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1248: chos nyid gang gi yang phyogs su ma lhung ba la /
NK117(she)001:1249: phyogs med cing cir yang 'char bas /
NK117(she)001:1250: 'khrul pa yang 'char ba shes bya'i bab yin te /
NK117(she)001:1252: chos rnams thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK117(she)001:1253: rig pa yul med rten med de //
NK117(she)001:1255: srid par 'byung ba shes bya'i bab //
NK117(she)001:1257: thig le gcig la grwa zur med //
NK117(she)001:1258: brdal ba chen po'i chos nyid de //
NK117(she)001:1259: gnyis su snang bar mi srid de //
NK117(she)001:1260: srid par 'byung ba shes bya'i bab //
NK117(she)001:1262: rang byung ye shes rgyu rkyen med //
NK117(she)001:1263: dug lngar 'char ba mi srid de //
NK117(she)001:1264: srid pa'i bab kyis dug lngar shar //
NK117(she)001:1268: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang gi rang ngo ma shes /
NK117(she)001:1269: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas bdag tu bzung zhing gzhan du mthong /
NK117(she)001:1271: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK117(she)001:1272: gshis chos nyid stong pa yin pa la /
NK117(she)001:1273: stong pa de yul du byar med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1274: yin no ba'i ston mkhan med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1275: sred pa la phyin ci log tu bltas pa dang bzhis ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1276: kun tu brtags pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK117(she)001:1277: chos nyid kyi lugs kyis gsal /
NK117(she)001:1278: gsal ba'i lugs kyis bye brag phye /
NK117(she)001:1279: bye phrag phyed pas nyams su myong /
NK117(she)001:1280: nyams myong gi rjes su 'brang pa la nyon mongs pa cha phra ba lnga byung /
NK117(she)001:1281: nyon mongs pa lnga'i babs sam /
NK117(she)001:1282: rig pa nyid 'od kha dog lngar snang bas /
NK117(she)001:1283: snang ba thams cad 'od lngar ma 'dres par snang ba la /
NK117(she)001:1285: yin rgyu'am 'dug rgyu'i dngos po ni ma rnyed /
NK117(she)001:1286: shes pa klong nge gnas pas /
NK117(she)001:1287: klong gi 'jig rten gyi khams bya ba shin tu tshan che bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1288: de'i dus su snang ba thams cad 'od du yod pas /
NK117(she)001:1290: dang po'i sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:1292: de'i dus su rkyen bzhis yar grol nas 'gro ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1293: mar 'khrul nas 'gro bar yang 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:1295: rgyu'i rkyen rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bas byas /
NK117(she)001:1296: dmigs pa'i rkyen 'od du snang ba ste /
NK117(she)001:1297: bdag po'i rkyen rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis 'od
NK117(she)001:1298: snang rang 'od yin par rang gi rang ngo shes
NK117(she)001:1299: pas / de ma thag pa'i rkyen gnyis 'dzin rang sar grol te /
NK117(she)001:1300: ye shes dang che ba'i yon tan thams cad phyogs med du shar nas /
NK117(she)001:1301: de nyid du sangs rgyas pa mang po 'byung bar yang gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1303: rgyu'i rkyen rang byung gi ye shes rang snang la lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas byas /
NK117(she)001:1305: bdag po'i rkyen rang gis rang ngo ma shes te /
NK117(she)001:1306: gzung 'dzin phra mo gnyis su byung /
NK117(she)001:1307: de ma thag pa'i rkyen bdag tu 'dzin cing yul du bzung ba las 'byung ba lngar shar /
NK117(she)001:1308: de la zhen pa brtas pa las /
NK117(she)001:1309: nang lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:1312: las gsum bsags pas 'bras bu khams gsum du 'khor zhing /
NK117(she)001:1314: thabs lam dang bral ba ni /
NK117(she)001:1315: de lta bu yin no bar ston pa'i thabs lam med pas kyang /
NK117(she)001:1318: rang bzhin dag pa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK117(she)001:1319: thabs dang lhan cig mi gnas pas //
NK117(she)001:1325: rkyen las dang nyon mongs pas /
NK117(she)001:1328: ma rig pa gnyis te gong bzhin la /
NK117(she)001:1329: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa zhes pa ni /
NK117(she)001:1330: rang sems ye nas sangs rgyas pa de dang /
NK117(she)001:1331: ma rig pa gnyis dus la snga phyi dang /
NK117(she)001:1332: go sa la tha dad dang /
NK117(she)001:1333: ngo bo la bzang ngan med par gcig pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1334: rang gis rang ngo ma shes pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK117(she)001:1335: gshis chos nyid snang stong la sogs pa'i mtha' la mi gnas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1336: cir yang snang la yul du byar med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1337: kun tu brtags pa'i ma rig pas /
NK117(she)001:1338: ngo ma shes kyis mi mdo ste /
NK117(she)001:1339: gnyis med rang snang la bdag tu 'dzin zhing zhor gyis yul gud par ltar mthong /
NK117(she)001:1341: rig med bem po ltar mthong zhing yul du bzung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:1343: de las nyon mongs pa phra mo lnga byung zhing /
NK117(she)001:1344: de la zhen pa'i mthu brtas pa las /
NK117(she)001:1345: gang mthong yang yul shes tha dad du 'dzin pa dus mnyam du khad khad byung /
NK117(she)001:1346: der nyon mongs pa rags pa lnga skyes /
NK117(she)001:1347: las dge mi dge lung ma bstan gsum na spyad pas /
NK117(she)001:1348: 'bras bu khams gsum du 'khor zhing rgyud drug tu 'khyams tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:1350: bshad pa bzhin du rang snang la //
NK117(she)001:1351: ma rig bdag lta brtags pa yis //
NK117(she)001:1352: zhor blo gud na 'dug pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1353: dzas bem brtags pa'i snang ba gsum //
NK117(she)001:1354: gol sa mnyam du skye ba nyid //
NK117(she)001:1355: log rtog rgyud la rtag gnas pas //
NK117(she)001:1356: nyon mongs las kyis cir snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:1358: yang rkyen bzhis 'khrul zhing grol bar yang gsung te /
NK117(she)001:1359: snang ba gang ltar shar yang /
NK117(she)001:1360: gong ltar rkyen bzhis 'khrul zhing grong bar shes par byas la /
NK117(she)001:1362: da lta gyi rtog pa gang skyes kyi steng du ngo sprod do //
NK117(she)001:1363: 'khrul tshul de gsum yang ming gi 'dogs lugs bag tsam mi 'dra yang /
NK117(she)001:1364: don gyi gnad gcig par shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:1365: 'khrul gyis mi mdo ste sdug bsngal zhing nyams thag pa ni /
NK117(she)001:1366: sdug bsngal gsum mam brgyad dam bcu gnyis la sogs pa'i sgo nas sdug bsngal zhing nyams thag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1368: sems mngon par 'du byed pa 'du byed kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:1370: ngan song gsum la sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal lo //
NK117(she)001:1372: gong ma gnyis spyir dang 'gro ba rig drug gi sdug bsngal te brgyad do //
NK117(she)001:1373: skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal bzhi ste bcu gnyis
NK117(she)001:1374: la sogs pa 'gro drug gi sdug bsngal bsam gyis
NK117(she)001:1375: mi khyab bo // de la dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal ni /
NK117(she)001:1378: nyi tshe nye 'khor gnyis te bco brgyad dang /
NK117(she)001:1379: chos la brten te gol nyams kyi dmyal ba yang mang por yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1391: chu bur rdol ba can dang /
NK117(she)001:1398: gol nyams kyi dmyal ba ni /
NK117(she)001:1399: gcan 'phrang nas dmyal khams nyi shu la sogs pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1400: de ltar dmyal ba la tsha grang gi sdug bsngal dpag tu med pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1401: yi dwags phyi'i sgrib pa can dang /
NK117(she)001:1403: me lce'i phreng ba can dang /
NK117(she)001:1404: mkha' la rgyu ba'i yid btags la sogs pa la
NK117(she)001:1405: bkres skom la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal dpag tu med
NK117(she)001:1408: bying dang kha 'thor gyi byol song la sogs pa rnams la nying sha nying gis za ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1409: gsod gcod dang bkol spyod kyi sdug bsngal la sogs pa sdug bsngal dpag tu med par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1410: mi yis med pa btsal gyis mi rnyed pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1411: skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK117(she)001:1412: lha ma yin 'thab rtsod kyi sdug bsngal dang /
NK117(she)001:1413: lha ltung ba'i sdug bsngal la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:1414: 'gro drug la sdug bsngal bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod de /
NK117(she)001:1415: 'khor ba dag la bde ba med //
NK117(she)001:1416: mi gtsang ba la dri zhim med //
NK117(she)001:1419: e ma rang gis rang brlagsa snying re rje //
NK117(she)001:1420: yi dwags byol song sdug bsngal skyi re phung //
NK117(she)001:1421: dmyal khams bco brgyad sdug bsngal ya re cha //
NK117(she)001:1422: skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal rgyun re ring //
NK117(she)001:1425: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rgya mtshor bying gyur te //
NK117(she)001:1426: zhe sdang 'bar ba'i mes ni rang rgyud bsregs //
NK117(she)001:1427: gti mug mun par 'thib pas shes rab ldong //
NK117(she)001:1428: 'dod chags rgya mtsho'i 'dam du rnam shes bying //
NK117(she)001:1429: nga rgyal dregs pa'i ri bos ngan 'gror mnan //
NK117(she)001:1430: phrag dog rlung dmar 'tshubs mas 'khor bar g.yeng //
NK117(she)001:1431: bdag tu lta ba'i mdud pa dam pos bcings //
NK117(she)001:1433: sdug bsngal drag po'i mda' zam char ltar 'bab //
NK117(she)001:1435: de la thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis gzigs pa la gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:1441: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK117(she)001:1442: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK117(she)001:1443: thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na //
NK117(she)001:1444: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK117(she)001:1446: gnyis su med cing 'brel pas mkhyen no //
NK117(she)001:1449: mkhyen mchog ye shes gsum ldan zhing //
NK117(she)001:1450: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK117(she)001:1454: dbyer mi phyed par mkhyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1456: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i rnam grangs thams cad ma 'dres par mkhyen pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1458: chos kun ma lus bdag gsal phyir //
NK117(she)001:1459: ye shes rnam grangs bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:1462: rang snang grangs med ye shes ni //
NK117(she)001:1463: sems dang chos dbyings nam mkha'i mtha' //
NK117(she)001:1464: phyogs ris bgrang bar mi nus pas //
NK117(she)001:1465: rnam grangs de yi tshul sbyar nas //
NK117(she)001:1466: ji ltar 'tshams pa'i tshul du snang //
NK117(she)001:1467: rang sems ye shes dbus mtha' med //
NK117(she)001:1468: 'od gsal rig pa thams cad mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1469: dus gcig kun mkhyen rig pa'i lung //
NK117(she)001:1470: sgrib dang sgro skur rnam par dpyad //
NK117(she)001:1471: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes yin //
NK117(she)001:1474: mthar thug pa med pa'i gzugs dang /
NK117(she)001:1476: 'du shes mtha' thug pa med pa nyid mi mkhyen pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1478: mi 'brel pa ni gang yang med de /
NK117(she)001:1480: snying po byang chub tu ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1483: de thams cad kyi chos nyid skye ba med cing /
NK117(she)001:1484: 'dus ma byas pa la sogs pa ji lta bar mkhyen pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1486: mkhyen ldan ye shes snying po yis //
NK117(she)001:1487: gang yang mi mkhyen rang gsal mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1488: mtha' dang dbus su mi dmigs pas //
NK117(she)001:1489: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1493: chos thams cad ye ji bzhin pa'i don phyin ci
NK117(she)001:1494: ma log par skye 'gag med par mkhyen pa la
NK117(she)001:1495: btags pas na / de ni don gyi dbang de kho na'i tshig bla dwags su rig par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:1498: de gnyis gnyis su med cing ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1500: mkhyen bya mkhyen byed gnyis med ye shes la //
NK117(she)001:1503: rnam rtog mi mnga' chos skur sa ler mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1504: de ni nges pa don gyi thams cad mkhyen pa yin //
NK117(she)001:1505: rdo rje sems dpas mkhyen pa'i mchog tu gsungs //
NK117(she)001:1507: rtsod pa'i skyon spang ba ni /
NK117(she)001:1508: mkhyen pas sems can la ci ltar phan zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1509: pha mngon par shes pa can gcig la bu gcig yod pas /
NK117(she)001:1510: bu'i rmi lam du mdze byung bas sdug bsngal ba la /
NK117(she)001:1511: phas gnyid bslangs pa dang 'dra bar /
NK117(she)001:1513: 'o na khams gsum gyi sems can mkhyen pa de /
NK117(she)001:1514: yul du byas nas mkhyen nam ma byas pa mkhyen byas pa la /
NK117(she)001:1515: yul du byas na sangs rgyas gzing 'dzin can du thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1517: ma rig rtog pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK117(she)001:1521: ji ltar 'dzin pa de ltar kun nas nyon mongs brten //
NK117(she)001:1522: zhes pa la sogs pa bka' rgyud du ma las gzung 'dzin 'khor ba'i chos su gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1523: yul du ma byas par mkhyen na sangs rgyas kyi
NK117(she)001:1524: dgongs pa las logs pa'i gdul bya yod dam med
NK117(she)001:1525: / yod na yul med du mkhyen pa'i dam bca' bud la /
NK117(she)001:1526: med na gcig sangs rgyas pas thams cad sangs rgyas par thal /
NK117(she)001:1527: 'dod na 'khor ba dong sprug par thal ba sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:1529: sangs rgyas las logs pa'i yul sems can med pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1530: phyir gyi gtan tshig ma grub na /
NK117(she)001:1531: yul med du mkhyen pa'i dam bca' bud do //
NK117(she)001:1533: yul du byas nas kyang mkhyen te /
NK117(she)001:1534: yul yul can du ma 'gags la mthar ma reg pa'i tshul du mkhyen te /
NK117(she)001:1535: de yang gnyis su ma 'gag la /
NK117(she)001:1536: gnyis kyi mthar ma lhung bas skyon gnyis las grol lo //
NK117(she)001:1538: ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:1539: yul med du yang mkhyen te /
NK117(she)001:1540: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'am /
NK117(she)001:1541: thugs rig pa'i ye shes las mi gzhan par mkhyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1543: thams cad rang gi ngo bo chos skur mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1544: mkhyen pa med pa'i mkhyen pa chen po ste //
NK117(she)001:1547: rang gsal ye shes rnam dag bde chen des //
NK117(she)001:1548: rnam pa ye gsal yul min thams cad mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1551: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mu mtha' med cing /
NK117(she)001:1552: kun la gnyis su med par khyab pas so //
NK117(she)001:1553: ngo bo rang yul yul can gnyis su med par /
NK117(she)001:1554: chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:1556: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK117(she)001:1557: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par gsal //
NK117(she)001:1559: gong gi lung rnams kyang ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dang mthun no //
NK117(she)001:1560: shin tu gting zab cing dpag par dka' bas /
NK117(she)001:1561: legs par dpyad la rtogs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:1562: yang rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mkhyen pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1563: rnam par mi rtog cing cir yang sa ler mkhyen ce na /
NK117(she)001:1564: rtog yul yod pa'i mi rtog pa yin nam /
NK117(she)001:1565: med pa'i mi rtog pa yin brtags /
NK117(she)001:1566: snga ma ltar na rtog yul 'dug pa'i phyir rtog byed kyang yod par thal /
NK117(she)001:1567: 'dod na mi rtog pa'i ye shes nyams so //
NK117(she)001:1568: ci'i phyir na rtog yul yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1569: phyi ma ltar na gcig grol bas thams cad grol ba la sogs pa'i skyon gong bazhinano //
NK117(she)001:1570: yang thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK117(she)001:1571: skad cig gcig la dus gsum mkhyen nam mi mkhyen /
NK117(she)001:1572: mi mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin cing /
NK117(she)001:1573: mkhyen par bshad pa'i lung rnams dang 'gal la /
NK117(she)001:1574: mkhyen na skad cig ma gcig gi dus na dus gsum yod dam med /
NK117(she)001:1575: med na dus gsum mkhyen pa 'gal la /
NK117(she)001:1576: yod na dus gsum rdzas yod du thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1577: dus gsum mkhyen pa rang ma yin par thal /
NK117(she)001:1578: ci'i phyir na skad cig la dus snga phyi med pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:1579: de skad du byas pa la /
NK117(she)001:1581: ma 'ongs pa ma skyes par mkhyen /
NK117(she)001:1582: da lta ba skyes la ma 'gag par mkhyen no ce na /
NK117(she)001:1583: de ltar na dus gsum gyi snang ba mngon sum du mkhyen nam rjes dpag tu mkhyen /
NK117(she)001:1584: snga ma ltar na dus gsum dngos su yod par thal la /
NK117(she)001:1586: sangs rgyas la dus kyi sgrib pa yod par thal /
NK117(she)001:1589: mkhyen pa'i skad cig gcig las ni //
NK117(she)001:1590: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun khyab can //
NK117(she)001:1591: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1592: 'og nas ston pa'i lung rnams dang 'gal lo //
NK117(she)001:1593: 'o na ji ltar mkhyen ce na /
NK117(she)001:1594: dus gsum rnam par bcad pa'am /
NK117(she)001:1595: skye 'gag can gyi skad cig gis mkhyen pa min la /
NK117(she)001:1596: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid dam /
NK117(she)001:1597: skye 'gag med pa'i skad cig gis /
NK117(she)001:1598: dus gsum ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1599: 'o na dus gsum skad cig gcig la yod dam med ce na /
NK117(she)001:1600: dus gsum rdzas yod dam skye 'gag can gyi skad cig tu 'dod pa min la /
NK117(she)001:1601: skye 'gag med pa'i skad cig la /
NK117(she)001:1602: dus gsum ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par yod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1603: de yang dus gsum ma 'dres te so sor mkhyen pas /
NK117(she)001:1604: dus gsum gcig pa'am mi mkhyen pa'i skyon las grol la /
NK117(she)001:1606: rang byung gi ye shes su dus gsum tha dad med cing dbyer med du yongs su rdzogs pas /
NK117(she)001:1607: skye 'gag can du 'dod pa las grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:1608: de yang dper na nam mkha' la dus gsum tha dad med cing /
NK117(she)001:1609: mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa bzhin du /
NK117(she)001:1611: rang byung gi ye shes la dus gsum tha dad med cing /
NK117(she)001:1612: mnyam pa nyid du gnas pas dus gsum ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par mkhyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1614: ma bcos ngang las gnyis med kyang //
NK117(she)001:1615: shes rab 'od gsal chen po yis //
NK117(she)001:1616: mkha' la gza' skar bkram pa'am //
NK117(she)001:1617: me tog mdzes pa'i phung po ltar //
NK117(she)001:1618: so sor gsal la gcig tu 'dus //
NK117(she)001:1619: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par ni //
NK117(she)001:1620: phyogs med ngang gsal ye shes su //
NK117(she)001:1621: dus matha'i tshad las 'das par mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:1624: dus gsum mnyam pa rang gsal yang //
NK117(she)001:1625: ma 'dres par yang so sor gzigs //
NK117(she)001:1626: ji bzhin pa dang ji snyed pa //
NK117(she)001:1627: snying po rang gsal rdzogs pa'i lung //
NK117(she)001:1629: rad na klong dgu'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:1630: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ma bcos la //
NK117(she)001:1631: mkhyen pa thams cad dus gcig gsal //
NK117(she)001:1632: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK117(she)001:1635: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid la sngon gyi mtha' mi dmigs /
NK117(she)001:1640: dus gsum mi dmigs pa'i tshul gyis dus gsum mi shes pa med pa ni /
NK117(she)001:1641: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po'i theg pa chen po'o //
NK117(she)001:1642: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:1643: gzhan yang sems can thams cad nang ma gro gcig
NK117(she)001:1644: la sangs rgyas pa'i thabs gcig mkhyen nam mi mkhyen
NK117(she)001:1645: / mi mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin par 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:1646: mkhyen na sangs rgyas la thugs rje med par thal lo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1647: sangs rgyas kyis ji lta ba dang ci snyed pa mkhyen pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1648: shes bya rang la sems can thams cad nang ma gros cig la sangs rgyas mi srid pas /
NK117(she)001:1649: sangs mi rgya ba rang du mkhyen pas skyon gnyis ka las grol lo //
NK117(she)001:1650: gzhan yang sems can gyi grangs mkhyen nam mi mkhyen /
NK117(she)001:1651: mi mkhyen na thams cad mkhyen pa ma yin la /
NK117(she)001:1654: sems can grangs dang log rtog grangs //
NK117(she)001:1655: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi mkhyen phyir //
NK117(she)001:1657: sems can la grangs yod par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1658: khams gsum sems can la grangs med pa la med
NK117(she)001:1659: par mkhyen pas de gnyis ka'i skyon mi 'ong ngo
NK117(she)001:1660: // de gnyis tha snyad tshig las don chung bas rgyas par ma bris so //
NK117(she)001:1661: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis gzigs nas thugs rje skye ba la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:1662: thugs rje skye ba'i rgyu rkyen dang /
NK117(she)001:1663: thugs rje skye ba'i ngo bo'am rnam grangs so //
NK117(she)001:1666: 'bras bu'i yon tan lhun grub pas //
NK117(she)001:1667: yid bzhin nor ltar snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:1669: rgyu sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa lhun grub phyogs med du snang ba /
NK117(she)001:1670: dpe nor bu rin po che dbang gi rgyal po lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:1671: rkyen gdul bya las dag pa klu'i rgyal po lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:1673: thugs rje chen pos gdul bya la //
NK117(she)001:1674: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK117(she)001:1677: rtag pa rgyun du thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1678: rang bzhin shugs kyis thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1679: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1680: yul dang mthun cing 'phrad pas thugs rje skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:1682: rang bzhin dbang btsan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1685: rig pa byang chub kyi sems rgyun chad med par ye nas gnas pa la bya ste /
NK117(she)001:1687: spros bral thugs kyis chos thams cad //
NK117(she)001:1688: kun la khyab pas rje nyid do //
NK117(she)001:1690: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje ni /
NK117(she)001:1691: sangs rgyas nas 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du /
NK117(she)001:1692: rtag par rgyun du don mdzad pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1694: sangs rgyas mya ngan yong mi 'da' //
NK117(she)001:1695: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK117(she)001:1696: le lo can la phan gdags phyir //
NK117(she)001:1697: sprul pa rnams ni 'das tshul ston //
NK117(she)001:1698: ji ltar nam mkha' zhig gyur na //
NK117(she)001:1701: 'o na sprul sku 'das nas da lta mi bzhugs pas mi rtag go zhe na /
NK117(she)001:1702: sku 'das pa'ang thugs rjes 'da' tshul ston pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:1703: rtag pa'i dngos por 'dzin pa sun phyung /
NK117(she)001:1704: le lo can la phan gdags /
NK117(she)001:1705: brtson 'grus can la bzhengs bskul gdab pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:1706: 'da' ba ltar snang ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:1707: dper na nyi ma gling bzhi la shar nub ltar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:1708: nyi ma'i dal la 'char nub med pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:1709: de bzhin du sprul sku sh+aakya thub pa 'di nas 'da' ba ltar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:1710: ngo bo la 'gro 'ong med cing brdal khyab chen po'i zhing na bzhugs la /
NK117(she)001:1711: byis pa rnams kyi ched du /
NK117(she)001:1712: me tog bkod pa'i 'jig rten du mtshan nges pa
NK117(she)001:1713: gcig tu ma grags pa zhes bya bar snang nas
NK117(she)001:1714: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa mdo sde las bshad do
NK117(she)001:1716: brdal khyab chen po'i zhing na bzhugs //
NK117(she)001:1718: de bzhin nyid du rnam par snang //
NK117(she)001:1719: byis pa'i ched du cho 'phrul dag /
NK117(she)001:1720: me tog bkod pa'i 'jig rten na //
NK117(she)001:1721: ma grags pa zhes bya bar snang //
NK117(she)001:1724: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK117(she)001:1725: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK117(she)001:1726: ma rig smin mdzad 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:1727: byung nas mya ngan 'da' bar ston //
NK117(she)001:1729: rang bzhin shugs kyis thugs rje skye ba ni /
NK117(she)001:1730: sangs rgyas rnams ni rtsol ba med par rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:1731: shugs kyis sems can la phan zhing don 'byung ba
NK117(she)001:1732: yin te / nam mkha' mtha' mnyam las /
NK117(she)001:1733: ye shes gsang ba'i ngang nyid las //
NK117(she)001:1734: thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' ltar bdal //
NK117(she)001:1735: thugs rje chen po nyi 'od ltar //
NK117(she)001:1739: ji bzhin nyid la bzhugs pas na //
NK117(she)001:1740: 'di zhes tshig tu ma gsung kyang //
NK117(she)001:1741: khyab pa gcig pa'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK117(she)001:1742: ci ltar 'dod pa so sor gsal //
NK117(she)001:1744: dper na nam mkha' la nyid ma 'char bas sa la dro ba 'byung zhing /
NK117(she)001:1745: chu lding tha dad pa'i nang du gzugs brnyan 'char ba ltar /
NK117(she)001:1746: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa las ma g.yos par /
NK117(she)001:1747: zhing khams dpag tu med par /
NK117(she)001:1748: sangs rgyas kyi rnam 'phrul dpag tu med pa 'jig rten du byon pa ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:1749: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:1750: mya ngan las 'da' bar la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:1751: mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'byung ba yang /
NK117(she)001:1752: rtsol ba med par rang bzhin shugs kyis 'byung ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:1754: ji ltar nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs brnyan gzhal yas khang las ma g.yos par //
NK117(she)001:1755: chu tha dad pa'i nang du gzugs brnyan tha dad par snang bzhin tu //
NK117(she)001:1756: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:1757: zhing khams dpag tu med par sangs rgyas mtha' yas par snang ngo //
NK117(she)001:1759: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pas thugs rje skye ba ni /
NK117(she)001:1760: spyir bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa dang /
