NK117(she)001:1761: bye brag tu bskul zhing gsol ba btab pas thugs rje skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:1763: 'og min du bskul zhing gsol ba btab pas thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1764: mi'i yul du bstan pa 'byung bar bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1766: bde chen brdal khyab chen po'i zhing khams 'og min
NK117(she)001:1767: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du sku lnga lhun
NK117(she)001:1768: grub kyi sangs rgyas la sogs te /
NK117(she)001:1769: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs shing /
NK117(she)001:1770: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par mkhyen nas /
NK117(she)001:1771: dgongs pa mnyam pa nyid du bzhugs pa la /
NK117(she)001:1772: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi yum pha rol tu phyin ma'am /
NK117(she)001:1773: chos kyi dbyings las bskul ba'i sgra byung bas /
NK117(she)001:1774: chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs so //
NK117(she)001:1777: yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK117(she)001:1778: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK117(she)001:1779: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK117(she)001:1780: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK117(she)001:1781: zhes pa la sogs pa'i sgra byung bas /
NK117(she)001:1782: chos kyi sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs nas bzhugs pa la /
NK117(she)001:1783: dngos kyi 'khor rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu gsol ba btab te /
NK117(she)001:1784: rgyud 'di nyid go rtog gi skal ba dang ldan pa la /
NK117(she)001:1786: 'di nyid go rtog gi skal pa dang mi ldan pa la /
NK117(she)001:1787: lam stegs kyi theg pa gzhan bshad du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1790: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi thugs chen po //
NK117(she)001:1791: ye shes don gyi snying po mchog dang ldan //
NK117(she)001:1792: rnal 'byor theg chen rdo rje kun 'dus lung //
NK117(she)001:1793: 'dus pa'i tshogs la rgya cher bshad du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1795: mi shes blun rmong 'dam bying 'gro ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:1796: sdug bsngal dra bas bcings pa thabs kyis khrol //
NK117(she)001:1797: ma rig mun pas mdongs pa 'od kyis phye //
NK117(she)001:1798: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho rol pa'i gru yis sgrol //
NK117(she)001:1801: de tshe rdo rje sems dpa' gang zhus pa //
NK117(she)001:1802: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa nges pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:1803: ma nor ma bcos rang byung chos sku ste //
NK117(she)001:1804: sems can blo yis nges par rtogs pa'i thabs //
NK117(she)001:1805: kun rig ston pa thugs rjes bshad du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1808: shin tu rnal 'byor bka' dogs 'byung ba dka' //
NK117(she)001:1809: sems can tshe thung skye rgas gting la thugs //
NK117(she)001:1810: ma rig mun par 'thib pa snying re rje //
NK117(she)001:1811: 'gro drug 'khor ba mi sgrol yi re mug /
NK117(she)001:1812: rang sems 'khor ba dag la sa mkhan mdzod //
NK117(she)001:1813: ces gsol ba btab pas 'og min la sogs par
NK117(she)001:1814: ston pa sku bzhis 'khor thun mong ma yin pa
NK117(she)001:1815: rnams la gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK117(she)001:1817: mi mjed kyi 'jig rten khams la sogs pa zhing khams dpag tu med par /
NK117(she)001:1818: sprul pa'i sku thub pa drug la sogs pa dpag tu med pas /
NK117(she)001:1820: bstan pa sde snod gsum la sogs pa gang ltar mtshams pa ltar gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1821: mi yul du 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK117(she)001:1822: rgyu'i chos 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1823: 'bras bu'i chos 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1824: bcom ldan 'das kyis dga' ldan gnas su byon pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1826: sangs rgyas pa'i tshul bstan te /
NK117(she)001:1828: grong khyer du chos bstan par dgongs shing gsungs pas /
NK117(she)001:1829: sh+aakya'i rigs rnams rigs mnyam po la chos mnyan pa dang dpon du bya ba mi 'ong /
NK117(she)001:1831: des gzhan yang nyan zhing go bar ma byung ste /
NK117(she)001:1832: mdo rgya che rol pa las /
NK117(she)001:1833: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK117(she)001:1834: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos cig bdag gis rnyed //
NK117(she)001:1835: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur bas //
NK117(she)001:1836: mi smra nags 'dabs nyid du gnas par bya //
NK117(she)001:1838: sgrol rgyu'i tshal du chos mi gsung bar bzhugs shing yod pa la /
NK117(she)001:1839: tshong dpon gon dang bzang po yis glang po che
NK117(she)001:1840: lam la 'gror ma 'dod par rtsa'i spyil po gcig
NK117(she)001:1841: la kha bltas nas 'dug pa la bltas pas /
NK117(she)001:1842: bcom ldan 'das bzhugs pa mthong nas /
NK117(she)001:1843: tshong dpon gyis yon bdag byas te chos ston drangs /
NK117(she)001:1844: der thams cad kyis chos zhus pas /
NK117(she)001:1846: tshangs pa 'khor dang bcas pas gser gyi 'khor lo rtsib stong dang ldan pa phul bas /
NK117(she)001:1847: ye shes chen po mchog gi dkyil 'khor bsgrub nas ni //
NK117(she)001:1848: phyogs bcu dag tu 'od zer rnam par bkye mdzad de //
NK117(she)001:1849: ye shes zer gyis mi'i pad+ma kha 'byed pa //
NK117(she)001:1850: smra ba'i nyi ma ci slad deng 'dir btang snyoms bzhugs //
NK117(she)001:1851: dam pa chos kyi rnga bo che ni brdung du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1852: chos kyi mchod sdong chen po bsgreng bar mdzad du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1853: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig gis gsol ba btab pa las /
NK117(she)001:1854: sngon la mdo sde shis pa brjod pa gsungs /
NK117(she)001:1855: de nas bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1856: bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:1857: tha ma nges pa'i don gyi'o //
NK117(she)001:1858: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos 'byung bar gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK117(she)001:1859: bcom ldan 'das mya ngan las 'das kar /
NK117(she)001:1860: gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan te /
NK117(she)001:1862: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK117(she)001:1863: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK117(she)001:1864: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK117(she)001:1865: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK117(she)001:1866: mi las skal ldan rigs can de //
NK117(she)001:1867: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK117(she)001:1868: sngon du ltas rnam snang bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:1869: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rir //
NK117(she)001:1870: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK117(she)001:1871: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK117(she)001:1872: lag na rdo rjes gnang bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:1874: rgyud lung man ngag gsum las /
NK117(she)001:1875: rgyud ni bcom ldan 'das sku mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK117(she)001:1877: rgyal po dza la po ti'i char bab pa la sogs pa'i rmis ltas rnam pa bdun byung ste /
NK117(she)001:1879: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1880: rin chen gleg bam bab pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1881: chos kyi bsgro ba byed pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1882: kun gyi dam par grags pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1883: pu dza chen po byed pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1884: rin chen char du 'bab pa dang //
NK117(she)001:1885: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1887: nang par bltas pas khar thog na //
NK117(she)001:1888: gser gyi gleg bam la beed+aur+ya /
NK117(she)001:1889: zhun mas bris pa'i gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mang po dang /
NK117(she)001:1890: phyag rdor gyi sku gcig byon nas 'dug go //
NK117(she)001:1891: de rnams la bltas pas gzhan gang yang shes par ma byung /
NK117(she)001:1892: rdo rje sems dpa' thugs kyi dang zhal mthong gi le'u gnyis shes nas /
NK117(she)001:1893: de nyid kyi sgo nas bsgrubs shing sku de la gsol ba btab pa las /
NK117(she)001:1894: gsang bdag mngon sum du byon nas /
NK117(she)001:1895: tan tra sde bco brgyad la sogs pa gsungs tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:1896: mdo dgongs 'dus la sogs pa lung gi chos rnams ni /
NK117(she)001:1897: sprul sku 'das nas lo nyer brgyad na /
NK117(she)001:1898: dam pa'i rigs can lngas ri ma la ya'i rtse la /
NK117(she)001:1899: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yid la byas nas /
NK117(she)001:1900: e ma kyi hud e ma klong /
NK117(she)001:1901: ston pa sgron ma'i 'od nub na //
NK117(she)001:1902: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK117(she)001:1903: zhes pa la sogs pa'i gdung tshig nyer gsum bton pas /
NK117(she)001:1904: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje bskul te /
NK117(she)001:1905: gsang ba pa yi bdag po khyod //
NK117(she)001:1906: sngon gyi go cha yal lam ci //
NK117(she)001:1907: 'jig rten sdug bsngal mi shes sam //
NK117(she)001:1908: snying rje'i sa la bab nas kyang //
NK117(she)001:1909: 'jig rten gdung ba bsal bar rigs //
NK117(she)001:1911: gsang bdag gi gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK117(she)001:1912: thog ma tha ma med pa ru //
NK117(she)001:1913: bskul ba'i dus ni gang byung ba //
NK117(she)001:1914: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK117(she)001:1917: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la /
NK117(she)001:1918: mdo dgongs 'dus la sogs pa gsungs tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:1919: bka' rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK117(she)001:1920: rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad rdzogs nas /
NK117(she)001:1922: ru kun dga' snying po la /
NK117(she)001:1923: rmi ltas bzhi rmis te thub pa drug gis skor ba byas te ru la thim pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1924: bdud dang khyab 'jug dang gu lang gsum gyur mid du zos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1925: phyag tu nyi zla gnyis thogs te 'jig rten gyi mun pa bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:1926: nam mkha' la sprin rin po che'i kha dog lta
NK117(she)001:1927: bu las char bab ste rtsi thog rgyas pa rmis
NK117(she)001:1928: nas / lha'i dbang po la bshad pas /
NK117(she)001:1929: lha'i dbang pos rtsol med kyi bstan pa 'byung bar shes te /
NK117(she)001:1930: rgyal ba thams cad la rtsol med kyi theg pa gsung du gsol /
NK117(she)001:1933: kye kye dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yis //
NK117(she)001:1934: rtsol bcas theg pa mthar bton nas //
NK117(she)001:1936: rtsol med theg pa bshad du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1938: rgyal ba thams cad kyis rdo rje sems dpa' bskul /
NK117(she)001:1939: rdo rje sems dpas phyag rdor thugs ka nas bton nas /
NK117(she)001:1940: 'chad pa'i skyes bu gsang ba'i bdag por dbang bskur te /
NK117(she)001:1941: dus gsum rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK117(she)001:1943: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba 'chang //
NK117(she)001:1944: khyod ni smra ba'i seng ge ste //
NK117(she)001:1945: rtsol med 'dus pa'i gang zag la //
NK117(she)001:1946: lhun grub theg pa gsung du gsol //
NK117(she)001:1948: phyag rdor gyis rgyal ba rigs lnga la gzhi 'bras kyi the tshom bcad nas /
NK117(she)001:1949: lha gnas gsum du rtsol med kyi bstan pa gsung tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:1950: de nas gsang bdag phyag na rdo rjes /
NK117(she)001:1951: sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje la gsang ba rdzogs
NK117(she)001:1952: pa chen po'i bstan pa'i bdag por dbang bskur nas
NK117(she)001:1953: / o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling du /
NK117(she)001:1954: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs pa rnams la /
NK117(she)001:1955: rtsol med rdzogs pa chen po gsung tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:1956: rgyas par rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes so //
NK117(she)001:1958: bla ma dkon mchog yi dam la gsol ba tab pas /
NK117(she)001:1960: dang po ni bla ma la mos gus byas shing spyi bor bsgom /
NK117(she)001:1962: theg pa mnyam nyid du 'gyur zhing /
NK117(she)001:1963: sangs rgyas bas kyang lhag par gsung ste /
NK117(she)001:1965: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas bas //
NK117(she)001:1966: bla ma gnyan par shes par bya //
NK117(she)001:1967: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1969: des na bla ma spyi bor bsgom //
NK117(she)001:1970: rdo rje slob dpon bsgom pa yis //
NK117(she)001:1971: chos kun ma lus bsgom pa yin //
NK117(she)001:1972: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa'i lha //
NK117(she)001:1973: 'bum du bsgom pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK117(she)001:1974: bla ma bsgom pa'i 'bum char min //
NK117(she)001:1977: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro byas shing gsol ba btab pas /
NK117(she)001:1978: dkon mchog gi thugs rje dang byin rlabs 'byung zhing /
NK117(she)001:1979: skyabs 'og tu tshud pa la sogs pa yon tan dpag tu med pa 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:1981: gang gi dkon mchog gsum po la //
NK117(she)001:1982: skyabs su 'gro ba byas pa yis //
NK117(she)001:1983: yon tan de la gzugs yod na //
NK117(she)001:1984: stong gsum 'di yang snod du chung //
NK117(she)001:1987: lha re bsgom zhing gsol ba btab /
NK117(she)001:1988: bsgrub pas dus nam zhig zhal mthong gsung thos pa la sogs pa byin brlabs 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:1990: lha la rtag tu mchod byas na //
NK117(she)001:1991: lha dang gnyis su med par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:1993: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor na //
NK117(she)001:1996: yul dang mthun cing 'phrad pas thugs rje skye ba ni /
NK117(she)001:1997: spyir sku lngas 'khor lnga la don mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:1998: bye brag tu sku gsum gyi thugs rjes mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:1999: ye shes rgya mtsho'i 'khor rnams la /
NK117(she)001:2000: ston pa chos kyi skus rig pa byin gyis brlabs sam /
NK117(she)001:2001: skye med don gyi gsung gis don mdzad de /
NK117(she)001:2003: chos sku nam mkha'i mtha' kun khyab //
NK117(she)001:2004: chos sku rang byung spros med pas //
NK117(she)001:2005: ye shes sku la 'gag med gsal //
NK117(she)001:2006: des na byin gyis brlabs kyis bshad //
NK117(she)001:2008: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la sogs pa'am /
NK117(she)001:2009: smin pa rgya mtsho'i 'khor rnams la /
NK117(she)001:2010: ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur snang nas /
NK117(she)001:2011: sku mdun dang rgyab med par zhal phyogs bcu kun tu tha le ba la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2012: dgongs pa brda'i sgo nas don mdzad de /
NK117(she)001:2014: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK117(she)001:2015: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK117(she)001:2016: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK117(she)001:2017: de bzhin gsungs mchog mi smra ste //
NK117(she)001:2018: sku yis chos rnams mjal bar ston //
NK117(she)001:2019: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:2020: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel //
NK117(she)001:2023: sdug po bkod pa'i rgyal ba yang //
NK117(she)001:2024: chos sku snying por gyur pas na //
NK117(she)001:2025: de yis 'gro ba mi smin phyir //
NK117(she)001:2026: gzugs skur bstan nas tshig lam brjod //
NK117(she)001:2028: gdul bya smin zhing rgyud dag pa rnams la /
NK117(she)001:2029: gong ltar longs skur snang la /
NK117(she)001:2030: dag pa dang ma dag pa rnams la sprul skur snang nas ngon mdzad de /
NK117(she)001:2031: spyir 'jig rten gyi khams bsam gyis mi khyab par /
NK117(she)001:2032: sprul pa'i sku bsam gyis mi khyab par snang bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:2034: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:2035: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:2037: bye brag tu sbyor lam dang mthong lam pa la sprul sku mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pas /
NK117(she)001:2038: dngos su gsung gis don mdzad de /
NK117(she)001:2040: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan dang mthu stobs pha mtha' yas //
NK117(she)001:2041: sems can rnams la chos rab stong pa sgrogs par byed //
NK117(she)001:2043: ma dag pa rnams la 'gro ba rang rang gi
NK117(she)001:2044: snang tshul dang mthun par gang la gang 'dul du
NK117(she)001:2046: skye ba thams cad kyi gzugs su snang ba ni //
NK117(she)001:2049: me khyer la sogs srog chags gang yin pa de dang de'i gzugs su snang bar mdzad cing /
NK117(she)001:2050: de dag gi cha byad kyis gang ji ltar mos pa rnams la /
NK117(she)001:2053: de'ang phyogs re tsam mtshon na /
NK117(she)001:2054: sngon byung ru tra la thugs rje skyes te btul ba lta bu'am /
NK117(she)001:2055: rkang chag lag rdum la sogs pa la thugs rje skye ba lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:2056: thugs rje skyes nas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:2057: don mdzad pa'i mdzad tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:2060: rten can gyi don mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2065: kri yog la sogs pa'i lugs kyis /
NK117(she)001:2066: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsum las /
NK117(she)001:2067: gzugs sku rang rgyud pa 'od sgo re ba cig 'og min na yod la /
NK117(she)001:2068: de dang de'i sprul pas 'gro don mdzad par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2071: mthar thug chos kyi sku dbyings rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa la /
NK117(she)001:2072: spang bya glo bur gyi dri ma dag pa'i dag pa gnyis kyi bdag nyid du bzhugs la /
NK117(she)001:2073: de las gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis byung nas don mdzad par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2074: yang chos sku stong pa la byas nas /
NK117(she)001:2075: gzugs sku gnyis gdul bya'i ngor snang tsam du 'dod pa'ang yod de /
NK117(she)001:2076: de ni sngon gyi smon lam gyi stobs las 'byung bar 'dod de /
NK117(she)001:2077: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK117(she)001:2079: de las sprul sku char lta bu byung nas don mdzad do zer ba yang yod do //
NK117(she)001:2080: ngo bo nyid kyis mdzad pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2081: don mdzad pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK117(she)001:2082: gdul bya sems can gnyis ngo bo dbyer med cing
NK117(she)001:2083: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par don mdzad pa'o
NK117(she)001:2085: chos kun rang byung ston pa'i mchog /
NK117(she)001:2087: nyid las mi gzhan rang byung nyid //
NK117(she)001:2089: gong gi mkhyen pa'i skabs kyi lung tshig bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:2091: spyir sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK117(she)001:2092: gang la gang 'dul du ji ltar 'tshams par don mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2095: mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pas don mdzad par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:2097: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK117(she)001:2098: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK117(she)001:2099: lhums su zhugs dang bltams pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2100: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2101: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis rol pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2102: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2103: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2104: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni //
NK117(she)001:2105: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK117(she)001:2106: mya ngan 'das par bzhed pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:2108: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK117(she)001:2109: shin tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2113: phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2115: phyin ci log gi gdul bya brgyud nas /
NK117(she)001:2116: yang dag pa'i don la 'dren pas thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2117: grong khyer gsum gyi ched du /
NK117(she)001:2118: sku gsum du snang nas don mdzad pas /
NK117(she)001:2120: sprul pa'i sku res drang don gyi chos gsungs nas /
NK117(she)001:2121: 'da' kar gsang sngags nges don gyi chos phyis 'byung bar lung ston pas rmad byung che ba'i dang /
NK117(she)001:2126: mthar thug gi las rgyun gcod pas /
NK117(she)001:2127: las rgyun gcod pa'i mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2128: bstan pa 'chad pa'i mdzad pa dang lngas don mdzad par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:2129: rgyas par rang gzhung bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:2131: 'gro ba drug gi snang tshul bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bstun nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2132: thabs mkhas theg pa sna tshogs kyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2134: 'gro drug gi snang ba dang bstun nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2135: 'byung ba lnga 'dod yon lngar snang nas don mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2136: phyi nang gi bskal pa zung gsum ya drug dang bstun nas don mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2138: 'gro ba drug gi bsam pa dang bstun nas don mdzad pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:2140: lha dang lha min gnas ris su //
NK117(she)001:2141: che ba nga rgyal 'joms pa bstan //
NK117(she)001:2142: shes pa mi yi gnas ris su //
NK117(she)001:2143: dge sdig rgyu 'bras sde snod bshad //
NK117(she)001:2144: gti mug byol song gnas ris su //
NK117(she)001:2145: rig pa shes pa'i chos kyang bstan //
NK117(she)001:2146: ser sna yi dwags gnas ris su //
NK117(she)001:2147: ma chags tshim pa'i chos kyang bstan //
NK117(she)001:2148: sdug bsngal dmyal ba'i gnas ris su //
NK117(she)001:2149: snga phyi dran pa'i zhen pa bzlog /
NK117(she)001:2153: 'dod yon lngar snang nas kyang rang bzhin gyis don mdzad pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:2155: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung //
NK117(she)001:2156: 'dod lnga kun tu sbyor ba yang //
NK117(she)001:2157: sangs rgyas thugs rje'i rol par shar //
NK117(she)001:2158: thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' ltar bdal //
NK117(she)001:2161: phyi nang gi bskal pa zung gsum ya drug tu snang nas /
NK117(she)001:2162: las ngan gyi rgyun gcod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:2163: nang dang mu ge mtshon nyid dang //
NK117(she)001:2164: me chu rlung dang nam mkha' stong //
NK117(she)001:2165: de dag rim par ji bstan pa //
NK117(she)001:2166: thugs rje rmad byung rol pa yin //
NK117(she)001:2167: ji lta ji ltar de dag tu //
NK117(she)001:2168: 'dul ba'i thabs su bstan pa yin //
NK117(she)001:2170: theg pas don mdzad pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:2171: rtsol ba'i theg pa theg pa rim pa brgyad kyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2172: rtsol med a tis don mdzad tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:2173: de dag gang 'chad kyang rang rang gi skabs dang sbyar la rgyas par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:2174: bye brag tu rgyud dang man ngag gi khog dbub pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:2175: rgyud dang man ngag gi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:2176: bye brag so so nas khog dbub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2178: bka' dang bstan chos kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:2179: rgyud lung man ngag gi khyad par ro //
NK117(she)001:2182: bye brag so so'i dbye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2184: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK117(she)001:2185: chos rnams thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis su 'dus //
NK117(she)001:2186: legs par gsung dang de yi dgongs 'grel pa /
NK117(she)001:2187: de yi dbang gis sh+aakya'i bstan pa 'di //
NK117(she)001:2188: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas pa yin //
NK117(she)001:2190: legs par gsung pa gcig bka'/
NK117(she)001:2191: de'i dgongs pa 'grel pa bstan bcos /
NK117(she)001:2193: sangs rgyas kyi bdag rkyen las byung zhing legs par gsung pa bka'/
NK117(she)001:2194: de la brten zhing de'i dgongs pa 'grel pa bstan bcos so //
NK117(she)001:2196: bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:2198: zhal nas gsung pa'i bka' dang /
NK117(she)001:2199: byin gyis brlabs kyis byung ba'i bka' dang /
NK117(she)001:2202: sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas dngos su gsungs pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2204: sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'i dus na /
NK117(she)001:2205: sangs rgyas kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK117(she)001:2207: sa rdo la sogs pa la yang chos 'byung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2208: dngos su 'khor rnams kyis zhus shing bshad pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2210: sangs rgyas kyis chos gsung zhig par lung ston pa las byung ba rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2212: bka' spyi dang bye brag gi dgongs pa 'grel pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2213: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi dgongs pa 'grel ba rnams yin te /
NK117(she)001:2214: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:2215: gnyis pa rgyud lung man ngag gi khyad par ni /
NK117(she)001:2218: phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshogs shing 'brel dang ma tshang ba med pa gcig rgyud lung /
NK117(she)001:2219: dpag par dka' ba'i don nyid mngon du bstan pas /
NK117(she)001:2220: btsal tshegs tshung zhing dgos don che bas man ngag go //
NK117(she)001:2222: phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshogs shing //
NK117(she)001:2223: 'brel dang ma tshang med pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2224: yongs su rdzogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK117(she)001:2227: thabs che tshegs chung don dpag med //
NK117(she)001:2228: bya sla dpag dka' man ngag go //
NK117(she)001:2233: man ngag gsum gyi dbye ba ste /
NK117(she)001:2234: zhus len 'dren mar gsungs shing tshang zhing 'brel pa'i cha nas rgyud /
NK117(she)001:2235: sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas ma bslad ji bzhin gsung pa'i cha nas lung /
NK117(she)001:2236: don gnyis mngon du phyung ba'i cha nas man ngag go //
NK117(she)001:2238: gsung gi 'gyur bas de mtshon na //
NK117(she)001:2239: skyes bu rgyal po'i bka' lung yin //
NK117(she)001:2240: zhus len phra men 'phel rgyas na //
NK117(she)001:2241: skyes bu rgyal po'i bka' rgyud yin //
NK117(she)001:2243: de nyid nges pa kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:2244: ma bslad ji bzhin bcas pa lung //
NK117(she)001:2245: bcas gzhi gtam rgyud las rgyud dang //
NK117(she)001:2246: rtog chen yan lag 'brel bcas rgyud //
NK117(she)001:2248: de gsum yang ngo bo gcig la rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas gsum du phye ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:2249: gsum du snang la gcig tu zad //
NK117(she)001:2250: dbyer med tshul gcig rang bzhin la //
NK117(she)001:2251: rtsal dang dam pa snang ba dag /
NK117(she)001:2252: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyi med //
NK117(she)001:2255: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag gsum //
NK117(she)001:2256: 'bangs dang rje dang rgyal po'i tshul //
NK117(she)001:2257: gcig la gcig brten gcig gi ngang //
NK117(she)001:2258: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK117(she)001:2262: man ngag khog dbub pa gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:2264: rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:2266: yongs su rdzogs pa rgyud kyi don dang /
NK117(she)001:2267: rgyud gdams shing gtad pa dang bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:2268: rang rang gi skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2278: khungs nas khungs su brgyud pa'i dgongs pa'i nyams myong la bya ste /
NK117(she)001:2280: rang gi mtshan nyid nyams su myong ba la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2284: nyams su blang ba'i lag len la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2289: nges par myur du 'grub pas man ngag yin gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2291: nyams su myong ba'i don mngon du phyung nas ston pa gcig la man ngag ces bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2293: lung gi dgongs pa rnams lta bar mi nus pa'i don du /
NK117(she)001:2294: gdam ngag gis lung gi bcud phyungs nas rtogs shing nyams su myong ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK117(she)001:2296: snyan rgyud zhal gyi man ngag dang /
NK117(she)001:2297: brda bral stong nyid rang grol ba'i man ngag dang /
NK117(she)001:2298: yi ge dkyus kyi man ngag go //
NK117(she)001:2299: snga ma ni kun bzang ngam /
NK117(she)001:2300: rdo rje 'chang man chad du snyan du brgyud pa yi ge ris su bri ma myong /
NK117(she)001:2301: bris pa dang 'gal ma myong ba'i dgongs pa'i don mtshon pa la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2303: dang po brda don sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2305: tha mar brda bral stong nyid rang grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2306: yi ge dkyus kyi man ngag ni /
NK117(she)001:2307: tshig dang yi ge ris su bris pa'i man ngag la bya ste /
NK117(she)001:2308: de kho na nyid ston pa'i man ngag dang /
NK117(she)001:2309: mngon par rtogs pa rim gyis pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2311: gnas skabs de kho na nyid ston pa theg pa
NK117(she)001:2312: 'og ma pa rnams kyi rang rang gi mthar thug
NK117(she)001:2314: mthar thug de kho na nyid ston pa a ti'i man ngag rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2315: mngon par rtogs pa rim gyis pa'i man ngag ni /
NK117(she)001:2316: theg pa spyi dang bye brag la 'jug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2317: rgyud spyi dang bye brag la 'jug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2318: lam spyi dang bye brag la 'jug pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2319: de la theg pa spyi la 'jug pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2322: snang ba bcu bdun pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2324: rang rang gi gnas skabs kyi man ngag rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2326: rgyud dbu zhabs mtshon pa'i 'grel pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2329: rgyud gnas skabs la 'jug pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2331: rgyud kyi don phun sum tshogs pa la 'jug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2332: rgyud gdams shing gtad pa la 'jug pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2334: sgyu 'phrul lam rim la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2335: lam rdzogs par ston pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2339: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2340: bye brag re re nas ston pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:2342: mdo sde la brten nas bstan bcos rtsom pa'i tshad dang /
NK117(she)001:2343: rgyud sde la brten nas man ngag rtsom pa'i tshad do //
NK117(she)001:2345: lung la 'dris shing tshad la mkhas //
NK117(she)001:2346: sgra dang don gnyis gtsor gyur pas //
NK117(she)001:2347: rig pa'i bstan bcos rtsom par bya //
NK117(she)001:2350: mngon sum dang rjes dpag gi tshad ma la mkhas pa /
NK117(she)001:2352: rang rang gi don spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:2353: khongs su chud pas bstan bcos rtsom par bshad do
NK117(she)001:2355: nges pa'i lung la rdzun mi tshud //
NK117(she)001:2356: rang gi nyams myong man ngag ldan //
NK117(she)001:2357: yongs su shes pa'i dngos po rnams //
NK117(she)001:2358: tshad du phyin pas gdams ngag brtsams //
NK117(she)001:2360: lung gi tshig dang don dgongs khrol ba /
NK117(she)001:2361: rang gis rtogs shing nyams su myong ba /
NK117(she)001:2362: khung nas khungs su brgyud pa'i gdams ngag dang ldan pa /
NK117(she)001:2363: yongs su shes pa'i dngos po bcu la mkhas shing /
NK117(she)001:2364: tshang du phyin pas brtsams par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:2367: 'bring yi dam lha'i lung bstan thob pa /
NK117(she)001:2368: tha ma shan 'byed cing la zlos pa /
NK117(she)001:2369: bka' lung gi tshig la mkhas pas kyang brtsam par bshad de /
NK117(she)001:2371: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rab //
NK117(she)001:2372: yi dam mkha' 'gro bla ma yi //
NK117(she)001:2373: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK117(she)001:2374: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK117(she)001:2375: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK117(she)001:2379: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bya ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2380: man ngag spyi don rtsis mgo lnga yis gzhom //
NK117(she)001:2382: yid ches shing khung btsun par bya ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:2383: slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2384: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:2385: rgyud gang nas btus shing phyogs gong du gtogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2386: bstan pa la mtshan nges shing /
NK117(she)001:2387: don gyi mdo tsam rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:2388: mtshan ci las btags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2389: dgos ched dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:2390: dgos ched gang gi don du mdzad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2391: dbu zhabs kyi don khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:2392: dbu zhabs su don bsdus bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2393: de rnams rang rang gi skabs dang sbyar la bshad do //
NK117(she)001:2394: bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis /
NK117(she)001:2395: rgyud dang man ngag gang 'chad kyang /
NK117(she)001:2398: dang po yid ches pa yi khung bstan phyir //
NK117(she)001:2399: lo rgyus don gyis bshad lugs bstan par bya //
NK117(she)001:2400: chos kun rtsa ba sems su 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2401: de nas rtsa ba'i don de bstan par bya //
NK117(she)001:2402: theg pa'i khyad par so sor dbye ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2403: yo ga don gyi rtsa ba bstan par bya //
NK117(she)001:2404: rtsol bsgrubs bya mi dgos par bstan pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2405: dgos ched don gyi dgos pa de ru bstan //
NK117(she)001:2406: ma rtogs don de rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2407: tshig gi don de sgra ru brjod par bya //
NK117(she)001:2410: man ngag byung khung lo rgyus dang //
NK117(she)001:2411: 'jug sgo theg pa yo ga'i don //
NK117(she)001:2412: rten gyi gang zag dgos pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:2413: dril nas mtshan gsol rtsa ba'i don //
NK117(she)001:2414: dbu zhabs dkyus bshad tshig gi don //
NK117(she)001:2415: spyi don lnga yis bshad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:2419: don gyis mi gnyis brgyud pa can //
NK117(she)001:2420: tha snyad bral ba'i don mtshon pa //
NK117(she)001:2421: man ngag tshad mas rang mtshan ston //
NK117(she)001:2422: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag tu'o //
NK117(she)001:2424: rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud pa /
NK117(she)001:2426: gang zag snyan nas snyan khung du brgyud pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2427: de yang ston pa sangs rgyas kyi che ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2428: bstan pa chos kyi che ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2430: mkhas pa pan ti ta'i che ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2431: sgra bsgyur lo ts+aa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2432: yon bdag zhing gi che ba /
NK117(she)001:2433: bzhengs pa rten gyi khyad par /
NK117(she)001:2434: bsgrub pa po grub thob kyi che ba /
NK117(she)001:2435: gtan la dbab bya gzhi'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2436: bgrod pa lam gyi che ba /
NK117(she)001:2437: mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i che ba dang bcu'o //
NK117(she)001:2439: ston pa yongs su rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:2440: gzhi rang byung gi ston pa kun tu bzang po 'khrul ma myong gi che ba'am /
NK117(she)001:2442: snga ma ni sde snod gsum la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK117(she)001:2443: sprul pa'i sku la sogs pa sku re res gsungs pa yin la /
NK117(she)001:2444: bka' rdzogs pa chen po ni /
NK117(she)001:2445: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2446: gnyis pa gzhi rang byung gi ston pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2447: ye ji bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas las 'khrul ma myong ste /
NK117(she)001:2450: theg pa so so'i sangs rgyas las phyogs 'dzin dang lam bgrod ma myong ste khyad par du 'phags /
NK117(she)001:2451: 'bras bu rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas las
NK117(she)001:2452: lam gyis rtogs ma myong bas khyad par du 'phags
NK117(she)001:2454: bstan pa yongs su rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:2455: che ba bdun nam lnga yis khyad par du 'phags te bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2458: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum ni rgyu'i theg pa yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:2459: sprul pa'i sku yi bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2460: de yang sde snod rnam pa gsum las chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong du gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2462: 'bras bu spyi'i rnam pa lam du byed la /
NK117(she)001:2463: longs sku'i bstan pa gtso che bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:2464: de la yang rgyud sde dpag tu med pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2465: nang pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa gsum ni /
NK117(she)001:2466: sku lnga lhun grub kyi bstan pa yongs su rdzogs shing /
NK117(she)001:2467: khyad par du ngo bo nyid du sku dang chos kyi sku'i bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2468: de la ma h+aa dang a nu ni /
NK117(she)001:2469: 'bras bu rang gi mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lam du byed cing /
NK117(she)001:2470: 'khor 'das gnyis su med par ston pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2471: ma h+aa ni sgyu 'phrul sde bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:2472: tan tra chen po sde bco brgyad la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:2473: dpag tu med cing brjod las 'das pa yod par
NK117(she)001:2474: gsungs so // a nu ni lung gi mdo chen
NK117(she)001:2475: po lnga la sogs pa lung gi chos dpag tu
NK117(she)001:2476: med cing brjod pa las 'das pa yod par gsungs
NK117(she)001:2477: gsungs so // so // a ti yo ga ni /
NK117(she)001:2478: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la rgyu 'bras
NK117(she)001:2479: gnyis su med cing 'khor 'das gnyis med rgya chad
NK117(she)001:2480: phyogs lhung med par gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2481: de'ang a nu man chad kyi theg pa'ang yongs su rdzogs par ston pa /
NK117(she)001:2482: khyad par a ti'i bstan pa nam mkha' dang 'dra ste /
NK117(she)001:2484: de'ang phyogs gcig tsam mtshon na /
NK117(she)001:2490: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa gdams ngag gi skor dang drug go //
NK117(she)001:2495: bkra shis mi 'gyur gsal par gnas pa'i rgyud la sogs pa rgyud sde chen po bco brgyad dang /
NK117(she)001:2497: phyi 'gyur bcu gsum ste gdams ngag bco brgyad la
NK117(she)001:2498: sogs pa dpag tu med par yod par gsungs so
NK117(she)001:2499: // klong sde'i skor la bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:2500: phyi rtsis rgya'i skor la glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2501: gzer bu brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK117(she)001:2503: kun tu bzang po rig pa rtsal shar ba'i rgyud la sogs pa man ngag brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK117(she)001:2504: gsang ba rgyal bu chung gi skor la rin po che bkod pa'i rgyud la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2505: bsam gtan brgya dang brgyad cu /
NK117(she)001:2506: dgongs pa gtad rgya'i skor la /
NK117(she)001:2507: klong chen po rab 'byams rgyal po'i rgyud la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2508: la bzla brgya dang brgyad cu yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2510: gong gi bshad lugs bzhi po de rnams yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2513: nya mo 'khor lo'i rgyud la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2514: rgyud bzhi bcu zhe gnyis man ngag dang bcas pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2516: bram ze rtsa ba'i rgyud drug /
NK117(she)001:2517: yan lag gi rgyud sum cu rtsa drug gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2518: de la nam mkha' klong yongs kyi rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:2519: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:2520: kun tu bzang po ye shes klong gi dang /
NK117(she)001:2521: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i dang /
NK117(she)001:2522: nges don 'dus pa gter gyi dang /
NK117(she)001:2523: 'khor ba rtsad nas gcod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:2524: spyi rgyud ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2525: la bzla rgyal po'i skor ni /
NK117(she)001:2526: bkra shis dus tshod 'dzin pa khu byug gi rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:2527: yon tan rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:2528: thig le sgron ma gsang ba bkod pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:2530: rig pa nam mkha' mnyam pa'i rgyud la sogs te /
NK117(she)001:2532: yan lag gi rgyud sde brgya thams pa /
NK117(she)001:2533: man ngag dang bcas pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2535: gab pa mngon du phyungs ba gab pa'i skor dang /
NK117(she)001:2536: rig pa gtan la 'bebs pa bsgag pa'i skor dang /
NK117(she)001:2537: chos nyid ma bu sprod pa rdzogs 'phrang gi skor dang /
NK117(she)001:2538: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa brgyud pa tha ma'i skor ro //
NK117(she)001:2539: de re re la'ang rgyud sde dang man ngag tu
NK117(she)001:2540: bcas pa yongs su rdzogs par yod par gsungs so
NK117(she)001:2541: // de tsho re re'i khong nas kyang mu stegs la sogs pa'i log rtog bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2542: theg pa rim pa brgyad kyi shan dbye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2543: rdzogs pa chen por la bzla ba rang grol mngon
NK117(she)001:2544: sum du ngo sprod pa la sogs pa theg pa
NK117(she)001:2545: thams cad kyi 'dod lugs yongs su rdzogs par gsungs
NK117(she)001:2548: phyi skor nang skor gsang skor /
NK117(she)001:2549: gsang ba bla na med pa'i skor la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2552: spros bral don gsal gyi skor dang /
NK117(she)001:2555: rgyal po bla gter gyi skor dang /
NK117(she)001:2556: kun grol gyi skor la sogs pa brjod pa las 'das pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2557: che ba bdun nam lnga yis khyad par du 'phags pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2558: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin pa'i che ba ri rgyal lhun po lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:2559: lung thams cad kyi rgyal po yin pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2560: nyi ma'i snying po lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:2561: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2562: 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' las 'byung ba lngar snang ba lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:2563: bka' thams cad kyi 'brel pa yin pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2564: nam mkha'i ngang las snod bcud thams cad gsal ba lta bu /
NK117(she)001:2565: man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2566: rgyal po'i bka' gsang thob pa'i mi lta bu /
NK117(she)001:2567: don thams cad kyi mjug sdud yin pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2568: mgron po byis log nas rang gi khyim du song ba lta bu /
NK117(she)001:2569: chos thams cad kyi me long yin pa'i che ba /
NK117(she)001:2570: me long g.ya' dag pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:2572: gling dang ri bo mu khyud bcas //
NK117(she)001:2573: lhun po'i rtse mo nyid nas gsal //
NK117(she)001:2574: ji snyed theg pa'i rnam grangs kun //
NK117(she)001:2575: de nyid chen po nyid mthong gsal //
NK117(she)001:2578: gzi ldan gsal ba'i nyi ma yin //
NK117(she)001:2579: chos kun yongs su rdzogs gsal ba //
NK117(she)001:2580: kun snang chen po de nyid do //
NK117(she)001:2582: go skabs chen po nam mkha' ni //
NK117(she)001:2583: chen po bzhi yi go 'byed ltar //
NK117(she)001:2584: gsang nyid 'dus pa de nyid kyis //
NK117(she)001:2585: brjod pa'i brjod kun gsal bar 'grel //
NK117(she)001:2587: gang gi bka' yi gsang thob na //
NK117(she)001:2588: mi gang gzhan la rag ma lus //
NK117(she)001:2589: gsang ba'i snying por kun chub na //
NK117(she)001:2590: smra brjod gang la'ang btsal mi dgos //
NK117(she)001:2592: rgyud dang bcas pa'i 'byung ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:2593: nam mkha'i ngang las 'byung zhing snang //
NK117(she)001:2594: de bzhin smra brjod 'byung ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:2595: de nyid zab mo'i dbyings nas 'byung //
NK117(she)001:2597: don du bya ba'i rnam grangs kun //
NK117(she)001:2598: mthar gyis 'bras bu grub par sdud //
NK117(she)001:2599: rnam grangs rgya cher brjod mod kyang //
NK117(she)001:2600: de kun de bzhin nyid du 'dus //
NK117(she)001:2602: me long gsal ba'i snying pos ni //
NK117(she)001:2603: bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan ston pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:2604: de nyid chos kyi me long gis //
NK117(she)001:2605: kun gyi rang bzhin gsal bar byed //
NK117(she)001:2607: che ba lnga ni gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:2610: rdzogs pa chen po 'khor 'das dbyer med chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:2611: rig pa mchog la mnga' brnyes pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:2612: slob dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dang /
NK117(she)001:2614: b+hi ma la mi tra la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2615: mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:2617: dam pa'i rigs can lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:2618: slob dpon h'u ka ra dang /
NK117(she)001:2619: gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK117(she)001:2620: chos nyid rgyun chad med pa mngon sum du rtogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2621: lha ma srin sde brgyad bran du 'khol zhing /
NK117(she)001:2623: sgra 'gyur sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa shes shing /
NK117(she)001:2624: rigs drug gi skad la thogs pa med par chos ston nus pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2627: bka' cog rin po che dang /
NK117(she)001:2628: gnyag dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK117(she)001:2629: slob dpon b+hee ro tsa na la sogs pa rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas shing /
NK117(she)001:2630: sgra 'gyur sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa shes pa /
NK117(she)001:2631: ris drug gi skad la thogs pa med cing /
NK117(she)001:2632: snyan gyis dus gcig la chos nyan nus pa /
NK117(she)001:2633: bstan pa thams cad thugs la rdzogs pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:2634: rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK117(she)001:2635: sprul pa'i sku'i lo ts+aa ba yin par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2637: rgyal po mes dbon rnam gsum sprul pa'i sku yin par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:2638: lha tho ri snyan shal phyag rdor gyi sprul pa /
NK117(she)001:2639: srong btsan sgam po thugs rje chen po'i sprul pa /
NK117(she)001:2640: khri srong sde btsan 'jam dpal gyi sprul par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2641: de yang dang po chos kyi da bu brnyes /
NK117(she)001:2643: tha ma khri srong sde btsan gyis chos dar zhing rgyas par byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2645: bod du rten bzhengs su ma btub pa la /
NK117(she)001:2649: me btsa' bzhi la sogs byas te /
NK117(she)001:2650: lha sa dang bsam yas la sogs te /
NK117(she)001:2651: gtsug lag khang brgya rtsa brgyad bzhengs /
NK117(she)001:2652: der rang byung gi lha tshogs mang po dngos su bzhugs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2653: bzhengs pa'i lha tshogs rnams la /
NK117(she)001:2655: slob dpon pad+ma 'byung gnas la sogs par rab gnas byas te /
NK117(she)001:2656: ye shes kyi lha tshogs dngos su spyan drangs /
NK117(she)001:2657: gnyis su med par bstims nas /
NK117(she)001:2658: rten thams cad kyang chos kyi bsgro ba mdzad par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2661: gnub nam mkha'i snying po la sogs pa dge slong mi bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:2663: gnyan a tsa ra dpal dbyangs la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2664: dpal yang dag gi sgo nas tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK117(she)001:2665: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sogs pa thob ste /
NK117(she)001:2666: lus por ma dgos par sangs rgyas pa /
NK117(she)001:2667: brgyud pa'i lugs re re la yang mang du byung bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2669: lce btsun seng ge dbang phyug dang /
NK117(she)001:2670: bla ma nyang chen po'i ri khrod pa la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2671: rdzogs pa chen po'i sgo nas 'khor 'das gnyis med du rtogs shing /
NK117(she)001:2672: snang srid chos skur shar bas /
NK117(she)001:2673: lus ma bor bar 'gro 'ong med par sangs rgyas pa mang du byung bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2675: rang rang gi brgyud pa'i khung dang sbyar la rgyas par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:2678: rang byung ye shes su gtan la 'bebs yin te /
NK117(she)001:2679: 'og nas gzhi'i skabs su ston pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:2680: dgu pa bgrod pa lam gyi che ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2681: bcu pa mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i khyad par ram che ba ni /
NK117(she)001:2682: gsang sngags kyi gzhi lam 'bras bu'i skabs nas bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2683: spyi don gnyis pa yo ga'i don ni /
NK117(she)001:2684: yo ga'i bye brag phye la a ti yo gar la bzla ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2685: spyi don gsum pa dgos ched ni /
NK117(she)001:2686: spyir theg pa rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:2687: khyad par du rtsol bsgrub can tshi chad pa'i nad dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:2689: don ma nor bar la bzlas nas /
NK117(she)001:2690: rang grol mngon sum du ston pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2691: bzhi pa dril nas mtshan du btags pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2692: chos kun rtsa ba sems nyid dam /
NK117(she)001:2693: rang byung ye shes su 'dus shing rdzogs la /
NK117(she)001:2695: rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2697: mdo sde sa lu ljang pa la sogs pa dpe la mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2698: lang kar gshegs pa la sogs pa yul la mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2699: lha'i bus zhus pa'i mdo la sogs pa zhu ba po las dang /
NK117(she)001:2700: rim gsum dang brgyad cu pa la sogs pa rnam grangs las dang /
NK117(she)001:2701: lam rim dang gsang snying la sogs pa brjod bya las mtshan du btags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2703: phreng ba la sogs pa brjod byed las dang /
NK117(she)001:2706: klong chen la sogs pa don la mtshan du btags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2707: de la sogs pa mtshan gyi 'dogs lugs dang /
NK117(she)001:2708: rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2709: lnga pa dbu zhabs kyi dkyus bshad pa'i tshig gi
NK117(she)001:2710: don ni rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o
NK117(she)001:2711: // gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa /
NK117(she)001:2712: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me zhes bya ba /
NK117(she)001:2713: chos kyi gter mdzod chen po las /
NK117(she)001:2714: chos spyi'i rnam gzhag khog dbub pa'i stong thun bstan pa'i le'u ste dang po'o ////
NK117(she)001:2715: spyi don gnyis pa snang ba rnam pa bzhi'am gzhi
NK117(she)001:2716: lam 'bras bu gsum du dril te bstan pa ni
NK117(she)001:2717: / spyir gsang sngags pa'i lugs kyis /
NK117(she)001:2718: chos thams cad snang ba rnam pa bzhi'am gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du 'dus te /
NK117(she)001:2719: de la dang po snang ba bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:2721: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya yi //
NK117(she)001:2722: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK117(she)001:2723: rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par bzhag /
NK117(she)001:2724: gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo yang //
NK117(she)001:2726: des na snang ba bzhi dag tu //
NK117(she)001:2727: lung rigs kun la gsal bar snang //
NK117(she)001:2729: rdo rje'i dra ba rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:2730: khyad par rim dang gang snang ba //
NK117(she)001:2731: rang bzhin gdul bya bde gshegs dang //
NK117(she)001:2732: 'khrul pa'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK117(she)001:2733: ma bcos ngang la tha dad med //
NK117(she)001:2737: de rtogs dam tshig rgyu 'bras lam //
NK117(she)001:2738: mthar phyir yon tan kun rdzogs 'bras //
NK117(she)001:2740: snang ba bzhi ngos bzung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2744: shes bya rang bzhin gyi snang ba 1 dang /
NK117(she)001:2746: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba 3dang /
NK117(she)001:2747: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang 4ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2750: byed pa pos ma byas pas rang 1bzhin /
NK117(she)001:2751: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bas na rang bzhin gyi snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2752: de ma yin pa der 'dzin pas 'khrul pa /
NK117(she)001:2753: log rtog spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres par snang bas 'khrul 2pa'i snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2754: rang bzhin nam sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pas na gdul bya /
NK117(she)001:2755: bstan pa blo dang mtshams tshad du snang bas gdul bya lam gyi snang 3 ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2756: gzhi dang lam gyi nyes pa zad pa'am /
NK117(she)001:2757: rtogs pa mthar phyin pas 'bras bu /
NK117(she)001:2758: spros pa'i zug rngu med pas bde ba /
NK117(she)001:2759: de bzhin nyid du nar son pas na gshegs pa /
NK117(she)001:2760: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes rang snang bas na 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i 4snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2762: chos kun ji ltar snang yang bcos pa slad med
NK117(she)001:2763: par sems nyid dam rang byung gi ye shes rang
NK117(she)001:2764: snang bas na rang bzhin gyi 1snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2765: de nyid rang gis rang ngo ma shes te /
NK117(she)001:2766: log par rtog pa sna tshogs su snang bas na ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i 2snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2767: blo dang chos su 'dzom nas rtogs shing gom par byed pas na gdul bya'i lam gyi 3snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2768: rtogs pa'i ye shes mthar phyin te sku gsung thugs
NK117(she)001:2769: yon tan phrin las phyogs med du snang ba ni
NK117(she)001:2770: 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i 4snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2771: de rnams kyi lung ni 'og nas ston no //
NK117(she)001:2773: snang ba bzhir 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK117(she)001:2774: chos kun snang ba bzhir 'dus ma 'dus brtags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2775: go rim nges pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK117(she)001:2776: snang ba bzhi'am gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gcig gam tha dad kyi brtags pa dang bzhi'o //
NK117(she)001:2778: shes bya ji ltar gnas tshul la rang bzhin gyi 1snang ba zhes bya ba /
NK117(she)001:2779: de ngo ma shes pas 'khrul pa'i snang ba 2byung /
NK117(she)001:2780: de rtog par byed pa'i thabs gdul bya lam gyi snang ba 3byung /
NK117(she)001:2781: rtogs pa mthar phyin pas 'bras bu bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba 4byung ngo //
NK117(she)001:2783: des na snang ba bzhi po der thams cad 'dus
NK117(she)001:2784: shing snang ba bzhi tshang ba'i gzhi lam 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:2785: gsum du yang bsdur btub bo //
NK117(she)001:2787: go rim nges pa yang de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:2788: de yang snang ba bzhi po de /
NK117(she)001:2790: 'khrul ba'i snang bas bzhi ru byung /
NK117(she)001:2791: lam pa'i snang bas bzhi ru phye /
NK117(she)001:2792: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang bas bzhi ru mkhyen pa yin gsung ngo //
NK117(she)001:2794: snang ba bzhi'am gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum po de ngo bo gcig gam mi gcig /
NK117(she)001:2795: mi gcig na 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:2796: gyi snang ba las ma byung bar thal ba dang
NK117(she)001:2797: / 'khrul pa'i snang ba'i rang bzhin shes kyang mi grol bar thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2798: rang bzhin gyi snang ba mngon du rtogs kyang sangs
NK117(she)001:2799: mi rgya bar thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong
NK117(she)001:2800: ngo // ci'i phyir na ngo bo mi gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:2801: 'dod na lam 'bad rtsol byas pa don med cing /
NK117(she)001:2802: sangs rgyas gtan mi 'byung bar thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:2803: ngo bo gcig na 'khrul grol khyad par med par thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2804: snang ba bzhir phye ba la dgos pa med par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:2805: ngo bo gcig la mtshon tshul tha dad do ce na /
NK117(she)001:2806: ngo bo gcig la ming gis tha dad pa zan
NK117(she)001:2807: dang lab ta la sogs pa 1lta bu yin nam
NK117(she)001:2808: / ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pa
NK117(she)001:2809: bum pa'i steng na byas pa dang mi rtag pa
NK117(she)001:2811: rigs pa'i rgyud gcig la snang tshul gyis ldog pa tha dad pa nam mkha' dang /
NK117(she)001:2812: bum pa'i nam mkha' 2la sogs pa lta bu yin nam /
NK117(she)001:2813: rigs pa'i rgyud tha dad la mtshan nyid gcig pa
NK117(she)001:2814: bum pa la sogs pa mtshan nyid gcig cing ngo
NK117(she)001:2815: bo tha dad pa 4lta bu yin /
NK117(she)001:2816: dang po ltar na 1sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis
NK117(she)001:2817: bde sdug khyad med par thal ba la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:2818: skyon 'ong ngo // gnyis pa ltar na byas pa
NK117(she)001:2819: dang mi rtag pa gnyis rdzas gcig gi steng na
NK117(she)001:2820: dus gcig la yod pa bzhin /
NK117(she)001:2821: 'khrul grol gnyis kyang rgyud gcig gi steng na dus gcig tu yod par thal /
NK117(she)001:2822: 'dod na dmyal ba la sangs rgyas kyi bde ba sngon du yod la /
NK117(she)001:2823: sangs rgyas la dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal yod par thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:2824: ci'i phyir na rgyud gcig gi steng gi ldog pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:2827: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal 'ong bar thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong te /
NK117(she)001:2828: rigs byed kyi mtha' gsang bar smra ba'i sde pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:2829: bzhi pa ltar na mtshan nyid gcig kyang ngo bo
NK117(she)001:2830: tha dad pas gzung 'dzin rang kha ma bden par
NK117(she)001:2831: thal ba dang / dbyer med du gsung ba'i lung rnams 'khrul pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2832: gnyis med rtogs par so sor snang la /
NK117(she)001:2833: chos kyi dbyings sam rang byung gi ye shes rgyun
NK117(she)001:2834: chad par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo
NK117(she)001:2836: tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma 'dres pa'i
NK117(she)001:2837: dbyer 1med dam ma 'dres la yongs su 2rdzogs pa
NK117(she)001:2839: snang ba rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:2840: tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma spang ste /
NK117(she)001:2842: chos kyi dbyings sam rang byung gi ye shes su gnyis su med cing dbyer med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2844: chos kun ma 'dres par so sor snang la /
NK117(she)001:2845: chos kyi dbyings sam rang byung gi ye shes la dbyer med du yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2846: de'ang gcig gis bsdus 1pa'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dang /
NK117(she)001:2847: rgyud tha dad kyis bsdus pa'i ma 'dres 2yongs rdzogs so //
NK117(she)001:2849: rig pa'i rgyud gcig la 'khrul grol gyi mtshon tshul tha dad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2851: rig pa'i rgyud rang ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2852: de yang ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gnyis rang gcig gam tha dad ce na /
NK117(she)001:2853: de gnyis rang yang ngo bo ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'am /
NK117(she)001:2854: ngo bo gcig dang tha dad las grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2855: de rnams rgyas par geg sel dang bcas pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2856: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi skabs nas ston no //
NK117(she)001:2858: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me zhes bya ba las /
NK117(she)001:2859: snang ba bzhi bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o ////
NK117(she)001:2860: spyi don gnyis pa snang ba bzhi po de /
NK117(she)001:2861: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:2863: gzhi lam 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:2866: bya ba gzhi dang byed pa rkyen //
NK117(she)001:2868: ji snyed chos kyi rtsa bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:2871: de nyid dgu ldan sems kyi gzhi //
NK117(she)001:2872: rin chen lam gyis nyams su blang //
NK117(she)001:2873: 'bras bu brtsal med lhun gyis grub //
NK117(she)001:2876: gzhi dang lam dang ngo bo yi //
NK117(she)001:2877: nges pa rnam pa gsum du gsung //
NK117(she)001:2879: de la gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2880: spyir the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:2881: bye brag so so nas rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2885: shes pa mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'o //
NK117(she)001:2886: yang thams cad 'byung zhing 'dus pas gzhi /
NK117(she)001:2887: 'jug cing bgrod par byed pas lam /
NK117(she)001:2888: rtsol med mngon du gyur pas 'bras bu'o //
NK117(she)001:2889: yang gshis rig pa rang snang ma rtog 'khrul pa dang bcas pa gzhi /
NK117(she)001:2890: rtogs shing goms par byed pa lam /
NK117(she)001:2891: rtogs pa mthar phyin pas 'bras bu'o //
NK117(she)001:2893: gnyug ma 'khrul snang ma nor gzhi //
NK117(she)001:2895: ji bzhin nyid du mngon rdzogs 'bras //
NK117(she)001:2896: rang snang dbyer med gcig gi ngang //
NK117(she)001:2898: rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas mtshon pa gang yang mi 'gal la /
NK117(she)001:2899: gnyis pa gegs sel ni gong ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:2900: bye brag so sor nas rgyas par bshad pa la gsum las /
NK117(she)001:2901: dang po gzhi la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:2902: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:2903: de ma rtogs te 'khrul tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:2906: gzhi yi ngo bo mtshan nyid dang //
NK117(she)001:2907: nges tshig dpe yi rnam pa dang //
NK117(she)001:2908: snang tshul gnyer gyis rtogs par bya //
NK117(she)001:2911: gnas pa'i ngo bo mtshon pa'i dpe //
NK117(she)001:2912: nges tshig rnam grangs dgos ched dang //
NK117(she)001:2913: rang bzhin mtshan nyid gnas pa'i dus //
NK117(she)001:2920: rang bzhin nam snang tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:2922: ye nas sangs rgyas par bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2923: gzhi gtan la phab pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:2924: the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:2926: chos kun sel med par sems nyid dam rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:2928: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:2929: rang byung chen pos kun tu khyab //
NK117(she)001:2930: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK117(she)001:2931: sems nyid las ni gzhan ma yin //
NK117(she)001:2934: sangs rgyas sems can la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:2935: thams cad ma lus lus pa med //
NK117(she)001:2936: rang rig ma rig rtog pa nyid //
NK117(she)001:2937: kun kyang rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK117(she)001:2940: rang sems ngo bo nyid kyi lhun grub ni //
NK117(she)001:2941: chos rnam kun gyi rtsa ba rang rig sku //
NK117(she)001:2942: de nyid ye shes chos skur lta ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2943: rgyal ba'i thugs nas dmyal ba yan chad kyi //
NK117(she)001:2944: kun gyi gzhir ni rang byung ngo bo nyid //
NK117(she)001:2948: rig pa mngon du phyungs pas na //
NK117(she)001:2951: 'dod pa'i khams kyang rang byung ye shes yin //
NK117(she)001:2952: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2955: ngo bo thams cad sems yin te //
NK117(she)001:2956: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med //
NK117(she)001:2959: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK117(she)001:2960: sems nyid las ni gzhan med de //
NK117(she)001:2961: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:2962: gdos pa can gyi chos min te //
NK117(she)001:2963: rtog med rang rig 'od gsal ba'i //
NK117(she)001:2964: shes pa 'ba' zhig kho na'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:2965: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:2966: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK117(she)001:2967: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK117(she)001:2970: phyi nang bye brag ci snyed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:2971: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:2972: ci bzhin ngang du ye gnas pas //
NK117(she)001:2973: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK117(she)001:2976: rgyu rkyen las kyis ma byas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:2977: gser gong las byas rdzas rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:2978: ming dbyibs las dngos tha dad kyang //
NK117(she)001:2979: ngo bo gser du gcig pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:2980: rang byung rang snang byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:2983: sems can bsam pa sangs rgyas dgongs pa yang //
NK117(she)001:2984: chos nyid gcig pu gzhan ni ci yang med //
NK117(she)001:2985: ces pa la sogs pa rgyud lung man ngag du ma las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:2987: 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos kun ji ltar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:2988: sel med par sems nyid dam /
NK117(she)001:2989: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bas de nyid kun gyi gzhi yin no //
NK117(she)001:2991: chos kun ji ltar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:2992: rang snang mtha' bral chen po'am /
NK117(she)001:2993: rang byung ye shes las mi 'da' bar 'dzin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:2995: mtshan nyid brjod mtha' kun bral bas //
NK117(she)001:2996: cir yang snang la gzung du med //
NK117(she)001:2999: gzhi rtsa gcig pa'i sems nyid las //
NK117(she)001:3000: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:3001: rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:3002: thams cad rig pa rang gi stobs //
NK117(she)001:3003: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3005: 'khor 'das thams cad 'byung zhing 'dus pas gzhi zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:3007: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:3008: ma lus 'byung bas gzhi zhes bya //
NK117(she)001:3011: ma bcos ye nas kun gyi gzhi //
NK117(she)001:3012: rang byung ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:3013: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba'i gzhir //
NK117(she)001:3014: dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyis gsungs //
NK117(she)001:3018: nam mkha' rgya mtsho rin chen sogs //
NK117(she)001:3019: nye ba'i dpe yis mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3022: cung zad mthun pa'i dpes bzung na 'di lta ste /
NK117(she)001:3025: nor bu rin po che dang /
NK117(she)001:3035: gser rdo rin po che dang /
NK117(she)001:3036: mngon par spro ba bskyed pa lta bu lags so //
NK117(she)001:3039: gzhan yang mtha' dbus med cing /
NK117(she)001:3040: cir yang snang bas nam mkha' dang lung pa'i dbyibs lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:3041: cir yang snang la de nyid las mi g.yo ba /
NK117(she)001:3042: rgya mtsho dang rlabs lta bu la sogs pa ste /
NK117(she)001:3043: gong gi dpe de rnams dgrol lo //
NK117(she)001:3046: sems nyid ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK117(she)001:3047: de min lta ba bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:3048: gnyis med mnyam dang sangs rgyas dang //
NK117(she)001:3049: bdag nyid lhun grub chos dbyings dang //
NK117(she)001:3050: byang chub chos nyid stong bsam 'das //
NK117(she)001:3051: de bzhin nyid dang skye 'gags med //
NK117(she)001:3052: mtha' bral 'das dang grol sogs su //
NK117(she)001:3053: bla dag tsam du brjod pa yin //
NK117(she)001:3056: byang sems lhun grub bde chen dang //
NK117(she)001:3057: rang snang dbu ma mnyam pa nyid //
NK117(she)001:3058: rdzogs pa chen po chos kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:3059: gnyis med bsam 'das ma bcos kyang //
NK117(she)001:3060: ming grangs rgyal bas brjod las 'das //
NK117(she)001:3062: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes las gzhan gyi sel med pas gnyis med dang /
NK117(she)001:3063: mnyam pa nyid la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3064: de nyid mtha' gang du yang ma lhung zhing /
NK117(she)001:3065: mtha' thams cad ma 'gag par rang shar bas ye nas sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3066: chos kun rig pa rang snang la gzhan gyi sel
NK117(she)001:3067: med cing de nyid du 'dus pas bdag nyid chen
NK117(she)001:3068: po dang / rig pa la mu mtha' med pas chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK117(she)001:3069: bcos bslad med pas chos nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:3070: ngos bzung med cing gang gi yang phyogs su ma
NK117(she)001:3071: lhung bas stong pa nyid dang mtha' bral la sogs
NK117(she)001:3072: pa dang / rgyu rkyen gnyen po med par rang snang bas skye 'gag med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3073: rdul cha med cing kun la khyab la /
NK117(she)001:3074: ma bsgribs rang gsal bas byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK117(she)001:3075: 'dus ma byas shing ma sgrib rang gsal bas rang byung gi ye shes dang /
NK117(she)001:3076: rtsol med cir yang snang bas rang snang dang /
NK117(she)001:3077: rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas 'dus ma byas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3078: de las gzhan med pas de bzhin nyid dang de kho na nyid la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3079: rang byung ye shes las gzhan gyi sel med pas rnam dag dang /
NK117(she)001:3080: ka dag la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3081: mu mtha' med cing cir yang 'char bas nges med dang /
NK117(she)001:3082: phyogs med la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3083: ye nas gnas shing 'gyur ba med pas lhun grub dang /
NK117(she)001:3084: mtha' dbus med pas dbu ma dang /
NK117(she)001:3085: chos nyid snying por gyur pas bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po dang /
NK117(she)001:3086: chos kun mu mtha' med cing rang byung ye shes su 'dus pas thig le nyag cig dang /
NK117(she)001:3087: de nyid la chos kun lhag ma med par rdzogs shing /
NK117(she)001:3088: gong na gzhan med pas rdzogs pa chen po dang /
NK117(she)001:3089: chos kun gang yang ma 'dres la chos kyi dbyings sam /
NK117(she)001:3090: rang byung gi ye shes la gnyis su med pas ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3091: de la sogs pa ming gi rnam grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par gsung la /
NK117(she)001:3092: de rnams kyang rgyu mtshan phyogs re nas ming du btags pa gang yang mi 'gal zhing /
NK117(she)001:3093: de nyid rtogs pa'i thabs sam rnam grangs su shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:3094: de rnams kyi lung ni rgyud lung man ngag gsum
NK117(she)001:3095: ka nas shin tu'ang rgyas par ston pas de rnams
NK117(she)001:3098: ming gi rnam grangs su btags pa ni /
NK117(she)001:3099: tha dad nga ji ltar btags pa de ltar chags pa grags pa ste /
NK117(she)001:3101: de nyid dang de kho na nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:3109: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3114: theg pa chen po zhes yongs su grags pa lags so //
NK117(she)001:3116: rang bzhin nam snang tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:3117: rgyu rkyen nam bcos bslad med par chos kun rig pa rang snang ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:3119: ma bcos rgyun gyi skad cig ma //
NK117(she)001:3120: de yis ma byas gang yang med //
NK117(she)001:3123: rgyu rkyen bral ba'i skad cig ma //
NK117(she)001:3124: rang snang nyid du byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:3127: sna tshogs snang yang gzhan byung min //
NK117(she)001:3128: rang byung rang snang ngo bo nyid //
NK117(she)001:3131: gcig pu 'khor 'das kun gyi dngos gzhi ste //
NK117(she)001:3132: ngo bo de nyid rtogs dang ma rtogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:3133: byed pa med par rang nyid cir yang shar //
NK117(she)001:3136: thog mtha' med par dus gsum mnyam pa nyid dam /
NK117(she)001:3137: rgyun chad med par gnas pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:3138: nam mkha' che dang la shan las //
NK117(she)001:3139: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK117(she)001:3140: sngon med phyis med gdon nas byung //
NK117(she)001:3143: thog ma tha ma med pa nas //
NK117(she)001:3144: byung ba snga phyi yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:3147: byang chub kyi sems de kho na nyid gsang ba dam pa de ni /
NK117(she)001:3148: skye 'gags med pa rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3149: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3151: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid la sngon gyi mtha' mi dmigs /
NK117(she)001:3154: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3155: gzhi ye sangs rgyas su bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:3156: gong gi khog dbub kyi skabs su rgyas par bstan pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3157: gzhi gtan la pheb pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK117(she)001:3158: de ltar lung man ngag rigs pa gsum gyis gtan la phab pas /
NK117(she)001:3159: shes bya'i gting phyin par rtogs te /
NK117(she)001:3161: don gyi la zlos nas rang grol mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3163: rang sems tshad ma'i gdengs ldan pas //
NK117(she)001:3164: mi 'gyur don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK117(she)001:3165: lung rigs don gyi bya ra bas //
NK117(she)001:3166: log rtog rkun po rdul du brlag /
NK117(she)001:3169: lung dang man ngag gnyer dag gis //
NK117(she)001:3170: blo gting yid ches 'gyur bar bya //
NK117(she)001:3172: the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba ni /
NK117(she)001:3173: so so skye bo'i snang ba rang ka ma 'di chos nyid yin nam min dang /
NK117(she)001:3174: gshis ka dag yin nam lhun grub yin dang /
NK117(she)001:3175: rno brtul yod med kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:3177: rgyud gcig gam tha dad kyi brtag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3179: snang ba 'di chos nyid yin nam min la sogs
NK117(she)001:3180: pa thams cad gnad gcig tu shes par bya ste
NK117(she)001:3181: / de la snang ba 'di chos nyid min par 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3184: min par 'dod pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:3186: yin par 'dod pa la skyon rgal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:3188: gshis sam don dam pa na stong zhing bdag med pa ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub cing /
NK117(she)001:3189: shes brjod gzhal bya las 'das par 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3190: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis su med cing /
NK117(she)001:3191: dbyings rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa la /
NK117(she)001:3192: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i sel med par 'dod la /
NK117(she)001:3193: 'gro drug gi snang ba 'di kun rdzob bam /
NK117(she)001:3194: 'khrul ba'i snang ba rdzun par 'dod de chos nyid min pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3195: bye brag tu yo ga man chad rang rang gi
NK117(she)001:3196: zhe 'dod kyi lta ba phyogs re la dam par
NK117(she)001:3197: lta zhing / snang ba 'di 'khrul snang rdzun par chos nyid min par 'dod de /
NK117(she)001:3198: rang rang gi skabs nas ston pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:3199: yang gsang sngags nang gi drang don phyogs re dam par lta zhing dgongs pa'i don ma longs pas /
NK117(she)001:3200: snang ba 'di 'khrul snang brdzun par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3202: chos nyid yin na lung man ngag rigs pa gsum dang 'gal te /
NK117(she)001:3203: lung ni theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyi min pa'i lung dang /
NK117(she)001:3205: kye lang ka'i bdag po thams cad snang ba de gsang sngags ma yin /
NK117(she)001:3206: gal te gsang sngags yin na /
NK117(she)001:3207: gsang sngags zhes brjod pa nyid dang 'gal la /
NK117(she)001:3209: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa khyad med par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:3212: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK117(she)001:3213: log par rtog pa tsam nyid las //
NK117(she)001:3214: phra zhing zab pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:3215: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod de //
NK117(she)001:3216: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3219: spyir ni log rtog bsam yas pa //
NK117(she)001:3220: ye nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK117(she)001:3221: so sor 'dzin rtog bag chags kyis //
NK117(she)001:3223: ci yang med la cir yang snang //
NK117(she)001:3224: don gyi snying po 'di las gol //
NK117(she)001:3227: dngos kun log rtog tsam nyid las //
NK117(she)001:3228: phra tsam skad tsam yod min pas //
NK117(she)001:3229: 'khrul pa'i snang ba zhes su gsung //
NK117(she)001:3230: ces pa la sogs pa chos nyid min pa'i lung rnams dang 'gal lo //
NK117(she)001:3232: 'gro drug gis bden pa mthong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:3233: 'khrul pa'i snang ba rgyun chad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3234: gsang sngags kyi nges tshig med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3235: chos nyid skye 'jig can du 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:3237: 'gro drug gi snang ba 'di chos nyid yin na /
NK117(she)001:3238: 'gro drug gis bden pa mthong bar thal /
NK117(she)001:3239: 'dod na 'gro drug ma 'khrul zhing 'bad pa med
NK117(she)001:3240: par grol bar 'gyur ba la sogs pa'i skyon du
NK117(she)001:3241: ma 'ong ngo // ci'i phyir na chos nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:3243: snang ba chos nyid yin na /
NK117(she)001:3244: 'khrul pa'i snang ba rgyun chad par thal /
NK117(she)001:3245: 'dod na 'khor ba dong nas sprug par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:3246: ci'i phyir na gong bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3249: gsang ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK117(she)001:3250: smrar med cing spyod yul du ma gyur pa la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:3252: yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas su brjod pa la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:3254: snang ba 'di smra brjod dang spyod yul du gyur cing /
NK117(she)001:3255: yon tan mi 'dug pas gsang sngags kyi nges tshig med do //
NK117(she)001:3257: khog dbub kyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3259: ma rtog pa'i dus su chos nyid min la /
NK117(she)001:3260: rtogs pa'i dus na yin par 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3261: ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas min la /
NK117(she)001:3262: yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas yin par dang /
NK117(she)001:3263: ngo bo'am bdag nyid gcig pa'i ngos nas yin la /
NK117(she)001:3264: mtshon tshul tha dad pa'i ngos nas min par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3265: de dag gi don rgyas par shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:3267: dang po ma rtogs pa'i dus kyi chos nyid min pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3268: rtogs pa'i dus kyi chos nyid yin pa gnyis gang bden /
NK117(she)001:3269: snga ma bden na phyi ma 'gal la phyi ma bden na snga ma 'gal lo //
NK117(she)001:3270: gnyis ka bden par mi 'thad de /
NK117(she)001:3271: gzhi gcig la yin min gnyis 'gal bas mi rigs so //
NK117(she)001:3272: yang ma rtog pa'i dus na chos nyid min na /
NK117(she)001:3274: de rtogs pa ma yin zhing log shes su thal ba'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:3275: gnyis pa ma 'dres pa de yongs su rdzogs pa yin nam min /
NK117(she)001:3276: min na yongs rdzogs kyi nges tshig med cing /
NK117(she)001:3277: yongs rdzogs rang ma yin par thal /
NK117(she)001:3278: yin na ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas min pa ltar /
NK117(she)001:3279: yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas kyang min par thal /
NK117(she)001:3280: yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas yin pa ltar ma 'dres pa'i ngos nas kyang yin par thal /
NK117(she)001:3281: 'dod na yin min gnyis su 'dod pa'i dam bca' bud do //
NK117(she)001:3282: ci'i phyir na ma 'dres pa nyid yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:3284: mtshon tshul de ngo bo'i mtshon tshul yin nam min /
NK117(she)001:3285: min na ngo bo gcig pa'i dam bca' bud /
NK117(she)001:3286: yin na ngo bo chos nyid yin pa ltar mtshon tshul kyang chos nyid yin par thal /
NK117(she)001:3287: 'dod na mtshon tshul tha dad pa'i ngos nas chos nyid min pa'i dam bca' bud la /
NK117(she)001:3288: ci'i phyir na ngo bo'i mtshon tshul yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:3289: ngo bo gcig kyang mtshon tshul tha dad pas /
NK117(she)001:3290: chos nyid min na ci lto ste /
NK117(she)001:3291: khyab pa ma grub ce na /
NK117(she)001:3292: mtshon tshul de la ngo bos ma khyab par thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:3293: gser las byas pa'i rgyan sna tshogs la gser gyis ma khyab cing /
NK117(she)001:3294: gser ma yin par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:3295: yin par 'dod pa'i lugs la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:3297: de la the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:3299: lha rje chen po rdo phu ba'i zhal nas /
NK117(she)001:3300: 'gro drug gi snang ba rang kha ma 'di //
NK117(she)001:3301: ma spangs pa'i ngos nas chos nyid yin la /
NK117(she)001:3302: mi ldan pa'i ngos nas chos nyid min gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3303: de yang 'gro drug gi snang tshul ji ltar snang
NK117(she)001:3304: yang chos nyid rang snang yin pas ma spangs pa
NK117(she)001:3305: zhes bya'o // 'khrul pa'i snang ba 'di kho na ltar /
NK117(she)001:3306: rang rgyud du mi gnas pas mi ldan pa zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:3307: brda' don sprad pa'i dbang du phye ba yin gsung skad /
NK117(she)001:3308: lha rje chen po shag dang /
NK117(she)001:3309: slob dpon rin chen pa'i zhal nas /
NK117(she)001:3311: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bas /
NK117(she)001:3312: chos nyid du ma gyur pa'i chos gcig kyang med de /
NK117(she)001:3313: 'gro drug gi snang ba so mnyams pa 'di rang chos nyid rang snang yin gsung ngo //
NK117(she)001:3314: de yang gong gi gzhi'i ngo bo dang /
NK117(she)001:3315: rnam grangs la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3316: the tshom gyi gegs bsal ba la gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:3317: chos nyid min par 'dod pas skyon bkal ba bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:3318: chos nyid min na slar skyon brjod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3319: yin par gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3320: dang po lung man ngag dang 'gal ba'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:3322: chos nyid snang ba'i mtha' mi gnas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3323: ma rtog te 'khrul pa'i ngos nas dgongs te gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3324: des na snang ba chos nyid yin par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:3327: gnas brtan rab 'byor gyis bstan te 'gal ba med do //
NK117(she)001:3330: gnas brtan rab 'byor gyis bstan te 'gal ba med do //
NK117(she)001:3331: zhes pa nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi bar du gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3332: tshad ma rnam nges las kyang /
NK117(she)001:3333: don gyi rang rig ngo bor gcig /
NK117(she)001:3334: bdag nyid mngon sum yin pa la //
NK117(she)001:3335: tshad ma rnams kyis brtag bya gang //
NK117(she)001:3336: ma mthong cha gzhan ci zhig yod //
NK117(she)001:3339: gal te snang ba gsang sngags ma yin //
NK117(she)001:3341: de las gzhan na yang gsang sngags yod pa ma yin /
NK117(she)001:3342: gal te de las gzhan pa zhig gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK117(she)001:3343: thams cad chos nyid du ma 'dus par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:3344: thams cad kyi rang bzhin mi snang ba de yang gsang sngags ma yin /
NK117(she)001:3345: gal te mi snang ba de gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK117(she)001:3346: gzhan mu chad pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:3348: des na gsang sngags ni snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:3351: gsang sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK117(she)001:3352: mthong ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pa
NK117(she)001:3353: gnyis kyi ngo bo nyid las grol ba dbu mar
NK117(she)001:3354: mi dmigs pa gang yin pa de kho na nyid
NK117(she)001:3357: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod do //
NK117(she)001:3359: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang med //
NK117(she)001:3360: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyun nyid kyang //
NK117(she)001:3361: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK117(she)001:3362: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid tshul //
NK117(she)001:3366: yul dang shes par snang ba yang //
NK117(she)001:3367: rang byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK117(she)001:3370: rgyu rkyen las kyis ma byas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:3371: gser gong las byas rdzas rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:3372: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3374: rigs pa dang 'gal ba'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:3376: 'gro drug gis bden pa mthong bar thal /
NK117(she)001:3378: gshis yin tshul nas mthong bar thal zer ram /
NK117(she)001:3379: nges pa'i shes pa dang bcas nas mthong bar thal zer /
NK117(she)001:3382: rang byung rang rig mngon sum snang dus na //
NK117(she)001:3383: rang byung ye shes de ni mthong zhes bya //
NK117(she)001:3386: dbang po cer mthong chos nyid gsal //
NK117(she)001:3387: snang ba rgya yan rig pa'i klong //
NK117(she)001:3389: mthong na sems can thams cad grol thal bar 'gyur ro ce na /
NK117(she)001:3391: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pas /
NK117(she)001:3393: snang la ma nges pa'i shes pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3394: de skad du byas pa la /
NK117(she)001:3395: mthong ba rang gi nges shes skye dgos sam ce na /
NK117(she)001:3396: 'o na mthong ba rang gi nges shes skye na /
NK117(she)001:3397: log rtog 'khrul pa rgyun chad par thal ba la sogs pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:3398: phyi ma ltar na gtan tshigs ma grub ste /
NK117(she)001:3399: mthong ba tsam zhig 'dug kyang nges par ma byas so //
NK117(she)001:3401: kun gzhi snang ba gnyis bral te //
NK117(she)001:3402: rtag tu rang mtshan mthong gyur yang //
NK117(she)001:3403: zhen la snang bar ma gyur pas //
NK117(she)001:3404: mig gis mig bzhin ma rig pa'o //
NK117(she)001:3407: grong khyer gsum gyi sems can rnams //
NK117(she)001:3408: thabs dang lhan cig mi gnas pas //
NK117(she)001:3409: bden pa mthong yang nges ma byas //
NK117(she)001:3412: gnyis pa chos nyid yin kyang 'gro drug gis yin
NK117(she)001:3413: par ngo shes nas 'dug pa'i phyir ma 'khrul bar
NK117(she)001:3414: thal zer ram / ngo ma shes pa'i phyir ma 'khrul bar thal zer /
NK117(she)001:3415: snga ma ltar na gtan tshigs ma grub ste gong du bstan pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3416: phyi ma ltar na ngo ma shes pa kas 'khrul pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:3417: 'khrul pa rgyun chad pa'i skyon mi 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:3418: 'o na snang ba 'di rang 'khrul snang yin nam chos nyid yin zhe na /
NK117(she)001:3419: snang ba 'di nyid chos nyid rang snang la /
NK117(she)001:3420: gzhan gyi sel med pas chos nyid yin la ma rtogs pas 'khrul ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:3421: bka' bzhi'i rigs pa yang gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:3422: gsum pa gsang sngags kyi nges tshig med pa'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:3423: snang ba 'di chos nyid rang snang phyogs med yin pas /
NK117(she)001:3424: yul du rtog cing phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyi smra
NK117(she)001:3425: brjod dang spyod yul du ma gyur pas gasnga ba
NK117(she)001:3426: zhes bya la / de nyid rtogs na yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i phyir sngagas zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:3427: des na gsang sngags su ma gyur pa ni gcig kyang med do //
NK117(she)001:3429: gsang sngags kyis ma khyab pa dang mi gnas pa
NK117(she)001:3430: dang gsang sngags su ma gyur pa ni gang yang
NK117(she)001:3431: med / gsang sngags kyi nges pa phyin ci ma
NK117(she)001:3432: log pa rnyed pa'i skyes bu gang la la dag
NK117(she)001:3433: med / / gsang sngags mthong bar 'dod pa'i me long du ni thams cad gyur te /
NK117(she)001:3434: ji lta ji ltar sangs rgyas nas srog chags ldem
NK117(she)001:3435: bu dang nam mkha' nas phra rdul yan chad kyis
NK117(she)001:3436: lhan ne lhang nge lhag ger gsal bar byed pa'o
NK117(she)001:3438: bzhi pa chos nyid skye 'jigs can du thal ba'i skyon sel ba ni /
NK117(she)001:3439: gong gi stong thun gyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:3440: spyi don gnyis pa chos nyid min na /
NK117(she)001:3441: lung man ngag rigs pa gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:3442: lung man ngag gong du chos nyid yin par bstan pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:3444: snang ba chos nyid min na chos nyid rgyun chad par thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:3446: grol ba 'thad par mi 'gyur ba la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:3447: chos nyid mngon sum rtogs pa rgyun chad par dang /
NK117(she)001:3448: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang 'khrul bar thal lo //
