NK117(she)001:10410: don la mkhas pa rab tu gces //
NK117(she)001:10412: rim pa dbang gis bgrod pa rgyal bu do'u 'bangs
NK117(she)001:10413: su 'khyams pa rgyal sar bton pa lta bu ni
NK117(she)001:10414: / lam dang rtogs pa gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i dbang las byung ba yin pas /
NK117(she)001:10415: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba'i dbang la sogs pa bskur bas /
NK117(she)001:10416: ma smin pa smin par byas /
NK117(she)001:10417: smin pa grol bar byas te /
NK117(she)001:10418: rgyud gong nas gang du 'phar nas chos kyi rgyal srid la dbang thob pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:10420: rgyal bu rgyal sar 'don pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:10421: rim pa dbang gi khyad par ste //
NK117(she)001:10422: sa lam rtsal gyis bsgrod pa yis //
NK117(she)001:10423: dbang rnams thob pa rab tu gces //
NK117(she)001:10425: thag lta bas 6bcad pa khyung nam mkha' la lding ba lta bu ni /
NK117(she)001:10426: chos kun mnyam nyid rang snang du rtogs pas phyogs ris re dog med par thag chod pas /
NK117(she)001:10427: gang la yang nyam nga med pa bya ste /
NK117(she)001:10429: khyung chen mkha' la lding ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:10430: theg pa'i spyod sgo bsam yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:10431: mnyam nyid re dog blang dor med //
NK117(she)001:10432: the tshom chod pa shin tu gces //
NK117(she)001:10434: don man ngag gis bsdu 7ba gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bu ni /
NK117(she)001:10435: snyan rgyud zhal gyi man ngag gis mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:10436: ngo sprod pas tshogs med cing bde blag tu 'gyur
NK117(she)001:10437: ba yin te / de nyid las /
NK117(she)001:10438: bsgyur ba sman snang gser 'gyur ltar //
NK117(she)001:10439: sems kyi gsang 'di sus mthong ba'i //
NK117(she)001:10440: man ngag can gyis 'grub pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:10441: man ngag ldan pa rab tu gces //
NK117(she)001:10443: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba rgya mtsho nor len gyi mi lta 8bu na /
NK117(she)001:10444: shes kyang nyams su ma blangs na don mi 'grub cing /
NK117(she)001:10445: rtogs pa'i don la dka' bas nyams su blangs pas rtogs pa mthar phyin te /
NK117(she)001:10446: bdag gzhan gyi don rnams 'grub pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:10448: dper na rgya mtsho nor len mi //
NK117(she)001:10449: nyams su ma blangs don med cing //
NK117(she)001:10450: dka' bas nyams blangs don rnams 'grub //
NK117(she)001:10451: ting 'dzin goms pa rab tu gces //
NK117(she)001:10453: spyod pas 9la dor ba glang po che chur 'jug pa lta bu ni /
NK117(she)001:10454: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya ste /
NK117(she)001:10455: 'bras bu thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa thob
NK117(she)001:10456: par 'dod pa'i brod tshul gyis spyod pa dus dang
NK117(she)001:10457: 'brel par dka' sla gang la yang nyam nga med
NK117(she)001:10460: dper na glang po chur 'jug ltar //
NK117(she)001:10461: rtsal chen sbyangs pa'i brod tshul gyis //
NK117(she)001:10462: nyams nga bag tsam med pa ru //
NK117(she)001:10463: spyod pa dus dang 'brel pa gces //
NK117(she)001:10465: mdo gcig tu 'dus pa mgron po byes nas log
NK117(she)001:10466: nas slar yang rang gi khyim du 'ong ba lta
NK117(she)001:10467: bu ni / theg pa'i rnam grangs ji snyed cig gsungs pa dang lam ji ltar bgrod kyang /
NK117(she)001:10468: sems nyid rtogs par bya ba'i thabs su gsung la /
NK117(she)001:10469: don sems nyid rtogs pa la thams cad 'dus shing rdzogs pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:10471: dper na kun tu rgyu ba'i mi //
NK117(she)001:10473: yul gyi rnam pa mtha' yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:10474: bgrod yul lam gnas gcig las med //
NK117(she)001:10475: de bzhin bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK117(she)001:10476: rnam grangs chos sgo ji snyed kyang //
NK117(she)001:10477: dkri ba drang pa'i tshig yin te //
NK117(she)001:10478: bsam pa'i yul ni gcig pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10479: don rnams gcig tu sdud pa yi //
NK117(she)001:10480: bslab par bya ba dam pa ste //
NK117(she)001:10481: nges pa gcig las med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:10482: kun 'dus dam pa'i bslab pa gces //
NK117(she)001:10484: de'i ngang la gnas pa'i bar chad bsrung ba ni /
NK117(she)001:10485: bla ma dkon mchog la blo bkal te gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10486: snying rje dang byams pas bgegs rigs la gtor ma byin te bden pa'i stobs brjod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10487: mkha' 'gro chos skyong la gtor tshogs btang te las bcol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10488: bsrung ba'i 'khor lo bsgom zhing yi dam lha yi bzlas pa bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10489: rtogs pa'i gdengs dang ldan pas gang la yang nyams nga med par grogs su khyer ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10490: de rnams rgyas par rang rang gi gzhung dang bla ma'i zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10491: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa //
NK117(she)001:10492: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las //
NK117(she)001:10493: lam gyi cha rkyen bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK117(she)001:10497: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum nyid //
NK117(she)001:10498: sems bzhi skye bar bstan pa ni //
NK117(she)001:10500: ngo bo shes rab gsum la bya //
NK117(she)001:10502: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK117(she)001:10504: ngo bo thabs shes rab la bya /
NK117(she)001:10506: 'jig sngang la sogs byang sems lnga //
NK117(she)001:10507: nges par skyes pa ngo bo yin //
NK117(she)001:10509: ngo bo sems lnga la bshad /
NK117(she)001:10511: rtogs nas 'dris par gang byed pa //
NK117(she)001:10512: lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:10514: lam gyi ngo bo byang chub sems la bshad do //
NK117(she)001:10515: de rnams gang yang mi 'gal bar sems kyi 'phel rim du 'dus pas /
NK117(she)001:10516: ngo bo sems lnga'am sems kyi 'phel rim la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10518: de la thog mar bstan pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:10519: skye sa rkyen gyis skye tshul dang //
NK117(she)001:10520: skyes pa'i ngo bo sems pa dang //
NK117(she)001:10521: tha ma rang byung nyid kyis rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:10524: sems skye ba'i gazhi'am skye sa bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10525: rgyu rkyen dang skye tshul lam rim bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10527: gzhi nas sems skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10530: skye sa ma nges pa nas skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10533: mun pa log sred byis pa'i sa //
NK117(she)001:10534: phyogs rim mtha' sel dam pa phyi //
NK117(she)001:10535: drug nas rgyu rkyen dbang gis g.yo //
NK117(she)001:10536: de la 'byung tshul rnam pa gsum //
NK117(she)001:10537: thog ma nyid nas brgyud pa dang //
NK117(she)001:10538: gzhi nas ma nges gang rung bgrod //
NK117(she)001:10539: mthar ni theg rtser gcig char 'jug /
NK117(she)001:10541: gnyis pa rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi ste bgrang /
NK117(she)001:10542: de la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK117(she)001:10543: snying po rang la rang chas su gnas pa dang
NK117(she)001:10544: / lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu gong ma'i yon tan thob pas /
NK117(she)001:10545: 'og ma la skyo gong ma la brod cing dwang ba skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10547: snying po'i don rang bzhin gyis gnas pa dang rang rang gi sa la skyo ba skyes pa /
NK117(she)001:10548: bdag po'i rkyen bla ma dam pa /
NK117(she)001:10549: dmigs pa'i rkyen gsang sngags kyi yon tan la sogs pa /
NK117(she)001:10550: mtshungs pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen /
NK117(she)001:10551: snga ma snga mas go phye nas phyi ma phyi mar 'brel pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10553: snying po rang bzhin mtshungs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:10554: bshes gnyen mgon la lung gnyis thob //
NK117(she)001:10555: yon tan mthong dang skyon mthong dang //
NK117(she)001:10556: de yi skyo rmongs brod dang pas //
NK117(she)001:10557: gnyis pa'i rgyu ru gsung pa yin //
NK117(she)001:10558: de bdag gsang sogs dmigs pa ste //
NK117(she)001:10559: skad cig 'phel ba de ma thag /
NK117(she)001:10562: dpon slob gnyis las dang thugs rje'i 'brel pa yod /
NK117(she)001:10563: slob bu dang bstan pa'i chos gnyis snod bcud dam shes bya shes byed kyi 'brel pa yod /
NK117(she)001:10564: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum bdag nyid gcig pa ngo bo nyid kyis 'brel ba yod do //
NK117(she)001:10566: de ltar rgyu rkyen tshogs pas gong bzhin sems lnga'i tshul du skye ba yin te bgrang /
NK117(she)001:10567: de la g.yo ba byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK117(she)001:10568: gsang sngags kyi don la spro zhing mos pas g.yo ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10570: rtogs shing khong du chud na ci ma rung snyams pa'i 'dun pa dang smon pa byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10572: dngos su gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs te /
NK117(she)001:10573: dbang bskur nas nyan bsam la sogs pa byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10575: rtogs shing gom par byed pa ste lam nyams su len pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10576: mthar phyin pa byang chub ni stobs su gyur te /
NK117(she)001:10577: lam mthar phyin pas skyed du byar med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10578: de yang snga ma snga mas go phye nas /
NK117(she)001:10579: phyi ma phyi ma'i don gsal bar byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10581: snga ma snga ma gang dang gang //
NK117(she)001:10582: phyi ma phyi ma'i thabs dang rgyu //
NK117(she)001:10583: de bzhin phyi ma phyi ma gang //
NK117(she)001:10584: snga ma snga ma las byung 'bras //
NK117(she)001:10586: 'o na sems lnga lam gyi ngo bo yin na /
NK117(she)001:10587: sems lnga mthar phyin pas lam lnga mthar phyin nam ma phyin /
NK117(she)001:10588: ma phyin na sems lam gyi ngo bo yin pa nyams la /
NK117(she)001:10589: phyin na tshogs lam lta bu'i sems lnga mthar phyin
NK117(she)001:10590: pas kyang lam lnga mthar phyin par thal lo zhe
NK117(she)001:10591: na / lam spyi'i sems lnga mthar phyin pas lam lnga mthar phyin la /
NK117(she)001:10592: bye brag gi sems lngas lam lnga mthar mi phyin no //
NK117(she)001:10593: yang sems lnga lam gyi ngo bo yin na /
NK117(she)001:10594: cir char ba la sems lnga skye'am mi skye /
NK117(she)001:10595: mi skye na lam gyi ngo bo yin pa nyams la /
NK117(she)001:10596: skye na cig char ba ma yin par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK117(she)001:10597: cig char ba la sems lnga skye yang /
NK117(she)001:10598: don 'khor 'das dbyer med la dus myur bar skye ste /
NK117(she)001:10599: se gol gcig la'ang sems lnga skye bas gnyis ka'i skyon ming 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:10600: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa //
NK117(she)001:10601: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las //
NK117(she)001:10602: lam gyi ngo bo bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK117(she)001:10606: de'ang rang bzhin sbyangs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:10607: snod du gyur la nye ring phyir //
NK117(she)001:10608: rim dang cig char bzhi cha yis //
NK117(she)001:10612: de nas 'jug pa'i tshul sgo ni //
NK117(she)001:10613: don la rim dang cig char ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10616: rim dang cig char las rkyen gyis //
NK117(she)001:10617: rang gnas ye shes mngon du rtogs //
NK117(she)001:10620: de'ang cig char thod rgal dang /
NK117(she)001:10621: rim gyis ba dang gsum gyis bstan //
NK117(she)001:10626: de la theg pa'i rim pa thod rgal cig char ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10627: lam rim thod rgal cig char ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10628: gnas skabs sam blo rim thod rgal gcig char ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10630: theg pa rnams la rim gyis 'jug cing bgrod pas rim gyis pa ste /
NK117(she)001:10632: bskal pa rdul snyed sngon song bas //
NK117(she)001:10633: thun mong de nyid sbyangs pa'i mtha' //
NK117(she)001:10635: rim gyis sbyangs nas gcig char 'jug /
NK117(she)001:10637: theg pa bor long du bgrod pas thod rgal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10638: de ni nyan thos nas sngags phyi pa man chad
NK117(she)001:10639: go rim med par gang rung nas sngags nang 'jug
NK117(she)001:10640: pa yin te / mdo bsres las /
NK117(she)001:10643: dang po nyid nas theg pa gang la yang ma sbyangs par /
NK117(she)001:10644: ma h+aa dang a nu cig char ba'am rdzogs pa
NK117(she)001:10645: chen po la 'jug cing go nus rtogs nus pa
NK117(she)001:10648: 'gro drug dbang ba'i gcig chod dam //
NK117(she)001:10649: sbyangs pa'i 'phro can gang yang rung //
NK117(she)001:10651: gnyis pa la yang gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:10652: lam lnga la sogs pa rim pa bzhin bgrod pa ni rim gyiis pa /
NK117(she)001:10653: lam bor long du bgrod pa thod rgal ba /
NK117(she)001:10654: cig char du bgrod pa ni gcig char ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10655: de rnams rang rang gi skabs bzhin 'og nas ston to //
NK117(she)001:10656: gsum pa ni theg pa'i lam gyi gnas skabs re
NK117(she)001:10657: re la'ang blo rim thod rgal cig char du skye
NK117(she)001:10658: ba dang / gzhan yang theg pa'am shes bya cig char ba /
NK117(she)001:10659: dang po nyid nas rdzogs chen gyi lta ba 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi don la 'jug cing /
NK117(she)001:10660: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas rtogs
NK117(she)001:10661: grol dus mnyam pa ni cig char ba blo cig
NK117(she)001:10663: shes rab chen pos skad cig la //
NK117(she)001:10664: chos kun khong du chud par 'chang //
NK117(she)001:10665: skad cig gcig gis rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:10666: skad cig gcig gis bye brag phyed //
NK117(she)001:10668: rdzogs chen gyi skabs su blo cig char ba bshad pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:10669: rtogs pa'i don la nyams su len dgos la /
NK117(she)001:10670: nyams la go rim nges med thod rgal du skye ba ni cig char ba'i blo thod rgal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10671: shes bya gcig chod la nyams rim gyis 'char ba ni cig char ba'i rim pas so //
NK117(she)001:10672: rgyas par rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10673: 'o na cig char ba lam la bgrod dang mi bgrod /
NK117(she)001:10674: mi bgrod na lam ma yin par 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:10675: bgrod na cig char ba nyams so zhe na /
NK117(she)001:10676: cig char ba lam la bgrod kyang shes bya cig
NK117(she)001:10677: chod la dus myur bar bgrod pas gnyis ka'i skyon
NK117(she)001:10678: las grol lo // bye brag so so rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:10682: yod shes rab gsum yod kyang /
NK117(she)001:10683: thabs dang gdams ngag la gtso ba la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10685: yod thabs dang gdam ngag yod kyang shes rab gsum gtso ba la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10686: de gnyis mgo 'brel lam ltag shal gyi brtag pa ni /
NK117(she)001:10687: de yang ltag shal ba ni mi 'thad de /
NK117(she)001:10688: spyir thabs shes rab zung du 'brel dgos par bshad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10689: bye brag tu thabs rkyang pas mi grol zhing thabs la shes rab kyis grol dgos par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:10690: yang bye brag tu cig char ba la sogs pa shes rab gcig bus grol la /
NK117(she)001:10691: thabs ched du mi dgos pa yang gsung ste /
NK117(she)001:10693: theg brgyad lam gyi gol sa ni //
NK117(she)001:10694: khyed cag blo dman ma rig pas //
NK117(she)001:10695: thabs dang shes rab 'brel dgos zer //
NK117(she)001:10696: 'khrul pa brtas pa'i rtog pa yin //
NK117(she)001:10697: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:10699: steng sgo rlung dang 'khor lo'i bde ba la brten
NK117(she)001:10700: nas ye shes skye ba bul bas na rim gyis
NK117(she)001:10701: pa'o // 'og sgo phyag rgya'i bde ba la brten
NK117(she)001:10702: nas ye shes skye ba myur bas na cig char
NK117(she)001:10703: pa'o // ba'o // de ltar thabs lam la brten nas rig pa 'byongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10704: shes rab kyi ye shes rang gnas ngo sprad pas /
NK117(she)001:10705: thabs shes rab zung du 'brel te zag bcas kyi bde ba zag med du gyur nas /
NK117(she)001:10706: ye shes rang gnas mngon sum du rtogs nas grol ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:10708: bla ma'i dgongs dang rlung gis dus //
NK117(she)001:10709: sbyor ba'i thabs dang bsod nams las //
NK117(she)001:10710: phyag rgya yon tan ldan gyur pas //
NK117(she)001:10711: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa myong //
NK117(she)001:10712: de phyir thabs su bshad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:10715: rol pa'i ka ra la sogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:10716: man ngag thabs kyis der 'jug dang //
NK117(she)001:10718: rgyas par gzhung man ngag dang bcas pa rang rang gi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10719: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa /
NK117(she)001:10720: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las /
NK117(she)001:10721: lam bgrod tshul dang thabs lam bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK117(she)001:10726: rdzogs pa chen po'i grol lam mo //
NK117(she)001:10729: rang bzhin ye shes rang gnas dang //
NK117(she)001:10731: bar chad med bsgrub rnam par smin //
NK117(she)001:10732: dbang bsgyur phyag rgya lhun grub lam //
NK117(she)001:10733: mngon byas rim par brjod par bya //
NK117(she)001:10735: gzhi ye shes rang la gnas par bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10736: rang gnas rtogs shing goms par byed pa'i lam dang /
NK117(she)001:10737: mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu rang la gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10739: gzhi'i skabs su rgyas par bstan pa bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:10740: bye brag tu shes bya bden pa gsum du bstan pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:10745: chos thams cad rang rig pa byang chub kyis spros
NK117(she)001:10746: bral skye ba med cing snang ba ngo bo nyid
NK117(she)001:10749: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:10750: rang byung chen pos kun tu khyab //
NK117(she)001:10751: rang byung de nyid dngos med par //
NK117(she)001:10752: kun gyi phyag rgya rgyu yin no //
NK117(she)001:10755: bzhin 'gyur bzhin las g.yos med ltar //
NK117(she)001:10756: snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu //
NK117(she)001:10759: don mchog lnga 'bras ye shes dbyings //
NK117(she)001:10760: bdun nam gsum phyir don dam las //
NK117(she)001:10761: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK117(she)001:10762: de kun ngo bo nyid rgyur gnas //
NK117(she)001:10764: de nyid las chos kun ji ltar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:10765: rang rig pa'i cho 'phrul las mi 'da' zhing ye nas chos sku chen por gnas par yin te /
NK117(she)001:10767: rang rig nyi ma'i ye shes nyid //
NK117(she)001:10768: dngos gnyis la sogs byed po'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:10769: cho 'phrul nyid las mi gzhan pas //
NK117(she)001:10770: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi rgyal por 'dod //
NK117(she)001:10773: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:10774: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK117(she)001:10775: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK117(she)001:10776: rang bzhin ngang gis de ltar gnas //
NK117(she)001:10778: kun rdzob ni chos kun rig pa'i cho 'phrul nyid
NK117(she)001:10779: rig pa sgyu ma'i ngo bor cir yang snang zhing
NK117(she)001:10780: / de nyid phung po khams dang skye mched rgyal ba'i dal du ye nas gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10782: phyi nang snod bcud thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:10783: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas //
NK117(she)001:10786: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni //
NK117(she)001:10787: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK117(she)001:10790: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK117(she)001:10791: gzhir rdzogs phyag rgyar ma 'dres gsal //
NK117(she)001:10794: cho 'phrul yul sems tshul nyid kyang //
NK117(she)001:10795: thabs dang shes rab mtshan nyid de //
NK117(she)001:10796: phung sogs yab yum dkyil 'khor du //
NK117(she)001:10797: brgyud min rang bzhin snang ba nyid //
NK117(she)001:10800: sems nyid spros bral skye ba med pa nyid kun
NK117(she)001:10801: rdzob rig pa sgyu ma'i ngo bor cir yang snang
NK117(she)001:10802: la / cir yang snang ba nyid don dam spros bral skye ba med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10803: de gnyis tshig la snga phyi byung yang don la tha dad med do //
NK117(she)001:10804: rang byung gi ye shes rang snang rang grol du bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10806: gzhi rtsa med las thams cad 'byung //
NK117(she)001:10807: med dang yod pa gnyis ka med //
NK117(she)001:10808: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med de //
NK117(she)001:10812: yul dang shes par snang ba yang //
NK117(she)001:10813: rang byung ye shes rang snang zad //
NK117(she)001:10814: rgyu 'bras snang yang gnyis pa med //
NK117(she)001:10815: phyi nang snang ba'ang de nyid dang //
NK117(she)001:10818: gnyis med byang sems ngo bo las //
NK117(she)001:10819: 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid rang gis med //
NK117(she)001:10822: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10823: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK117(she)001:10824: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10827: gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha' lta ba bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10830: gsang sngags mngon sum gyi tshad mas dngos su ngo sprad cing rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10831: he dus gtan la phab cing rtogs par bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10833: stong thun gyi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10835: sngon byung sku lnga dang tshul mthun pa'i tshul gyi he du dang /
NK117(she)001:10838: ngo bo nyid kyi sku yi gsung ngo bo nyid kyi he dus go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10839: chos sku'i gsung gi tshul skye med don gyis go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10840: longs sku'i gsung gi tshul dgongs pa brda' yis go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10841: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung gi tshul grags stong dbyer med kyis go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10842: sprul pa'i sku'i gsungs tshangs pa dbyangs kyis go ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10844: rtogs dang ldan pa'i blo rnams la //
NK117(she)001:10845: dngos po sna tshogs sems gsang sngags //
NK117(she)001:10846: des lung yin phyir chos tshul ston //
NK117(she)001:10847: zhes pa la sogs pa gsung pas /
NK117(she)001:10848: rgyas par de nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10849: tshig gi he du la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:10850: dpyad du med pa'i he du dang /
NK117(she)001:10851: dpyad pas go ba'i he du'o //
NK117(she)001:10853: rtog dpyod rtsibs lnga ba med par gdam ngag bstan
NK117(she)001:10854: par tsam gyis rang snang yul med du go ba
NK117(she)001:10855: yin te / rtog dpyod dmigs 'dzin mi tshol bar //
NK117(she)001:10856: de brjod nyid kyis de nyid mthong //
NK117(she)001:10859: tshig don mi mthun he du dang /
NK117(she)001:10861: snga ma ni thun mong ma yin pa'i ci yang min pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:10862: he du ci yang ma yin par gtan la 'bebs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10863: des mtshon ci yang yin pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:10864: sems chos ci yang ma yin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10865: de phyir ma yin kun yin pas //
NK117(she)001:10866: ci yang yin no lhun gyis grub //
NK117(she)001:10867: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:10870: tshad ma bka' gzhung he du dang //
NK117(she)001:10871: sgra mthun don spags he du'o //
NK117(she)001:10874: gsang sngags rang gzhung gi he du yis mngon sum rtogs par byed pa yin la /
NK117(she)001:10875: phyi ma ni 'og ma pa dang sgra mthun kyang
NK117(she)001:10876: don khyad par du spags te mngon sum du rtogs
NK117(she)001:10877: par byed pa'o // rgyas par gzhung bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10879: ldem dgongs man ngag gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:10880: skabs kyi don gnyis mthong bar byed //
NK117(she)001:10881: dngos po lo rgyus gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:10882: bdag nyid chen po smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:10884: ldem dgongs man ngag he du yis skabs su ngo sprod cing dngos su rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10885: dngos po lo rgyus kyi he du yis yid ches par bya zhing dngos su ngo sprad par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:10886: gtan la 'bebs pa'i grub mtha' lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:10887: gong ltar ngo sprad cing gtan la phab pas /
NK117(she)001:10888: gong gi bden pa rnam pa gsum gyi don de kho na nyid khongs su chud cing /
NK117(she)001:10889: da ltar gyi snang ba 'di nyid rig pa rang snang bas /
NK117(she)001:10890: blta bya lta byed med par yul med rang gsal du rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:10892: dom ma nor ba nyid khong du chud cing /
NK117(she)001:10893: the tshom yid gnyis med par gdeng dang ldan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10895: yul med rang gsal nyams rnyed la //
NK117(she)001:10896: mthong zhes tha snyad btags par zad //
NK117(she)001:10899: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK117(she)001:10900: dmigs med tshul du der snang ngo //
NK117(she)001:10902: don dang sems can rtog med gsal //
NK117(she)001:10903: rang byung ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:10905: rang rig mngon sum dmigs bral bas //
NK117(she)001:10906: rang gsal gsum bral mi bsgul pa //
NK117(she)001:10907: nges par gdeng du gang byas pa //
NK117(she)001:10908: thos bsam byas pa lta mthar phyin //
NK117(she)001:10910: lta bya lta byed med par chos kun rig pa
NK117(she)001:10911: rang gsal du rtogs pa ni lta ba'i nges tshig
NK117(she)001:10913: de phyir lta dang lta byed pa //
NK117(she)001:10914: chos kun rang rig rang snang ba //
NK117(she)001:10915: me long lta bu'i tshul bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:10916: mi rtog gsal bas nges tshig 'grub //
NK117(she)001:10918: de ltar na chos kun sems nyid rang snang du rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:10919: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid khong du chud de /
NK117(she)001:10920: gdod ma nas sangs ma rgyas kyi bar du dmigs phyed cing khong du chud pa 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:10922: lta ba lta ba gtsor brjod mod //
NK117(she)001:10923: don du shes rab kun mnyam nyid //
NK117(she)001:10924: ded dpon rin chen ji bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:10925: gdod matha'i bye brag 'dir shes dgos //
NK117(she)001:10927: de ltar na zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid
NK117(she)001:10928: gi mtshan nyid mngon sum mthong ngam ma mthong zhe
NK117(she)001:10933: chos nyid spyi'i mtshan nyid stong nyid bdag med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:10934: rang gi mtshan nyid yul med rang gsal du mthong ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10937: spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid yod de /
NK117(she)001:10938: don byed nus pa rang gi dang /
NK117(she)001:10943: mi 'gag pa spyi'i mtshan nyid do //
NK117(she)001:10947: snga ma ni zag bcas kyi skabs su /
NK117(she)001:10948: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong na /
NK117(she)001:10949: lung man ngag rigs pa gsum dang 'gal ba'i skyon 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:10951: gzhi gsum pa gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid la 'jug go //
NK117(she)001:10955: de dag zag bcas bsam gtan te //
NK117(she)001:10956: gnyis med yul bral de mthong min //
NK117(she)001:10959: zag bcas kyi skabs su rang gi mtshan nyid mthong na zag med dang /
NK117(she)001:10963: gzhan gyi skyon bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:10965: snga ma ni lung man ngag dang 'gal ba'i skyon mi 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:10966: zag med bzhin du ma mthong ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10967: rigs pa'i skyon yang mi 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:10968: rgyun dum bu ba 'phel 'grib can du yod pas zag med dang khyad par yod do //
NK117(she)001:10969: rgyal ba'i sras dang shing sna'i me //
NK117(she)001:10970: rang mtshan mthong yang stobs ma rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:10972: gnyis pa mthong ba'i lugs ni /
NK117(she)001:10974: bden pa mthong ba dang po zag bcas kyi skabs
NK117(she)001:10975: su rgyun dum bu ba 'phel 'grib can du mthong
NK117(she)001:10976: ba'o // lam rim dang spyan 'byed la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:10977: lta ba'i skabs nas mthong bar bshad pa rnams dang
NK117(she)001:10979: sprin bar nyi 'dra gsal yid ches //
NK117(she)001:10981: mthong ba gnyis pa zag med mthong lam gyi skabs su 'grib pa med la 'phel ba yod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:10983: skabs 'dir bden pa bar ma mthong //
NK117(she)001:10985: zag kun zad pa'i rin chen 'di //
NK117(she)001:10986: ji ltar bshad kyang ldog pa med //
NK117(she)001:10988: tha ma ni sangs rgyas kyi dus su sgrib g.yogs kun dang bral te /
NK117(she)001:10989: gsal ba mthar phyin pa mthong bas 'phel 'grib med par mngon du gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:10991: tha ma'i tha ma zhen bral ba'i //
NK117(she)001:10995: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pas //
NK117(she)001:10996: spang thob gnyis med de bzhin gshegs //
NK117(she)001:10997: zhen mtha' kun bral bde chen gyi //
NK117(she)001:11000: dang po zag bcas kyi skabs su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid mthong ba ni /
NK117(she)001:11001: lung man ngag rigs pa gsum las /
NK117(she)001:11003: rang bzhin ye nas sangs rgyas la //
NK117(she)001:11004: mthong dang ma mthong rnam gnyis las //
NK117(she)001:11005: dman pa'i skabs na de mthong min //
NK117(she)001:11006: mthong ba dam pa'i skabs na'o //
NK117(she)001:11007: mthong bas mngon thos rnam gnyis las //
NK117(she)001:11008: mthar phyin dam pa mngon sum pa //
NK117(she)001:11012: da lta chos skur ma shes na //
NK117(she)001:11013: gsang sngags man ngag ci la che //
NK117(she)001:11014: de phyir bstan shes bsgom ma dgos //
NK117(she)001:11018: rgyu 'bras phyir na cig shos la //
NK117(she)001:11019: yul med rang gsal mngon sum pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11021: lam rim le'u gnyis pa las /
NK117(she)001:11022: lnga dang dmig dbye med phyir te //
NK117(she)001:11023: de bas yul med rang gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11025: gzhan yang khog dbub kyi skabs su chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:11027: gsang sngags kyi lugs kyi zag bcas skabs su chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid ma mthong na /
NK117(she)001:11028: gsang sngags 'bras bu lam du byed pa ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:11029: rgyu lam du byed pa dang khyad par med par thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11030: chos nyid mngon sum du ngo sprod pa'i man ngag rgyun chad dang /
NK117(she)001:11031: rang rig pa'i tshad ma rgyun chad par thal pa dang /
NK117(she)001:11032: mngon sum par rtogs par byed pa'i he du gtan tshigs rgyun chad par thal ba'i skyon 'ongango //
NK117(she)001:11034: gsal ba mthar phyin ma phyin gyi bye brag ste /
NK117(she)001:11035: dper na dbang po'i yul du mthong yang /
NK117(she)001:11036: thag nye ring gis gsal ba mthar phyin ma phyin yod pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:11038: dbang po dang snga ma'i spyod yul las /
NK117(she)001:11039: nye ring drung bzhin stobs 'phel bas //
NK117(she)001:11041: gsal ba'i bye brag rim pas 'gro //
NK117(she)001:11043: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK117(she)001:11045: de yang rang bzhin sbyangs pa yis //
NK117(she)001:11046: snod du gyur pa nye ring phyir //
NK117(she)001:11047: rim dang cig char bzhi cha yis //
NK117(she)001:11049: cig char ba dang rim gyis pa'i bye brag bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:11050: cig char ba'i cig char ba ni /
NK117(she)001:11051: rtogs grol dus mnyam pa gong gi sku lnga dang tshul mthun par rtogs shing grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11052: cig char ba'i rim gyis pa ni /
NK117(she)001:11053: rtogs pa'i don la myong ba'i rgyud brtan pa tsam las lam gyi rim pa med par grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11054: srid pa rdzogs par smin tshul du /
NK117(she)001:11055: lhag pa'i gdeng ldan skyes bu yin //
NK117(she)001:11056: bsgom pa rnam bzhi zung ldan pa //
NK117(she)001:11057: gdod ma nyid nas goms par byed //
NK117(she)001:11059: rim gyis pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:11060: rim gyis pa'i cig char pa ste thod rgal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11061: rim gyis pa'i rim gyis pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11062: snga ma ni lam nges med bor long du bgrod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11063: rgyas par lam rim bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11065: ting nge 'dzin bzhi dang ldan pas bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11066: de yang spyir lam lnga ste /
NK117(she)001:11067: tshogs gnyis mngon du sogs pas tshogs lam dang /
NK117(she)001:11068: lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gyis zag med mthong lam la sbyor bas sbyor lam dang /
NK117(she)001:11069: zag pa med pa'i chos nyid rang mtshan rgyun du mthong bas mthong lam dang /
NK117(she)001:11070: mthong ba'i don la goms pas bsgom lam dang /
NK117(she)001:11071: goms pa mthar phyin nas sangs rgyas pas mthar lam mo //
NK117(she)001:11073: ldog bcas bzhi dang sbyor lam dang //
NK117(she)001:11075: lta ba mngon du rtogs nas de bzhin nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:11076: ting nge 'dzin stong nyid goms par byed pa dang
NK117(she)001:11077: / kun snang gi dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje bsgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:11078: mu tra gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin snang stong zung 'jug rgyal ba'i sku ru bsgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:11079: snang 'byed ting nge 'dzin gyis snang stong zung 'jug
NK117(she)001:11080: mu tra spros pa bsgom pa dang bzhi ni tshogs
NK117(she)001:11081: lam mo // bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa ni sbyor lam mo //
NK117(she)001:11083: skabs 'dir bden pa bar ma mthong //
NK117(she)001:11085: rnam smin dang tshe dbang gnyis mthong lam mo //
NK117(she)001:11086: zag pa med pa bsgom pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:11087: mi g.yo rnal 'byor nyid du'ang brjod //
NK117(she)001:11088: zhes pas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin ni bsgom lam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11089: tha ma'i ming grangs mthar phyin lam //
NK117(she)001:11090: rang rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK117(she)001:11091: de nyid dang ni mthar sbyor lam //
NK117(she)001:11092: yang dag rdzogs pa'i rgyal tshab pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11094: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin ni mthar lam par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11095: de la dang po ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting
NK117(she)001:11096: nge 'dzin gyis chos thams cad sems nyid rang snang
NK117(she)001:11097: la dngos po dang mtshan ma med pas bsgom bya
NK117(she)001:11098: bsgom byed med par ma bcos de bzhin nyid du
NK117(she)001:11099: bsgom zhing / zhi gnas lhag mthong zung 'brel du bsgom pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11100: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med par //
NK117(she)001:11101: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK117(she)001:11102: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:11103: de nyid rang gsal mi g.yo ba //
NK117(she)001:11104: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel //
NK117(she)001:11106: kun tu snang gi ting nges de ltar ma rtog
NK117(she)001:11107: pa'i sems can thams cad la dmigs pa med pa'i
NK117(she)001:11109: thams cad ye shes sgyu ma'i ngo bor gsal ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:11110: snying rje chen po'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK117(she)001:11111: srid gsum sgyu ma 'dra bar ni //
NK117(she)001:11112: rdzogs pa'i byang chub mkhas pas shes //
NK117(she)001:11113: 'gro ba'i ched du go bgos te //
NK117(she)001:11114: 'gro ba de ltar snga nas shes //
NK117(she)001:11115: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK117(she)001:11116: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK117(she)001:11117: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK117(she)001:11118: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK117(she)001:11121: lha yab yum zung gcig lhag pa'i lha dgu nyid dang bcu bsgom zhing /
NK117(she)001:11122: de nyid snang stong zung 'jug rang byung rang snang du bsgom zhing rtsal sbyong ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11123: phyi ma tshangs pa srin po tshul //
NK117(she)001:11124: rdzogs par bya ba zung du 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11126: gzhal yas lha yi dkyil 'khor yang //
NK117(she)001:11127: sems kyi cho 'phrul rang snang phyir //
NK117(she)001:11128: lha la dmigs med rig pa nyid //
NK117(she)001:11129: bzhi rdzogs sku der rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11132: dal dang tshom bu la sogs pa rnam grangs spros par bsgom zhing /
NK117(she)001:11133: snang stong zung 'jug ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rig pa rang gsal du bsgom pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11134: stang dpyal gnyis kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK117(she)001:11135: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor yang //
NK117(she)001:11136: ri rab til 'bru'i tshul bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:11137: dpe byad mtshan gyis brgyan spras pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11139: phung sogs dkyil 'khor lhar snang ba //
NK117(she)001:11140: rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan ji bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:11141: kun dngos rang rig lhar gsal ba //
NK117(she)001:11142: gcig dang du ma yongs kyis med //
NK117(she)001:11144: gnyis pa bar chad med par tshogs bsgrub pa ni /
NK117(she)001:11145: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi byas /
NK117(she)001:11146: bsnyen bsgrub rnam pa bzhis gzhung bsrangs nas /
NK117(she)001:11147: bar chad med par tshogs bsgrubs te //
NK117(she)001:11148: zag med mthong lam la sbyor ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11149: phun sum tshogs pa lnga gzhi la //
NK117(she)001:11150: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi yis gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11151: gang dag mos pa ji bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:11152: zhi dang khro bor bsgrub par bya //
NK117(she)001:11154: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK117(she)001:11155: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK117(she)001:11156: rab 'bring ji bzhin mi bslu bar //
NK117(she)001:11157: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK117(she)001:11159: gsum pa zag med kyi lam gsum la /
NK117(she)001:11160: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:11161: mthong lam la rnam smin dang tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin no //
NK117(she)001:11163: yid lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po'i stobs rdzogs shing /
NK117(she)001:11164: lus lha'am mi'i lus su yod la /
NK117(she)001:11165: lus kyi rgya mdud grol ma thag phyag rgya chen po la sbyor ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11166: lha yi rnal 'byor gsal rdzogs nas //
NK117(she)001:11167: lus kyi dra bas bsgrib 'gyur na //
NK117(she)001:11168: ka la ping ka mi 'jigs bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11169: bral nas snang byed de rnam smin //
NK117(she)001:11171: rgya mig rgya sa ji lta bar //
NK117(she)001:11172: mu tra thob las ma reg pa'i //
NK117(she)001:11173: gzugs rdzogs stobs ldan de kho na //
NK117(she)001:11176: zag bcas kyi lus nyid zag med 'byung ba rdo
NK117(she)001:11177: rje'i lus su gyur cing lus ma bor ba sangs
NK117(she)001:11179: lus khams skye gnas zag pa zad //
NK117(she)001:11180: rdo rje'i lus gyur tshe yi rigs //
NK117(she)001:11181: mthong ba'i chos la mya ngan 'das //
NK117(she)001:11182: lus ma bor bar sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11184: phyag rgya chen po'i rigs 'dzin ni /
NK117(she)001:11185: rang lus rgyal ba'i sku phyag rgya chen po gyur te mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11186: rang sems phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK117(she)001:11187: bsgom pa gang yin mngon gyur sku //
NK117(she)001:11188: thun mong mchog gi mtshan dper ldan //
NK117(she)001:11189: longs spyod gnyis pa phyag rgya'i rigs //
NK117(she)001:11191: lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs 'dzin ni /
NK117(she)001:11192: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa phra mo de bcom
NK117(she)001:11193: nas skad cig ma phyi ma la sangs rgyas pa'o
NK117(she)001:11194: // sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje nyid //
NK117(she)001:11195: lhun mnyam ngang la mi g.yo zhing //
NK117(she)001:11196: mi rtog nyid du bzhugs pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:11197: bag la nyal ba 'joms byed cing //
NK117(she)001:11200: mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas ni /
NK117(she)001:11201: mtshan nyid tha ma'i tha ma ni //
NK117(she)001:11202: ngo bo tshul dang khyad par gyis //
NK117(she)001:11205: 'bras bu chos nyi shu rtsa lnga gsung ste /
NK117(she)001:11206: lus gsum snga ma brjod bya ba //
NK117(she)001:11207: sku dang gsung dang thugs nyid dang //
NK117(she)001:11208: yon tan phrin las rmad byung ba //
NK117(she)001:11209: lnga dang lnga yi ngo bor gnas //
NK117(she)001:11211: tshul ni mar la mar bzhag pa bzhin rgyud du sangs rgya ba yang ma yin /
NK117(she)001:11212: shing gi me dpung ltar sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres pa'ang min te /
NK117(she)001:11213: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11214: don dam gcig pur ma yin phyir //
NK117(she)001:11215: chu la chu ltar gcig pa'ang min //
NK117(she)001:11217: shing gi me dpung ltar brjod pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:11218: drang ba tsam ste de nyid min //
NK117(she)001:11220: mnyam pa gsum pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:11222: tha snyad bral ba'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK117(she)001:11225: grub mtha' so so'i sangs rgyas la //
NK117(she)001:11226: grangs rdzogs ngo bo'i byin rlabs las //
NK117(she)001:11227: snang dang don byed che chung gis //
NK117(she)001:11228: dpag pa'i ngo bo nyid kyis gsal //
NK117(she)001:11230: grangs rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:11231: ngo bo 'dus byas ma byas kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:11232: byin rlabs mngon du snang mi snang gi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:11233: phrin las don byed che chung gi khyad par la
NK117(she)001:11234: sogs pa rgyas par gzhung bzhin du shes par bya'o
NK117(she)001:11235: // gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa /
NK117(she)001:11236: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las /
NK117(she)001:11237: ma h+aa yo ga'i 'dod pa bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK117(she)001:11239: a nu yo ga'i 'dod pa bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:11240: ma h+aa dang shan dbye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11243: yod bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka yod kyang /
NK117(she)001:11244: bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK117(she)001:11245: yod bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka yod kyang rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtsor ston pa a nu /
NK117(she)001:11246: bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi tha snyad las grol ba a ti'o //
NK117(she)001:11247: yang gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum gyi khyad par yod de /
NK117(she)001:11249: ma h+aa don dam pa snang ba 'di nyid dngos su khas len mi nus shing /
NK117(she)001:11250: kun rdzob kyi snang ba sems kyi cho 'phul lha'i dal du 'dod la /
NK117(she)001:11251: de gnyis su med pa ni bden pa dbyer med du 'dod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11252: des na 'khrul pas brtags pa'i snang ba 'di nyid chos nyid du khas len mi nus pas /
NK117(she)001:11253: don dam phyogs 'dzin gyi rgya dang ma bral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11254: kun rdzob kyang sems kyi cho 'phrul du 'dod pas /
NK117(she)001:11255: gzhi ngo bo sems dang bcas shing dngos su mi bden pas /
NK117(she)001:11256: bden rdzun gyi mtha' dang ma bral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11257: dbyer med kyang de gnyis kyi ngo bo dbyer med
NK117(she)001:11258: yin pas mnyam pa nyid kyi dgongs pa mngon du
NK117(she)001:11259: ma gyur pa'o // a nu dbyings sam don dam la nang ba rtsal rdzogs su 'dod cing /
NK117(she)001:11260: 'khrul pas brtag pa'i snang ba 'di nyid chos nyid
NK117(she)001:11261: rang snang mngon sum du snang bar 'dod cing rtogs
NK117(she)001:11262: pas / phyogs 'dzin gyi rgya dang bral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11263: kun rdzob bam ye shes ni /
NK117(she)001:11264: don dam mam dbyings kyi rtsal lam rol pa rang snang bas /
NK117(she)001:11265: gzhi po'i sems gcig ma grub cing bden rdzun gnyis su med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11266: dbyer med kyang ma h+aa ngo bo dbyer med las /
NK117(she)001:11267: a nu mtshon tshul kyang dbyer med cing mnyam pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:11268: des na gazhi'am lta ba la khyad par yod pas /
NK117(she)001:11269: lam bsgom pa la yang khyad par yod de /
NK117(she)001:11270: ma h+aa yo ga'i yan lag gsum gyis lha bsgom zhing bskyed rdzogs rim par bsgom pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11271: spyod pa'ang dam rdzas dang rtsol bsgrub la rag las pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11272: a nu ni lha skad cig dran rdzogs su bsgom
NK117(she)001:11273: zhing bskyed rdzogs dus gcig rang byung rang snang du
NK117(she)001:11275: spyod pa'ang dam rdzas dang rtsol ba la rag ma
NK117(she)001:11276: las shing lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin la 'dus
NK117(she)001:11277: par gsungs so // 'bras bu ni lta ba la
NK117(she)001:11278: khyad par yod pas de mngon du byas pa 'bras
NK117(she)001:11279: bu la khyad par yod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11280: gshis dag par byar med cing rtsol med bde ba chen por gnas pa la /
NK117(she)001:11281: rtsol bsgrubs kyis dag par byas pas 'bras bu sku lnga thob kyang /
NK117(she)001:11282: shes bya ji lta ba bzhin mngon sum du gyur ma gyur gyi khyad par yod de /
NK117(she)001:11283: rang rang gi 'bras bu'i skabs nas ston pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:11284: rang gi 'dod pa bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:11286: gzhi dang thabs dang 'bras bu yi //
NK117(she)001:11287: tshul gsum 'bebs pa'i don du bshad //
NK117(she)001:11290: gzhi ni spyir gzhi'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:11291: bye brag tu dbyings ye shes sam dal gsum du 'dus te /
NK117(she)001:11292: de la dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras
NK117(she)001:11293: bde ba chen po dang dal rnam pa gsum du
NK117(she)001:11294: yang bstan pa'o // dang po la gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:11295: yul du snang ba thams cad chos dbyings mu mtha' med pas yum kun tu bzang mo /
NK117(she)001:11296: de nyid ma bsgrib rig pa rang gsal bas ye shes sam yab kun tu bzang po /
NK117(she)001:11297: de gnyis 'du 'bral med cing gnyis su med pas sras bde ba chen po de /
NK117(she)001:11299: snod du gyur pa yum gyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:11300: bcud rnams rgyal ba yab kyi mkha' //
NK117(she)001:11302: 'di ni rdo rje dam tshig yin //
NK117(she)001:11306: gang yang sems las gzhan min pas /
NK117(she)001:11307: rang bzhin cir yang ma skyes phyir //
NK117(she)001:11308: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK117(she)001:11309: kun gzhi bzang mo'i mkha' klong las //
NK117(she)001:11310: cir yang snang ba yum gyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:11315: ma skyes rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK117(she)001:11316: rtsal rdzogs rol pa rang snang bas //
NK117(she)001:11317: grangs mdog ma nges sku gsung thugs //
NK117(she)001:11318: rang snang phyag rgya bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:11319: kun bzang rol phyir blang dor med //
NK117(she)001:11321: dbyer med dam sras bde chen ni //
NK117(she)001:11322: rang snang rol pa bsam yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:11323: ba ga'i klong las g.yos med de //
NK117(she)001:11325: sangs ma rgyas pa gcig med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11327: dal gsum ni khog dbub kyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:11329: chos kun ji ltar snang yang rang byung gi ye shes sems nyid rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11331: srid pa'i sems can thams cad dang //
NK117(she)001:11332: thar pa chos kyi rnam grangs kun //
NK117(she)001:11333: so sor snang ba ma yin te //
NK117(she)001:11334: kun kyang mnyam pa nyid du gsal //
NK117(she)001:11337: phyi nang bye brag ji snyed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:11338: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:11339: ji bzhin ngang du ye gnas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:11340: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK117(she)001:11342: lam ni rtogs nas nyams su len par byed pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11343: de yang rtogs pa'i lta ba dang rtogs nas nyams su blang ba'i rim pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11346: rtogs pa'i lta ba gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:11348: lung man ngag rig pa'i sgo nas rtogs par bya ste /
NK117(she)001:11349: khog dbub stong thun gyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:11350: rgyas par 'dod na gud na rgyas par yod do //
NK117(she)001:11352: chos kun ji ltar snang yang rang byung gi ye
NK117(she)001:11353: shes rang snang bas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su
NK117(she)001:11354: med cing mthong bya mthong byed med pa yul med
NK117(she)001:11356: gol sgrib kyi dmig byed ji bzhin pa nyid du
NK117(she)001:11357: thag chod nas the tshom dang yid gnyis med pa'o
NK117(she)001:11359: gnyis su lta ba ma skyes phyir //
NK117(she)001:11360: gnyis kyi 'du shes ni byung yang //
NK117(she)001:11361: rang byung zhi ba ma bkag chos //
NK117(she)001:11362: ye nas ma bcos don gyis gsal //
NK117(she)001:11364: chos nyid dbyings su ro gcig phyir //
NK117(she)001:11365: shes dang shes bya gnyis med de //
NK117(she)001:11366: ye nas shes nyid chos shes na //
NK117(she)001:11367: chos nyid gzhan nas btsal mi dgos //
NK117(she)001:11370: mtha' yas ji snyed chos kun gyi //
NK117(she)001:11371: rang bzhin ji ltar gnas pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11372: ma bcos phyin ci ma log pa //
NK117(she)001:11373: de bzhin nyid du thag chod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11376: ye shes rang snang nam mkha' la //
NK117(she)001:11377: nam mkha' nyid du snang bar zad //
NK117(she)001:11378: mthong ba med pa'i don de nyid //
NK117(she)001:11379: yid kyi ngo la snang gyur pa //
NK117(she)001:11380: lta ba med pa'i lta ba ni //
NK117(she)001:11381: 'di ni lta ba dam pa dang //
NK117(she)001:11383: rtogs nas goms pa'i lam bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:11387: rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam pa'i gcig char ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11388: rtogs pa'i don la myong ba'i rgyu brten pa tsam
NK117(she)001:11389: gyis lam gyi rim pa med par grol ba pa'o
NK117(she)001:11391: tshul gyi he du la sogs pa yis lta ba yul med rang gsal cig chod du rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:11392: bsgom pa yang cig chod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11393: rtogs grol dus mnyam pas 'bras bu cig char du sangs rgya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11395: sa dang sa yi 'byung gnas pa //
NK117(she)001:11396: kun gzhi kun gyi sa yin te //
NK117(she)001:11397: gang gis sa chen 'di non na //
NK117(she)001:11398: sa rnams skad cig tsam bgrod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11401: de bas mnyam pa'i don 'di la //
NK117(she)001:11402: btud de gcig char 'jug shes na //
NK117(she)001:11403: bsgom pa'i yun ni ring thung dang //
NK117(she)001:11404: las 'phro yod dang med pa dang //
NK117(she)001:11405: nam zhig mnyam pa'i khar ma lus //
NK117(she)001:11408: gang dag blo chen mngon rtogs pas //
NK117(she)001:11409: mnyam nyid yul bral rang gsal bar //
NK117(she)001:11410: mi g.yo cig char gang 'jug pa //
NK117(she)001:11411: sa dang lam gyi grangs rtsol med //
NK117(she)001:11414: rtogs pa'i don la dran pa'i rgyun brten nas /
NK117(she)001:11415: bsgom bya bsgom byed med pa rang lugs rtsol med du nyams su blangs pas /
NK117(she)001:11416: nyams dang yon tan phyogs med du shar nas grol bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:11418: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsam gtan ni //
NK117(she)001:11419: ji bzhin pa yi de nyid la //
NK117(she)001:11420: ma bcos pa yi blo bzhag ste //
NK117(she)001:11424: skad cig tsam gyi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK117(she)001:11425: sgrib pa'i phung po phyags par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11426: ji ltar mar mes mun bsal ltar //
NK117(she)001:11427: mun nyid snang bar 'gyur ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11428: skad cig ma yi don rig pas //
NK117(she)001:11429: sngon nas bsags pa'i mun pa sel //
NK117(she)001:11432: de nyid las mtha' zhi gnas dang //
NK117(she)001:11433: lhag pa'i don mthong 'dres pa yi //
NK117(she)001:11434: sde gsum nges par rdzogs pas na //
NK117(she)001:11435: 'bum phrag mtha' yas brjod mi long //
NK117(she)001:11438: rgya mtsho dwangs ba'i nyi zla ltar //
NK117(she)001:11439: sems ni chu gsal nam mkha' la //
NK117(she)001:11440: dngos grub nyi zla skar tshogs bkram //
NK117(she)001:11441: rang byung rang snang the tshom med //
NK117(she)001:11442: ltas dang sbyar la bsgrub mi dgos //
NK117(she)001:11443: don mthong yon tan dus gcig 'char //
NK117(she)001:11447: gcig shos 'jug pa lnga dang bcu //
NK117(she)001:11448: spros pas bzhi bcur gyur pa yin //
NK117(she)001:11450: rim 'jug dbang po rab lnga phrag dang /
NK117(she)001:11452: tha ma sum cu rtsa bzhi phrag gam /
NK117(she)001:11453: bzhi bcu phrag tu bgrod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11454: de rnams rgyas par 'dod na gud na bris nas yod pas der blta'o //
NK117(she)001:11455: tha ma mngon du byas pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK117(she)001:11457: gzhan rnams rdzogs chen gyi 'bras bu'i skabs nas 'chad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11458: 'dir shes bya ji lta ba nyid mngon du gyur
NK117(she)001:11459: pas yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod pa
NK117(she)001:11461: bsdu na sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ru 'dus par gsung ste /
NK117(she)001:11464: bya med mthong gom mthar phyin pas //
NK117(she)001:11465: lnga bcu'i sa mthar gang phyin pa //
NK117(she)001:11466: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK117(she)001:11467: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK117(she)001:11469: dwang ba'i chu dang me long dang //
NK117(she)001:11470: nyi zla gza' skar bzhin tshul du //
NK117(she)001:11471: 'du shes zad pa'i rang rig nyid //
NK117(she)001:11472: dpag med yon tan ngo bor shar //
NK117(she)001:11475: lang ka'i bdag po de yang min pa zhig yin par bsgrub pa'am /
NK117(she)001:11476: mi 'dra ba zhig 'dra bar bcos pa ni ma yin gyis /
NK117(she)001:11478: ma byas ma brtsams par ye nas rang bzhin gyis de ltar yin pa nyid du zad do //
NK117(she)001:11482: ngo bo bsam yas bsdus pas lnga //
NK117(she)001:11483: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan dang //
NK117(she)001:11484: mdzad pa'i phrin las nyid dang lnga //
NK117(she)001:11486: ngo bo sku rnam pa lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:11489: yon tan lnga dang phrin las lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:11492: ngo bo nyid dang gsang ba dang //
NK117(she)001:11493: chos dang longs spyod sprul pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11495: mi mthun gnyen po med par gnas lugs ji bzhin
NK117(she)001:11496: pa nyid mngon du gyur pas ngo bo nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:11497: sku dang / chos dbyings skye ba med cing rnam
NK117(she)001:11498: par dag pa nyid sgrib g.yog dang bral bas chos
NK117(she)001:11499: sku dang / kyi sku'o // sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan zhing /
NK117(she)001:11500: dgongs pa bde ba chen por longs spyod pas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK117(she)001:11501: thugs rje'i rnam 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK117(she)001:11502: dag pa dang dag pa'i sems can la gang la gang 'dul du sprul pa ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK117(she)001:11503: ngo bo dbyer med cing gsang ba dam pa bde ba chen po ni gsang ba'i sku'o //
NK117(she)001:11505: sprul pa ni gang med pa las rgyun gyis 'byung ba la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11506: rdzogs longs spyod pa ni smin pa phun sum tshogs pa la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11507: chos kyi sku ni yongs su rnam par dag pa la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11508: ngo bo nyid ni ji bzhin pa de nyid la bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11511: ngo bo nyid kyi gsung ni ma brjod ngo bo nyid kyis go ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11513: rang gsal byin gyis brlabs kyis mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11514: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i gsung ni dgongs pa brda' yis mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11515: gsang ba'i sku'i gsung ni gsang ba'i brda' yis mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11516: sprul pa'i sku'i gsung ni tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi sgo nas tshig gis mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11518: gang ngo bo nyid med pa'i gsung ni nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:11519: rnam par dag pa'i gsung ni nyi ma'i snying po lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:11520: yongs su smin pa'i gsung ni me long lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:11521: gsang ba dam pa'i gsung ni seng ge lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:11522: rgyun du 'byung ba'i gsung ni gsung gcig la yan lag bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11524: gsum pa thugs ye shes lnga ni stong nyid dam
NK117(she)001:11525: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes ni chos kun mtshan
NK117(she)001:11526: ma med par rang gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11527: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni chos dbyings sgrib
NK117(she)001:11528: pa med cing rtog pa med par rang gsal ba'o
NK117(she)001:11529: // mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes ni /
NK117(she)001:11530: bzang ngan che chung med par mnyam pa nyid du gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11531: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes ni /
NK117(she)001:11532: chos kun bye brag ma 'dres par gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11533: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni rtsol bsgrub med par bya ba byed cing dgos 'dod 'byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11535: kha cig tu ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11536: kha cig tu ni rnam dag gsal ba'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11537: kha cig tu ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11538: kha cig tu ni so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11539: kha cig tu ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11542: stong nyid thugs ni nam mkha' bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11543: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:11544: chen po lta bu'i ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:11545: sna tshogs bkod pa'i ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:11546: yid bzhin nor bu'i ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:11549: bde ba chen po la sogs pa zhing khams yon tan can dang /
NK117(she)001:11550: rin po che snang ba las grub cing mdzes par brgyan pa'i gzhal yas khang yon tan can dang /
NK117(she)001:11551: thugs rje'i 'od zer snang ba'i rtags su 'od zer
NK117(she)001:11552: rnam pa lnga la sogs pa 'od zer yon tan
NK117(she)001:11553: can dang / mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK117(she)001:11554: nyi zla pad+ma la sogs pa'i gdan dang rin po che dang /
NK117(she)001:11555: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan zhing rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:11556: rgyan sna tshogs la sogs pa rgyan yon tan can
NK117(she)001:11558: zhing khams gzhal yas 'od zer dang /
NK117(she)001:11559: gdan khri rgyan rnams zad 'phel med //
NK117(she)001:11561: lnga pa phrin las lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:11566: rigs lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis gang la
NK117(she)001:11567: gang 'dul du ji ltar 'tsham pa ltar don mdzad
NK117(she)001:11569: tshad med phrin las zhi drag dang //
NK117(she)001:11570: dbang rgyas lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11572: rgyas par gegs sel dang bcas pa 'og nas ston no //
NK117(she)001:11573: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa /
NK117(she)001:11574: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las /
NK117(she)001:11575: a nu yo ga'i 'dod pa bstan pa'i le'u ste /
NK117(she)001:11577: rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs shing nyams su blang ba la bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:11578: 'og ma a nu man chad dang shan dbye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11579: bye brag gi gol sa bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:11580: rdzogs pa chen po'i che ba'am yon tan dang /
NK117(she)001:11581: rtogs shing grol ba'i thabs bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11588: lung man ngag la sogs pa'i khung dang khyad par ni /
NK117(she)001:11589: rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:11590: snang ba bcu bdun pa la sogs pa las kyang /
NK117(she)001:11591: ma h+aa yo ga don dam du //
NK117(she)001:11592: rang rig gnyis med de bzhin nyid //
NK117(she)001:11593: rtogs pa'i cho 'phrul la sogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:11594: lhar snang ngang la 'khor ba med //
NK117(she)001:11596: a nu yo ga don dam du //
NK117(she)001:11597: bde chen rtogs pa'i rig rtsal bas //
NK117(she)001:11598: kun rdzob lha yi dkyil 'khor snang //
NK117(she)001:11599: de phyir skye bos brtags pas 'khrul //
NK117(she)001:11601: a ti yo ga bden gnyis bral //
NK117(she)001:11602: thams cad rang byung rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11604: ma h+aa yo ga pas snang ba sems kyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK117(she)001:11605: a nus sems kyi rtsal snang bar 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11606: a tis ni 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:11607: thams rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bas khyad
NK117(she)001:11608: par yod de / 'og ma gnyis ni sems la snang ba cho 'phrul dang rtsal du 'dod pas /
NK117(she)001:11609: gzhi ngo bo sems su lta zhing shugs kyis 'dzin pa'i cha dang ma bral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11610: a ti ni chos kun rang byung ye shes la
NK117(she)001:11611: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas chos kun mnyam pa
NK117(she)001:11613: yang ma h+aa snang ba chos nyid du 'dod la /
NK117(she)001:11614: brtags zhen chos nyid du mi 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11615: brtags zhen chos nyid du mi 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11616: a nu snang brtags gnyis chos nyid du 'dod la zhen pa mi 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11617: a ti chos kun rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum snang bas /
NK117(she)001:11618: zhen pa bcos bslad med par chos nyid rang snang du 'dod cing /
NK117(she)001:11619: chos nyid min pa'i chos gcig kyang med pa'o gsung ngo //
NK117(she)001:11621: rang bzhin nyid mthun rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:11622: de phyir lta sogs khyad par bas //
NK117(she)001:11624: bskyed rdzogs gnyis sems nyid rang snang bar mthun la /
NK117(she)001:11625: shes bya gting phyin ma phyin gyi khyad par yod de /
NK117(she)001:11626: ma h+aa bden pa gnyis dang /
NK117(she)001:11627: a nu dbyings ye shes gnyis med la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:11628: phyogs 'dzin gyi zhen pa yis bden pa ldog mi
NK117(she)001:11629: thub la / shes bya lhag ma dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11630: a ti ni bden pa ldog thub cing shes bya
NK117(she)001:11631: lhag ma med par chos kun rang snang mnyam pa
NK117(she)001:11633: gnyis dang gnyis med kyi phyogs la mi gnas cing rang grol lo //
NK117(she)001:11635: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:11636: 'gyur ba min zhing drang por gnas //
NK117(she)001:11637: nam mkha' bzhin du mtha' mnyam la //
NK117(she)001:11638: gzhan ltos 'gyur ba'i chos ma yin //
NK117(she)001:11641: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:11642: bden pa gnyis kyis bsnyad las 'das //
NK117(she)001:11645: mnyam pa nyid kyis dpag pa'i thabs mchog 'di //
NK117(she)001:11646: theg pa kun gyi yang tsar mnyam par bzhag /
NK117(she)001:11647: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11651: mtshan bcas mtshan med dang bsnyen bsgrub bzhi la sogs pa rtsol bsgrubs las ma 'das la /
NK117(she)001:11652: a ti ni bsgom bya bsgom byed med par rang nyid kyi ngang bsgom yin te /
NK117(she)001:11653: ye shes klong du phyin pa la ma yengs don dang mi 'bral ba'i dgongs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11655: 'og ma gnyis bya byed rtsol bsgrub can la /
NK117(she)001:11656: a ti ni bya byed rtsol bsgrub med la bya bral bde ba chen por gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11658: 'og ma gnyis zhe 'dod rtsol bsgrub kyis bsgrub pas /
NK117(she)001:11659: shugs kyis spang thob can du 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:11661: shes bya ji lta ba nyid che ba lngar sangs rgyas la /
NK117(she)001:11662: de nyid bcos pa med par mngon du byas pas spang thob lhag ma med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:11663: rgyas par rang rang gi skabs nas gsal zhing ston to //
NK117(she)001:11665: a ti la skur pa 'debs pa'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK117(she)001:11666: kha 'byams tshig gi lta bar gol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11667: ma rtog pa'i bsgom par gol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11668: a ti la ltos nas a nu man chad kyang gol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:11670: rdzogs pa chen po bstan pa nam mkha' dang 'dra zhing theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK117(she)001:11671: bstan pa thams cad kyi snying po 'di la blo
NK117(she)001:11672: chung phyogs 'dzin can rnams kyis skur pa btab pas
NK117(she)001:11673: / nam mkha' gnas kyi bar du dmyal bar 'gro bar gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:11675: gang zhig gsang ba'i gsung mchog la //
NK117(she)001:11676: gang zhig spong zhing skur btab pa //
NK117(she)001:11677: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog spangs ba yis //
NK117(she)001:11678: thar pa'i sems dang gtan du bral //
NK117(she)001:11680: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:11681: de don rdzogs chen snying po'i don bshad du //
NK117(she)001:11682: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' skrag /
NK117(she)001:11683: rgyud lung rnal 'byor sgro skur 'debs shing 'phya //
NK117(she)001:11684: tshul 'chos sde pa zhe sdang dbang gis phrag dog byed //
NK117(she)001:11685: nges don 'di la 'gal sems sdig can rnams //
NK117(she)001:11686: dmyal bar nges 'gro gtan du snying re rje //
NK117(she)001:11689: don bstan skad cig de nyid la //
NK117(she)001:11690: rgyud lung sangs rgyas skrag cing sdangs //
NK117(she)001:11691: nyan thos mdo sde brgyal zhing 'bogs //
NK117(she)001:11692: lha dang lha min srin po'i tshogs //
NK117(she)001:11693: sgro skur 'debs pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK117(she)001:11694: gtan du dmyal ba chen por ltung //
NK117(she)001:11697: khyed kyis gzhan la spel bar mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:11698: gal te spel na gang zag de nyid kyis //
NK117(she)001:11699: kun bzang dgongs pa 'di la gshe gyur na //
NK117(she)001:11700: nam mkha' ci srid gnas kyi bar du ni //
NK117(she)001:11701: shi ba'i 'og tu rdo rje dmyal bar 'gro //
NK117(she)001:11704: bstan pa'i snyigs ma tha ma'i tshe //
NK117(she)001:11705: nyon mongs sdug bsngal des drag pas //
NK117(she)001:11706: 'khor ba'i chos la yid dbyung zhing //
NK117(she)001:11707: bstan pa'i sgor zhugs chos byed kyang //
NK117(she)001:11708: bstan snyigs grub mtha' ngan pa yis //
NK117(she)001:11709: chos la phyogs dang ris bzung nas //
NK117(she)001:11710: log rtog rtsod pa 'phel ba dang //
NK117(she)001:11711: nyon mongs phrag dog dbang gis ni //
NK117(she)001:11712: chos pas chos spang las byed 'byung //
NK117(she)001:11713: phyogs bral mnyam nyid ma rtogs par //
NK117(she)001:11714: byis pa'i blo can rmongs pa'i mis //
NK117(she)001:11716: rang chos bstod cing gzhan la smod //
NK117(she)001:11717: bstan pa'i snying po gsang sngags la //
NK117(she)001:11720: de sogs chos spong las byed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:11721: snyigs ma'i dus kyi chos pa ni //
NK117(she)001:11722: bye ba'i sgro ba kha sbubs ltar //
NK117(she)001:11723: rdo rje dmyal dang mnar med sogs //
NK117(she)001:11725: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud lung man ngag tu ma las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11727: chos kun rang byung ye shes mngon sum du snang zhing ye nas sangs rgyas pa nyid /
NK117(she)001:11728: blo che ba rnams la da ltar gyi snang ba
NK117(she)001:11729: 'di nyid ma bcos ma bslad par 'khor ba rang
NK117(she)001:11730: grol lam gnyis med rang snang du ngo sprad pas
NK117(she)001:11732: snang srid chos skur shar nas /
NK117(she)001:11733: sa dang lam gyi grangs rtsol med par sangs rgya bar gsung pa la /
NK117(she)001:11734: de ltar ma rtogs te 'khrul grol gyi shan ma
NK117(she)001:11735: phyed par kha 'byams tshig gis lta ba la mngon
NK117(she)001:11737: snang ba 'di ka ltar sangs rgyas yin zhes dngos
NK117(she)001:11738: po rang kha mar smra ba ni gol sar gsung
NK117(she)001:11739: te / nam mkha' mtha' mnyam las /
NK117(she)001:11740: skal med sgra bzhin spyod pa dag /
NK117(she)001:11742: rang gi rnam rtog mi mthun pas //
NK117(she)001:11743: rang gsal gnyis med ye shes la //
NK117(she)001:11744: yin dang ma yin char 'dzin cing //
NK117(she)001:11748: gshog ma rgyas par 'phur mi nus //
NK117(she)001:11749: nyams su ma blang kha tshig gis //
NK117(she)001:11750: chags sdang zil gyis mi non te //
NK117(she)001:11751: skye bo rang rgyud pa ru gol //
NK117(she)001:11753: ye shes gting nas rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:11754: yang dag don gyi lta ba'i gdeng med par //
NK117(she)001:11755: tshig gam lung las chos kyi khug phyungs nas //
NK117(she)001:11756: byar med chos kyi nga rgyal blo gtang nas //
NK117(she)001:11757: lung ngag rtsing chos phags ral spyod byed pa //
NK117(she)001:11758: sangs rgyas kyis kyang 'khor ba mi skyob ste //
NK117(she)001:11759: sdug bsngal ya nga'i 'bras bu the tshom med //
NK117(she)001:11761: rang byung bde ba'i 'khor lo las /
NK117(she)001:11762: dper na bya sgro rlung khyer ltar //
NK117(she)001:11763: nges med gzhi la blo gtad pas //
NK117(she)001:11764: ma rtogs rtsol bsgrub ci spyad kyang //
NK117(she)001:11765: mi grol dug lnga rgyas par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11768: lta spyod log pa'i nga rgyal can //
NK117(she)001:11769: ma bcos rang snang rol pa dang //
NK117(she)001:11770: rnam rtog zhen pas brtag pa dag /
NK117(she)001:11771: bye brag ma phyed rmongs pa'i blo //
NK117(she)001:11772: rdo la gser du 'dzin pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11773: 'od gsal lhun grub rang snang dang //
NK117(she)001:11774: brtag pa'i zhen pa bsres nas smra //
NK117(she)001:11775: ma bcos rig pa'i gdeng med par //
NK117(she)001:11776: lta ba yang rab mthong 'dod pa //
NK117(she)001:11777: bag chol 'dod lnga spyod pas log /
NK117(she)001:11778: de yi dus kyi gang zag rnams //
NK117(she)001:11779: sbrel ma g.yang du ltung ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11780: rdo rje khab tu lhung gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:11781: byang chub sems kyi rigs dang bral //
NK117(she)001:11784: snying rje med pa'i gang zag rnams //
NK117(she)001:11785: deng sang dus na 'byung ba dag /
NK117(she)001:11786: kun bzang tshig tsam smra byed cing //
NK117(she)001:11787: gdeng chen don dang mi ldan par //
NK117(she)001:11788: phag hral rtsing chos na rag snod //
NK117(she)001:11789: rgyu 'bras don la yid dbyung zhing //
NK117(she)001:11790: tshig tsam lta ba brten pa dang //
NK117(she)001:11791: gdeng med spyod cing 'chal ba'i rgyu //
NK117(she)001:11792: bskal par dka' ba ci spyad kyang //
NK117(she)001:11795: snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK117(she)001:11796: gdengs med lta ba mtho 'dod pas //
NK117(she)001:11797: rang gi nga rgyal snyems byed pa //
NK117(she)001:11798: ri bos srog chags mnan pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:11799: nam du thar pa'i khar mi 'byung //
NK117(she)001:11800: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud lung man ngag tu ma las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11802: don ma rtogs par bsgom kyang mi grol zhing gol bar gsung te /
NK117(she)001:11804: dpyid dus so nam ma byas par //
NK117(she)001:11805: ston dus btsa' ru 'gro ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:11806: rang sems don nyid ma rtog pas //
NK117(she)001:11807: bsgom du 'gro ba snying re rje //
NK117(she)001:11808: rkyal ma sbyangs par chur 'jug ltar //
NK117(she)001:11809: de bzhin ma rtogs su bsgom pa //
NK117(she)001:11812: yul dang gol sa ma chod par //
NK117(she)001:11816: bdag dang snang srid dbyer med par //
NK117(she)001:11817: rtogs nas blo yul ma zad par //
NK117(she)001:11818: bdag gi blo yul byas pa yis //
NK117(she)001:11819: nyams len thams cad rang nyid 'ching //
NK117(she)001:11822: drang don chos kyis sangs mi rgya //
NK117(she)001:11824: ma rtogs chos kun ci spyad kyang //
NK117(she)001:11825: rnam par grol bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:11828: de phyir rang sems ma rtogs dge ba yis //
NK117(she)001:11829: rgyu med 'bras bu mi 'byung dpe bzhin te //
NK117(she)001:11830: bskal pa stong du tshogs bsags sgrib sbyangs kyang //
NK117(she)001:11831: 'bras bu gzugs sku sangs rgyas 'byung mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11834: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong bar //
NK117(she)001:11835: bsam med ngang du gang 'jug pa //
NK117(she)001:11836: byis pa de nyid blun po ste //
NK117(she)001:11837: mun pa'i skye mched nyid du ltung //
NK117(she)001:11840: bsam gyis mi khyab ma mthong bar //
NK117(she)001:11842: blun po mun sprul blo can de //
NK117(she)001:11843: long ba'i grong khyer chen por 'gro //
NK117(she)001:11844: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11845: bzhi pa a ti la ltos nas /
NK117(she)001:11846: a nu man chad gol bar gsung te /
NK117(she)001:11848: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes rang snang zhing /
NK117(she)001:11849: ye nas 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes su sangs rgyas pa la /
NK117(she)001:11850: nyan rang gis skyon du bzung nas /
NK117(she)001:11851: spang zhing bkag pas gol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11852: dbu ma sems tsam gyis bden pa gnyis la gnyis su bzung sbyang bas gol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:11854: sngags nang pa gnyis bsgyur zhing dbang du byed pas
NK117(she)001:11855: rang byung ye shes la bcos shing gol bar gsung
NK117(she)001:11857: 'di min mnyam pa'i rgyu 'bras theg chen la /
NK117(she)001:11858: spong 'geg sbyong ba'i byin brlabs sna tshogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:11859: rang sems chos nyid de la bsgrib cing gol //
NK117(she)001:11860: rang ngam bzhag nas gzhan la rgyang du tshol //
NK117(she)001:11861: byar med bde bor rtsol ba dang du len //
NK117(she)001:11862: tshi chad nad du de las che ba med //
NK117(she)001:11863: ma yengs ting nge 'dzin gyi rto phur yin //
NK117(she)001:11864: ye nas yin la yengs med shor ba med //
NK117(she)001:11865: ma yengs ting 'dzin re ba'i bslu mkhan des //
NK117(she)001:11866: rgyu 'bras theg chen drang ba'i lung bstan yin //
NK117(she)001:11869: mdo sde dang ni kri yog dang //
NK117(she)001:11870: u pa ya dang yo ga dang //
NK117(she)001:11871: ma h+aa yo ga a nu drug /
NK117(she)001:11872: rdzogs pa chen po'i gol sa ste //
NK117(she)001:11876: mu stegs rang bsam log pa dang //
NK117(she)001:11877: brgyad kyis rang 'dod dbyings la bltas //
NK117(she)001:11878: phyi nang gnyis la spro bsdu byas //
NK117(she)001:11879: ngo bo nyid la dmigs 'dzin byas //
NK117(she)001:11880: rang byung nyid la rgyu yis brtsam //
NK117(she)001:11881: ma bcos cir yang ma yin la //
NK117(she)001:11882: cir yang 'dzin pa'i bsam pas brtags //
NK117(she)001:11883: bgrod med 'bras bu lhun grub la //
NK117(she)001:11884: lam brgyad bgrod pas bgrod med bslad //
NK117(she)001:11885: dpyad med don la dpyad pas na //
NK117(she)001:11886: ma yin log rtog zhen lta yin //
NK117(she)001:11889: log lta mu stegs rnam gnyis dang //
NK117(she)001:11890: phyi rol yang dag gsang sngags dang //
NK117(she)001:11891: gsang chen 'dul tshul ngas bshad nyon //
NK117(she)001:11894: rgyud lung man ngag yul la lta //
NK117(she)001:11895: de phyir ma nor chos kun min //
NK117(she)001:11898: rang sems yul la mi dpyod don la gnas //
NK117(she)001:11899: de tsam nyid na chos sku bde ba'i klong //
NK117(she)001:11900: lam la mi bgrod chos nyid ye shes sku //
NK117(she)001:11901: sa dang lam la ltos na byang chub gegs //
NK117(she)001:11904: de dag skabs kyi rang rang gis //
NK117(she)001:11905: lha la zhen pas stungs pa yin //
NK117(she)001:11906: ltung ba'i phyir na gol sa ste //
NK117(she)001:11907: des na gol sgrib thun mong 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11908: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11909: spyi don gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po'i yon tan nam che ba bstan pa la drug ste /
NK117(she)001:11910: bka' rdzogs pa chen po ni lnga brgya'i tha ma la /
NK117(she)001:11911: byang phyogs kha ba can gyi ljong 'dir dar zhing
NK117(she)001:11912: sems can gyi sgron ma byed par lung bstan pa
NK117(she)001:11913: dang / bstan pa 'di 'dzin cing 'chang ba'i yon tan dang /
NK117(she)001:11919: bstan pa'i snying po bka' rdzogs pa chen po lnga
NK117(she)001:11920: brgya'i tha ma la bod kha ba can gyi rgyal
NK117(she)001:11921: khams 'dir dar zhing rgyas nas sems can gyi sgron
NK117(she)001:11922: ma byed par lung bstan te /
NK117(she)001:11923: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:11924: dus kyi tha ma lnga brgya na //
NK117(she)001:11926: mtshon dang mu ge tshe thung dus //
NK117(she)001:11927: rdzogs chen snying po dus der bshad //
NK117(she)001:11928: de'ang rdo rje sems dpa' nyon //
NK117(she)001:11929: de'ang dus kyi deng sang na //
NK117(she)001:11930: sangs rgyas bstan pa 'jig pa'i tshe //
NK117(she)001:11931: 'dzam gling bod kyi byang phyogs su //
NK117(she)001:11932: lung dang tan tra mang po 'byung //
NK117(she)001:11933: lung dang sems kyi chos dar te //
NK117(she)001:11934: sde snod chos kun nub 'gyur zhing //
NK117(she)001:11936: rang sems rtogs pa tsam gyis ni //
NK117(she)001:11940: de nas thugs rje'i byin brlabs dang //
NK117(she)001:11941: dad pas las 'phro ldan pa yi //
NK117(she)001:11942: gnyis su med par mthun pa yis //
NK117(she)001:11943: mtha' 'khob yul du snang gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:11944: skal ldan rigs rgyud 'dzin pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:11945: rang gsal rig pa'i don go nas //
NK117(she)001:11946: sangs rgyas sa la bgrod par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11947: 'di rnams dad ldan rgyal sras te //
NK117(she)001:11948: rigs su nges pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11951: rtsol bral gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK117(she)001:11952: lha gnas gsum du grags 'gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:11953: yang sprul gang zag thugs sras kyis //
NK117(she)001:11954: 'dzam gling dbus su rgyas par byed //
NK117(she)001:11955: rgyal sras gsang ba'i snod ldan la //
NK117(she)001:11956: rnar brgyud rim pa sngags kyi don //
NK117(she)001:11957: 'phrul tshig rig pa'i sgo nas bstan //
NK117(she)001:11958: gsang 'dzin rig pa'i snod ldan rnams //
NK117(she)001:11959: ma bcos gsang ba'i don go nas //
NK117(she)001:11961: de nas gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK117(she)001:11963: de yang gsang ba dam pa 'di //
NK117(she)001:11964: skal ldan gdul bya'i ngo dag tu //
NK117(she)001:11965: rig pa'i sgron ma byed par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11967: gnyis pa bstan pa 'di 'dzin cing 'chang ba la
NK117(she)001:11968: yang rgyal ba kun gyis bu bzhin du skyob cing
NK117(she)001:11969: / rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin cing bka' la gnas par bstan pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:11972: kun kyang bu bzhin skyong bar byed //
NK117(she)001:11974: bstan pa'i snying po gang 'chang ba //
NK117(she)001:11975: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs 'chang bas //
NK117(she)001:11976: de bzhin ma nor rig pa 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:11979: rgyud 'di glegs bam la bris te //
NK117(she)001:11981: rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin bka' la gnas //
NK117(she)001:11983: tha ma ming tsam 'dzin cing mos pas kyang ngan
NK117(she)001:11984: song du mi ltung zhing thar lam rnyed par gsung
NK117(she)001:11986: skyes bu dam pa'i spyod yul te //
NK117(she)001:11987: yon tan sgra bsgrags sus thos pa //
NK117(she)001:11988: ming tsam gyis kyang bde thob cing //
NK117(she)001:11989: dran pas ngan 'gro las skyob yin //
NK117(she)001:11993: ngan song sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK117(she)001:11994: thar pa bde ba'i lam rnyed 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:11995: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:11996: gsum pa 'di la mos pa byed pa sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:11997: rnams dang skal pa mnyam zhing sangs rgya bar gsung
NK117(she)001:11998: ste / nam mkha' mtha' mnyam las /
NK117(she)001:11999: 'di la mos pa'i gang zag ni //
NK117(she)001:12000: sangs rgyas sa la skal pa mnyam //
NK117(she)001:12003: nges don 'di la gang mos rnams //
NK117(she)001:12004: bka' dang mthun par don go nas //
NK117(she)001:12005: rdul tsam du yang ma bsgom kyang //
NK117(she)001:12006: sangs rgyas sa la smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:12010: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis rlabs //
NK117(she)001:12011: bsod nams mi zad gter dang mjal //
NK117(she)001:12013: kun tu bzang pos de skad bshad //
NK117(she)001:12016: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK117(she)001:12017: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK117(she)001:12018: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad kyi //
NK117(she)001:12019: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK117(she)001:12020: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:12021: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12023: gzhung bzhin du mnyan zhing spyad na sangs rgyas par gsung te /
NK117(she)001:12026: dbang po rab kyi don du ni //
NK117(she)001:12027: bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:12028: thig le nyag cig chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:12029: shes pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas nges //
NK117(she)001:12032: gzhung 'di thos shing spyod pa ni //
NK117(she)001:12033: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa 'thob //
NK117(she)001:12034: rgyal ba nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK117(she)001:12035: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:12037: lnga pa gzhung bzhin spyad pa'i yon tan ni /
NK117(she)001:12038: bla ma'i yon tan gyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:12040: rtogs na ma bsgom kyang sangs rgya ba'i yon tan dang /
NK117(she)001:12041: rtogs shing goms pa'i yon tan rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12043: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK117(she)001:12044: de rtogs na ma bsgom kyang sangs rgyas shing yon tan rdzogs par gsung te /
NK117(she)001:12046: bde legs ji snyed ma lus kun gyi dngos //
NK117(she)001:12047: bde gshegs byang chub rtogs pa nyid la 'dus //
NK117(she)001:12050: dbang po rab kyi don du ni //
NK117(she)001:12051: bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:12052: thig le nyag cig chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:12053: shes pa tsam gyis sangs rgyas nges //
NK117(she)001:12054: sa na se yi 'bras bu bzhin //
NK117(she)001:12059: de bzhin chos sku nges don la //
NK117(she)001:12060: rtogs pa tsam gyis yon tan rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12063: skye shi med pa rang gi sems //
NK117(she)001:12064: de rtogs bsgom du rdul tsam med //
NK117(she)001:12065: de nyid rig pa byang chub sku //
NK117(she)001:12066: ma bsgom 'bral med bde ba'i mchog /
NK117(she)001:12068: 'og nas rtogs grol thar pa dus mnyam pa'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:12069: gnyis pa la bcu bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:12070: gol sa thams cad dus gcig la chod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK117(she)001:12071: 1 sgrib pa thams cad dus gcig la dag pa'i yon tan dang /
NK117(she)001:12072: 2 tshogs gnyis dus gcig la rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12073: 3 mkha' 'gro chos skyong thams cad bka' nyan pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12074: 4 mchod pa thams cad kyi mchog yin pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12076: 6 sdom pa gsum rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12077: 7 shes rab gsum rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12078: 8 dge ba bcu rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12079: 9 pha rol tu phyin pa drug rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12080: 10 tshad med bzhi rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12081: 11 gsang sngags kyi bsgrub pa ma lus pa rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12082: 12 sa dang lam dus gcig la rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12083: 13 'bras bu sku lnga la sogs pa sangs rgyas kyi yon tan 14ma lus pa rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12085: chos kun rang byung ye shes la yul dang yul can med par rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:12086: go yul du gol sa med /
NK117(she)001:12088: sgrib tu sgrib byed med pas gol sa thams cad dus gcig la chod pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12090: nyi shar mun sgrib med pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:12091: rang byung chos sku'i don rtogs pas //
NK117(she)001:12092: gol sgrib yul sems gzhi nas dag /
NK117(she)001:12093: chos kun sel med byang chub sku //
NK117(she)001:12097: ci yang mi bsgom da lta nyid //
NK117(she)001:12099: ye shes zang thal nyams pa med //
NK117(she)001:12101: byung tshor rjes su ma 'brangs pas //
NK117(she)001:12102: 'jig rten phal pa'i sar mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12103: sgo lnga'i shes pa mi 'geg pas //
NK117(she)001:12104: 'du shes med par de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12105: shes rab zab mo'i don 'dzin pas //
NK117(she)001:12106: lung du ma bstan der mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12107: zhi gnas ro la ma zhen pas //
NK117(she)001:12108: sems 'dzin bsan gtan sar mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12109: yod med yul du ma bsgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12110: rtag chad mtha' ni de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12111: rnam rtog ma spang rang zhi bas //
NK117(she)001:12112: nyan thos 'gog par de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12113: rtogs dka' stong par ma bsgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12114: rang rgyal sems su de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12115: rang rig skad cig ma bsgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12116: sems tsam lta bar de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12117: yul 'di kun rdzob blos byas te //
NK117(she)001:12118: he du dag gis gzhig byas nas //
NK117(she)001:12119: mtshan ma stong par ma bsgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12120: dbu ma gnyis su de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12121: dag bzhi ting 'dzin ma bsgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12122: kri ya'i theg par de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12123: chos nyid dbyings kyi ye shes kyi //
NK117(she)001:12124: cho 'phrul lha yi nga rgyal gyis //
NK117(she)001:12125: byang chub rnam lngar ma sgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12126: yo ga'i sems dpar de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12128: phung po khams dang skye mched kyi //
