NK117(she)001:12129: rtog tshogs rnam grangs mang po yis //
NK117(she)001:12130: rnam rtog lha ni ma bsgom pas //
NK117(she)001:12131: ma h+aa yo gar de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12132: kun gzhi dag pa'i mkha' klong du //
NK117(she)001:12133: bde chen gnyis med rig pa'i rtsal //
NK117(she)001:12135: a nu yo gar de mi gol //
NK117(she)001:12137: lung de rnams kyi ngag don blang la mtha' dgrol zhing rgyas par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:12138: lung de rnams mu chags su yod kyang /
NK117(she)001:12139: tshig bzhi bzhi yod pa'i tha ma gnyis gnyis blangs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12140: la la ni tshig bzhi ka'ang blangs so //
NK117(she)001:12142: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:12143: rig pa la sgribs yog med cing mtshan ma rang grol te /
NK117(she)001:12144: las dang las kyis gos pa med cing thog ma
NK117(she)001:12145: med pa nas bsags pa'i sgrib pa thams cad dus
NK117(she)001:12148: bskal par bsags pa'i mu nag thib po yang //
NK117(she)001:12149: rig pa'i rgyal po ye shes nyi zer gyis //
NK117(she)001:12150: gnyen po mi mthun spong la mi ltos par //
NK117(she)001:12151: skad cig yul tsam nyid la gsal ba'i don //
NK117(she)001:12154: snying po don gyi gzhi rtogs na //
NK117(she)001:12155: rang bzhin tshogs rdzogs sgrib pa med //
NK117(she)001:12158: ci ste las kyi dbang gyur na //
NK117(she)001:12159: rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:12162: thog ma med nas bsags pa yi //
NK117(she)001:12163: rnam rtog sprin dpung dpag med pa //
NK117(she)001:12164: dngos med chos skur rig pa yis //
NK117(she)001:12165: rnam rtog stong pa'i ngang du sangs //
NK117(she)001:12166: 'di shes rang rig bsgom pa'i mchog /
NK117(she)001:12169: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:12170: gang la'ang phyogs ris dang zhen 'dzin med cing /
NK117(she)001:12171: bla ma dang rgyal ba thams cad mnyes pas bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs la /
NK117(she)001:12172: de nyid rang gsal sgrib pa med pas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs te /
NK117(she)001:12174: rang gi lhar ni bdag bsgom na //
NK117(she)001:12175: bsod nams ye shes gcig char rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12178: 'bras bu ye shes tshogs ni sems nyid de //
NK117(she)001:12179: bsod nams ye shes byang chub sems la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12180: spyad pas mi mdzad ma bsags dbri ba med //
NK117(she)001:12181: klong yangs nam mkha' rgya mtsho lta bu'i don //
NK117(she)001:12182: tshogs chen rnam gnyis cig char rang la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12185: rtogs shing nyams su myong ba la lha srin sde brgyad dang /
NK117(she)001:12186: mkha' 'gro chos skyong thams cad kyi gnod pas mi tshugs shing bran bzhin byed pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12187: nges don rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor la //
NK117(she)001:12188: lha srin mkha' 'gro dgrar langs kyang //
NK117(she)001:12189: gnod pas mi tshugs bka' bzhin byed //
NK117(she)001:12190: de phyir lung bstan shin tu snyan //
NK117(she)001:12193: don 'di tshig tu ma khyer bar //
NK117(she)001:12194: gnad kyi gdeng du chud pa gang //
NK117(she)001:12195: dman pa'i lus la dam pa'i sems //
NK117(she)001:12196: dus gsum sangs rgyas sras gcig po //
NK117(she)001:12197: 'jig rten dregs pas bcings pa yi //
NK117(she)001:12198: lha srin sde brgyad thams cad kyis //
NK117(she)001:12199: jo bo'i tshul du khur bar byed //
NK117(she)001:12200: sangs rgyas kun dang dgongs pa mnyam //
NK117(she)001:12203: sems nyid rtogs shing nyams su blang na rgyal ba thams cad dang dgongs pa gnyis su med pas /
NK117(she)001:12204: mchod pa thams cad kyi mchog tu gyur par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:12206: dus gsum sangs rgyas rtag tu sems bltas mchod //
NK117(she)001:12207: de yi yon tan mi 'bral de thob nas //
NK117(she)001:12208: chos rnams kun byed rgyal por nges par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:12211: sangs rgyas mi mchod bdag nyid mchod //
NK117(she)001:12212: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12214: rtogs shing goms pa la skyabs gnas dkon mchog gsum rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12215: skyabs dang bsrung ba thams cad kyi mchog yin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12217: rang sems ye nas sangs rgyas shing sku lnga lhun grub la sogs par rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:12218: sangs rgyas dkon mchog rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12219: de nyid bstan pa thams cad kyi gzhi ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:12220: chos rnams de nyid rtogs par byed pa'i thabs su 'dus pas chos dkon mchog dang /
NK117(she)001:12221: phyin ci log gi rtog pa thams cad rang grol zhing /
NK117(she)001:12222: yang dag pa'i don la 'dun cing gnas pas dge 'dun dkon mchog go //
NK117(she)001:12223: sems bsgom don bcu gnyis pa las /
NK117(she)001:12224: bdag med gnyis nyid bder gshegs mi rtog ye shes chos dbyings sku brnyes pa //
NK117(she)001:12225: kun gyi rang bzhin 'di la bsal zhing bla med lam mchog ste //
NK117(she)001:12226: mi ldog pa la sogs te dbang phyug rgyal ba kun dang gcig brnyes pa //
NK117(she)001:12227: gnas gsum mnyam nyid de la mtshan med yid kyis rab tu dad pa mos //
NK117(she)001:12230: de rtogs sangs rgyas rang byung bcom ldan 'das //
NK117(she)001:12231: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thugs la bkra //
NK117(she)001:12232: de phyir yang dag nges don snying po 'di //
NK117(she)001:12233: skyabs dang mgon du lta ba mchog tu gsungs //
NK117(she)001:12236: rtogs shing nyams su myong bas bdud bzhi la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12237: lus kyi na tsha dang sems kyi sdug bsngal la
NK117(she)001:12238: sogs pa 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal ma lus pa las
NK117(she)001:12241: rang lus na tsha bzod dka' ste //
NK117(she)001:12242: rkyen dbang mi gol gdam ngag ni //
NK117(she)001:12243: gang na blo yis ma bzungs pas //
NK117(she)001:12244: bzod dka' rang rig chos skur shes //
NK117(she)001:12245: snga phyi ma btang da lta yi //
NK117(she)001:12246: bde sdug dag kyang chos skur gsal //
NK117(she)001:12247: sdug bsngal rang bzhin chos skur shar //
NK117(she)001:12248: yid chad 'khang gzhi'i rkyen rnams thub //
NK117(she)001:12251: byang chub sems kyi srog 'di la //
NK117(she)001:12252: bdud bzhi'i tshogs kyis mi chom bzhin //
NK117(she)001:12253: dgra gsum dag gis gsad du med //
NK117(she)001:12254: g.yang sa drug tu mi ltung bas //
NK117(she)001:12255: bya bral ltung las nyams pa med //
NK117(she)001:12257: rang byung ye shes rang gi klong //
NK117(she)001:12258: bde dang sdug bsngal btang snyoms kyang //
NK117(she)001:12259: rang byung rang zhi nyid du gsal //
NK117(she)001:12260: rang rig klong du rnam par dag /
NK117(she)001:12261: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12263: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs shing nyams
NK117(she)001:12264: su myong bas sdom pa gsum rdzogs pa yin te
NK117(she)001:12265: / nyes pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pas nyan thos kyi 'dul khrims rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12266: gnyis su med pa'i snying rjes 'gro don rdzogs pas byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK117(she)001:12267: de nyid las mi 'da' bas gsang sngags kyi dam tshig yongs su rdzogs par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:12268: sems bsgom bcu gnyis pa las /
NK117(she)001:12269: tshul khrims la sogs pha rol phyin lam spyod pa rgya mtsho'i gzhir gyur pa /
NK117(she)001:12271: dkyil 'khor gsang bar zhugs shing theg chen dam tshig mchog kyang bsdus pa yin /
NK117(she)001:12272: tshul khrims sdom pa kun kyang 'dus shing sbyin gnas dam pa rab tu basngagasa /
NK117(she)001:12275: sdom pa phyi nang dam tshig kyang //
NK117(she)001:12276: gdul bya ci ltar 'dul bar ston //
NK117(she)001:12277: tha snyad tsam du rdul med kyang //
NK117(she)001:12278: dam du bca' ba rdul tsam med //
NK117(she)001:12281: chos kun sems kyi ming 'dogs su thos shing go bas /
NK117(she)001:12282: tshig dang yi ge ris kyi rjes su mi 'brang
NK117(she)001:12283: ba ni thos pa las byung ba'i shes rab dang
NK117(she)001:12284: / de'i don la bsam pas rtog dpyod the tshom med par thag chod pa ni /
NK117(she)001:12285: bsam pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyis blo'i sgro 'dog chod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12286: de kha tsam tshig tsam min par nyams su myong
NK117(she)001:12287: bas spangs blangs dgag bsgrub med par rang grol ba
NK117(she)001:12288: ni / bsgom pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyis don mngon du shar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:12289: de gsum yang cig char ba dang rim gyis pa'i dmigs shes par bya ste rgyas par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:12291: chos kun rang byung ye shes su rtogs shing nyams
NK117(she)001:12292: su myong bas mi dge ba'i sel med cing ci
NK117(she)001:12293: byed dge bar 'gro bas dge ba bcu yongs su
NK117(she)001:12295: de'i bye brag shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:12296: de gnyis kyi lung ni 'og nas bsdus te ston no //
NK117(she)001:12298: rtogs shing nyams su myong ba la pha rol tu phyin pa drug tshang ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:12299: zhen 'dzin phyogs 'dzin med pas sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12300: mi dge ba'i nyes byas mi 'byung zhing dri ma med pas tshul khrims kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:12301: khong khro med cing rtogs pa'i klong du kun shong bas bzod pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12302: ma yengs 'du 'bral med pas brtson 'grus kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:12303: rgyun mi chad cing snying po'i don la mi g.yeng bas bsam gtan gyi dang /
NK117(she)001:12304: rang byung ye shes rtogs shing 'khor 'das kyi rtsa
NK117(she)001:12305: ba chod pas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin
NK117(she)001:12306: pa rdzogs pa'o // nam mkha' klong yangs las /
NK117(she)001:12307: lo ka gol bar don rtogs pas //
NK117(she)001:12308: ser sna 'dzin pa'i sems med phyir //
NK117(she)001:12309: re ba med pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK117(she)001:12310: sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12311: ma nor khrims las mi 'da' phyir //
NK117(she)001:12312: lus ngag yid kyi las rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:12313: mi dge nyes byas mi 'byung bas //
NK117(she)001:12314: tshul khrims pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12315: zab la rgya che lta ba yis //
NK117(she)001:12316: yin dang min pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:12317: chos kyi dbyings su kun shong bas //
NK117(she)001:12318: bzod pa'i pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12319: ngo bo nyid las 'bras med phyir //
NK117(she)001:12320: ched du mi bsgom da lta nyid //
NK117(she)001:12321: lta ba'i don la yengs med pas //
NK117(she)001:12322: brtson 'grus pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12323: bzhi gsum dus gsum 'bral med pas //
NK117(she)001:12324: ye shes kun tu rgyun mi chad //
NK117(she)001:12325: snying po'i don las ma g.yos pas //
NK117(she)001:12326: bsam gtan pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12327: dang po 'khor ba rtsad chod pas //
NK117(she)001:12328: ye shes rig pa ngos zin phyir //
NK117(she)001:12329: yid ches gdeng gis thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:12330: shes rab pha rol phyin pa rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12333: bdag gzhan gnyis su med par rtogs shing mi gtong par 'dzin pas snying rje dang /
NK117(she)001:12334: brtse bas kun la khyab cing snyoms pas byams pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12335: mi 'bral zhing spro bas dga' ba dang /
NK117(she)001:12336: kun la snyoms shing nye ring med pas btang snyoms so //
NK117(she)001:12337: rgya mtsho klong dgu'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:12338: snying rje mi phyed yul las bral //
NK117(she)001:12339: byams pa nam mkha'i mtha' ltar bdal //
NK117(she)001:12340: dga' ba rang byung gsang ba'i nyams //
NK117(she)001:12341: btang snyoms 'dzin bral yengs pa med //
NK117(she)001:12344: snying rje chen po cir mi mdzad //
NK117(she)001:12345: byams pa don nyid rnam sbyang phyir //
NK117(she)001:12346: dga' ba chen po btsal med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12347: btang snyoms mnyam nyid kun tu khyab //
NK117(she)001:12350: gsang sngags kyi bsgrub pa kun rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12353: rtogs shing nyams su len pa la bskyed rim la
NK117(she)001:12354: sogs pa bsgrub pa thams cad don gyis tshang zhing
NK117(she)001:12356: 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog grol zhing rkyen rnams grogs
NK117(she)001:12357: su shar bas phyi nang gi mtshams bcad rdzogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:12358: dang / rang gis rang ngo shes pas ma rig nyon mongs dang /
NK117(she)001:12359: las dang las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12360: shes bya'i sgrib pa la sogs pa rang sar dag pas don gyi bshags pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12361: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing rang sems sangs rgyas su rtogs pas byin dbab pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12362: 'byung lnga rang byung ye shes su gsal bas 'byung ba rim brtsegs rdzogs pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12363: thams cad sems nyid la gnas shing bzhugs pas gzhal yas khang dang /
NK117(she)001:12364: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing rang sems rgyal ba'i
NK117(she)001:12365: dal du rtogs pas brten pa lha bskyed pa'i dang
NK117(she)001:12366: / sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su med cing dbyer
NK117(she)001:12367: med pas spyan drang zhing bstim pa la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:12368: / rdzogs pa'i dang / phyogs 'dzin log rtog bsgral
NK117(she)001:12369: zhing gnyis med don la sbyor bas sbyor srol la
NK117(she)001:12370: / rdzogs pa'i dang / sogs pa'i dang / yon
NK117(she)001:12371: tan thams cad lhun gyis grub cing mthar phyin pas
NK117(she)001:12373: chos kun sku gsung thugs su 'dus shing /
NK117(she)001:12374: de'i rol pa rang snang bas don gyi bzlas pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12375: snod bcud rig par longs spyod pas tshogs kyi mchod pa'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12376: 'khor 'das thig le nyag cig tu 'dus shing ci spyod don las mi 'da' bas /
NK117(she)001:12377: dal bsdu ba la sogs pa rdzogs pa'i yon tan no //
NK117(she)001:12379: lta ba nges pa'i gdeng zin pas //
NK117(she)001:12380: mi rtog ye shes bgegs bsal bas //
NK117(she)001:12381: rnam par rtog pa'i bgegs med phyir //
NK117(she)001:12382: phyi nang mtshams bcad de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12383: ye nas ngo bo nyid sku la //
NK117(she)001:12384: bsgrub tu med pa'i chos nyid pas //
NK117(she)001:12385: ma rig rnam rtog sgrib pa med //
NK117(she)001:12386: don gyi bshags pa de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12387: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med phyir //
NK117(she)001:12388: yul dang dbang po mi 'byed pas //
NK117(she)001:12389: gnyis med don gyi blo gsal bas //
NK117(she)001:12390: byin chen dbab pa de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12391: dbang po yul gyi rnam pa la //
NK117(she)001:12392: dngos po byung ba'i rtsa ba de //
NK117(she)001:12393: sa chu me rlung kun khyab pas //
NK117(she)001:12394: dbang chen rim pa de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12395: gdan dang yig 'bru la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:12396: rang gi sems kyi cho 'phrul te //
NK117(she)001:12397: phyogs bcur rang bzhin lhun grub pas //
NK117(she)001:12398: gzhal yas khang chen de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12400: rig tshor don gyi lha yin pas //
NK117(she)001:12401: ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK117(she)001:12402: ye shes lha rnams de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12403: ngo bo nyid kyi snying po la //
NK117(she)001:12404: sangs rgyas sems can rgyu gcig phyir //
NK117(she)001:12405: ched du byar med rang rig 'dir //
NK117(she)001:12406: spyan drangs bstim pa de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12407: ye nas snying po byang chub la //
NK117(she)001:12408: blo dang dngos po gcig pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12409: sems dang chos su don 'byor pas //
NK117(she)001:12410: sbyor sgrol mchod pa de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12411: ye nas gnas pa'i don go bas //
NK117(she)001:12412: skye shi med par thag chod phyir //
NK117(she)001:12413: yon tan thams cad lhun grub pas //
NK117(she)001:12414: mthar phyin smon lam de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12415: sangs rgyas che ba'i yon tan gyi //
NK117(she)001:12416: sku gsung thugs kyi don tshangs bas //
NK117(she)001:12417: da lta nyid du rtogs pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12419: dga' ldan lha dang 'byor ldan tshogs //
NK117(she)001:12420: nges pa'i lta ba gdeng zin pas //
NK117(she)001:12421: snod bcud ye nas tshogs yin phyir //
NK117(she)001:12422: tshogs kyi mchod pa de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12424: thig le gcig tu 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12425: ci spyod rang gi lus ngag las //
NK117(she)001:12426: dkyil 'khor bsdu ba de la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12428: de la sogs pa lung man ngag du ma nas gsung nas 'dug go //
NK117(she)001:12430: chos kun rang byung ye shes la bgegs rigs dang /
NK117(she)001:12431: nyon mongs pa la sogs pa ngang gi zhi bas na zhi ba'i dang /
NK117(she)001:12432: rang byung ye shes la mtha' dbus phyogs mtshams med
NK117(she)001:12433: cing yon tan thams cad rdzogs pas rgyas pa'i dang
NK117(she)001:12434: / rig pa la dbang thob cing snang ba dbang du 'dus pas na dbang gi dang /
NK117(she)001:12435: log rtog phyogs 'dzin la sogs pa gnyis su med par bsgral bas drag po'i'o //
NK117(she)001:12437: de yi phrin las phya btsal med //
NK117(she)001:12438: nyon mongs rang sar zhi ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12439: byang chub sems ni zhi bar grags //
NK117(she)001:12440: yon tan mchog tu rgyas pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12441: byang chub sems ni rgyas par grags //
NK117(she)001:12442: rig pa rang dbang thob pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12443: byang chub sems ni dbang du grags //
NK117(she)001:12444: 'khrul pa rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12445: byang chub sems ni drag por grags //
NK117(she)001:12448: rang byung ye shes la 'khor 'das gnyis su med pas /
NK117(she)001:12449: lam la bgrod du med cing lam lnga dus gcig la rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12450: sa la sbyang du med cing sa rnams dus gcig la non pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12452: rang byung ye shes dngos su rtogs pas tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs te tshogs lam dang /
NK117(she)001:12453: chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid la mngon du spyor pas sbyor lam dang /
NK117(she)001:12454: chos nyid brjod bral spros pa med par mngon du mthong bas mthong lam dang /
NK117(she)001:12455: de'i ngang la g.yos pa med par gnas pas bsgom lam dang /
NK117(she)001:12456: de nyid rtogs pa mthar phyin pas mthar lam ste /
NK117(she)001:12457: de rnams rang snang ba mngon du rtogs pas dus gcig la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12459: ye nas thig le dbyer med tshogs kyi lam //
NK117(she)001:12460: rtogs pas ye shes dbyer med sbyor ba'i lam //
NK117(she)001:12461: chos nyid don rtogs bde chen mthong ba'i lam //
NK117(she)001:12462: yid kyi g.yo ba zad pa bsgom pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:12463: bya byed med par don rdzogs mthar phyin lam //
NK117(she)001:12466: rgyu rkyen ma bskyed rang byung bas //
NK117(she)001:12467: gsal 'grib med pa'i ye shes yin //
NK117(she)001:12468: rtsol bsgrub dag las ma byung bas //
NK117(she)001:12469: rang byung lam la rag ma lus //
NK117(she)001:12470: yul las ma byung ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:12471: lung ldan rkyen gyis rtogs pas chog /
NK117(she)001:12473: yang dag don gyi chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:12474: lam gyi dbye ba med mod kyang //
NK117(she)001:12475: rnal 'byor blo yi rim pa lnga //
NK117(she)001:12476: theg pa'i bye brag tha dad pas //
NK117(she)001:12477: lam lnga'i dbye ba dus gcig rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12478: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12480: gnas lugs ji bzhin pa nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12481: de nyid rtogs pas sa rnams dus gcig la non pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12483: klong yangs 'ub chub bdal khyab pa //
NK117(she)001:12484: spyir chib sa bcu 'dus pa'i klong //
NK117(she)001:12485: gcig la bye brag phye ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12486: sa bcur snang ba yon tan yin //
NK117(she)001:12489: sa med rdzogs chen chos sku ye shes las //
NK117(she)001:12490: gar yang mi 'gro sa mchog spyir chibs pas //
NK117(she)001:12491: bgrod med sems nyid ye shes mchog gi lam //
NK117(she)001:12492: ye shes chos sku mthar phyin chos nyid pa //
NK117(she)001:12495: 'khor ba byang chub lam du gsal //
NK117(she)001:12496: gcong rang ye shes gnas su spar //
NK117(she)001:12497: bgrod med bla ma'i sa la 'jug /
NK117(she)001:12498: sa gcig mnan pas sa kun non //
NK117(she)001:12500: de yang sems nyid rtogs pa la pha rol tu
NK117(she)001:12501: phyin pa'i sa bcu dus gcig la rdzogs pa dang
NK117(she)001:12502: / 'bras bu'i sa thams cad dus gcig la rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12505: sa lam thams cad lhun grub de nyid rang //
NK117(she)001:12506: mi 'gyur kun gzhi sems kyi sa gzhi la //
NK117(she)001:12507: de nyid yang dag mthong bas rab tu dga' //
NK117(she)001:12508: de la gzung 'dzin dag pas dri ma med //
NK117(she)001:12509: de nyid rgya ma chad pas 'od byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12510: rtogs pa'i ye shes 'byung bas 'od 'phro ba'o //
NK117(she)001:12511: blo yi spyod yul ma gyur spyangs dka' ba'o //
NK117(she)001:12512: rang gi ngo bor gyur pas mngon du gyur //
NK117(she)001:12513: 'dod pa'i blo ma skyes pas ring du song //
NK117(she)001:12514: ma skyes mi 'gag g.yo ba med pa'i sa //
NK117(she)001:12515: skyon rnams kun gyis ma gos legs blo gros //
NK117(she)001:12516: thams cad chos kyi dbyings las mi phyed sprin //
NK117(she)001:12519: rang byung gi ye shes ma bsgribs rang gsal bas kun tu 'od kyi sa zhes kyang bya /
NK117(she)001:12520: gang la yang chags pa med cing skyon gyis ma gos pas ma chags pad+ma spyan gyi sa dang /
NK117(she)001:12521: skye 'jig med pas rdo rje 'dzin gyi sa dang /
NK117(she)001:12522: dpag tu med cing thams cad mnyam par bkod pas sdug po bkod pa'i sa dang /
NK117(she)001:12523: byang chub sems su thams cad 'dus shing bkod pas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dang /
NK117(she)001:12524: thams cad sku gsung thugs su dbyer med cing mnga' mdzad pas rdo rje 'chang gi sa dang /
NK117(she)001:12525: 'khor 'das dbye ba med cing bzang ngan blang dor
NK117(she)001:12526: med par rtogs pas kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i
NK117(she)001:12528: rang byung ye shes ma 'gags pa yi rtags //
NK117(she)001:12529: dbang po sgo lnga kun tu gsal ba la //
NK117(she)001:12530: kun tu 'od kyi sa zhes brtags pa yin //
NK117(she)001:12531: yul la mi rtog chags pa med pa la //
NK117(she)001:12532: ma chags pad+ma spyan du brtags pa yin //
NK117(she)001:12533: skye 'jig med pa'i byang chub sems de la //
NK117(she)001:12534: rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes su nga yis btags //
NK117(she)001:12535: rang gi rang bzhin chos dbyings dpag med la //
NK117(she)001:12536: rang byung ye shes mi rtog mnyam par bkod //
NK117(she)001:12537: stug po bkod pa'i sa zhes btags pa yin //
NK117(she)001:12538: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkyil 'khor te //
NK117(she)001:12539: rang la gnas pa'i byang chub chos rnams la //
NK117(she)001:12540: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sa rnams te //
NK117(she)001:12541: sku gsung thugs la skye dang 'jig med pas //
NK117(she)001:12542: rdo rje 'chang gi sa zhes bshad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:12543: byang chub sems la rgyu 'bras gnyis med pas //
NK117(she)001:12544: sems las byung ba'i chos rnams thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:12545: bzang ngan blang dor ye nas med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12546: dbye ba med pa'i sa zhes nga yis bshad //
NK117(she)001:12547: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12549: rang sems mngon du rtogs pas sku lnga la sogs
NK117(she)001:12550: pa che ba'i yon tan thams cad dus gcig la
NK117(she)001:12552: de'i dbye ba rgyas par 'bras bu'i skabs nas ston no //
NK117(she)001:12554: sangs rgyas rnams kyi che ba yang //
NK117(she)001:12555: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang //
NK117(she)001:12556: mtshan ni sum cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK117(she)001:12557: stobs dang mi 'jigs la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:12558: thig le chos sku rtogs par 'dus //
NK117(she)001:12560: chos sku gzhi nges rtogs pa la //
NK117(she)001:12561: ma rig med pas dug lnga grol //
NK117(she)001:12562: thams cad rang byung chos skur gsal //
NK117(she)001:12563: lung ldan rkyen gyis ma reg dag /
NK117(she)001:12564: dug lnga byang chub lam yin phyir //
NK117(she)001:12565: sku lnga lhun grub dus gcig rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12568: de bas shes bya shes byed dag pa la //
NK117(she)001:12569: pha rol phyin dang sa bcu lam lnga rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12570: sku dang ye shes yon tan ma lus rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12573: tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing sgrib gnyis shugs kyis 'byangs //
NK117(she)001:12574: dge bcu pha rol phyin drug tshad med bzhi //
NK117(she)001:12575: skyabs 'gro sdom pa gsum dang shes rab gsum //
NK117(she)001:12576: las bzhi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu klong dgu rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12577: dkar po'i phyogs kyi yon tan ma lus rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12579: rtogs shing grol ba'i thabs ni bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:12580: ngo sprad cing rtogs pa'i thabs dang /
NK117(she)001:12581: mi rigs rigs pa'i chos gsum gyis khyad par dpag te bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12582: rdzogs chen gyi dgongs pa'i gnas lugs sam rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12583: bsgom zhing grol tshul bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12586: de rtogs par bya ba'i thabs so //
NK117(she)001:12588: gzhi'i skabs su chos kun rang byung ye shes su
NK117(she)001:12589: lhag ma med par rdzogs shing ye nas sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:12592: shes bya da nga rtogs thabs dbyer med du gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12595: mngon du phyung ba'i mdo lugs dang /
NK117(she)001:12599: gtan la 'bebs pa'i mdo lung dang lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:12601: chos kun ci ltar snang yang rang byung gi ye
NK117(she)001:12602: shes mngon sum du snang bas mngon du phyung ba'i
NK117(she)001:12605: rang byung ye shes chos kyi snying po las //
NK117(she)001:12606: snang zhing srid pa'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK117(she)001:12607: mi snang ba la dngos su 'byin nus pas //
NK117(she)001:12608: chos kyi snying po yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12612: rig pa mngon du phyung bas na //
NK117(she)001:12613: byang chub sems la dgag tu med //
NK117(she)001:12616: ji ltar snang ba'i chos can chos nyid kun //
NK117(she)001:12617: rtsol ba ma byas byang chub mi 'gyur dbyings //
NK117(she)001:12618: mi snang ba la mngon du 'byin nus phyir //
NK117(she)001:12619: chos kyi snying po yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12622: chos kun rang byung ye shes la don dam kun rdzob dang /
NK117(she)001:12623: bden rdzun yin min gnyis su med cing snang srid
NK117(she)001:12624: chos skur rtogs pas ma nor nges pa'i mdo lung
NK117(she)001:12626: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK117(she)001:12627: don dam kun rdzob bden rdzun gnyis med par //
NK117(she)001:12628: ma nor nges pa'i byang chub sems ston pas //
NK117(she)001:12629: the tshom som nyi med par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12632: nyon mongs bde sdug la sogs kun //
NK117(she)001:12633: spang du med de bdag nyid rang //
NK117(she)001:12634: byang chub sems las gzhan med par //
NK117(she)001:12635: skye med rang gi rgyan du rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12638: sems can kun la khyab pa'i snying po 'di //
NK117(she)001:12639: thams cad rang las byung ba'i ye shes de //
NK117(she)001:12640: lung ldan bstan pas shes phyir nges pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:12641: nges pa'i sangs rgyas yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12644: chos kun rang byung ye shes yin pas /
NK117(she)001:12645: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med cing 'khor 'das gnyis su med par ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12647: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK117(she)001:12648: rgyu la mi brten rkyen las mi bsgrub pas //
NK117(she)001:12649: gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK117(she)001:12650: rang byung ye shes yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12653: rgyu 'bras rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK117(she)001:12654: rgyu med ye nas chos nyid klong //
NK117(she)001:12655: rgyu 'bras rang byung ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:12659: ye nas gnas pa'i rang byung snying po 'di //
NK117(she)001:12660: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas //
NK117(she)001:12661: rgyu 'bras gnyis med ye nas chos sku 'di //
NK117(she)001:12662: rang byung ye shes yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12665: chos kun ye nas rang byung ye shes su lhun gyis grub pas /
NK117(she)001:12666: rgyu rkyen rtsol ba med par bdag gzhan gyi don rnams rtogs pas 'grub pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12668: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK117(she)001:12669: rgyu rkyen med par lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12670: phrin las brtsal zhing bya byed bya mi dgos //
NK117(she)001:12671: ma bcos lhun gyis grub par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12674: chos kyi dbyings las btsal du med //
NK117(she)001:12675: btsal du med pa'i don de la //
NK117(she)001:12676: rang bzhin gnas pas de bzhin nyid //
NK117(she)001:12677: de la sus kyang bcos su med //
NK117(she)001:12680: gzhan nas ma brtsal rang las rnyed pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12681: gnyen pos ma bskyed rang bzhin yin pas na //
NK117(she)001:12682: lus ngag ched du btsal du med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12683: ma btsal lhun gyis grub par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12686: rang byung ye shes la bstan pa thams cad rdzogs shing de nyid ma bsgribs rang gsal bas /
NK117(she)001:12687: chos rnams thams cad gnyis su med par ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12689: rang byung ye shes gcig gi ngo bo de //
NK117(she)001:12690: rang byung ye shes ye nas ma bsgribs pas //
NK117(she)001:12691: chos rnams thams cad gtan la 'bebs pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12692: ston pa'i sgron me yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12696: thog bab car phog shugs 'byung dang //
NK117(she)001:12697: klong rdol rang shar rang lugs kyis //
NK117(she)001:12698: 'gro drug grong khyer gtan nas bcom //
NK117(she)001:12701: sde snod chos rnams man ngag kun gyi ni //
NK117(she)001:12702: 'byung gnas gtan la 'bebs pa'i chos yin pas //
NK117(she)001:12703: bstan pas go zhing rtogs pa 'byung ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:12704: kun gyi spyi 'grel yin par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12706: de ltar shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med
NK117(she)001:12707: par rang byung rang snang ba yin zhing khyad par
NK117(she)001:12708: du phyi nang snod bcud bde sdug sna tshogs su
NK117(she)001:12709: snang ba 'di rang byung ye shes mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:12710: snang ba'o // rtogs thabs rgyas pa ni /
NK117(she)001:12711: lung man ngag rigs pas dngos su ngo sprod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12712: gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab ste dngos su rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12714: lung man ngag rig pa'i tshad mas mngon sum gcer 'phrad du ngo sprad pa ni /
NK117(she)001:12715: gong gi stong thun gyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:12716: he dus dngos su rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK117(she)001:12717: rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid kyi gtan tshigs kyis mngon sum du rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:12718: he dus gtan la phab ste rtogs par bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:12720: rgyud lung man ngag thams cad kyang byang chub kyi sems yin par dang /
NK117(she)001:12721: des na rang sems nyid ston par snang nas mngon sum du ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12723: byang chub kyi sems la thams cad tshangs zhing 'brel pas rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:12724: byang chub sems kyis thams cad zin pas lung dang /
NK117(she)001:12725: de nyid kyis de nyid gnyis su med par ngo sprod pas man ngag yin te /
NK117(she)001:12726: de rnams kyang byang chub kyi sems la tshang zhing rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12727: de yang mtshon bya don gyi rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:12728: mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:12730: lung la ma brten man ngag rang rig 'di //
NK117(she)001:12731: rgyud ni byang chub sems su thams cad 'brel //
NK117(she)001:12732: lung ni byang chub sems kyis thams cad zin //
NK117(she)001:12733: man ngag byang chub sems la gzung 'dzin med //
NK117(she)001:12734: nyid kyis nyid rtogs nyid du rtogs //
NK117(she)001:12737: theg pa'i khyad par ji snyed du //
NK117(she)001:12738: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsung pa yang //
NK117(she)001:12739: klong chen gcig gi yon tan te //
NK117(she)001:12740: gdul bya rnams la bstan par zad //
NK117(she)001:12743: phyi 'byung ba rnam pa lnga la sogs par snang nas ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12744: nang nyon mongs pa lngar snang nas chos nyid mngon sum du ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12746: rang byung gi ye shes nyid phyi 'byung ba rnam
NK117(she)001:12747: pa lnga dang 'dod yon lnga la sogs par snang
NK117(she)001:12748: zhing / rang gi ye shes mngon sum du phyung
NK117(she)001:12749: nas tshig dang yi ge ma yin par don mngon
NK117(she)001:12750: sum du ngo sprod cing gnyis su med par gtan
NK117(she)001:12753: snang ba chos dbyings bla ma ni //
NK117(she)001:12754: 'byung chen lnga yi bla ma ste //
NK117(she)001:12755: 'dod yon lnga sogs chos rnams ni //
NK117(she)001:12756: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon par //
NK117(she)001:12757: ldem dgongs rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK117(she)001:12758: snang ba chos kyi dbyings su bstan //
NK117(she)001:12761: stong pa bas kyang snang ba gtso //
NK117(she)001:12762: snang ba rang shar nges med kyis //
NK117(she)001:12764: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:12765: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12768: byang chub sems kyi ye shes de //
NK117(she)001:12769: ston pa sa yi skur byung nas //
NK117(she)001:12770: tshig dang yi ges mi mtshon te //
NK117(she)001:12771: rang gi rang bzhin ston byed pa //
NK117(she)001:12772: bdag tu mi rtog gzhan mi rtog /
NK117(she)001:12773: mi rtog mnyam pa'i dngos po ston //
NK117(she)001:12774: khams sum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK117(she)001:12775: de rtogs sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK117(she)001:12777: 'byung ba lnga la sogs pas chos ston cing //
NK117(she)001:12778: rang gi ngo bos gtan la 'bebs par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12780: nang nyon mongs pa la sogs par rang byung ye
NK117(she)001:12781: shes nyid mngon du snang nas gnyis su med par
NK117(she)001:12782: ngo sprod cing rang grol du gtan la 'bebs pa
NK117(she)001:12783: yin te / de yang sems can sangs rgyas su ngo sprod cing gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:12784: sdug bsngal bde chen du dang /
NK117(she)001:12787: sangs rgyas bas kyang sems can gtso //
NK117(she)001:12788: sems can dngos su snang ba yis //
NK117(she)001:12789: dngos med sangs rgyas gtan la 'bebs //
NK117(she)001:12790: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:12791: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12793: bde chen bas kyang sdug bsngal gtso //
NK117(she)001:12794: sdug bsngal zhen chags mtshan ma yis //
NK117(she)001:12795: bde chen chags med gtan la 'bebs //
NK117(she)001:12796: gnyis su med par thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:12797: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12799: ye shes pas kyang nyon mongs gtso //
NK117(she)001:12800: nyon mongs 'ching ba'i zhags pa yis //
NK117(she)001:12801: rang byung ye shes gtan la 'bebs //
NK117(she)001:12802: nyon mongs ye shes dbyer med de //
NK117(she)001:12803: gnyis med klong du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:12804: rang sar grol bar yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12807: dug lnga spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK117(she)001:12808: sangs rgyas bya ba'i ming yang med //
NK117(she)001:12809: de nyid rtogs na sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:12810: nor bu rin chen rnyed pa'i mi //
NK117(she)001:12811: 'jig rten so nam mi dgos bzhin //
NK117(she)001:12812: ma bsgoms sems kyi don rtogs na //
NK117(she)001:12813: de las mi 'da' dam tshig yin //
NK117(she)001:12814: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12815: de rnams ngo sprod pa ni /
NK117(she)001:12816: snyan rgyud zhal gyi gdams pa las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:12817: he dus gtan la dbab pa ni /
NK117(she)001:12818: he du chen po bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:12820: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i he du dang /
NK117(she)001:12821: bdag nyid chen po gcig gi he du'o //
NK117(she)001:12823: chos kun 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes ma bcos rang snang bas /
NK117(she)001:12824: rang bzhin skye med kyi he du dang /
NK117(she)001:12825: de nyid cir yang snang bas rol pa 'gag med kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:12826: de gnyis dbyer med pas mtshan nyid gnyis med kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:12827: bcing grol med par blo ngo bo nyid du rang grol ba'i gtan tshigs so //
NK117(she)001:12831: ngo bo nyid kyi sku ru ngo sprad do //
NK117(she)001:12833: rang bzhin skye med kyi gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:12834: lhun gyis grub par yid ches bya //
NK117(she)001:12835: rol pa 'gags meda gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:12836: cir yang 'char bar yid ches bya //
NK117(she)001:12837: mtshan nyid gnyis med gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:12838: chos rnams gcig par yid ches bya //
NK117(she)001:12839: ngo bo blo bral gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:12840: rtsol ba med par yid kyang ches //
NK117(she)001:12843: ma bcos par rang gsal bas ngang gis gtan tshigs so //
NK117(she)001:12844: cir yang snang ba de nyid las mi 'da' bas rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs dang /
NK117(she)001:12845: gnyis su med pas bdag nyid chen po'i he du'o //
NK117(she)001:12847: dang ni rig pa gsal pa ste //
NK117(she)001:12848: rang bzhin rig pa cir yang snang //
NK117(she)001:12849: bdag nyid snang stong tha dad med //
NK117(she)001:12850: 'khrul pa byang chub sems su shes //
NK117(she)001:12853: chos nyid mu mtha' med pas dbyings kyi dang //
NK117(she)001:12854: mi bsgribs dang gsal bas ye shes kyi dang /
NK117(she)001:12855: de gnyis gnyis su med pas gnyis su med pa'i he du'o //
NK117(she)001:12857: dbyings dang ye shes he du ni //
NK117(she)001:12858: dbyings ni dag pa rgyu yin te //
NK117(she)001:12859: ye shes 'bras bu nyid du gsal //
NK117(she)001:12863: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su lhag ma
NK117(she)001:12864: med par rdzogs pas bdag nyid chen po gcig gi
NK117(she)001:12866: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis //
NK117(she)001:12867: thams cad byang chub sems su shes //
NK117(she)001:12870: ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK117(she)001:12871: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' las 'das //
NK117(she)001:12872: gzhan yang chos kyi dbyings kyi klong //
NK117(she)001:12873: rdzogs ni lhag ma med par rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:12874: 'khor ni dus gsum rgyal bar ldan //
NK117(she)001:12875: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i sa //
NK117(she)001:12876: skad cig rtogs pas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:12878: gnyis pa mi rigs rigs pa gsum ni /
NK117(she)001:12880: mi rigs rigs par bshad gsum ni //
NK117(she)001:12881: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK117(she)001:12882: mi rigs rigs par bshad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:12883: lung las ma byung gdams ngag yang //
NK117(she)001:12884: mi rigs rigs pa bshad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:12885: zhes pas sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK117(she)001:12886: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu dang /
NK117(she)001:12887: lung las ma byung gi gdam ngag bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12889: sangs rgyas kyi go ba dang /
NK117(she)001:12892: sangs rgyas pa'i rgyas lugs so //
NK117(she)001:12894: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su ye nas
NK117(she)001:12895: sangs rgyas shing dus gsum snga phyi 'pho 'gyur med
NK117(she)001:12896: par ye nas gnas pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12897: de yang phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa thams cad rang byung gi ye shes rang snang zhing /
NK117(she)001:12898: yul dang yul can med par snang srid chos skur sangs rgyas pas /
NK117(she)001:12899: sems las ma byung ba'i sangs rgyas yin te /
NK117(she)001:12901: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK117(she)001:12902: rang byung ye shes chos sku de //
NK117(she)001:12903: sangs rgyas kun gyi nges pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:12904: rnal 'byor kun gyi dam pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:12905: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes mchog /
NK117(she)001:12907: thog mtha' chod nas dus gsum gcig /
NK117(she)001:12909: snga phyir med par rang byung sku //
NK117(she)001:12910: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:12913: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas ni //
NK117(she)001:12914: chos nyid mkha' la dbyings nyid klong //
NK117(she)001:12915: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:12918: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen po //
NK117(she)001:12919: sangs rgyas bas kyang sngar sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:12920: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12921: de yang theg pa gzhan dag rgyu rkyen rtsol ba'i
NK117(she)001:12922: sgo nas tshogs bsags sgrib pa sbyangs nas sems las
NK117(she)001:12924: 'dir sems las byung ba'i sangs rgyas ma yin gyis /
NK117(she)001:12925: sems nyid rang ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo
NK117(she)001:12926: yin pas tshogs gnyis la sogs pas sangs rgyas pa
NK117(she)001:12927: ma yin cing de nyid rtogs pas mngon du sangs
NK117(she)001:12930: tshogs bsags sgribs sbyangs kun btags pa'i //
NK117(she)001:12931: sems bral rang byung chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:12932: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas 'di //
NK117(she)001:12933: theg pa kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:12936: rang zhal rang gis mthong ba la //
NK117(she)001:12937: sangs rgyas zhes su btags par zad //
NK117(she)001:12938: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12939: des na dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs
NK117(she)001:12940: pa yang chos kun sems nyid rang byung gi ye
NK117(she)001:12941: shes su ye nas sangs rgyas pa de nyid rtogs
NK117(she)001:12944: dus gsum sangs rgyas dgongs pa ni //
NK117(she)001:12945: 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:12946: rgyu dang rkyen gyis ma bskyed par //
NK117(she)001:12947: chos rnams kun gyi snying po ru //
NK117(she)001:12948: rang byung lhun gyis grub pa'i sku //
NK117(she)001:12949: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs par 'dus //
NK117(she)001:12952: mtha' gang du yang ma lhung bas sangs /
NK117(she)001:12953: mtha' thams cad du ma 'gag par rang snang bas rgyas pa zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:12954: de yang snang stong gnyis kyi mthar ma lhung bas sangs /
NK117(she)001:12955: snang stong gnyis su ma 'gags par rang shar bas rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12956: de la sogs pa ste yod med bdag gzhan 'khor
NK117(she)001:12957: 'das la sogs pa'i mtha' gang du yang ma lhung
NK117(she)001:12958: bas sangs / mtha' thams cad du ma 'gag par rang shar bas rgyas pa zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:12961: rgyas ni chos sku gsal bas rgyas //
NK117(she)001:12963: khog dbub kyi skabs kyi lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:12965: spyir rnam pa shes pa'i tshogs brgyad du snang ba ni sems nyid rang snang ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:12966: de ngos zin pa ni rang byung gi ye shes mngon du rtogs pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:12967: de ltar rtogs pas mngon sum du snang ba nyid sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12968: de ngo sprad pa ni snyan rgyud zhal gyi gdams pa las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:12970: ngo bo ni rnam par shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:12971: ngos zin pa ni ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:12972: mngon sum pa ni sangs rgyas so //
NK117(she)001:12974: de yang bye brag cig la ngo sprad na /
NK117(she)001:12975: nyon mongs pa'am rnam par rtog pa gang shar yang
NK117(she)001:12976: de nyid rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:12978: de zhal gyi gdam ngag gis ngo sprad la cir
NK117(she)001:12979: snang rang grol chos sku chen por rtogs par bya'o
NK117(she)001:12981: thog ma med pa rang gi rtsal //
NK117(she)001:12982: gang mthong chos nyid cer mthong la //
NK117(she)001:12983: sgrib g.yog med pa ngo mtshar che //
NK117(she)001:12986: da lta'i shes pa 'di nyid la //
NK117(she)001:12987: ma bcos rang gsal chos skur shes //
NK117(she)001:12990: ye shes pas kyang nyon mongs gtso //
NK117(she)001:12991: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:12992: sangs rgyas pa'i rgyas lugs ni /
NK117(she)001:12993: che ba lngar sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK117(she)001:12994: khog dbub kyi skabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:12995: gnyis pa rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK117(she)001:12996: de ltar chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su ye nas sangs rgyas pa de nyid /
NK117(she)001:12997: rgyu las ma byung rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas /
NK117(she)001:12998: 'dus ma byas kyi ye shes mngon du rtogs shing sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK117(she)001:12999: rgyu las ma byung ba'i 'bras bu yin te /
NK117(she)001:13001: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu ni //
NK117(she)001:13002: byang chub sems kyi 'bras bu ste //
NK117(she)001:13003: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu yin //
NK117(she)001:13006: rang byung ye shes rgyus ma bskyed //
NK117(she)001:13007: rkyen med rang gsal rgyun mi chad //
NK117(she)001:13008: gnyen po rkyen gyis bcos su med //
NK117(she)001:13009: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu yin //
NK117(she)001:13011: des na 'bras bu sangs rgyas tshogs gnyis las ma
NK117(she)001:13012: byung bar ye nas sangs rgyas pa de nyid rtogs
NK117(she)001:13013: pas yon tan thams cad mngon du gyur pa yin
NK117(she)001:13015: skye med rang byung don rtogs na //
NK117(she)001:13016: tshogs gnyis ma bsags khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:13017: de phyir tshogs sogs rtse mo 'dra //
NK117(she)001:13019: gsum pa lung las ma byung gi gdam ngag ni /
NK117(she)001:13020: de ltar chos kun rang byung ye shes su sangs
NK117(she)001:13021: rgyas shing cir snang chos nyid cer mthong yin pas
NK117(she)001:13022: / tshig dang rtog dpyod ma yin par /
NK117(she)001:13023: snang ba gang snang gis rig pa'i rang ngo bstan
NK117(she)001:13024: nas rtogs shing nyams su myong ba ni lung las
NK117(she)001:13025: ma byung ba'i gdam ngag yin te /
NK117(she)001:13027: lung las ma byung gdam ngag ni //
NK117(she)001:13028: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don //
NK117(she)001:13029: sprul pa gang zag skal ldan yis //
NK117(she)001:13030: ci ltar rtogs shing rig pa de //
NK117(she)001:13031: lung las ma byung gdams ngag yin //
NK117(she)001:13034: ye nas rig pa rang la shar //
NK117(she)001:13035: dus de nyid du ma rig sangs //
NK117(she)001:13036: de phyir lung las ma byung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:13037: nges don snying po chos zhes bya //
NK117(she)001:13040: ye shes pas kyang nyon mongs gtso //
NK117(she)001:13041: zhes pa la sogs pa'i lung rnams dang ngo sprad do //
NK117(she)001:13042: de ltar rtogs shing nyams su myong ba ni theg
NK117(she)001:13043: pa thams cad sems su 'dus shing 'khor ba rang
NK117(she)001:13044: grol chos sku chen por shar te spang blang med
NK117(she)001:13045: par mngon du sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13046: rang byung bde ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:13047: sems las ma byung sangs rgyas rnyed //
NK117(she)001:13048: rgyu las ma byung 'bras bu rtogs //
NK117(she)001:13049: lung la ma brten chos rnams shes //
NK117(she)001:13050: theg dgu chos rnams gcig las med //
NK117(she)001:13051: dug lnga mya ngan 'das par dag /
NK117(she)001:13052: thugs kyi klong rdol chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:13054: gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po'i dgongs pa'am rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:13055: rdzogs chen gyi dgongs pa'i don bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13056: de mngon du rtogs pa'i lta ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13058: shes bya la gting mtha' med pas rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13059: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i dgongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13060: mtha' bzhi rang grol gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13061: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i dgongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13062: thig le nyag cig la sogs pa ming grangs kyis bsam mi khyab par bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13065: klong chen gcig po kun yin pas //
NK117(she)001:13066: thams cad kun gyi dngos gzhir shar //
NK117(she)001:13067: phyogs 'dzin gang yang ma spangs pas //
NK117(she)001:13068: phyogs med kun tu shar ba yin //
NK117(she)001:13069: zang thal yin pas kun tu shar //
NK117(she)001:13070: mu mtha' med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:13071: rang byung ye shes rgya chad med //
NK117(she)001:13072: rang bzhin gcig la mtha' med pas //
NK117(she)001:13073: byang chub sems la rgya chad med //
NK117(she)001:13074: ces pas spyir shes bya la gting mtha' med pas
NK117(she)001:13075: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i dgongs pa bstan pa
NK117(she)001:13076: dang / bye brag tu bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13078: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par rang byung ye shes kyi klong 'dus la /
NK117(she)001:13079: de nyid mu mtha' med cing klong yangs rgya khyon bral bas /
NK117(she)001:13080: shes bya la gting mtha' med pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:13081: de yang chos kyi dbyings la gting mtha' med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13082: sems can gyi khams la gting med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13083: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la gting mtha' med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13085: chos kyi dbyings kyis ma khyab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13087: ma gyur pa gcig kyang med pas mu mtha' med cing tshad las 'das pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13089: spyir chos kyi dbyings de sems can gyi khams kyis
NK117(she)001:13090: khengs shing bye brag tu yung 'bru tsam re re'i
NK117(she)001:13091: go sa na yang sems can tshad med grangs las
NK117(she)001:13093: de rnams kyang gcig gi go sa gcig gis ma bkag par gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13095: khams gsum gnas pa'i sems can kun //
NK117(she)001:13096: skad cig ma yis tshod tsam las //
NK117(she)001:13097: dus gcig dag tu sangs rgyas kyang //
NK117(she)001:13098: de la mang du gyur pa med //
NK117(she)001:13099: sems can nyung du mi 'gro ste //
NK117(she)001:13102: yung 'bru re re'i go sa na yang bskal pa
NK117(she)001:13103: nas bskal par bton kyang nyung du mi 'gro bar
NK117(she)001:13105: spyir sangs rgyas zhing khams mtha' med cing bye brag tu rdul phran re re'i steng na yang /
NK117(she)001:13106: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams tshad med cing grangs las 'das pa bzhugs par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:13107: mdo theg chen sgron ma las /
NK117(she)001:13108: skra yi nyag ma gcig la yang //
NK117(she)001:13109: sangs rgyas bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:13110: de dag 'dres par gyur pa med //
NK117(she)001:13113: rdul cig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te //
NK117(she)001:13114: zhing der bsam gyis mi khyab sangs rgyas rnams //
NK117(she)001:13117: rdul phran re re'i steng na'ang /
NK117(she)001:13118: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yas man dang /
NK117(she)001:13119: 'phred chags la sogs pa zhing khams dpag tu med pa yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:13120: des na shes bya la gting mtha' med pas mtha'
NK117(she)001:13121: phyogs re re 'dzin pa ni mun pa'i blo can
NK117(she)001:13123: shin tu gting ring dpag dka' bas //
NK117(she)001:13124: yangs la rgya che nam mkha'i klong //
NK117(she)001:13125: nam mkha'i klong la kha gting med //
NK117(she)001:13126: rang gsal rig pa phyi nang med //
NK117(she)001:13128: rdzogs chen lta ba gting mtha' med //
NK117(she)001:13129: ye bdal chen po'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:13130: thug pa med ces skyon 'gel ba //
NK117(she)001:13131: mtha' med ma go mun pa'i blo //
NK117(she)001:13132: mu med gcig chod bstan pa de //
NK117(she)001:13133: 'og ma'i klong du mi rigs ste //
NK117(she)001:13134: rdzogs pa chen po rigs pa'i gnad //
NK117(she)001:13136: phyi nang sgo phug med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:13137: ye nas kha gting med par gsal //
NK117(she)001:13139: des na shes bya la gting mtha' med pas rgya
NK117(she)001:13140: chad kyi snang ba gang yang ma spang ba'i rgya
NK117(she)001:13141: chad phyogs lhung med pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:13142: de gang du yang rgya ma chad cing phyogs su
NK117(she)001:13143: ma lhung bas phyogs med kun tu rang 'char ba
NK117(she)001:13144: yin la / phyogs med kun tu rang 'char zhing
NK117(she)001:13145: 'dug pa kas gang gis kyang phyogs su ma lhung
NK117(she)001:13146: yin la / ba'o // de yang gshis chos nyid
NK117(she)001:13147: de stong par rgya ma chad cing phyogs su ma
NK117(she)001:13149: lam gyis bsdus pa'i snang ba thams cad du rang
NK117(she)001:13150: yin la / ba'o // lhung pas / shar ba'o
NK117(she)001:13151: // shar ba'i dus nyid na snang ba rgya ma
NK117(she)001:13152: yin la / ba'o // lhung pas / shar ba'o
NK117(she)001:13153: // chad de / rang byung gi ye shes la
NK117(she)001:13154: dngos po'i sel med cing stong par rang grol ba'o
NK117(she)001:13155: yin la / ba'o // lhung pas / shar ba'o
NK117(she)001:13156: // chad de / // de gnyis su rgya ma
NK117(she)001:13157: yin la / ba'o // lhung pas / shar ba'o
NK117(she)001:13158: // chad de / // chad de / ngo bo
NK117(she)001:13159: dbyer med cing gnyis su med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13160: gnyis med du rgya ma chad de /
NK117(she)001:13161: phyogs med kun tu rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13162: de yang de nyid cir yang snang bas 'khor ba 'khrul pa'i chos su yang rang snang ba la /
NK117(she)001:13163: de nyid rgya chad kyi snang ba gang yang ma
NK117(she)001:13164: spangs pas dmyal ba la tsha grang gi sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:13165: du snang zhing dngos por zhe na /
NK117(she)001:13166: de'i dus nyid na rang byung gi ye shes de
NK117(she)001:13167: nyid dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal du rgya ma chad de
NK117(she)001:13168: / dmyal ba tsha grang gi sdug bsngal de nyid
NK117(she)001:13169: so ma nyams par sangs rgyas la sku dang ye
NK117(she)001:13170: shes dgongs pa bde ba chen por rang shar ro
NK117(she)001:13171: / // yang rgya chad kyi snang ba gang yang ma spangs pas /
NK117(she)001:13172: sangs rgyas la sdug bsngal gyi sel med cing dgongs pa bde ba chen por rgya ma chad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13173: de'i dus nyid na chos nyid rang byung gi ye
NK117(she)001:13174: shes de nyid sangs rgyas kyi phyogs su ma lhung
NK117(she)001:13175: ste / sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bde ba chen
NK117(she)001:13176: po de nyid so ma nyams par dmyal ba la
NK117(she)001:13177: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal du rang shar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13178: de gnyis gnyis kyi phyogs su ma lhung ste tha
NK117(she)001:13179: dad kyi snang ba so ma nyams par rang byung
NK117(she)001:13180: gi ye shes su dbyer mi phyed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13181: de'i dus nyid na dbyer med kyi phyogs su ma
NK117(she)001:13182: lhung ste tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma
NK117(she)001:13185: rig pa yul med yul du shar //
NK117(she)001:13186: kun gyi dngos gzhi yin pa ste //
NK117(she)001:13187: phyogs 'dzin gang yang ma spangs pas //
NK117(she)001:13188: phyogs med klong na 'byams pa ste //
NK117(she)001:13189: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:13190: nam mkha'i dbyings ltar dngos dang bral //
NK117(she)001:13191: mtha' bzhir ma 'gag ma zhen pas //
NK117(she)001:13192: yul la dmigs pa med pa ste //
NK117(she)001:13193: mi 'gyur lhun grub bdal ba che //
NK117(she)001:13194: klong yangs rgya khyon med par gsal //
NK117(she)001:13196: mtha' gnyis ma grub ma spangs pas //
NK117(she)001:13197: chos nyid klong la yangs dog med //
NK117(she)001:13198: bde bdal byang chub sems kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:13199: thams cad 'dus pas thig ler gcig /
NK117(she)001:13202: gang zag cig gi shes pa'i rgyud la sbyar na /
NK117(she)001:13203: rang gi sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes de
NK117(she)001:13204: nyid kor ling du rgya ma chad cing phyogs su
NK117(she)001:13205: ma lhung ste / rig pa la mu mtha' med
NK117(she)001:13206: cing kun la gnyis su med par khyab pas klong
NK117(she)001:13207: yangs rgya khyon bral ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:13208: shes bya la gting mtha' med cing phyi nang mtha' dbus med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13209: de nyid kyang rgya chad kyi snang ba gang yang
NK117(she)001:13210: ma spangs ba'i rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa yin
NK117(she)001:13212: yang rang byung gi ye shes de nyid snang stong
NK117(she)001:13213: rtag chad gcig tha dad la sogs pa rgya chad
NK117(she)001:13214: kyi snang ba gang yang ma spang pa'i rgya chad
NK117(she)001:13215: phyogs lhung med pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:13216: gong bzhin kun la shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:13217: khyad par du de nyid rnam rtog cig gi steng du ngo sprad nas rtogs par bya ba ni /
NK117(she)001:13218: gdams pa'i gnad las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:13219: de ltar ngo sprad cing rtogs pas phyogs 'dzin rang sar grol /
NK117(she)001:13220: cir snang rang byung ye shes su rtogs pas gol du gol sa med /
NK117(she)001:13222: 'gal du 'gal sa med par sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK117(she)001:13223: pa mngon sum du rtogs pa ni shes bya'i gting
NK117(she)001:13224: phyin pa'o // gnyis pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:13225: spyir snang srid 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:13226: thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang
NK117(she)001:13227: / bye brag so so nas ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13229: snang ba rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa snang tshul gang yang ma 'dres la /
NK117(she)001:13230: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13231: de'i rgyu mtshan ni rang byung ye shes su ma
NK117(she)001:13232: gyur pa'i chos gcig kyang med pas rang byung ye
NK117(she)001:13233: shes nyid 'khrul grol la sogs pa tha dad kyi
NK117(she)001:13234: snang ba gang yang ma 'dres la /
NK117(she)001:13235: de nyid mu mtha' med cing kun la gnyis su
NK117(she)001:13236: med par khyab pas yul med du yongs su rdzogs
NK117(she)001:13237: pa'o // de yang rig pa la mu mtha' med cing rgya chad phyogs lhung med pas /
NK117(she)001:13238: rig pa gcig gi klong du'ang thams cad ma 'dres par gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13239: des na 'dres pa'ang med la tha dad pa'ang med de ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13240: de'ang ma 'dres pa'i dus nyid na thams cad dbyer med dam yul med du yongs su rdzogs la /
NK117(she)001:13241: yongs rdzogs kyi dus nyid na ma 'dres par so sor snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13242: des na ma 'dres pas yongs rdzogs kyi go sa ma bkag /
NK117(she)001:13243: yongs rdzogs kyis ma 'dres pa'i go sa ma bkag par ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13245: mnyam nyid gcig pa'i klong dkyil nas //
NK117(she)001:13246: mi mnyam klong phran mtha' yas shar //
NK117(she)001:13248: cir yang yin no gang yang 'dra //
NK117(she)001:13249: dbyings la bzang ngan bye brag med //
NK117(she)001:13251: klong chen gcig gi klong dkyil nas //
NK117(she)001:13252: klong phran mtha' yas kun shar kyang //
NK117(she)001:13254: kun kyang 'byams pa de ru gcig /
NK117(she)001:13257: sangs rgyas ye shes thugs dang sems can sems //
NK117(she)001:13258: 'brel med so sor snang ba ma yin te //
NK117(she)001:13259: btsal med rang sems chos skur gcig pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:13260: blo dngos gcig par yid ces sems nyid yin //
NK117(she)001:13263: yongs su rdzogs par kun mnyam yang //
NK117(she)001:13264: ma 'dres par yang kun tu snang //
NK117(she)001:13266: thams cad ma 'dres tha dad pa //
NK117(she)001:13267: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK117(she)001:13268: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK117(she)001:13269: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK117(she)001:13272: rang byung ye shes mkha' klong nas //
NK117(she)001:13273: shar ba'i chos rnams thams cad kun //
NK117(she)001:13274: 'dzin pas so sor brtags pa kun //
NK117(she)001:13275: dbyings la bye brag gang yang med //
NK117(she)001:13276: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dbyings kyi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13277: rang sar grol ba dbyings kyi klong //
NK117(she)001:13279: de yang ma 'dres pa ni ngo bo ma 'dres te shes pa'i rgyud ma 'dres /
NK117(she)001:13280: mtshan nyid ma 'dres te 'khrul grol la sogs pa mtshan nyid so sor 'dzin /
NK117(she)001:13281: mtshon tshul ma 'dres te 'khrul grol la sogs pa mtshon tshul tha dad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13282: yongs rdzogs ni rig pa la mu mtha' med cing
NK117(she)001:13283: kun la gnyis su stod par khyab pas yul med
NK117(she)001:13285: de yang yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas ngo bo /
NK117(she)001:13286: mtshan nyid mtshan tshul gsum ka dbyer med du yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13288: rgyud gcig gis bsdus pa'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs dang /
NK117(she)001:13289: rgyud tha dad kyis bsdus pa'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs so //
NK117(she)001:13290: snga ma ni rig pa'i rgyud gcig la 'khrul gro la sogs pa mtshon tshul tha dad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13292: rig pa'i rgyud ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13293: de yang gzhi chos dbyings ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13294: 'gro drug gi 'khrul snang ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13295: lam theg pa dgu ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13296: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13298: gzhi la rig pa ma 'dres te /
NK117(she)001:13299: 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad du so sor rang snang ba la /
NK117(she)001:13300: de nyid rang byung gi ye shes mu mtha' med
NK117(she)001:13301: pas kun la gnyis su med cing yul med du
NK117(she)001:13304: dbyings nyid med la mi zad pa //
NK117(she)001:13305: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK117(she)001:13306: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK117(she)001:13307: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK117(she)001:13310: nyon mongs dang ni ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:13311: snang srid skye dgu yod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:13312: mi srid med pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:13313: rang byung ye shes klong dkyil du //
NK117(she)001:13314: ma rdzogs pa ni med pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:13315: rdzogs chen lhun grub bla na med //
NK117(she)001:13316: mnyam pa nyid du thag chod pas //
NK117(she)001:13317: kun kyang rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK117(she)001:13320: dngos de nyid kyang mdor bstan na //
NK117(she)001:13321: chos sems ye nas gnyis su med //
NK117(she)001:13322: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal //
NK117(she)001:13325: 'gro drug gi shes rgyud ma 'dres te bde sdug la sogs pa sna tshogs so sor snang la /
NK117(she)001:13326: de nyid rig pa mu mtha' med pas gnyis su med par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13327: de yang phyi 'byung ba lnga ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13328: nang gzugs sgra dri ro la sogs pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13329: bde sdug la sogs pa snang tshul tha dad pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13330: chos can gcig la chos can tha dad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13332: snang ba rang sar dag pa la //
NK117(she)001:13333: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung //
NK117(she)001:13334: nam mkha' la sogs 'byung ba lnga //
NK117(she)001:13335: rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:13336: de yang rig pa rang gi stobs //
NK117(she)001:13338: chos nyid 'dzin pa kun bral la //
NK117(she)001:13339: gzugs dang sgra dang dri dang ro //
NK117(she)001:13340: reg la sogs pa'i 'dod yon lnga //
NK117(she)001:13341: rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:13342: de yang rig pa rang gi stobs //
NK117(she)001:13344: rang bzhin gcig pa'i chos rnams la //
NK117(she)001:13346: rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:13347: de yang rang snang gcig gis stobs //
NK117(she)001:13350: chos can ma 'dres sna tshogs pa //
NK117(she)001:13351: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK117(she)001:13352: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK117(she)001:13353: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK117(she)001:13355: de yang spyir chos can gcig la 'khor 'das kyi
NK117(she)001:13356: chos kun ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin
NK117(she)001:13357: te / chos can gcig la snang tshul bcu bdun
NK117(she)001:13358: la sogs pa ma 'dres par rang snang bas so
NK117(she)001:13359: te / // bye brag tu rdul phran re re'i
NK117(she)001:13360: steng na yang sems can kyi khams ma 'dres la
NK117(she)001:13362: yang me chu la sogs pa tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma 'dres la /
NK117(she)001:13363: snang ba gcig la me chu la sogs pa'i snang
NK117(she)001:13364: ba cir yang snang bas gnyis med du yongs su
NK117(she)001:13366: khams ni ma 'dres sa bon nyid //
NK117(she)001:13367: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK117(she)001:13368: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK117(she)001:13369: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK117(she)001:13372: lam ma 'dres te theg pa rim pa dgu la
NK117(she)001:13373: sogs pa so sor snang la rang byung gi ye
NK117(she)001:13376: theg pa'i khyad par ji snyed du //
NK117(she)001:13377: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK117(she)001:13378: klong chen gcig gi yon tan ste //
NK117(she)001:13379: gdul bya rnams la bstan par zad //
NK117(she)001:13381: gnyen po ye shes phra rags kyis //
NK117(she)001:13382: brgyad khri bzhi stong theg pa'i grangs //
NK117(she)001:13383: mnyam pa'i klong las ma g.yos te //
NK117(she)001:13384: tha dad med par dbyings su gcig /
NK117(she)001:13386: lta bsgom spyod pa 'bras bu rnams //
NK117(she)001:13387: gser dngul phra men rdzas lta bur //
NK117(she)001:13388: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gcig gi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13389: khyad par gyur pas a ti'i rdzongs //
NK117(she)001:13392: chos kun ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pa //
NK117(she)001:13393: nges par ji ltar yin pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:13394: phyin ci ma log nyid brjod na //
NK117(she)001:13395: de ni rnam dag lam chen yin //
NK117(she)001:13398: sangs rgyas kyi thugs dgongs ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:13399: de yang spyir sku dang ye shes la sogs pa ma 'dres so sor snang la /
NK117(she)001:13400: rang byung gi ye shes su tha dad med par yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13401: bye brag tu rdul phran re re'i steng na yang /
NK117(she)001:13402: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams la sogs pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13404: chos kun rnam par dag pa nyid //
NK117(she)001:13405: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK117(she)001:13406: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs na //
NK117(she)001:13407: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK117(she)001:13409: rdzogs sku ma 'dres phun sum tshogs //
NK117(she)001:13411: sprul pa med 'byung rgyun mi chad //
NK117(she)001:13413: ye shes kun mkhyen skye 'gag med //
NK117(she)001:13414: yongs su rdzogs pa stong bdag med //
NK117(she)001:13415: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs pa //
NK117(she)001:13416: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK117(she)001:13419: 'bar ba'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK117(she)001:13420: rang gsal rig pa kun mkhyen thugs //
NK117(she)001:13421: mnyam la ma 'dres kun tu bzang //
NK117(she)001:13422: ma 'dres gsal ba'i ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:13425: mkha' la gza' skar bkram pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:13426: ma 'dres rang gsal dbyings su rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:13427: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK117(she)001:13428: ma bcos ji bzhin rig pa'i klong //
NK117(she)001:13430: de ltar na dmyal ba la sangs rgyas kyi bde ba yongs su rdzogs sam ma rdzogs /
NK117(she)001:13431: sangs rgyas la dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal yongs su rdzogs sam ma rdzogs /
NK117(she)001:13432: ma rdzogs na yongs rdzogs nyams la /
NK117(she)001:13433: rdzogs na bde sdug khyad par med par 'gyur ro
NK117(she)001:13434: zhe na tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma
NK117(she)001:13435: 'gag pas gnyis med du yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13436: de yang dbyer med pa'i ngos nas sems can la sangs rgyas kyi bde ba yongs su rdzogs la /
NK117(she)001:13437: tha dad kyi snang ba ma spangs pa'i ngos nas
NK117(she)001:13438: rang gis rang ngo ma shes te sems can la
NK117(she)001:13440: yang yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas sangs rgyas la dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal rdzogs la /
NK117(she)001:13441: tha dad kyi snang ba gang yang ma spangs pa'i ngos nas /
NK117(she)001:13442: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su lhag ma med par rtogs te /
NK117(she)001:13443: sdug bsngal gyi sel med par rang grol zhing dgongs pa bde ba chen por gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13444: des na dmyal ba la sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams
NK117(she)001:13445: kyang lcags sreg gi sa gzhi la sogs par snang
NK117(she)001:13446: la / sangs rgyas la lcags sreg gi sa gzhi
NK117(she)001:13447: la sogs pa yang bde ba can la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:13448: zhing khams rnam par dag par snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13449: des na ma 'dres te tha dad par yang snang la /
NK117(she)001:13450: yongs su rdzogs te dbyer med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13451: de ltar chos kun ma 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs par rtogs pas /
NK117(she)001:13452: gang gi yang phyogs su ma lhung zhing gang dang yang mi 'gal bas /
NK117(she)001:13453: phyogs ris zhe 'dod med par dgongs pa'i gting phyin par rtogs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:13454: gsum pa mtha' bzhi rang grol ni /
NK117(she)001:13455: stong mtha' rang grol rang byung ye shes su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13456: snang mtha' rang grol rang byung ye shes su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13457: gnyis mtha' rang grol rang byung ye shes su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13458: gnyis med rang grol rang byung ye shes su ngo sprad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13460: stong par gsung ba rnams kyang drang don phyogs gcig yin te /
NK117(she)001:13461: de yang spyir shes bya'i gshis stong ma myong ste /
NK117(she)001:13462: 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad du rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13464: ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i dus su stong ma myong ste /
NK117(she)001:13465: 'gro drug gi snang tshul bsam gyis mi khyab par rang snang /
NK117(she)001:13466: lam nyams su len pa'i dus su stong ma myong ste /
NK117(she)001:13467: theg pa'i bye brag dang ting nge 'dzin gyi mthong snang dang /
NK117(she)001:13468: lam gyi yon tan phyogs med du rang snang /
NK117(she)001:13469: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa stong ma myong ste /
NK117(she)001:13470: sku dang ye shes la sogs pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes su rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13472: snang gsum grags pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:13473: 'di la btags na btags snang phyir //
NK117(she)001:13474: thams cad kun snang gzhi rtsar bshad //
NK117(she)001:13477: ji ltar snang zhing grags pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:13478: rang las byung bas rang gi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13481: thog ma med pa rang gi rtsal //
NK117(she)001:13482: gar mthong chos nyid cer mthong la //
NK117(she)001:13483: sgrib g.yog med par ngo mtshar che //
NK117(she)001:13485: gzhan yang snang bar bshad pa la sogs pa'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:13486: de ltar snang ba sems nyid rang snang du ngo sprad pa /
NK117(she)001:13487: snang ba phyogs med rang grol rang byung ye shes mngon sum du snang zhing rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13488: gnyis pa snang bar gsung pa'i lung rnams kyang drang don phyogs re yin te /
NK117(she)001:13489: chos kun ji ltar snang yang sems nyid dam rang byung gi ye shes rang snang ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:13490: sems nyid las log pa rdul cha tsam yang med cing /
NK117(she)001:13491: sems nyid la bdag gzhan dang dngos po dang mtshan ma'i sel med pas /
NK117(she)001:13492: snang ba rang grol chos kun stong pa chen po yin te /
NK117(she)001:13494: bdag las gzhan pa mi snang zhing //
NK117(she)001:13496: snang med stong pa chen por gsung //
NK117(she)001:13498: stong pa de yang chad stong snang ba gtan med kyi stong pa ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:13499: rnam pa mchog ldan gyi stong pa chen po yin te /
NK117(she)001:13500: rnam pa kun ldan stong chen po //
NK117(she)001:13501: sangs rgyas pas kyang sngar sangs rgyas //
NK117(she)001:13504: mtshan med thig le lhun 'byams la //
NK117(she)001:13505: phyi nang gnyis ka gnyis med stong //
NK117(she)001:13506: kun stong khyab bdal chos kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:13507: ji ltar stong yang dbyings nyid gsal //
NK117(she)001:13509: stong nyid snying po klong chen 'di //
NK117(she)001:13510: skad cig rtog pa tsam gyis kyang //
NK117(she)001:13511: byang chub klong du der son pas //
NK117(she)001:13512: mtshan ma'i chos la rag ma lus //
NK117(she)001:13513: stong pa'i chos la blo mi gnas //
NK117(she)001:13515: stong par gsung pa'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:13516: de nyid kyang sems nyid rang snang du ngo sprad la /
NK117(she)001:13517: stong pa chos nyid rang grol rang byung ye shes rang gsal du rtogs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:13519: snang stong gnyis la sogs pa gsungs 'ang drang don phyogs re yin te /
NK117(she)001:13520: ngo bo snang stong gnyis su med cing bden pa dbyer med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13521: de yang ji ltar snang yang rang byung gi ye
NK117(she)001:13522: shes rang snang yin la ji ltar stong yang rang
NK117(she)001:13523: byung gi ye shes rang stong yin pas /
NK117(she)001:13524: chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la snang stong
NK117(she)001:13525: gnyis su med cing bden rdzun gnyis su med pas
NK117(she)001:13526: ngo bo dbyer med chen po yin te /
NK117(she)001:13528: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:13529: bden pa gnyis kyi snyad las 'das //
NK117(she)001:13532: yod mthong grags pa'i chos rnams dang //
NK117(she)001:13533: med snang brtags pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK117(she)001:13534: rang las tha dad med pas na //
NK117(she)001:13535: gnyis su med par ye nas gsal //
NK117(she)001:13536: ltos pa med par rang sar grol //
NK117(she)001:13538: gzhan yang dbyer med la sogs pa'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:13539: de nyid kyang sems nyid rang snang du ngo sprad la /
NK117(she)001:13540: gnyis med chos nyid rang grol rang byung ye shes mngon sum du rtogs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:13542: gnyis med dang dbyer med la sogs pa gsung pa'ang drang don phyogs re yin te /
NK117(she)001:13543: ngo bo rang snang stong gnyis la sogs pa snang
NK117(she)001:13544: tshul phyogs med du 'char zhing ma 'dres la yongs
NK117(she)001:13547: cis kyang ma bsgribs ye shes mchog /
NK117(she)001:13548: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gsal //
NK117(she)001:13551: cir yang snang ba'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:13552: sna tshogs 'byung ba dbyings kyi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13553: mu mtha' med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:13554: mtha' yas snang ba dbyings kyi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13555: brjod du med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:13556: rnam grangs 'byung ba ngo mtshar che //
NK117(she)001:13558: gnyis med dang ma 'dres la sogs pa'i lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:13559: de nyid kyang sems nyid rang snang du ngo sprad la /
NK117(she)001:13560: ma 'dres gnyis snang chos nyid rang grol rang byung la ye shes mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13561: de re re la yang mtha' bzhi rang grol rang
NK117(she)001:13562: byung ye shes su gtan la dbab cing rtogs par
NK117(she)001:13563: bya ba dang spyir dril te /
NK117(she)001:13564: mtha' bzhi rang grol rang byung ye shes mngon sum du ngo sprad cing rtogs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:13566: mtha' bzhir ma 'gags ma zhen pas //
NK117(she)001:13567: yul la dmigs pa med pa ste //
NK117(she)001:13568: mi 'gyur lhun grub bdal ba che //
NK117(she)001:13569: klong yangs rgya khyon med par gsal //
NK117(she)001:13571: de ltar mtha' bzhi rang grol mngon sum du rtogs pas gol sa thams cad shugs la chod /
NK117(she)001:13572: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa rang sar grol //
NK117(she)001:13573: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mngon du rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13575: mtha' yi mun pa sel ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:13576: ye shes sgron ma dbyings su gsal //
NK117(she)001:13577: mtha' bzhi ma spangs byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:13578: mtha' yi skyon gyis ma reg pas //
NK117(she)001:13579: gol sa thams cad shugs la chod //
NK117(she)001:13580: g.yang sa med pa'i sems nyid la //
NK117(she)001:13581: btsal med sku gsum lhun rdzogs kyang //
NK117(she)001:13583: bzhi pa mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen pa'i dgongs pa bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:13585: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams dril //
NK117(she)001:13586: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13588: spyir chos kun mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen por bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:13590: dang po ni chos kun rang byung gi ye shes su bzang ngan blang dor med par mnyam zhing /
NK117(she)001:13591: chos kun lhag ma med par rig pa bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:13592: chen po'i rgyan nam rol par yongs su rdzogs pa'o
NK117(she)001:13594: thams cad gcig tu rdzogs pas na //
NK117(she)001:13595: theg pa'i yang theg spyi yi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13596: bdag nyid chen po kun 'dus dpal //
NK117(she)001:13597: rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa'i mchog /
NK117(she)001:13600: rang byung gyi ye shes rgya chad phyogs lhung med
NK117(she)001:13601: pas 'gro drug yul yul can gyi snang ba yang
NK117(she)001:13602: rang snang bas 'gro drug yul du snang ba dang
NK117(she)001:13603: yang mnyam la / de nyid yul yul can med
NK117(she)001:13604: par rang byung gi ye shes su yongs su rdzogs
NK117(she)001:13605: yang mnyam la / pas / 'gro drug rang grol /
NK117(she)001:13606: cir snang rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan no //
NK117(she)001:13607: yang chos nyid la dngos por ma grub cing mtshan
NK117(she)001:13608: ma rang sar grol bas mu steg chad pa dang
NK117(she)001:13610: de nyid chos nyid rang snang 'pho 'gyur med cing
NK117(she)001:13611: chos kun rang byung ye shes su lhag ma med
NK117(she)001:13613: chad pa rang grol de nyid kyang rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan no //
NK117(she)001:13614: yang rang byung gi ye shes la dus gsum 'pho
NK117(she)001:13615: 'gyur med pas mu stegs rtag pa dang yang phyogs
NK117(she)001:13616: gcig mnyam la / de nyid la dngos por mtshan
NK117(she)001:13617: ma'i sel med cing mtha' dbus phyogs cha med pas
NK117(she)001:13619: chos kun rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan nam rol par rang snang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13620: yang rang byung gi ye shes de nyid ji ltar bltas pa ltar snang bas /
NK117(she)001:13621: theg brgyad kyi 'dod pa dang yang mnyam la /
NK117(she)001:13622: de nyid phyogs ris med pa rang byung gi ye shes su rdzogs pas theg brgyad rang grol /
NK117(she)001:13623: chos kun rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan no //
NK117(she)001:13624: yang chos kun rang byung ye shes su sangs rgyas pas sangs rgyas thams cad dang yang mnyam la /
NK117(she)001:13625: de nyid rang byung ye shes su rdzogs pas sangs
NK117(she)001:13626: rgyas gzhan nas tshol ba'i zhe 'dod rang grol zhing
NK117(she)001:13627: / chos kun rig pa bdag nyid chen po'i rgyan no //
NK117(she)001:13628: de nyid rgyas par 'dod na gong gi theg brgyad
NK117(she)001:13629: kyi dmigs phye la bye brag so so nas rgyas
NK117(she)001:13630: par bshad do // klong chen las /
NK117(she)001:13631: rigs drug rgyud lnga'i sems can la //
NK117(she)001:13632: chos nyid spyi khyab yin pas na //
NK117(she)001:13633: yul med rig pa ye nas che //
NK117(she)001:13635: a ti yo ga'i lta ba ni /
NK117(she)001:13636: chos nyid rgya chad med pa la //
NK117(she)001:13637: gnyis ka rang shar rang grol bas //
NK117(she)001:13638: mu stegs ma spangs rdzogs chen rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13640: a ti yo ga'i lta ba ni //
NK117(she)001:13641: rgya chad med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:13642: gnyis ka rang shar rang grol bas //
NK117(she)001:13643: a nu ma spangs rdzogs chen rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13645: nyan thos nas ma h+aa man chad la de bzhin du 'agre'o //
NK117(she)001:13646: de ltar chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la
NK117(she)001:13647: gang dang yang ma 'dres par rang sa rang sar
NK117(she)001:13648: mnyam la / shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma
NK117(she)001:13649: med par bdag nyid chen por rdzogs pas phyogs ris
NK117(she)001:13651: chos kun mnyam nyid rang snang du rtogs pa ni shes bya'i gting phyin /
NK117(she)001:13653: phyogs med kyi klong du grol ba ni sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13655: bya bral ngang du kun rdzogs pas //
NK117(she)001:13656: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13657: ma spang rang sar grol ba'i klong //
NK117(she)001:13658: sangs rgyas sku dang sems can lus //
NK117(she)001:13659: ji ltar snang ba dbyings kyi rgyan //
NK117(she)001:13661: lnga pa thig le nyag cig la sogs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:13662: 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa thams cad thig le
NK117(she)001:13663: nyag cig tu dbyer med cing klong yangs rgya khyon
NK117(she)001:13664: bral bas thams cad 'dus shing rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:13666: phyogs mtshams bla 'og mthon dman kun //
NK117(she)001:13667: thig le gcig gi rgyar mnyam pas //
NK117(she)001:13668: sangs rgyas gong na med par gsal //
NK117(she)001:13672: thig le chen po gcig po nyid //
NK117(she)001:13673: ther zug rgyun las ye nas grol //
NK117(she)001:13676: thig ni mi yo mi 'gyur drang po spros dang bral //
NK117(she)001:13677: le ni kun dngos bdag la khyab gcig ste gcig po de ltar shar //
NK117(she)001:13678: nyag ni zab cing phra ste shin tu brtag par dka' //
NK117(she)001:13679: gcig ni ci bsam ci dran yul dang sems kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:13680: zhes yid skyob las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:13681: de bzhin du rang snang dang /
NK117(she)001:13684: mnyam pa nyid la sogs pa rgyu mtshan phyogs re
NK117(she)001:13685: nas mtshon pa'i ming du btags shing gang yang mi
NK117(she)001:13687: gzhi'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:13688: gnyis pa mngon sum du rtogs pa'i lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:13689: de ltar chos kun rang byung ye shes mngon sum du rtogs pas phyogs ris zhe 'dod bral /
NK117(she)001:13690: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid shes /
NK117(she)001:13692: rang sems ngo bo mthong bas the tsom yid gnyis grol /
NK117(she)001:13693: 'gyur med gdengs dang ldan zhing log rtog rtsad nas grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:13695: rang sems tshad ma'i gdengs ldan pas //
NK117(she)001:13696: mi 'gyur don gyi g.yung drung yin //
NK117(she)001:13697: lung rig don gyi bya ra bas //
NK117(she)001:13698: log rtog kun bsal rdul du brlagsa //
NK117(she)001:13701: rigs pa mchog ldan bde gshegs bka' //
NK117(she)001:13702: rang byung tshad ma mngon sum gsal //
NK117(she)001:13705: ye nas rang byung ye shes la //
NK117(she)001:13706: chos kun 'dus gsum sgrib med pas //
NK117(she)001:13707: spong dang len pa mi mnga' ste //
NK117(she)001:13708: rang byung ye shes 'gyur med gnas //
NK117(she)001:13710: de yang hril gyis dril na /
