NK117(she)001:15429: nga yi yon tan phyogs su ma chad pas //
NK117(she)001:15430: yon tan mchog tu gyur par rgyal bas gsung //
NK117(she)001:15432: man ngag rgya mtsho klong las /
NK117(she)001:15433: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK117(she)001:15434: kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK117(she)001:15435: chos nyid rig pa'i rgyan zhes gsung //
NK117(she)001:15438: chos sku 'bras bu rang gsal la //
NK117(she)001:15439: rin chen 'bar ba lhun grub ltar //
NK117(she)001:15441: skal ldan rang rkyen nyi ma bzhin //
NK117(she)001:15445: dag pa'i zhing dang gzhal yas khang //
NK117(she)001:15447: ye shes gsal ba'i ngo bor snang //
NK117(she)001:15453: a mu'i skabs dang zhing khams la sogs pa'i skabs nas ston pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:15455: brtsal med lhun grub kyi phrin las dang /
NK117(she)001:15456: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi phrin las dang lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:15458: rtsol ba med par lhun grub bde ba chen po'i ngang las /
NK117(she)001:15459: gang la gang 'dul du thabs mkhas mdzad pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas don 'byung ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:15461: bya bral 'od gsal chos dbyings la //
NK117(she)001:15462: phrin las brtsal med lhun grub la //
NK117(she)001:15463: 'od gsal ye shes phyogs ris med //
NK117(she)001:15464: brtsal med phrin las mchog gi klong //
NK117(she)001:15466: gdul bya'i bsam pa ji bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:15467: thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK117(she)001:15468: thabs mkhas spyod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:15469: dus gcig nyid la gsal bar 'char //
NK117(she)001:15472: phyogs ris med par ye bdal pas //
NK117(she)001:15473: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las yin //
NK117(she)001:15474: rnam dag dbyings la bzhugs bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:15475: yongs la khyab pa'i thugs rje 'byung //
NK117(she)001:15478: man ngag brgya mtsho'i klong las /
NK117(she)001:15479: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod kyang //
NK117(she)001:15480: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa la //
NK117(she)001:15482: zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi ba dang /
NK117(she)001:15485: drag pos 'dul ba la drag pos don mdzad de gang la gang 'dul du don mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15486: drug pa dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:15487: gzhan gyi mtha' bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:15488: dgongs pa ji ltar bzhugs pa'i tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:15490: shing gi me dpung ltar sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma 'dres par rgyud tha dad par 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:15491: chu la chu thim pa ltar sangs rgyas thams cad rgyud cig tu 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15493: shing tha dad kyi me rang bzhin nam mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:15494: me ru gcig kyang ngo bo tha dad pa ltar
NK117(she)001:15495: dang / 'bras bu'i phung po ltar mtshan nyid dang
NK117(she)001:15496: tshogs pa gcig kyang ngo bo tha dad pa ltar
NK117(she)001:15497: dang / / sangs rgyas thams cad kyang sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:15498: par mtshan nyid gcig kyang sbyangs pa'i ye shes ma
NK117(she)001:15499: dang / / 'dres te / rgyud tha dad par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15500: de yang sangs rgyas la gzung 'dzin yod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:15501: dgongs pa kor ling mu mtha' can gyi skyon 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:15502: dbu ma'i skabs su bshad pa'i skyon de rnams kyang 'ong la /
NK117(she)001:15504: shing gi me dpung ltar 'dod pa //
NK117(she)001:15505: drang pa tsam ste de nyid min //
NK117(she)001:15508: phyi pas shing gi me dpung ltar //
NK117(she)001:15509: rang bzhin dbyer med ngo bo nyid //
NK117(she)001:15510: kun mkhyen tha dad bzhugs pa de //
NK117(she)001:15511: phan tshun mi mkhyen kun mkhyen bral //
NK117(she)001:15512: mkhyen pa gzung 'dzin rnam rtog ste //
NK117(she)001:15513: rang bzhin spros bral dmar thag las //
NK117(she)001:15514: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:15516: mar la mar thim pa ltar du gcig tu thim ste stong nas med par 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:15517: rig pa'i rgyud cig tu thim nas mkhyen pa la sogs pa yod par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15519: gong du skur 'debs kyi mtha' bsal ba'i skabs nas bshad pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:15521: mu steg rig byed kyi mtha' gsang gsang bar smra ba'i sde pa dang 'dra ba'i skyon 'ong ste /
NK117(she)001:15522: mu stegs kyi skabs su bshad pa dang mthun no //
NK117(she)001:15524: don dam gcig pur ma yin phyir //
NK117(she)001:15525: chu la chu ltar gcig pa'ang min //
NK117(she)001:15528: kun tu ma 'dres ma shes par //
NK117(she)001:15529: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:15531: 'o na dgongs pa'i bzhugs tshul ji ltar yin na /
NK117(she)001:15532: thun mong pa'i gcig dang tha dad las grol zhing /
NK117(she)001:15533: dgongs pa'i rgyud ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par bzhugs pa gsung te /
NK117(she)001:15535: gcig dang du ma bral ba yin //
NK117(she)001:15536: mtha' dang dbus med de bzhin nyid //
NK117(she)001:15539: mnyam pa gsum pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:15540: nges par rgyud cig ma 'dres pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15541: tha snyad bral ba'i tshul du bzhugs //
NK117(she)001:15544: gcig dang tha dad yin pas na //
NK117(she)001:15545: gcig dang tha dad grol bar gsung //
NK117(she)001:15546: de bas 'khor 'das 'brel zhing rgya yang chad //
NK117(she)001:15547: mtha' dngos mtha' bral kun dngos kun dang bral //
NK117(she)001:15549: gong gi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15550: bdun pa theg pa rim dgu'i 'bras bu gcig gam tha dad pa ni /
NK117(she)001:15551: shes bya ji lta ba nyid mthar phyin te /
NK117(she)001:15552: mthar thams cad rdzogs pa chen po ltar spangs thob
NK117(she)001:15553: med par sangs rgyas tsam na khyad par med la
NK117(she)001:15554: / rang sa rang sa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK117(she)001:15555: theg pa dgu ka la khyad par yod de /
NK117(she)001:15557: gong ma gong ma'i lam stegs dang /
NK117(she)001:15558: gong ma gong ma la sems bskyed dgos par bshad pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15559: de la a nu man chad kyi khyad par ni rang rang gi skabs nas bshad pa bzhin la /
NK117(she)001:15560: 'dir a nu man chad dang a ti'i khyad par ni /
NK117(she)001:15561: khyad par 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK117(she)001:15564: lta ba la khyad par yod pa bzhin 'bras bu la yang khyad par yod de /
NK117(she)001:15565: lta ba'i don de nyid mngon du byas pa nyid 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:15567: mi mthun gzhung gis sangs rgyas pa'ang /
NK117(she)001:15568: lta spyod ting nge 'dzin lam rim bzhin //
NK117(she)001:15569: grub pa'i mtha' la khyad par pas //
NK117(she)001:15570: lta ba'i sgrib pas phyi pa yin //
NK117(she)001:15573: byang chub sems dpa'i sangs rgyas kyang //
NK117(she)001:15574: yang ti rdzogs chen yas bltas na //
NK117(she)001:15575: nges don snying po ma mthong phyir //
NK117(she)001:15576: gzhi gnas ma rig yod pas na //
NK117(she)001:15577: rtsol ba byas pas chos sku bsgribs //
NK117(she)001:15578: de phyir yang dag sangs rgyas min //
NK117(she)001:15580: de dag rgyud lung sangs rgyas kyang //
NK117(she)001:15581: yang ti rdzogs chen yas bltas na //
NK117(she)001:15582: rang byung nges don ma shes pas //
NK117(she)001:15583: ched du byas pa'i rtsol bas sgrubs //
NK117(she)001:15584: re dog phra mo yod pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:15585: nges lung ma shes snang bar 'chil //
NK117(she)001:15586: gzugs can sangs rgyas 'dod pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:15587: chos sku'i sangs rgyas don la sgrib //
NK117(she)001:15590: gnyis med don la gnyis gzung nas //
NK117(she)001:15591: bskal pa grangs med gsum nyid du //
NK117(she)001:15592: sa bcu lam lnga pha rol phyin //
NK117(she)001:15593: sbyong zhing gnyis rtog spong len can //
NK117(she)001:15594: rang sa thob kyang mthar ma phyin //
NK117(she)001:15597: dbyings dang ye shes rang bzhin gyis //
NK117(she)001:15598: rgyu 'bras dag pa'i tshul du blta //
NK117(she)001:15600: rdo rje sems dpa'i sa la 'gro //
NK117(she)001:15601: rang sa 'bras bu mngon thob kyang //
NK117(she)001:15602: mthar thug 'bras bu de la med //
NK117(she)001:15605: sbyangs bgrod rtsol bas 'jug gnas brtan //
NK117(she)001:15606: bsti gnas tsam du bstan pa yin //
NK117(she)001:15609: kun tu 'od kyi sa ru bzhag pa yin //
NK117(she)001:15610: don la nges par brtags na drang ba tsam //
NK117(she)001:15611: zhes pa la sogs pa a ti'i rgyud lung man ngag thams cad las gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:15613: ngo bo la spang thob yod med kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:15614: shes bya la phyogs tsam 'dzin mi 'dzin gyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:15615: don che ba lnga yis khyad par du dpag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15617: a nu man chad 'khor ba la grol 'dod kyi blos /
NK117(she)001:15618: sangs rgyas bzang po gcig thob par 'dod pas mtshan
NK117(she)001:15619: nyid pa dngos su spang thob can du 'dod pa
NK117(she)001:15620: dang / ma h+aa dang a nu la'ang shugs kyis spang thob byung bas /
NK117(she)001:15621: shes bya ji lta ba nyid lhag ma med par mngon du ma gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:15622: a ti ni chos kun rang byung gi ye shes la 'khor 'das gnyis su med pas /
NK117(she)001:15623: spang bya 'khor ba dang thob bya sangs rgyas gnyis su med de /
NK117(she)001:15624: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par mngon du gyur pas khyad par du dpag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15626: nyan thos a nu man chod du //
NK117(she)001:15627: theg pa'i bye brag bsam yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:15628: bsgrubs nas grub pa'i 'bras bu de //
NK117(she)001:15629: bsgrub bya sgrub byed yod pas na //
NK117(she)001:15630: de'ang yul dang yul can med //
NK117(she)001:15633: bskal pa'i grangs dang tshe rabs su //
NK117(she)001:15634: dman pas blang dor ci byas dang //
NK117(she)001:15635: 'bring gis dmigs pas grol thob kyang //
NK117(she)001:15636: don 'di nyams su ma myong na //
NK117(she)001:15637: brtag pa nyid la ma rtogs pa //
NK117(she)001:15638: spang thob ngo bo gdod nas med //
NK117(she)001:15641: nang pa snang stong zung 'jug mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:15643: byang sems bde chen chos nyid bdal //
NK117(she)001:15644: snang dang stong dang bden gnyis las //
NK117(she)001:15645: grol la dbyer med mur thug pas //
NK117(she)001:15646: phyogs med bde chen dmar thag las //
NK117(she)001:15650: len med spong dang yongs su bral bas na //
NK117(she)001:15651: dus gsum mnyam nyid rdo rje sku gsung thugs //
NK117(she)001:15654: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15655: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od bdal yang //
NK117(she)001:15656: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du //
NK117(she)001:15657: sangs ma rgyas par byed pa yi //
NK117(she)001:15658: chos ni rdul tsam yod min pas //
NK117(she)001:15659: sangs rgyas med pa'i che bar gsung //
NK117(she)001:15662: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:15664: nam mkha' klong yangs kyi rgyud las /
NK117(she)001:15665: ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK117(she)001:15666: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' las 'das //
NK117(she)001:15667: gzhan yang chos kyi dbyings kyi klong //
NK117(she)001:15668: rdzogs ni lhag ma med par rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:15671: ma h+aa dang a nus sku lnga la sogs pa thob kyang /
NK117(she)001:15672: a nu gnyis su med pa'i sras bde ba chen po la mchog tu bzung bas /
NK117(she)001:15673: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor rgya theg mnyam pa nyid du ma rtogs te /
NK117(she)001:15674: phyogs 'dzin gyi rgya dang ma grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:15677: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor la lhag ma med par mngon du byas pas /
NK117(she)001:15678: gang la'ang phyogs su 'dzin pa med par chos kun
NK117(she)001:15679: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas khyad par du dpag
NK117(she)001:15680: pa yin te / brgal lan la /
NK117(she)001:15681: mnyam pa nyid kyis dpag pa'i theg mchog 'di //
NK117(she)001:15682: theg pa kun gyi yang rtser mnyam par bzhag /
NK117(she)001:15683: mi len mi spong mnyam pa'i rgyal pos dpag /
NK117(she)001:15686: tha snyad kyis chos rnams ril //
NK117(she)001:15687: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po rgyan //
NK117(she)001:15689: mnyam rdzogs bdag nyid chen po'i skabs kyi lung rnams so //
NK117(she)001:15692: che ba lnga yis dpag pa'i 'bras bu de //
NK117(she)001:15693: mnyam pa nyid kyis dpag pa ma go'am //
NK117(she)001:15695: che ba lnga yis 'og ma rnams las khyad par du dpag pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:15696: rgyas pa khog dbub kyi skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15697: brgyad pa sangs rgyas la ma rig pa yod med
NK117(she)001:15698: kyi brtags pa ni ma rig pa ma spangs par
NK117(she)001:15699: ral grol nas / de nyid sangs rgyas la che ba'i yon tan du shar ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:15700: de yang ma rig pa dang nyon mongs pa nyid
NK117(she)001:15701: rang byung gi ye shes su ye nas sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:15702: pa yin la / de nyid rtogs pa mngon du
NK117(she)001:15703: gyur pas ma rig pa dang nyon mongs pa rang
NK117(she)001:15704: pa yin la / sar grol te / shes bya'i
NK117(she)001:15705: dkyil 'khor la spang thob med par sangs rgyas pa'o
NK117(she)001:15706: pa yin la / sar grol te / // des
NK117(she)001:15707: na sangs rgyas la ma rig pa spangs pa med
NK117(she)001:15708: par rang grol nas mkhyen pa'i ye shes phyogs med
NK117(she)001:15709: du rgyas pas ma rig pa med ces bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15710: ma rig pa spang pa med par che ba'i yon tan du shar bas yod ces kyang bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15711: de yang rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK117(she)001:15712: ma rig pa dang bcas pa'i sems can rnams ni ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par yod do //
NK117(she)001:15713: de rnams kyi yod lugs dang lung ni rgyud cig gam tha dad dang /
NK117(she)001:15714: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:15715: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i skabs bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15716: dgu pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gzigs tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:15717: ye shes ci ltar yod pa'i tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:15718: des ci ltar gzigs pa'i tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:15720: ye shes zhes bya ba ni 'dus ma byas shing rang byung gi ye shes yin pas /
NK117(she)001:15721: skye 'gag med par rgyun dang bcas pa dus gsum 'phel 'grib med par gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15723: gang gi de yang 'bras bu sku lnga dang //
NK117(she)001:15725: rang byung ye shes rgyus ma bskyed //
NK117(she)001:15726: skye med rang gsal rgyun mi chad //
NK117(she)001:15729: kye lang ka'i bdag po byang chub kyi sems de
NK117(she)001:15730: kho na nyid gsang ba dam pa de ni skye
NK117(she)001:15731: 'gag med par rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15733: gsang ba'i bdag po gang gi rgyun dang bcas pa lags /
NK117(she)001:15735: lang ka'i bdag po ye shes rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15736: phrin las rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15737: yon tan rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15738: byin rlabs rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15739: smon lam rgyun dang bcas pa'i phyir rgyun ma chad pas so //
NK117(she)001:15742: dus gsum rgyun bcas mkhyen pa'i skad cig gis //
NK117(she)001:15743: ri rab til 'bru skad cig bskal chen dang //
NK117(she)001:15744: zhing khams phyag mthil 'khor lo'i nang gnas lta //
NK117(she)001:15745: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs thams cad mkhyen par gsal //
NK117(she)001:15746: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:15750: dbyer med par mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:15751: geg sel dang bcas pa khog dbub kyi skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15752: bcu pa gzigs nas thugs rje skye tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:15754: phyogs ris med pa'i thugs rje ni //
NK117(she)001:15755: mthar thug med pa'i 'gro ba la //
NK117(she)001:15756: gdung med nyi ma'i 'od bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:15757: 'gro ba kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK117(she)001:15758: 'gro don med pa'i rgyal ba ni //
NK117(she)001:15759: ma byung 'byung bar mi srid do //
NK117(she)001:15761: thugs rje chen pos phyogs ris med par 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:15762: thams cad kyi dpal du shar nas don byed par
NK117(she)001:15763: gsungs te / de yang rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:15765: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:15766: yul dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rje skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:15768: gdod nas tha ma ris su ma chad pas //
NK117(she)001:15769: thugs rjes gzung ba'i gdul bya smon pa 'brel //
NK117(she)001:15770: ma btsal 'gro don rgyun chad med par sel mdzad pa //
NK117(she)001:15771: rang shugs skul ma 'phrad pa'i yul don rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:15773: gzhan rnams khog dbub kyi skabs bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15774: 'dir yul dang mthun pa'i skabs su sku lngas 'khor lnga la don mdzad pa'i yin te /
NK117(she)001:15775: dang po ngo bo nyid kyi sku'i zhing khams ni /
NK117(she)001:15776: chos dbyings spyad du med pa /
NK117(she)001:15777: gnas ni spros bral rig pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK117(she)001:15778: 'khor ni sangs rgyas dang sems can tha snyad med cing thams cad sangs rgyas pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:15779: bstan pa ni rang gsal ngo bo nyid kyi gsung ngo //
NK117(she)001:15780: dus ni tshad las 'das pa ste dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:15781: sdud pa po kun 'dus rig pa'i skyes bu'o //
NK117(she)001:15783: ngo bo mthong tshul gnyis kyis so //
NK117(she)001:15784: rang rig ye shes ma yin pa //
NK117(she)001:15785: rnam par spyad pa'i chos mi gnas //
NK117(she)001:15786: sku gsum rig pa'i klong du rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:15787: gnas ni spros bral rig pa ste //
NK117(she)001:15788: bstan pa rang gsal me long yin //
NK117(she)001:15790: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK117(she)001:15792: rang gsal rang las ma yin pa //
NK117(she)001:15793: phun sum tshogs pa mi gnas te //
NK117(she)001:15794: rig pa 'pho 'gyur med pa'i gter dang //
NK117(she)001:15795: bsam gyis mi khyab dus na shes //
NK117(she)001:15798: gang ngo bo nyid med pa de'i zhing khams ni bskyed du med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15799: 'khor ni sangs rgyas tu med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15801: mdzad pa ni cir yang mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15804: ngo bo nyid skus chos sku la //
NK117(she)001:15805: dus bzhi mnyam pa'i dus nyid na //
NK117(she)001:15806: tha dad mi gnas pa yi gnas //
NK117(she)001:15807: kun 'dus rang grol bstan pa te //
NK117(she)001:15808: ma bsgribs mthong thos rang shar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:15810: ston pa chos sku'i zhing khams ni //
NK117(she)001:15811: bde chen bdal khyab chen po'o //
NK117(she)001:15812: gnas ni ya bdag don gyi 'og min no //
NK117(she)001:15814: ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs so //
NK117(she)001:15816: byin gyis rlabs kyi gsungs te bskyed rdzogs gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:15817: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste thams cad du'o //
NK117(she)001:15818: sdud pa po rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK117(she)001:15820: zhing khams chos nyid bde ba'i klong //
NK117(she)001:15821: ces pa la sogs pa gong gi lung dang sbyar ro //
NK117(she)001:15823: gang rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams ni gdal ba chen po'o //
NK117(she)001:15824: 'khor ni ye shes rgya mtsho'i tshogs so //
NK117(she)001:15825: bstan pa ni bya ba med pa'i chos so //
NK117(she)001:15826: dus ni thams cad nas thams cad du'o //
NK117(she)001:15827: mdzad pa ni chos thams cad snang bar mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15831: yin la rkyen gyis shar bas so //
NK117(she)001:15832: yang dag don gyi 'og min du //
NK117(she)001:15833: bsam gyis mi khyab dus gang du //
NK117(she)001:15834: mi nub don du gtad pa yin //
NK117(she)001:15835: bstan pa bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum //
NK117(she)001:15837: ston pa longs sku'i zhing khams ni /
NK117(she)001:15839: gnas ni 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang /
NK117(she)001:15840: 'khor ni rig 'dzin byang chub sems dpa' ste smin pa rgya mtsho'i tshogs /
NK117(she)001:15841: dus ni mnyam bzhag rig pa'i dus /
NK117(she)001:15842: bstan pa ni dgongs pa brda'i sgo nas phyi'i theg pa gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:15843: sdud pa po gsang bdag rdo rje 'chang ngo //
NK117(she)001:15845: gang smin pa'i zhing khams ni bde ba can no //
NK117(she)001:15846: 'khor ni yongs su smin pa rgya mtsho'i tshogs so //
NK117(she)001:15847: bstan pa ni brjod du med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15848: dus ni gnas gtsang ma na'o //
NK117(she)001:15849: mdzad pa ni rnal 'byor dam pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:15852: ston pa longs sku rig pa'i gnas //
NK117(she)001:15854: rang rig bde chen shar ba'i dus //
NK117(she)001:15855: bstan pa phyi yi theg pa gsum //
NK117(she)001:15856: mtshan dang dpe byad lha yis bsdus //
NK117(she)001:15857: cha mthun longs sku'i bstan par gsungs //
NK117(she)001:15859: ston pa sprul sku'i zhing khams ni //
NK117(she)001:15860: mi mjed kyi 'jig rten la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15861: gnas ni nges pa med de rdo rje gdan la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15862: 'khor ni mos pa tha dad pa'i tshogs te 'gro ba drug dang tshogs sbyor dang mthong lam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15863: dus ni sgron me bkod pa la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15864: bstan pa ni tshig gi gsung ste sde snod rnam pa gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:15865: sdud pa pa ni nges pa med pa ste rang rang gi 'khor gyi dam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15867: gang rgyun gyi zhing khams ni mos pa can no //
NK117(she)001:15868: 'khor ni mos pa tha dad pa'i tshogs so //
NK117(she)001:15869: bstan pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15870: dus ni sgron ma yongs su bkod pa na'o //
NK117(she)001:15871: mdzad pa ni gang gis mun pa sel bar mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15874: sprul sku stong gsum mi mjed na //
NK117(she)001:15875: gnas gcig nges med dgongs pas sprul //
NK117(she)001:15876: mos pas spyod pa'i 'khor rnams dang //
NK117(she)001:15877: sdug bsngal rtsol bsgrub 'khor rnams la //
NK117(she)001:15878: sdug bsngal rtsol bsgrub bcas dus su //
NK117(she)001:15879: bstan pa mtshan nyid sde gsum ste //
NK117(she)001:15880: skus 'dul mi rtag la stsogs mthun //
NK117(she)001:15882: rgyas par khog dbub tu bshad par blta'o //
NK117(she)001:15883: ston pa gsang ba'i sku'i zhing khams ni pad mo can no //
NK117(she)001:15884: gnas ni gsang ba yum gyi mkha' //
NK117(she)001:15885: 'khor ni dngos kyi rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang /
NK117(she)001:15886: go bye ba ni skyes bu blo ldan chags pa can no //
NK117(she)001:15887: dus ni gtsug tor 'khor los bsgyur ba ste gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:15888: bstan pa ni stong nyid bde ba chen po'i don ste gsang ba rgya mtsho nyid do //
NK117(she)001:15890: gang gsang ba dam pa de'i zhing khams ni pad mo can no //
NK117(she)001:15891: 'khor ni rgya ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs so //
NK117(she)001:15892: bstan pa ni gsang sngags gsang ba'i rgya mtsho nyid do //
NK117(she)001:15893: dus ni gtsug tor 'khor lo bsgyur bar 'dod pa na /
NK117(she)001:15894: rgyal ba kun gyi sku bskrun par 'byor ba'i dus nyid na'o //
NK117(she)001:15895: mdzad pa ni skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa dam pa'i the tshom gcod par mdzad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:15898: ston pa gsang ba yum gyi mkhar //
NK117(she)001:15899: gtsug tor 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i dus //
NK117(she)001:15900: skyes bu chags can 'khor bcas la //
NK117(she)001:15901: stong nyid bde chen bstan pa'i gtso //
NK117(she)001:15903: de rnams ni rgyas par 'dod na nam mkha' mtha' mnyam la sogs pa'i rgyud lta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15904: de ltar na sku lnga mtho dman dang bzang ngan yod dam med /
NK117(she)001:15905: yod na sku gzhan mthar thug gi sangs rgyas ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:15906: rgyud gcig pa sangs rgyas pa'i dus kyi sku lnga la'ang bzang ngan yod pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:15907: med na gcig gi 'khor gcig yin pa la 'gal lo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:15908: mthar thug gi sku lnga la bzang ngan dang mtho dman med la /
NK117(she)001:15909: 'og ma 'og ma'i sku gsum la sogs pa dang mtho dman yod par gsungs te /
NK117(she)001:15910: des na mthar thug gi sku lnga la mtho dman
NK117(she)001:15911: med pas sku gzhan mthar thug gi sangs rgyas ma
NK117(she)001:15913: 'og ma'i sku gsum la sogs pa dang khyad par
NK117(she)001:15914: yod pas 'khor du bshad pa dang yang 'gal ba
NK117(she)001:15915: med do // yang mthar thug gi sku lnga la
NK117(she)001:15916: khyad par med la rang rang gi rgyal tshab kyi
NK117(she)001:15917: ston pa sku lnga dang khyad par yod pas gong
NK117(she)001:15918: gi skyon gnyis las grol lo //
NK117(she)001:15919: de bzhin du 'og ma'i sku lnga dang gsum la
NK117(she)001:15920: sogs pa'ang rang rang gi sku lnga la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:15922: 'og ma 'og ma dang khyad par yod cing rang
NK117(she)001:15923: rang gi rgyal tshab byed pa'i ston pa dang khyad
NK117(she)001:15924: par yod pas na gong bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:15925: yang sku lnga ngo bo gcig gam mi gcig /
NK117(she)001:15926: gcig na gong gi skyon dang sku lnga'i gdul gzhi la sogs pa tha dad pa'i skyon yod la /
NK117(she)001:15927: mi gcig na'ang gong gi skyon gnyis po de 'ong ngo zhe na /
NK117(she)001:15928: spyir thugs rgyud tha dad pa sangs rgyas pa'i sangs
NK117(she)001:15929: rgyas ni ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas ma
NK117(she)001:15930: 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi skabs bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:15931: bye brag tu rgyud gcig pa sangs rgyas pa'i sku lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:15932: ngo bo gcig la mtshon tshul tha dad pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:15933: de yang gdul bya'i snang ba dang mthun par sku
NK117(she)001:15934: rnam pa lngar snang yang ngo bo dbyer mi phyed
NK117(she)001:15936: de'i skyon sel dang theg pa gong 'og gi bye
NK117(she)001:15937: brag la sogs pa ni gong ma bzhin du shes
NK117(she)001:15938: par bya'o // tha ma thugs rje skyes nas phrin las kyi don mdzad tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:15939: gong gi yon tan dang phrin las kyi skabs dang khog dbub bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:15940: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa /
NK117(she)001:15941: chos kyi gter mdzod chen po /
NK117(she)001:15942: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las /
NK117(she)001:15943: mthar thug gi 'bras bu bstan pa'i le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa'o ////
NK117(she)001:15944: dus gsum rgyal ba ma lus bskyed pa'i yum //
NK117(she)001:15945: chos dbyings mi zad gter mdzod chen po 'di //
NK117(she)001:15946: don gyi khog 'bub gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don //
NK117(she)001:15947: gol sa'i dmigs bcad theg pa'i shan phye ste //
NK117(she)001:15948: don gyi la bzla rang grol mngon ston pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15949: chos kyi gter mdzod kun 'dus sgron me 'di //
NK117(she)001:15950: ngag la nges 'dzin chos kyi spun grogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:15951: ban d+he sh+aakya badz+ra bdag bskul nas //
NK117(she)001:15952: rgyal ba'i bstan pa dam chos bdud rtsi yi //
NK117(she)001:15953: bka' rgyud dri med gzhung mang rgya che dang //
NK117(she)001:15954: mkhas pa'i 'grel dang ti ka bstan bcos dang //
NK117(she)001:15955: zab mo'i gdam ngag dgongs pa'i gter mdzod la //
NK117(she)001:15956: legs dpyad shes rab rnam grol lde mig gis //
NK117(she)001:15957: don gyi gnad ston dgongs pa'i bcud blang 'di //
NK117(she)001:15958: rje yi gsung dang rang gi nyams myong la //
NK117(she)001:15959: lung dang man ngag mi 'gal rig par sbyar //
NK117(she)001:15960: gzhan phan srid snyam sems bskyed go cha dang //
NK117(she)001:15961: bskul don brtse bas bcud bsdus yi ger bkod //
NK117(she)001:15962: grogs dag rang 'dod phyogs 'dzin khengs sems dang //
NK117(she)001:15963: dad tsam gang zag rjes 'brang ma yin par //
NK117(she)001:15964: chos kyi rjes su tshad ma rnam gsum gyis //
NK117(she)001:15965: legs dpyod 'di don dgongs pa'i bcud longs mdzod //
NK117(she)001:15966: 'di don rtogs nas yal bar ma 'jog par //
NK117(she)001:15967: ma yengs bsgrub pas tshul bzhin nyams su longs //
NK117(she)001:15968: gzhan yang chos 'di la dad mos gus che //
NK117(she)001:15969: 'di bas phyi ma gtsor mdzad blo ldan la //
NK117(she)001:15970: rang 'dod zhen 'khris med pa'i phan sems kyis //
NK117(she)001:15971: yal bar mi gzhag dgongs pa'i don 'di bstan //
NK117(she)001:15972: thog med dus nas ma rig thib po yis //
NK117(she)001:15973: lam stor lam log lam gol 'khyams pa la //
NK117(she)001:15974: ma rig mun sel yang dag lam ston pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15975: shes rab gsal ba'i sgron ma 'di ston cig /
NK117(she)001:15976: thar pa'i blo ster gros kyi gzhi nor bas //
NK117(she)001:15977: 'khor ba'i mdud gros ci byas sdug bsngal la //
NK117(she)001:15978: deng nas gtan du bde legs kun 'byung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:15979: thar pa'i blo gros mdun ma 'di ston cig /
NK117(she)001:15980: chags sdang nyon mongs dug gi sdong po la //
NK117(she)001:15981: 'khor ba'i 'dab rgyas 'bras bu sdug bsngal la //
NK117(she)001:15982: nyon mongs rtsad gcod 'khor ba'i 'dams 'breg pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15983: rang byung thogs med ral gri 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:15984: gzung 'dzin zhags pas shes pa'i rgyud sdoms shing //
NK117(she)001:15985: log rtog dmag dpung 'khor ba'i brtson ra la //
NK117(she)001:15986: gzung 'dzin sgrogs gcod 'khor ba'i g.yul 'joms pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15987: gnyis med ye shes don chen 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:15988: bdag lta 'khor ba'i gcong nad snying la zhen //
NK117(she)001:15989: sdug bsngal bzod dka' me dbal gdung ba la //
NK117(she)001:15990: 'khor ba'i gcong 'byin nad sel sman gyi mchog /
NK117(she)001:15991: dam chos bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:15992: ma rig ling tog mig nad chen po yis //
NK117(she)001:15993: bka' rgyud bstan pa'i snang med long ba la //
NK117(she)001:15994: ma rig mig 'byed chos kun gsal ston pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15995: shes rab spyan 'byed thur ma 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:15996: rang 'dod phyogs 'dzin lta la zhen pa yi //
NK117(she)001:15997: nges pa'i gzhung la 'gal 'jug rtsod pa la //
NK117(she)001:15998: log rtog tshar gcod grub pa mthar 'byin pa'i //
NK117(she)001:15999: smra ba'i mtshon cha mnyam grol 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:16000: gzhi rtsa ma chod tha snyad tshig tshogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:16001: blo khrid log rtog spros pas g.yengs ba la //
NK117(she)001:16002: the tshom kun gcod sgrub pa nyams len pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16003: ngo sprod nyams kyi man ngag 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:16004: rang rtog nyer len zhags pas bkug pa yi //
NK117(she)001:16005: gdon gyis gnod skyes lus kyi na tsha la //
NK117(she)001:16006: byams pa'i lam ster skye med don ston pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16007: bogs 'don theg chen lam mchog 'di bsten cig /'byung bzhi 'dus pa'i phung po 'dor len la //
NK117(she)001:16008: skye shir mthong nas nyams thag 'khyams pa la //
NK117(she)001:16009: skye shi rtsad gcod 'pho 'gyur gnyis med pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16010: rang byung 'chi med rdo rje 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:16011: thog med dus nas rang gter nor bu stor //
NK117(she)001:16012: 'dod pas mi ngom dbul phong sdug bsngal la //
NK117(she)001:16013: sems nyid yid bzhin dgos 'dod kun 'byung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:16014: chos dbyings mi zad gter chen 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:16015: sangs rgyas bde 'dod rang bzhag gzhan nas tshol //
NK117(she)001:16016: re dogs brtsol ba'i nad kyis zin pa la //
NK117(she)001:16017: rang sems sangs rgyas chos skur ngo sprod pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16018: bde chen lhun grub rtsol med 'di bsten cig /
NK117(she)001:16019: shes bya gnas lugs rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ni //
NK117(she)001:16020: gzung 'dzin zab cing gting dpag med gyur la //
NK117(she)001:16021: bdag 'dras lung rigs man ngag dgongs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:16022: bcud bsdus zab mo'i don rnams yi ger bkod //
NK117(she)001:16023: bka' lung don dang 'gal ba mchis gyur na //
NK117(she)001:16024: bla ma bshes dang theg mchog dam pa dang //
NK117(she)001:16025: yi dam mkha' 'gro sngags 'chang la sogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16026: mkhyen brtse rnams la gnyis med ngang du bshags //
NK117(she)001:16028: rtsod ldan lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma 'dir //
NK117(she)001:16029: rang bzo gzu lum log rtog rtsod dar la //
NK117(she)001:16030: bstan pa'i spyi 'grel lde mig 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16031: bka' dang mi 'gal gzhung bzhin spyod par shog /
NK117(she)001:16032: phyogs re'i gzhung brten bsten snyigs grub mtha' log /
NK117(she)001:16033: theg pa'i bye brag ma phyed rmongs don du //
NK117(she)001:16034: la shan theg pa'i spyi mdo 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16035: theg pa'i bye brag ma nor don rtogs shog /
NK117(she)001:16036: rang 'dod lta la mchog 'dzin zhen pa yis //
NK117(she)001:16037: phyogs 'dzin 'chings pa'i rgyar chud dgrol don du //
NK117(she)001:16038: dgongs pa'i spyi mdzod kun gsal 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16039: phyogs ris kun grol mnyam nyid don rtogs shog /
NK117(she)001:16040: phyogs re'i rgyu 'bras la zhen rmongs pa yis //
NK117(she)001:16041: zab mo'i rgyu 'bras skur 'debs tshi chad la //
NK117(she)001:16042: rgyu 'bras kun mtshon me long 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16043: rgyu 'bras mig phye zab mo'i don rtogs shog /
NK117(she)001:16044: gzhung mang thos tshe tha snyad tsheg mkhas kyang //
NK117(she)001:16045: rang rgyud ma grol gdams pa'i gnad med la //
NK117(she)001:16046: ngo sprod nyams kyi man ngag 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16047: snying po'i don rtogs nyams myong bcu ldan shog /
NK117(she)001:16048: phyogs re'i gdams pas nyams myong drod skyes kyang //
NK117(she)001:16049: sa lam lta ba'i mig med grol don du //
NK117(she)001:16050: sa lam rig pa'i sgron me 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16051: sa lam dmigs ldan yang dag lam gnas shog /
NK117(she)001:16052: ma rig log lta bdag lta'i gcong zin cing //
NK117(she)001:16053: nyon mongs nad kyis gdung ba'i 'gro don du //
NK117(she)001:16054: dri med bdud rtsi dam chos 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16055: 'khor ba'i gcong 'byin nyon mongs nad sel shog /
NK117(she)001:16056: rgyud lung man ngag gzhung gsal rgya che yang //
NK117(she)001:16057: de don ma mthong chos kyis dbul don du //
NK117(she)001:16058: kun 'dus chos kyi gter mdzod 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16059: bstan pa'i bcud longs chos kyis dbul sel shog /
NK117(she)001:16060: bskul ba'i don dang gzhan phan sems bskyed mthus //
NK117(she)001:16061: bla ma'i gsung dang lung rigs man ngag gis //
NK117(she)001:16062: dgongs pa'i bcud blangs legs bshad 'di bsdus pas //
NK117(she)001:16063: dge bas 'gro kun ma nor lam rnyed shog /
NK117(she)001:16064: dge ba 'di dang dge gzhan ci mchis pa //
NK117(she)001:16065: ma lus thams cad gcig tu bsdus byas te //
NK117(she)001:16066: nam mkha'i mtha' khyab sems can rgyud smin nas //
NK117(she)001:16067: 'gro kun bla med byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK117(she)001:16068: bde legs kun 'byung 'gro ba'i skyabs gnas mchog /
NK117(she)001:16069: zhen mtha' kun grol yon tan phyogs med rgyas //
NK117(she)001:16070: mkhyen dang brtse dang mdzad pa'i lcags kyu yis //
NK117(she)001:16071: 'gro ba ma lus mi gtong 'dzin par shog /
NK117(she)001:16072: rgyal ba'i zhal nas legs par gsung pa yi //
NK117(she)001:16073: bka' lung dri med bstan pa rin po che //
NK117(she)001:16074: dam chos bdud rtsi'i rnam grol lam chen gyis //
NK117(she)001:16075: 'gro kun nad sel yang dag lam 'jug shog /
NK117(she)001:16076: rgyal ba'i bka' bzhin rjes su sgrubs pa yis //
NK117(she)001:16077: thar pa'i dge slong byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK117(she)001:16078: dam pa'i rigs can rig pa 'dzin pa yis //
NK117(she)001:16079: 'gro kun smin byed thar pa'i lam 'dren shog /'gro kun 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal rgya mtsho las //
NK117(she)001:16080: yid dbyung thar pa 'dod pa'i blo skyes shing //
NK117(she)001:16081: 'jig rten bslu brid chos la ma chags par //
NK117(she)001:16082: yid ches dad pas chos la 'jug par shog /
NK117(she)001:16083: mchog gsum rjes dran gus pas skyabs song nas //
NK117(she)001:16084: skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya mi nyams gzhung gnas shing //
NK117(she)001:16085: so so'i 'dul khrims byang sems sdom la sogs //
NK117(she)001:16086: sangs rgyas bstan pa gzhung bzhin 'jug par shog /
NK117(she)001:16087: lung rigs man ngag nyams myong rtogs la sogs //
NK117(she)001:16088: dam pa'i mdzod mnga' thabs mkhas mdzad pa yis //
NK117(she)001:16089: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston mdzad pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16090: tshad ldan bla ma rgyun du bsten par shog /
NK117(she)001:16091: bla ma'i skyon rnams nam yang mi mthong zhing //
NK117(she)001:16092: rtag tu yon tan 'ba' zhig mthong gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:16093: rgyun du 'bral med dad gus shes rab dang //
NK117(she)001:16094: spyod lam cis kyang bla ma mnyes byed shog /
NK117(she)001:16095: lung rigs man ngag don dang 'brel ba yi //
NK117(she)001:16096: bla ma'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i bdud rtsi yis //
NK117(she)001:16097: rang gnas ye shes mngon du ngo 'phrod nas //
NK117(she)001:16098: mi shes 'ching ba kun las grol bar shog /
NK117(she)001:16099: g.yo sgyu khram zol ma lus spo byed cing //
NK117(she)001:16100: bla ma mched la gus shing brtse gdung ldan //
NK117(she)001:16101: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK117(she)001:16102: yi dam mkha' 'gros mi khrel bsrung bar shog /
NK117(she)001:16103: rtag chad mu mtha' la sogs phyogs 'dzin gyi //
NK117(she)001:16104: gol sgrib nor ba'i lam rnams dmigs phyed cing //
NK117(she)001:16105: theg pa'i bye brag ma lus shan phyed nas //
NK117(she)001:16106: chos kun mnyam nyid ngang du la zlo shog /
NK117(she)001:16107: chos kun gang nas ma 'ongs gar mi 'gro //
NK117(she)001:16108: gang du mi gnas dus gsum mnyam nyid pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16109: mtha' bzhi rang grol rgya chad phyogs lhung med //
NK117(she)001:16110: skye med rang snang mngon du rtogs par shog /
NK117(she)001:16111: rtogs pa'i don la ma yengs gnas byed cing //
NK117(she)001:16112: rang lus rtsol med rang gnas dgos pa la //
NK117(she)001:16113: nyams myong drod rtags gzhung bshad bzhin 'byung zhing //
NK117(she)001:16114: nyams rtogs gong nas gong du 'phel bar shog /
NK117(she)001:16115: rtogs pa'i ngang gnas tshul bzhin bsgrub pa la //
NK117(she)001:16116: mi yi 'tshe ba chags sdang g.yeng ba dang //
NK117(she)001:16117: gdon gyis gnod skyes lus kyi na tsha sogs //
NK117(she)001:16118: bar chad rkyen rnams mi 'byung grogs byed shog /
NK117(she)001:16119: gnas dang nye 'khor chos mthun longs spyod ldan //
NK117(she)001:16120: bka' rgyud gdams pa'i mdzod la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK117(she)001:16121: bzo dang bstan chos las tshogs la sogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16122: mthun rkyen tshogs rnams rtag tu 'dzom par shog /
NK117(she)001:16123: bdag gi spyod lam rnam thar thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:16124: mi dge chos brgyad dri mas mi gos shing //
NK117(she)001:16125: gzhan gyis sgro skur gshe ba'i phyogs bral te //
NK117(she)001:16126: 'gro ba kun gyi yid 'ong don 'gyur shog /
NK117(she)001:16127: gdon dang nad kyis nyen pa la sogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16128: sdug bsngal mgon med longs spyod dbul phong rnams //
NK117(she)001:16129: bdag gi mthu dpal byams dang snying rje yis //
NK117(she)001:16130: skyob cing phan thogs bde la 'khod par shog /
NK117(she)001:16131: bdag la dad gus chos kyis 'brel tshad dang //
NK117(she)001:16132: mi mthun gnod skyel dgra dang bgegs rnams dang //
NK117(she)001:16133: bdag gi gzugs mthong ming tsam thos la sogs //
NK117(she)001:16134: ma lus bdag gis sangs rgyas sar 'dren shog /
NK117(she)001:16135: rtogs pa'i ngang gnas shes rab snying rje yis //
NK117(she)001:16136: bdag lta'i rtsa ba rtsad nas gcod byed cing //
NK117(she)001:16137: 'jig rten chos brgyad chags sdang la sogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16138: nyon mongs 'ching ba kun las grol bar shog /
NK117(she)001:16139: zag med mngon gyur mnyam nyid dgongs pa las //
NK117(she)001:16140: ma g.yos thugs rje'i mdzad pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:16141: 'gro ba gang la gang gis 'dul ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:16142: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen spyod par shog /
NK117(she)001:16143: lhun grub ngang gnas dgongs spyod thugs rje yis //
NK117(she)001:16144: mdzad pa rlabs chen cir yang ston byed cing //
NK117(she)001:16145: 'od gsal mtha' bral rang rig ye shes kyis //
NK117(she)001:16146: shes sgrib phra bcom rdzogs sangs rgyas thob shog /
NK117(she)001:16147: chos dbyings mngon gyur spang thob lhag med pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16148: 'gro 'ong gsal 'grib med pa'i dgongs pa la //
NK117(she)001:16149: sku dang gsung thugs yon tan phrin las sogs //
NK117(she)001:16150: bsam yas lhun grub mngon du byed par shog /
NK117(she)001:16151: mkhyen pa'i ye shes brtse ba'i thugs rje dang //
NK117(she)001:16152: mdzad pa'i phrin las lhun grub phyogs med kyis //
NK117(she)001:16153: gang la gang 'dul de la der ston cing //
NK117(she)001:16154: srid gsum 'gro ba ma lus 'dren par shog /
NK117(she)001:16155: dge ba 'di dang chos dbyings mtha' klas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16156: 'khor 'das gnyis bsdus dge gzhan ma lus la //
NK117(she)001:16157: yid rang spro bas gcig tu bsdus byas te //
NK117(she)001:16158: 'gro kun rgyud smin byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK117(she)001:16159: dus gsum sangs rgyas yi dam lha mchog dang //
NK117(she)001:16160: rig 'dzin byang sems bka' rgyud bla ma dang //
NK117(she)001:16161: rgyun du mi 'bral dgongs pa dbyer med pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16162: bla ma dkon mchog rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK117(she)001:16163: sangs rgyas bstan pa dar zhing rgyas pa dang //
NK117(she)001:16164: theg pa mchog dang mi 'bral bcud longs nas //
NK117(she)001:16165: 'gro kun smin byed chos kyi char 'bebs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16166: theg chen dam pa'i chos kyi bkra shis shog /
NK117(she)001:16167: bla ma mched dang 'khor slob yon bdag rnams //
NK117(she)001:16168: mthun par 'grogs shing dad gus brtse ba dang //
NK117(she)001:16169: tshe ring nad med longs spyod chos mthun cing //
NK117(she)001:16170: chos 'khor 'dab rgyas don grub bkra shis shog /
NK117(she)001:16171: deng nas bzung nas dus rnam thams cad du //
NK117(she)001:16172: mi mthun bar chod rkyen rnams mi 'byung zhing //
NK117(she)001:16173: dgongs spyod 'phel zhing ci bsam 'grub pa yi //
NK117(she)001:16174: bkra shis bde legs phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK117(she)001:16175: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don mtshon pa //
NK117(she)001:16176: chos kyi gter mdzod chen po /
NK117(she)001:16177: kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me las /
NK117(she)001:16178: mjug smon lam dang bcas pa'i le'u ste nye shu rtsa gsum pa'o ////
NK117(she)001:16179: bka' thams cad gsal bar ston pas bstan pa'i spyi 'grel zhes kyang bya /
NK117(she)001:16180: theg pa thams cad kyi shan 'byed cing la zlos pas theg pa'i spyi mdo zhes kyang bya /
NK117(she)001:16181: lta ba dang dgongs pa thams cad kyi spyi phugs ston pas dgongs pa'i spyi mdzod zhes kyang bya /
NK117(she)001:16182: rgyu 'bras kyi chos kun gsal bar ston pas chos kyi me long zhes kyang bya /
NK117(she)001:16183: sems nyid kyi ngo sprod cing nyams myong gi don
NK117(she)001:16184: ston pas ngo sprod nyams kyi man ngag zhes kyang
NK117(she)001:16185: bya / sa dang lam gyi dmigs pa ma 'dres par ston pas /
NK117(she)001:16186: sa lam rig pa'i sgron me zhes kyang bya /
NK117(she)001:16187: nyon mongs kyi gcong snying rtsad nas 'byin par byed
NK117(she)001:16188: pas dri ma med pa'i bdud rtsi zhes kyang bya
NK117(she)001:16189: / chos dbyings mi zad pa'i gter chen /
NK117(she)001:16190: dgongs pa rnams kyi mdzod btus nas /
NK117(she)001:16191: bka' dang man ngag thams cad kyi bcud bsdus te
NK117(she)001:16192: chos kun gsal bar ston pa'i chos kyi gter mdzod
NK117(she)001:16193: chen po kun 'dus rig pa'i sgron me zhes bya
NK117(she)001:16194: ba sh+aakya'i dge slong ban d+he sh+aakya rdo rjes rgyal
NK117(she)001:16197: zab mo'i gdams ngag rnams kyi dgongs pa'i bcud blangs /
NK117(she)001:16198: bla ma'i gsung dang rang gi nyams myong gi don
NK117(she)001:16199: dril te bskul ba po'i don phyir yi ger bkod
NK117(she)001:16200: pa rdzogs so //// theg mchog bstan pa rin chen dar ba dang //
NK117(she)001:16201: theg rtse rdzogs chen dgongs pa mngon gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16202: slob ma'i tshogs kyis rgyal khams kun gang nas //
NK117(she)001:16203: bstan 'dzin sku tshe brtan pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK117(she)001:16204: slar yang lung spel bgyid pa po ni kahthoga pa si tu chos kyi rgya matsho'o //
NK117(she)001:16208: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:16209: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin chen lde
NK117(she)001:16210: mig bzhugs / na mo gu ru d+harma k+aa ya
NK117(she)001:16211: sam+b+ho k+aa ya nirma k+aa ya sarba sid+d+hi pha la
NK117(she)001:16212: mig bzhugs / h+aum / gang zhig rnam grol dpal
NK117(she)001:16213: yon phung po srid zhi'i sgro skur bral ba chos
NK117(she)001:16214: kun mnyam pa chen po'i ngang //
NK117(she)001:16215: spros tshogs yongs spangs cir yang mi dmigs gnas lugs
NK117(she)001:16216: gnyug ma skye 'gag gnas gsum bral ba'i bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:16217: can // kun rdzob sgyu ma rang ngor grol bas
NK117(she)001:16218: shes dang shes bya ro gcig bzlum pa bde chen
NK117(she)001:16219: can // sgyu ma'i sku // rigs brgya'i khyab bdag
NK117(she)001:16220: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang chen bde chen 'khor lo'i
NK117(she)001:16221: rgyan du bzhugs nas byin gyis rlobs //
NK117(she)001:16222: rang bzhin dbyings su 'khor 'das thams cad lhun gyis grub cing skye med ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK117(she)001:16223: mkhyen gnyis ye shes rtogs pa'i rgyun las yongs su grol ba mi 'gyur thig le'i ngang nyid las //
NK117(she)001:16224: skye ba'i cho 'phrul sgyu ma'i rol gar bsam yas skur ston dpal ldan sangs rgyas pad+ma skyes //
NK117(she)001:16225: 'ja' lus mchog gi sku brnyes dri med bshes gnyen
NK117(she)001:16226: la sogs snga 'gyur bstan pa'i gsal byed rnams la
NK117(she)001:16227: 'dud // gang gi zhing khams b+ho ta'i ljongs su mdo sngags bstan pa spel phyir du //
NK117(she)001:16228: 'khor ba'i mtshang las nges par grol yang srid par 'jug la skyo med bzhin //
NK117(she)001:16229: dpag med 'gro rnams phan bde'i lam du bkri mdzad mkhyen brtse nus pa'i bdag /
NK117(she)001:16230: rigs gsum rnam sprul mes dbon gsum gyi bka' drin dran bzhin snying nas mos //
NK117(she)001:16231: mtha' 'khob pre ta pu ri rmongs pa'i thun gsum 'thibs pa'i smag rum du //
NK117(she)001:16232: dge legs 'od stong rab tu 'bar bas mdo sngags bstan pa gsal mdzad cing //
NK117(she)001:16233: 'phral phug phan dang bde ba'i pad tshal kun nas rab tu rgyas mdzad pa //
NK117(she)001:16234: bee ro tsa na ka cog rma gnyags la sogs lo pan yongs la 'dud //
NK117(she)001:16235: mdo sgyu sems gsum yang phur la sogs dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i mnga' bdag rim gnyis 'bras smin rje //
NK117(she)001:16236: ye shes sgyu ma'i rol rtsal dpag med thabs mkhas thugs rje'i cho 'phrul ngo mtshar rgya chen pos //
NK117(she)001:16237: 'khor ba'i mtshor ltung nyam thag 'gro la smin grol bdud rtsi'i char chen 'bebs mdzad grub brnyes mchog /
NK117(she)001:16238: so zur gnubs gsum bstan pa rgya mtsho'i ri dbang spo na mngon par mtho 'di bstod basngagasa yul //
NK117(she)001:16239: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i 'od zer 'bum ldan lnga bdo'i chu 'dzin rum du yib la nye ba'i tshe //
NK117(she)001:16240: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab 'thor rlung drag po'i rtsal shugs rab tu g.yos pa'i nus stobs kyis //
NK117(she)001:16241: rgol ngan sprin nag ring du bskrad dang chabs cig ma h+aa san+d+ha'i nyin byed gsal ba dang //
NK117(she)001:16242: bstan 'dzin chu skyes tshal rgyas grub gnyis dri bzang srid 'dir spro byed klong chen pa khyod rgyal //
NK117(she)001:16243: ji lta ba dang ji snyed mkhyena pa'i mnga' bdag 'jam dpal rnon po'i rjes 'gro dam pa'i mgon //
NK117(she)001:16244: byams sdang ris bral thugs brtse'i gter mdzod phyag na pad+ma zlos pa'i sgyu 'phrul sprul pa'i sku //
NK117(she)001:16245: bdud sde'i dpung tshogs gzhom nus 'od zer brgya pas mun par ji bzhin gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:16246: rigs gsum gzhan na med de rgyal bstan 'dzin mchog 'jigas meda gling pa gtan gyi skyabs su grub //
NK117(she)001:16247: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i mdo sngags chos so cog /
NK117(she)001:16248: nyung ngu'i tshig gis ji bzhin rtogs nus gzhung //
NK117(she)001:16249: yon tan rin chen mdzod kyi sgo brgya'i lcags //
NK117(she)001:16250: 'byed nus bsdus lde rgya mtsho'i chu thig nor //
NK117(she)001:16251: kho bo'i skal bar thob bzhin don gnyer mkhan //
NK117(she)001:16252: blo gsal 'chi med ne gu'i gtsug rgyan du //
NK117(she)001:16253: sbyin la dad dang thos bsam byi dor dang //
NK117(she)001:16254: gzhan phan smon lam sems mchog bskyed dang kwa ye //
NK117(she)001:16255: zhes mchod par brjod pa dang rtsom par dam bca'
NK117(she)001:16256: ba'i tshig gis mdun bsus nas 'grel pa dngos la
NK117(she)001:16257: 'jug pa la klad kyi don dang /
NK117(she)001:16259: mjug gi don dang gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:16260: dang po la ni gzhung 'di'i mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16261: de nyid rtsom pa la bar chad med cing byin
NK117(she)001:16262: rlabs 'jug pa'i phyir mchog gsum rin po cher phyag
NK117(she)001:16263: 'tshal ba dang / rtsom par dam bca' ba'o //
NK117(she)001:16265: rgyu phar phyin theg pa'i sa lam 'bras bu dang bcas pa bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16266: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa spyi dgos
NK117(she)001:16267: kyi smin grol gnyis dang bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi dam
NK117(she)001:16268: tshig gi 'bras bu dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16269: gsum pa la sbyar byang dge bsngo la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16270: dang po mtshan bstan pa'i thog mar rgya skad smos pa'i don ni /
NK117(she)001:16271: spyir 'dren pa stong gi 'byon bzhugs kyi yul yin
NK117(she)001:16272: pa dang mdo sngags kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung
NK117(she)001:16274: de yang rgya la dkar nag gnyis yod pa la
NK117(she)001:16275: sngon ma ni gos rgyan dkar po la rten 'brel
NK117(she)001:16277: rjes mas nag po gtsigs su byed pa dang chos
NK117(she)001:16278: dang 'jig rten gal che chung yang de mtshungs byed
NK117(she)001:16279: pa sogs kyi khyad par ro //
NK117(she)001:16280: rgya dkar po'i skad la rgya gar skad du zhes
NK117(she)001:16281: bris pa'i dgos ched ni lo ts+aa bas sum rtags
NK117(she)001:16282: dang bstun nas 'jug pa bde ba'i phyir de ltar
NK117(she)001:16283: bsdebs pa'o // de yang 'di skad ces smos na /
NK117(she)001:16285: gu na ko sha rat+na pra mo d+ha pri n+aa ma /
NK117(she)001:16287: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba /
NK117(she)001:16289: rgya bod kyi skad gnyis shan sbyar ba shes par byas nas /
NK117(she)001:16291: gzhung 'di'i nang na rim dgu'i theg pa'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:16292: thams cad tshang ba ni rin po che'i gter mdzod
NK117(she)001:16293: lta bu yin la gang zhig shes bya don du
NK117(she)001:16294: gnyer ba rnams kyi mi shes pa'i tha ba brlan
NK117(she)001:16295: nas blo gros kyi lo 'bras rgyas par byed pa
NK117(she)001:16296: la dga' ba'i dpe so nam pa'i zhing sar char
NK117(she)001:16297: rgyun dus su babs pa dang chos mtshungs pa /
NK117(she)001:16299: mtshan gong du gsal ba'i gzhung ngos bzung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:16300: spyi don dang po'i gnyis pa mchod brjod ni /
NK117(she)001:16301: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:16305: u dum w+aa ra'i me tog bzhin //
NK117(she)001:16306: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'jig rten na dkon pa'i yid
NK117(she)001:16307: bzhin nor bu la sogs pa'i rin po che'i rigs
NK117(she)001:16308: rnams dkon yang mchog ma yin de 'bad rtsol gyis
NK117(she)001:16309: bsgrub tu yod pa dang 'jig rten gyi 'dod pa
NK117(she)001:16310: 'jo ba tsam las thar pa dang rnam mkhyen ster
NK117(she)001:16312: sangs rgyas ni bskal pa grangs med mang por tshogs
NK117(she)001:16313: bsags pa'i mthus thob dgos pas rab tu dkon pa'i
NK117(she)001:16315: dam pa'i chos kyang sangs rgyas kyis gsung dgos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16316: de nyid nyams su blangs na gang zag gi blo
NK117(she)001:16317: rim bzhin mngon mtho dang nges legs kyi go 'phang
NK117(she)001:16318: ster nus pas de lta bu'i dngos po dkon pa
NK117(she)001:16319: dang / dge 'dun yang sangs rgyas kyi zhal skyin
NK117(she)001:16320: dam chos kyi 'byung khungs tshogs bsags pa'i zhing mchog
NK117(she)001:16321: yin pas de yang dkon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16322: yul de gsum la dad gus mos gsum gyi phyag
NK117(she)001:16323: rgya ni lag pa'i 'du byed de thal mo pad+ma
NK117(she)001:16324: kha 'bus bzhin spyi mgrin snying ga gsum du bzhag
NK117(she)001:16325: pas sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa 'dag par gsung phyir
NK117(she)001:16327: de yang gzhung 'di brtsams pa'i thog mar rtsom pa
NK117(she)001:16328: pos mchod par brjod pa dang rjes su thos bsam
NK117(she)001:16329: byed pa dag gis kyang de ltar dran dgos pa
NK117(she)001:16330: yin no // de ltar dkon mchog gsum gyi khungs
NK117(she)001:16331: dang rgyu mtshan cung zad bstan nas da ni phan
NK117(she)001:16332: yon dang 'brel bas spro ba bskyed pa ni /
NK117(she)001:16334: rin chen rnam gsum grags pa'i spring yig gis //
NK117(she)001:16335: mu tig 'khri shing rab tu dga' byas nas //
NK117(she)001:16336: bdud kyi bu mo'i bzhin ras kun+da'i tshal //
NK117(she)001:16337: skal ngan bgyid la mngon phyogs sangs rgyas mthu //
NK117(she)001:16340: ston pa bla med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK117(she)001:16341: skyob pa bla med dam chos rin po che //
NK117(she)001:16342: 'dren pa bla med dge 'dun rin po che //
NK117(she)001:16343: bla med dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:16344: zhes gsungs pa ltar spyir dkon mchog gsum zhes grags
NK117(she)001:16345: pa'i spring yig gi sgra dbyangs rgya che rgyun mi
NK117(she)001:16346: 'chad pa de nyid mi khom pa brgyad kyi gnas
NK117(she)001:16347: su grags kyang tshul bzhin thos pa dang nyams len
NK117(she)001:16349: de ma yin pa gang du grags pa'i yul mchog
NK117(she)001:16350: dman su la yang dge zhing legs pa'i sa bon
NK117(she)001:16352: sngon byung gi gtam rgyud dang sbyar nas ston pa ste /
NK117(she)001:16354: nor chen zhes bya'i tshong pa ni //
NK117(she)001:16355: w+aa ra n+aa sir sngon byung gyur //
NK117(she)001:16356: de yi khyim thab bsod nams can //
NK117(she)001:16357: rin chen ldan zhes bya bar gyur //
NK117(she)001:16358: bdag po lnga pa nyid gyur tshe //
NK117(she)001:16359: bud med de yis mchod rten rtser //
NK117(she)001:16360: do shal chen po gus ldan pas //
NK117(she)001:16361: mchod pa byas nas phul bar gyur //
NK117(she)001:16362: bsod nams rnam smin des de nyid //
NK117(she)001:16363: sing+ga la yi bdag po yi //
NK117(she)001:16364: bu mo mu tig 'khri shing gyur //
NK117(she)001:16365: de nyid skye ba gzhan la ni //
NK117(she)001:16366: phyug pas rgyags shing rmongs gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:16367: mchod pa smod cing sgrin gyur pa //
NK117(she)001:16368: de yis yun ring 'bangs mor gyur //
NK117(she)001:16369: dge dang mi dge'i las gang gang //
NK117(she)001:16370: skye ba'i zhing la skye bos btab //
NK117(she)001:16371: ces pa ltar sh+aakya'i khyim du 'bangs mo ro hi
NK117(she)001:16372: ta zhes par skyes tshe ston pas chos gsungs pa
NK117(she)001:16373: mnyan phyir sh+aakya'i ming can gyi chung ma dang 'bangs
NK117(she)001:16374: mo gnyis ka phyin tshe dpon mo'i mu tig gi
NK117(she)001:16375: do shal khyim du lus pa bran mo len du
NK117(she)001:16376: mngags tshe mo'i bsam pa la 'di lta bu'i chos
NK117(she)001:16377: zab mo nyan dbang med par 'gro dgos pa skal
NK117(she)001:16378: ba shin tu dman no snyam bzhin 'gro grab byas
NK117(she)001:16379: tshe / ston pas de'i bsam pa mkhyen nas chos
NK117(she)001:16380: tshigs su bcad pa gcig bslabs pa 'don bzhin song
NK117(she)001:16381: ba lam du ba drus ma zhig gis brdungs te
NK117(she)001:16382: tshe 'phos 'phral sing+ga la'i rgyal po'i bu mor srid
NK117(she)001:16383: pa bzung nas btsas ma thag tu mu tig gi
NK117(she)001:16384: char chen po babs pas mu tig can nam mu
NK117(she)001:16386: de yi bsod nams kyi mthus mnyan yod kyi tshong
NK117(she)001:16387: pa rnams rgya mtsho brgal nas sing+ga lar slebs pa'i
NK117(she)001:16388: mtshan thun la ston pas gsungs pa'i tshigs bcad 'ga'
NK117(she)001:16389: zhig glur blangs tshe bu mos thos pas yid phrogs
NK117(she)001:16390: te bzang po dag glu de da dung longs dang
NK117(she)001:16391: zer bas tshong pas 'di ni glu ma yin de
NK117(she)001:16392: sangs rgyas kyi gsung yin tshul bshad pas sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:16393: kyi mtshan thos pa'i mod la mu tig can rma
NK117(she)001:16394: byas dbyar rnga thos pa ltar gyur nas sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:16396: tshong pa rnams kyis ci nus bzhin rnam thar brjod
NK117(she)001:16397: pas bu mo de sngon las kyang dga' ba cher
NK117(she)001:16398: skyes nas ston pa'i zhabs drung du spring yig 'di
NK117(she)001:16399: bzhin phul ba mkhyen bzhin du bklags par /
NK117(she)001:16400: kye ma bsod nams tshong zong dag gis rnyed par gyur pa khyod ni dran pa nyid //
NK117(she)001:16401: rgud dang gdung ba dang ni sred pa 'joms pa'i srid pa'i sman bzang ci yang yin //
NK117(she)001:16402: bcom ldan las byung gtam gyis nyer bskrun yang dag rin pa myong ba'i sa //
NK117(she)001:16403: bcom ldan 'di de bdag gi bdud rtsi yang dag bgo skal chen por gyur pa yin //
NK117(she)001:16404: zhes pa la gzigs nas ri mo mkhan gyis bri
NK117(she)001:16405: bar mi nus pa'i rang gi sku gzugs ras kyi
NK117(she)001:16406: ngos la 'od zer bkye ba ltar bkod nas bka'i
NK117(she)001:16407: tshigs bcad 'ga' dang bcas bu mo de la slar
NK117(she)001:16408: spring bar mjal ma thag tu skyabs su 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:16409: gsum dang / bslab pa'i gnas lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:16411: 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:16412: rang bzhin shes nas rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:16414: de nas bu mos yul de'i mi rnams bstan pa'i sgor bcug /
NK117(she)001:16415: dkon mchog gsum la mu tig mchog ma ga d+ha'i bre re re phul /
NK117(she)001:16416: bu mor gnang ba'i sku de la thub pa 'od
NK117(she)001:16417: zer mar grags te sku gzugs kun gyi thog ma'o
NK117(she)001:16418: // tshul de 'dra bar bsams na mchog gsum rin
NK117(she)001:16419: po che'i rgyu 'bras mtha' dag dang 'brel ba'i chos
NK117(she)001:16420: kyi gtam yang dag pa ni 'gro ba yongs kyi
NK117(she)001:16421: mnyan par 'os pa spring yig lta bu'ang yin la
NK117(she)001:16422: // / 'khor ba'i rang bzhin nyon mongs pa dang
NK117(she)001:16423: rnam rtog las gyur pa'i 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi
NK117(she)001:16424: khur 'khyer ba la bdud kyi bu mo zhes smad
NK117(she)001:16426: de nyid la sangs rgyas kyi bka'i 'brel ba ma thob /
NK117(she)001:16427: rnam dkar la blo phyogs par ma gyur tshe de'i
NK117(she)001:16428: bzhin ras zhes gdong me tog kun+d+ha'i tshal ltar mdzes
NK117(she)001:16429: pa de yang sngon chad skal ba ngan pa'o zhes
NK117(she)001:16430: skyon mtshang las ldog par bgyid pa la mngon par
NK117(she)001:16431: phyogs pa de yang sangs rgyas kyi mathu'o //
NK117(she)001:16433: rtsom par dam bca' ba ni /
NK117(she)001:16435: blo mchog rnams kyi yon tan dag byed gter //
NK117(she)001:16436: gcig tu barlingasa nas spyi brtol rlabs phreng gi //
NK117(she)001:16437: ca co sgrogs 'di mdzes pa mi ngom yang //
NK117(she)001:16438: dam chos brjod la brten slad mnyan par 'os //
NK117(she)001:16440: 'di ltar blo mchog rgyal ba rnams kyis mdo sngags kyi sde snod rgya mtsho lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:16441: 'phags pa'i gang zag rnams kyis chings chen po lnga
NK117(she)001:16442: dang dgos 'brel yan lag bzhis gtan la dbab pa'i
NK117(she)001:16443: bstan bcos sogs bka' dang dgongs 'grel mchis bzhin du
NK117(she)001:16444: chos nyid kyi bden pa ma mthong lhas gnang ba
NK117(she)001:16445: ma thob / rig pa'i gnas lnga la ma sbyangs
NK117(she)001:16446: pa dag gis spyi brtol bskyed pa'i gzhung ngan dag
NK117(she)001:16447: la nang pa'i tshul gsum nyung zhing phyi rol pa'i
NK117(she)001:16448: ngan pa drug kyang 'dres srid pa'i dpe gcong rong
NK117(she)001:16449: gi 'bab chu drag shul can ca co'i sgra bar
NK117(she)001:16450: med du sgrogs pa lta bu la yon tan gyi
NK117(she)001:16451: mdzes cha gang yang ngom rgyus dben yang /
NK117(she)001:16452: gzhung 'di ni de ltar ma yin te de rtsom
NK117(she)001:16453: pa'i rgyu gsum gyi don la rang dbang bsgyur zhing
NK117(she)001:16454: dam pa gsum dang 'brel ba'i bstan bcos 'dzam gling
NK117(she)001:16455: rgyan drug mchog gnyis sogs 'phags bod kyi mkhas grub
NK117(she)001:16456: sngon byon rnams kyi rjes su 'gro bar gdon mi
NK117(she)001:16457: za bas som nyi spongs la /
NK117(she)001:16458: thos bsam sgom gsum 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum sogs dam
NK117(she)001:16459: pa'i chos ni brjod pa la brten dgos pa'i slad
NK117(she)001:16462: gzhung don la 'jug pa'i thog mar 'khor ba'i skyon mtshang ston pa ste /
NK117(she)001:16464: thog ma med nas skye rga na 'chi yi //
NK117(she)001:16465: rims kyis btab par sman chen bdud rtsi'i ro //
NK117(she)001:16466: dam chos lag tu mchis pa spong byed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16467: skye bo rnams la bdag gis ji ltar 'doms //
NK117(she)001:16468: de yang 'khor ba'i thog ma 'di 'dra'o zhes dpogs
NK117(she)001:16469: par nus pa ma yin bzhin skye rga na 'chi
NK117(she)001:16470: bzhis rtag par mnar ba'i dpe rims nad kyis btab
NK117(she)001:16471: pa'i nad pa'i tshogs la phan byed kyi sman chen
NK117(she)001:16472: po bdud rtsi'i ro lta bu ni dam pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:16473: kho na las gzhan ma mchis na /
NK117(she)001:16474: de nyid lag tu mchis pa zhes dge sgrub sdig
NK117(she)001:16475: spang sogs rnam dkar sgrub min rang la rag lus
NK117(she)001:16476: pa'i dus 'dir sgo gsum sdig la bsgyur bzhin dge
NK117(she)001:16477: tshogs spangs na thar lam dang 'brel ba gtan chad
NK117(she)001:16478: du 'gyur bar nges pas dge sdig go log tu
NK117(she)001:16479: spyod pa'i skye bo rnams la bdag gis ji ltar
NK117(she)001:16480: bshad / bshad kyang phan thogs par dka' zhes shugs kyis bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16481: de nas dal 'byor rnyed par dka' ba ston pa'i
NK117(she)001:16482: phyir mi khom pa brgyad kyi skyon mtshang 'chad pa
NK117(she)001:16484: ring nas bshes pa 'khor ba'i 'brog dgon du //
NK117(she)001:16485: mgo dang yan lag bcad pas gdungs byas shing //
NK117(she)001:16486: phyin chad gdung 'gyur lkog tu gyur pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:16487: da dung mtho ris bde la sred cing rmongs //
NK117(she)001:16489: dus thung ngu tsam ma yin zhing yun shin tu
NK117(she)001:16490: ring ba thog ma med pa'i dus nas 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:16491: 'brog dgon du zhes pa phan 'dogs mkhan gyi mi
NK117(she)001:16492: med cing dgra jag chom rkun dang gcan gzan dug
NK117(she)001:16493: sbrul sogs kyis gnod 'tshe sbyor ba'i yul ngan lta
NK117(she)001:16494: bu'i mi khom pa brgyad kyi gnas rigs su yang
NK117(she)001:16495: yang 'khor tshe mgo dang yan lag sogs bcad gtubs
NK117(she)001:16496: bgyis pas rab tu gdungs shing da lta'i gnas skabs
NK117(she)001:16497: 'dir yang mi'i lus rten tsam thob dam pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:16498: kyi sgor zhugs nas ltar snang legs pa tsam mang
NK117(she)001:16499: yang 'jig rten chos brgyad las ma 'das shing brtag
NK117(she)001:16500: dpyad zhib tu byas na chung ma med pa kho
NK117(she)001:16501: na la rab byung mchog tu brtsi ba dang /
NK117(she)001:16502: 'dre rdung gi lag len shes pa la rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:16503: theg pa bar brtsi ba sogs la phugs bcol nas
NK117(she)001:16504: dad dam dang snying rje sogs cang mi sems par
NK117(she)001:16505: rgya gar gyi phyi rol pa la la dang bod
NK117(she)001:16506: kyi bon po 'ga' zhig bzhin sha khrag gi dmar
NK117(she)001:16507: ston rgya chen po bstar nas tshe ldan gyi rim
NK117(she)001:16508: gro dang gshin por dge rtsa sgrub rloms byed pa
NK117(she)001:16509: sogs sgo gsum mi dger 'jug pa'i skye bo mtha'
NK117(she)001:16510: dag dang khyad par chos la khungs bcol nas srog
NK117(she)001:16511: gcod sogs kyi mchod sbyin byed pa rnams skye ba
NK117(she)001:16512: 'di'i 'og tu ngan song gsum sogs mi khom pa'i
NK117(she)001:16513: gnas rigs tha chad du skyes nas sdug bsngal dpag
NK117(she)001:16514: med myong ba gdon mi za yang da lta'i dus
NK117(she)001:16515: 'dir khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal bltar mi
NK117(she)001:16516: mngon bzhin phyi ma bzod par dka' ba'i sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:16517: lkog tu gyur pa rnams kyang /
NK117(she)001:16518: da dung lha mi'i gnas su e skyes re ba
NK117(she)001:16519: byed pa rnams ni bde ba 'dod bzhin sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:16520: gyi rgyu la spyod pa'i rmongs pa ba lang lta
NK117(she)001:16522: bsam brlag de ni 'di nas yang ltung la //
NK117(she)001:16523: ngan song gsum dang 'du shes med pa'i lha //
NK117(she)001:16524: mtha' 'khob dbang po ma tshang lta ba log /
NK117(she)001:16525: sangs rgyas 'byung ba med pa dag tu 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:16526: zhes pa bsam brlag ni bsam pa mi dge ba
NK117(she)001:16527: skyes par gnyen pos sleb rgyu bral bzhin phyir zhing
NK117(she)001:16528: sems pa'i las kyis sdig la spyod pa ni rang
NK117(she)001:16529: gi bde ba gtan brlag tu 'gro bar nges shing
NK117(she)001:16530: de lta bu'i mi rnams ni 'jig rten 'di nas
NK117(she)001:16531: phyi mar 'gro tshe dmyal ba yi dwags dud 'gro
NK117(she)001:16532: gsum dang lha tshe ring po ste gzugs med khams
NK117(she)001:16533: mtha' 'khobs sam kla klo sogs dge sdig go log
NK117(she)001:16534: tu spyod pa rnams dang dbang po ma tshang ba
NK117(she)001:16535: mig rna ba lce gsum la skyon byung na rim
NK117(she)001:16536: bzhin chos mi mthong mi thos brjod mi shes pa
NK117(she)001:16537: sogs kyi skyon dang yid dbang smyo 'bog sogs kyis
NK117(she)001:16538: dran pa las su mi rung ba /
NK117(she)001:16539: lta ba log pa ni dge sdig gi rnam smin
NK117(she)001:16540: gyi 'bras bus bde sdug bskyed pa min zhes rgyu
NK117(she)001:16542: sangs rgyas 'byung ba med pa ni rtsod ldan gyi
NK117(she)001:16543: dus 'dir ston pa 'jig rten du byon yang mi
NK117(she)001:16544: rnams tshe lo rim gyis dman zhing nad mtshon mu
NK117(she)001:16545: ges mnar bas rgyal bstan yang re zhig nub skabs
NK117(she)001:16546: dang sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa rdzogs nas 'byung
NK117(she)001:16547: 'gyur gyi mun bskal shar tshe srid pa bzung ba
NK117(she)001:16549: thang gcig skabs btsal ma yin lcags sreg gzhir //
NK117(she)001:16550: mtshon gyi chad pa rtsub mos yang dang yang //
NK117(she)001:16551: srog 'phrog 'chi bar mi nus dmyal ba pa //
NK117(she)001:16552: da dung khong khro'i las ngan rnyi la thogs //
NK117(she)001:16554: mi khom pa brgyad kyi dang po dmyal ba la
NK117(she)001:16555: tsha dmyal brgyad dang grang dmyal brgyad nyi tshe nye
NK117(she)001:16556: 'khor ba gnyis dang bco brgyad du gsungs pas de
NK117(she)001:16557: dag so so'i sdug bsngal la spyod kyang der skye
NK117(she)001:16558: ba'i rnam smin ma zad par 'chi bar mi nus
NK117(she)001:16559: shing da dung yang khong khro'i sems dang bcas te
NK117(she)001:16560: las ngan gyi 'phro rnyi lta bu la thogs nas
NK117(she)001:16561: thar pa'i go sar slebs mi thub pas chos byed
NK117(she)001:16563: yi dwags la yang byings na gnas pa dang mkha'
NK117(she)001:16564: rgyu gnyis te spyi mthun du bkres skom gyi sdug
NK117(she)001:16565: bsngal la rtag tu spyod pas chos byed du mi
NK117(she)001:16566: khom pa'o // dud 'gro la yang spyi mthun du
NK117(she)001:16567: rmongs shing gti mug gi mun pa 'thibs pa'i dge
NK117(she)001:16568: sdig mi shes pa dang phan tshun gcig gis gcig
NK117(she)001:16569: la 'tshe ba la sogs pas sdug bsngal zhing /
NK117(she)001:16570: bye brag mi yul na yod pa rnams srog gcod khrag btsags spu btog /
NK117(she)001:16571: khal 'gel ba dang zhon pa'i ched du bkol zhing
NK117(she)001:16572: rta drel la srab dang mdzo khal la sna zung
NK117(she)001:16573: sgrog dang tha gus 'ching ba sogs mdor na rang
NK117(she)001:16574: gis ci dgar spyod chog pa'i phyir lus 'dul ba'i
NK117(she)001:16575: mnar spyod sems la 'dzin pa las chos byed du
NK117(she)001:16577: rnag khrag phyi sa sogs kyang mi rnyed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16578: yi dwags phongs pas nyam thag smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:16579: chu klung ljon pa bltas pa'i mod la bskams //
NK117(she)001:16580: nang khrol 'tshig pa'i sdug bsngal zad mi shes //
NK117(she)001:16581: sgrib pa'i mthus byas tshe tshad nges pa med //
NK117(she)001:16582: dud 'gro phan tshun gcig la gcig bza' zhing //
NK117(she)001:16583: rngon pa'i dam bzhag rtsub mos srog 'phrog dang //
NK117(she)001:16584: bkol phyir 'dul ba 'dzin pas nyam thag pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16585: gnas su skye ba thob na ci byar yod //
NK117(she)001:16586: ces pa rnams ni 'og tu 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs
NK117(she)001:16587: kyi skabs su 'chad dgos pa dang bshad ma thag
NK117(she)001:16589: 'tsho ba'i las mtha' shin tu ring pos bsring //
NK117(she)001:16590: skye ba'i go skabs mi dbye gzugs med dang //
NK117(she)001:16591: thos bsam rten 'gags 'du shes med pa'i lha //
NK117(she)001:16592: 'chi khar log par lta bas khom ldan min //
NK117(she)001:16594: gzugs med khams su skyes pa dag tshe ring por
NK117(she)001:16595: 'tsho yang rtsa thig rlung gsum la brten pa'i lus
NK117(she)001:16596: rten min phyir shes bya la 'jug pa'i skabs dang
NK117(she)001:16599: rkang pa gnyis pa'i khyogs la rab brten yang //
NK117(she)001:16600: de yi 'du shes bsod nams ma yin pas //
NK117(she)001:16601: dam la bzhag cing gzhungs pa'i kla klo rnams //
NK117(she)001:16602: blang dor shin tu 'chol ba'i nang na 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:16604: kla klo ni rkang pa gnyis kyis btegs nas 'gro
NK117(she)001:16605: ba dang phung khams skye mched rnam pa mi dang
NK117(she)001:16606: 'dra yang bsam spyod byed las thams cad mi dge
NK117(she)001:16607: ba kho na yin pas chos byed du mi khom
NK117(she)001:16609: dbang po'i dam bca' nyams pa'i lkugs pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:16610: 'phags pa'i ded dpon dag dang phrad gyur kyang //
NK117(she)001:16611: brag ca'i cho gas bzung ba'i ca co bzhin //
NK117(she)001:16612: brda' mi 'phrod pa'i 'brog dgon chen por gdungs //
NK117(she)001:16614: ngag lkugs pas tshig gi brda' mi 'phrod pa dang
NK117(she)001:16615: yid lkugs pas skyes bu dam pa dang 'brel yang
NK117(she)001:16616: dge sdig gi blang dor la rmongs pas mi khom
NK117(she)001:16618: skye ba'i rgya mtsho brgal ba'i gru bo che //
NK117(she)001:16619: rnam rig ba dan g.yo ba thob nas slar //
NK117(she)001:16620: sangs rgyas 'byung la mnyes par mi bgyid pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16621: log par blta ba 'dzin de bdud kyis gtses //
NK117(she)001:16623: gang dag gzugs dang longs spyod ldan zhing rnam rig
NK117(she)001:16624: shin tu grungs pa'i tshul gyis gzhan la phan slob
NK117(she)001:16625: nyes ldog gi rnam 'gyur ngom yang sangs rgyas 'byung
NK117(she)001:16626: ba la mnyes par mi bgyid cing brnyas smod kyi
NK117(she)001:16627: sgo nas las dge sdig gi 'bras bu bde sdug
NK117(she)001:16628: dang tshe phyi ma med ces mu stegs byed dang
NK117(she)001:16629: mtshungs par smra ba ni log par blta ba 'dzin
NK117(she)001:16630: pa ste / dge ba'i las la rgyab kyis phyogs pas mi khom pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16632: thub pa rnams kyis spangs pa'i bskal pa yi //
NK117(she)001:16633: gcong rong mun nag 'thibs por lhung de slar //
NK117(she)001:16634: ldang bar brtson kyang lam min rgyun ldan te //
NK117(she)001:16635: nyam nga'i ltung bar 'og nas 'og tu 'gro //
NK117(she)001:16637: bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas stong gi bstan pa ji srid gnas kyi bar la sgron bskal dang /
NK117(she)001:16638: bstan pa nub tshe thub pa rnams kyis spangs pa'i
NK117(she)001:16639: mun bskal gcong rong mun nag 'thibs pa lta bu
NK117(she)001:16640: der skyes tshar nas lam min rgyun ldan du zhugs
NK117(she)001:16641: pa skyes bu rkang pa chag pa zhig mtshan mo
NK117(she)001:16642: rbab tu shor ba ltar 'og tu lhung ba las
NK117(she)001:16643: yar thar pa'i thabs zad pa lta bu'i mi khom
NK117(she)001:16644: pa'o // de nas gzhung 'di'i rtsa ba na mi
NK117(she)001:16645: gsal yang 'grel pa na skabs 'dir mi lus thob
NK117(she)001:16646: kyang mi khom pa bcu drug yod tshul gsungs pa
NK117(she)001:16649: dug lnga 'khrugs dang blun rmongs bdud kyis zin //
NK117(she)001:16650: le lo can dang las ngan mtsho chen brdol //
NK117(she)001:16651: gzhan dbang 'jigs skyob chos ltar bcos pa ste //
NK117(she)001:16652: 'phral byung rkyen gyis mi khom rnam pa brgyad //
NK117(she)001:16653: thar lam chos kyi snod min phyin ci log /
NK117(she)001:16655: dug lnga gcig las gcig mtho ba chu bo dba'
NK117(she)001:16656: klong 'khrugs pa lta bus rgyud mi dge ba la
NK117(she)001:16657: sbyar ba dang / rang rgyud blun zhing rmongs pas sdig grogs kyi dbang du song ba dang /
NK117(she)001:16658: bdud kyi bshes gnyen dang 'phrad nas lta spyod phyin ci log dang /
NK117(she)001:16659: chos la dang ba tsam yod kyang brtson 'grus med pa'i le lo can dang /
NK117(she)001:16660: las ngan gyi mtsho rdol ba zhes dgra gyod mi
NK117(she)001:16661: kha na tsha sogs kyi 'gal rkyen byung ba lam
NK117(she)001:16662: khyer ma shes nas bar chod du song ba /
NK117(she)001:16663: chos sgor 'jug blo yod kyang lus ngag gzhan dbang du song ba /
NK117(she)001:16664: lto gos dang dpya khral kho nas 'jigs skyob don
NK117(she)001:16665: du gnyer nas bstan la zhugs bardzu byas kyang chos
NK117(she)001:16666: min gyi bsam spyod 'ba' zhig la brtson pa /
NK117(she)001:16667: sems rgyud chos dang 'gal yang gzhan ngor chos ltar
NK117(she)001:16668: bcos nas rnyed bkur dang grags pa sgrub pa rnams
NK117(she)001:16670: 'ching ba dam ldan kun spyod shin tu ngan //
NK117(she)001:16671: 'khor bar mi skyo dad pa cung zad med //
NK117(she)001:16672: mi dge sdig spyod chos la sems pa med //
NK117(she)001:16673: sdom dang dam tshig nyams pa zhes bya ba //
NK117(she)001:16674: ris chad blo yi mi khom rnam pa brgyad //
NK117(she)001:16675: chos las ring 'gyur thar lam sgron me nub //
NK117(she)001:16677: rdzas dang yo byad mchod sbyin la mi gtong ba ha cang 'ching ba dam pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16678: mi gzhi ngan pas bsam sbyor gang yang sdig sbrul lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:16679: 'khor ba'i skyon mtshang ji tsam mthong zhing thos kyang
NK117(she)001:16680: nges 'byung dang skyo shas mi skye ba chos snang
NK117(she)001:16681: ba'i sgo dad pa gtan nas med pa sgo gsum
NK117(she)001:16682: shin tu rtsings pas nyes spyod kho nas dus 'da'
NK117(she)001:16683: ba / mchog gsum rin po che'i yon tan mthong thos su gyur kyang dad gus mi skye ba /
NK117(she)001:16684: bstan la zhugs par rloms kyang sdom gsum so sor
NK117(she)001:16685: nyes 'gal byung ba la ci mi snyam pa ste
NK117(she)001:16686: / 'di dag gi skyon sel dang mthun sgrub la brtson pa gal che zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16688: sdig sdug 'thor rlung 'khrugs pa'i gnas rigs su //
NK117(she)001:16689: ngal zhing skrag bcas bsod nams rnyog pa can //
NK117(she)001:16690: chos la phrag pa dog pa'i mi khom brgyad //
NK117(she)001:16691: bsam nas rang gi dal ba don yod mdzod //
NK117(she)001:16693: sdig pa'i las kyis 'phangs pas sdug bsngal 'thor rlung
NK117(she)001:16694: ltar 'khrugs pa'i gnas rigs mi khom pa brgyad du
NK117(she)001:16695: skyes na 'phral phugs gnyis ka bde ba'i thabs la
NK117(she)001:16696: rmongs shing sdug bsngal kho na'i rgyu bsgrub pa la
NK117(she)001:16697: nan tan bgyis pas ngal zhing skrag pa dang bcas
NK117(she)001:16698: pa'i bsod nams rnyog pa can ni bsod nams ma
NK117(she)001:16699: yin pa'i las mi dge ba bcu yin la /
NK117(she)001:16700: de dag ni chos dang rgyab 'gal lta bu yin
NK117(she)001:16701: phyir phrag pa dog pa'i tha snyad bzhag pa yin
NK117(she)001:16702: la de lta bu'i mi khom pa'i skyon dang dal
NK117(she)001:16703: 'byor gyi yon tan la bsams nas rang gi dal
NK117(she)001:16704: rten don yod par mdzod ces gdams pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16706: yul dbus sa gzhi gtsang mar dbang po dang //
NK117(she)001:16707: yan lag rab rdzogs dad pa'i gnas la dad //
NK117(she)001:16708: las matha'i me tog sdig tos ma bcom pa'i //
NK117(she)001:16709: mir gyur dpag bsam ljon pa shin tu dkon //
NK117(she)001:16710: rgyal ba u dum w+aa ra 'jig rten byon //
NK117(she)001:16711: chos kyi me tog kha phye bstan pa'i tshal //
NK117(she)001:16712: nub pa med par gnas la yang dag zhugs //
NK117(she)001:16713: dam pa'i grib bsil la brten de bas nyung //
NK117(she)001:16715: rang 'byor lnga dang gzhan 'byor lnga ste /
NK117(she)001:16717: dam pa'i chos gang du dar ba'i yul de nyid
NK117(she)001:16718: sa gzhi gtsang ma lta bur dbang po tshang zhing
NK117(she)001:16719: yan lag la skyon med pa dang dad pa yod
NK117(she)001:16721: dmag dpon tshong dpon rngon pa nya pa sogs sdig
NK117(she)001:16722: spyod chos la 'jug pa'i skal ba dman pa'i rigs
NK117(she)001:16723: su ma skyes pa la las matha'i me tog sdig
NK117(she)001:16724: tos ma bcom pa'i zhes rten mir gyur pa ni
NK117(she)001:16725: dpag bsam ljon pa lta bu shin tu rnyed pa
NK117(she)001:16726: dkon tshul dper sbyar ba dang /
NK117(she)001:16727: de yang mi lus thob pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16728: chos dar ba'i yul du skyes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16731: rgyal bstan la dad pa lnga ni rang 'byor lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:16733: 'khor ba'i skyon mtshang gis 'jigs pa las rgyal ba
NK117(she)001:16734: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du 'byon pa ni u dum
NK117(she)001:16735: w+aa ra'i me tog ltar dkon yang ston mchog thub
NK117(she)001:16736: pa'i dbang po 'jig rten du byon pa dang chos
NK117(she)001:16737: kyi me tog kha phye zhes pa ni bstan pa'i
NK117(she)001:16738: pad tshal rab tu rgyas shing /
NK117(she)001:16739: de nyid kyang nub pa med par mdo sngags gang
NK117(she)001:16740: la 'jug 'dod pa'i gnas de la yang dag par
NK117(she)001:16741: zhugs pa dang / der 'jug pa'i thabs ston pa'i
NK117(she)001:16742: skyes bu dam pa'i skyabs 'og la brten pa ni
NK117(she)001:16743: rim bzhin dkon par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:16744: de yang sangs rgyas byon pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16746: gsungs pa'i chos ma nub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16747: rang nyid legs su 'dod pa rnams der spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16748: de bzhin snying nas chos sgrub pa rnams la yul gong mas byams brtses skyong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:16749: 'og mas kyang dad 'dun gyi brtse sems yod pa sogs ni gzhan 'byor lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:16750: de lta bu'i dal 'byor bco brgyad dang ldan pa'i
NK117(she)001:16751: lus rten de nyid shin tu rnyed par dka' ba'i
NK117(she)001:16753: gang phyir rang nyid 'byor pa'i ljon pa dang //
NK117(she)001:16754: gzhan dbang rkyen gyis 'byor pa'i u dum w+aar //
NK117(she)001:16755: gnyis ka'i yon tan 'byor pa rnam pa bcus //
NK117(she)001:16756: dal ba brgyad la 'khyud 'di slar mi rnyed //
NK117(she)001:16757: gang phyir zhes don ci'i slad du na rang 'byor
NK117(she)001:16758: lnga ni dpag bsam gyi ljon pa ltar dkon zhing
NK117(she)001:16759: de las kyang gzhan 'byor lnga po ni u dum
NK117(she)001:16760: w+aa ra'i me tog bzhin rab tu dkon zhing /
NK117(she)001:16761: rang gzhan gnyis ka'i yon tan 'byor pa rnam pa
NK117(she)001:16762: bcus dal ba brgyad kyi rten mi lus la 'khyud
NK117(she)001:16763: pa 'di 'dra ba slar mi rnyed do //
NK117(she)001:16766: ci phyir rus sbal mgrin dang gnya' shing dpe //
NK117(she)001:16767: grangs ni mi dang dud 'gro nyin mtshan gyi //
NK117(she)001:16768: skar mas phye ba de snyed yi dwags dang //
NK117(she)001:16769: dmyal ba rnams la rim pas shes par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:16771: ston pa sh+aakya thub pas dge slong dag 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:16772: khams 'di rgya mtsho chen po gcig tu gyur pa'i
NK117(she)001:16773: gting rum na rus sbal long ba zhig yod pa
NK117(she)001:16774: de nyid lo brgya re lon pa'i 'phror rgya mtsho'i
NK117(she)001:16775: khar lan re rgyu ba na /
NK117(she)001:16776: rgya mtsho de'i kha na gnya' shing bug pa gcig
NK117(she)001:16777: pa zhig phyogs bzhi'i rlung gis rgyu phyogs so sor
NK117(she)001:16778: bsgyur ba zhig yod pa'i gnya' shing de'i bug par
NK117(she)001:16779: rus sbal gyi mgrin pa tshud pa las ni mi
NK117(she)001:16780: lus thob pa dka' zhes mdo sde las rgyas par
NK117(she)001:16781: bstan pa'i tshig sna bstungs te bshad pa ni dpe'i
NK117(she)001:16782: sgo nas rnyed par dka' tshul dang /
NK117(she)001:16783: grangs kyi sgo nas rnyed par dka' ba ni mi'i
NK117(she)001:16784: 'gro ba nyin mo'i skar ma tsam la dud 'gro
NK117(she)001:16786: de bzhin du yi dwags dang dmyal bar bgres shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:16788: de phyir dal ba'i gru chen 'dzin pa'i dus //
NK117(she)001:16789: sdug bsngal chu gter pha mtha' ma brgal na //
NK117(she)001:16790: chos lam mgron pos gnyer zhing skabs btsal ba'i //
NK117(she)001:16791: mnyan pa 'bras med bgyid la phyogs pa yin //
NK117(she)001:16792: da res mi khom pa brgyad du ma skyes shing
NK117(she)001:16793: dal 'byor gyi mi lus rin po che thob pa
NK117(she)001:16794: 'di ni rgya mtsho sgrol ba'i gru bo che lta
NK117(she)001:16795: bu 'di nyid ma zhig par 'dzin pa'i dus 'dir
NK117(she)001:16796: / 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho las sgrol
NK117(she)001:16797: ba'i thabs zhig ma byas na chos la 'jug blo
NK117(she)001:16798: tsam yod kyang lam zhugs kyi mgron pos rin po
NK117(she)001:16799: che don du gnyer phyir grur zhugs nas rgya mtsho
NK117(she)001:16800: brgal ba'i skabs btsal yang thog tu ma khel ba
NK117(she)001:16801: lta bu'i tshe 'dir snang gi dbang du song ba
NK117(she)001:16802: rnams la skyon mtshang bstan phyir lus kyi gru la
NK117(she)001:16803: sems kyi gnyan pa khyod kyis 'khor ba sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:16804: gyi rgya mtsho ma bsgral na dal 'byor bco brgyad
NK117(she)001:16805: dang ldan pa'i mi lus rin po che 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:16806: med pa la phyogs par byas so //
NK117(she)001:16808: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:16809: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:16810: lde mig las le'u dang po'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:16811: gnyis pa 'chi ba mi rtag pa 'chad pa ni /
NK117(she)001:16813: srid pa brtan g.yo chags gnas 'jig stong bzhi'i //
NK117(she)001:16814: ngo bos bskal pa'i tshad du btags pa yang //
NK117(she)001:16815: 'jig pa'i rten gyur ming gis sma phab pa'i //
