NK117(she)001:16816: chad pa gcod la me bdun chu gcig 'ong //
NK117(she)001:16818: snod kyi 'jig rten la chags gnas 'jig stong bzhi yod pa la /
NK117(she)001:16820: nam mkha' stong pa'i klong du rlung rdo rje rgya
NK117(she)001:16821: gram gzhom gzhig bral ba chags pa'i steng du chu'i
NK117(she)001:16822: dal dang de'i steng du dbang chen gser gyi sa
NK117(she)001:16823: gzhi ser po mtsho khar dar chags pa lta bu
NK117(she)001:16824: / de sprin char gyis brlan pa'i rkyen las dbus
NK117(she)001:16825: su ri bo mchog rab phyogs bzhi rim bzhin shar
NK117(she)001:16828: gser rnams las grub pa'i phyogs so so'i nam mkha'i mdog kyang de ltar snang ba /
NK117(she)001:16829: lhun po dpag tshad brgyad khri chur nub cing steng du'ang de snyed kyis 'phags so //
NK117(she)001:16830: de la gser ri bdun gyis mu khyud ltar bskor
NK117(she)001:16831: ba ni nang nas rim bzhin gnya' shing 'dzin lhun
NK117(she)001:16833: de las rim bzhin phyed phyed kyis dma' bas gshol mda' 'dzin /
NK117(she)001:16839: de dag gi bar rnams su rol pa'i mtsho bdun gyis bskor zhing 'khyil ba'o //
NK117(she)001:16840: mu khyud 'dzin gyi phyi'i 'khor yug lcags las grub cing de'i phyed dang mnyam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16841: de'i phyi rol gyi gling bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:16842: shar lus 'phags po zla ba phyed pa lta bu /
NK117(she)001:16843: lho 'dzam bu'i gling sog ka lta bu de'i dbus
NK117(she)001:16844: su 'dren pa stong bzhugs pa'i gnas rdo rje'i gdan
NK117(she)001:16845: / nub na ba glang spyod zlum po /
NK117(she)001:16846: byang sgra mi snyan gru bzhi /
NK117(she)001:16848: shar nas brtsis te gling bzhi'i g.yas dang g.yon du /
NK117(she)001:16850: rnga yab dang rnga yab gzhan /
NK117(she)001:16852: sgra mi snyan dang sgra mi snyan gyi zla /
NK117(she)001:16853: de ltar gling bcu gnyis po'i mdun ngos lhun po la phyogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16854: g.yo ba bcud kyi sems can rnams kyang yas rim gyis chags te /
NK117(she)001:16855: dang po dmyal ba mnar med dang de'i steng nas
NK117(she)001:16856: tsha dmyal brgyad lugs ldog gi tshul gyis yang sos
NK117(she)001:16858: de'i byang du dpag tshad nyi shu gzhal ba na grang dmyal brgyad mas rim du yod do //
NK117(she)001:16859: nyi tshe ba yang nges med kyi gnas na yod
NK117(she)001:16860: cing nye 'khor ba tsha dmyal gyi phyogs bzhir bzhi
NK117(she)001:16862: yi dwags gtso chen rnams 'dzam bu'i gling gi rgyal
NK117(she)001:16863: po'i khab kyi 'og dpag tshad lnga brgya na yod
NK117(she)001:16864: cing / lhag ma phal cher lha mi'i gnas na yang yod ces gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:16865: dud 'gro byings gnas rgya mtsho dang kha 'thor ba ni 'dod pa'i khams na yod do //
NK117(she)001:16866: mtho ris dang po mi rnams ni rnga yab gling ma gtogs pa'i gling gzhan na gnas shing /
NK117(she)001:16867: rnga yab gling pa srin po kho na yin pas yi dwags srin po'i rigs can du bsdu'o //
NK117(she)001:16868: mtho ris kyi phyogs gnyis pa lha la 'dod gzugs gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:16869: 'dod lha drug gi dang po rgyal chen rigs bzhi ni ri rab kyi bang rim bzhi po dang /
NK117(she)001:16870: nyi zla gza' skar gyi steng dang /
NK117(she)001:16873: ri dang shing dang nags kyi lha sogs rgyal chen bzhi'i rigs su gtogs so //
NK117(she)001:16874: de yang bang rim dang po 'og mar byas nas rim bzhin lag na gzhong thogs dang /
NK117(she)001:16876: sbrang chang gis rtag myos bzhi'o //
NK117(she)001:16877: rgyal chen bzhi bzhugs pa'i yul shar na yul 'khor srung /
NK117(she)001:16880: byang na lcang lo can bzhi pho brang yin la
NK117(she)001:16881: de na rgyal chen sde bzhi bzhugs pa la phyogs
NK117(she)001:16883: dri za grul bum klu gnod sbyin rnams kyis bskor ba lha'i longs spyod sogs dpag tu med do //
NK117(she)001:16884: ri gnya' shing 'dzin gyi rtse mo'i bla na nyi
NK117(she)001:16885: ma'i dal zheng la dpag tshad nga gcig dang 'khor
NK117(she)001:16886: yug la de'i sum 'gyur 'og gzhi me shel /
NK117(she)001:16887: zla ba dpag tshad lnga bcu 'khor yug gong mtshungs 'og gzhi chu shel /
NK117(she)001:16888: gnyis ka'i srid du dpag tshad phyed drug dang dpag
NK117(she)001:16889: tshad kyi bco brgyad cha gcig steng du gnas so
NK117(she)001:16890: // nyi zla gnyis ka'i steng gi 'khor yug la
NK117(she)001:16891: gser dang dngul gyi ra bas bskor ba'i nang na
NK117(she)001:16893: zla ba'i nang na lha mo mang pos gang zhing /
NK117(she)001:16894: skar ma rnams chu shel dang gser zangs mkhar ba
NK117(she)001:16895: ci rigs yod la steng gi cha gser gyi ra
NK117(she)001:16896: bas bskor ba / che tshad rgyang grags bco brgyad chung ba rgyang grags gcig tsam mo //
NK117(she)001:16897: 'dod lha'i gnas gnyis pa ni ri rab kyi steng
NK117(she)001:16898: na nye dbang gi gnas ma 'dres pa dang chos
NK117(she)001:16899: bzang lha'i 'dun sa la sogs pa sum cu rtsa
NK117(she)001:16900: gsum na gtso bo nye dbang so gnyis /
NK117(she)001:16901: lha'i dbang po dang so gsum yod pa la sum cu rtsa gsum pa zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:16902: ri dbang gi rtse mo'i mtshams bzhi'i khang bu na
NK117(she)001:16903: gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje zhes lha'i rigs gnas
NK117(she)001:16904: la / grong khyer blta na sdug nas dpag tshad
NK117(she)001:16905: nyi shur gzhal ba'i sa na phyogs bzhi'i shar nas
NK117(she)001:16906: la / rim bzhin / shing rta sna tshogs pa'i tshal /
NK117(she)001:16910: tshal de na 'dren pa stong gi gzims khri dpal yon ldan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:16911: de'i phyi rol na sa gzhi bzang po bzhi yod pa ni sna tshogs zhes bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:16914: dga' ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:16915: grong khyer mchog de'i byang shar na shing yongs 'du
NK117(she)001:16916: sa brtol dang de'i drung na a mo ni ka
NK117(she)001:16917: ltar dkar ba'i rdo leb ma chu zheng dpag tshad
NK117(she)001:16918: lnga bcu pa'i steng du sum cu rtsa gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:16919: lha rnams dbyar zla ra ba la 'dus nas 'dod
NK117(she)001:16920: yon lnga la longs spyod do //
NK117(she)001:16921: grong khyer blta na sdug de'i lho nub na chos bzang lha'i 'dun sa yod do //
NK117(she)001:16922: de ltar 'dod lha'i gnas gnyis po de ni sa gzhi la brten pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16923: bsod nams cha mthun gyi rgyu las mkha' la gnas pa'i 'dod lha rigs bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:16927: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed rnams mas rim gyis chags so //
NK117(she)001:16928: lha min kyang 'dod khams par gtogs shing tshe sngon
NK117(she)001:16929: dge sdig 'dres mar spyad pa dang khyad par yi
NK117(she)001:16931: rdzogs byed lha'i dge bas rdzogs pas dpal 'byor lha dang 'gran tsam yod do //
NK117(she)001:16932: ri rab rgya mtshor nub pa'i khong seng gi chu mtshams na sgra gcan 'dzin /
NK117(she)001:16933: de'i 'og nas mar la rim bzhin /
NK117(she)001:16936: gser gyi sa gzhi la gnas pa rnams 'dod lha'i 'byor pa dang mnyam zhing /
NK117(she)001:16944: rta mchog la sogs pa lha dang 'gran pa ltar yod cing /
NK117(she)001:16945: gzhan lha ma yin rnams ni 'dzam gling /
NK117(she)001:16948: ri rab la sogs nges med na yod pa rnams bdud rigs kyi mi ma yin rnams so //
NK117(she)001:16949: 'dod pa'i gnas ris bstan zin to //
NK117(she)001:16950: 'dod khams las dpag tshad bzhi khri gyen du 'phags pa'i nam mkhar mas rim gyis /
NK117(she)001:16953: tshangs chen gsum ni bsam gtan dang po chung 'bring che gsum thob pa las byung ngo //
NK117(she)001:16956: 'od gsal gsum ni bsam gtan gnyis pa chung 'bring che gsum gong bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:16959: dge rgyas gsum ni bsam gtan gsum pa sogs 'gres so //
NK117(she)001:16962: 'bras bu che ba gsum ni bsam gtan bzhi pa gong ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:16963: de'i steng na gtsang ris lnga yod de /
NK117(she)001:16969: de dag ni bsam gtan bzhi pa spel mar bsgoms pa las grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:16970: 'og ma bzhi po ni so so skye bo'i gnas gzhan bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:16971: de'i steng ma lnga ni nyan rang 'phags pa'i gnas gtsang ris lnga yin no //
NK117(she)001:16972: de yang tshangs chen man chad gling bzhi pa'i 'jig
NK117(she)001:16973: rten yan chad 'phred la de 'dra ba stong phrag
NK117(she)001:16974: gcig gis 'khor yug tu bskor ba'i mtha' lcags ri
NK117(she)001:16975: gcig gis bskor ba'i steng du snod kyi kha chod
NK117(she)001:16976: ltar 'od gsal chen po'i gnas kyis khebs pa la
NK117(she)001:16977: stong spyi phud kyi 'jig rten khams zer /
NK117(she)001:16978: yang de 'dra ba stong thad kar bsgrigs pas zlum
NK117(she)001:16979: por bskor ba'i mtha' lcags ris bskor ba'i kha chod
NK117(she)001:16980: lta bur dge rgyas kyi gnas gcig gis khebs pa
NK117(she)001:16981: man la stong gnyis bar ma'i 'jig rten zer /
NK117(she)001:16982: yang de 'dra ba stong phred la bsgrigs pa'i mtha'
NK117(she)001:16983: gong ltar dang spyir 'jig rten re re'i 'go gzhi
NK117(she)001:16985: de 'og chu'i dkyil 'khor re re yod cing /
NK117(she)001:16986: de kun gyi 'og gzhi rlung gi dkyil 'khor chen po gcig gis brten pa yar bzung /
NK117(she)001:16987: 'og min mar bzung la stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams zer /
NK117(she)001:16988: gzugs med khams kyang der 'thus dgos par gsungs /
NK117(she)001:16989: der ma zad stong gsum chen po'i phyogs bzhi mtshams
NK117(she)001:16990: brgyad kyi phyi rol so sor gzhal ba'i nam mkhas
NK117(she)001:16991: gar khyab thams cad snga ma lta bu rten dang
NK117(she)001:16992: brten pas bar med du khyab cing /
NK117(she)001:16993: de thams cad kyi sa steng khong seng sa bla kun /
NK117(she)001:16994: mi dang lha dang lha min sogs kyis gang zhing /
NK117(she)001:16995: 'og ngan song gsum gyis gang ba ni shes dgos shing /
NK117(she)001:16996: stong gsum la sogs pa'i bgrang gzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:16998: gling bzhi dang ni nyi zla dang //
NK117(she)001:16999: ri rab dang ni 'dod lhar bcas //
NK117(she)001:17000: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK117(she)001:17001: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK117(she)001:17002: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK117(she)001:17003: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK117(she)001:17004: de stong la ni stong gsum ste //
NK117(she)001:17007: 'og gzhi rlung gi dkyil 'khor yar bzung 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:17008: che ba mar bzung chags 'jig gnas stong 'ol spyi
NK117(she)001:17009: tsam mnyam pa'o // de yang bye brag tu dbye
NK117(she)001:17010: na me chu rlung gsum gyis 'jig tshe bsam gtan
NK117(she)001:17011: bzhi pa so so'i 'jig min gyi rgyu rkyen yang
NK117(she)001:17013: de lta bu'i stong gsum de la mi mjed 'jig rten zer zhing /
NK117(she)001:17014: de yang lha las mi mched tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:17015: mdo sde las 'od gsal gyi lha las mched pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17016: rgyal chen sde bzhi las mched par yang bshad rgyud
NK117(she)001:17017: dag las lha'i bu nyi ma dang zla ba gnyis
NK117(she)001:17018: bardzusa te skyes pa las 'dzam gling gi mi rnams
NK117(she)001:17019: mched pas las kyi sa pa zhes grags /
NK117(she)001:17020: de dus kyi mi rnams gzugs khams kyi lha dang
NK117(she)001:17021: mtshungs shing nyon mongs pa mngon rgyu ba med cing
NK117(she)001:17022: yon tan phal cher lha dang mtshungs kyang ji zhig
NK117(she)001:17023: na bskal pa bzang po nyams pa'i mgo zug bsod
NK117(she)001:17025: nyon mongs pa bag la nyal langs su nye /
NK117(she)001:17026: tshe lo dpag med nas brgyad khri yan gyi lus tshad la rang khru sum cu so gnyis /
NK117(she)001:17027: de nas rim bzhin nyi shu pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17028: bcu drug dang brgyad dang bzhi pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17029: rim bzhin bri nas tshe lo bcu pa la gtugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17030: gzhan gling gsum po yang lha las mched cing gling
NK117(she)001:17031: bzhi so so'i nam mkha' yang ri rab phyogs bzhi'i
NK117(she)001:17033: mdor na tshe lo dpag med nas rim gyis bri
NK117(she)001:17034: ste lo bye ba thub dus mi rnams sgo nga
NK117(she)001:17035: las skye / de nas yang rim gyis bri ste
NK117(she)001:17036: lo sa ya drug 'bum thub dus drod gsher du
NK117(she)001:17037: las skye / skye / de nas sngon bzhin tshe
NK117(she)001:17038: lo bri ba'i skyon gyis lo dgu khri thub tshe
NK117(she)001:17039: bltas pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags byung /
NK117(she)001:17040: de las lo lnga brgya bris tshe bgad pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags /
NK117(she)001:17041: de las kyang lnga brgya bris tshe reg pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags byung /
NK117(she)001:17042: de dag ni nyon mongs pa rim gyis je rags
NK117(she)001:17043: su song bas yon tan je nyung dang skyon je
NK117(she)001:17044: mang du song ba yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:17045: skabs de dag 'gar mu ge dang mun pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:17046: skabs kyang byung bar bshad cing de'i tshe 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:17047: spyi mthun gyi bsod nams las nyi zla gnyis byung
NK117(she)001:17048: ba bzhin gza' skar bcas byung /
NK117(she)001:17053: lus bongs rnams rim gyis phris bzhin gnyis 'khyud kyi 'dod chags las mngal skyes byung /
NK117(she)001:17054: de dus 'bras s+aa lu'i zhing btab pa'i 'tsho bar
NK117(she)001:17055: brten yang rku 'phrog sogs dar bar rtsod pa bsal
NK117(she)001:17056: phyir bgo bsha' byas pa las bgo mkhan nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:17057: skal ba chad pas kun yid ches bzhin de nyid
NK117(she)001:17058: rgyal por bskos pa la mang pos bkur ba'i rgyal
NK117(she)001:17059: po zer / gzhan dmangs kyi nang nas khyim spangs
NK117(she)001:17060: te gtsang sbra lta bur len pa dag la bram
NK117(she)001:17061: po zer / ze dang / khyim bzung ste pha ma sogs rgan rabs bkur ba la rje'u rigs /
NK117(she)001:17062: pha ma dang rgan rabs sogs bkur 'os su mi
NK117(she)001:17063: 'dzin cing lus kyi mi dge ba gsum la rgyun
NK117(she)001:17064: du brtson cing rlangs por spyod pa dag ni dmangs
NK117(she)001:17066: de dag ni mtho ris kyi chags tshul mdo tsam mo //
NK117(she)001:17067: ngan song ji ltar chags tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:17068: lha mi'i dug gsum gyi las bsags pa che chung
NK117(she)001:17069: gis gshin rje gtso 'khor du skyes nas mtshon cha'i
NK117(she)001:17070: rigs rnams so so'i las snang gis sprul pas snang
NK117(she)001:17071: ba yin la / des mnar spyod myong ba'i sems
NK117(she)001:17072: can dmyal ba mnar med pa la sogs tsha dmyal
NK117(she)001:17073: ba yin la / brgyad dang / de'i byang gi nye logs su grang dmyal brgyad gnas shing /
NK117(she)001:17074: de dag gi phyi rol du 'khor lhag pa bcu drug bcas las kyi mthus grub pa yin /
NK117(she)001:17075: 'dod chags kyi las bsags pas yi dwags srid pa
NK117(she)001:17076: la phyi dang nang dang spyi mthun dang sgos khur
NK117(she)001:17077: gyi sgrib pa can la sogs pa grub pa yin
NK117(she)001:17078: la / gti mug gi las kyis dud 'gro srid pa la gcig la gcig za ba dang /
NK117(she)001:17079: bkol spyod sogs 'tshe bas nyam thag pa can du grub bo //
NK117(she)001:17080: de ltar snod bcud chags pa'i grangs tshad gang gis
NK117(she)001:17081: bzung na dmyal ba mnar med du sems can gcig
NK117(she)001:17082: skyes nas sdug bsngal myong ba de ma thar gyi
NK117(she)001:17083: yun la snod chags pa'i bar bskal gcig ste /
NK117(she)001:17084: bcud chags pa la de 'dra ba bcu dgu /
NK117(she)001:17085: gnyis ka la bar bskal nyi shu'o //
NK117(she)001:17086: gnas pa'i bar bskal nyi shu ni /
NK117(she)001:17087: tshe lo dpag med nas brgyad khri'i bar du lo nyis brgya na re re bri'o //
NK117(she)001:17088: brgyad khri nas bcu pa'i bar du brgya tsho rer lo re bri'o //
NK117(she)001:17090: tshe lo bcu pa'i 'og tu srog gcod spangs pas tshe lo nyi shur 'phel /
NK117(she)001:17091: ma byin blangs spangs pas bzhi bcu /
NK117(she)001:17093: phra ma spangs pas nyis brgya /
NK117(she)001:17096: brnab sems spangs pas nyis stong /
NK117(she)001:17098: log par lta ba spangs pas nyi khri /
NK117(she)001:17099: ma rig pa'i 'dod chags spangs pas bzhi khri /
NK117(she)001:17100: log pa'i chos spyod pa spangs pas brgyad khri bar 'phel lo //
NK117(she)001:17101: de ltar yar 'phel gyi gnas skabs su tshe dang
NK117(she)001:17102: gzugs dang longs spyod sogs kyang 'phel zhing rgyas pa'o
NK117(she)001:17103: // de nas yang mi dge'i sde tshan rer 'gribs
NK117(she)001:17104: shing tshe lo bcu pa la gtugs nas yang yar
NK117(she)001:17106: de dag la bar khug bco brgyad ces so //
NK117(she)001:17108: bar khug bco brgyad rdzogs pa'i rjes su yar 'phel
NK117(she)001:17109: du song nas tshe lo dpag med thub pa mar
NK117(she)001:17110: 'grib la phyogs tshe sangs rgyas mos pa byon pa
NK117(she)001:17111: yan du bskal bzang sangs rgyas dgu brgya dang dgu
NK117(she)001:17112: bcu go dgu'i bstan pa rdzogs pa yin zhing mos
NK117(she)001:17113: pa'i bstan pa de'i yun dang mnyam par bshad pa
NK117(she)001:17114: yang thos so // dang po ya thog 'grib tshe 'khor ba 'jig brgyad khri dang /
NK117(she)001:17117: sh+aakya thub pa brgya pa'i dus su byon zhing /
NK117(she)001:17118: tshe lo bcu pa nas yar 'phel te brgyad khri'i
NK117(she)001:17119: dus byams pa byon bzhin sangs rgyas rnams phal cher
NK117(she)001:17120: tshe lo brgyad khri pa man chad la 'byung zhing
NK117(she)001:17123: gtsug tor can gsum ni gong du byon zhing phyis kyang 'byon pas ma nges par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:17124: de'i phyir na brgyad khri nas brgya pa'i bar kho na las mi 'byung bar mi blta ste /
NK117(she)001:17125: mgon po tshe mtha' yas dang /
NK117(she)001:17126: rnam gzigs ni tshe lo dpag med kyi dus na byon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17127: rang rgyal rnams ni sangs rgyas ma byon pa'i skabs
NK117(she)001:17128: dang nyan thos zad nas rgyal bstan nub pa'i dus
NK117(she)001:17130: mi rnams tshe lo dpag med thub pa nas brgyad
NK117(she)001:17131: khri'i bar du sngon gyi 'khor los bsgyur ba spyi
NK117(she)001:17132: bo skyes sogs rab bdun dang /
NK117(she)001:17133: gzhan yang gling gcig pa nas bzhi'i bar rim bzhin /
NK117(she)001:17134: lcags zangs dngul dang gser gyi 'khor los bsgyur rgyal
NK117(she)001:17135: byon nas rang rang gi nus pa'i rjes su 'gro
NK117(she)001:17137: rgyal po bzhi pos sngon gyi bsod nams bsags tshul
NK117(she)001:17138: dang mthun pa'i mchog dang nye ba'i rin chen sna
NK117(she)001:17139: bdun bcas 'byor pa longs spyod dpag tu med do
NK117(she)001:17140: // de nas tshe lo mar 'grib pa'i rgyu ni
NK117(she)001:17141: mi rnams mi dge du mar spyod pas bsod nams
NK117(she)001:17147: bcu pa rnams kyi bar tshe dang longs spyod kha dog /'od dang /
NK117(she)001:17149: de dus dge sdig go log pa spyod pa'i skyon cher 'phel te mtshon gyis zhag bdun /
NK117(she)001:17150: nad kyi bskal pa zla ba bdun dang zhag bdun /
NK117(she)001:17151: de bzhin du mu ges lo bdun /
NK117(she)001:17152: zla ba bdun zhag bdun sogs su mnar nas mi rnams phal cher zad par byed do //
NK117(she)001:17153: byang chub sems dpa'i sa las ni mar 'grib sum cu pa la mu ge /
NK117(she)001:17155: bcu pa la mtshon 'byung bar gsungs pa sogs rang gzhung gi bzhed tshul ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:17156: de ltar mi'i 'gro ba stongs mthar dge ba la
NK117(she)001:17157: brtson pa 'ga' zhig ri'i ljongs dang brag dbar sogs
NK117(she)001:17158: su zhugs pa zhag bdun du chus 'tsho zhing 'dug
NK117(she)001:17159: pa grong du 'ongs pa phan tshun 'phrad tshe sngon
NK117(she)001:17160: gyi nyes byas gleng nas rang rang gi rgyud kyi
NK117(she)001:17161: mi dge ba sdom pa la 'bad do //
NK117(she)001:17162: de'i tshe de dag gi nang nas byams pa'i sprul
NK117(she)001:17163: pa 'phags chos ldan pa zhig byung bar rgyu mtshan
NK117(she)001:17164: dris pa'i lan du srog gcod spangs pa'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:17165: yin tshul bshad pa ltar kun gyis de ltar byas
NK117(she)001:17166: pas de dag gi rigs brgyud rnams rim gyis nyi
NK117(she)001:17167: shu pa dang / yang sprul pa de nyid la brten nas lus kyi mi dge ba gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:17168: ngag gi mi dge ba bzhi /
NK117(she)001:17170: mi rigs pa'i 'dod pa dang chos min gyi chags
NK117(she)001:17171: pa log pa'i chos gsum gcig tu bsdoms pas phyin
NK117(she)001:17172: ci log lhag ma dgu spangs shing /
NK117(she)001:17173: mi chos gtsang ma'i lugs la spyad pa'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:17174: gyis tshe lo yar 'phel nas brgyad khri bar 'phel
NK117(she)001:17175: bzhin / bsod nams dang longs spyod sogs kyang 'phel ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:17176: de lta bu'i 'phel 'grib bco brgyad ni bar gyi khug pa yin la /
NK117(she)001:17178: bar khug rdzogs matha'i ma thog 'phel 'grib yun shin
NK117(she)001:17179: tu ring bas ya thog ring mo dang ma thog
NK117(she)001:17180: ring mo zhes kyang thos so //
NK117(she)001:17181: 'di la ma thog thung ngu zhes 'chad na skyon mang du 'adu'o //
NK117(she)001:17182: de ltar bskal pa gnas pa'i ring la 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:17183: du bsod nams dang bsod nams ma yin pa sogs
NK117(she)001:17184: dge mi dge sna tshogs dang /
NK117(she)001:17187: lo zla zhag dus sogs gzung 'dzin gyis bskyed pa'i 'khrul snang dpag tu med do //
NK117(she)001:17189: 'jug gnas byung gsum ka mi shes pa 'gro ba phal pa rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:17190: gsum ka shes pa byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:17191: 'jug gnas gnyis shes la dbyung ba mi shes pa nyan rang gnyis /
NK117(she)001:17192: shes bzhin du 'jug cing gnas dbyung gnyis mi shes pa 'khor los bsgyur ba rnams so //
NK117(she)001:17193: 'dod pa gzhan du nyan tha sa dang 'khor los bsgyur ba mthun pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17194: de yang byang sems 'khor los bsgyur ba rnams mi shes bzhin du 'jug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17196: gzhan yang gling bzhi'i mi dang lha gnas gsum sogs
NK117(she)001:17197: kyi rnam thar yi ge'i 'jigs nas ma spros kyang
NK117(she)001:17199: de yang gnya' shing 'dzin yan chad nyi zla med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17200: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad gzugs kyi mtha' rdul phra rab dus mtha' skad cig ma /
NK117(she)001:17202: de la rdul phra rab bdun la rdul phran gcig /
NK117(she)001:17203: de nas rim bzhin de ltar 'gyur bar lcags chu
NK117(she)001:17204: ri bong lug glang nyi zer gyi rdul bar 'gyur
NK117(she)001:17205: bartsi'o // nyi zer gyi rdul bdun la sro ma /
NK117(she)001:17206: yang de'i 'gyur brtsis pas shig dang nas 'bru sor mo dbus ma'i tshigs rnams rim pas 'gyur bartsi'o //
NK117(she)001:17207: sor mo nyi shu rtsa bzhi khru gang /
NK117(she)001:17210: grong pa nas rgyang grags lnga 'das par dgon pa /
NK117(she)001:17211: grong pa zad pa'i matha'i brgyang grags phyed 'das par bas matha'o //
NK117(she)001:17212: de yang rgyang grags brgyad la dpag tshad gcig go //
NK117(she)001:17213: gzhan yang sa gzhung 'ga' zhig na bshad pas /
NK117(she)001:17214: rgya nag lugs kyi le bar zhes pa ni /
NK117(she)001:17215: gzhu 'dom brgya phrag gsum dang drug cu la le
NK117(she)001:17216: bar gcig ces rgya nag tu grags pa yin zhes
NK117(she)001:17217: thos so // dus matha'i skad cig ma ni /
NK117(she)001:17218: skyes bu stobs can gyis se gol gcig gtogs pa'i yun la skad cig ma drug cu rtsa bzhi 'da'/
NK117(she)001:17219: de'i cha brgya dang nyi shu la de'i skad cig /
NK117(she)001:17220: de'i skad cig ma drug cu la thang cig /
NK117(she)001:17221: de dgu brgya la zhag cig /
NK117(she)001:17222: thang cig sum cu la yud tsam /
NK117(she)001:17223: yud tsam sum cu la nyin zhag gcig go //
NK117(she)001:17224: des zla ba dang lo sogs rim par gzhal lo //
NK117(she)001:17225: dbyar nyi ma byang bgrod kyi tshe 'phul byed rlung
NK117(she)001:17226: stobs chung la rten byed stobs che bas nyi ma
NK117(she)001:17227: ring zhing drod che ba dang /
NK117(she)001:17228: dgun nyi ma lho bgrod kyi tshe 'phul byed stobs
NK117(she)001:17229: che la rten byed stobs chung bas nyi ma thung
NK117(she)001:17230: zhing / nyi zer la rlung gis reg pa dang rgyang ring bas byed pa bsdoms pas grang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17231: de dag gi lo rgyus dang /
NK117(she)001:17232: gzhan yang lo zla zhag dus sogs kyi rnam bzhag rgyas pa 'grel chen la blta'o //
NK117(she)001:17233: de yang yi ge 'dus pa la ming /
NK117(she)001:17234: ming 'dus pa la tshig tshig 'dus pa la bka' bstan gyi chos grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17235: de lta bu'i kun rdzob kyi chos rnams don la rang bzhin med pa nam mkha' ltar gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17236: 'jig pa'i bar bskal nyi shu ni /
NK117(she)001:17237: bcud 'jig pa la bar bskal bcu dgu /
NK117(she)001:17238: snod 'jig pa la gcig ste nyi shu'o //
NK117(she)001:17239: de yang bcud kyi 'gro ba'i dang po dmyal ba'i
NK117(she)001:17240: 'jig rten dang yi dwags dud 'gro byings gnas bcas
NK117(she)001:17242: dud 'gro kha 'thor ni mtho ris 'jig pa dang lhan cig go //
NK117(she)001:17244: tshe lo bcu pa'i mthar mi gcig gi bsam gtan
NK117(she)001:17245: gnyis pa thob pa'i dga' bde la ched du brjod
NK117(she)001:17246: pa'i sgras 'dzam gling thams cad khyab ste gzhan dag
NK117(she)001:17247: de'i rjes su bslabs pas 'od gsal gyi lhar skyes
NK117(she)001:17249: de ltar gling bzhi gling phran dang bcas pa'i 'gro
NK117(she)001:17250: ba rnams stongs mthar 'dod lha drug kyang bsam gtan
NK117(she)001:17251: gnyis pa thob nas 'od gsal gyi lhar skye'o //
NK117(she)001:17252: gzugs khams kyi 'gro ba rnams kyang de bzhin du
NK117(she)001:17253: gyur nas 'jig rten na sems can gcig kyang med
NK117(she)001:17254: par 'gyur ro // phyi snod ni me chu rlung gsum gyis rim par 'jig pa la /
NK117(she)001:17255: dang po mes 'jig tshe 'jig rten 'dir nyi ma
NK117(she)001:17256: bdun shar ba'am yang na nyi ma gcig po 'di
NK117(she)001:17257: la nyi ma bdun gyi tsha drod 'bar nas chu
NK117(she)001:17258: dang sa'i dngos po ma lus pa tshig nas stongs
NK117(she)001:17259: par 'gyur ro // chus 'jig tshe bsam gtan gnyis
NK117(she)001:17260: pa man chad lan tsh+wa chur zhu ba ltar 'gyur
NK117(she)001:17261: par 'gyur ro // ro // rlung gis 'jig tshe
NK117(she)001:17262: 'og gzhi'i rlung rdo rje rgya gram g.yos te bsam
NK117(she)001:17263: gtan gsum pa man chad gzhig ste stongs par 'gyur
NK117(she)001:17264: par 'gyur ro // ro // ro // de yang
NK117(she)001:17265: bsam gtan dang po na sems dang sems byung gi
NK117(she)001:17266: rtog dpyod me lta bu yod pas mes lan bdun
NK117(she)001:17267: 'jig tshe bsam gtan gnyis pa yan mi 'jig la
NK117(she)001:17269: pa na dga' bde'i nyams chu rgyun lta bu yod
NK117(she)001:17271: gsum pa na dbugs 'byung rngub g.yo 'gul rlung lta bu yod pas rlung gis 'jigs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17272: bsam gtan bzhi pa la 'byung ba'i gnod pa med
NK117(she)001:17273: kyang rang rang gi las kyi 'chi 'pho ba yod
NK117(she)001:17274: pa'o // bsam gtan de dag 'jig tshe de na
NK117(she)001:17275: yod pa'i lha rnams gong ma'i sems rang byung du
NK117(she)001:17276: thob nas dge rgyas la sogs par skye'o //
NK117(she)001:17277: de ltar stongs pa'i yun srid kyang gong ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:17278: slar yang de'i 'og tu mun pa'i bskal pa drug
NK117(she)001:17279: cur chags gnas 'jig stongs kyang de'i grangs 'byung zhing
NK117(she)001:17280: de'i 'og tu bskal pa skar ma lta bu'i sgron
NK117(she)001:17281: bskal la sangs rgyas grangs med pa 'byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17282: de ltar chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhi po mtshungs par
NK117(she)001:17283: bsdoms pa'i bar bskal brgyad cu la bskal pa chen
NK117(she)001:17285: de yang nang bcud sems dang sbyar na kun gzhi nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:17286: ma rig pa kun rtog gi rlung la 'dod chags kyi chu dang /
NK117(she)001:17287: pha ma'i khu khrag las lhun po lta bu'i lus /
NK117(she)001:17289: gling bzhi gling phran lta bu'i skye mched /
NK117(she)001:17291: ri bdun 'khor yug bcas pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad /
NK117(she)001:17292: 'gro drug dang mthun pa'i rtsa 'khor dru ga de
NK117(she)001:17293: dag gi mthun 'gal dang mtshungs pa'i bde sdug sna
NK117(she)001:17294: tshogs 'jig stongs dang mtshungs pa'i na rga 'chi ba
NK117(she)001:17297: lha mi'i ston pa rdo rje'i sku mchog kyang //
NK117(she)001:17298: rtag par blta la gzigs pa yol ba yis //
NK117(she)001:17299: gzhom gzhig bral ba'i sri zhus lhod gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:17300: zhi ba'i dbyings la dgyes pa'i mngon rtogs ngom //
NK117(she)001:17302: lha mi'i ston pa dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams rdo
NK117(she)001:17303: rje'i sku mchog brnyes nas 'gyur ba mi mnga' yang
NK117(she)001:17304: 'gro ba'i snang ngor rtag par blta ba ste sku
NK117(she)001:17305: mya ngan las mi 'da' ba'i gnas la gzigs pa
NK117(she)001:17306: yol te gzhom gzhig dang bral ba'i bsti stangs sri
NK117(she)001:17308: mya ngan las 'das pa la zhi ba'i dbyings la
NK117(she)001:17309: dgyes pa'i mngon rtogs ngom zhes pa ni chos sku'i
NK117(she)001:17312: bsam gtan grub nas bskal par gnas pa'i khur //
NK117(she)001:17313: don med gyur te 'chi ba de mthong nas //
NK117(she)001:17314: tshangs dbang bde 'byung 'khor los sgyur rnams kyang //
NK117(she)001:17315: 'chi bdag bdud las gzur ba'i thabs mi bsam //
NK117(she)001:17317: bsam gtan grub nas bskal chen brgyad khrir 'tsho ba'i
NK117(she)001:17318: khur khyer ba'i lha'i drang srong chen po rnams kyang
NK117(she)001:17319: mthar tshe ring ba don med du gyur nas 'chi
NK117(she)001:17320: ba'i tshul de lta bu mthong nas tshangs pa dang
NK117(she)001:17321: dbang po dang dbang phyug dang khyab 'jug dang 'khor
NK117(she)001:17322: los bsgyur ba sogs 'jig rten na mthu stobs che
NK117(she)001:17323: ba sus kyang 'chi bdag gi bdud las gzur ba'i
NK117(she)001:17324: thabs mi bsam zhing bsams kyang thog tu khel ba
NK117(she)001:17326: mtho ris sman ljongs nyams dgar 'khrigs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:17327: skyes bu'i tshe srog yid la yang nas yang //
NK117(she)001:17328: bgyid pa'i rngon pa lag na be con can //
NK117(she)001:17329: don gnyer gcig pu nyid las gzhan mi sems //
NK117(she)001:17331: mtho ris lha mi'i gnas rtsi thog me tog sogs
NK117(she)001:17332: sngo sman sna tshogs skyes pa'i sman ljongs nyams dga'
NK117(she)001:17333: ba lta bur mthun grogs kyi khyu bsags te 'khrigs
NK117(she)001:17334: pa'i skyes bu rnams kyi tshe srog gcod pa yang
NK117(she)001:17335: nas yang du bgyid pa'i rngon pa gzhan zhig ma
NK117(she)001:17336: yin te lag na be con can gshin rje'i pho
NK117(she)001:17337: nya yin te don du gnyer bya mnar spyod kho
NK117(she)001:17338: na las gzhan mi sems so //
NK117(she)001:17340: sos ka'i tsha bas gdungs pa'i skye bo dag /
NK117(she)001:17341: ston zla gsal ba'i 'od la dga' gyur nas /
NK117(she)001:17342: nyin zhag brgya yis rang gi tshe thal ba'i //
NK117(she)001:17343: gnas la sems nas skrag par gyur pa med //
NK117(she)001:17345: sos ka'i tsha bas gdung ba'i tshe skye bo blun
NK117(she)001:17346: po dag 'di las bsil ba'i ston zla gsal ba'i
NK117(she)001:17347: ngogs su ngal bso chog pa zhig yin na dga'
NK117(she)001:17348: ba la snyam pa ni de bar nyin zhag mang
NK117(she)001:17349: zhig zad pa ltar rang gi tshe yang thal ba'i
NK117(she)001:17350: gnas la sems nas skrag par mi 'gyur ba 'di
NK117(she)001:17351: 'dra ni shin tu tha shal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17353: skyes bus rtsol ba byas la nyag phran myur //
NK117(she)001:17354: de bas sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwags te //
NK117(she)001:17355: de bas mkhar rgyu de bas nyi zla'i rta //
NK117(she)001:17356: kun las mgyogs pa mi yi tshe 'gro yin //
NK117(she)001:17357: 'di ltar gyad stobs chen gyis nyag phran gyi mda'
NK117(she)001:17358: 'phangs pa las ni sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwags
NK117(she)001:17359: mgyogs shing de las kyang mkha' rgyu gzhan la gnod
NK117(she)001:17360: 'tshe rtsoms pa rnams mgyogs de las kyang nyi zla'i
NK117(she)001:17362: de bas kyang shin tu myur ba'i lha mgyogs /
NK117(she)001:17363: de rnams kun las skyes bu'i tshe 'gro ba mgyogs zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17365: dar la babs pa rga ba'i chad pas 'tshe //
NK117(she)001:17366: 'du ba rnal mar gnas pa na bas dkrug /
NK117(she)001:17367: phun tshogs rten cing 'brel 'byung rgud pas 'joms //
NK117(she)001:17368: 'chi bas srog la rgol ba myur por 'ong //
NK117(she)001:17370: 'jig rten ma rungs par byed pa bzhi po 'dis
NK117(she)001:17371: ni 'gro ba kun nyams nyes par byed pa yang
NK117(she)001:17372: rgyal po la gdams pa'i mdo las /
NK117(she)001:17373: rgyal po chen po rga bas ni dar la babs pa 'joms shing 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:17374: na bas ni nad med pa 'joms shing 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:17375: rgud pas ni phun sum 'tshogs pa thams cad 'joms shing 'ong ngo //
NK117(she)001:17377: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'grel pa la sbyar ro //
NK117(she)001:17379: gang tshe gshin rje'i g.yul ngor pham pa de //
NK117(she)001:17380: skyabs dang dpung gnyen bral ba'i g.yang sar rgyug /'tsho ba'i mdangs dang dbang pos rnam par spang //
NK117(she)001:17381: sman dang sman pa dag kyang de la 'bros //
NK117(she)001:17382: bskyod la ngal ba thob pa'i yan lag dang //
NK117(she)001:17383: dbugs ni dbang med mthu yis g.yob cing dar //
NK117(she)001:17384: nye du 'brel bas bskor zhing gdungs na'ang //
NK117(she)001:17385: bshol 'debs lcags kyu'i brtan pa bral bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:17386: de yi dbugs kyi 'gyur ba rta rnga'i lce //
NK117(she)001:17387: 'chi bdag dgra s+t+wa rnon pos gzas gyur pas //
NK117(she)001:17388: mdzes pa spangs pa'i so zho ngom bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:17389: las dbang srid pa'i mun nag stug por 'jug /
NK117(she)001:17391: gang gi tshe gshin rje'i g.yul ngor pham pa zhes
NK117(she)001:17392: lus sems bral ba de nyid mgon skyabs dang dpung
NK117(she)001:17393: gnyen med cing / dper na g.yang sa nyam nga
NK117(she)001:17394: bar rbab rdo rgyug pa bzhin ldog tu med tshe
NK117(she)001:17395: gnyen med cing / / lang tsho'i mdzes pa nyams
NK117(she)001:17396: shing dbang po lnga'i bya byed kyang nub 'tsho byed
NK117(she)001:17397: gzhon nu yod kyang tshe zad pa skad cig kyang
NK117(she)001:17398: gnyen med cing / / bsring mi nus / rkang
NK117(she)001:17399: lag tshul bzhin bskyod pa la rang dbang bral te
NK117(she)001:17400: dbang med du g.yob mthar ngal ba thob ste sgul
NK117(she)001:17401: gnyen med cing / / bsring mi nus / bskyod
NK117(she)001:17402: med cing / dbugs kyang 'jug pa thung zhing rtsub
NK117(she)001:17403: la ldog pa ring zhing g.yo ba drag pas ngar
NK117(she)001:17405: pha ma nye du nye 'brel srog barje nus pa
NK117(she)001:17406: 'dra mo mang pos bskor zhing gdung ba'i smre sngags
NK117(she)001:17408: 'chi ba las bshol 'debs dper na lcags kyus zin
NK117(she)001:17409: pa lta bu'i brtan pa cung zad kyang bral bar
NK117(she)001:17410: 'gyur zhing / 'chi bar nges pa de'i dbugs kyi 'jug ldog gi 'gyu ba rta lnga'i lce ste /
NK117(she)001:17411: rtse mo shin tu phra ba de yang snying rje
NK117(she)001:17412: med pa'i 'chi bdag gi dgra s+t+wa rnon pos bkas
NK117(she)001:17413: pa zhes bcad par gyur tshe /
NK117(she)001:17414: gson dus dga' nas dgod pa ltar ma yin zhing
NK117(she)001:17415: shi tshe kha bsgrad nas mdzes pa spangs pa'i so
NK117(she)001:17416: zho ngom bzhin du mchis kyang gzhan rnams skyugs bro
NK117(she)001:17417: las ma mchis shing shi ba kho nas mi chog
NK117(she)001:17418: par tshe 'dir las bzang ngan gang bsags pa ltar
NK117(she)001:17419: srid pa'i gnas rigs drug po mun nag stug po
NK117(she)001:17421: de ltar 'chi ba mi rtag pa bsgoms pa la don ci mchis snyam na /
NK117(she)001:17422: dang po chos la 'jug pa'i rgyu byed /
NK117(she)001:17423: bar du chos nyams su len pa'i rkyen byed /
NK117(she)001:17424: tha ma 'chi ba 'od gsal nyams su myong ba'i grogs byed de /
NK117(she)001:17425: sngon rgyal po'i khab na khyim bdag dpal skyes bya
NK117(she)001:17426: ba lo brgya lon pa zhig yod pa des ston
NK117(she)001:17427: pa la rab tu byung bar zhus pas gnang ste
NK117(she)001:17428: / moong+gala gyi bu la rab tu byung bcug pas
NK117(she)001:17429: sde snod gsum shes pa zhig byung yang mi rtag
NK117(she)001:17430: pas skyo nas chu la mchongs par chas pa moong+gala
NK117(she)001:17431: bus de las bzlog ste chos bstan pas dgra bcom
NK117(she)001:17433: de'i phyir 'du shes rnams kyi nang nas mchog tu
NK117(she)001:17434: gyur pa ni mi rtag pa bsgom pa yin zhes
NK117(she)001:17435: ston pas gsungs phyir nan tan bskyed par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:17436: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:17437: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:17438: lde mig las le'u gnyis pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:17439: spyi don gsum pa rgyu 'bras rnam par bzhag pa ni /
NK117(she)001:17441: de ltar 'jig rten pha rol son pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:17442: go 'phang gang gi tha gus 'dogs pa'i tshul //
NK117(she)001:17443: dge spyad sdig goms kho nas nye bar len //
NK117(she)001:17444: kun rdzob bden pa bslu ba med pa yin //
NK117(she)001:17446: de ltar shi ba zhes lus po shul du bskyur
NK117(she)001:17447: sems pha rol bar do nas rigs drug gi gnas
NK117(she)001:17448: gang du son pa rnams ni log par blta ba
NK117(she)001:17449: 'dzin pa bzhin du sems mar me shi ba ltar
NK117(she)001:17451: stes dbang gis gnas rigs mtho dman du slebs pa
NK117(she)001:17452: ltar ma yin par rten 'byung bslu med bzhin mtho
NK117(she)001:17453: ris dang ngan song gang gis tha gus 'dogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:17454: tshul tshe 'dir dge ba spyad pa dang sdig la
NK117(she)001:17455: goms pa kho nas yang srid phyi ma nye bar
NK117(she)001:17456: len pa ni kun rdzob sna tshogs chos can gyi
NK117(she)001:17457: bden pa bslu ba med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17459: gang zhig sa bon rnam pa sna tshogs mthu //
NK117(she)001:17460: zhing pa rnams kyi thog la gsal ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:17461: skye ba gzhan du 'dris shing goms byas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:17462: las tshul mang pos 'gro 'di sna tshogs byas //
NK117(she)001:17464: gang zhig sa bon nas btab na 'bras bu yang nas /
NK117(she)001:17465: de bzhin du gro la gro /
NK117(she)001:17466: sran ma bra bo sogs btab par rang rang gi
NK117(she)001:17467: 'bras bu smin pa ltar tshe 'dir dge sdig gi
NK117(she)001:17468: las rnam pa gang byas kyi mthu las phyi ma
NK117(she)001:17469: bde sdug mngon pa zhing pa rnams kyi lo thog
NK117(she)001:17470: la sa bon bzang ngan dang kha mngar sogs snga
NK117(she)001:17471: ma ci bzhin rjes ma yang de ltar gsal ba
NK117(she)001:17472: dang 'dra zhing / de yang skye ba gzhan ma
NK117(she)001:17473: rnams su dge sdig gi las gang la 'dris shing
NK117(she)001:17474: goms par byas pa'i las tshul dge ba las da
NK117(she)001:17475: lta bde skyid phun sum 'tshogs bzhin rnam dkar la
NK117(she)001:17476: dang 'dra zhing / brtson pa dang / sngon ma
NK117(she)001:17477: mi dge ba la goms pas da lta dbul phongs
NK117(she)001:17479: dbang po ma tshang ba sogs sdig pa'i 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:17480: sdug bsngal myong bzhin da dung sdug bsngal gyi rgyu
NK117(she)001:17481: sdig pa mang po la spyod pas 'og nas 'og
NK117(she)001:17482: tu ltung ba sogs kyis 'gro ba 'di dag sna
NK117(she)001:17484: sa bla mthon por gshegs pa'i mkha' lding gi //
NK117(she)001:17485: grib ma re zhig blta bar mi mngon yang //
NK117(she)001:17486: gzugs can nyid dang 'du bral spangs pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:17487: tshogs shing dus la bab tshe lhag par mngon //
NK117(she)001:17489: sa bla ni nam mkha' ste der 'dab gshog gi
NK117(she)001:17490: rtsal gyis bgrod pas bya rgod la sogs pa shin
NK117(she)001:17491: tu mtho ba'i gnas su slebs tshe grib ma yang
NK117(she)001:17492: re zhig blta bar mi mngon yang gzugs can gang
NK117(she)001:17493: yin pa de dang 'du 'bral spangs pa bzhin du
NK117(she)001:17494: tshe 'dir dge sdig gang byas pa lus dang grib
NK117(she)001:17495: ma ltar 'grogs nas bya sa la babs dus rang
NK117(she)001:17496: grib dang lhan gcig tu 'dzoms pa ltar mi dag
NK117(she)001:17497: kyang rigs drug gang du skyes pa la tshogs shing
NK117(she)001:17498: zhes yang srid bzung ba'i dus la babs tshe dge
NK117(she)001:17499: sdig gi 'bras bu lhag par mngon par 'gyur ro
NK117(she)001:17501: bsod nams ma yin bya ba rta gdong mes //
NK117(she)001:17502: mtho ris rgya mtsho'i rlabs kyang skems nus shing //
NK117(she)001:17503: rnam mkhyen gru gzings bshig pa'i dpe dang don //
NK117(she)001:17504: las brgya pa dang rgya chen rol pas bstan //
NK117(she)001:17506: bsod nams ma yin pa'i bya ba ni mi dge
NK117(she)001:17507: ba bcu de'i char gtogs pa'i rigs rnams yin la
NK117(she)001:17509: phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po rab tu barlingasa shing gzhom
NK117(she)001:17510: gzhig dka' ba de yang rta gdong rgod ma kha'i
NK117(she)001:17511: mes bskams par nus bzhin mi dge ba'i stobs kyis
NK117(she)001:17512: rgya mtsho chen po'i dba' rlabs lta bu'i mtho ris
NK117(she)001:17513: kyi bde ba phri nus shing der ma zad rnam
NK117(she)001:17514: mkhyen gyi sar bgrod pa'i gru gzings lta bu'i lus
NK117(she)001:17515: rten yang bshig par 'gyur ba'i dpe dang don gnyis
NK117(she)001:17516: ston pa thams cad mkhyen pas mdo sde las brgya
NK117(she)001:17517: pa dang rgya cher rol pa sogs las bstan pa
NK117(she)001:17518: yang / moong+gala gyi bu kun tu rgyus bkrongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17519: 'phags pa sgur chung bza' btung med pas ltog grir gum pa /
NK117(she)001:17520: dge slong ma ut+pa la'i mdog lhas sbyin gyis bkrongs pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:17521: de yang las mi dge bas mtho ris su skye
NK117(she)001:17522: ba la bar du gcod nus na nyan rang sogs
NK117(she)001:17523: kyi sa thob pa la nges par bar du gcod
NK117(she)001:17526: mnar la shin tu brtul phod ngan song gis //
NK117(she)001:17527: dge bcu'i dpung pa btsan pa'i dpa' bo'i yul //
NK117(she)001:17528: g.yul gyi phru mas btab pa ma mchis te //
NK117(she)001:17529: dam bca' nyams pa mtha' dag khyod dbang song //
NK117(she)001:17530: la la'i tshul khrims la la'i tshe dang srog /
NK117(she)001:17531: la la'i dka' thub la la'i chos dang nor //
NK117(she)001:17532: la la'i ngo tsha la la'i khrel yod rnams //
NK117(she)001:17533: sdig pa'i ched du gtong ba shin tu mang //
NK117(she)001:17535: mnar ba'i las la shin tu brtul phod pa zhes
NK117(she)001:17536: dpa' ba'i stobs dang ldan pa ni ngan song gsum
NK117(she)001:17537: po yin kyang / dge ba bcu'i dmag dpung mang
NK117(she)001:17538: zhing btsan pa ni dpa' bos bzung ba'i yul du
NK117(she)001:17539: po yin kyang / / ngan 'gro'i g.yul gyi phru
NK117(she)001:17540: ma ste dmag sgar btab pa cang ma mchis mod
NK117(she)001:17541: po yin kyang / / de / so thar dang
NK117(she)001:17542: byang sems dang sngags kyi dam sdom nyams pa mtha'
NK117(she)001:17543: dag khyod ces ngan song ba'i dbang du gyur pa'o
NK117(she)001:17544: po yin kyang / / de / // de yang
NK117(she)001:17545: sngon dam bca' nyams pa la skyon ji ltar byung
NK117(she)001:17546: po yin kyang / / de / // tshul ni
NK117(she)001:17547: / khyim du gnas pa'i ched du bslab pa gtong
NK117(she)001:17548: ba sngon gyi rgyal rigs rin chen grags dang da
NK117(she)001:17549: lta'i skya sar 'bab pa la dga' ba'i btsun gzugs
NK117(she)001:17551: zhe sdang gi dbang gis rang srog 'dor ba mu stegs pa sam ga +aa tsar+ya lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:17552: phrag dog gis dka' thub gtong ba dge slong lhas sbyin lta bu /
NK117(she)001:17553: 'dod chags kyis ngo tsha gtong ba tshong dpon gyi bu mo lta bu /
NK117(she)001:17554: rang 'dod kyis khrel yod gtong ba rgyal po bde spyod kyi bu lta bu /
NK117(she)001:17555: da lta yang 'di mtshungs shin tu mang ba ni smos ma dgos so //
NK117(she)001:17556: mdor na 'jig rten na sdig pa'i phyogs su lus
NK117(she)001:17557: srog kyang 'dor phod la dge ba'i phyogs su sa
NK117(she)001:17558: dang chu yang phangs pa'i skyon gyis ngan song ni
NK117(she)001:17559: sa chen po'i rdul tsam dang /
NK117(she)001:17560: mtho ris ni sen mo'i steng gi rdul tsam gyi
NK117(she)001:17561: khyad par la dpyad nas dge sgrub sdig spang la
NK117(she)001:17563: gang phyir yon gnas nye du 'khor 'bangs dang //
NK117(she)001:17564: yul khams bsrung ba'i slad du stobs chen gyi //
NK117(she)001:17565: sdig pa'i gnyis 'thung dkris pa btang na'ang //
NK117(she)001:17566: rnam smin bgo bsha' bya ru med pa yin //
NK117(she)001:17568: de la sdig pa'i mtshan nyid ni rnam smin gtos
NK117(she)001:17569: che ba glang po che'i gzugs brnyan dang spong sems
NK117(she)001:17570: de nyid thag pas dkris pa dang btang ba ni
NK117(she)001:17571: nyes pa bag med du spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17572: de'ang rang gzhan gang gi ched du sdig pa byas
NK117(she)001:17573: kyang byed pa po kho na las rnam smin bgo
NK117(she)001:17575: khyad par yon gnas kyi dam pa dkon mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:17576: ni 'gro ba kun la bu gcig po'i ma ltar
NK117(she)001:17577: brtse bar nges na srog chags bsad nas dmar ston
NK117(she)001:17578: byed pa dang / gzhan gyi longs spyod phrogs nas
NK117(she)001:17579: mchod sbyin byed pa sogs ni nyes pa kho na'i
NK117(she)001:17580: rgyu las ci yang med de /
NK117(she)001:17581: 'tshe ba chos su smra ba kla klo'i grub mtha' yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:17582: de bzhin du rang gi gnyen nye du'i ched du sdig pa byas pa'ang /
NK117(she)001:17583: moong+gala mas khyim thab dang bu'i ched du ser sna
NK117(she)001:17584: sogs sdig pa mang du byas pas mo rang ngan
NK117(she)001:17585: song dang / bus dgra bcom pa thob /
NK117(she)001:17586: khyo pho tshangs pa'i gnas su skyes so //
NK117(she)001:17587: gzhan yang 'khor 'bangs dang yul khams bsrung ba'i slad
NK117(she)001:17588: du g.yul 'gyed pa sogs 'khrug rtsod chen po byed
NK117(she)001:17589: pa yang / byed pa po byang chub sems dpa'i
NK117(she)001:17590: thabs dang ldan pa ma gtogs gzhan phan du mi
NK117(she)001:17591: pa yang / 'gyur zhing / rang bsrung kho na yin pas sdig che'o //
NK117(she)001:17592: sdig pa'i las de'i mod la mtshon bzhin du gcod
NK117(she)001:17593: par mi byed kyang 'chi ba'i dus dang shi ba'i
NK117(she)001:17597: rnyed la brkam zhing bde ba 'ba' zhig sred //
NK117(she)001:17598: snyan pa lhur len bstod na khengs 'gyur la //
NK117(she)001:17599: gang las gcig shos bzhi yis sma bab pa'i //
NK117(she)001:17600: byis pa 'di dag 'jig rten chos kyis bslus //
NK117(she)001:17602: 'di ltar dam pa'i chos dang 'gal ba'i 'jig rten chos brgyad ni /
NK117(she)001:17603: zas nor rnyed 'tshol la re zhing brkam /
NK117(she)001:17606: gzhan gyis bstod na khengs dregs skye ste chos bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:17607: rnyed tshol ma byung na zhum pa dang mi bde ba byung na sdug bsngal dang /
NK117(she)001:17608: mi snyan pa thos na 'gyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17609: smad pa thos na khong khro langs pa ste bzhi
NK117(she)001:17610: po bsdoms pa'i brgyad po 'dis byis pa rnams bslu
NK117(she)001:17611: bar nges pas blang dor ma nor ba gal che'o
NK117(she)001:17612: // don bsdu na 'jig rten chos brgyad las gyur
NK117(she)001:17613: pa'i rnam par rtog pa rnyed pa la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:17614: sngon ma bzhi la dga' ba dang /
NK117(she)001:17615: ma rnyed pa la sogs te rjes ma bzhi la mi dga' ba med par mgo snyoms dgos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17617: rigs gzugs dbang thang la sogs 'phang bstod cing //
NK117(she)001:17618: snyom las 'phye bo'i phag tu yib pa dang //
NK117(she)001:17619: mngon pa'i nga rgyal ma rungs slong ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:17620: dka' thub dpal la sdang ba'i srin por 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:17621: brkam chags sems kyi nus pa brtan po yis //
NK117(she)001:17622: zil gyis non pa'i g.yo sgyu'i 'khri shing gis //
NK117(she)001:17623: gzhan dag rmongs byas bdag nyid bsrung na yang //
NK117(she)001:17624: gnod chen de ni rang gi khong du zhugs /
NK117(she)001:17630: lang tsho sogs kyis rgyags pa zhes nga rgyal dang
NK117(she)001:17631: khengs dregs bsdoms pas spyi ming yin zhing skyon de
NK117(she)001:17632: dag gis rang mgo rang gis bstod nas thos bsam
NK117(she)001:17633: sgom gsum la brtson 'grus byed rgyu phar zhog /
NK117(she)001:17634: za nyal gnyid gsum sogs snyoms las dang le lo
NK117(she)001:17635: zhes pa sgo gsum gnad du bsnun pas sun te
NK117(she)001:17636: tshogs drug bag yangs su lhod cing ltar snang gi
NK117(she)001:17637: chos la 'jug pa ni 'phye bo ste mi gang
NK117(she)001:17638: rkang lag zha ba'i phag tu yib pa lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:17639: 'grul bgrod sogs las gang la'ang 'jug mi 'dod pa
NK117(she)001:17640: bzhin gong gsal gyi rgyags pas lkog gyur tsam ma
NK117(she)001:17641: yin zhing mngon sum gyi nga rgyal gzhan la khong
NK117(she)001:17642: 'khrug ma rungs pa slong bar byed pa rnams ni
NK117(she)001:17643: dam sdom la dka' thub ste de'i mthun phyogs kyi
NK117(she)001:17644: dpal la ldang ba'i srin po ni chags sdang gnyis
NK117(she)001:17645: dang brkam pa ni rang gi zas nor dam du
NK117(she)001:17646: 'dzin pa dang / chags pa ni gzhan gyi lus
NK117(she)001:17647: longs spyod la sred pa sogs kyis rnam par g.yengs
NK117(she)001:17648: bzhin bsam spyod drang por mi gnas pa la g.yo
NK117(she)001:17649: 'dzin pa dang / ba dang / gzhan mgo bskor ba'i thabs byed pa la sgyu zhes so //
NK117(she)001:17650: de lta bu'i 'jig rten gyi chos bcu gsum pos
NK117(she)001:17651: bdag bsrungs shing gzhan rmongs par byed nus kyang dug
NK117(she)001:17652: ldan gyi zas khong du song ba dang 'dra bas
NK117(she)001:17653: spang bar bya ba kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:17655: 'khor bar 'du byed dkar nag las 'bras gnyis //
NK117(she)001:17656: sa bon nyung ngu las kyang 'bras bu'i gzugs //
NK117(she)001:17657: sbom por bskyed pa mi dbang nga las nu //
NK117(she)001:17658: sran rdog bdun las 'khor los sgyur ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:17659: gang zhig sa bon yungs 'bru tsam pa'i shing //
NK117(she)001:17660: a sho ta yi 'bras bu lo dus su //
NK117(she)001:17661: yal ga re la'ang dpag tshad tsam 'phel bas //
NK117(she)001:17662: dge sdig gzugs brnyan 'phel ba'i dper mi phod //
NK117(she)001:17664: 'di ltar 'khor ba mtho dman du 'du bar byed
NK117(she)001:17665: pa po dkar nag gi las kyi 'bras bu gnyis
NK117(she)001:17667: dge sdig gi sa bon nyung ngu tsam las kyang
NK117(she)001:17668: bde sdug gi 'bras bu'i gzugs sbom por bskyed du
NK117(she)001:17669: yod de / sngon gyi tshe mi dbang nga las
NK117(she)001:17670: nu zhes pa'i skye ba sngon ma byis pa'i tshe
NK117(she)001:17671: sangs rgyas rnam gzigs kyi sku la sran ma spar
NK117(she)001:17672: gang gtor bas rdog po bzhi lhung bzed du song
NK117(she)001:17673: yod de / / gnyis thugs kar phog pas gser gyi 'khor los bsgyur rgyal du gyur cing /
NK117(she)001:17674: rim pas rgyal chen bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:17675: sum cu rtsa gsum du lha'i dbang po dang stan gcig tu sdod pa'i mthu thob ltar /
NK117(she)001:17676: gang zhig sa bon yungs 'bru tsam las med kyang
NK117(she)001:17677: 'phel ka shin tu che ba'i shing a sho ta'i
NK117(she)001:17678: 'bras bu shing gzhan las 'phel stobs che bas lo
NK117(she)001:17679: gcig tsam lon pa'i dus su yal ga re la'ang
NK117(she)001:17680: dpag tshad tsam re 'phel ba bas kyang dge sdig
NK117(she)001:17681: gi gzugs brnyan 'phel ba'i stobs che bas dper mi
NK117(she)001:17682: phod ces pa'o // sh+aa ri'i bus sngon tshe rang
NK117(she)001:17683: sangs rgyas la ras yug dang khab skud phul bas
NK117(she)001:17684: mkhyen rab rlabs che ba sogs shes rab can gyi
NK117(she)001:17685: mchog tu gyur pa sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:17686: mdor na sangs rgyas la gus sems kyis me tog
NK117(she)001:17687: gcig nam mkhar gtor na 'bras bu chud mi za
NK117(she)001:17688: bar gsungs so // mi dge ba'i 'bras bu yang
NK117(she)001:17689: de ltar smin par nges pas dge sdig gi spang
NK117(she)001:17690: blang mi 'dzol ba zhig gnad dam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17692: gang la byed po ma mchis rang bzhin min //
NK117(she)001:17693: dkar nag chos kyis btsos pa'i kun slong gis //
NK117(she)001:17694: las dang de yi 'bras bu mthu chen byas //
NK117(she)001:17695: sbyor rjes gnyis dang mi ldan nus pa chung //
NK117(she)001:17697: 'di ltar las dge sdig gi lci yang mi dngos
NK117(she)001:17698: gzhi dge sdig gang yin chung ngu las ma byas
NK117(she)001:17699: kyang sbyor ba'i dus bsam pa'i las kyis dge sdig
NK117(she)001:17700: gi bya ba dran zhing sems pa'i las kyis de
NK117(she)001:17701: la nan tan du 'jug pa ma yin bzhin las
NK117(she)001:17702: dkar nag gang yin spyod cing rjes la dge bar
NK117(she)001:17703: dga' spro / sdig la 'gyod sems bskyed na dge ba stobs che zhing /
NK117(she)001:17704: sdig pa mthu chung ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:17705: de'i phyir na gang la zhes 'gro ba su yang
NK117(she)001:17706: tshe phyi ma'i dus bde sdug gi don la byed
NK117(she)001:17707: pa po ma mchis bzhin du rang bzhin gyis de
NK117(she)001:17709: las dkar nag gi tshos kyis btsos pa'i kun slong
NK117(she)001:17710: dag ma dag gis las dge sdig gang yin dang
NK117(she)001:17711: de'i 'bras bu mthu chen po byas pa yin zhes
NK117(she)001:17712: bstan nas / dngos gzhi dge sdig gang rung spyad
NK117(she)001:17713: kyang sbyor rjes gnyis dang mi ldan na nus pa
NK117(she)001:17714: chung zhes gong du bkral ba ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:17715: spyir nang pa'i chos thams cad kyi mdo don yang
NK117(she)001:17716: dag pa'i lta ba zhes 'jig rten pha rol yod
NK117(she)001:17717: par nges kyang de ltar du mi 'dod cing rgyu
NK117(she)001:17718: 'bras la yid mi ches pas log par lta ba
NK117(she)001:17719: des rnam smin phyin ci log tu 'byung ste phyi
NK117(she)001:17720: rol pa la la bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:17721: de yang sngon dge slong zhig gis khyim bdag gcig
NK117(she)001:17722: la bza' btung bslangs pas khyim bdag gis dgra bcom
NK117(she)001:17723: pa yin na 'dren min na mi ster byas pas
NK117(she)001:17724: dgra bcom min zer nas song ba la 'dod pa
NK117(she)001:17725: chung lugs la dgra bcom par nges snyam nas chos
NK117(she)001:17726: ston drangs pas dgra bcom la drangs pa'i bsod nams
NK117(she)001:17727: thob pas mtshon kun slong bzang ngan gyi 'phen byed
NK117(she)001:17728: las dge sdig stobs che chung gi rjes su 'gro
NK117(she)001:17731: rtsa ba sman du mchis na myu gu'ang sman //
NK117(she)001:17732: rtsa ba dug yin myu gu smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:17733: bsam pa dge dang mi dge'i 'phen byed las //
NK117(she)001:17734: dge sdig gzugs brnyan che chung rjes mi 'gro //
NK117(she)001:17736: dper na sa bon sman btab na de'i rtsa ba
NK117(she)001:17737: dang myu gu lo 'bras kun sman yin la rtsa
NK117(she)001:17738: ba dug yin na myu gu sogs dug yin pa
NK117(she)001:17739: ma smos kyang los shes te bshad ci la dgos
NK117(she)001:17740: zhes 'grel nas / las dkar nag gang yin kyang
NK117(she)001:17741: bsam pa dge mi dge kho na'i 'phen byed las
NK117(she)001:17742: dge sdig gang yin kyang gzugs brnyan dang che chung
NK117(she)001:17743: gi rjes su mi 'gro zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17744: de yang sngon dus lam kha zhig na sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:17745: kyi sku gzugs gcig char pas 'jig tu nyen pa
NK117(she)001:17746: la mi zhig gis rang gi lham khrad kyis char
NK117(she)001:17747: skyob byas nas bkab pa mi gzhan zhig gis sku
NK117(she)001:17748: la nongs kyi dogs nas bsal bas gnyis ka rgyal
NK117(she)001:17751: 'di ltar rtag dang mngon zhen gnyen po med //
NK117(she)001:17752: yon tan gtso ldan gzhi las byung ba'i las //
NK117(she)001:17753: rnam pa lnga po dge sdig lci yang gi //
NK117(she)001:17754: nye bar len pa'i rnam rig lags par gsungs //
NK117(she)001:17756: de la rtag pa ste sdig pa chung ngu zhig
NK117(she)001:17757: yin kyang yun ring por sems la brnag pa'i mthar
NK117(she)001:17758: srog gcod sogs sdig la spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17759: mngon par zhen pa ni yid la brnag pa'i sdig
NK117(she)001:17760: pa de ma 'grub bar du sems rnal du mi
NK117(she)001:17761: phebs shing de kho na la 'bad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17762: gnyen po med pa ni chags sdang gi sems gang
NK117(she)001:17763: skyes pa de la cung zad tsam yang mi 'gyod
NK117(she)001:17764: cing de nyid 'grub pa'i thabs la brtson pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17765: gzhi la gnyis te yon tan gtso ldan ni /
NK117(she)001:17766: dkon mchog gsum dang skye ba gcig gis thogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:17767: byang sems dang gang zag nyon mongs las grol ba
NK117(she)001:17768: dang / dge sgrub sdig spang la snying nas brtson pa thams cad do //
NK117(she)001:17769: gzhi phan 'dogs kyi cha nas pha ma dang /
NK117(she)001:17770: lugs bzung gnyis ka'i sgo nas drin che ba rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:17771: mgon med skyabs med du gyur pa'i khas nyen dbul phongs dang dgra 'dres mnar ba la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17772: rnam pa lnga po de ni dge mi dge gnyis
NK117(she)001:17773: ka'i 'jug ldog 'phyug mi rung ba'i las gal chen
NK117(she)001:17776: kun gyi rten byed kun gzhi lung ma bstan //
NK117(she)001:17777: de las yid dang yul lnga'i shes pa langs //
NK117(she)001:17778: kun la khyab byed ma rig gdon chen gyis //
NK117(she)001:17779: nyon mongs gsum bzung 'khor bar mtho dman byas //
NK117(she)001:17781: 'di ltar kun gzhi ni sems can thams cad kyi
NK117(she)001:17782: sems kyi ngo bo ma rig pa gti mug gi
NK117(she)001:17783: sa pa nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi
NK117(she)001:17784: mched yul dge sdig gi rtog tshogs gang yang ma
NK117(she)001:17785: shar ba'i lung ma bstan de ka'o //
NK117(she)001:17786: de las rnam par rig byed kyi sems kun gzhi'i
NK117(she)001:17787: rnam shes kun rdzob kyi chos thams cad kyi 'char
NK117(she)001:17788: yul du gyur kyang phyir ma 'phros la 'phro la
NK117(she)001:17789: khad pa 'di ni deng dus phra ba zhes la
NK117(she)001:17791: de las der 'dzin gyi blo ngos 'dzin rgyu yod
NK117(she)001:17792: tsam shar nas rtog gzhi phra ba la phra mo'i
NK117(she)001:17793: dpyad pa cung zad res yod res med byed pa
NK117(she)001:17794: ni nga med la nga yir 'dzin pa'i yid do
NK117(she)001:17795: // de las dug lnga sogs chags sdang gi sems
NK117(she)001:17796: zhes sngon ma 'char grab byed pa dang shar nas
NK117(she)001:17797: dgag sgrub kyi rnam par shar ba ni nyon mongs
NK117(she)001:17799: de la'ang blang dor gyi 'jug ldog byed pa thams cad yid kyi rnam shes so //
NK117(she)001:17800: mdor na kun gzhi rtog med ni rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17801: de las nga yir 'dzin pa ni lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17802: de las yid dang nyon mongs pa can gyi yid
NK117(she)001:17803: kyis bskyed nas phyi nang gi gzung 'dzin gyi rnam
NK117(she)001:17804: par shar ba thams cad kun brtag gi ma rig
NK117(she)001:17805: pa yin no // de yang dbang po'i sgo lnga
NK117(she)001:17806: la brten nas yul lnga la 'jug pa'i shes pa
NK117(she)001:17807: sngon ma las phyi ma'i tshogs skye zhing mched pas
NK117(she)001:17809: 'di ltar dbang po lnga dang shes pa lnga dang
NK117(she)001:17810: yul lnga bcas 'dus te phan tshun reg pa la
NK117(she)001:17811: 'dus te reg pa dang de las chags sdang sogs
NK117(she)001:17812: skyes pa la rkyen gyis tshor ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17813: de yang nang du yid kyi dbang po ni phyi
NK117(she)001:17814: rol sgo lnga'i rnam shes las shar ba'i chags sdang
NK117(she)001:17815: re dogs spang blang gnyis 'dzin thams cad kyi bdag
NK117(she)001:17816: po byed cing / nang du lkog gyur gyi rtog
NK117(she)001:17817: tshogs thams cad kyi byung gnas 'gro gsum gyi rten
NK117(she)001:17818: po byed cing / byed cing / de'i brten yul lam gzhi de sems zhes 'dod la /
NK117(she)001:17819: phyi nang gi rtog tshogs thams cad so so rang
NK117(she)001:17820: rang gi rnam pa ji bzhin par shes pa la
NK117(she)001:17822: 'on kyang mdo rgyud dang grub mtha' so so'i 'dod gzhung yod kyang 'dir de tsam mo //
NK117(she)001:17823: mdor bsdu na rnam par shes bya'i yul /
NK117(she)001:17825: yid la byed pa gsum las dug gsum gyi kun
NK117(she)001:17826: slong shar nas las bsags pa thams cad mi dge
NK117(she)001:17827: ba'o // de las log nas byams snying rje sogs kyis las bsags pa thams cad dge ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17828: de'ang dam pa gsum gyis zin pa'i rnam dkar gyi
NK117(she)001:17829: las ci tsam bsags kyang lha mi'i bde 'bras bskyed
NK117(she)001:17830: nas zad par 'gyur bas na bsod nams cha mthun
NK117(she)001:17831: gyi dge ba'o // de las log nas gong ma
NK117(she)001:17832: gsum gyis zin pa la thar pa cha mthun te
NK117(she)001:17834: de gnyis ka dang 'gal ba'i dug gsum gyi kun
NK117(she)001:17835: slong dang 'dres pa'i dge bas kyang ngan song sogs
NK117(she)001:17836: sdug bsngal gyi rgyu byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17838: ji ltar me ni 'bar zhing bsreg pa yi //
NK117(she)001:17839: gnyen por chas pa chu las gzhan med na //
NK117(she)001:17840: dkon mchog gsum po bslus shing spangs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:17841: sdig chen de la do zla rnyed pa min //
NK117(she)001:17843: 'di ltar me ni cher 'bar zhing gang 'phrad bsreg
NK117(she)001:17844: par byed pa yang gzhil zhing gsod pa'i gnyen po
NK117(she)001:17845: chu las gzhan med pa ltar /
NK117(she)001:17846: sdig pa'i las dpag med bsags kyang dkon mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:17847: la skyabs su gsol nas bshags pa phul na bshags
NK117(she)001:17848: su yod kyang / sku gsung thugs rten bshig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17849: gsung rab sogs btsongs pa'i bslus zos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17850: dkor bag med la 'bags kyang dkor sbyong ma byas
NK117(she)001:17851: pa mchog gsum rin po cher brnyas gshungs kyi sgo
NK117(she)001:17852: nas smod skur btab pa sogs ni bshags yul spangs
NK117(she)001:17854: me gsod pa'i thabs la chu basngagasa kyang chu mer
NK117(she)001:17855: gyur na de gsod thabs bral bzhin lags pas rang
NK117(she)001:17856: nyid legs su 'dod pa dag mkhas rloms kyi sgo
NK117(she)001:17857: nas mchog gsum ma spongs shig /
NK117(she)001:17858: de yang skye bo ma brtags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17859: bab col du 'jug pa rnams ni dkon mchog gi
NK117(she)001:17860: dkor la ci mi snyam du spyod pa sogs ni
NK117(she)001:17861: mtshams med lnga dang mnyam par gsungs mod /
NK117(she)001:17862: de ni sku gsung thugs rten gyi dang bla ma'i
NK117(she)001:17863: rdzas dang yo byad la rku 'phrog sogs byas pa
NK117(she)001:17864: sogs la 'jug pa las gzhan gson gshin gyi ched
NK117(she)001:17865: du bla ma dang dge 'dun pa la 'bul ba
NK117(she)001:17866: byas pa la gsungs pa min te /
NK117(she)001:17867: de ltar na tshogs bsag yul dben pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:17869: de las gzhan du 'gro ba'i kun rtog la //
NK117(she)001:17870: rang bzhin 'brel gyur sems dang sems byung las //
NK117(she)001:17871: mtha' dag blo yis thug pa ma mchis kyang //
NK117(she)001:17872: lus ngag yid la rten dang brten pa can //
NK117(she)001:17873: spang bya'i rgyu 'bras rnam pa bcur gnas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:17874: zhes pa ni gong du bshad pa'i dbang po'i sgo
NK117(she)001:17875: lnga dang yid shes tsam gyis las mi gsog kyang
NK117(she)001:17876: nyon yid kyis kun gzhi'i steng du las gsog pa'i
NK117(she)001:17877: sems rtog rag pa'i tshor ba ni gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:17878: yul yid du 'ong ba la bde ba /
NK117(she)001:17880: bar ma la btang snyoms so //
NK117(she)001:17882: yul la 'jug pa rgya che ba chung ba bar ma'o //
NK117(she)001:17883: de las kyang 'du byed la sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste /
NK117(she)001:17884: ldan pa'i 'du byed kun tu 'gro ba lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:17890: yul so sor nges pa lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:17908: rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa drug ni /
NK117(she)001:17915: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shu ni /
NK117(she)001:17938: dpyod pa bzhi ni gzhan du 'gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17939: nyon mongs pa'i rtog tshogs brgyad khri bzhi stong blos thug pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:17940: de rnams mdor bsdus te 'chad na /
NK117(she)001:17942: lus kyi gsum ni srog gcod ma byin blang //
NK117(she)001:17943: log par g.yem las dang po srog gcod ni //
NK117(she)001:17944: 'du shes ma 'khrul gzhan srog bsam bzhin gcod //
NK117(she)001:17945: phyogs mthun brdeg btsog la sogs 'tshe ba bgyid //
NK117(she)001:17946: ma byin blang ba gzhan nor shes bzhin brku //
NK117(she)001:17947: phyogs mthun g.yo dang sgyu yis len pa dang //
NK117(she)001:17948: 'dod log gla rngan thob la reg pa sprod //
NK117(she)001:17949: phyogs mthun bgrod bya ma yin 'khrig pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:17950: zhes pa ni de la srog gcod kyi nyes pa la yan lag lnga ste /
NK117(she)001:17951: gzhi sems can yin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17952: yin pa la sems can du 'du shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17953: de gsod par bsam pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17954: sbyor ba gsod grab byas 'phral du shi ba'i dus gzhan du shi ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17955: phyogs mthun ni gsod sems med bzhin du spyod lam ma gzo ba'i rkyen gyis shi ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17956: ma byin blang la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:17957: zas nor gang yin gzhan gyi yin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17958: yin par rang gis shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17959: shes bzhin du brku bar bsam pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17960: brkus nas rang gi thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17961: phyogs mthun ni nyo tshong sogs la mgo g.yog btang ba g.yo dang /
NK117(she)001:17962: bre log srang log 'jug pa lta bu sgyu dang /
NK117(she)001:17963: dbang shed kyis 'phrog pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:17964: 'dod log la rnam pa bdun te /
NK117(she)001:17965: rang gi khu ba 'byin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17966: rang gi chung ma yin kyang nyin par dang /
NK117(she)001:17967: bsnyen gnas la sdod skabs dang /
NK117(she)001:17968: na ba sbrum pa mya ngan can /
NK117(she)001:17970: bang ma sangs pa dag go //
NK117(she)001:17971: gnas ma yin pa pha ma /
NK117(she)001:17972: bla ma dang rten gsum gyi drung du'o //
NK117(she)001:17973: yan lag ma yin pa ni /
NK117(she)001:17974: kha dang gshang lam sogs mo dbang las gzhan pa thams cad do //
NK117(she)001:17975: gzhan yang sdom ldan ma'i sdom pa nyams rkyen byas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:17978: ming po sogs pha ming phyogs dang /
NK117(she)001:17979: gyos sgyug sogs gzhan phyogs nas bsrung ba smad 'tshong ma lta bu'ang gzhan gyis gla rngan byin zin /
NK117(she)001:17980: bud med min kyang skyes pa dang dud 'gro sogs la spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:17982: yul dus sogs de dang der 'du shes pa /
NK117(she)001:17984: tshor ba nyams su myang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:17986: ngag gi bzhi ni rdzun smras gzhan dag 'khrul //
NK117(she)001:17987: phyogs mthun 'du shes bslad nas gzhan sems bslu //
NK117(she)001:17988: phra ma mthun nam btang snyoms gnas pa 'dral //
NK117(she)001:17989: phyogs mthun skyon tshig gzhan bzlos 'khon du 'chos //
NK117(she)001:17990: ngag 'khyal bre mo'i gtam las chags sdang bskyed //
NK117(she)001:17991: phyogs mthun dmag dang chom rkun 'brel med gtam //
NK117(she)001:17992: chig rtsub pha rol snying la 'bigs pa ste //
NK117(she)001:17993: phyogs mthun gzhan yid mi bde'i rkyen dang sprod //
NK117(she)001:17994: ces pa ni de yang rdzun dngos ni yan lag bzhis rdzogs te smra ba'i gzhi ma nor ba /
NK117(she)001:17995: gzhan bslu ba'i bsam pa yid la bzhag nas mi bden par smras pa /
NK117(she)001:17997: gzhan yang the tshom za ba'i rigs la ma nges
NK117(she)001:17998: bzhin du kha tshon gcod pa yang rdzun yin par
NK117(she)001:17999: gsungs so // bla ma dag rang bsam sbyor gang
NK117(she)001:18000: yang tha mal las ma 'phags bzhin du yon tan
NK117(she)001:18001: dang mngon shes sogs yod tshul gyis lkog gyur ston
NK117(she)001:18002: rloms sogs ni rdzun rlabs chen po mi chos bla
NK117(she)001:18004: gzhan la gnod min gyis rdzun che chung du dbye tshul yang shes dgos so //
NK117(she)001:18005: phra ma ni yan lag gsum gyis rdzogs te /
NK117(she)001:18006: dbye gzhi mthun nam btang snyoms pa 'dral ba /
NK117(she)001:18007: dbyen sbyor gyi tshig smras pa /
NK117(she)001:18009: de la'ang btsan phra ni ngos dbyen /
NK117(she)001:18011: gzhogs phra ni dbye gzhi dga' bar byas nas dbyen 'jug pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18012: ngag 'khyal ba ni yan lag gnyis te chos min gyi tshig brjod par 'dod pa dang smra ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18013: 'di ltar chags sdang gi sems kyis don dang mi
NK117(she)001:18014: ldan pa'i gtam brjod pa kun ngag 'khyal du bsdu'o
NK117(she)001:18015: // tshig rtsub ni yan lag gsum gyis rdzogs te /
NK117(she)001:18016: gzhi brjod yul gyi mi de la ched du dmigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18017: sbyor ba de'i skyon tshig sogs brjod pa /
NK117(she)001:18018: mthar thug mi dga' bar byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18019: dbye na ngor rtsub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18022: yid kyi gsum las dang po brnab sems ni //
NK117(she)001:18023: gzhan 'byor dpal la barngamasa shing bdag gir byed //
NK117(she)001:18024: phyogs mthun pha rol rdzas la brkam zhing myang //
NK117(she)001:18025: gnod sems gzhan la khong 'khrugs 'tshe ba slong //
NK117(she)001:18026: phyogs mthun phan pas 'brel la 'du 'bral bsgom //
NK117(she)001:18027: log lta rgyu 'bras med dang rtag chad blta //
NK117(she)001:18028: phyogs mthun med la sgro 'dogs yod la bskur //
NK117(she)001:18029: zhes pa ni brnab sems ni yan lag gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:18030: gzhi brnab rgyu'i dngos rdzas gzhan gyi yin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18031: de la brnab sems bskyed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18032: don ni gzhan gyi 'byor pa longs spyod rnams bdag
NK117(she)001:18033: gi yin na dang thob na snyam nas rloms pa
NK117(she)001:18034: byed pa'o // gnod sems ni yan lag gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:18035: gzhi gnod pa byed yul shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18036: de la gnod sems skyes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18037: de yang chos bzhi dang ldan pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:18038: gnod byed mnar 'dod zhe sdang gi sems /
NK117(she)001:18039: 'khon 'dzin mi brjod pa khong khro'i sems /
NK117(she)001:18040: de la bzod pa bral ba nga rgyal gyi sems /
NK117(she)001:18041: de nyid bsad na dang brdeg na snyam pa 'khu ba'i sems /
NK117(she)001:18042: ngo tsha dang nyes dmigs la cang mi sems pa gti mug gi sems so //
NK117(she)001:18043: log lta ni yan lag gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:18044: gzhi rgyu 'bras bslu med la bsam pa phyin ci
NK117(she)001:18045: log dge sdig gnyis la bde sdug gi 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:18048: kun la 'bras bu bzhi bzhir smin pa'i tshul //
NK117(she)001:18049: rnam smin rgyu mthun dbang dang byed pa las //
NK117(she)001:18053: dbang ngam bdag po'i 'bras bu dang gsum /
NK117(she)001:18056: rnam smin 'bras bu chos lnga ldan nam min //
NK117(she)001:18057: kun slong gsum gyi chung ngus dud 'gro dang //
NK117(she)001:18058: 'bring gis yi dwags chen pos dmyal bar 'phen //
NK117(she)001:18059: 'di ltar rnam smin gyi 'bras bu la chos lnga
NK117(she)001:18060: ldan ni zhes pa'i dug gsum gang rung gis kun
NK117(she)001:18062: rjes su spyod pa'i sbyor ba dang /
NK117(she)001:18063: sbyor gzhi bsam pa de nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:18064: sbyor 'bras dngos gzhi nyid spyad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18065: mjug rjes su yi rang ba ste chos lnga po
NK117(she)001:18066: de tshang na mi dge ba'i las de mthar phyin
NK117(she)001:18067: pa'o // de yang mi dge ba bcu po de chung ngu spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18068: gti mug kho nas byas na dud 'gro dang /
NK117(she)001:18070: 'dod chags kyi sgo nas byas na yi dwags /
NK117(she)001:18072: zhe sdang gi sgo nas byas na dmyal bar skye
NK117(she)001:18073: ba sogs dran pa nyer bzhag las bshad pa nyung
NK117(she)001:18074: ngur bsdus so // pha dang rang sangs rgyas gsod pa srog gcod kyi ma rungs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18075: mchog gsum gyi yo byad 'phrog pa ma yin len pa ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18076: ma dang dgra bcom ma la spyod pa log g.yem nang na ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18077: sangs rgyas rnams la skur 'debs byed pa rdzun gyi nang na ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18078: dge 'dun par dbyen byed pa phra ma'i nang na ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18079: 'phags pa rnams la mi snyan pa brjod pa tshig rtsub ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18080: chos 'dod rnams g.yeng bar byed pa ngag 'khyal ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18081: yang dag 'jog gi zas nor 'phrog par rloms pa brnab sems ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18082: mtshams med kyi las byed la gnod sems ma rungs pa /
NK117(she)001:18083: rang lta mchog tu 'dzin pa log lta ma rungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18085: rgyu mthun 'bras bu rnam pa gnyis grub ste //
NK117(she)001:18086: byed pa rgyu mthun byed las mthun par skye //
NK117(she)001:18087: zhes pa ni 'di la gnyis byed pa rgyu mthun dang myong ba rgyu mthun no //
NK117(she)001:18089: tshe 'dir mi dge ba kho nas dus 'da' bar
NK117(she)001:18090: byas pa'i byed pa rgyu mthun re zhig mtho ris
NK117(she)001:18091: mi'i lus rten tsam thob kyang da dung las snga
NK117(she)001:18092: ma'i mu mthud na srog gcod la mtshon na bshan
NK117(she)001:18093: pa tshos de ring srog mang du bcad nas do
NK117(she)001:18094: nub gnyid log na sang yang srog gcod pa la
NK117(she)001:18095: dga' zhing brtson pa dang mtshungs so //
NK117(she)001:18096: tshul de lta bu'i mi dge ba gzhan yang rjes su dpag go //
NK117(she)001:18098: myong ba rgyu mthun mtho ris thob gyur kyang //
NK117(she)001:18099: rim bzhin mi dge bcu la gnyis gnyis ldan //
NK117(she)001:18100: 'tsho ba thung la nad kyang rnam grangs mang //
NK117(she)001:18101: yo byad nyung zhing dgra dang thun mong can //
NK117(she)001:18102: khyim thab mi mdzes dgra zlar 'brel ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18103: bskur bas gdung zhing gzhan gyis bslu ba mang //
NK117(she)001:18104: 'khor g.yog ngan zhing 'dum par dka' ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18105: mi snyan mang thos 'thab mo'i tshig tu 'drul //
NK117(she)001:18106: tshig bzung mi nus yid ches zhan pa dang //
NK117(she)001:18107: chog mi shes dang 'dod pas gdung ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18108: gnod pa 'du zhing phan pa 'bral ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18109: blta ba ngan dang g.yo sgyus 'khrugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18110: zhes pa ni srog bcad pa'i rnam smin gyis re
NK117(she)001:18111: zhig dmyal bar ma skyes nas mir skyes na'ang myong
NK117(she)001:18112: ba rgyu mthun gyi tshe thung zhing nad mang ba'o
NK117(she)001:18113: // ma byin len gyi myong ba rgyu mthun gyis
NK117(she)001:18114: longs spyod chung zhing gzhan dang thun mong du 'gyur
NK117(she)001:18117: lhod pa dang bcas pa'i chung ma dang g.yog 'khor mi bsrun pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18119: skur ba mang ba dang gzhan gyis bslu ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18121: g.yog mi mthun dang ngan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18123: tshig ngan dang 'thab tshig thos par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:18137: dbang gi 'bras bu yul dang rten cing 'brel //
NK117(she)001:18138: srog gcod sdig to'i khur gyis non pa ste //
NK117(she)001:18139: sa phyogs bag chung sman shing me tog nyung //
NK117(she)001:18140: lo 'bras bza' btung mthu nyams 'ju dka' zhing //
NK117(she)001:18141: srog la ya nga'i gnas su phyin par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:18142: ma byin blang pas myu gu 'joms pa sla //
NK117(she)001:18143: bza' shing yod kyang 'bras bus rnam par smad //
NK117(she)001:18144: sad kyis gdungs dang ser bas rnam par 'thag /
NK117(she)001:18145: mu ge'i sdug bsngal snying la 'pho bar skye //
NK117(she)001:18146: log par g.yem pas gshang gci'i 'dam rdzab khrod //
NK117(she)001:18147: dri nga'i tshor ba rtsub mos dbugs mi phyin //
NK117(she)001:18148: mi gtsang ljan ljin dog cing nyams mi dag'i //
NK117(she)001:18149: yul du skye ba'i 'khri shing dbang med 'dzug /
NK117(she)001:18150: rdzun gyis 'byor pa g.yo zhing yul mi mthun //
NK117(she)001:18151: gzhan gyis bslu dang 'jigs pas brtabs shing skrag /
NK117(she)001:18152: phra mas sa phyogs ngan grog gcong rong can //
NK117(she)001:18153: bgrod dka' mtho dman can gyi yul la gnas //
NK117(she)001:18154: brjod pa rtsub mos rdo gseg tsher ma can //
NK117(she)001:18155: sdong dum 'bras ngan rtsub dang nyams mi bde //
NK117(she)001:18156: tsh+wa sgo can dang rdul mang nyal nyil khrod //
NK117(she)001:18157: yid mi bde ba'i tshor ba nyams su myong //
NK117(she)001:18158: kyal kas so nam ngal ba 'bras med cing //
NK117(she)001:18159: dus kyi rjes su mi 'gro mi brtan 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:18160: brnab sems sbun dang 'bras bu go ldog cing //
NK117(she)001:18161: gnas dus gdug pas skabs btsal mthong bar skye //
NK117(she)001:18162: gnod sems sdig spyod rgyal po dang 'brel zhing //
NK117(she)001:18163: chom rkun sbrul gdug mi rgod gcan gzan rtsub //
NK117(she)001:18164: lo tog 'bras bu'i ro yang tshang zhing kha //
NK117(she)001:18165: rang bzhin gnod pas bkab pa'i yul du skye //
NK117(she)001:18166: log ltas rin po che sogs phun tshogs kyi //
NK117(she)001:18167: 'byor pas kun nas spong zhing sman shing nyung //
NK117(she)001:18168: me tog 'bras bu dag kyang mthu chung la //
NK117(she)001:18169: skyabs dang skyob pa dpung gnyen med par skye //
NK117(she)001:18170: 'di ni rtsa ba nyid kyis gsal ba las 'grel pa logs su mi dgos so //
NK117(she)001:18172: skyes bus byed pa'i 'bras bu gang byas las /
NK117(she)001:18173: mang por 'phel bas sdug bsngal mtha' dag bskyed //
NK117(she)001:18174: 'di ni byed pa rgyu mthun dang mi 'dra ba'i khyad par yang /
NK117(she)001:18175: snying thag pa nas sdig pa la dga' bar byed
NK117(she)001:18176: pa de dag ni tshe 'dir yang phyir zhing sdig
NK117(she)001:18177: pa 'phel bas sdug bsngal bar 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:18178: phyi ma yang de dang mtshungs pa'i lus len par
NK117(she)001:18179: 'gyur zhing mthar ngan song las thar pa rnyed par
NK117(she)001:18181: 'di ltar mun pa las kyang mun nag can //
NK117(she)001:18182: 'khor ba'i brtson ra shin tu brnag dka' bar //
NK117(she)001:18183: nyer len phung po'i steng du sdug bsngal dbal //
NK117(she)001:18184: bzod daka'i tshor ba thob 'di sdig pas byas //
NK117(she)001:18185: zhes pa ni 'di ltar mun pa las zhes pa
NK117(she)001:18186: 'jig rten na snang byed 'gag pa'i mtshan mo las
NK117(she)001:18187: kyang shin tu nag pa'i ma rig pa'i mun pa
NK117(she)001:18189: 'khor ba'i btson ra 'gro ba rigs drug spyi dang
NK117(she)001:18190: khyad par shin tu brnag par dka' ba'i ngan song
NK117(she)001:18192: nye bar len pa'i phung po lnga'i steng du sdug
NK117(she)001:18193: bsngal gyi dbal bzod dka' ba'i tshor ba thob pa
NK117(she)001:18194: 'di dgra 'dre sus kyang byas pa ma yin zhing
NK117(she)001:18195: sdig pa kho nas byas pa'o zhes 'bru mnan nas
NK117(she)001:18196: 'grel sbyar zhing / de las gal chen rags rim zhig smos na /
NK117(she)001:18197: de'ang sdig pa stobs che ba /
NK117(she)001:18198: pha dang ma dang dgra bcom pa bsad pa dang gsum /
NK117(she)001:18199: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byed pa dang bzhi /
NK117(she)001:18200: rgyal ba'i sku la ngan sems kyis khrag 'byin pa
NK117(she)001:18201: ni sngon sangs rgyas zhal bzhugs pa'i dus su lhas
NK117(she)001:18202: sbyin gyis sgyogs 'phangs pa lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:18203: deng dus sku gzugs bshig bral byed pa rnams ni mtshams med pa lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:18204: de dang nye ba lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:18207: dgra bcom ma la chags pa spyod pa /
NK117(she)001:18209: dge 'dun par bkur sti'i sgo bkag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18216: mi chos kyi mna' zos pa /
NK117(she)001:18219: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa rnams lci'o //
NK117(she)001:18220: yang gti mug gi dbang gis ston pa'i sku la smad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18221: nga rgyal gyi dbang gis mkhas pa'i yon tan smad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18222: phrag dog gi dbang gis bden pa'i tshig smad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18223: phyogs ris kyi dbang gis chos la dgag bsgrub byas pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:18224: mtshams med lnga las khrag 'byin dang /
NK117(she)001:18225: mi dge bcu las log lta thu /
NK117(she)001:18226: mnyam pa'i chos la khyad gsod dang /
NK117(she)001:18227: rang bzhin med pa la gal 'dzug pa ste /
NK117(she)001:18228: de dag re re bzhin log pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18231: skur ba'i lci ba zhes so //
NK117(she)001:18233: dge smad sdig bstod gnyis dang /
NK117(she)001:18234: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK117(she)001:18235: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK117(she)001:18236: bla ma yi dam mched lcam spangs pa ste bdun /
NK117(she)001:18238: de dag thams cad byang chub sems dpa' la brten pa'i nyes pa bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK117(she)001:18239: mdor na las 'bras khyad gsod byed pa dge slong
NK117(she)001:18240: lhas sbyin dang legs skar 'bri gung dpal 'dzin sogs
NK117(she)001:18241: sa gas pa'i nang nas dmyal bar song ba mthong
NK117(she)001:18243: sngon tsi na'i yul du las 'bras la skur pa
NK117(she)001:18244: 'debs pa'i skyes bu zhig mal sar nyal bzhin sbrul
NK117(she)001:18245: du gyur pa sogs mang bas lta sgom go thos
NK117(she)001:18246: tsam la brten nas rtogs so snyam pa'i spyod rtsing
NK117(she)001:18247: gis rgyu 'bras rdog pas ma bardzi zhig /
NK117(she)001:18248: ces bla ma'i rjes su 'brangs nas skyar zlos byas pa las rang mthong gis ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:18249: de'i phyir na rnam pa kun tu rang rgyud brtag
NK117(she)001:18250: dpyad zhib mos dge sdig gnyis sngo bgrang byed pa
NK117(she)001:18251: la mkhas pa gal shin tu che bar gsungs /
NK117(she)001:18252: lar skyes bu dam pa ni gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:18255: de yang sngar mi dge ba gang byas kyis las
NK117(she)001:18256: la snying nas 'gyod pa drag po bskyed pa rnam
NK117(she)001:18258: yul mchog gsum dang bla ma la bsten nas sngon
NK117(she)001:18259: mi dge ba'i las gang byas pa snying thag pa
NK117(she)001:18260: nas bshags pa la brtson pa rten gyi stobs dang
NK117(she)001:18261: / sngon gyi nyes byas dran bzhin rnam smin la
NK117(she)001:18262: 'jigs nas sgo gsum chos la bkol ba gnyen po
NK117(she)001:18263: kun tu spyod pa'i stobs so //
NK117(she)001:18264: nyes pa las ldog pa'i stobs ni /
NK117(she)001:18265: sdig pa byed pa dang mchog gsum blos gtong ba'i
NK117(she)001:18266: gla rngan du nor rdzas ri tsam spungs nas brid
NK117(she)001:18267: pa'am / yang na dge sgrub sdig spangs mi bshol
NK117(she)001:18268: na da lta nyid du gsod par nges kyang dge
NK117(she)001:18269: sdig pa 'jug ldog mi nor ba zhig cis kyang
NK117(she)001:18270: byed par som nyi med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18271: de ltar byas na mtshams med pa lnga byas pa byang bar 'gyur ba yang /
NK117(she)001:18272: sngon ston pa'i gcung dga' bo zhes pa bud med
NK117(she)001:18273: la rab tu chags shing chos yid la mi byed
NK117(she)001:18274: pa dang / bram ze sor mo'i phreng ba ni
NK117(she)001:18275: slob dpon ngan pas mang bsad dge ba'i lung la
