NK117(she)001:18276: mnyan nas mi dgu brgya dang go dgu bsad pa
NK117(she)001:18277: pa dang / dang / mthong ldan nam ma skyes
NK117(she)001:18278: dgra ni zhe sdang che ba'i khar sdig grogs dang
NK117(she)001:18279: pa dang / dang / 'phrad skyon gyis / pha
NK117(she)001:18280: chos ldan gyi rgyal po gzugs can snying po bsad
NK117(she)001:18282: ma skyes dgra'i bu bde byed kyis rang gi chung
NK117(she)001:18283: ma spangs nas gzhan gyi chung ma dang nyal po
NK117(she)001:18284: byas pa bkag pas ma bsad /
NK117(she)001:18285: de dag kun kyang bshags pas dag pa yin pa gzhung rnam dag rnams las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:18287: de phyir ma dag gzhan dbang gnas skabs na //
NK117(she)001:18288: mtho ris 'phen byed dge ba'i las lam bcu //
NK117(she)001:18289: mi dge bcu las phyi rol phyogs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:18290: dge ba'i las bcu yang dag bsnyen par mdzod //
NK117(she)001:18291: de bsnyen pa las bsod nams cha mthun bcus //
NK117(she)001:18292: bde 'gror 'phen zhing mi dge rnam pa bcus //
NK117(she)001:18293: ngan 'gror 'phen pa'i dkar nag rgyu 'bras la //
NK117(she)001:18294: blang dor bgyid pa skyes bu chung ngu'i lam //
NK117(she)001:18295: zhes pa ni de la rnal 'byor spyod pa'i gzhung las gsungs pa'i /
NK117(she)001:18300: chos dang gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK117(she)001:18301: mdor na dngos po'i yul du med kyang blos yod par bzung ba rnams so //
NK117(she)001:18302: gzhan dbang la yang ma dag gzhan dbang ni 'byung
NK117(she)001:18303: ba lnga sogs dbang po'i sgor snang du rung ba'i
NK117(she)001:18304: snod bcud kyi rnam pa 'khrul ngor shar ba thams
NK117(she)001:18305: cad do // dag pa gzhan dbang ni /
NK117(she)001:18306: rgyal ba rnams kyis gzigs ngor snang ba'i zhing khams dang gzhal yas la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18307: rnal 'byor pa la sku dang zhing khams sogs dag snang shar ba'ang der bsdu'o //
NK117(she)001:18309: 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs grub ni /
NK117(she)001:18310: 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul pa gnyis su med par
NK117(she)001:18311: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i chos nyid
NK117(she)001:18312: rang chas su ldan pa'i stong pa nyid 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:18313: mi mnga' ba gshis kyi gnas lugs dam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18314: de las rang gis stong pa ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin bden par ma grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18315: gzhan gyis stong pa ni chos de las gzhan pa'i chos med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18316: gnyis kas stong pa ni chos gang la gnyis su med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18317: spyir mi dge ba bcu spang ba'i steng du dge ba bcu bsgrubs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:18318: gzhan gyi srog skyob sbyin pa gtong ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18319: sdom pa bsrung zhing bden par smra ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18320: mkhon pa bsdum dang zhi dul drang por smra //
NK117(she)001:18321: chos dang mthun pa'i gtam smra 'dod pa chung //
NK117(she)001:18322: byams brtse sgom zhing sgo gsum chos la bkol //
NK117(she)001:18323: zhes pa ltar dam pa gsum dang ma 'brel ba'i
NK117(she)001:18324: dge ba rgya ji ltar che yang sdig pa dang
NK117(she)001:18325: 'dres min dang dad pa che chung gis dbye bas
NK117(she)001:18328: che ba gsum gyi rjes su 'gro bas mi dang 'dod lha dang /
NK117(she)001:18329: chen pos 'phen byed byas nas tshangs gnas su skye bar yang srid cing /
NK117(she)001:18330: khams gong ma'i gnas su skye ba'i rgyu ni bsam
NK117(she)001:18331: gtan bzhi dang gzugs med kyi ting nge 'dzin mthu
NK117(she)001:18333: de'ang gzugs khams pa rnams ni kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18334: 'jug shes gtso bor ldan la gzhan dag ni 'khor gyi tshul lo //
NK117(she)001:18335: gzugs med khams su kun gzhi nyid gtso bor ldan la /
NK117(she)001:18336: gzhan dag bag nyal du yod pas gnyid 'thug gi
NK117(she)001:18337: skabs ltar dge sdig gang yang mi spyod cing gti
NK117(she)001:18339: de'i phyir gzugs med kyi sems de tshe snga ma'i
NK117(she)001:18340: dge 'bras yin kyang bsod nams cha mthun yin pas
NK117(she)001:18342: mi'i lus la brten nas thar pa dang rnam mkhyen
NK117(she)001:18343: bsgrub tu yod pas lha las lhag pa'i lus zhes
NK117(she)001:18345: thar pa cha mthun zag med dam pa'i rgyu //
NK117(she)001:18346: dge bcu bsam gtan gzugs med sbyin sogs drug /
NK117(she)001:18347: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi slob lam lngas bsdus //
NK117(she)001:18348: zhes pa ni 'di ltar kun rdzob bden pa'i phyogs bsod nams kyi tshogs dge ba bcu dang /
NK117(she)001:18349: pha rol tu phyin pa lngas bsdus pa rnams /
NK117(she)001:18350: don dam bden pa'i phyogs ye shes kyi tshogs stong
NK117(she)001:18351: nyid snying rje zung 'jug gis zin nas lam lnga'i
NK117(she)001:18352: rim pa mtha' dag gis gnas skabs su'ang mngon mtho
NK117(she)001:18353: dang / mthar thug zhi ba dam pa'i sar gzhol
NK117(she)001:18354: ba ni thar pa cha mthun gyi rnam par smin
NK117(she)001:18355: dang / pa'i 'bras bu'o // de'i rgyu mthun gyi
NK117(she)001:18356: 'bras bus mtho ris kyi yon tan phal mo che
NK117(she)001:18357: dang / pa'i 'bras bu'o // dang ldan zhing /
NK117(she)001:18358: dbang 'bras bde skyid 'dzoms pa'i yul dang 'phrad par
NK117(she)001:18359: dang / pa'i 'bras bu'o // dang ldan zhing / gsungs so // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:18360: de yang bdag med gnyis kyi don rtogs nas //
NK117(she)001:18361: thabs shes zung 'brel dge ba gser 'gyur rtsis //
NK117(she)001:18362: srid dang zhi bar 'gal ba'i lcags khams la //
NK117(she)001:18363: thebs pas mi gnas ye shes rgyal ba'i khams //
NK117(she)001:18364: grub pa 'jig rten 'das pa'i dge ba yin //
NK117(she)001:18365: zhes pa ni 'di ltar nyan rang gi lugs kyi
NK117(she)001:18366: bdag med gnyis la dmigs pa can ma yin par
NK117(she)001:18367: / gzung ba gang zag gi bdag dang 'dzin pa
NK117(she)001:18368: chos kyi bdag gnyis rang bzhin med par rtogs pas
NK117(she)001:18369: thabs kyi cha la rgyas thebs pa'i thabs shes zung
NK117(she)001:18370: 'brel gyi dge ba ni gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta
NK117(she)001:18371: / bu ste / dge ba spyod dus nas bzang
NK117(she)001:18372: ngan gyi blo las grol bas dngos mtshan du 'dzin
NK117(she)001:18373: pa'i cha nas srid pa dang zhi bar 'gal ba'i
NK117(she)001:18374: lcags kyi khams la thebs pas mi gnas pa'i ye
NK117(she)001:18375: shes rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i grong khyer chen
NK117(she)001:18378: lam dus dmigs par bcas pa bsod nams tshogs //
NK117(she)001:18379: dmigs med ye shes tshogs te zung 'jug gis //
NK117(she)001:18380: sgrib pa gnyis sbyang sku gnyis mngon du 'thob //
NK117(she)001:18381: dag pa'i rgyu 'bras zab mo'i rten 'brel lags //
NK117(she)001:18382: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dmigs bcas sbyin pa la sogs pa'i bsod nams kyi tshogs lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:18383: dmigs med shes rab ni ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK117(she)001:18384: de gnyis zung du 'brel bas sgrib gnyis dag nas 'bras bu sku gnyis mngon du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18385: de'ang sa mtshams kyi sgo nas dbye na sbyor lam chos mchog man chad 'jig rten pa'i lam dang /
NK117(she)001:18386: mthong lam zag med myang 'das kyi lam mo //
NK117(she)001:18387: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:18388: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:18389: lde mig las le'u gsum pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:18390: spyi don bzhi pa 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rnam bzhag ni /
NK117(she)001:18392: mngon mtho'i gru bo mchog la brten pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:18393: re zhig ngan song chu srin gdug pa'i lces //
NK117(she)001:18394: btang yang thar pa'i skam sar ma phyin pas //
NK117(she)001:18395: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi yi ded dpon brten //
NK117(she)001:18396: zhes pa ni bdag cag mngon mtho mi'i lus rten
NK117(she)001:18397: gru bo che lta bu bde ba'i tshor ba 'ba'
NK117(she)001:18398: zhig myong ba thob na'ang ngan song chu srin gdug
NK117(she)001:18399: pa can gyi lces bldag pa la nye ba 'khor
NK117(she)001:18400: ba'i mtsho las ma 'dus pas thar pa'i skam sar
NK117(she)001:18401: slebs pa'i thabs 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi'i ded dpon
NK117(she)001:18402: bsten par bya'o // zhes gsungs bzhin bdag cag gi
NK117(she)001:18403: ston pas 'khor lnga sde bzang po la dge slong
NK117(she)001:18404: bsten par bya'o // dag / sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:18407: lam dang bzhi po gsungs nas /
NK117(she)001:18408: dge slong dag sdug bsngal shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:18411: lam rgyud la bsten par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:18412: yang dge slong dag sdug bsngal shes par bya ste
NK117(she)001:18413: shes par byar med pa'i mi skye ba shes pa
NK117(she)001:18414: dang / kun 'byung dang 'gog pa dang lam gsum
NK117(she)001:18415: la yang de ltar du sbyor ba shes par bya'o
NK117(she)001:18416: dang / // de ltar bden bzhi lan gsum bzlos te gsungs pa las /
NK117(she)001:18418: de la sdug bsngal shes par bya ba ni //
NK117(she)001:18419: gnas rigs drug po dma' 'am mtho yang rung //
NK117(she)001:18420: sdug bsngal 'gyur dang khyab pa 'du byed kyis //
NK117(she)001:18421: dam la ma bzhag 'khor ba yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:18422: zhes pa ni 'di ltar sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal dang /
NK117(she)001:18424: khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal /
NK117(she)001:18425: dang po ni sdug bsngal gcig thog tu gnyis brtsegs pa nad thog tu dgra byung ba lta bu /
NK117(she)001:18427: lo zla zhag dus kyi bde skyid mi rtag par 'gyur ba /
NK117(she)001:18429: mthong chos su dga' bde'i rgyu bza' btung longs spyod
NK117(she)001:18430: la sogs pa phyis sdug bsngal gyi rgyur song ba'o
NK117(she)001:18432: phung krol bskyed la mgo 'phang bstod pa yi //
NK117(she)001:18433: ma rungs 'dod pa'i gdon dang yul gyi dug /
NK117(she)001:18434: phan tshun 'dzings shing gtugs pa'i btson ra nas //
NK117(she)001:18435: thar pa'i skabs med nyam thag skyo ba 'phel //
NK117(she)001:18436: zhes pa ni 'di ltar 'dod pa ni phung krol kun gyi rtsa ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:18437: bdag gzhan gnyis kar gnod pa'i dug sbrul mgo 'phang bstod pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:18438: de las 'dod khams pa kun gyi sred pa 'phel
NK117(she)001:18439: ba'i rtsa ba nges 'byung gi bslab pa'i gegs thar
NK117(she)001:18440: lam gyi dgra bo yul bud med kho na'i skyon
NK117(she)001:18441: dang gzhan yang dbang po'i sgo lngar snang ba'i yul
NK117(she)001:18442: gyi dbang du gyur pa'i dug lnga po phan tshun
NK117(she)001:18443: 'dzings shing phye dka' bar gtugs pa'i btson ra nas
NK117(she)001:18444: thar pa'i skabs med pas nyam thag par skyo ba
NK117(she)001:18446: bde ba 'dod la mngon sbyor brtson pa dag /
NK117(she)001:18447: gti mug mthus non sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyi //
NK117(she)001:18448: mtshon cha rnon po'i dbal la brten byas pas //
NK117(she)001:18449: gnod pa'i gnas su rang nyid yang dag sbyar //
NK117(she)001:18450: mar me'i gzugs dang phye ma leb bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:18451: sgra dang dri ro reg byas bslu ba ni //
NK117(she)001:18452: ri dwags bung ba nya dang glang po che //
NK117(she)001:18453: 'dod pa'i yul lnga dag dang rten cing 'brel //
NK117(she)001:18454: zhes pa ni de'ang bde ba 'dod bzhin de'i mi
NK117(she)001:18455: mthun phyogs mi dge ba la mngon par brtson pa
NK117(she)001:18456: dge blo gti mug gi mthus non nas sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:18457: gyi rgyu mi dge ba dang 'bras bu der mthun
NK117(she)001:18458: la spyod dgos pa'i dpe mtshon cha rnon po'i dbal
NK117(she)001:18459: la brten par byas pas rang nyid la gnod pa'i
NK117(she)001:18460: gnas su yang dag par sbyar ba ste /
NK117(she)001:18461: 'di ltar mar me'i 'od la chags pas phye ma leb tshig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18462: ri dwags gling bu'i sgra la chags nas rngon pas bsad pa /
NK117(she)001:18463: bung ba me tog gi dri dang bcud la chags pas 'chi ba /
NK117(she)001:18464: nya lcags kyu'i sha gzan gyi bslus pas 'chi ba /
NK117(she)001:18465: glang po che glang mo'i reg byar chags rkyen gyis 'chi ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18466: de lta'i 'dod yon re res kyang srog 'phrog nus
NK117(she)001:18467: na yul lnga por rtag tu 'brel na smos ci
NK117(she)001:18469: srid pa'i yul la thu ba gtum po'i me //
NK117(she)001:18470: khro ba'i mngon spyod rtsub pa gcan gzan dang //
NK117(she)001:18471: mi rgod rgyal po'i chad pa las myur ba'i //
NK117(she)001:18472: sdug bsngal snga phyi brgyud mas 'gro 'di mnar //
NK117(she)001:18473: zhes pa ni 'di ltar 'khor ba ni sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:18474: thams cad kyi rten dang brten pa kho na yin
NK117(she)001:18475: pas 'jig rten srid pa'i yul na 'phrad pa tsam
NK117(she)001:18476: gyis bsreg pa la thu ba gtum po'i me dang
NK117(she)001:18477: / de bzhin du stag seng dom dred mi rgod
NK117(she)001:18478: sogs dang rgyal po'i chad pa gang las kyang 'phags
NK117(she)001:18479: pa rnams kyi gzigs ngo na rigs drug so so'i
NK117(she)001:18480: sdug bsngal snga phyi brgyud mas 'gro ba 'di rnams
NK117(she)001:18481: mnar bas thu bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:18483: bdag la bshes sam mi mthun nye dang 'khon //
NK117(she)001:18484: bsam par mi nus mtha' dag sems ldan gyis //
NK117(she)001:18485: dgra dang mdza' bshes bar ma'i phyogs bzung nas //
NK117(she)001:18486: phan dang gnod pa sbyin pa bsam las 'das //
NK117(she)001:18487: zhes pa ni da lta'i dus kyi bdag la phan pa'i mdza' bshes dang nye du'am /
NK117(she)001:18488: 'khon yul gyi dgra zla sogs bsam par mi nus pa'i mtha' dag sems ldan rnams kyis /
NK117(she)001:18489: skye ba thog ma nas da lta'i bar du dgra dang mdza' bshes dang bar ma'i phyogs bzung nas /
NK117(she)001:18490: phan btags pa dang gnod pa sbyin pa bsam las
NK117(she)001:18491: 'das pa yod mod kyang de kun skye ba 'di'i
NK117(she)001:18492: nye du dang dgra zla ltar ma lags te phal
NK117(she)001:18493: cher go ldog 'dra mor gyur pa yang /
NK117(she)001:18494: 'phags pa k+aa t+y+aa na khyim bdag gcig gi sgo drung du bsod snyoms slong du phyin pas /
NK117(she)001:18495: des dgra bo bu ru skyes pa pang du bzung /
NK117(she)001:18496: pha nya ru skye ba bza' zhing mur /
NK117(she)001:18497: ma khyi ru skyes pas nya rus 'cha' ba la brdeg pa gzigs pas thugs skyo nas 'di ltar /
NK117(she)001:18498: pha sha za zhing ma la brdeg /
NK117(she)001:18499: las ngan dgra bo pang du khur //
NK117(she)001:18500: chung mas khyo yi rus pa 'cha' //
NK117(she)001:18501: 'khor ba'i chos la gad mo bro //
NK117(she)001:18504: rdul phran lta bu'i lus kyi bdag gcig pu'i //
NK117(she)001:18505: srog rten gzugs su gyur dang 'dod pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:18506: mgo dang yan lag bcad gtubs bgyis so cog /
NK117(she)001:18507: spungs na lhun po'i che thang nyams par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:18508: dmyal gnas zangs zhun khol ma 'thungs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:18509: yi dwags las gyur rnag khrag mi gtsang zos //
NK117(she)001:18510: kun tu sdug bsngal rgyu las mchi ma zag /
NK117(she)001:18511: phyogs mtha' gtugs pa'i chu klung dag las mang //
NK117(she)001:18512: zhes pa ni srog chags grog sbur sogs rdul phran
NK117(she)001:18513: lta bu'i lus kyi bdag gcig pu'i srog rten pa'i
NK117(she)001:18515: srog chags gzhan gyi lus blang tshe sha dang pags
NK117(she)001:18516: pa sogs 'dod pa'i phyir mgo dang yan lag rnams
NK117(she)001:18517: bcad gtub bgyis so cog mnyam du bsags nas spungs
NK117(she)001:18518: na ri rgyal lhun po las kyang mtho zhing de'i
NK117(she)001:18519: che thang yang nyams dma' bar 'gyur zhing /
NK117(she)001:18520: dmyal ba'i gnas su skyes nas zangs zhun khol ma
NK117(she)001:18521: 'thungs pa dang yi dwags kyi lus su gyur tshe
NK117(she)001:18522: rnag khrag dang mi gtsang ba zos pa sogs kun
NK117(she)001:18523: tu sdug bsngal gyis mnar ba'i rgyu las mchi ma
NK117(she)001:18524: zag pa bsags na phyogs mtha' gtugs pa'i chu klung
NK117(she)001:18525: dag las mang zhes gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18527: khyad par dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal tshad med de //
NK117(she)001:18528: phan tshun gcig gis gcig gsod yang sos la //
NK117(she)001:18529: thig nag sog les gshog 'byar rgyun mi 'chad //
NK117(she)001:18530: bsdus 'joms mgo brnyan ri dang tho bas 'thag /
NK117(she)001:18531: ngu 'bod lcags zhun bskol bar 'tshod cing dbad //
NK117(she)001:18532: 'bod sgrog chen po lcags khyim 'bar bar bsreg /
NK117(she)001:18533: tsha ba gsal shing 'bar bas lus la 'bigs //
NK117(she)001:18534: rab tu tsha ba mdung thung rtse gsum las //
NK117(she)001:18535: lus kyi gzhung 'bigs phyi nas lcags bsregs dkri //
NK117(she)001:18536: khro chu khol mar 'tshod dang mnar med ni //
NK117(she)001:18537: lcags khyim 'bar bar me dang gnyis med bsreg /
NK117(she)001:18538: ces pa ni rigs drug po'i nang nas dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal tshad med par gsungs pa yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:18539: de yang phan tshun gcig gis gcig gsod pa'i yang sos dang /
NK117(she)001:18540: lus la thig nag po mang du btab nas sog
NK117(she)001:18541: le me rab tu 'bar bas gshog pa 'byar ba
NK117(she)001:18542: rgyun mi 'chad du byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18543: bsdus 'joms ni srog chags kyi mgo brnyan du gyur
NK117(she)001:18544: pa'i ri bar du 'thag cing tho bas brdung ba
NK117(she)001:18545: la sogs pa'o // ngu 'bod ni lcags khyim me
NK117(she)001:18546: rab tu 'bar bar btsud nas lcags zhun bskol bar
NK117(she)001:18548: 'bod sgrog chen po ni lcags khyim me rab tu 'bar ba nyis rim du bsreg pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18549: tsha ba ni gsal zhing rtse gcig pas lus kyi
NK117(she)001:18550: gzhung nas 'bigs shing klad par thal 'byin zhing dbang
NK117(she)001:18551: po'i sgo sogs nas me 'bar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18552: rab tu tsha ba mdung thung rtse gsum pas klad
NK117(she)001:18553: pa dang thal gong gnyis su thal bar 'byin zhing
NK117(she)001:18554: lus kyi phyi nas lcags bsregs leb mos dkri ba
NK117(she)001:18555: dang / khro chu khol mar 'tshod cing mnar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18556: mnar med ni lcags khyim me rab tu 'bar ba'i
NK117(she)001:18557: nang du me dang lus gnyis su med par bsreg
NK117(she)001:18558: pa'i thabs ma zad bar du bsregs shing mnar ba'i
NK117(she)001:18559: las ma rdzogs bar mnar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18561: sdug bsngal nyid las dbugs 'byin kun rtog gis //
NK117(she)001:18562: nye 'khor sgo 'phar dbye ba mdag me'i 'obs //
NK117(she)001:18563: ro myags 'dam rdzab stug dang ral gri'i nags //
NK117(she)001:18564: chu bo rab med gshin rje'i kha bas thu //
NK117(she)001:18565: zhes pa ni de ltar tsha dmyal brgyad po spyi
NK117(she)001:18566: dang khyad par mnar med du skyes pa dag sdug
NK117(she)001:18567: bsngal chen po 'di las dbugs 'byin thob res kun
NK117(she)001:18568: rtog gi ngang nas las de zad pa'i skabs su
NK117(she)001:18569: bab pa na lcags bsregs kyi khang pa'i sgo phye
NK117(she)001:18570: ba las thon te phyin pa na nye 'khor sgo
NK117(she)001:18571: 'phar bye ba'i phyir slebs pa na mdag me'i 'obs
NK117(she)001:18572: su tshud cing sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:18573: de bzhin du ro myags 'dam rdzab shin tu stug pa dang ral gri lo ma'i nags tshal dang /
NK117(she)001:18574: thal tshan gyi chu bo rab med na gnas pa'i
NK117(she)001:18575: gshin rje'i kha bas thu ba la sogs so so'i
NK117(she)001:18576: mnar spyod kyis mnar bar byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18578: mdza' gcugs dam bca' dran nas bsnyegs pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:18579: tsher ma rnon pos tshabs cher phug pa'i lus //
NK117(she)001:18580: 'bar zhing rtsub pa'i lcags kyi bud med kyis //
NK117(she)001:18581: 'khyud mthar khwa dang bya rgod mig la 'dru //
NK117(she)001:18582: zhes pa ni tshe 'dir pho mo phan tshun chags
NK117(she)001:18583: sbyor gyi sgo nas mdza' gcugs su gyur pa'i bag
NK117(she)001:18584: chags goms pa'i dam bca' dran pa'i mod la pho
NK117(she)001:18585: la mos 'bod pa dang mo la phos 'bod pa'i
NK117(she)001:18586: 'khrul snang shar ma thag der bsnyegs nas phyin pa'i
NK117(she)001:18587: lam du lcags bsregs las grub pa'i tsher ma rnon
NK117(she)001:18588: pos tshabs cher phug bzhin mdza' grogs kyi gam du
NK117(she)001:18589: slebs 'phral pho la mo dang mo la phor snang
NK117(she)001:18590: ba de nyid lcags bsregs me rab tu 'bar ba'i
NK117(she)001:18591: lus su gyur te 'khyud nas lus thal ba bun
NK117(she)001:18592: gyis bsregs mthar khwa dang bya rgod kyi mig 'dru
NK117(she)001:18593: ba la sogs kyis mnar ba nyams su myong ba'o
NK117(she)001:18595: bu yug sbrebs pa 'dar ba'i thag pa yis //
NK117(she)001:18596: bcings te bskyod par ma nus bzhin gson yang //
NK117(she)001:18597: rlung gi mtshon chas rus pa'i gting phug pa'i //
NK117(she)001:18598: grang reg so yi bar du 'tshir ltar gdung //
NK117(she)001:18599: zhes pa ni 'di ltar grang dmyal du skye ba
NK117(she)001:18600: rnams ni gangs ri chen po gcong rong mi bzod
NK117(she)001:18602: kha char dang rlung drag pos rab tu sbrebs pa'i
NK117(she)001:18603: gnas su dbang med du tshud nas 'dar ba'i thag
NK117(she)001:18604: pa zhes rgyun mi chad du 'dar zhing lus po
NK117(she)001:18605: bcings te bsgongs pa ltar mnar spyod ci tsam byas
NK117(she)001:18606: kyang 'chi mi nus la bzhin ni gson po ltar
NK117(she)001:18607: yang / rlung mtshon cha lta bu'i reg byas rus
NK117(she)001:18608: pa'i gting tshun phug pa'i tshor ba'i grang reg so'i
NK117(she)001:18609: bar du 'tshir ba lta bus gdung zhing nyam thag
NK117(she)001:18611: chu bur can dang chu bur brdol ba dang //
NK117(she)001:18612: a chu'i smre sngags kyi hud so 'thams can //
NK117(she)001:18613: ut+pa la ltar pags pa drug tshal 'gas //
NK117(she)001:18614: pad+ma dang ni pad+ma chen po ltar //
NK117(she)001:18615: brgyad dang bcu drug grangs med gas pa'i rma //
NK117(she)001:18616: srog chags mchu rnon can gyis 'bigs shing bza' //
NK117(she)001:18617: zhes pa ni chu bur can ni ha cang grang ches pas lus la chu bur rdol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:18618: chu bur brdol nas rmar gyur pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18619: de'i skyon gyis a chu'i smre sngags dang kyi hud
NK117(she)001:18620: zer ba dang so 'thams nas skad mi thon pa
NK117(she)001:18621: dang / ut+pala ltar pags pa drug tshal dang /
NK117(she)001:18623: pad+ma chen po ltar de las mang du gas pa'i nang nas chu ser dang /
NK117(she)001:18627: mgal dum bcad dang sgo 'phar med la 'thums //
NK117(she)001:18628: sgo dang ka ba thab dang thag pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:18629: sna tshogs las kyis sprul pa'i rang gzugs la //
NK117(she)001:18630: nye bar len pa'i sdug bsngal zad mi shes //
NK117(she)001:18631: zhes pa nyi tshe ba ni /
NK117(she)001:18632: ri brag chu shing me dang nam mkha' sogs la
NK117(she)001:18633: gnas te grangs dang tshe tshad sdug bsngal sogs ma
NK117(she)001:18637: gangs dang chab rom gyi nang du 'khyags shing rengs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18639: me nang du tsha zhing bsreg pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18640: shing dang lo ma'i sbubs su btums pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18641: nam mkhar g.yo ba sogs kyis sdug bsngal lo //
NK117(she)001:18642: nyi tshe ba kha cig ni 'di bzhin te /
NK117(she)001:18643: sngon grong khyer rdo 'jog tu 'phags pa k+aa t+y+aa
NK117(she)001:18644: na la shan pa gcig gis mtshan mo srog mi
NK117(she)001:18645: gcod pa'i khrims mnos pa las /
NK117(she)001:18646: de sngon gyi mi dge ba'i rgyus nyi tshe ba'i
NK117(she)001:18647: dmyal bar skyes nas nyin mo sdug bsngal yang mtshan
NK117(she)001:18648: khrims ma nyams pas lha'i longs spyod la dbang ba
NK117(she)001:18649: bzhin no // yang la la dag ni /
NK117(she)001:18650: moong+gala gyi bus rgya mtsho'i mthar phyin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18651: de na nyi tshe ba'i dmyal ba pa gtun lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:18658: ka ba la sogs par 'khrul nas sdug bsngal sna tshogs myong ba gzigs pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:18659: gzhan yang rgyal po'i khab kyi ba lang gsod pa'i
NK117(she)001:18660: shan pa zhig rus gong bya rog gis 'thog pas
NK117(she)001:18661: sdug bsngal kho rang gis tshor ba lta bu dang
NK117(she)001:18662: / de bzhin du shing sdong bcad gtub byas pa'i sdug bsngal kho rang gis tshor ba lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:18663: rna ba bye ba ris zhes pa lam 'khyal skabs
NK117(she)001:18664: khang pa d+r+wa ba can zhig tu gan+d+aa brdungs 'phral
NK117(she)001:18665: nyan thos kyi gzugs brnyan lnga brgya tsam 'dus ma
NK117(she)001:18666: thag tu gsod res byas shing yang thams cad phyir
NK117(she)001:18667: thon nas song ba mthong ba sogs mang du yod
NK117(she)001:18668: do // spyir dmyal ba'i rnam grangs bco brgyad du bsdus kyang /
NK117(she)001:18669: de tsam du ma zad nam mkha' snying po'i mdo
NK117(she)001:18670: sogs las de las ches mang du bshad pa yod
NK117(she)001:18672: yi dwags na'ang 'dod pas phongs pa yis //
NK117(she)001:18673: bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal rgyun chags mi 'chos pa //
NK117(she)001:18674: bkres skom grang dro ngal dang 'jigs pa yis //
NK117(she)001:18675: bskyed pa shin tu mi bzad bsten 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:18676: zhes pa ni bkres skom la sogs pas yid gdung
NK117(she)001:18677: ba'i 'dod zhen nam yang mi rdzogs pas bskyed pa'i
NK117(she)001:18678: sdug bsngal rgyun chags shing de'i skyon gyis bza' btung
NK117(she)001:18679: 'ba' zhig btsal phyir rgyug pas ngal zhing /
NK117(she)001:18680: bza' btung mthong na'ang skyes bu mtshon cha thogs pas bsrung ba sogs mthong nas 'jigs pas /
NK117(she)001:18681: bskyed pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzad pa bsten pa shes dgos so //
NK117(she)001:18683: khyad par nang sgrib can ni /
NK117(she)001:18684: lto ba ri tsam che zhing kha khab mig tsam du chung ba /
NK117(she)001:18685: zas skom gzhan gyis bsrung ba'am med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:18686: mi gtsang ba sogs cung zad tsam rnyed kyang khar
NK117(she)001:18687: mi tshud cing lto mi khengs pas sdug bsngal lo
NK117(she)001:18688: // zas skom gyi sgrib pa can ni /
NK117(she)001:18689: sdug bsngal snga ma'i thog tu mtshan mor lto nas me 'bar zhing /
NK117(she)001:18690: zas skom yang mer 'gyur ba sogs so //
NK117(she)001:18691: spyi mthun gyi sgrib pa ni /
NK117(she)001:18692: sha med pas rus 'go rnams lpags pas g.yogs shing skems la rid pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18693: de'i nang nas kyang dmangs rigs zhes pa rnams bza' btung tha chad tsam yang mi rnyed cing /
NK117(she)001:18694: phan tshun 'phrad ma thag 'dzing rtsod brdung brdeg sogs byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18696: dbyar dus zla ba'ang tsha zhing dgun dus nyi ma'ang grang bar 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:18697: ljon shing lo 'bras phun sum tshogs pa bltas pa'i mod la skam zhing /
NK117(she)001:18698: chu klung yang de mtshungs su 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:18699: mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags ni /
NK117(she)001:18700: lus srul po dang ro langs dang /
NK117(she)001:18702: brjed byed gnod sbyin sha za grib gnon dang /
NK117(she)001:18704: nam gru dang byad gdon dang /
NK117(she)001:18707: rgyal po la sogs 'byung po'i rigs can mtha' dag go //
NK117(she)001:18708: 'di dag ni gdon gyi rigs su bsdu ste /
NK117(she)001:18709: deng dus gshin po gang du'ang mi 'gro zhing gson
NK117(she)001:18710: gral na yod do zer ba ni ba lang gser
NK117(she)001:18711: mdog ngom pa'i mun sprul kho na las ma mchis
NK117(she)001:18712: shing / tshe 'das gang yin de nyid las bsags
NK117(she)001:18713: tshul gyis mkha' rgyu'i yi dwags 'di dag gi rigs
NK117(she)001:18714: sam 'khor du skyes nas gson po'i mi nor la
NK117(she)001:18715: lan chags dang sha mkhon yod tshul gyis gnod pa'o
NK117(she)001:18716: shing / // de yang gang du snying nye nas
NK117(she)001:18717: phyin pa de dag la rang nyid sngon 'chi ka'i
NK117(she)001:18718: gnad 'chad pa'i tshor ba spo ba'i 'du shes kyis
NK117(she)001:18719: gnod cing 'tshe ba la nus ldan gyis rigs sngags
NK117(she)001:18720: dang thun gyi chad pa 'beb pa sogs kyis mnar
NK117(she)001:18721: shing / // ba dang / gzhan yang nyi tshe
NK117(she)001:18722: ba dang mtshungs pa'i lus dang sdug bsngal kyang yod
NK117(she)001:18723: shing / // ba dang / do // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:18724: dud 'gro'i skye gnas na yang gsod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:18725: bcings dang brdeg sogs sdug bsngal sna tshogs pa //
NK117(she)001:18726: zhi gyur dge ba spangs pa rnams la ni //
NK117(she)001:18727: gcig la gcig za shin tu mi bzad pa //
NK117(she)001:18728: zhes pa ni dud 'gro la kha 'thor dang /
NK117(she)001:18729: bying gnas gnyis las dang po ni gcig gis gcig
NK117(she)001:18730: gsod pa dang che bas chung ba mang po za
NK117(she)001:18731: ba dang / chung ba mang pos che ba'i lus 'bigs bzhin za ba /
NK117(she)001:18732: gzhan yang rdog pa sogs kyis gsod pas sdug bsngal lo //
NK117(she)001:18733: thag pas bcings pa dang brdung brdeg dang dbang med
NK117(she)001:18734: du bkol ba sogs kyis sdug bsngal sna tshogs pa
NK117(she)001:18735: nyams su myong zhing zhi bar gyur pa'i sems dang
NK117(she)001:18736: bral bzhin dge ba spangs pa rnams la ni gcig
NK117(she)001:18737: la gcig za ba sogs shin tu mi bzad pa'i
NK117(she)001:18738: sdug bsngal dos drag la yun ring ba spyod dgos
NK117(she)001:18739: par gsungs shing klu rnams kyang dud 'gror bsdu dgos
NK117(she)001:18740: des ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal cung zad bshad
NK117(she)001:18742: de phyir skye ba'i shwa 'od sdug bsngal gyi //
NK117(she)001:18743: dba' rlabs ca co sgrogs 'di ma bzlog na //
NK117(she)001:18744: lha bas lhag pa'i lus rten chu lon yang //
NK117(she)001:18745: brtan pa bral ba'i mya ngam thang du 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:18746: zhes pa ni de phyir zhes 'khor ba spyi dang
NK117(she)001:18747: sgos ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las bzlog pa'i
NK117(she)001:18748: ched du / skye ba'i sdug bsngal la shwa 'od
NK117(she)001:18749: de chu log lta bu dang de'i dba' rlabs kyi
NK117(she)001:18750: ca co sgrogs pa lta bu'i skyon can 'di tsho
NK117(she)001:18751: 'dir bzlog ma nus na lha bas lhag pa'i mi
NK117(she)001:18752: lus chu lon lta bu 'di glo bur du bshigs
NK117(she)001:18753: nas srid par yang yang skye ba la brtan pa
NK117(she)001:18754: bral bzhin rang dbang med par gsha' chu mya ngam
NK117(she)001:18755: gyi thang du 'khyams pa lta bur 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:18757: gzugs med ting 'dzin lung ma bstan pa'i las //
NK117(she)001:18758: zad nas srid pa phyi mar 'du byed dang //
NK117(she)001:18759: gzugs khams bsam gtan snga ma'i las zad de //
NK117(she)001:18760: 'og mar ltung ba 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal myong //
NK117(she)001:18761: zhes pa ni gzugs med pa rnams der skye ba'i
NK117(she)001:18762: las zad pa dang zhi gnas kyi ting 'dzin las
NK117(she)001:18763: sad pa chabs gcig pas phyi ma'i sdug bsngal 'du
NK117(she)001:18765: gzugs khams pa rnams kyang der skye ba'i rgyu bsam
NK117(she)001:18766: gtan gyi bde ba de 'gyur nas srid pa phyi
NK117(she)001:18767: mar ltung ba'i sdug bsngal la spyod dgos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18769: tshangs dang lha dbang 'khor los sgyur ba yang //
NK117(she)001:18770: sprin bar nyi bzhin dkar po'i rnam smin gyis //
NK117(she)001:18771: skabs btsal spangs pa'i mod la mar me'i lces //
NK117(she)001:18772: 'thungs pa'i zhun mar bzhin du nyams par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:18773: zhes pa ni gzugs khams kyi gtso bo lha chen
NK117(she)001:18774: tshangs pa chags bral gyi bde ba thob pa dang
NK117(she)001:18775: / 'dod khams kyi gtso bo koo shi ka dpal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18776: mi'i gtso bo 'khor los bsgyur ba rin po che
NK117(she)001:18777: sna bdun dang dpung tshogs yan lag bzhi dang lhan
NK117(she)001:18778: cig gling bzhi la dbang bsgyur ba sogs de dag
NK117(she)001:18779: thams cad kyang lus rten de lta bu ni /
NK117(she)001:18780: sprin bar gyi nyi ma bzhin thob pa yang dkar
NK117(she)001:18781: po'i rnam smin gyis bde ba'i skabs cung zad btsal
NK117(she)001:18782: nas rnyed pa de yang gnyid sad pa ji bzhin
NK117(she)001:18783: bde skyid spangs pa'i mod la der skye ba'i rgyu
NK117(she)001:18784: mar me'i lces 'thungs pa'i mar khu bzhin du zad
NK117(she)001:18787: mnan na nem pa'i reg pa 'jam po dang //
NK117(she)001:18788: lha klu mi'am ci yi la thod kyis //
NK117(she)001:18789: rkang pa'i chu skyes dmar byas dbang po yang //
NK117(she)001:18790: lcags kyi gsal shing 'bar ba'i rtse mor gdungs //
NK117(she)001:18791: zhes pa ni grong khyer blta na sdug gi sa
NK117(she)001:18792: gzhi mnan na nem zhing btegs na mtho bar byed
NK117(she)001:18793: pa'i gzhi la rkang pa bzhag na reg pa shin
NK117(she)001:18795: sum cu rtsa gsum pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18797: mi'am ci la sogs kyi mgo bo'i rgyan nor bu
NK117(she)001:18798: dang bcas te brgya byin gyi zhabs la gtugs tshe
NK117(she)001:18799: rkang pa'i chu skyes kyang dmar por 'gyur ba'i stobs
NK117(she)001:18800: thob pa'i khengs dregs can de yang dmyal ba'i gnas
NK117(she)001:18803: mtho ris bu mo'i nu ma gsar pa la //
NK117(she)001:18804: reg pa'i 'khri shing bsten de dga' tshal dang //
NK117(she)001:18805: gzhal med khang mdzes mu tig d+r+wa phyed can //
NK117(she)001:18806: spangs nas me mur 'obs nang spyi'u tshugs ltung //
NK117(she)001:18807: zhes pa ni 'di ltar matshe'u dal gyis 'bab par
NK117(she)001:18808: lha'i bu mo rnams kyi nu ma la reg pa'i
NK117(she)001:18809: bde ba nyams su myong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:18810: dga' ba'i tshal du bza' btung gos rgyan rol mo'i
NK117(she)001:18811: bye brag sna tshogs dang gnas khang rgyan bkod rnams
NK117(she)001:18812: phun sum tshogs par gyur kyang de dag nyams su
NK117(she)001:18813: myong ba'i rnam dkar gyi las de zad ma thag
NK117(she)001:18814: tu me ma mur gyi 'obs sogs su sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:18817: gos stan me tog rnyings pa'i lha mo dag /
NK117(she)001:18818: rdul gyis gdong pa bkru ba'i zol zhig nas //
NK117(she)001:18819: nye du rnams la blta zhing ngu ba yi //
NK117(she)001:18820: 'chi 'pho'i sdug bsngal lta bu mi la med //
NK117(she)001:18821: ces pa ni 'di ltar gzhan 'phrul dbang byed man
NK117(she)001:18822: chad srog la chags pa'i nyes pa yod kyang gnad
NK117(she)001:18823: 'chad pa'i sdug bsngal ni yod pa ma yin mod
NK117(she)001:18824: / 'on kyang 'chi 'pho ba'i snga ltas rnams byung nas sdug bsngal myong dgos pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:18825: gos stan dang me tog gi rgyan rnams rnying zhing
NK117(she)001:18826: dri ma chags pa sogs 'chi ba'i rtags byung ba'i
NK117(she)001:18827: lha mo dag sems kyi dpa' zhum zhing rdul dreg
NK117(she)001:18828: gis gdong g.yogs pa yang sngar ltar bkru ba'i zol
NK117(she)001:18829: zhig nas rang gi mdza' mthun gyi yul du gyur
NK117(she)001:18830: pa nye du rnams la blta zhing ngu ba yi
NK117(she)001:18831: sdug bsngal de lta bu mi la med ces pa'o
NK117(she)001:18833: gnya' shing 'dzin ri'i sa bla 'gegs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:18834: gdugs gyur snang byed chen po nyi zla gnyis //
NK117(she)001:18835: slan chad mun pa'i smag gi btson ra ru //
NK117(she)001:18836: long ba chen po'i gnas skabs 'thob par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:18837: zhes pa ni ri gnya' shing 'dzin gyi sa bla
NK117(she)001:18838: ste nam mkhar gdugs ltar gyur nas 'jig rten gyi
NK117(she)001:18839: mun pa bsal nus pa'i snang byed chen po nyi
NK117(she)001:18840: zla gnyis po'i rten me shel dang chu shel gnyis
NK117(she)001:18841: kyi gzhal med khang pa 'od kyi rang bzhin de
NK117(she)001:18842: yang ji zhig na brten pa lha'i bu gnyis po
NK117(she)001:18843: spangs nas 'jig rten gyi mun pa'i smag rum du
NK117(she)001:18844: lhungs nas srid pa'i gnas 'di long bar gyur te
NK117(she)001:18845: ci yang mi mthong ba'i gnas skabs thob par 'gyur
NK117(she)001:18847: lha yi dpal la sdang ba'i phrag dog gi //
NK117(she)001:18848: dgra s+t+was rang snying tshal bar bkas nas slar //
NK117(she)001:18849: dpung pa gtum po'i g.yul ngor bdag nyid kyi //
NK117(she)001:18850: mgo dang yan lag gtubs pas lha min mnar //
NK117(she)001:18851: zhes pa ni 'di ltar lha min ni rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:18852: gyis nga rgyal che ba'i khar lha'i dpal la sdang
NK117(she)001:18853: ba'i phrag dog dang 'dzam bu'i gling pa rnams mi
NK117(she)001:18854: dge ba stobs chen bsags pa'i skyon dang lha dag
NK117(she)001:18855: lha min gyi bu mor blta dogs dang /
NK117(she)001:18856: lha min rnams lha'i bdud rtsi la chags pa'i dbang
NK117(she)001:18857: gis dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i dpal dang longs spyod
NK117(she)001:18858: lhas dbang zhing rtsa ba lha min yul du yod
NK117(she)001:18859: pa don med do snyam nas s+t+wa res gcod par
NK117(she)001:18860: rtsom pa la rtsod pa 'byung ba yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:18861: de lta bu'i rtsod yul la thob shor gyi re
NK117(she)001:18862: dogs kyis dgra s+t+was rang snying tshal par bkas pa
NK117(she)001:18863: lta bu'i khong khro'i zug rngu bzod glags med pa
NK117(she)001:18864: byung nas slar lha'i dmag dpung gtum po'i g.yul ngor
NK117(she)001:18865: zhugs te mgo dang yan lag bcad gtubs bgyis pas
NK117(she)001:18866: lha min mnar zhing sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:18867: de'i tshe lha rnams mgo chad pa ma gtogs mi
NK117(she)001:18868: 'chi zhing lha min ni mi bzhin gnad du phog
NK117(she)001:18870: sgra gcan dud 'gro yin pas mig gis nyi zla'i
NK117(she)001:18871: bkrag mi bzod cing lag pas sgrib par bshad pa
NK117(she)001:18872: dang dus 'khor nas gdong mjug gis bsgrib par du
NK117(she)001:18873: me 'jug pa zhes dang gzhung la lar khas zos
NK117(she)001:18874: pa ol bar thon pa yang bshad do //
NK117(she)001:18875: de dus dge sdig gang byas kyang zla bar 'bum 'gyur dang /
NK117(she)001:18876: nyi mar bye ba'i 'gyur yod par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:18877: sa g.yo ba yang byang chub sems dpa' sa nas sar 'phar ba'am /
NK117(she)001:18878: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pas 'jig rten du cho 'phrul mdzad dam /
NK117(she)001:18879: mi dge ba'i las rlabs po che las byung ba'am /
NK117(she)001:18880: nya bo che 'gre ldog byas pa'i skyon nam /
NK117(she)001:18881: yang na lha min dbang po thags bzang ris khros
NK117(she)001:18882: nas lha la g.yul 'gyed pa'i ched du gser gyi
NK117(she)001:18883: sa gzhi la rkang pa brdab pa'i skyon yin pa
NK117(she)001:18884: sogs ma nges par bshad pa yang yad do //
NK117(she)001:18886: 'tsho ba chu bur lta bur g.yo ba yi //
NK117(she)001:18887: mi dag yid mi bde dang 'khrugs pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:18888: sdug bsngal snga mas phyi ma nye bar len //
NK117(she)001:18889: mdze can phol gyi thog tu rmas gtugs bzhin //
NK117(she)001:18890: zhes pa ni 'di ltar tshe'i snyigs ma chu bur
NK117(she)001:18891: ltar mi rtag cing g.yo bas mi dag yid mi
NK117(she)001:18892: bde ba dang 'khrugs pa la sogs kyis sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:18893: ba de yang snga ma ma sangs steng du gcig
NK117(she)001:18894: thog tu gnyis snon lta bu'i phyi ma yang nye
NK117(she)001:18895: bar len zhing / mdze nad yod pa'i thog tu phol mig gi rmas gtugs pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:18897: mngon mtho'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i skyed tshal du //
NK117(she)001:18898: 'dod pa'i ro la gdung ba dug can gyi //
NK117(she)001:18899: bza' bas rnam par sma bab dka' thub lus //
NK117(she)001:18900: mig 'phrul lta bur thob 'di 'gyur ba can //
NK117(she)001:18901: zhes pa ni skyes bu gang zhig mngon mtho'i dpal
NK117(she)001:18902: yon rdzogs pa'i gnas su bde skyid kyi longs spyod
NK117(she)001:18903: la rol tshe 'dod pa'i ro la gdung ba che
NK117(she)001:18904: skyon gyis dug ldan gyi bza' btung la spyod pas
NK117(she)001:18905: rnam par sma bab pa'i dka' thub kyis lus rid
NK117(she)001:18906: cing mig 'phrul lta bur skad cig gis thob pa
NK117(she)001:18907: 'di 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal gyi chos can no //
NK117(she)001:18909: rkang pa'i reg pa khur du mi bzod pa'i //
NK117(she)001:18910: ngal bcas sems kyis glang po'i gnyar 'dzegs kyang //
NK117(she)001:18911: de yi bsam pa rtse dgas rgod gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:18912: g.yang sar smad pa 'du byed sdug bsngal mtshon //
NK117(she)001:18913: zhes pa ni 'di ni skyes rabs kyi gtam rgyud dang sbyar na /
NK117(she)001:18914: 'od ldan zhes pa'i rgyal khab tu rgyal po rab
NK117(she)001:18915: gsal zhes pa glang chen zhon par spro ba skyes
NK117(she)001:18916: nas 'dul sbyong mkhan la glang po che 'dul bar
NK117(she)001:18917: bsgos pas de'i rgyal po'i bka' phebs bzhin btul bas
NK117(she)001:18918: lus thul nas lcags kyi tho lum me 'bar ba'am
NK117(she)001:18919: snas tsham tshom med par len pa'i bar btul kyang
NK117(she)001:18920: / sems nyon mongs pa dang bcas pa btul ma
NK117(she)001:18921: nus bzhin rje 'bangs gnyis glang chen zhon nas yul
NK117(she)001:18922: nye bar spyod pa'i skyo sangs la phyin pas na
NK117(she)001:18923: glang mo'i dri bser bus khyer ba glang po che
NK117(she)001:18924: dri 'dzin gyi sgor phog pa tsam gyis yid rtse
NK117(she)001:18925: dgas rab tu rgod par gyur nas myur bar rgyug
NK117(she)001:18926: pas rgyal po rab gsal srog dang bral bar nye
NK117(she)001:18927: ba lta bu ni khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug
NK117(she)001:18928: bsngal sems can kun la yod kyang mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:18929: bltar mi mngon par lus dang grib ma ltar 'grogs
NK117(she)001:18932: de ltar sdug bsngal nyid gsum 'brog dgon na //
NK117(she)001:18933: skye rga na 'chi'i tshor ba rnam par 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:18934: smon pa med pa'i mi sdug dgra dang phrad //
NK117(she)001:18935: sdug pa yid la goms byas gnas min phyogs //
NK117(she)001:18936: 'dod pa'i yul la 'byor pas ngo tshar byas //
NK117(she)001:18937: nyer len phung po'i steng du dka' thub 'dus //
NK117(she)001:18938: rnam pa brgyad kyi sdug bsngal rtul phod pas //
NK117(she)001:18939: mi yi skye ba'i 'khri shing rtag tu gtser //
NK117(she)001:18940: zhes pa ni sdug bsngal nyid gsum ni sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal /
NK117(she)001:18942: khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal gsum ni 'brog
NK117(she)001:18943: dgon pa srog la ya nga ba'i gnas lta bur
NK117(she)001:18944: skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba rnam
NK117(she)001:18945: par 'khyams pa ni de'i ngang du lus pa'o //
NK117(she)001:18946: de'i tshe 'phral du smon pa med pa'i mi sdug pa'i dgra dang thug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:18947: mdza' zhing mthun pa sdug pa yid la bcags shing
NK117(she)001:18948: goms par byas pa gnas min zhes phyi ma'i lam
NK117(she)001:18949: du phyogs pa / yid la gang 'dod pa'i yul
NK117(she)001:18950: mthun rkyen gyi rigs 'byor pas ngo tsha byas nas
NK117(she)001:18952: mi 'dod pa'i rkyen ma bsgrubs kyang dbang med du thog tu 'bab pa /
NK117(she)001:18953: de lta bu sdug bsngal nye bar len pa po
NK117(she)001:18954: phung po lnga kho na las gzhan med pas de'i
NK117(she)001:18955: steng du dka' thub 'dus pa yang /
NK117(she)001:18956: rnam pa brgyad kyi sdug bsngal rtul phod pa zhes
NK117(she)001:18957: 'gro rnams mnar ba la shin tu dpa' bas mi
NK117(she)001:18958: yi skye ba'i ljon pa la gtser ba'i sems kyi
NK117(she)001:18959: 'khri shing rtag tu gtser zhes sdug bsngal bar byas
NK117(she)001:18961: shin tu dri nga mi gtsang rnyog ma can //
NK117(she)001:18962: kun nas dog pa mun nag 'thibs po'i khrod //
NK117(she)001:18963: mngal gnas lcags khyim sgo 'phar spangs lta'i nang //
NK117(she)001:18964: ma rig rnam shes khu khrag dbus na brten //
NK117(she)001:18965: zhes mngal gyi rang bzhin ni dri nga ba dang
NK117(she)001:18966: mi gtsang ba'i khrod lcags khyim sgo 'phar spangs pa
NK117(she)001:18967: lta bu'i nang du bar do'i dri za nye bar
NK117(she)001:18968: 'jug pa'i rnam shes rig bral de rlung sems kyi
NK117(she)001:18969: chas khur nas pha ma'i khu khrag gi dbus na
NK117(she)001:18971: mer mer nur nur ltar ltar mkhrang gor nya //
NK117(she)001:18972: rus sbal bzhin te bdun phrag bdun rtsa drug /
NK117(she)001:18973: gnas 'gyur yid mi 'ong ba'i rnam pa la //
NK117(she)001:18974: dbang po yan lag ba spu la sogs 'grub //
NK117(she)001:18975: bdun phrag sum cu rtsa bdun grangs snyed tshe //
NK117(she)001:18976: brtas dang cher bskyed g.yo zhing tshor bas gdungs //
NK117(she)001:18977: ma yi spyod lam bkres skom tsha grang gis //
NK117(she)001:18978: rnam 'gyur las byung sdug bsngal dpag tu med //
NK117(she)001:18979: btsa' ba'i dus kyi rjes 'gro de yi lus //
NK117(she)001:18980: bzod daka'i bsdus 'joms khur du 'phos pa lta'i //
NK117(she)001:18981: sdug bsngal nye bar len pas mtho btsams nas //
NK117(she)001:18982: ma bu gnyis ka mod la srog 'dor ram //
NK117(she)001:18983: gcig shos gnod pa bdo ba'i khur gyis btsa' //
NK117(she)001:18984: mngal gnas rlon pas dkris shing dri nga ba //
NK117(she)001:18985: sran mi bzod pa sha rmen zhig pa ltas //
NK117(she)001:18986: sngon gyi dran pa'i stobs rnams nyams byas shing //
NK117(she)001:18987: reg pa'i gnod pas gzir ba'i sdug bsngal myong //
NK117(she)001:18988: zhes pa ni mngal du zhugs pa'i bdun phrag dang por mer mer po dngul chu lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:18989: gnyis pa nur nur po snabs lta bu /
NK117(she)001:18990: gsum pa ltar ltar po mdzub mo lta bu /
NK117(she)001:18991: bzhi pa mkhrang gyur sgo nga lta bu /
NK117(she)001:18992: lnga pa gor gor po khur ba lta bu /
NK117(she)001:18993: drug pa khyab 'jug nya'i rnam pa lta bu /
NK117(she)001:18994: bdun par rus sbal ltar mgo dang rkang lag cung
NK117(she)001:18995: zad mngon zhing de nas bdun phrag brgyad dang dgu
NK117(she)001:18996: dang bcu nas rim bzhin brtsis pa'i bdun phrag nyi
NK117(she)001:18997: shu rtsa drug gi bar du lus phyi nang yan
NK117(she)001:18998: lag dang sor mo ba spu sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:18999: nang gi don snod dbang sgo la sogs pa'i lus
NK117(she)001:19000: kyi cha yongs su rdzogs kyang khams kyi zas spyod
NK117(she)001:19001: du med pas gshang gci yang med bzhin gong gi
NK117(she)001:19002: 'phror brtsis pas bdun phrag nyer bdun nas sum cu
NK117(she)001:19003: rtsa drug gi bar du mas zas skom la spyod
NK117(she)001:19004: pa'i dwangs mas bu 'tsho bar byed cing bdun phrag
NK117(she)001:19005: sum cu rtsa bdun pa la mngal gyi gnas de
NK117(she)001:19006: nyid la mun nag gi snang ba sogs skyon gyi
NK117(she)001:19007: rnam pa gang yod mngon du gyur nas mi gtsang
NK117(she)001:19008: ba dang / dri mi zhim pa /
NK117(she)001:19011: phyir 'byung ba bcas 'du shes lngar shar bzhin bdun
NK117(she)001:19012: phrag sum cu rtsa brgyad 'das tshe btsa' ba'i dus
NK117(she)001:19013: la bab ste las kyi rlung gis mgo mjug ldog
NK117(she)001:19015: de yang bu rnams ni ma'i mngal gyi g.yas nas
NK117(she)001:19016: kha nang du bltas te thal mo gnyis kyis gdong
NK117(she)001:19018: bu mo g.yon nas kha phyir bltas kyi de bzhin du gnas shing /
NK117(she)001:19019: rtags kyi sgo nas 'jog tshe ma'i gru g.yas mtho
NK117(she)001:19020: zhing nu zho g.yas pa snga bar babs na bu
NK117(she)001:19021: dang / de nyid go ldog na bu mo yin par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:19023: rga bas chad pas non pa'i lang tsho la //
NK117(she)001:19024: nyams dang yid mi bde ba'i khur bab pas //
NK117(she)001:19025: bskyod pa'i mthu nyams 'khar ba'i gzhan dbang can //
NK117(she)001:19026: 'gro ldog g.yo ba'i lhu tshigs rnam par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:19027: dbang po rgud pas 'dod pa'i yon tan dang //
NK117(she)001:19028: yul gyi longs spyod sprin gyi bkab pa yi //
NK117(she)001:19029: tsha zer bzhin du rmongs dang mthu nyams pa'i //
NK117(she)001:19030: 'du shes 'khrugs pa'i mal du shin tu 'khyam //
NK117(she)001:19031: zhes pa ni gzhon nu'i lang tsho ni rim bzhin
NK117(she)001:19032: rgas pa'i chad pas non zhing lus stobs dang dbang
NK117(she)001:19033: po rnams nyams pas 'dod yon lnga la spyod pa'i
NK117(she)001:19034: stobs zad cing lus dang yan lag bskyod pa'i mthu
NK117(she)001:19035: nyams shing 'khar ba'i gzhan dbang can du gyur pas
NK117(she)001:19036: 'gro ldog sogs g.yo 'gul byed pa'i lhu tshigs kyang
NK117(she)001:19037: rnam par 'gyur zhing dbang po rgud pas 'dod yon
NK117(she)001:19038: dang yul lnga'i longs spyod sprin gyis bkab pa'i tsha
NK117(she)001:19039: zer bzhin du rmongs shing spyod pa'i mthu nyams pas
NK117(she)001:19040: 'du shes rnal du mi phebs bzhin rab tu 'khrugs
NK117(she)001:19041: pa'i mal du shin tu 'khyams nas sdug bsngal la
NK117(she)001:19043: rang bzhin snyoms ldan 'du ba'i rdzing bu ni //
NK117(she)001:19044: rnyog pa can bgyid na ba'i tshor ba yis //
NK117(she)001:19045: phung po lnga yi nyer len dub byas te //
NK117(she)001:19046: 'tsho ba'i brtan pa bral ba'i dogs pas skrag /
NK117(she)001:19047: ces pa ni 'di ltar lus can spyi la rlung
NK117(she)001:19048: mkhris bad dkan sogs rang bzhin snyoms par ldan tshe
NK117(she)001:19049: 'du ba'i rdzing bu rnyog pa can bgyid pa'i na
NK117(she)001:19050: ba'i tshor ba rtsub mos gzugs tshor 'du shes 'du
NK117(she)001:19051: byed rnam shes kyi phung po ste de dag gi
NK117(she)001:19052: so so'i nye bar len pa dub par byas te
NK117(she)001:19053: gdung bas 'tsho ba'i brtan pa bral zhing 'chi bar
NK117(she)001:19054: dogs pas skrag par byed do //
NK117(she)001:19056: srid pa 'di na srog gi rin thang la //
NK117(she)001:19057: thug pa med pas 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal gyis //
NK117(she)001:19058: rnam par gtugs pa'i skyes bu gnyen 'dun dang //
NK117(she)001:19059: longs spyod las thal sa tshugs med par 'gro //
NK117(she)001:19060: zhes pa ni 'jig rten 'di na srog gi rin
NK117(she)001:19061: thang la thug pa med kyang 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:19062: gyis rnam par gtugs pa'i skyes bu 'chi la babs
NK117(she)001:19063: pa gang zhig gnyen nye du 'dun grogs longs spyod
NK117(she)001:19064: kun las brgal zhing sa tshugs med pa'i gnas su
NK117(she)001:19068: mi sdug yul dang phrad pa'i sdug bsngal gyis //
NK117(she)001:19069: pho nyas rnam par gzir zhing smad pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:19070: bde ba'i 'bab stegs zhig pa'i ngal gso ltar //
NK117(she)001:19071: dbugs 'byin thob pa med pas lhag par nyen //
NK117(she)001:19072: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dgra mi sdug pa'i yul
NK117(she)001:19073: dang 'phrad pa'i sdug bsngal gyi pho nya ste log
NK117(she)001:19074: sbyor gyis rnam par gzir zhing smad pa'i yul du
NK117(she)001:19075: gyur pa rnams ni khur lci bas dub pa gang
NK117(she)001:19076: zhig ngal gso ba'i 'bab stegs la gnas skabs zhig
NK117(she)001:19077: nas bde ba'i dbugs 'byin thob pa med pas lhag
NK117(she)001:19080: byams sdug 'du 'bral gsar par bkod pa yi //
NK117(she)001:19081: gdung bas nyams pa'i dka' thub gzugs gyur na //
NK117(she)001:19082: nor bzang dri za mo yi dbang gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:19083: lam phrang 'tshe bas bkab las las mtha' ring //
NK117(she)001:19084: zhes pa ni yid la sdug pa'i mdza' bshes dang
NK117(she)001:19085: bral ba gang zhig de'i yon tan dang spyod lam
NK117(she)001:19086: dang / rnam 'gyur dran nas sems gdung ba'i dpe
NK117(she)001:19087: gzhon nu nor bzang dri za'i bu mor bral tshe
NK117(she)001:19088: lam 'phrang 'tshe ba can bgrod pa las kyang dka'
NK117(she)001:19089: zhing las mtha' ring ba nyid do //
NK117(she)001:19092: sngon gyi dus yul lnga len zhes par grong khyer
NK117(she)001:19093: glang po'i khyim gyi rgyal srid kyi bdag por rgyal
NK117(she)001:19094: po nor can zer ba bu med pa zhig yod
NK117(she)001:19095: pa des 'jig rten lha la gsol ba btab 'bras
NK117(she)001:19096: kyis bu zhig yod pa de nyid legs par bskyed
NK117(she)001:19097: bsrings nas ming nor bzang du btags so //
NK117(she)001:19098: des kyang 'jig rten lugs kyi bstan bcos dang rig
NK117(she)001:19099: gnas kun la byang bar byas te chung ma gsum
NK117(she)001:19101: skabs zhig tu rngon pa spang leb can ri dwags
NK117(she)001:19102: bshor ba zhig ri bo gzhan zhig tu phyin pa
NK117(she)001:19103: na lo ma dang myu gu dang me tog dang
NK117(she)001:19104: 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa'i bsti gnas zhig na
NK117(she)001:19105: drang srong dka' thub la gnas pa zhig bzhugs pa
NK117(she)001:19106: mthong ba dang phyag byas te dris pa /
NK117(she)001:19107: khyed 'dir bzhugs nas ci tsam yin zhus pas /
NK117(she)001:19109: khyod yun ring de srid du 'dir sdod ring la ngo mtshar ba'i chos 'ga' gzigs lags sam /
NK117(she)001:19111: drang srong gis rngon pa la khyod kyis mtsho ma
NK117(she)001:19112: gi mthong ngam dris pas des mthong lags zer bar
NK117(she)001:19113: / drang srong gis 'di ni tshangs pa 'du ba'i rdzing zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:19115: chu bya sna tshogs yod pa /
NK117(she)001:19116: dri zhim pa'i me tog du mas bskor ba'i chu
NK117(she)001:19117: rdzing 'dir tshes bco lnga'i nyin mi'am ci'i rgyal po
NK117(she)001:19118: ljon pa'i bu mo yid 'phrog ma bu mo lnga
NK117(she)001:19119: brgyas bskor nas 'ongs te khrus dang bsku mnyes sna
NK117(she)001:19120: tshogs byed cing glu gar bro dang rol mo sna
NK117(she)001:19121: tshogs kyis yid 'phrog par byed do //
NK117(she)001:19122: kho bo'ang de'i sgra thos pas dga' ba dang yid
NK117(she)001:19123: bde ba chen po skyes nas zhag bdun 'da' nus
NK117(she)001:19124: pas ngo mtshar ba de 'dra mthong ngo //
NK117(she)001:19126: rngon pa des klu las don yod zhags pa thob
NK117(she)001:19127: pa des yid 'phrog ma bzung snyam nas tshes bco
NK117(she)001:19128: lnga'i dus la bab tshe mtsho 'gram du 'khris nas
NK117(she)001:19130: ji zhig na yid 'phrog ma 'khor bcas byung nas
NK117(she)001:19131: khrus kyi bya ba la 'jug par rtsoms tshe rngon
NK117(she)001:19132: pas don yod zhags pas bzung ba dang 'khor rnams
NK117(she)001:19133: bros so // der mos rngon pa la ma rabs
NK117(she)001:19134: khyod kyis nga la ma reg cig zer bas rngon
NK117(she)001:19135: pas mo 'bros par dogs pa dang mo'i gtsug gi
NK117(she)001:19136: nor bu bkrol te rngon par gtad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19137: de'i tshe gzhon nu nor bzang yang ri dwags bshor bar der slebs pa dang 'phrad tshe /
NK117(she)001:19138: rngon pas bu mo 'di gzhon nu 'di la 'os
NK117(she)001:19139: so snyam nas phul bas gzhon nus brtags par bud
NK117(she)001:19140: med kyi skyon thams cad dang bral zhing yon tan
NK117(she)001:19141: kun tshang ba thugs su chud de /
NK117(she)001:19142: yid 'phrog ma rgyan dang bcas pa bzhes te glang
NK117(she)001:19143: po'i khyim gyi grong khyer du phyin nas pho brang
NK117(she)001:19144: gi rtse'i khang bzang zhig tu dga' mgur spyod cing
NK117(she)001:19145: gnas so // de'i dus na bram ze gnyis ljongs rgyu ba la 'ongs tshe /
NK117(she)001:19147: gcig shos nor bzang la rten bcas shing /
NK117(she)001:19148: rgyal po'i mdun na 'don byed du bcug cing longs spyod kyi skal ba yang byin /
NK117(she)001:19149: rgyal bus longs spyod kyi skal ba tsam zhig byin pa dang des smras pa /
NK117(she)001:19150: gzhon nu nyid rgyal sar bzhugs tshe nga la ci zhig bgyi zhus pas /
NK117(she)001:19151: de ltar na khyod kyi grogs por yab kyis bgyi ba ji bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:19152: zhes gsungs pa yab rgyal po'i mdun na 'don de'i
NK117(she)001:19153: thos tshe phrag dog skyes nas gzhon nu rgyal srid
NK117(she)001:19154: mi thob pa'i thabs bsam pa la /
NK117(she)001:19155: yul gzhan gyi ri bor ba zhes chom pos yul
NK117(she)001:19156: der gnod 'tshe byed pa zhig yod pa la de
NK117(she)001:19157: brlag pa'i ched du dmag gi dpung chen po zhig
NK117(she)001:19158: chas na rgyal bu yang dmag dpon du btang thabs
NK117(she)001:19159: byas na de nas phyir ldog mi thub snyams nas
NK117(she)001:19160: rgyal po la g.yo thabs kyis de tshul zhus par
NK117(she)001:19161: rgyal pos de bzhin du bya'o zhes gzhon nu mdun
NK117(she)001:19162: du bos nas de bzhin bsgos pas des kyang khas
NK117(she)001:19163: blangs nas 'gro grab la zhugs tshe yid 'phrog ma
NK117(she)001:19164: yid la bcags te 'phrad tsam byas nas mo'i gtsug
NK117(she)001:19165: rgyan gyi nor bu rgyal bu'i ma la bcol nas
NK117(she)001:19166: gal te yid 'phrog ma'i srog gi nyen pa'i gal
NK117(she)001:19168: de min na ma byin zer nas dpung tshogs yan
NK117(she)001:19169: lag bzhi'i dmag dpung khrid nas phyin pas rgyal bu'i
NK117(she)001:19170: bsod nams kyi mthu las rgyal chen rnam thos sras
NK117(she)001:19171: kyis grogs bgyid pa'i thugs bskyed nas gnod sbyin gyi
NK117(she)001:19172: sde dpon lnga len la khyod kyi dmag dpung khrid
NK117(she)001:19173: la ri bor ba rnams phob cig ces bsgos pa
NK117(she)001:19174: bzhin du / de rnams cham la phab nas las sna ba bskos te /
NK117(she)001:19176: gate'u yang bzung ste dmag dpung phyir log tshe /
NK117(she)001:19177: rgyal po nor can gyi rmi lam na bya rgod gcig 'ongs te /
NK117(she)001:19178: rgyal po'i lto dral nas rgyu ma drangs shing grong
NK117(she)001:19179: khyer gyi mtha' bskor ba dang rin po che sna
NK117(she)001:19180: bdun gyis khyim bkang ba rmis so //
NK117(she)001:19181: der rgyal po shin tu skrag cing 'jigs nas bram ze 'dun na 'don la de tshul bshad pas /
NK117(she)001:19182: des rmi lam de ni rgyal srid las nyams pa'am
NK117(she)001:19183: sku tshe bar chod kyi ltas su nges so zhus
NK117(she)001:19184: pas rgyal pos de bzlog thabs bdog gam zer bar
NK117(she)001:19185: / bram zes bzlog thabs nus dang mi nus mang
NK117(she)001:19186: rabs las khyad par mi ma yin gyi tshil bdug
NK117(she)001:19187: na rgyal po skyon las grol zhes g.yo zol gyis
NK117(she)001:19189: rgyal po de bzhin sgrub rgyu byas nas gzhan rnams
NK117(she)001:19190: grub pa dang mi ma yin gyi tshil bu'i ched
NK117(she)001:19191: du yid 'phrog ma gsod rgyur bos tshe gzhon nu
NK117(she)001:19192: ma la gtsug nor bcol ba gtod de bros shig
NK117(she)001:19193: ces bsgos pas de ma thag tu nam mkha' la
NK117(she)001:19194: 'phur te bros nas sngon gyi bram ze de'i gam
NK117(she)001:19195: du phyin nas khyod kyis bdag bstan pas mi lag
NK117(she)001:19196: tu song yang srog dang ma bral tsam du thar
NK117(she)001:19197: byung bas / nga'i rjes su gzhon nu nor bzang
NK117(she)001:19198: slebs byung na sor gdub 'di gtod la kho mo'i
NK117(she)001:19199: rjes su lam bgrod par dka' bas ma longs shig
NK117(she)001:19200: byung bas / / gal te ldog ma nus na
NK117(she)001:19201: gtam 'di rnams zlos shig ces bram zer smras nas
NK117(she)001:19203: de nas gzhon nu rang yul du slebs tshe yid
NK117(she)001:19204: 'phrog ma bros pas gtam de go nas kun nas
NK117(she)001:19205: kun tu rgyu zhing tshol ba na bram ze des
NK117(she)001:19207: mo'i rjes su 'ongs na bgrod dka' tshul shod la phyir ldog thabs gyis /
NK117(she)001:19208: gal te nan gyis ma ldog na gtam 'di rnams zlos byas pa bram zes smreng ba /
NK117(she)001:19209: ri'i rgyal po gangs can na shin tu 'o ma
NK117(she)001:19210: 'dzag ces pa'i sman yod pas de mar du bcos
NK117(she)001:19211: nas btung na skom pa dang bkres pa med cing
NK117(she)001:19212: dran pa dang mthu stobs 'phel lo //
NK117(she)001:19219: pi wang bcas bcang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:19221: lam 'phrang gi 'jigs pa chen po so so la
NK117(she)001:19222: 'di dang 'di dgos kyi bslab bya rnams bsnyad do
NK117(she)001:19223: // de nas bram zes bshol kyang ma nyan nas
NK117(she)001:19224: yid 'phrog mas bslab pa'i chas rnams thogs te bshul
NK117(she)001:19225: lam rim bgrod kyis ri dang chu bo dang /
NK117(she)001:19227: g.yang sa sogs 'jigs pa'i yul thams cad la sman dang gsang sngags dang /
NK117(she)001:19228: sman dug gsal gyi sbyor bas rgyal bar byas nas
NK117(she)001:19229: mi'am ci'i rgyal po'i grong khyer nye bar phyin pa
NK117(she)001:19230: dang / der khrus kyi rdzing bu dpal yon gyis
NK117(she)001:19231: brgyan par mi'am ci mo rnams chu len du 'ongs
NK117(she)001:19232: par gzhon nus chu mang po 'dis ci byed dris
NK117(she)001:19233: par yid 'phrog ma'i khrus chu yin par zer byung
NK117(she)001:19234: bar gzhon nus sngon gyi sor gdub de bum pa
NK117(she)001:19235: zhig tu mi mthong bar bcug nas bum pa 'dis
NK117(she)001:19236: sngon du khrus gyis zhes bsgos pas des kyang de
NK117(she)001:19237: la don gcig yod snyam nas khrus bgyis pas ji
NK117(she)001:19238: zhig na sor gdub lhung bas 'phrigs nas /
NK117(she)001:19239: chu blangs sar mi zhig 'ongs sam dris pas 'ongs zer /
NK117(she)001:19240: de khrid la dben pa zhig tu zhog zer ba ltar byas so //
NK117(she)001:19241: der yid 'phrog mas yab la zhu ba sna tshogs
NK117(she)001:19242: phul mthar yab kyis gzhon nu'i tshod bgams nas nyams
NK117(she)001:19243: sad pa'i las mang po byas kyang de rnams las
NK117(she)001:19244: rgyal mthar yid 'phrog ma 'khor stong gis bskor ba
NK117(she)001:19245: rgyan yongs kyis spud nas rin po che'i skyes dang
NK117(she)001:19246: bcas te gzhon nur byin nas yul der re zhig
NK117(she)001:19247: bzhugs 'jags gnang mthar mi'am ci'i rgyal po dang bgros
NK117(she)001:19248: te nam mkha'i lam nas mi'am ci'i shugs kyis bskyod
NK117(she)001:19249: nas glang po'i khyim gyi grong khyer du slebs so
NK117(she)001:19250: // der ngal sos pa dang yab rgyal po'i drung
NK117(she)001:19251: du phyin nas de lta'i lo rgyus rnams zhib tu
NK117(she)001:19252: zhus pas rab tu mnyes nas gzhon nu rgyal sar
NK117(she)001:19253: bkod pa dang gzhon nus sngon bsod nams bsags pa'i
NK117(she)001:19254: stobs kyis de ltar byung ba yin par shes nas
NK117(she)001:19255: lo bcu gnyis su gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin
NK117(she)001:19257: de lta bas na skyes bu dam pa rnams ni
NK117(she)001:19258: 'jig rten pa'i spyod pa dang mthun pas 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:19260: zhes nor bzang gi skyes pa'i rabs tshig nyung ngur byas nas don snying por dril te brjod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19262: 'dod pas phongs dang dbul ba'i skyes bu rnams //
NK117(she)001:19263: bkres skom don ma grub pa'i re dogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:19264: gzhan dbang kho nar lus ngag chud gson pa'i //
NK117(she)001:19265: sdug bsngal sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwags dngos //
NK117(she)001:19266: zhes pa ni ji srid du chog shes dang 'dod
NK117(she)001:19267: pa'i nyes dmigs skyon du rigs nas spang blo ma
NK117(she)001:19268: skyes bar du 'dod sred kyi don 'grub min gyi
NK117(she)001:19269: re dogs dang / bsam bzhin thog tu ma khel
NK117(she)001:19270: bas phongs pa dang dbul ba dag bkres skom sogs
NK117(she)001:19271: bsal ba'i don ma grub bar gzhan dbang kho nar
NK117(she)001:19272: lus ngag chud gson pa'i sdug bsngal ni mi yin
NK117(she)001:19273: kyang sa la rgyu ba'i yi dwags dang mtshungs so
NK117(she)001:19276: gzugs la rten bcas tshor bas rang bzhin shes //
NK117(she)001:19277: 'du shes las de rgyun chags 'du byed kyis //
NK117(she)001:19278: phyin chad sa bon bskrun dang rnam shes kyis //
NK117(she)001:19279: sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba'i nye bar len //
NK117(she)001:19280: phung po lnga po 'di dag sdug bsngal rnams //
NK117(she)001:19281: kun gyi 'byung gnas kun gyi rten dang snod //
NK117(she)001:19282: kun gyi rgyu 'bras bdag por mkhyen 'tshal nas //
NK117(she)001:19283: kun 'byung las dang nyon mongs spang 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:19284: zhes pa ni rang gi gzugs kyi phung po 'di
NK117(she)001:19285: bde sdug bsngal thams cad kyi gnas rten yin pa
NK117(she)001:19286: dang / tshor ba'i phung pos de dag so so'i rang bzhin shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19287: 'du shes kyi phung pos las yid la zhen nas 'brel rgyun chags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19288: 'du byed kyis ni 'byung 'gyur gyi sa bon 'debs shing /
NK117(she)001:19289: rnam shes phung pos thams cad nye bar len to //
NK117(she)001:19290: de'i phyir na phung po lnga po 'di dag rnams
NK117(she)001:19291: ni sdug bsngal kun gyi 'byung ba'i gnas dang rten
NK117(she)001:19292: dang snod lta bu dang kun gyi rgyu dang 'bras
NK117(she)001:19293: bu dang bdag po yin pa mkhyen par byas la
NK117(she)001:19294: kun 'byung gi bden pa las dang nyon mongs pa
NK117(she)001:19295: thams cad spang 'tshal lo zhes de ltar du 'dod
NK117(she)001:19297: de ltar spangs nas skyes bu 'bring gi lam //
NK117(she)001:19298: bden pa bzhi yi shing rta la zhon nas //
NK117(she)001:19299: 'gog pa mngon gyur mya ngan 'das pa'i khams //
NK117(she)001:19300: thar pa mchog gi go 'phang nyid du 'gro //
NK117(she)001:19301: de ltar kun 'byung spangs pa gang yin pa de ni thar pa /
NK117(she)001:19302: thar pa ni lam gyi bden pa des sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:19303: spangs shing 'gog pa mngon du gyur pa ni mya
NK117(she)001:19305: thar pa mchog gi go 'phang nyid du 'gro zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19306: de yang nyan rang gnyis dang theg chen dang gsum las /
NK117(she)001:19307: nyan thos theg pa'i ngo bo ni rang gcig pu
NK117(she)001:19308: thar par 'dod pa'i blo gang zag gi bdag med
NK117(she)001:19310: de ni nga med bdag med kyi gzhi rtsa chod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19311: nges tshig ni slob dpon las chos nyan zhing gzhan la sgrogs pas nyan thos so //
NK117(she)001:19312: dgos pa ni srid pa tha ma'i byang chub 'grub nas 'khor ba las nges par 'byin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19313: 'bras bu ni lhag bcas dang lhag med kyi myang 'das thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19314: de la'ang mdo sde dang bye brag smra ba gnyis yod de /
NK117(she)001:19315: dang po ni mdo sde la yid rton cing lam
NK117(she)001:19316: sgrub pa dang shes rab zab pas yang dag pa'i
NK117(she)001:19318: sde gnyis po gang zag gi bdag med par rtogs pa 'dra yang /
NK117(she)001:19319: chos kyi khams bye brag tu smra ba las /
NK117(she)001:19321: de yang cha dang bcas pa'i rdul phran /
NK117(she)001:19324: ldan pa ma yin pa'i 'du byed phung po'i gzhi /
NK117(she)001:19326: snang ba gzugs kyi gzhi dang lnga po gtso bor khegs la /
NK117(she)001:19327: chos kyi khams gzung yul rags pa'i snang ba rdul
NK117(she)001:19328: phran reg la ma 'byar ba'i 'dzin pas de'ang cha
NK117(she)001:19329: med du rtogs pas bye brag pa las 'phags pa'o
NK117(she)001:19330: // bye brag tu smra ba ni /
NK117(she)001:19331: bshad mdzod chen mo'i rjes su 'brang ba yin te /
NK117(she)001:19332: de yang kun rdzob kyi bden pa 'di g.yag rnga dang ne'u gsing ltar 'dod pa'i /
NK117(she)001:19333: snang dus na 'tshogs pa gcig pa ltar te /
NK117(she)001:19334: don dam par rdul phran cha ldan sil bur 'dod
NK117(she)001:19335: la shes pa'i rgyun kun rdzob skad cig don dam
NK117(she)001:19336: cha med pa bum chu lta bu ste /
NK117(she)001:19337: phung khams skye mched rags snang rngul phran bskor ba dang bcas par 'dod la /
NK117(she)001:19338: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs kyang chos bdag rdul
NK117(she)001:19339: phran dang skad cig yod par khas blangs pas mdo
NK117(she)001:19341: shes pa'i rnam pa sdug bsngal shes bya /
NK117(she)001:19344: 'gog pa thob bya'i tshul gyis shes par bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:19345: lam bdag med pa'i ngang tshul bsgoms pas mthong ba dang bsgom pas spang bya /
NK117(she)001:19346: bzhi brgya dang bcu gnyis spangs shing zad pa dang
NK117(she)001:19347: mi skye ba shes pa'i ye shes dam pa mngon
NK117(she)001:19348: du rtogs nas grol bar 'dod do //
NK117(she)001:19349: bye mdo gnyis ka'ang lam sgom dus dug gsum gyi gnyen por bdag med dang sgyu ma bsgom la /
NK117(she)001:19350: so so'i gnyen por 'dod chags la mi gtsang ba'i
NK117(she)001:19351: rdzas brgyad la keng rus bsgom la zhe sdang la
NK117(she)001:19352: byams pa gti mug la rten 'brel lugs ldog bsgom
NK117(she)001:19353: zhing / rnam rtog gi gnyen por dbugs dbyung rngub grangs su gzhal zhing mi yengs par bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:19354: des bdag med bsgom pa'ang yul dang yul can 'gag
NK117(she)001:19355: pa'i 'gog pa ci yang mi dmigs pa'i don bsgom
NK117(she)001:19356: zhing / gti mug dang bying rmugs la spyi bo mar me la sems gtod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19357: de ltar byas pas dbang po dman 'bring yin yang
NK117(she)001:19358: brtson 'grus rab kyis tshe de nyid la 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:19359: thob cing / dbang rnon byang chub sems dpa'i rigs
NK117(she)001:19360: kha cig lam lnga sngon song gis mthus stan thog
NK117(she)001:19361: gcig tu lam lnga rdzogs par 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19362: de'ang nyan thos theg pa nas /
NK117(she)001:19363: rang lam de blo chung 'bring che bas nyan rang
NK117(she)001:19364: dang sangs rgyas 'grub par 'dod kyis sngags lta ci
NK117(she)001:19365: theg chen yang blor ma shong bas na /
NK117(she)001:19366: ston pa thabs la mkhas pas rigs can gsum gyi theg pa rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19367: rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK117(she)001:19368: nyan thos kyi sde snod la thos bsam mkhas par
NK117(she)001:19369: byas nas skye ba de'i 'og tu sangs rgyas dang
NK117(she)001:19370: nyan thos med pa'i dus su skyes nas slob dpon
NK117(she)001:19371: med bzhin srid pa tha ma'i tshe 'bras bu mngon
NK117(she)001:19372: du byed pa'i thabs bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs
NK117(she)001:19374: nges tshig ni sems can mang po'i don ma yin par rang gcig sangs rgyas 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19375: dgos pa ni 'khor ba las thar ba'i byang chub 'bring thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19376: 'bras bu ni dgra bcom gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:19377: dbye na ne tso ltar khyus 'tsho ba dang /
NK117(she)001:19378: bse ru ltar gcig pur gnas pa gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:19379: snga mas ni rten 'brel lugs 'byung gi skyon dang
NK117(she)001:19380: lugs ldog gi yon tan rig na sa rtsa ba
NK117(she)001:19381: chod / bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs pa gzhir
NK117(she)001:19382: byas te sbyor lam dang bsgom lam gyi mthar zad
NK117(she)001:19383: pa dang mi skye ba shes pa gnyis mngon du
NK117(she)001:19384: byas nas dgra bcom thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19386: bden pa gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos rnams la rten
NK117(she)001:19387: 'brel lugs 'byung du bsgoms pas khams gsum pa'i phra
NK117(she)001:19389: lta ba'ang sngon ma dang mtshungs shing /
NK117(she)001:19390: de'ang chos bdag la phyi bzung yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa gnyis sgro btags pa yin la /
NK117(she)001:19391: gang zag gi bdag ni nga dang nga yir 'dzin
NK117(she)001:19392: pa ste gang zag dang chos kyi bdag ces bya
NK117(she)001:19393: ba'o // nyan thos kyis snga ma las phyi ma ma rtogs /
NK117(she)001:19394: rang rgyal gyis snga ma dang phyi ma'i phyi gzung ba med par rtogs kyang /
NK117(she)001:19395: nang 'dzin pa med pa ma rtogs so //
NK117(she)001:19396: chos bdag ni phyi rol gyi yul thams cad rang bzhin med par bsgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19397: nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa yang skye 'gag gnas
NK117(she)001:19398: gsum dang bral ba'i stong pa nyid de phyi ma
NK117(she)001:19399: 'di theg pa chen po'i rtogs pa kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:19400: nyan rang gnyis ka la dkar po rnam par mthong
NK117(she)001:19401: ba'i sa la sogs pa dman pa'i sa brgyad bshad
NK117(she)001:19402: de / de la brten nas rgyun zhugs dang /
NK117(she)001:19404: phyir mi 'ong ba dgra bcom pa ste re re
NK117(she)001:19405: la zhugs gnas ga nyis gnyis su phye bas zung
NK117(she)001:19406: bzhi ya brgyad ces grags so //
NK117(she)001:19407: byang chub sems dpa' la ni sa bcu por dge
NK117(she)001:19408: sbyong gi 'bras bu bzhi yod par bshad pa ni
NK117(she)001:19409: kun mkhyen chen po'i lugs rnam par bzhag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19410: de yang dgra bcom pa ni zad pa dang mi skye ba shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19411: zad pa ni phung po lhag med dang sems rtog
NK117(she)001:19412: tshogs thams cad 'gog pa'i dbyings la bzhugs shing sngon
NK117(she)001:19413: tshogs ji tsam bsags pa'i yun la de ltar gnas
NK117(she)001:19414: nas mthar bde chen zhing la sogs su skyes nas
NK117(she)001:19415: sangs rgyas kyis thugs rjes bskul te gdod sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:19417: rten chos kun gyi rtsa ba ma rig pa //
NK117(she)001:19418: de las 'du byed rnam shes ming dang gzugs //
NK117(she)001:19419: de las skye zhing mched pa rnam pa drug /
NK117(she)001:19420: de las reg pa de las tshor ba ste //
NK117(she)001:19421: de las sred pa sred las len pa dang //
NK117(she)001:19422: de las srid pa srid las skye ba ste //
NK117(she)001:19423: skye ba yod na 'dod pas phongs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:19424: mya ngan na rga 'chi sogs sdug bsngal gyi //
NK117(she)001:19425: phung po shin tu che ba grub pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:19426: skye ba 'gags pas thams cad 'gag gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:19427: rten cing 'brel 'byung rgyu 'bras zab mo ni //
NK117(she)001:19428: rgyal ba bden par smra ba'i gsung gi mdzod //
NK117(she)001:19429: ces pa ni 'di ltar ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed de /
NK117(she)001:19430: 'du byed kyi rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa /
NK117(she)001:19431: rnam par shes pa'i rkyen gyis ming dang gzugs /
NK117(she)001:19432: de bzhin du rten 'brel lugs 'byung du skye ba'i rkyen gyis rga nad 'chi ba /
NK117(she)001:19433: de'i rkyen gyis mya ngan dang smre sngags 'don pa yid mi bde ba la sogs 'byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:19434: de yang ma rig pa 'gags pas 'du byed la sogs pa gzhan rnams 'gag par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:19435: ma rig pa ni so so rang rig gi ye
NK117(she)001:19436: shes kyi bden pa rnam par mi shes pa de
NK117(she)001:19437: ni don dam par ma rig pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19438: de yang ma rig pa dang sred pa dang len pa gsum nyon mongs pa'i lam mo //
NK117(she)001:19439: 'dud byed dang srid pa las kyi lam mo //
NK117(she)001:19440: yan lag lhag ma rnams ni rnam par smin pa'i lam mo //
NK117(she)001:19442: 'du byed rnam shes sred pa len pa srid pa
NK117(she)001:19443: ste rgyu drug po tshe sngon rdzogs nas lhag ma
NK117(she)001:19444: drug 'bras bu'i tshul du tshe 'dir rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19445: shes sla ba'i phyir rang gi go tshod tsam brjod pa /
NK117(she)001:19446: thog mar sems 'khrul pa'i dus dang 'chi khar bar
NK117(she)001:19447: do'i thim rim rnams rdzogs nas gzhi lam gyi 'od
NK117(she)001:19448: gsal ma bu 'dres pa'i skabs rang ngo rang gis
NK117(she)001:19449: ma rig pa gnyis ha lam mtshungs shing /
NK117(she)001:19450: rkyen des byas nas srid pa bar do 'du bar
NK117(she)001:19451: byed cing de'i rnam shes las rlung dang 'grogs pas
NK117(she)001:19452: dbang med du bya sgro rlung gis khyer ba lta
NK117(she)001:19453: bu dang / ming bzhi 'dus pa'i gzugs phung las rags pa'i rten med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19454: yid lus kyi dbang po drug las rnam shes drug skye zhing mched pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19455: rnam shes drug po yul drug la reg pas dga'
NK117(she)001:19456: sdug bar ma'i tshor ba nyams su myong ba dang
NK117(she)001:19457: / de'i rkyen gyis lus len pa la sred pa
NK117(she)001:19458: dang sred pa'i rkyen gyis mngal du 'jug pa blangs
NK117(she)001:19459: / pas len pa'o // mngal du zhugs nas phyir ma dbyung bar srid pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19460: phyir thon pa la skye ba dang de'i rkyen gyis
NK117(she)001:19461: na rga 'chi ba sogs snga ma'i rkyen gyis phyi
NK117(she)001:19463: de dag ni rang gi rten 'brel te /
NK117(she)001:19465: sa bon la brten nas myu gu 'byung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:19466: drod gsher la brten nas rtsi shing skye ba /
NK117(she)001:19467: pha ma la brten nas bu phrug bskyed pa /
NK117(she)001:19468: chu ngogs la brten nas gza' skar gyi gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa /
NK117(she)001:19469: ka gdung la brten nas khang pa'i thog rim mang
NK117(she)001:19470: du brten pa bzhin 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams rten
NK117(she)001:19471: cing 'brel 'byung kho na la brten pa yin te
NK117(she)001:19472: / mdor na dge ba la brten nas bde ba dang /
NK117(she)001:19473: sdig pa la brten nas sdug bsngal bskyed pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:19475: de lta mod kyi srid par 'du byed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:19476: mtho dman las dang dkar nag rgyu 'bras chos //
NK117(she)001:19477: kun las 'das pa zhi ba dam pa'i dngos //
NK117(she)001:19478: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid rtogs las 'byung //
NK117(she)001:19479: zhes pa ni 'di ltar 'khor bar 'du byed pa'i rgyu'i gtso bo ni ma rig pa ste /
NK117(she)001:19480: des gnas ris mtho dman dang las bzang ngan dang
NK117(she)001:19481: dkar po dge ba nag po sdig pa'i rgyu 'bras
NK117(she)001:19482: kyi chu kun bskyed pa yin zhing de dag las
NK117(she)001:19483: 'das pa zhi ba dam pa'i dngos zhes pa ni
NK117(she)001:19484: / skye ba med pa'i chos nyid ces don dam pa'i bden pa rtogs pa las byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:19485: de la bden pa bzhi char ma grub pa nyid de /
NK117(she)001:19486: yum las 'phags pa'i bden pa rnams kyang ngo bo nyid med do //
NK117(she)001:19487: de bzhin du rten 'brel kyang rten chos phan tshun phrad par ma grub ste /
NK117(she)001:19488: yum las rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba rnams kyang rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag /
NK117(she)001:19490: de lta mod kyi rgyu 'bras la rmongs pa'i gnyen
NK117(she)001:19491: por dge mi dge la brten nas 'bras bu 'dod
NK117(she)001:19492: mi 'dod 'byung ba shes nas 'dor len la brtson
NK117(she)001:19493: cing / rten 'brel snang la rang bzhin ma grub pa tsam du blta ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:19494: dgra bcom pa yang yongs su mya ngan las 'das
NK117(she)001:19495: nas bskal pa stong phrag bcu na sangs rgyas pa'o
NK117(she)001:19496: // nyan thos dgra bcom dag sngar lam bsgrub dus
NK117(she)001:19497: rang kho na sangs rgyas thabs bsams pa'i blo ngan
NK117(she)001:19498: des sangs rgyas kyi zhing sbyongs shing sems can la
NK117(she)001:19499: phan 'dogs pa la bar du gcod cing /
NK117(she)001:19500: byang sems las dang po pa zhig dang sems bskyed pa dus mnyam yang /
NK117(she)001:19501: nyan rang bskal pa bzhi bcu bul bar 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:19502: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:19503: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:19504: lde mig las le'u bzhi pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:19505: da ni skyes bu mchog gi 'jug ngogs kyi thog mar 'khor lo chen po bzhi ston pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:19506: yul ni mthun par gyur pa dag la bsten //
NK117(she)001:19507: skyes bu dam pa bsten las yon tan 'thob //
NK117(she)001:19508: legs par smon dang bsod nams skyabs 'dun la //
NK117(she)001:19509: 'khor lo chen po bzhi zhes klu dbang bzhed //
NK117(she)001:19510: ces pa ni 'di ltar yul mthun par gyur pa
NK117(she)001:19511: ni gang zhig sems mnyam par bzhag pa dang mi
NK117(she)001:19512: mthun pa med cing 'tshe dogs thams cad dang bral
NK117(she)001:19513: ba'o // dam pa bsten pa ni lung rtogs phun
NK117(she)001:19514: sum tshogs pa la bsten na de'i yon tan bdag
NK117(she)001:19516: legs par smon pa ni bdag nyid kyis ji skad
NK117(she)001:19517: bshad pa bzhin byed pa'i sgo nas legs pa bsgrub
NK117(she)001:19518: pa'o // bsod nams kyi skyabs la 'dun pa ni tshe sngon ma dang /
NK117(she)001:19519: da lta yang tshogs bsag pa la dga' zhing 'dun pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19521: tshogs kyi dbus na dug can zas lta bu'i //
NK117(she)001:19522: yul dang rkyen gyi rnam 'gyur shin tu rgod //
NK117(she)001:19523: de las bsrings nas gcig pur zhi la mos //
NK117(she)001:19524: rnyed la ma chags rlung dang mkha' lding bzhin //
NK117(she)001:19525: 'di ltar rgyal po'i khab la sogs bdag tu bzung
NK117(she)001:19526: ba'i khyim che chung gang du gnas kyang rung ste
NK117(she)001:19527: / mi mang 'tshogs pa'i skyon gyis dgra gnyen dang
NK117(she)001:19528: 'thab rtsod dang phyogs ris sogs la brten nas dug
NK117(she)001:19529: can gyi zas zos pa lta bu'i chags sdang gi
NK117(she)001:19530: yul dang bde sdug gi rkyen gyis rnam rtog gi
NK117(she)001:19531: 'gyur ldog shin tu rgod par 'gyur na /
NK117(she)001:19532: de las thag bsrings nas rang gcig pur sems kyi
NK117(she)001:19533: nyon mongs pa zhi ba mos bzhin rnyed pa tshol
NK117(she)001:19534: ba la ma chags par nam mkha'i rlung dang mkha'
NK117(she)001:19535: lding gi brtul zhugs bzhin du dben par song zhig
NK117(she)001:19536: pa'o // de ltar ma yin par yul dang 'brel
NK117(she)001:19537: na sngon dge slong dpal byin zhes pa sdom khrims
NK117(she)001:19538: bsrung sems shin tu brtan pa zhig yod pa de'i
NK117(she)001:19539: mdun du khyim bdag mo nyal bas der ma nyal
NK117(she)001:19540: zhes nan du ldog kyang ma nyan pas ji zhig
NK117(she)001:19541: na dge slong chags sems skyes nas der log par
NK117(she)001:19544: ri dwags bzhin du dben par gnas pa de //
NK117(she)001:19545: bab col spyod pas 'khrugs par mi 'gyur la //
NK117(she)001:19546: gzhi la brten na gzhan ngo bsrung ba dang //
NK117(she)001:19547: phrag dog bzod pa'i snying stobs bri bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:19549: de la dben pa'i gnas gang du'ang ri dwags bzhin
NK117(she)001:19550: du mi las byol zhing bag phebs nas gnas pa
NK117(she)001:19551: de nyid la chags sdang la sogs bab col gyi
NK117(she)001:19552: spyod pas lus sems 'khrugs par mi 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:19553: de ltar ma yin pa'i khyim gzhi la brten nas
NK117(she)001:19554: gzhan gyi ngo bsrung ba dang gzhan gyi phun tshogs
NK117(she)001:19555: la phrag dog skyes pa'i skyon gyis bzod pa'i snying
NK117(she)001:19556: stobs rnam pa gsum rim gyis bri bar 'gyur ro
NK117(she)001:19558: yid ni shin tu rengs pa'i byi la yang //
NK117(she)001:19559: 'gro 'dug zhi zhing spyod lam des pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:19560: sdig pa'i grogs kyis bag phebs bsten pa'i yul //
NK117(she)001:19561: phun sum tshogs kyang chos las 'phral du nyams //
NK117(she)001:19562: zhes pa ni 'di ltar yid ni shin tu rengs
NK117(she)001:19563: pa'i byi la de yang g.yo thabs kyis 'gro 'dug
NK117(she)001:19564: zhi zhing spyod lam des pa ltar /
NK117(she)001:19565: chos la bar chad rtsom pa'i sdig pa'i grogs po
NK117(she)001:19566: la la dag gis bslu thabs kyis bag phebs par
NK117(she)001:19568: gnas bcas na longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa byung
NK117(she)001:19569: yang dge ba'i chos sgrub pa las 'phral du nyams
NK117(she)001:19571: bskyod pa yang ba'i nyi zla kun dang mdza' //
NK117(she)001:19572: 'dris shing gnyug mar gnas pa khro bas gdung //
NK117(she)001:19573: gsar pa gsar par gyur pa'i yul 'jam zhing //
NK117(she)001:19574: skye bo kun kyang bshes par 'gyur ba mthong //
NK117(she)001:19575: zhes pa ni gling gcig tu mi sdod par rgyu
NK117(she)001:19576: ba'i nyi zla gnyis gling bzhi'i 'gro ba kun dang
NK117(she)001:19577: mdza' ba bzhin chos ltar spyod pa rnams kyang mchog
NK117(she)001:19578: dman su la'ang 'dris che ba dang mkhon che ba'i
NK117(she)001:19579: bsam spyod spang zhing rtag tu gnyug mar gnas pa'ang
NK117(she)001:19580: 'dris sun gyis 'khro bas gdung ba sogs la byol
NK117(she)001:19581: nas gsar pa gsar par gyur pa'i yul 'jam zhing
NK117(she)001:19582: phrag dog khong 'khrugs mi slong ba'i gnas su bag
NK117(she)001:19583: phab na der gnas pa'i skyes bu kun kyang mdza'
NK117(she)001:19586: sems ldan lta bur ca co sgrog 'gyur yang //
