NK117(she)001:19587: brjod pa bzang ngan rjes su de yi sems //
NK117(she)001:19588: 'gro ba ma yin brag cha lta bu yi //
NK117(she)001:19589: kun spyod can la yul gyi dam bca' bral //
NK117(she)001:19590: zhes pa ni 'di ltar sems ldan lta bur rjes su zlo zhing ca co sgrog par 'gyur yang /
NK117(she)001:19591: de la brjod pa bzang ngan ci 'dra zhig smras kyang dga' sdug bral ba ltar /
NK117(she)001:19592: 'jig rten chos brgyad mgo snyoms nas gzhan gyis bstod
NK117(she)001:19593: smad sogs kyi rjes su de'i sems 'gro ba ma
NK117(she)001:19594: yin pa'i sgom chen pa brag cha lta bu'i kun
NK117(she)001:19595: spyod can la yul bzang ngan gyi dam bca' bral
NK117(she)001:19597: skyes bu tshangs par mtshungs par spyod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:19598: bsam gtan don la gcig tu sems pa yi //
NK117(she)001:19599: brtul zhugs brtan par ma son gang dang gang //
NK117(she)001:19600: yul dang grogs la brten nas mtho dman byed //
NK117(she)001:19601: ces pa ni 'di ltar skyes bu gang dag rab
NK117(she)001:19602: tu byung nas tshangs par mtshungs par spyod pa rnams
NK117(she)001:19603: dang / sgom chen du rloms shing bsam gtan gyi
NK117(she)001:19604: don la rtse gcig tu sems shing zhen pa'i tshul
NK117(she)001:19605: khrims dang bsam gtan gyi brtul zhugs brtan par ma
NK117(she)001:19606: son bzhin du bltar snang legs pa tsam don du
NK117(she)001:19607: gnyer bas btsun gzugs gang dang gang yin kyang chags
NK117(she)001:19608: sdang gi yul dang grogs la brten nas res mtho
NK117(she)001:19609: res dma' lta bu'i rang skyon ngom par 'gyur ro
NK117(she)001:19610: dang / // de la tshangs pa zhes pa ni mya ngan las 'das pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19611: de'i don du spyod pas na tshangs par spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19613: ston pas gnang bas gzhan la bsod nams bskyed //
NK117(she)001:19614: bdag kyang dka' thub nyams par mi 'gyur la //
NK117(she)001:19615: slong ba rnams kyis yid bzhin nor bur lta //
NK117(she)001:19616: mthun par gyur pa'i bsod snyoms kho na yin //
NK117(she)001:19617: zhes pa ni de la rang gzhan gyi don sgrub
NK117(she)001:19618: par 'dod pa rnams ni bdog pa thams cad la
NK117(she)001:19620: ston pas gnang bas bsod snyoms la brten nas slong yul gzhan la bsod nams bskyed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19621: bdag nyid kyang bslab pa gsum gyi dka' thub nyams par mi 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:19622: slong mo ba rnams kyi yid bzhin nor bu lta
NK117(she)001:19623: bu ni chos dang mthun pa'i bsod snyoms kho na
NK117(she)001:19626: 'tsho ba shin tu ma dag thabs kyis brku //
NK117(she)001:19627: rnyed pas rnyed 'tshol kha gsag tshul 'chos dang //
NK117(she)001:19628: thob kyis 'jal ba'i log 'tsho rnam pa lngas //
NK117(she)001:19629: drang srong rnams kyi brtul zhugs sma bab 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:19630: de phyir gnas mal bzang dang 'tsho ba bzang //
NK117(she)001:19631: grogs dang sbyor ba bzang pos snying stobs slong //
NK117(she)001:19632: zhes pa ni 'dir dmigs bsal gyi log 'tsho lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:19633: ster du re nas gzhan sngun du sdug phongs kyi tshig zlo ba'am /
NK117(she)001:19634: zas gos yod pa sbas nas nyam thag pa'i tshul
NK117(she)001:19635: gyis rnyed tshad thams cad 'tsho ba ma dag thabs
NK117(she)001:19637: rnyed pas rnyed pa tshol ba ni /
NK117(she)001:19638: bza' btung dang nor rdzas phra mo re phar btang
NK117(she)001:19639: nas tshur mang po 'ong ba'i thabs sna tshogs byed
NK117(she)001:19641: rang gi yon tan sna tshogs thabs mkhas kyis brjod
NK117(she)001:19642: cing skyon tshogs sbas nas rnam dkar rgya chen bsag
NK117(she)001:19643: bardzusa gzhan mgo bskor nas rnyed pa thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19645: rang gis bsrung sdom ma dag bzhin du gzhan sngun
NK117(she)001:19646: du zhi dul drang gsum gyi spyod pa ngom pa
NK117(she)001:19647: dang / yang na chos brgyad mgo snyoms par bardzusa
NK117(she)001:19648: nas spyod pa hral po ma bcos zhig po'i spyod
NK117(she)001:19649: pa ngoms nas rnyed pa tshol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:19651: sbyin bdag gi sar cho ga dang kha ton bzlas
NK117(she)001:19652: brjod kyis ched du phyin par 'bul ba'i nor rdzas
NK117(she)001:19654: gzhan yang 'don brjod 'di tsam la 'bul ba 'di
NK117(she)001:19655: tsam dgos pa ma byung zhes nyo btsong ltar sems
NK117(she)001:19656: pa'o // de las kyang sha chang gis brid nas tshol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:19657: sbyin pa gnyis ka ston pas bkag bzhin de dag
NK117(she)001:19658: la bag med du spyod na sngon byon gyi rgyal
NK117(she)001:19659: ba dang de'i rjes 'brang drang srong rnams kyi brtul
NK117(she)001:19660: zhugs sma bab par 'gyur ro zhes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19661: tshul de'i phyir na gnas mal bzang po 'gal rkyen
NK117(she)001:19662: med pa'i sar 'tsho ba bzang po log 'tsho lnga
NK117(she)001:19664: grogs bzang dge ba spyod pa sbyor ba bzang po
NK117(she)001:19665: rnam dkar la brtson pa sogs kyis rang gis rang
NK117(she)001:19666: la snying stobs slong dgos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19668: bslab pa kun gyi yon tan rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:19669: skyes bu dam pa dag la bsten par bgyi //
NK117(she)001:19670: ji ltar ma la ya yi nags klung du /
NK117(she)001:19671: rnam par 'khyams pa'i sdong dum phal pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:19672: yal 'dab brlan pa'i tsan dan dris bsung ltar //
NK117(she)001:19673: gang la bsten pa de yi rjes su 'gro //
NK117(she)001:19674: zhes pa ni 'di ltar skyabs su 'gro ba nas
NK117(she)001:19675: bzung rnam par grol ba'i bar gyi bslab pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:19676: thams cad shes pa ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten
NK117(she)001:19678: ji ltar na tsan+dana ma la ya yi nags klung
NK117(she)001:19679: du shing dman pa rnam par 'khyams pa'i sdong po'i
NK117(she)001:19681: dri'i mchog dang yun ring ba'i 'grogs pa'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:19682: gyis yal 'dab rnams dri bzangs kyis brlan pas tsan+dana
NK117(she)001:19683: gyi dri bsung ltar du slob dpon gang la bsten
NK117(she)001:19684: pa de'i rjes su 'gro zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19686: dam pa'i chos tshul mtha' dag rdzogs pa ni //
NK117(she)001:19687: snyigs ma'i mthus byas rnyed par dka' na'ang //
NK117(she)001:19688: sdom gsum gnang bkag gtsang ma'i sa gzhi la //
NK117(she)001:19689: thos dang snying rje chen pos thugs rgyud brlan //
NK117(she)001:19690: sde snod sngags rgyud rgya mtsho'i cho ga mkhas //
NK117(she)001:19691: spangs rtogs ye shes dri med 'bras bus phyug /
NK117(she)001:19692: bsdu dngos bzhi yi me tog rnam bkra bas //
NK117(she)001:19693: skal bzang slob ma'i bung ba sdud la bsten //
NK117(she)001:19694: sngon bskal pa yar ldan gyi tshe slob dpon dang
NK117(she)001:19695: slob ma gnyis ka yon tan dang ldan pa 'dzoms
NK117(she)001:19696: par gyur kyang deng dus 'dir dam pa'i chos tshul
NK117(she)001:19697: mtha' dag rdzogs pa snyigs ma'i mthus byas skyon gyis
NK117(she)001:19699: so thar byang sems gsang sngags te sdom gsum gnang
NK117(she)001:19700: ba dang bkag pa'i dbye tshul shes pa'i dpe sa
NK117(she)001:19701: gzhi gtsang ma lta bu la mang du thos pa
NK117(she)001:19702: dang snying rje chen pos thugs rgyud brlan pas gzhan
NK117(she)001:19703: rjes su 'dzin pa la brtson pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19704: de yang sde snod gsum dang sngags rgyud phyi nang
NK117(she)001:19705: gi rgyud sde rgya mtsho'i cho ga la mkhas shing
NK117(she)001:19706: spangs pas nyon shes kyi dri ma bcom pa dang
NK117(she)001:19707: rtogs pas ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa'i ye
NK117(she)001:19708: shes dri ma med pa'i 'bras bus phyug cing mkho
NK117(she)001:19709: ba sbyin pa dang snyan par smra ba dang 'jig
NK117(she)001:19710: rten gyi don dang mthun pa dang /
NK117(she)001:19711: gdul bya'i don la spyod pa bzhi yi dpe me
NK117(she)001:19712: tog rnam par bkra ba lta bus skal ba bzang
NK117(she)001:19713: po'i slob ma'i bung ba sdud pa'i slob dpon la
NK117(she)001:19715: khyad par man ngag ston pa'i bla ma ni //
NK117(she)001:19716: dbang thob dam tshig la gnas shin tu zhi //
NK117(she)001:19717: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud don khong du chud //
NK117(she)001:19718: bsnyen sgrub rtags rdzogs rtogs pas rang rgyud grol //
NK117(she)001:19719: snying rje tshad med gzhan don 'ba' zhig gnyer //
NK117(she)001:19720: bya ba nyung zhing nan tan chos la sems //
NK117(she)001:19721: skyo shas cher ldan gzhan yang de la bskul //
NK117(she)001:19722: thabs la mkhas shing brgyud pa'i byin rlabs ldan //
NK117(she)001:19723: de lta bu la bsten na dngos grub myur //
NK117(she)001:19724: zhes pa ni khyad par gsang sngags kyi man ngag ston pa'i bla ma ni /
NK117(she)001:19725: dkyil 'khor phyi nang gi dbang rdzogs par thob pa /
NK117(she)001:19726: sdom pa dang dam tshig dag pa /
NK117(she)001:19727: thugs rgyud shin tu zhi ba /
NK117(she)001:19728: gzhi rgyud bde gshegs snying po dang /
NK117(she)001:19729: lam rgyud bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi de nyid rtogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:19730: thabs bden gnyis kyi bye brag /'bras rgyud sku lnga
NK117(she)001:19731: ye shes lnga la sbyor tshul sogs khong du chud
NK117(she)001:19732: pa / lam smin grol gnyis la brten nas bskyed
NK117(she)001:19733: rdzogs la 'jug cing bdag byin gyis brlabs pa'i bsnyen
NK117(she)001:19734: pa lha dang dbyer med bsgrub pa'i rtags rnams rdzogs
NK117(she)001:19735: shing rdzogs rim yang dmigs bcas gtum mo sgyu lus
NK117(she)001:19736: rmi lam 'od gsal bar do 'pho ba bcas gsang
NK117(she)001:19737: sngags spyi'i lugs dang rdzogs chen ltar na lam thod
NK117(she)001:19738: rgal gyi nyi ma ser khrid zla ba dkar khrid
NK117(she)001:19739: mar me dmar khrid mun pa nag khrid de khrid
NK117(she)001:19740: chen bzhi dang dmigs med gzhi khregs chod rtogs pas
NK117(she)001:19741: rang rgyud grol nges pa go ba ra ri tsam
NK117(she)001:19742: pa / ma yin pa / snying rje tshad med pas gzhan don 'ba' zhig don du gnyer zhing /
NK117(she)001:19743: 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi bya ba nyung zhing phyi
NK117(she)001:19744: ma'i don la nan tan dang thos bsam sgom gsum
NK117(she)001:19745: sogs rnam dkar gyi chos la rtag tu sems pa
NK117(she)001:19746: / 'khor ba'i chos la skyo shas te skyon du
NK117(she)001:19747: rig nas de la mi skye thabs byed pa dang
NK117(she)001:19748: nges 'byung ni de las thar nas gtan bde sgrub
NK117(she)001:19749: pa'i blo yang dag pa de yin zhing gzhan rjes
NK117(she)001:19750: 'brang rnams kyang tshul de ltar bsgrub pa la bskul
NK117(she)001:19751: / ba dang / gdul bya chos la 'dzud pa'i
NK117(she)001:19752: thabs la mkhas shing brgyud pa la sel med cing
NK117(she)001:19753: byin rlabs kyi nus pa dang ldan pa /
NK117(she)001:19754: de lta bu'i bla ma dam pa la bsten na
NK117(she)001:19755: thun mong kun rdzob bden pa'i dngos grub dang mchog
NK117(she)001:19756: don dam bden pa'i dngos grub myur du thob ces
NK117(she)001:19758: bram ze bzhin du cho rigs bsrung ba'am //
NK117(she)001:19759: bsti gnas nyams par dogs pa'i rdzing bu ru //
NK117(she)001:19760: thos bsam 'bras bu gnas min khrus la zhugs //
NK117(she)001:19761: shing gi rang 'thag lta bu'i lam ston dang //
NK117(she)001:19762: zhes pa ni 'di ltar bram ze ni cho ste ma phyogs zhang po dang /
NK117(she)001:19763: rigs ni bram ze rang gi pha mes kyi ring lugs dang rig byed dang /
NK117(she)001:19764: ngan sngags sogs la brtson bzhin de dag ma nyams par bsrung ba bzhin du /
NK117(she)001:19765: 'jig rten chos brgyad la yi dam byed pa'i bla
NK117(she)001:19766: ma'i ming gis snyan pa la la dag rang nyid
NK117(she)001:19767: kyi bsti gnas khyim che chung gang yin kyang rung
NK117(she)001:19768: ste / de nyid nyams par dogs pa'i rang 'dod
NK117(she)001:19769: rdzing bu lta bur thos bsam sogs mkhas pa'i bya
NK117(she)001:19770: ba gsum la brtson pa 'dra yang /
NK117(she)001:19771: 'bras bu ni gnas min te tshe 'di'i ched du
NK117(she)001:19772: khrus la zhugs pa shing gi rang 'thag gis 'bru
NK117(she)001:19773: mi choms pa lta bu'i ltar snang mdzes pa kho
NK117(she)001:19774: na'i lam ston du rloms pa rnams ni slob ma'i
NK117(she)001:19775: thar lam 'gag pa'i bdud yin no //
NK117(she)001:19777: so so'i skye bo'i rang bzhin ma 'gal yang //
NK117(she)001:19778: blun po'i dad pas bab col gnas la sbyar //
NK117(she)001:19779: rnyed dang bkur bsti'i mchod pas khengs gyur pa //
NK117(she)001:19780: khron pa'i lag 'gro lta bu'i bshes gnyen dang //
NK117(she)001:19781: zhes pa ni de yang 'phags pa dang so skye gnyis chos nyid mi mtshungs te /
NK117(she)001:19783: 'phags nor bdun ni phal mo che tshang zhing rdul
NK117(she)001:19784: dang lta ba thams cad dang bral ba yin la
NK117(she)001:19786: blun rmongs kyi bsam spyod dang /
NK117(she)001:19787: brkam chags dang byas pa mi gzo zhing /
NK117(she)001:19788: kha gsag dang khro gtum sogs kyi rang bzhin mi 'gal bar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:19789: blun po gzhan gyis de'i rgyu mtshan ma rtogs bzhin
NK117(she)001:19790: du rmongs zhen gyi dad pas bab col zhes hol
NK117(she)001:19791: rgyug gis dad bardzusa gnas la sbyar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:19792: de yang 'phags pa'i bsam spyod kyis btang ba'i so
NK117(she)001:19793: so skye bo'i skyon ldan la la dag rnyed pa
NK117(she)001:19794: 'tshol ba'i phyir kun nas kun tu jag chom rgyu
NK117(she)001:19795: ba ltar 'phyan tshe gzhan gyis bkur bsti'i mchod pas
NK117(she)001:19796: khengs dregs skye ba dag dper na khron pa'i lag
NK117(she)001:19797: 'gro ste sbal pa lta bu'i bshes gnyen dang zhes
NK117(she)001:19799: nam zhig gi tshe rgya mtshor gnas pa'i sbal pa
NK117(she)001:19800: zhig rlabs kyis 'phangs nas khron pa zhig tu phyin
NK117(she)001:19801: pa dang de na sbal pa zhig yod pas khyed
NK117(she)001:19802: gang nas 'ongs dris pas rgya mtsho chen po nas
NK117(she)001:19804: kho rang gnas pa'i khron pa las lhag pa med snyam nas /
NK117(she)001:19805: de la gsum cha tsam bstan nas rgya mtshor 'di
NK117(she)001:19806: tsam yod dam dris pas des de las lhag tshul
NK117(she)001:19807: bshad pa dang / yang nyis cha tsam sogs dpags
NK117(she)001:19808: te dris mthar de 'dra mang pos kyang do zla
NK117(she)001:19809: med pa'i gtam bshad pas kho skyengs tshul gyi dpe
NK117(she)001:19810: bshad pa dang / ltar ro // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:19811: thos pa nyung zhing sdom dang dam tshig 'chal //
NK117(she)001:19812: rgyud tshod dma' la kun spyod sa blar gshegs //
NK117(she)001:19813: byams dang snying rje'i dpyang thag chad pa yi //
NK117(she)001:19814: smyon pa'i lam mkhan rnams las sdig pa 'phel //
NK117(she)001:19815: zhes pa ni phyogs re tsam las ma thos pa'i
NK117(she)001:19816: lung gi yon tan nyung zhing so thar dang byang
NK117(she)001:19817: sems kyi bslab sdom dang sngags kyi dbang bzhi'i dam
NK117(she)001:19818: tshig 'chal bas rgyud tshod su las dman yang rgyan
NK117(she)001:19819: chas 'byor pa 'khor g.yog sogs kyi pher yong dang
NK117(she)001:19820: am ldir gyis kun spyod sa bla ste nam mkhar
NK117(she)001:19821: gshegs pa lta bu'i bzang bardzu la la ni byams
NK117(she)001:19822: dang snying rje'i dpyang thag chad pa'i smyon pa'i lam
NK117(she)001:19823: mkhan rnams ni blun dad can 'ga' la sdig pa
NK117(she)001:19824: 'phel thabs slob pa kho nar bas so //
NK117(she)001:19826: khyad par rang las yon tan lhag bcas min //
NK117(she)001:19827: byang chub sems bral grags pa'i mthus bsten na //
NK117(she)001:19828: long ba'i ded dpon nor ba chen po ste //
NK117(she)001:19829: zol 'grogs mun pa'i smag tu 'khyam par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:19830: de phyir dam pa shin tu ma brtags na //
NK117(she)001:19831: dad pa can gyi dge tshogs chud gson cing //
NK117(she)001:19832: dal ba skabs shig rnyed pa sbrul gdug dang //
NK117(she)001:19833: shing gi grib ma nor bzhin bslu bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:19834: zhes pa ni 'di ltar slob ma rang nyid las
NK117(she)001:19835: slob dpon de nyid yon tan gyis mtho zhing lhag
NK117(she)001:19836: pa dang bcas pa zhig min na /
NK117(she)001:19837: byang chub kyi sems bral ba'i snyan grags dang go
NK117(she)001:19838: sa mtho ba zhig rgyu mtshan ma rtogs bzhin du
NK117(she)001:19839: blo srab pa'i mthus bsten na long ba'i ded dpon
NK117(she)001:19840: la lam sna bcol ba dang 'dra bas nor ba
NK117(she)001:19841: chen po gtan gyi 'dun ma nyes pa yin te
NK117(she)001:19842: / de lta bu'i bshes gnyen dang 'grogs kyang yon
NK117(she)001:19843: tan mi skye ba'i khar skyon gyis gos par 'gyur
NK117(she)001:19844: zhing dad pa yod bardzu'i zol gyis 'grogs kyang dge
NK117(she)001:19845: sgrub sdig spang la rmongs pa'i smag tu 'khyam par
NK117(she)001:19846: / 'gyur ro // de'i phyir na dang po nas
NK117(she)001:19847: dam pa shin tu brtags par ma byas na mi
NK117(she)001:19848: blun dad can bsod nams chung ba dag gis bla
NK117(she)001:19849: ma mi dge ba'i lam rgyus mkhan la bsten nyes
NK117(she)001:19850: pas rnam dkar gyi dge tshogs chud gson cing /
NK117(she)001:19851: de ltar dal ba skabs shig rnyed pa 'di dpe
NK117(she)001:19852: dang sbyar na mtshan mo'i dus zhig tu mi zhig
NK117(she)001:19853: gis khur chen po khur nas phyin pa la sbrul
NK117(she)001:19854: gdug pa can zhig lam khar nyal nas yod pa
NK117(she)001:19855: shing grib tu 'khrul nas de'i khar ngal gsos 'phral
NK117(she)001:19856: sbrul gyis zos pa bzhin du bshes gnyen ngan pas
NK117(she)001:19858: gtam rgyud dang sbyar na rngam glog las /
NK117(she)001:19859: sngon 'das pa'i dus dge slong dri med spyod pa
NK117(she)001:19860: zhes bya ba zhig rnal 'byor gyi tshul 'dra ba
NK117(she)001:19862: de don la mkhas pa'i bla ma rnams mi bzhugs
NK117(she)001:19863: nas bla ma de dag gi tshom bu 'bum gyi
NK117(she)001:19864: 'khor rnams kyis bla ma'i gdung 'tshob par gsol zhes
NK117(she)001:19865: dpon bstabs pas / dge slong de che bas dregs
NK117(she)001:19866: pa skyes te mi shes bzhin du tshul 'dra ba
NK117(she)001:19867: log par spyod pas dge slong de tshom bu 'bum
NK117(she)001:19868: gyi 'khor dang bcas pa ru trar bskal pa grangs
NK117(she)001:19870: zhes dbang khrid lung gsum med bzhin du thos lo
NK117(she)001:19871: bsags pa dang bsam nyes kyis rgyu 'bras khyad gsod
NK117(she)001:19872: byed pa / lta sgom nor ba'i go ba skam
NK117(she)001:19873: pos stong 'dzin kho na la blo phyogs pa'i chad
NK117(she)001:19874: par lta ba dag gis slob dpon gyi sa bzung
NK117(she)001:19875: na bshad pa ma thag pa ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:19877: mtha' dag yon tan 'byor ba'i bla ma ni //
NK117(she)001:19878: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes thugs rje'i khams //
NK117(she)001:19879: gdul bya'i yul la skyes bu'i gzugs kyis byon //
NK117(she)001:19880: dngos grub kun gyi rtsa ba bla na med //
NK117(she)001:19881: ces pa ni mang du thos pa lung gi yon tan dam pas phyug cing /
NK117(she)001:19882: rtogs pa'i shes rab bla na med pas slob ma'i
NK117(she)001:19883: rgyud grol ba la mkhas pa de ni mtha' dag
NK117(she)001:19884: yon tan 'byor ba'i bla ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:19885: de lta bu'i dam pa ni sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK117(she)001:19886: ye shes dang thugs rje'i khams yin pas de nyid
NK117(she)001:19887: gdul bya'i yul la skyes bu'i gzugs kyis byon pa
NK117(she)001:19888: yin la de'i yon tan ni dngos grub kun gyi
NK117(she)001:19889: rtsa ba bla na med ces basngagasa pa brjod pa'o
NK117(she)001:19891: drang ba'i don du kun dang phyogs mthun la //
NK117(she)001:19892: nges pa'i don du kun dang rnam gzhag 'gal //
NK117(she)001:19893: dgongs pa can phyir kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:19894: the tshom gcod mkhas log bsgrub skyo ngal bzod //
NK117(she)001:19895: ces pa ni kun rdzob drang ba'i don ltar na
NK117(she)001:19896: su dang yang mi mthun pa med pas kun dang
NK117(she)001:19898: nges pa'i don du kun dang rnam bzhag 'gal zhes
NK117(she)001:19899: pa byis pas rang don byed pa dang skyes bu
NK117(she)001:19900: dam pas gzhan don byed pa gnyis mi mtshungs pa
NK117(she)001:19901: dang / dgongs pa can phyir ni lugs zung gang
NK117(she)001:19902: yang gzhan don kho na las rang don yid byed
NK117(she)001:19903: dang bral bas kun las khyad par du 'phags pa'o
NK117(she)001:19904: dang / // slob ma'i the tshom gcod pa la
NK117(she)001:19905: mkhas shing gzhan gyis log bsgrub la skyo ngal bzod
NK117(she)001:19907: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol ba'i gru bo che //
NK117(she)001:19908: lam mchog 'khrul par mi 'gyur ded dpon dngos //
NK117(she)001:19909: las nyon me tshogs 'joms pas bdud rtsi'i char //
NK117(she)001:19910: ma rig mun pa sel bas nyi zlar mtshungs //
NK117(she)001:19911: theg pa shin tu che bas sa gzhi 'dra //
NK117(she)001:19912: phan dang bde ba'i 'byung gnas dpag bsam shing //
NK117(she)001:19913: chos kyi mdzod ldan bum pa bzang po ste //
NK117(she)001:19914: kun 'byung yid bzhin nor bu las kyang lhag /
NK117(she)001:19915: kun la snyoms par byams pas pha ma yin //
NK117(she)001:19916: che zhing myur ba'i snying rje chu klung mtshungs //
NK117(she)001:19917: 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dga' ba ri dbang 'dra //
NK117(she)001:19918: 'khrugs pa med pa'i btang snyoms char sprin bzhin //
NK117(she)001:19919: de 'dra'i bla ma sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam //
NK117(she)001:19920: gnod pa byas kyang bde ba'i lam 'brel na //
NK117(she)001:19921: zol med dad pas bsten pa'i skyes bu la //
NK117(she)001:19922: mngon mtho nges legs yon tan char bzhin 'bab //
NK117(she)001:19923: ces pa ni skye rga na 'chi bzhi ni srid
NK117(she)001:19924: pa'i mtsho yin te de las sgrol ba'i gru bo
NK117(she)001:19926: thar pa'i lam mchog 'khrul par mi 'gyur ba'i tshong dpon dngos lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:19927: las dang nyon mongs pa'i me tshogs 'joms pas bdud rtsi'i char lta bu /
NK117(she)001:19928: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel bas nyi zlar mtshungs
NK117(she)001:19929: shing khur shin tu che yang theg pa'i sa gzhi
NK117(she)001:19930: dang 'dra zhing / bstan 'gror phan bde 'byung ba'i
NK117(she)001:19931: gnas su gyur pa ni dpag bsam gyi shing lta
NK117(she)001:19932: dang 'dra zhing / bu / mdo sngags kyi chos
NK117(she)001:19933: thams cad kyi mdzod dang ldan pa bum pa bzang
NK117(she)001:19935: dgos 'dod kyi re ba kun 'byung ba ni yid bzhin nor bu las kyang lhag ste /
NK117(she)001:19936: bla ma dam pa la bsten na thar pa dang
NK117(she)001:19937: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang thob par 'gyur ba'i
NK117(she)001:19938: phyir ro // 'gro ba kun la snyoms par byams
NK117(she)001:19939: shing brtse bas pha ma lta bu yin zhing dgra
NK117(she)001:19940: gnyen ris med la che zhing myur ba'i snying rje
NK117(she)001:19942: 'gro rnams bde ba dang ldan sdug bsngal dang bral
NK117(she)001:19943: ba la 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dga' ba ri dbang
NK117(she)001:19944: dang 'dra zhing / chags sdang gang gis kyang 'khrugs
NK117(she)001:19945: pa med pa'i btang snyoms char sprin dang 'dra ba'i
NK117(she)001:19946: bla ma sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam zhing gnod pa
NK117(she)001:19947: byas kyang bde ba'i lam dang 'brel na /
NK117(she)001:19948: zol med dad pas snying nas bsten pa'i skyes bu
NK117(she)001:19949: de la mngon mtho lha mi'i bde skyid dang nges
NK117(she)001:19950: legs thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal yon
NK117(she)001:19953: nad pas sman pa mgron pos skyel ma dang //
NK117(she)001:19954: 'jigs pas ra mda' tshong pas ded dpon dang //
NK117(she)001:19955: gru pas mnyan pa bzhin du skye shi dang //
NK117(she)001:19956: nyon mongs dgra yi 'jigs pas bsten par bya //
NK117(she)001:19957: de yang skyes bu dam pa ji ltar bsten pa
NK117(she)001:19958: na nad pas sman pa dang 'jigs yul bgrod pa'i
NK117(she)001:19960: dgra tshogs dang 'phrad dogs kyi 'jigs pa'i ra mda'
NK117(she)001:19961: dang rgya mtsho bgrod pa sogs tshong pas ded dpon
NK117(she)001:19962: dang chu bor brgal ba'i gru pas skya ba bzhin
NK117(she)001:19963: du skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal sogs nyon mongs
NK117(she)001:19964: dgra yis 'jigs pa las skyob pa'i phyir skyes bu
NK117(she)001:19965: dam pa la bsten par bya zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:19967: de la nye bar len pa slob ma ste //
NK117(she)001:19968: snod dang bral la bcud kyis phan mi thogs //
NK117(she)001:19969: zang zing tsam gyis tshim pa thob gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:19970: bcos ma'i dad pas dus bzhi'i 'gyur ldog ngom //
NK117(she)001:19971: dang po chos lam mi tshud g.yag rgod bzhin //
NK117(she)001:19972: bar du thos bsam la sdang tshe 'di gnyer //
NK117(she)001:19973: tha mar sdig pa'i grogs kyi phyogs bzung nas //
NK117(she)001:19974: las mtha' log pa nags matha'i mi rgod 'dra //
NK117(she)001:19975: zhes pa ni de la snod bral gyi slob ma
NK117(she)001:19976: ngan pa ni the tshom dang gsar ngas che ba
NK117(she)001:19977: la sogs skyon kun gyis sbags pa khyad par bla
NK117(she)001:19978: ma'i skyon rtog pa la mkhas shing yon tan mi
NK117(she)001:19979: mthong ba rang las bla ma dman par 'dzin pa
NK117(she)001:19980: de lta bu'i slob ma rigs rus dang 'byor pas
NK117(she)001:19981: dregs shing dam sdom la mi gnas pa thos lo
NK117(she)001:19982: bsags pas khengs pa sogs skyon ldan gyi snod du
NK117(she)001:19983: smin grol gyi bcud ci tsam blugs kyang phan cung
NK117(she)001:19984: zad tsam yang mi thogs shing /
NK117(she)001:19985: zang zing gi gnang sbyin cung zad tsam thob tshe
NK117(she)001:19986: des tshim nas bcos ma'i dad pas tshugs mi thub
NK117(she)001:19987: ste dbyar dgun ston dpyid kyi sa gzhi'i 'gyur ldog
NK117(she)001:19988: bzhin ngom zhing / dang po'i dus tha mal gyi
NK117(she)001:19989: spyod pa la goms ches pas chos lam du mi
NK117(she)001:19990: tshud pa'i dpe g.yag rgod lta bu /
NK117(she)001:19991: bar du phyi'i sgrigs lam kun spyod ltar snang mdzes
NK117(she)001:19992: pa tsam byung yang thos pas phyi'i sgro 'dogs mi
NK117(she)001:19993: gcod bsam pas dge sgrub sdig spang sogs rgyu 'bras
NK117(she)001:19994: la mi sems pa'i khar rnam dkar la sdang zhing
NK117(she)001:19996: tha mar sdig pa'i grogs kyi phyogs bzung nas gsod
NK117(she)001:19997: gcod rku 'phrog sogs mi dge ba la brtson pas
NK117(she)001:19998: las mtha' log pa nags matha'i mi rgod dang 'dra
NK117(she)001:19999: zhes pa'o // de las kyang bcud sdig can ni
NK117(she)001:20000: sems can gcig sangs rgyas na'ang kho rang gi mnga'
NK117(she)001:20002: las dang po pa blo las su mi rung ba
NK117(she)001:20003: de'i snying bdud kyi mdas phugs nas bla slob kyi
NK117(she)001:20004: bar la sel 'jug cing bsam spyod gang gi thad
NK117(she)001:20005: nas kyang bla ma dang mched grogs kun dang 'gal
NK117(she)001:20006: ba'i las la sbyor zhing nyams chags kyi 'dam du
NK117(she)001:20008: dam pa'i drung na gnas tshe 'bros la rings //
NK117(she)001:20009: yul gang bgrod par phyogs na sdig pas 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:20010: dben par ched du bskul na chos tshugs zhig /
NK117(she)001:20011: rlung gi rjes 'gro ku sha'i rtse mo bzhin //
NK117(she)001:20012: zhes pa ni blo las su ma rungs pa'i slob
NK117(she)001:20013: ma dag ni dam pa'i drung du gnas tshe yul
NK117(she)001:20014: gzhan du 'bros la rings pa ltar 'gro zhing /
NK117(she)001:20015: yul gang du bgrod par phyogs tshe rku 'phrog g.yo
NK117(she)001:20016: zol sogs sdig pas ltos bcas skyong ba'i las 'dzin
NK117(she)001:20017: zhing / bla mas dben par sgom sgrub la bskul
NK117(she)001:20018: na ltar snang mdzes pa'i chos tshugs zhig cing thos
NK117(she)001:20019: bsam sgom gsum gang yang brtson 'grus kyis btang nas
NK117(she)001:20020: rlung gi rjes su 'gro ba'i ku sha'i rtse mo
NK117(she)001:20021: bzhin brtan pa bral ba de yang bla mas slob
NK117(she)001:20022: ma gang yin de'i rgyud tshod dang bstun pa'i dben
NK117(she)001:20023: zhing / par bskul lam / 'gro don la mngags sam /
NK117(she)001:20024: rang sar bstan pa 'dzin skyong byed du bcug pa
NK117(she)001:20025: de bsgrubs na bar chod med cing bkra shis so
NK117(she)001:20027: mi gzhi ngan pa'i zol sbyor tha gu'i lces //
NK117(she)001:20028: bla ma spos kyi glang po ltar bsnyen nas //
NK117(she)001:20029: dam chos gla rtsi'i rnyed pa thob nas slar //
NK117(she)001:20030: rngon la yang dag spro bas dam tshig 'phen //
NK117(she)001:20031: zhes pa ni 'di ltar mi gzhi ngan pa ni
NK117(she)001:20032: g.yo sgyu'i bsam sbyor gyis dus 'da' zhing lto 'gro
NK117(she)001:20033: ltar lce gnyis ngom bzhin bla ma spos kyi glang
NK117(she)001:20034: po ltar bsnyen pa las dad pas ma yin zhing
NK117(she)001:20035: / smin grol gyi chos gla rtsi'i rnyed pa thob
NK117(she)001:20036: nas dam tshig bsrung ba phar zhog rngon la yang
NK117(she)001:20037: dag spro bas zhes bla ma gsod pa la yang
NK117(she)001:20038: cang mi sems zhing dam sdom rdo bzhin 'phen pa'o
NK117(she)001:20040: blo sna nyams 'og ma chud mtha' dag ni //
NK117(she)001:20041: gdams pa'i gnad 'gag thob pa slar btang nas //
NK117(she)001:20042: sna tshogs yig sna 'tshol bas dub pa'i mthar //
NK117(she)001:20043: gsar pa ma mthong sngon ma mtha' dag nyams //
NK117(she)001:20044: zhes pa ni 'di ltar gang zag blo sna nyams
NK117(she)001:20045: 'og tu ma chud pa la la dag smin grol
NK117(she)001:20046: gyi gdams pa'i gnad 'gag thob pa rnams nyams su
NK117(she)001:20047: mi len bzhin slar gang dgar btang nas /
NK117(she)001:20048: gzhan nas sna tshogs yig sna mang po 'tshol bas
NK117(she)001:20049: dub pa'i mthar zab gnad ldan pa gsar pa ma
NK117(she)001:20050: mthong zhing sngon ma thos shing mnyan pa mtha' dag
NK117(she)001:20053: yang dag don la sbyor ba'i dad pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20054: ltar snang tshe 'di bsgrub pa'i 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20055: gnyis kar lung du ma bstan gzu lum can //
NK117(she)001:20056: gsum du gnas pa'i mtshan nyid brtag pa gces //
NK117(she)001:20057: zhes pa ni de yang yang dag don la sbyor
NK117(she)001:20058: ba'i dad pa mos gus kyis chos la 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:20059: dang / ltar snang tsam du chos bsgrub tshul sngon
NK117(she)001:20060: ma dang mtshungs kyang don la tshe 'di kho na'i
NK117(she)001:20061: ched du bsgrub pa'i 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20062: de gnyis kar lung du ma bstan pa'i blun po
NK117(she)001:20063: gzu lum ste mkhas rloms can 'di phyi gnyis ka
NK117(she)001:20064: gnyer ba med bzhin rang gar chos la 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:20065: dang gsum du gnas pa'i gang yin gyi mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:20067: de gsum gyi dang po dpe mkhyud med par rjes
NK117(she)001:20068: su bzung zhing phyi ma gnyis ni thabs rten 'brel
NK117(she)001:20069: du mas yang dag pa'i lam du bsgyur dgos pa'o
NK117(she)001:20071: go cha che la blo gros shin tu brtan //
NK117(she)001:20072: lus dang srog la mi blta rim gro bgyid //
NK117(she)001:20073: ces gsung bkar dkrii bdag nyid mi bsrung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:20074: skyes bu de ni mos gus kho nas grol //
NK117(she)001:20075: zhes pa ni go cha'i brtson 'grus ni dus da
NK117(she)001:20076: lta nas bzung ste rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go
NK117(she)001:20077: 'phang ma thob kyi bar du byang chub bsgrub pa
NK117(she)001:20078: la cung zad kyang lhod par mi byed pa'i blo
NK117(she)001:20079: gros shin tu brtan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20080: lus dang srog la mi blta zhing bla ma dam par bkur bsti dang rim gro bgyid pa /
NK117(she)001:20081: bla mas ci gsung rgyal ba'i bkar dkri zhing bka'
NK117(she)001:20082: bzhin bsgrub nas bdag nyid mi bsrung ba'i skyes bu
NK117(she)001:20083: de ni dad pa dang mos gus kho nas grol
NK117(she)001:20084: zhes pa'o // 'di ltar slob dpon 'phags pas ngar
NK117(she)001:20085: snabs dor ba klu'i byang chub kyis blangs nas khar
NK117(she)001:20086: bcug pas sa dang po'i bden pa mthong /
NK117(she)001:20087: slob dpon gnyags btson dong du bcug pa dpal gyi
NK117(she)001:20088: ye shes kyis btson srung ba gnyis bsad nas spyan
NK117(she)001:20089: drangs pas dngos grub thob pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:20091: dad dang shes rab thos dang snying rje che //
NK117(she)001:20092: sdom dang dam tshig la gus sgo gsum dul //
NK117(she)001:20093: khong yangs gtong phod dag snang khrel yod ldan //
NK117(she)001:20094: zhes pa ni slob ma'i yon tan gyi khyad par yang dag pa'i dad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20095: shes rab kyis chos kyi gnad rtogs pa thos pas chos ma yin pa shes pa /
NK117(she)001:20096: snying rje chen pos sems can blos mi gtong ba /
NK117(she)001:20097: so sor thar pa dang byang chub sems dpa'i bslab
NK117(she)001:20098: sdom sngags kyi dam tshig rnams dang ldan pas sgo
NK117(she)001:20100: khong yangs pas mched grogs dang nye 'khor rnams dang mdza' zhing bshes pa /
NK117(she)001:20101: gtong phod dang dag snang khrel yod ldan pas tshogs gnyis gong 'phel du gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20103: bla ma shin tu bsrung bas mdzangs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20104: bka' bkyon dag la mi khro rta mchog bzhin //
NK117(she)001:20105: gru ltar 'gro 'ong gnas la skyo ba spangs //
NK117(she)001:20106: zam pa lta bur bzang ngan thams cad theg /
NK117(she)001:20107: bzo stegs bzhin du tsha grang gang yang bzod //
NK117(she)001:20108: bka' bzhin nyan pa bran khol lta bu dang //
NK117(she)001:20109: nga rgyal spangs pa phyag dar lta bu dang //
NK117(she)001:20110: dregs pa spangs pa khyu mchog rwa chad ltas //
NK117(she)001:20111: bla ma bsten zhes sde snod dag las gsungs //
NK117(she)001:20112: zhes pa ni de yang rang gi lus srog la
NK117(she)001:20113: thug kyang mi bsrung zhing bla ma la log sbyor
NK117(she)001:20114: cung zad tsam yang rang gi mig 'bras ltar bsrung
NK117(she)001:20116: bka' bkyon dag la mi khro ba rta mchog la
NK117(she)001:20117: lcag gis ji ltar brdeg kyang lan mi shom pa
NK117(she)001:20118: bzhin dang / bla mas gang du mngags kyang gru
NK117(she)001:20119: ltar 'gro ba dang 'ong ba'i gnas la skyo ngal
NK117(she)001:20120: spangs nas dka' ba dang du blang lci ba rgyab
NK117(she)001:20122: zam pa'i khar mchog dman thams cad 'gro ba lta
NK117(she)001:20123: bur bzang ngan skyid sdug legs nyes thams cad theg
NK117(she)001:20124: pa dang / bzo stegs kyi steng du tsha ba'i
NK117(she)001:20125: lcags bsregs grang ba'i chu 'khyags sogs tsha grang gang
NK117(she)001:20126: yang bzod pa ltar bla mas gang bsgos pa'i las
NK117(she)001:20127: 'jam rtsub lcogs min gang 'dra zhig yin kyang bzod
NK117(she)001:20128: pa dang / pa dang / bka' ji bzhin nyan
NK117(she)001:20129: pa las mi rung ba dang mi nus pa zhig
NK117(she)001:20130: yin kyang bka' las mi 'da' ba bran khol lta
NK117(she)001:20131: pa dang / pa dang / bu dang / bla
NK117(she)001:20132: ma'i zhabs 'degs la gnas tshe nga rgyal dang dregs
NK117(she)001:20133: pa spangs pa khyu mchog zhes ma he rwa chad
NK117(she)001:20134: pa lta bus bla ma bsten dgos zhes sde snod
NK117(she)001:20137: 'byor pa yod na dkon mchog bzhi pa mchod //
NK117(she)001:20138: zhabs tog sri zhu lus ngag bkol ba'i las //
NK117(she)001:20139: mtha' dag nam yang chud zos gyur pa med //
NK117(she)001:20140: mnyes pa gsum gyi nang nas bsgrub pa mchog /
NK117(she)001:20141: ces pa ni 'di ltar mchog gsum gyi khar bla
NK117(she)001:20142: ma bsnan pa'i dkon mchog bzhi pa yin zhes bstan
NK117(she)001:20143: nas 'byor pa yod na de nyid mchod na mchog
NK117(she)001:20144: gsum mchod pa dang mnyam zhes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20145: mchog gsum 'dus pa'i ngo bo bla ma'i zhabs tog
NK117(she)001:20146: dang sri zhur lus ngag bkol nas dka' las ji
NK117(she)001:20147: ltar byas pa mtha' dag nam du yang chud zos
NK117(she)001:20149: zang zing gis mnyes par byas pa dang lus ngag
NK117(she)001:20150: gi zhabs phyis mnyes thabs dang sgom sgrub la nan
NK117(she)001:20151: tan byas nas mnyes thabs gsum gyi nang nas bsgrub
NK117(she)001:20152: pa mchog yin no zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20154: mdzad spyod gang yang log par mi blta ste //
NK117(she)001:20155: 'phags pa'i yul gyi dbang phyug phal mo che //
NK117(she)001:20156: gdol pa g.yung po sdig spyod phal pa'i tshul //
NK117(she)001:20157: nyams pa las kyang shin tu nyams pa yod //
NK117(she)001:20158: rang gi nyer len dbang du ma gyur par //
NK117(she)001:20159: 'khrul pa brtag pa'i nyes pa tshad med de //
NK117(she)001:20160: sde snod bcu gnyis blo la chub pa yi //
NK117(she)001:20161: dge slong skar bzang sdig pa'i mthus btab nas //
NK117(she)001:20162: ston pa'i mdzad pa g.yo sgyur mthong ba'i tshul //
NK117(she)001:20163: legs par bsams nas rang gis rang nyid 'chos //
NK117(she)001:20164: zhes pa ni de yang yul gzhan ma rnams las
NK117(she)001:20165: khyad par 'phags pa'i rgya gar rdo rje'i gdan sangs
NK117(she)001:20166: rgyas stong gi gdan sa dam pa'i chos kyi 'byung
NK117(she)001:20167: gnas de na dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa
NK117(she)001:20168: dang 'byon 'gyur gyi mkhas shing grub pa'i dbang phyug
NK117(she)001:20169: phal mo che zhes rtsing spyod kyi brtul zhugs la
NK117(she)001:20170: gnas pa la la dag mi rigs bzhi'i nang nas
NK117(she)001:20171: gtsang dme sogs kyis 'dor len med pa'i gdol spyod
NK117(she)001:20172: dang g.yung po ste dman spyod dang /
NK117(she)001:20173: srog gcod sogs la brtson pas sdig spyod dang tshong
NK117(she)001:20174: so nam sogs kyang mi 'dor ba'i phal pa'i spyod
NK117(she)001:20175: pa la sogs pas 'dul sdom gyi rtsa ba bzhi
NK117(she)001:20176: sogs las nyams pa las kyang cung zad tsam yang
NK117(she)001:20177: mi bsrungs pas shin tu nyams pa dag yod mod
NK117(she)001:20178: kyang / de dag gi mdzad pa ni gang la
NK117(she)001:20179: gang 'dul ltar nges med kyis gdul bya'i don byed
NK117(she)001:20180: kyang / pa yin na / rang gi nyer len
NK117(she)001:20181: sems nyid 'di dbang du 'du bar ma gyur bar
NK117(she)001:20182: du gzhan gyi 'khrul pa brtag pa'i nyes pa tshad
NK117(she)001:20184: sngon sde snod bcu gnyis blo la zin zhing byang
NK117(she)001:20185: chub pa'i dge slong legs skar ram skar bzang ston
NK117(she)001:20186: pa la log lta byas pa'i sdig pa'i mthus btab
NK117(she)001:20187: nas / thabs mkhas kyi mdzad pa thams cad g.yo
NK117(she)001:20188: sgyur mthong ba'i skyon gyis kho rang tshe thung zhing
NK117(she)001:20189: yi dwags su skyes pa'i tshul sogs la legs par
NK117(she)001:20190: bsams nas rang gi rgyud rang gis 'chos pa las
NK117(she)001:20191: gzhan gyis bcos dka' bas rang skyon 'chos pa gal
NK117(she)001:20192: nas / che zhes pa'o // de yang gang gi
NK117(she)001:20193: de dag gi rgyu mtshan cung zad bkrol te 'chad
NK117(she)001:20194: nas / che zhes pa'o // na / bram ze
NK117(she)001:20195: chen po sgra gcan 'dzin nam sa ra ha rigs
NK117(she)001:20196: las nyams pa'i khar gnas brtan gyi spyod pa btang
NK117(she)001:20197: nas smyig mkhan mor spyod pas rgyal po sogs kun
NK117(she)001:20199: shwa ba ri pa bud med dang lhan cig rngon pa'i bya ba byed pa /
NK117(she)001:20200: da ri ka pas smad 'tshong ma'i g.yog byed pa /
NK117(she)001:20201: bya da li pa bya sna tshogs gsod pa /
NK117(she)001:20202: yan lag med pa'i rdo rje phag rdzi mor spyod cing khro zhing brdeg pa /
NK117(she)001:20203: bi na sa pi wang la chags pa /
NK117(she)001:20204: sgeg mo rdo rje chang 'tshong ma chags sred can du bstan pa /
NK117(she)001:20205: la ba pa gnyid la dga' ba'i tshul bstan pa /
NK117(she)001:20206: in+d+ra b+hu ti 'dod chags can du mthong ba /
NK117(she)001:20207: dza lan+d+ha ri pa byis pa'i spyod pa can du mthong ba /
NK117(she)001:20208: til+li pa nya gson bsreg byed pa sogs ma nges par spyod pa /
NK117(she)001:20209: tan+ta pa thags mkhan du spyod pa /
NK117(she)001:20210: ga ya pa ti glu la dga' tshul ngom pa /
NK117(she)001:20211: g+hun+di ri byi'u 'ba' zhig bsad nas za ba sogs
NK117(she)001:20212: spyod pa dman yang lta sgom mtho ba ches mang
NK117(she)001:20213: ngo // tshul 'di dag la bsams nas rang gi
NK117(she)001:20214: bla ma'i mdzad pa la 'khrul pa mi brtag pa
NK117(she)001:20216: gal te bla mas sdang bar mngon gyur na //
NK117(she)001:20217: bdag skyon gzigs nas spyo bas 'dul ba yi //
NK117(she)001:20218: dus la bab par rig nas bshags bsdom bya //
NK117(she)001:20219: cang shes skyes bu bdud kyi dbang mi 'gro //
NK117(she)001:20220: zhes pa ni gal te rang gi nus tshod kyi
NK117(she)001:20221: bla ma mnyes pa'i thabs sna tshogs byas kyang bla
NK117(she)001:20222: mas rang mnyes bzhin du thugs sdang bar mngon par
NK117(she)001:20223: gyur na / bdag gi skyon rang gi las sgrib
NK117(she)001:20224: kyis ma mthong ba bla mas gzigs nas spyo ba
NK117(she)001:20225: zhes rtsub spyod kyis 'dul ba'i dus la babs par
NK117(she)001:20226: rig nas rang gi nyes byas la bshags bsdom snying
NK117(she)001:20227: nas byed pa'i ci yang shes pa'i skyes bu de
NK117(she)001:20228: lta bu ni bdud kyi dbang du mi 'gro zhes
NK117(she)001:20230: bla ma bzhengs tshe stan la 'dug pa min //
NK117(she)001:20231: bzhugs pa'i dus na bsnyun 'dri nyer spyod dbul //
NK117(she)001:20232: gshegs na zhabs 'bring sngon rjes g.yas nas min //
NK117(she)001:20233: stan dang bzhon pa smad sogs bsod nams nyams //
NK117(she)001:20234: sgo 'phar brdeg dang sgeg chos ngo 'dzum gnag /
NK117(she)001:20235: rdzun dang bab col bzhad gad 'brel med gtam //
NK117(she)001:20236: gus dang 'jigs bcas ma yin ji mi snyam //
NK117(she)001:20237: spangs la sgo gsum nye bar zhi bas bsten //
NK117(she)001:20238: zhes pa ni bla ma bzhengs bzhud kyi tshe rang
NK117(she)001:20239: stan la sdod pa tshul min gyi spyod pa dang
NK117(she)001:20240: / bzhugs pa'i dus na bsnyun 'dri zhes pa /
NK117(she)001:20241: skyabs mgon rin po che mtshan dpe'i dkyil 'khor bde
NK117(she)001:20242: bar bzhugs sam sku la snyun cang mi mnga' 'am
NK117(she)001:20243: la sogs dang nyer spyod gzugs sgra dri ro reg
NK117(she)001:20245: bla ma gshegs bzhud kyi tshe rang zhabs 'bring la phyin na /
NK117(she)001:20246: mdun nas 'gro mi rung ste thog ma dang /
NK117(she)001:20247: g.yas gral mgo yin pas de yang bkag rgyab kyang
NK117(she)001:20248: zhabs rjes bardzi bas mi rung zhing g.yon nas phyin
NK117(she)001:20249: du rung ba'o // bla ma'i gzim mal sogs stan la 'gom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20250: bzhon pa ni chibs zhon pa sogs la smad pa'i
NK117(she)001:20251: sgra dang de la sogs pas bla ma brnyas thabs
NK117(she)001:20252: ci byas kyang bsod nams nyams pa'i rgyu yin zhes
NK117(she)001:20253: pa dang / khang pa'i sgo 'phar sogs 'byed gcod
NK117(she)001:20254: kyi tshe brdeg pa dang rang bla ma'i mdun sar
NK117(she)001:20255: gnas tshe sgeg chos byed pa dang ngo 'dzum gnag
NK117(she)001:20256: pa zhes mi dga' ba'i tshul ston pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20257: bla ma'i gsung 'phros kyi lan sogs la rdzun dang
NK117(she)001:20258: bab col zhes don med kyi smra ba mang po
NK117(she)001:20259: dang bzhad gad dang 'brel med ces ngag 'khyal gyi
NK117(she)001:20260: gtam sna tshogs dang gus pa dang 'jigs pa dang
NK117(she)001:20261: bcas pa ma yin par de las ldog pa'i bsam
NK117(she)001:20262: spyod kyi ji mi snyam pas brnyas pa sogs spangs
NK117(she)001:20263: la lus gus pas phyag dang zhe sa ngag gus
NK117(she)001:20264: pas gsol 'debs dang skyabs 'gro yid gus pas dad
NK117(she)001:20265: pa dang dag snang sogs sgo gsum nye bar zhi
NK117(she)001:20266: ba'i sgo nas bla ma bsten mkhas par bya zhes
NK117(she)001:20268: bla ma dmod cing sdang ba'i gang zag dang //
NK117(she)001:20269: bshes par mi bya nus pas de bzlog cing //
NK117(she)001:20270: bag phebs smra na sdig pa'i gzhan dbang ni //
NK117(she)001:20271: lhag par mthu che dam tshig skyon can byed //
NK117(she)001:20272: ces pa ni gal te skye bo gang zhig bla
NK117(she)001:20273: ma dang dgra zlar gyur pas dmod cing sdang ba'i
NK117(she)001:20274: sems dang ldan pa'i gang zag rnams dang mdza' zhing
NK117(she)001:20276: rang nyid nus pa dang ldan na bla mar 'tshe ba'i bsam sbyor de las bzlog cing /
NK117(she)001:20277: de ltar ma thub kyang dgra zla des rang dang
NK117(she)001:20278: mdza' ba'i phyir bag phebs pa'i thabs smra bar byed
NK117(she)001:20279: na'ang sdig pa'i gzhan dbang ni lhag par mthu che
NK117(she)001:20280: bas rang gi dam tshig skyon can byed pa la
NK117(she)001:20283: 'grogs par bde ba ska rags lta bu dang //
NK117(she)001:20284: 'jug pa bde ba lan tsh+wa lta bu dang //
NK117(she)001:20285: bzod sran che ba ka ba lta bu yis //
NK117(she)001:20286: bla ma'i 'khor dang rdo rje'i spun la gnyen //
NK117(she)001:20287: zhes pa ni 'di ltar bla ma'i nye du dang
NK117(she)001:20288: ltos bcas kyi gtsos skye dgu su la'ang rgyun du
NK117(she)001:20289: 'grogs kyang bde ba ska rags la 'dris sun med
NK117(she)001:20291: mchog dman kun dang 'dres pas 'jug pa bde ba lan tsh+wa lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:20292: skyo ba sun dang log bsgrub thams cad bzod pa
NK117(she)001:20293: ka ba lta bus bla ma'i 'khor dang rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:20296: rdzing bu mchog la bsten pa'i ngang pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20297: bung bas me tog bcud la ro myang bzhin //
NK117(she)001:20298: rtag tu 'grogs pa'i spyod pa ngo mtshar can //
NK117(she)001:20299: skyo ngal med pas bla ma'i thugs bzung nas //
NK117(she)001:20300: dad pa'i nye bar len pas yon tan myang //
NK117(she)001:20301: zhes pa ni 'jig rten na rdzing bu mchog la
NK117(she)001:20302: ngang pa'i khyu ci rigs bsten yang dga' sdug bral
NK117(she)001:20303: ba dang / bung bas me tog bcud la ro
NK117(she)001:20304: myang ba bzhin du rtag tu ci tsam 'grogs kyang
NK117(she)001:20305: log lta dang 'dris sun sogs med pa'i spyod pa
NK117(she)001:20306: ngo mtshar can gyis bla ma'i bka' bsgrub pa la
NK117(she)001:20307: skyo ngal med pas thugs bzung zhes pa mthun par
NK117(she)001:20308: byas nas dad pa'i nye bar len pas yon tan
NK117(she)001:20309: myong ba'i dag snang la 'jug dgos pa zhes pa'o
NK117(she)001:20310: ba dang / // spyir bla ma dang 'gal ba'i
NK117(she)001:20311: las che phra thams cad spang zhing mnyes pa'i thabs
NK117(she)001:20312: phyi nang gsang gsum mtha' ma bkag par bsgrub pa
NK117(she)001:20313: ba dang / // dang / bka' yi gnang ba
NK117(she)001:20314: ma byung ba gang yang mi bya zhing bka' gnang
NK117(she)001:20315: byung rigs rnams lus srog la babs kyang bsgrub dgos
NK117(she)001:20316: shing khyad par byin rlabs 'jug min dad pa kho
NK117(she)001:20317: na la rag las pa yang sngon dam pa sangs
NK117(she)001:20318: rgyas la slob bu zhig gis dam pa byin rlabs
NK117(she)001:20319: gcig zhu byas pas bu lhod po mos gus shig
NK117(she)001:20320: ba dang / // dang / zhu dang gsungs /
NK117(she)001:20321: de bzhin jo bo rje rin po ches kyang theg
NK117(she)001:20322: chen gyi yon tan thams cad bla ma la brten
NK117(she)001:20323: nas skye dgos pa la khyed bod kyis bla ma
NK117(she)001:20324: la tha mal pa'i 'du shes las med pas ga
NK117(she)001:20325: na skye gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:20327: 'jug pa'i spyod la nges par zhugs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:20328: dam pa mchog gi bsod nams ye shes tshogs //
NK117(she)001:20329: gang gi khrod du'ang don mthun spyod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20330: mngags gzhugs bang phyin phyag dar tshun chod kyang //
NK117(she)001:20331: ngal ba 'bras bcas tshogs kyi lam mchog yin //
NK117(she)001:20332: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dge tshogs gang la'ang 'jug
NK117(she)001:20333: pa'i spyod pa la nges par zhugs pa'i slob bu
NK117(she)001:20334: dag gis rang stobs kyis sbyor dngos rjes gsum thabs
NK117(she)001:20335: shes ya bral du ma gyur pas gang ltar byas
NK117(she)001:20336: kyang rung gis de las gzhan pa dag ni dam
NK117(she)001:20337: pa mchog gi rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs mchod sbyin
NK117(she)001:20338: gyi las dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs sgom
NK117(she)001:20339: sgrub la 'jug pa'i skabs gang gi khrod du'ang rang
NK117(she)001:20340: gi zang zing gi dngos rdzas dang sgo gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:20341: dka' spyad snying rus sogs bla ma'i mdzad pa dang
NK117(she)001:20342: don mthun par lhan cig tu spyod pa dang bla
NK117(she)001:20343: ma'i bka' sgrub phyir mngags gzhugs dang bang mir phyin
NK117(she)001:20344: pa bzhugs gnas la phyag dar gyi las tshun chod
NK117(she)001:20345: rnams kyang ngal ba don med pa ma yin te
NK117(she)001:20346: / bla ma dam pa'i tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang
NK117(she)001:20347: rang gi tshogs kyang lhan du 'dums nas 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:20348: dang bcas te tshogs kyi lam mchog yang dag pa
NK117(she)001:20350: ci phyir skyabs su 'gro dang tshogs kyi zhing //
NK117(she)001:20351: bla ma bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor phyi nang gnyis //
NK117(she)001:20352: bskyed rdzogs bsgrub bya'i ngo bo 'dir 'dus pas //
NK117(she)001:20353: mdo rgyud kun nas sangs rgyas nyid du bstan //
NK117(she)001:20354: zhes pa ni 'di ltar lam gyi thog ma skyabs
NK117(she)001:20355: 'gro'i skabs tshogs kyi zhing du gsal ba bla ma
NK117(she)001:20357: rgyud dag par byed pa'i phyir spyi gtsug tu bsgom pa ni nang ltar bsgrub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20358: snying gar bsgom pa ni gsang ba ltar bsgrub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20359: rang lus su bsgrub pa'am bskyed rim gyi tshe bla
NK117(she)001:20360: ma yi dam gyi rnam par bsgyur ba yang gsang
NK117(she)001:20362: bla ma kho na las lhag pa'i mchog gsum rtsa gsum logs na med de /
NK117(she)001:20363: yod na de ka rang bla mar bsten nas byin rlabs dang dngos grub zhus pas chog mod /
NK117(she)001:20364: de'i phyir na sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi rten 'brel mtha' dag bla ma la bsgrig pa gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:20366: rmongs pa phal cher gzugs brnyan 'dri zhing bsgom //
NK117(she)001:20367: dngos su bzhugs la rim gro bgyi ba med //
NK117(she)001:20368: gnas lugs bsgom zer bla ma'i thugs mi shes //
NK117(she)001:20369: sgrub dang bsgrub bya 'gal ba nyon re mongs //
NK117(she)001:20370: mos gus med bzhin bar dor mjal ba mtshar //
NK117(she)001:20371: zhes pa ni bod 'dir rang la drin che ba'i
NK117(she)001:20372: bla ma de las lhag pa'i chos 'brel ye ma
NK117(she)001:20373: thob pa'i ming gis snyan pa zhig bla mar re
NK117(she)001:20374: zhing bsten nas gsol ba 'debs lo byas kyang rang
NK117(she)001:20375: skal du ma thob pa'i nor bu la gsol ba
NK117(she)001:20376: btab pa bzhin rang gi bla mar yid ma ches
NK117(she)001:20378: gzhan dang rten cing ma 'brel ba sogs la rmongs
NK117(she)001:20379: pa phal cher zhes pa blun po la la dag
NK117(she)001:20380: gzhan gyi ltar snang tsam du bla ma'i gzugs brnyan
NK117(she)001:20381: 'dri zhing bsgom lo 'dra mo byed kyang dngos su
NK117(she)001:20382: bzhugs pa la dad mos dang rim gro bgyi ba
NK117(she)001:20384: rang gi sems kyi gnas lugs logs su bkar nas
NK117(she)001:20385: bsgom zer yang bla ma dang thugs yid bsre ma
NK117(she)001:20386: shes skyon gyis / sgrub byed kyi thabs mang btsal
NK117(she)001:20387: yang bsgrub bya bla ma'i thugs las gzhan pa zhig
NK117(she)001:20388: btsal bas 'gal ba ltag sprod du gyur pa nyon
NK117(she)001:20389: re mongs zhes pa ma shes pa dang des 'thums
NK117(she)001:20390: shes skyon gyis / pa'o // da lta mos gus
NK117(she)001:20391: med bzhin bar dor mjal du re ba dgra 'jigs
NK117(she)001:20392: che ba'i sar sngar 'brel 'dris ye med pas mi
NK117(she)001:20393: dpa' bo zhig gis rang mgo 'don du re ba
NK117(she)001:20394: 'di 'dra mtshar ba'i chos so zhes khrel ded pa'o
NK117(she)001:20395: shes skyon gyis / pa'o // // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:20396: dang po bla ma brtag la mkhas pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20397: bar du bla ma bsten la mkhas pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20398: tha mar dgongs spyod bslab la mkhas pa yi //
NK117(she)001:20399: skyes bu de ni yang dag lam la 'gro //
NK117(she)001:20400: zhes pa ni deng sang dus snyigs ma'i dbang gis
NK117(she)001:20401: yon tan thams cad dang ldan pa'i bla ma dka'
NK117(she)001:20407: stong nyid rtogs pa sogs cha re dang ldan yang bla mar bzung bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:20408: mdor na gzhan sngun du ltar snang ji tsam mdzes
NK117(she)001:20409: kyang bsam spyod gnyis ka 'jig rten chos brgyad dang
NK117(she)001:20410: mthun pa'i slob dpon ni bsten bya ma yin mod
NK117(she)001:20411: kyang / de yang brtag dka' ba'i gnas yin te /
NK117(she)001:20412: sngon bdag cag gi ston pas kyang bdud lhas sbyin
NK117(she)001:20413: bla mar bsten nas pha rol tu phyin pa drug
NK117(she)001:20414: rdzogs par mdzad pa'i lo rgyus bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:20415: bar du bla ma bsten pa'i thabs kyang mdor bsdu
NK117(she)001:20416: na lugs zung gang gi thad nas bla mas bka'
NK117(she)001:20417: ji ltar bstsal ba rung dang mi rung la mi
NK117(she)001:20418: ltos par dka' ba dang du blangs nas lus srog
NK117(she)001:20419: gi nyen la thug kyang mi ldog pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20420: tha ma bla ma'i dgongs spyod ni stong pa nyid
NK117(she)001:20421: snying rje dang 'brel ba'i lta sgom la bslab pa
NK117(she)001:20422: la mkhas pa'i skyes bu gang yin kyang rung ste
NK117(she)001:20423: yang dag pa'i lam la 'gro zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20425: gang tshe zhi la sdang ba'i 'byung po yi //
NK117(she)001:20426: bsam pa skyes bu'i gzugs su 'ongs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20427: g.yo dang sgyus spyod nag po'i chos la bsten //
NK117(she)001:20428: dam pa dmod sogs dkar po'i chos la sdang //
NK117(she)001:20429: ji tsam 'grogs bzhin sdig spyod 'thor rlung 'tshub //
NK117(she)001:20430: dge ba'i lo tog 'joms pa'i sdig grogs la //
NK117(she)001:20431: bsten pa'i blo gros blun po bdud sdes bcom //
NK117(she)001:20432: zhes pa ni dus nam gyi tshe yin kyang rung
NK117(she)001:20433: ste nyon mongs pa'i rtogs tshogs zhi ba'i thabs la
NK117(she)001:20434: gnyer ba'i lam gyi gang zag gi bsam sbyor la
NK117(she)001:20435: sdang ba'i 'byung po'i lus mi dang bsam pa mi
NK117(she)001:20436: dge ba'i las la spyod pa'i skyes bu'i gzugs su
NK117(she)001:20438: de yang g.yo zhes pa mi shes pa /
NK117(she)001:20440: ma thos pa'i tshul ston pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20441: sgyu ni tshul de dag la bsten nas gzhan bslu
NK117(she)001:20442: ba'i thabs la spyod cing nag po'i chos bzhi spyi
NK117(she)001:20443: la bsten pa dang khyad par dam pa dmod sogs
NK117(she)001:20444: dkar po'i chos bzhi la sdang /
NK117(she)001:20445: grogs ngan de lta bu dang ji tsam 'grogs bzhin
NK117(she)001:20446: rgyu 'bras khyad gsod dang mi dge'i sdig spyod 'thor
NK117(she)001:20447: rlung 'tshub pa lta bu'i skyon gyis dge ba'i lo
NK117(she)001:20448: tog lhag med du 'joms pa yin la de lta
NK117(she)001:20449: bu'i sdig grogs thos lo bsags pas nga rgyal gyis
NK117(she)001:20450: rgyags pa dang / bsam nyes kyis rten cing 'brel 'byung med par 'dzin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20451: lta sgom nyes pas chad lta la yi dam byed
NK117(she)001:20452: pa dag la bsten pa'i blo gros blun po ni
NK117(she)001:20455: de phyir dge ba'i bshes dang grogs bsten pas //
NK117(she)001:20456: dge legs yon tan mthong ba'i chos la zin //
NK117(she)001:20457: rgyal dang rgyal sras rnams kyis rtag tu dgongs //
NK117(she)001:20458: mngon mtho nges legs yon tan kun gyis 'byor //
NK117(she)001:20459: tshogs rdzogs sgrib dag dngos grub rnam gnyis thob //
NK117(she)001:20460: sa lam yon tan bla nas blar 'gro bas //
NK117(she)001:20461: rnal 'byor bsgom zhing bsgrub pa bsod nams tshogs //
NK117(she)001:20462: thugs rgyud gcig tu bsre ba ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:20463: tshogs gnyis 'bras bu'i thus ka yin pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:20464: bskal par rgyal dang rgyal sras bsnyen bkur zhing //
NK117(she)001:20465: bskyed rim brgya phrag bsgom las bla ma ni //
NK117(she)001:20466: skad cig dran pa mchog ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK117(she)001:20467: zhes pa ni de ltar phung 'tshengs shin tu che
NK117(she)001:20468: bas dge bshes dang sdig bshes dge grogs dang sdig
NK117(she)001:20469: grogs mi nor ba gal shin tu che ba de'i
NK117(she)001:20470: phyir dge ba'i bshes dang dge ba'i grogs po la
NK117(she)001:20472: dge bcu sogs rnam dkar gyi phyogs dang bde legs
NK117(she)001:20473: kyi dpal dang yon tan tshe 'dir mthong ba'i chos
NK117(she)001:20475: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa rnams kyis rtag tu
NK117(she)001:20476: dgongs klong nas mi 'dor zhing mngon mtho lha mi'i
NK117(she)001:20477: bde skyid dang nges legs thar pa dang rnam mkhyen
NK117(she)001:20478: gyi dpal yon kun gyis 'byor zhing /
NK117(she)001:20479: rgyu bsod nams dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs
NK117(she)001:20480: chen gnyis rdzogs shing nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gnyis
NK117(she)001:20481: dag nas mchog thun gyi dngos grub rnam gnyis thob
NK117(she)001:20482: cing / sa bcu dang lam lnga'i yon tan bla
NK117(she)001:20483: nas blar zhes pa gong nas gong du 'gro bar
NK117(she)001:20484: cing / byed pa la / bla ma'i rnal 'byor
NK117(she)001:20485: bsgom zhing bsgrub pa rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs dang
NK117(she)001:20486: bla ma'i thugs dang rang sems gcig tu bsre ba
NK117(she)001:20487: 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK117(she)001:20488: tshogs gnyis kyi 'bras bu'i thus ka'am ngo bo nyid
NK117(she)001:20489: yin pa'i phyir ji srid bskal pa'i bar du rgyal
NK117(she)001:20490: dang rgyal sras bsnyen bkur byas shing /
NK117(she)001:20491: bskyed rim brgya phrag bsgoms pa las ni bla ma
NK117(she)001:20492: nyid skad cig dran pa mchog ces rgyal ba rnams
NK117(she)001:20495: dam chos bdud rtsi'i chu klung dpag med mdzod //
NK117(she)001:20496: rgyud la 'drongs pa'i dmigs pa bzang po rnams //
NK117(she)001:20497: ston pa'i bla ma bzang por rten cing 'brel //
NK117(she)001:20498: thabs bzang ba las man nag 'khyams mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:20499: nges 'byung bzang po'i rig sngags nus pa can //
NK117(she)001:20500: 'khor bar skyo ba med pa'i gdon la thebs //
NK117(she)001:20501: bzang po bzhi dang ldan pa'i legs smon yin //
NK117(she)001:20502: zhes pa ni 'di ltar lung dang rtogs pa'i dam
NK117(she)001:20503: pa'i chos kyi bdud rtsi'i chu klung dpag tu med
NK117(she)001:20504: pa'i mdzod du gyur pa'i rgya mtsho chen po lta
NK117(she)001:20505: bu / rang gi rgyud la 'drongs pa'i dmigs pa
NK117(she)001:20506: bzang po ni chos gang yang rung la dmigs pa'i
NK117(she)001:20507: byed las la brten nas rgyud la sbyor bar byed
NK117(she)001:20508: pa'i ngo bo ni 'dun pa'ang yin la /
NK117(she)001:20509: de ston pa ni bla ma bzang po dang rten
NK117(she)001:20510: cing 'brel ba dang de'i grogs su thabs kyi cho
NK117(she)001:20511: ga med na man ngag kyang rnam par 'khyam par
NK117(she)001:20512: 'gyur ba dang / de rnams kun kyang nges 'byung
NK117(she)001:20513: gi blo bzang po bskyed dgos shing de lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:20514: 'khor ba la nges par 'byung ba de ni rig
NK117(she)001:20515: sngags nus pa can lta bu yin te gang la
NK117(she)001:20516: thebs na 'khor bar skyo ba med pa'i gdon la
NK117(she)001:20517: 'gyur ba dang / thebs pa'o // de lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:20518: bzang po bzhi dang ldan pa'i legs smon yin zhes
NK117(she)001:20519: 'gyur ba dang / thebs pa'o // pa'o // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:20520: chos sgor zhugs kyang mod la sun pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20521: kun slong dug can 'dres pa'i thos bsam bsgom //
NK117(she)001:20522: chos las blo nyams bsrung sdom khur du song //
NK117(she)001:20523: chos brgyad dmod pas theg chen brtul zhugs 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:20524: legs smon dka' thub bshig pa'i rnyogs pa yin //
NK117(she)001:20525: zhes pa ni 'di ltar gang zag la la dag
NK117(she)001:20526: ni gnyen bshes kyi chos sgor bcug lo byas kyang
NK117(she)001:20527: rang gis sngon bsod nams ma bsags legs smon ma
NK117(she)001:20528: btab pas chos sgor zhugs 'phral chos kyis sun nas
NK117(she)001:20529: rgyal po'am blon po sogs kyi bran nam mngags gzhug
NK117(she)001:20530: byed dam yang na thos bsam bag re byas kyang
NK117(she)001:20531: tshe 'di kho na las legs smon rgyab 'gal gyis
NK117(she)001:20532: dang po yi ge ma lobs kyis dogs pa /
NK117(she)001:20533: bar du des rnyed pa ma grub kyis dogs pa /
NK117(she)001:20534: tha mar gzhan dag gong du shor dogs kyi bsam
NK117(she)001:20535: ngan sogs kun slong dug can 'dres pa'i thos bsam
NK117(she)001:20536: sgom gsum dang / tshe 'di'i ltar snang legs pa
NK117(she)001:20537: tsam las yang dag pa'i chos las blo nyams nas
NK117(she)001:20538: so thar byang sems sngags gsum gyis bsrung sdom mi
NK117(she)001:20539: lcogs pa'i khur chen khyer ba lta bu'i 'tsher ngang
NK117(she)001:20540: sgom gsum dang / du song zhing / 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:20541: chos brgyad dmod pa zhes de dag gi skyon sel
NK117(she)001:20542: zhing yon tan spel ba ni theg pa chen po'i
NK117(she)001:20543: brtul zhugs yin na de nyid gnas min du 'khyams
NK117(she)001:20544: pa lta bu'i skyon sngon ma tshos dgos na legs
NK117(she)001:20545: smon zhes thar pa don gnyer gyi dka' spyod mi
NK117(she)001:20546: thub par bshig pa'i rnyog pa yin no zhes pa'o
NK117(she)001:20547: sgom gsum dang / du song zhing / // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:20548: thad ka thad ka'i nyon mongs dug chen lnga'i //
NK117(she)001:20549: gnyen por che ba skyes bu rnam gsum gyi //
NK117(she)001:20550: shing rtar 'dzegs la dus bzhir skyo ba med //
NK117(she)001:20551: snang ba mtha' dag chos dang bla mar shar //
NK117(she)001:20552: rnam mkhyen rgyur song legs smon grub pa yin //
NK117(she)001:20553: zhes pa ni 'di ltar 'dod chags kyi thad kar
NK117(she)001:20554: gnyen po mi sdug pa bsgom pa mtshon zhe sdang
NK117(she)001:20555: dang gti mug sogs dug lnga so so'i thad kar
NK117(she)001:20556: gnyen por che ba skyes bu chung ngus lha mi'i
NK117(she)001:20559: chen pos sems can gyi don du sangs rgyas kyi
NK117(she)001:20560: go 'phang gnyer ba'i lam rnam pa gsum ni shing
NK117(she)001:20561: rtar dpe byas nas der 'dzegs pa la 'das pa
NK117(she)001:20562: dang ma 'ongs pa dang da lta dang de gsum
NK117(she)001:20563: dmigs pa'am 'dzin pa bral bas mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:20564: dus stong pa nyid la rang byan chud na /
NK117(she)001:20565: snang ba mtha' dag chos dang bla mar shar bas
NK117(she)001:20566: rnam mkhyen gyi rgyur song ba la legs smon grub
NK117(she)001:20569: mtho ris yon tan bdun pa'i dga' ba dang //
NK117(she)001:20570: dal bas yang dag mtho la nad med cing //
NK117(she)001:20571: ting nge 'dzin dang rnam 'byed shes rab lnga //
NK117(she)001:20572: sngon chad bsod nams la gus mngon rtags yin //
NK117(she)001:20573: zhes pa ni 'di ltar gnas skabs su mngon par mtho ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20574: mthar thug nges par legs pa 'grub pa'i rgyu thams cad ni bsod nams la rag las pa ste /
NK117(she)001:20575: sngon nas bsod nams rgya chen po bar ma chad par 'du byas pa dag ni tshe 'di la /
NK117(she)001:20582: bde skyid dang ldan pa ste /
NK117(she)001:20583: de lta'i mtho ris kyi yon tan bdun po las skyes pa'i dga' ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20584: dal ba brgyad kyi dpal yon la spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20585: mngon par yang dag par mtho ba la nad med cing /
NK117(she)001:20586: ting 'dzin las su rung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20587: drang nges sogs rnam par 'byed pa'i shes rab ste /
NK117(she)001:20588: lnga po de ni sngon chad bsod nams bsags pa'i mathu'am gus pa'i mngon rtags yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20589: de yang dpe don gyi sgo nas bshad na 'khor
NK117(she)001:20590: 'das kyi legs tshogs thams cad 'phel 'grib gnyis ka'i
NK117(she)001:20591: byed pa po ni bsod nams dang bsod nams ma
NK117(she)001:20592: yin pa'i las kho na yin te /
NK117(she)001:20593: sngon rgyal po spyi bo skyes sam nga las nus
NK117(she)001:20594: sangs rgyas rnam gzigs la sran rdog bdun phul bas
NK117(she)001:20595: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal por gyur cing /
NK117(she)001:20596: rgyal chen rigs bzhi'i dpung las rnam par rgyal nas
NK117(she)001:20597: sum cu rtsa gsum du lha'i dbang po'i gdan phyed
NK117(she)001:20598: la sdod pa'i dpal thob kyang sdig sems kyi blo
NK117(she)001:20599: gros kyis rnam dkar bshig pa chos nyid yin phyir
NK117(she)001:20600: lha'i dbang po la 'khu ba'i sems skyes 'phral skar
NK117(she)001:20601: mda' lhung ba ltar mi yul du ldog pa bzhin
NK117(she)001:20603: ma bsgoms pas ni rig pa 'joms shing 'ong //
NK117(she)001:20604: rgyags pa rgyas pas dpal 'byor 'joms shing 'ong //
NK117(she)001:20605: rnam par sdang bas legs tshogs 'joms shing 'ong //
NK117(she)001:20606: chags pas yang dag mtho ba 'joms shing 'ong //
NK117(she)001:20607: gang phyir las dang nyon mongs sdig pa yis //
NK117(she)001:20608: rnam par dkrugs pa ma yin blo gros ni //
NK117(she)001:20609: shes rab mthu dang skal bas bkol btub pa //
NK117(she)001:20610: bsod nams bsags pa'i rtags su rgyan las bshad //
NK117(she)001:20611: ces pa ni gang zhig le lo can brtson 'grus
NK117(she)001:20612: zhan pa dag gi ma bsgoms pas ni sngon shes
NK117(she)001:20613: pa'i thos bsam sogs rig pa 'joms shing 'ong /
NK117(she)001:20614: rang 'byor pa longs spyod kyis rgyags pa rgyas pas
NK117(she)001:20615: bsod nams ma yin pa la spyod pas dpal 'byor
NK117(she)001:20616: 'joms shing 'ong / dgra zla'am btang snyoms pa'ang rung
NK117(she)001:20617: ste rnam par sdang bas legs tshogs 'joms shing 'ong
NK117(she)001:20618: 'joms shing 'ong / / rang gzhan gang yang rung
NK117(she)001:20619: ste yul bud med dam zas nor sogs la chags
NK117(she)001:20620: pas yang dag mtho ba ste mtho ris su skye
NK117(she)001:20622: de dag gang gi phyir na las nyon dang sdig
NK117(she)001:20623: pas rnam par dkrugs pa ma yin pa'i blo gros
NK117(she)001:20624: rnam dag ni / shes rab kyi mthu dang skal
NK117(she)001:20625: bas bkol du btub pa ni sngon tshe bsod nams
NK117(she)001:20626: bsags pa'i rtags yin par rgyan las bshad pa yin
NK117(she)001:20627: rnam dag ni / no // zhes lung khungs bcas mu sbrel ba'o //
NK117(she)001:20628: de yang bsod nams kyi rgyu mthun pa ni rgyal ba sras bcas rnams kyi khyad chos yin na /
NK117(she)001:20629: sems can gang dag thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen
NK117(she)001:20630: pa don du gnyer ba rnams la smos ci 'tshal
NK117(she)001:20631: / de ltar yang skyes rabs las /
NK117(she)001:20632: sngon rgyal po gsal ba'i stobs zhes bya bar /
NK117(she)001:20637: bsod nams stobs zhes rang gi yon tan gyi cha
NK117(she)001:20638: las btags pa lnga yod pa la so so'i yon
NK117(she)001:20639: tan gyi phyogs 'dzin cing snyem par byed do //
NK117(she)001:20640: de'i tshe bsod nams stobs kyis smras pa /
NK117(she)001:20641: bsod nams med na gzhan bzhi po gang gis kyang
NK117(she)001:20642: mi phan pas bsod nams gal che ste 'khor 'das
NK117(she)001:20643: kyi legs tshogs thams cad bsod nams kyi mthu kho
NK117(she)001:20644: na'o // zer yang mched bzhi po'i rang rang gi
NK117(she)001:20645: phyogs 'dzin pa las de ltar du khas mi len
NK117(she)001:20646: na'o // to // de nas yab kyis de dag
NK117(she)001:20647: gi stangs phyed pa'i phyir phal pa'i cha lugs kyis
NK117(she)001:20648: yul khams gzhan du mngags pa la gzugs stobs gzhan
NK117(she)001:20649: gyi yid du 'ong bas skye bo dag gis dga'
NK117(she)001:20651: brtson 'grus ldan gyi chu klung drag pos tsan+d+hana gyi
NK117(she)001:20652: shing khyer ba gzhan gyis blang mi nus pa de'i
NK117(she)001:20653: nus pa las byung ba'i longs spyod tsam gyis 'atsho'o
NK117(she)001:20654: // bzod ldan ni de las byung ba'i gla rngan gyi longs spyod tsam gyis 'atsho'o //
NK117(she)001:20655: shes rab ldan ni tshong dpon gnyis 'khon pa bsdum pa las byung ba'i rnyed pa tsam gyis so //
NK117(she)001:20656: bsod nams stobs ni dbul po zhig gi khyim du zhugs pa na der nor dang /
NK117(she)001:20659: dngul mang po byung bas dbul po des de rnams
NK117(she)001:20660: kyi mthur rig nas bkur sti rgya chen po byas
NK117(she)001:20661: pa'i grags pas kun tu khyab pas ji zhig na
NK117(she)001:20662: yul de'i rgyal po bu med pa'i btsun mo /
NK117(she)001:20664: grong khyer gyi gtso rnams 'dus nas rgyal bu bsod nams stobs rgyal por dbang bskur /
NK117(she)001:20665: des bsod nams kyi mthus mnga' ris bde ba'i gnas la reg go //
NK117(she)001:20666: rgyu mtshan de rnams rgyal po gsal ba'i stobs kyis
NK117(she)001:20667: thos nas rgyal srid kyi bdag por gzhon nu bsod
NK117(she)001:20669: de dang gzhan yang ston pa 'das nas lo brgya
NK117(she)001:20670: lon skabs grong khyer pa ta li pu trar rgyal
NK117(she)001:20671: po mya ngan med ces bya ba 'khor los bsgyur
NK117(she)001:20672: ba'i dpal yon gyi bzhi cha dang ldan pa zhig
NK117(she)001:20673: dang po mi dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi rjes su
NK117(she)001:20674: 'brang nas sdig pa'i las mang du byas /
NK117(she)001:20675: phyi nas bsod nams bsag pa lhur byed pa zhig byung tshe /
NK117(she)001:20676: des nor gyi ched du tshong pa lnga brgya nor bu len phyir mngags pa la /
NK117(she)001:20677: de rnams kyis rin po che dang /
NK117(she)001:20683: bye ru sogs kyis gru bkang ste rang yul du
NK117(she)001:20684: chas pa dang rgya mtsho'i dkyil tsam du klus gru
NK117(she)001:20685: bcom ste nor rnams lhag med du phrogs so //
NK117(she)001:20686: rgyal pos skyed mos tshal byi dor byas rgyan gyis
NK117(she)001:20687: brgyan nor bu'i rigs rnams dgram pa'i gnas dang spyod
NK117(she)001:20688: sta gon dang der blta phyir skye bo'i tshogs thams
NK117(she)001:20690: de'i tshong pa rnams nyam thag pa'i rang bzhin du 'ongs nas rgyal po la de'i rgyu smras so //
NK117(she)001:20691: der dge slong dbang pos bslab bzhin zangs ma'i byang bu la /
NK117(she)001:20692: sa 'di rgya mtshos gtugs par skyong //
NK117(she)001:20693: rgyal po stobs ldan mya ngan med //
NK117(she)001:20694: rab tu drag cing btsan pa yi //
NK117(she)001:20695: nor khyer mtshor gnas gang yin pa //
NK117(she)001:20696: de dag 'dir ni myur ba ru //
NK117(she)001:20697: nga yi drung du bskyal bar gyis //
NK117(she)001:20698: zhes bris nas mtshor bskyur bas klu'i rgyal pos phyir 'dzam bu'i gling du 'phang ngo //
NK117(she)001:20699: der pho nyas rgyal por bsnyad pas /
NK117(she)001:20700: rgyal po sems khong du chud nas thabs gang yod
NK117(she)001:20701: bsam pa'i tshe lhas ston pa'i sku gdung la mchod
NK117(she)001:20702: pa byas na bsod nams 'phel nas don 'grub bo
NK117(she)001:20703: // zhes smras par rgyal po'i skra bkrus /
NK117(she)001:20705: dri dang me tog gi phreng ba sogs thogs nas
NK117(she)001:20706: phyogs bcu'i rdzu 'phrul thob pa rnams spyan 'dren pa
NK117(she)001:20707: dang gsol 'debs kyi gdung dbyangs chen po byed pa
NK117(she)001:20708: na / dgra bcom pa stong phrag drug cu 'dus
NK117(she)001:20709: pa dang dge slong gi dge 'dun bcas pa la
NK117(she)001:20710: gdugs tshod drangs pa sogs bsnyen bkur rgya chen po
NK117(she)001:20711: na / dang / bcom ldan 'das kyis sku gdung
NK117(she)001:20712: la mchod pa rnam lnga sogs mchod pa'i bye brag
NK117(she)001:20713: dpag tu med pa phul lo //
NK117(she)001:20714: de'i tshe rgyal po dang klu'i gzugs gnyis byas te
NK117(she)001:20715: gser snod du bzhag nas bsod nams che chung brtags
NK117(she)001:20716: pas klu gzugs la rgyal pos phyag byed pa mthong
NK117(she)001:20717: bas / dge slong dbang pos da dung yang bsod nams bsags par mdzod ces smras pas /
NK117(she)001:20718: rgyal pos rim gyis tshogs rgya chen bsags pa'i mthar
NK117(she)001:20719: gzigs pas klu'i yan lag thams cad kyis rgyal por
NK117(she)001:20721: kye ma dkon mchog gsum mchod pa'i //
NK117(she)001:20723: rgya mtsho'i nang na gnas pa'i klu //
NK117(she)001:20724: bdag gis btul zhing 'di dbang bgyis //
NK117(she)001:20725: blo gros chung ba'i mi rnams kyang //
NK117(she)001:20726: su zhig sangs rgyas mchod mi bgyid //
NK117(she)001:20728: su zhig yid kyis sems mi bgyid //
NK117(she)001:20729: bdag nyid che ba thob 'dod pa'i //
NK117(she)001:20730: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams kyis //
NK117(she)001:20731: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yang dag mchod //
NK117(she)001:20732: skye ba zad cing yang srid med //
NK117(she)001:20734: dge slong dbang pos yang zangs ma'i byang bu klu
NK117(she)001:20735: yul du bskyur cig ces bsgos pa bzhin byas pas
NK117(she)001:20736: klu'i rgyal pos yi ge spyi bos blang shing nor
NK117(she)001:20737: rnams phyir gtad par khas blangs so //
NK117(she)001:20738: de yang dbang pos bslabs bzhin zangs byang la /
NK117(she)001:20739: 'dzam bu'i gling gi dbang phyug dam pa'i bka' bcag
NK117(she)001:20740: pa'i chad par khyed cag rang rang gi phrag par
NK117(she)001:20741: khur la 'dir skyol cig bya ba bris nas bskyur
NK117(she)001:20742: bas klu skrag nas zhag bdun nas 'phrod par khas
NK117(she)001:20743: blangs pa bzhin grong khyer phyi dbus su skye bo
NK117(she)001:20744: mang po 'tshogs pa'i dbus su rgyal po seng+ge'i khri
NK117(she)001:20746: klu rnams mi'i cha byad du sprul nas nor bu
NK117(she)001:20747: rnams phrag la bkal ba'i khur phog rgyal po'i rkang
NK117(she)001:20749: rgyal pos sangs rgyas kyi bka'i yon tan rjes su brjod pa /
NK117(she)001:20750: bsod nams me yis mi 'tshig ste //
NK117(she)001:20753: sa bzhin du ni khyer mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:20754: rgyal po dang ni chom rkun gyis //
NK117(she)001:20755: 'phrog tu med par bsod nams gnas //
NK117(she)001:20756: skyes pa dang ni bud med kyis //
NK117(she)001:20757: 'phrog par nus pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:20758: bsod nams bde ba skyed pa'i gter //
NK117(she)001:20760: gang dang gang du skyes pa ru //
NK117(she)001:20761: de dang der ni rjes su 'brang //
NK117(she)001:20763: de ltar bsod nams kho na la 'bad pa'ang tshe
NK117(she)001:20764: 'di'i ched du ma yin par mthar thug sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:20765: pa'i thabs kyi chos la sems dgos pa yang /
NK117(she)001:20767: chos la sems pa'i go cha rnam par sra //
NK117(she)001:20768: zab rgyas chos khams rgya mtsho dbang po'i mtshon //
NK117(she)001:20769: bdungs bar blo yis spobs sam mi spobs kun //
NK117(she)001:20770: snying stobs gnyen po'i dbang du gtong ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:20771: lam mi 'chugs par phyin drug steng du 'gro //
NK117(she)001:20772: zhes pa ni bdag cag gi ston pas byang chub
NK117(she)001:20773: mchog tu thugs bskyed nas bskal pa grangs med gsum
NK117(she)001:20774: du tshogs bsags pa'i ched du dka' ba sna tshogs
NK117(she)001:20775: spyad de mngon par sangs rgyas nas 'gro ba'i mgon
NK117(she)001:20777: bdag cag kyang de lta bu'i go 'phang bsgrub pa
NK117(she)001:20778: la don mthun pa'i chos la 'jug phyir rkyen ngan
NK117(she)001:20779: dang bar chod ci lta bu zhig byung yang de'i
NK117(she)001:20780: dbang du mi 'chor ba'i sems bskyed pa'i go cha
NK117(she)001:20781: le los ma phed cing rnam par sra ba gyon
NK117(she)001:20782: nas zab pa gting mi mngon pa'i chos chen po
NK117(she)001:20783: rnam pa gsum rgya mtsho dang 'dra ba'am rgya che
NK117(she)001:20784: ba'i chos rten cing 'brel 'byung nam mkha' lta bu
NK117(she)001:20786: gnyis ka la 'jug pa'i spobs pa dman pa'i sems
NK117(she)001:20787: gzengs stod dgos te 'di ltar lha'i dbang po'i gzhu
NK117(she)001:20788: ni gling bzhi'i khams kyi gyad stobs po che sus
NK117(she)001:20789: kyang bdungs par mi spobs kyang snying stobs dang ldan
NK117(she)001:20790: na de yang mtha' ma bkag pa'i dpe ded dpon
NK117(she)001:20791: slong ldan gyi nor bu klus rgya mtsho'i klong du
NK117(she)001:20792: khyer ba rgya mtsho skems par 'dod nas chu snyim
NK117(she)001:20793: pas phyags shing dbo ba la brtun pa mi lhod
NK117(she)001:20794: pa'i snying stobs la klu skrag nas nor bu phyir
NK117(she)001:20795: gtad pa lta bu'i snying stobs dang gnyen po'i dbang
NK117(she)001:20796: du gtong ba'i gang zag rnams ni lam cung zad
NK117(she)001:20797: kyang mi 'chugs par phyin drug gi steng du 'gro
NK117(she)001:20799: de yi mthun phyogs yan lag bdun pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20800: chu gtor la sogs bsag sbyangs mtha' dag yin //
NK117(she)001:20801: mi mthun phyogs kyis de la mi bardzi zhing //
NK117(she)001:20802: lam du 'gro ba bsod nams dag la bsten //
NK117(she)001:20803: 'di ni skyes bu chen po'i lam stegs yin //
NK117(she)001:20804: zhes pa ni 'dir bsod nams kyi bya ba'i mthun
NK117(she)001:20805: phyogs yan lag bdun pa dang chu gtor la sogs
NK117(she)001:20806: pa'i khong nas yar mchod mar sbyin la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:20807: tshogs bsag dang sgrib sbyangs mtha' dag yin zhing pha
NK117(she)001:20808: rol tu phyin pa drug gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK117(she)001:20809: kyis de la mi bardzi zhing lam lnga'i steng du
NK117(she)001:20810: 'gro ba'i thabs sam rgyu ni bsod nams bsag pa
NK117(she)001:20811: kho na yin pas de la bsten pa 'di ni
NK117(she)001:20812: skyes bu chen po'i lam stegs yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20813: mdor na sbyin pa'i dngos po chung yang bsam pa rgya chen po ni mchog yin no //
NK117(she)001:20814: des na rtog pa gcig 'gyu ba yan chad ngos
NK117(she)001:20815: bzung nas bsod nams dang 'gal rkyen spangs shing mthun
NK117(she)001:20817: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:20818: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:20819: lde mig las le'u lnga pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:20820: nang pa sangs rgyas kyi lam gyi 'jug sgo dang po skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK117(she)001:20822: 'jigs pa gsum gyi chu gter 'khrugs pa la //
NK117(she)001:20823: skyabs su 'os par yid ches srog brtan pa'i //
NK117(she)001:20824: dkon mchog gsum gyi grags pa'i gdugs dkar ni //
NK117(she)001:20825: bstan la zhugs pa'i thog ma nyid du 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:20826: zhes pa ni de la 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal spyi la 'jigs pa ni nyan rang lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:20827: rang don yid byed kyis 'jigs pa ni gzhan don
NK117(she)001:20828: spangs pas nyan rang dang mtshungs pa'i byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:20830: ni sngags lam du zhugs kyang snod bcud tha mal
NK117(she)001:20831: las gnas ma 'gyur bas sngags rloms dang phar phyin
NK117(she)001:20832: pas snang ba sgyu ma'i lam khyer dang bral ba
NK117(she)001:20833: dpa' 'am / bzhin no // de la 'grel tshul
NK117(she)001:20834: gnyis byas kyang rung ste ngan song gsum gyis 'jigs
NK117(she)001:20835: nas lha mi'i go 'phang gnyer ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20836: 'khor ba spyi'i sdug bsngal gyis 'jigs nas thar pa don du gnyer ba'i nyan rang dang /
NK117(she)001:20837: rang don yid byed kyis 'jigs nas gzhan don gnyer ba'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams so //
NK117(she)001:20838: de lta bu'i 'jigs pa gsum gyi chu gter 'khrugs
NK117(she)001:20839: pa lta bu la skyabs su 'os par yid ches
NK117(she)001:20840: pa ni dkon mchog gsum kho na las gzhan mthu
NK117(she)001:20841: bo che su yang med na /
NK117(she)001:20842: des nges par tshe 'di'i srog dang phyi ma thar
NK117(she)001:20843: pa'i srog gnyis ka brtan par byed pas na dkon
NK117(she)001:20844: pa'i mchog gsum gyi grags pa'i gdugs dkar zhes srin
NK117(she)001:20845: dkar gyi phung po 'dra ba de nang pa'i bstan
NK117(she)001:20846: pa la zhugs pa'i thog ma nyid du 'dzin zhes
NK117(she)001:20847: bslab sdom thams cad kyi sngon du mchog gsum skyabs
NK117(she)001:20850: thar par 'gro ba'i lam dang yon tan gyi //
NK117(she)001:20851: rten dang snod du dam bca' mi bslu ba //
NK117(she)001:20852: skyabs su 'gro ba nyid de de'i sngon du //
NK117(she)001:20853: ston dang bstan pa'i yon tan shes pa gces //
NK117(she)001:20854: zhes pa ni de bzhin du thar pa dang rnam
NK117(she)001:20855: mkhyen gyi sar 'gro ba'i lam bgrod thabs dang de'i
NK117(she)001:20856: yon tan gyi rten yul lam snod mchog tu dam
NK117(she)001:20857: bca' mi bslu ba ni skyabs su 'gro ba nyid
NK117(she)001:20858: de / de'i sngon du ston pa sangs rgyas dang
NK117(she)001:20859: bstan pa lung rtogs chos kyi yon tan shes pa
NK117(she)001:20860: gal che zhing gces zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20862: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba dad pa ni //
NK117(she)001:20863: skyes bu'i sems la lung du ma bstan pa //
NK117(she)001:20864: ston pa mthong dang sde snod bklags pa yi //
NK117(she)001:20865: mod la ba spu'i 'khri shing slong bzhin ldang //
NK117(she)001:20866: de la dang ba'i dad pa dang po ste //
NK117(she)001:20867: de bzhin 'dod dang yid ches phyir mi ldog /
NK117(she)001:20868: rnam pa bzhi las skyabs 'gro'i gnas skabs 'dir //
NK117(she)001:20869: srog la bab kyang phyir mi ldog pa dgos //
NK117(she)001:20870: zhes pa ni de la chos thams cad kyi rtsa
NK117(she)001:20871: ba dad pa yin te dad pa skye ba dang
NK117(she)001:20872: lhan cig rnam dkar gyi chos mtha' dag mngon du
NK117(she)001:20873: 'du byed cing / de yal ba dang dge legs
NK117(she)001:20874: dang yon tan gyi tshogs 'grib par gsungs pas chos
NK117(she)001:20875: rnams kun gyi rtsa ba brtan par byed pa'i thabs
NK117(she)001:20876: dad pa yin kyang skyes stobs dang sbyangs stobs kyi
NK117(she)001:20877: shes rab dang mi ldan pa'i skyes bu rmongs pa
NK117(she)001:20878: rnams kyi sems la dad pa gab nas lung ma
NK117(she)001:20880: dge sdig ston pa'i bla ma mthong ba dang sde
NK117(she)001:20881: snod gsum la sogs pa'i lung rtogs kyi gsung rab
NK117(she)001:20882: bklags pa'i rkyen gyis ba spu'i 'khri shing slong bzhin
NK117(she)001:20883: ldang zhing g.yo ba tsam byed pa de la dang
NK117(she)001:20884: ba'i dad pa zhes dang po yin la /
NK117(she)001:20886: sngon ma skyes dgra'i glang po che nor skyong ston
NK117(she)001:20887: pa la rbad tshe dang po zhe sdang gi sems
NK117(she)001:20888: kyis brgyugs kyang bcom ldan 'das mthong ma thag tu
NK117(she)001:20889: khro gtum gyi sems zhi ba bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:20890: dang ba'i dad pa de ni /
NK117(she)001:20892: gang zag dge sgrub sdig spang tshul bzhin bsgrub pa dag mthong na /
NK117(she)001:20893: de la dang ba dang rjes su yi rang ba sogs dga' ba'i 'dod chags dang lhan cig pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20894: de bzhin du 'dod pa'i dad pa ni sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:20895: bden pa'i rang mtshang skye zhing 'chi ba la skrag
NK117(she)001:20896: cing de las skyob byed dam pa'i chos 'gog lam
NK117(she)001:20897: gyi bden pa ston byed kyi bla ma snying nas
NK117(she)001:20899: yid ches kyi dad pa ni mchog gsum gyi yon
NK117(she)001:20900: tan la nges shes 'drongs shing des mi bslu bar
NK117(she)001:20901: yid ches pa'o // phyir mi ldog pa'i dad pa ni /
NK117(she)001:20902: de ltar dad pa rnam pa gsum gyis chos sgor
NK117(she)001:20903: zhugs phyin rkyen bzang ngan ci byung yang phyir mi
NK117(she)001:20904: ldog pa'i dpe sngon nang pa'i dge bsnyen gcig mu
NK117(she)001:20906: khyod rang gi lha dang lta ba thong nga'i grub mtha' la zhugs dang mi gsod /
