NK117(she)001:20907: de mi byed na gsod do byas tshe khos tshig tsam du de ltar byed /
NK117(she)001:20908: snying nas ma yin no byas pas de srog dang
NK117(she)001:20909: bral yang phyi ma 'bras bzang smin pa ltar ro
NK117(she)001:20911: dad pa skye ba'i rgyu ni bzhi yin te //
NK117(she)001:20912: dam pa bsten dang dam pa'i grogs dang 'grogs //
NK117(she)001:20913: dkon mchog rjes su dran dang 'khor ba la //
NK117(she)001:20914: snying po med pa'i nyes dmigs bsams las skye //
NK117(she)001:20915: zhes pa ni bla ma dam pa la bsten pa
NK117(she)001:20916: dang dam pa'i grogs dang 'grogs phyin dad pa sogs
NK117(she)001:20917: rnam dkar gyi dge ba thams cad gong 'phel du
NK117(she)001:20918: 'gyur ba dang / dkon mchog gsum po rtag par
NK117(she)001:20919: rjes su dran bzhin dad pa mos pa dang 'khor
NK117(she)001:20920: ba'i bya ba la snying po med nges kyi nyes
NK117(she)001:20921: dmigs bsams shing skyo shas bskyed pa las dad pa
NK117(she)001:20922: 'gyur ba dang / skye'o zhes pa'o // dad pa
NK117(she)001:20923: med bzhin skyabs 'gro dang gsol 'debs sogs bzlas pa
NK117(she)001:20924: la ci tsam brtson yang 'bras bu dman pa las
NK117(she)001:20925: 'gyur ba dang / skye'o zhes pa'o // mi 'byin no // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:20926: thub pa rnams kyi yon tan mtha' yas te //
NK117(she)001:20927: spangs pa gnyis kyis nyon shes sgrib pa bcom //
NK117(she)001:20928: spyan dang mngon shes dbang bcu gzungs kyi sgo //
NK117(she)001:20929: stobs bcu mi 'jigs bzhi dang so so rig /
NK117(she)001:20930: ma 'dres bco brgyad rdzogs pa sangs rgyas te //
NK117(she)001:20931: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:20932: sa bcu'i 'khor la longs spyod rdzogs par ston //
NK117(she)001:20933: zhes pa ni de yang byang chub mchog tu sems
NK117(she)001:20934: bskyed nas sangs ma rgyas bar du bzod dka' ba
NK117(she)001:20935: rnams thub cing yon tan mtha' yas pa tshang ba
NK117(she)001:20936: dang / 'dod chags la sogs pa byang chub la
NK117(she)001:20937: bar du gcod pa'i bdud sde bcom pa dang skal
NK117(she)001:20938: ba khyad par can dang dbang phyug la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:20940: sred len sogs srid chos thams cad las 'das pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20941: dngos po'i chos nyid ji bzhin gnas pa de bzhin du rtogs pas de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20942: mthong spangs dang bsgom spangs kyis nyon mongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:20943: shes bya'i sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs pa la bcom zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20944: sangs rgyas kyi sas bsdus pa ni rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan no //
NK117(she)001:20945: chos kyis ni 'phags pa'i gang zag dbang po rno rtul thams cad mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20946: shes rab kyis ni chos thams cad rang gi ngo
NK117(she)001:20947: bo nyid kyis stong pa'i don mngon sum du mthong
NK117(she)001:20948: ba'o // lha'i spyan gyis 'gro rnams 'chi ba dang skye ba ji bzhin shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20949: sha'i spyan gyis dpag tshad brgya nas stong gsum tshun
NK117(she)001:20950: chad kyi gzugs phra rags thams cad mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:20951: mthong ba'o // 'phrul gyi mngon shes ni /
NK117(she)001:20952: sa g.yo ba dang gcig tu bsgyur zhing du mar sprul pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20953: lha'i rna ba'i mngon shes ni /
NK117(she)001:20954: 'jig rten khams kyi sgra rnams ji bzhin du rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20956: gzhan rgyud nyon mongs dang bral min sogs ji bzhin shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20957: sngon gnas rjes dran gyi ni /
NK117(she)001:20958: rang gzhan gyi tshe rabs snga ma brgya stong sogs shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20959: lha'i mig gi ni bskal pa dang ma bskal pa'i
NK117(she)001:20960: gzugs phra rags thams cad mngon sum gyis mthong ba'o
NK117(she)001:20961: // zag pa zad pa'i mngon par shes pa ni sgrib pa gnyis spong thabs dang /
NK117(she)001:20962: spangs pa'i bral ba mngon du shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20963: bskal pa'i bar du 'tsho bar 'dod kyang sdod nus pa la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20964: ting nge 'dzin grangs med la dbang thob pa sems la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20965: nam mkha' mdzod kyi longs spyod la mnga' brnyes pas yo byad la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20966: bzo dang sgyu ma sogs la mnga' brnyes pas las la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20967: gang la gang 'dod du skye bar 'dod pas skye ba la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20968: 'gro khams rnams su rgyal ba'i skus gang bar ston nus pa sogs mos pa la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20969: byang chub chen po'i sprul pa 'gyed nus pas smon lam la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20970: gdul bya'i yul sna tshogs la dus gcig tu rdzu
NK117(she)001:20971: 'phrul sna tshogs ston nus pas rdzu 'phrul la dbang
NK117(she)001:20972: ba dang / shes bya kun thogs med du mkhyen pa'i ye shes la dbang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:20973: chos kyi tshig don kun la mkhas pas chos la dbang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:20978: shes rab mngon du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20979: chos rnams kyi tshig rab tu tha dad pa shes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:20982: gnas dang gnas min mkhyen stobs dang //
NK117(she)001:20983: de bzhin las rnam smin blo dang //
NK117(she)001:20984: mos pa sna tshogs thugs chud dang //
NK117(she)001:20985: sna tshogs khams kyi mkhyen stobs dang //
NK117(she)001:20986: de bzhin dbang mchog mchog ma yin //
NK117(she)001:20987: mkhyen dang thams cad du 'gro dang //
NK117(she)001:20988: bsam gtan rnam thar ting 'dzin dang //
NK117(she)001:20989: snyoms par 'jug sogs mkhyen stobs dang //
NK117(she)001:20990: sngon gnas dran pa mkhyen pa dang //
NK117(she)001:20992: zag rnams zad pa mkhyen stobs dang //
NK117(she)001:20993: stobs bcu po ni 'di dag go //
NK117(she)001:20995: bdag gi mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so zhes
NK117(she)001:20996: chos rnams kun gyi rang bzhin mkhyen par zhal gyis
NK117(she)001:20997: bzhes pa dang / chos mthun gyi rgol ba med
NK117(she)001:20998: pas rtogs pa phun sum tshogs pa la mi 'jigs
NK117(she)001:20999: bzhes pa dang / pa dang / sgrib gnyis kyis
NK117(she)001:21000: bsdus pa'i spang bya mtha' dag 'di ma spangs so
NK117(she)001:21001: zhes chos mthun gyi rgol ba med pas bar chad
NK117(she)001:21002: kyi chos bstan pa la mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21003: gzhi dang lam shes pa la sogs pa thar pa
NK117(she)001:21004: dang rnam mkhyen gyi nges par 'byung ba'i lam du
NK117(she)001:21005: bstan pa la mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21006: lam 'di bstan kyang nges par 'byung bar byed mi
NK117(she)001:21007: nus so zhes chos mthun gyi rgol ba med pas
NK117(she)001:21008: nges par 'byung ba'i lam bstan pa la mi 'jigs
NK117(she)001:21009: pa dang / zag pa thams cad zad par zhal
NK117(she)001:21010: gyis bzhes pa la zag pa 'di ma zad do
NK117(she)001:21011: zhes chos mthun gyi rgol ba med pas spangs pa
NK117(she)001:21012: phun sum tshogs pa la mi 'jigs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21013: so so yang dag rig bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:21014: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21015: rnam byang gi chos rnams kyi khams dang ming gi
NK117(she)001:21016: rnam grangs mkhyen pas chos so so yang dag par
NK117(she)001:21017: rig pa dang / de dag gi rang dang spyi
NK117(she)001:21018: mtshan nyid la ma rmongs pas don so so yang
NK117(she)001:21020: gdul bya'i yul dang mthun pa'i gsung rnam pa thams
NK117(she)001:21021: cad pa yin pas tshig so so yang dag par
NK117(she)001:21022: rig pa dang / rang gi ngo bo nyid dang
NK117(she)001:21023: rnam dbye thams cad mkhyen pa chags thogs med par
NK117(she)001:21024: 'jug pas spobs pa so so yang dag par rig
NK117(she)001:21025: rig pa dang / pa dang / sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad ni /
NK117(she)001:21027: 'khrul dang ca co mi mnga' ste //
NK117(she)001:21028: ston la dran pa nyams mi mnga' //
NK117(she)001:21029: mnyam par ma bzhag thugs mi mnga' //
NK117(she)001:21030: 'du shes sna tshogs kyang mi mnga' //
NK117(she)001:21031: ma brtags btang snyoms mi mnga' ste //
NK117(she)001:21033: shes rab rnam grol rnam grol gyi //
NK117(she)001:21034: ye shes gzigs pa nyams mi mnga' //
NK117(she)001:21035: las rnams ye shes sngon 'gro dang //
NK117(she)001:21036: 'dus la ye shes sgrib pa med //
NK117(she)001:21037: de ltar bco brgyad 'di rang bzhin //
NK117(she)001:21038: ston pa'i ma 'dres yon tan yin //
NK117(she)001:21042: gsung gi yon tan yang 'chad par 'os te /
NK117(she)001:21043: drin lan bsab pa'i mdo las gsungs pa tshig sna cung zad bstungs te bri na /
NK117(she)001:21044: zhabs mthil mnyam zhing gang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21045: 'khor lo rtsibs stong ri mo yod pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21046: zhabs kyi rting pa zlum la gang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21047: phyag sor phra la ring zhing bar rnams d+r+wa bar 'brel ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21048: phyag zhabs 'jam zhing mnyen pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21049: byin pa ri dwags e na ya ltar zlum la shugs kyis gzhol ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21050: long bu phyir mi snang ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21051: shing nya gro ta ltar sku'i yan lag yongs su rdzogs pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21052: ba spu gyen du nyal zhing g.yas su 'khyil ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21053: sku gser btso ma ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21054: ltag pa'i 'od 'dom gang dang ldan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21055: lpags pa mnyen 'jam la rdul dris mi dgos pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21056: gnas bdun yongs su gang ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21057: sku stod seng+ge lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:21058: lag ngar zlum la shugs kyis gzhol ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21061: tshems bzhi bcu ldan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21062: tshems thags bzang zhing mdog dkar ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21063: 'gram pa seng+ge ltar gang ba yin /
NK117(she)001:21064: ro bro ba'i mchog dang ldan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21065: sha'i do ker dang ldan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21066: ljags ring la yangs pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21067: tshangs pa'i sgra dbyangs ldan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21068: spyan mdog mthon mthing ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21069: spyan khyu mchog gi rgyal po ltar 'dug pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21070: mdzod spu dkar po ldan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:21074: ltag pa'i phyogs te bdun yin no //
NK117(she)001:21077: sen mo zangs mdog la snum pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21078: shang shong med cing mtho ba /
NK117(she)001:21079: zlum la rgyas pa phra ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21080: rtsa mi mngon zhing mdud pa med pa long bu mi mngon zhing mnyam pa /
NK117(she)001:21081: mi zil gyis gnon pa la mkhas pas seng ge'i stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21082: de bzhin du klu la glang chen lta bur gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21083: nam mkhar ngang pa'i stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21084: sems can gyi sna 'dren pa la mkhas pa khyu mchog gi stabs su gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21085: g.yas su ldog cing gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21086: mdzes pa dang drang por gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21087: 'khril bag chags par gshegs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21088: sku byi dor byas pa lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:21089: sku ring thung dang sbom phra sogs ma 'chol ba /
NK117(she)001:21091: 'jam pa dang rnam par dag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21092: mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21093: sku'i kho lag yangs shing bzang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21094: gom pa dal myur snyoms pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21095: dri ma ra ri med pas spyan gnyis dog pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21096: gzhon sha chags shing zhum pa med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21097: sha tshugs rgyas shing grims pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21098: yan lag dang nying lag rnams dbyes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21099: gzigs pa rnam par dag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21103: sku'i phyal mtho dman med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21104: lte ba zab cing g.yas su 'khyil ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21105: spyod lam blta na sdug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21107: sme ba dang gnag bag med pa /
NK117(she)001:21108: phyag 'jam zhing ri mo gsal ba dang rgyang nas gsal ba'i zab pa /
NK117(she)001:21110: zhal ha cang mi ring ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21111: zhal la gzugs kyi gzugs brnyan snang zhing mchu sgros bim pa ltar dmar ba /
NK117(she)001:21112: ljags ring zhing mnyen pa srab la dmar ba /
NK117(she)001:21113: gsung 'brug sgra lta bu dang snyan zhing 'jam pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21114: mche ba zlum zhing rno la dkar ba mnyen pa byin gyis phra ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21115: shangs gzengs mtho zhing dag cing gtsang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21116: spyan yangs shing rdzi ma stug pa dkar nag ma 'dres pa pad 'dab ltar rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21117: smin tshugs ring ba 'jam pa snum pa spu mnyam pa /
NK117(she)001:21121: dpral ba legs par dbyes pa /
NK117(she)001:21122: dbyes che ba dbu gdugs ltar rgyas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21123: skra bung ba ltar gnag pa go mtshams med par stug pa 'jam pa ma 'dzing ba /
NK117(she)001:21127: phyag zhabs kyi mthil la ri mo gru bzhi pa'i bkra shis dang /
NK117(she)001:21128: srin lag la sogs pa'i gsham du ri mo bdun
NK117(she)001:21129: g.yas su 'khyil ba'i g.yung drung 'khyil bas brgyan pa'o
NK117(she)001:21130: // mdor na sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams
NK117(she)001:21131: gang yod phyogs gcig tu spungs pa bas kyang sangs
NK117(she)001:21132: rgyas kyi ba spu gcig gi mtshan gyis 'phags so
NK117(she)001:21133: // // de las kyang sangs rgyas kyi gsung khyad par 'phags te /
NK117(she)001:21134: 'jig rten khams na gnas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK117(she)001:21135: kyis dus gcig tu rang skal dang mtshams pa'i dri
NK117(she)001:21136: ba mi 'dra ba dpag tu med pa dris kyang
NK117(she)001:21137: de rnams kun la dbyangs gcig gis lan btab pa
NK117(she)001:21138: so so'i 'dod tshul ltar go nus pas khyad par
NK117(she)001:21139: 'phags so // de yang gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu ni /
NK117(she)001:21140: nyi khri las bstan pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas bsdus te 'chad na gsung mnyen pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21149: rgol bas mi bardzi ba'i phyir mi tshugs pa /
NK117(she)001:21159: dga' bde skyed par byed pa /
NK117(she)001:21160: yongs su gdung ba med pa /
NK117(she)001:21162: rnam par rig par bya ba /
NK117(she)001:21165: rang don bral ba rnams mngon par dga' bar bya ba /
NK117(she)001:21167: rnam par rig par bya ba /
NK117(she)001:21174: lag 'gro'i dbang po'i sgra dbyangs dang /
NK117(she)001:21176: ka la ping ka'i sgra dbyangs dang /
NK117(she)001:21178: shang shang te'u'i sgra dbyangs dang /
NK117(she)001:21179: lha dbang gi dbyangs ltar snyan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21183: sgra'i mtshan nyid thams cad pa'i rjes su zhugs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21185: ma tshang ba med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21193: sgra thams cad rdzogs par byed par dang /
NK117(she)001:21194: dbang po thams cad tshim par byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21199: rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang ldan pa ste gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu'o //
NK117(she)001:21200: de ltar gzugs sku'i rang bzhin mtshan dpe rgya mtsho lta bu'i rten la /
NK117(she)001:21201: brten pa ye shes kyi chos nyid ni rnam kun mchog ldan gyi chos sku'o //
NK117(she)001:21202: de yang dbyings dag mnyam chen po sku thams cad
NK117(she)001:21203: kyi chos nyid byed pa'i cha nas ngo bo nyid
NK117(she)001:21204: sku dang / spangs rtogs mthar phyin pa rig pa'i
NK117(she)001:21205: ngo bo byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa
NK117(she)001:21206: bdun gyi bdag nyid la ni rtogs pa ye shes
NK117(she)001:21208: de la bsam gtan dang po gnyis pa gsum pa bzhi pa ste rang rang gi dngos gzhi bzhi /
NK117(she)001:21211: ci yang med pa'i skye mched /
NK117(she)001:21212: 'du shes med 'du shes med min te gzugs med pa'i dngos gzhi bzhi /
NK117(she)001:21213: 'gog pa'i snyom 'jug ste mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu /
NK117(she)001:21214: zad par sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dang /
NK117(she)001:21215: sngo ser dmar dkar po ste zad par rnam shes
NK117(she)001:21216: kyi skye mched de zad par gyi rnam pa bcu
NK117(she)001:21217: / dbyibs dang kha dog zil gyis gnon pa bzhi gnyis brgyad /
NK117(she)001:21219: smon lam mkhyen pa la sogs mdor na de'i rang
NK117(she)001:21220: bzhin ngo bo nyid dbyings nam mkha' lta bu la
NK117(she)001:21221: rtogs pa ye shes kyi nyi ma lta bu glo
NK117(she)001:21222: bur gyi sgrib pa cha dang bcas pa spangs shing
NK117(she)001:21223: rtogs pa'i yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i chos nyid
NK117(she)001:21224: nges pa nyid du blo bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o
NK117(she)001:21226: kun gzhi tshogs dang bcas pa dbyings su nub pa'i
NK117(she)001:21227: snang cha'i yon tan stong gzugs kyi skur yongs su
NK117(she)001:21228: rdzogs pa'i nges pa lnga ldan ni /
NK117(she)001:21229: gnas nges pa 'og min stug po bkod par /
NK117(she)001:21230: ston pa nges pa rigs lnga /
NK117(she)001:21231: 'khor nges pa byang sems sa bcu pa /
NK117(she)001:21232: chos nges pa theg chen 'ba' zhig /
NK117(she)001:21233: dus nges pa rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo 'byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21235: chos ni bsod nams lam dang mya ngan 'da' //
NK117(she)001:21236: brjod bya'i don te de la'ang 'bras bu dang //
NK117(she)001:21237: bya ba'i rang bzhin gnyis su gnas pa las //
NK117(she)001:21238: bden gnyis zhes bya 'gog lam rnam gnyis yin //
NK117(she)001:21239: zhes pa ni 'dir dam pa'i chos kyi rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:21240: ni bsod nams dang lam dang myang 'das gsum brjod
NK117(she)001:21242: gsung rab ni rjod byed kyi tshig tu shar bas so //
NK117(she)001:21243: de la'ang 'bras bu 'gog bden gyi chos dang bya
NK117(she)001:21244: ba'i rang bzhin lam bden gyi chos gnyis yin no
NK117(she)001:21245: // de la so so rang gi rig pa ni ye shes kyi spyod yul yin gyis /
NK117(she)001:21246: rtog dpyod kyi spyod yul ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:21248: brjod bya rjod byed la ltos lung rtogs chos //
NK117(she)001:21249: lung ni gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis dang //
NK117(she)001:21250: gnyen po'i sgo nas sde snod gsum du shar //
NK117(she)001:21251: thabs kyis che ba rig 'dzin sde snod yin //
NK117(she)001:21252: glegs bam yi ger gnas pa dam tshig rten //
NK117(she)001:21253: zhes pa ni de yang brjod bya'i don dang rjod
NK117(she)001:21254: byed la ltos nas lung rtogs kyi bstan pa gnyis
NK117(she)001:21255: su bzhag pa la lung gi chos gsung rab yan
NK117(she)001:21258: mdo sde dbyangs bsnyad lung bstan dang //
NK117(she)001:21259: tshigs bcad ched brjod gleng gzhi dang //
NK117(she)001:21260: rtogs brjod de lta bu byung dang //
NK117(she)001:21261: skyes rabs shin tu rgyas pa dang //
NK117(she)001:21262: rmad byung gtan la dbab pa'i sde //
NK117(she)001:21263: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:21264: de yang kun rdzob sgrub pa ston pa ni drang
NK117(she)001:21265: don dang don dam sgrub pa ston pa ni nges
NK117(she)001:21266: don / gnyen po'i sgo nas sde snod gsum du shar zhes pa ni /
NK117(she)001:21267: gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis kyi dang po lnga nyan thos kyi mdo sde'i sde snod dang /
NK117(she)001:21268: bar pa gsum nyan thos kyi 'dul ba /
NK117(she)001:21269: tha ma bzhi'i skyes pa rabs kyi sdes byang sems kyi 'dul ba'i sde snod kyi 'khor dang /
NK117(she)001:21270: shin tu rgyas pa dang rmad du byung ba gnyis
NK117(she)001:21271: kyis byang chub sems dpa'i mdo sde'i sde snod gtan
NK117(she)001:21273: nyan thos dang byang sems gnyis ka'i thun mong gi chos mngon pa'i sde snod do //
NK117(she)001:21274: rang sangs rgyas la sde snod logs pa med de nyan thos kyi sde snod la dmigs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21275: mdor na mdo sdes ni bslab pa gsum ka bshad do //
NK117(she)001:21276: 'dul bas ni lhag pa tshul khrims dang /
NK117(she)001:21277: lhag pa'i sems bsgrub pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:21278: tshul khrims dang ldan pa ni rim gyis ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:21279: mngon pas lhag pa'i shes rab bsgrub pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:21280: don phyin ci ma log pa ston pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:21281: de dag kyang gdul bya'i sgo nas dbye bas thabs
NK117(she)001:21282: kyis che ba ni rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod
NK117(she)001:21283: do // de lta bu'i sde snod bzhi po yang bdag po'i rkyen gyi 'du byed las yi ge /
NK117(she)001:21286: tshig 'dus pa las glegs bam du gnas pa ni
NK117(she)001:21287: skyabs su 'gro ba'i gang zag gi rten yin no
NK117(she)001:21289: rtogs pa'i chos ni dran pa nyer gzhag nas //
NK117(she)001:21290: rim bzhin lam lnga'i yon tan mtha' dag dang //
NK117(she)001:21291: 'phags pa'i spang rtogs ye shes snying po can //
NK117(she)001:21292: bskyed dang rdzogs pa gzungs dang zad par dang //
NK117(she)001:21293: slob lam bzhi dang mi slob lam gyi dngos //
NK117(she)001:21294: rgyu yi sa bcu 'bras bu'i bcu gsum sogs //
NK117(she)001:21295: rdo rje theg pa'i rigs dbye dpag tu med //
NK117(she)001:21296: gang gi ye shes rgyud la brten pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21297: zhes pa ni de la rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi rten du gyur pas na sa yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:21298: de'ang nyan rang dang byang chub sems dpa' gnyis las snga ma ni /
NK117(she)001:21304: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i sa dang /
NK117(she)001:21305: byas pa rtogs pa'i sa dang /
NK117(she)001:21307: rang rgyal gyi sa ste brgyad du gnas zhes so //
NK117(she)001:21308: byang chub sems dpa' la ni sa bcu bshad de /
NK117(she)001:21309: de lta bu'i rten du gyur pa ni lam lnga ste /
NK117(she)001:21310: de la dang po thos bsam dang bsod nams kyi
NK117(she)001:21311: tshogs la gtso bor spyod pa ni tshogs lam yin
NK117(she)001:21312: la / de'ang tshogs lam chung ngur dran pa nye
NK117(she)001:21313: bar bzhag pa bzhi yod pa'i lus dran pa nyer
NK117(she)001:21314: la / bzhag ni / mnyam bzhag nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK117(she)001:21315: rjes thob tu mi gtsang ba dang sgyu ma lta bur bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:21316: tshor ba dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK117(she)001:21317: mnyam bzhag tu ma skyes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21318: rjes thob tu gang ci tshor yang sdug bsngal dang snying po med par bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:21319: sems dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK117(she)001:21320: rang bzhin gyis stong pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21321: rjes su thob tu mi 'gag la mi gnas pa bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:21322: chos dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK117(she)001:21323: mnyam bzhag mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:21324: rjes thob tu sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad du bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:21325: tshogs lam 'bring po mi dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams mi bskyed /
NK117(she)001:21327: dge chos ma skyes pa bskyed /
NK117(she)001:21328: skyes pa gong du spel lo //
NK117(she)001:21329: tshogs lam chen por rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:21330: zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi ting nge 'dzin sems rtse
NK117(she)001:21331: gcig pa bsgoms pas spyan dang mngon shes dang rdzu
NK117(she)001:21332: 'phrul la sogs pa'i don 'grub pa ste /
NK117(she)001:21337: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mthong lam la sbyor ba ni sbyor lam gyi mtshan nyid de /
NK117(she)001:21338: lam gyi ngo bo drod dang /
NK117(she)001:21341: chos mchog bzhir gnas pa la /
NK117(she)001:21342: drod rtse ga nyis su dbang po lnga po bsgom ste /
NK117(she)001:21348: bzod chos gnyis su stobs lnga bsgom ste /
NK117(she)001:21349: dad pa'i stobs la sogs gong ltar bsgyur ro //
NK117(she)001:21350: de ltar sbyor lam cha bzhi po'i ye shes la
NK117(she)001:21351: chung 'bring chen po gsum gyi dbye bas nges 'byed
NK117(she)001:21352: cha mthun bcu gnyis zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:21353: de'ang drod rtse gnyis chung ngu dang /
NK117(she)001:21354: bzod pa 'bring chos mchog chen po ste tshe de nyid la mthong lam skye ba sbyor lam mo //
NK117(she)001:21355: lam de la 'og ma las 'phags chos lnga yod de /
NK117(she)001:21359: thag bsring gi gnyen po sogs lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:21360: chos nyid dngos su mthong tshe mthong lam ste /
NK117(she)001:21361: mthong lam gyi rten byang chub kyi yan lag bdun yin te /
NK117(she)001:21362: dran dang chos rab rnam 'byed brtson 'grus dang //
NK117(she)001:21363: dga' dang shin tu sbyangs dang ting 'dzin dang //
NK117(she)001:21364: btang snyoms 'di bdun byang chub yan lag ste //
NK117(she)001:21366: 'di'i tshe sgrib gnyis las grol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21367: sbyin pa la sogs phar phyin lnga'i sgrib pa ser sna la sogs pa ni nyon sgrib dang /
NK117(she)001:21368: shes rab la 'khor gsum bden zhen dang ma bsgribs
NK117(she)001:21369: lung ma bstan gyi ngo bo gzung 'dzin du gyur
NK117(she)001:21370: pa shes sgrib yin pas de gnyis ka las grol
NK117(she)001:21371: ba'o // de'ang 'das pa'i ye shes thog mar thob
NK117(she)001:21372: pa de'i tshe spang bya sa bon dang bcas pa
NK117(she)001:21374: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis bdag med gnyis
NK117(she)001:21375: mngon sum du rtogs pas sngon med pa'i dga' ba
NK117(she)001:21376: rgya chen thob pas rab tu dga' ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21377: 'di'i dus skad cig gcig la sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal
NK117(she)001:21378: mjal ba dang byin gyis brlabs par shes pa dang
NK117(she)001:21379: rang nyid kyang sprul pa brgya 'gyed pa dus bskal
NK117(she)001:21380: brgyar ston pa / sngon dang phyi ma'i gnas brgya la ye shes kyi gzigs pa 'jug pa /
NK117(she)001:21381: ting nge 'dzin brgya la 'jug cing ldang ba /
NK117(she)001:21382: sems can brgya smin par byed pa /
NK117(she)001:21383: zhing khams brgya g.yo zhing 'od kyis gsal bar byed pa /
NK117(she)001:21384: chos sgo brgya 'byed cing lus brgyar ston bzhin de re re la 'khor de ltas bskor ba /
NK117(she)001:21385: srid pa phyi mar 'dzam gling la dbang ba'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin nus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21386: bsam bzhin du skye ba gzhan yang 'dzin par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:21387: 'di'i dus 'phags lam yan lag brgyad ldan te /
NK117(she)001:21388: yang dag lta dang 'tsho dang rtsol ba dang //
NK117(she)001:21389: dran dang ting 'dzin ngag dang las mtha' dang //
NK117(she)001:21390: yang dag rtogs nyid lam gyi yan lag brgyad //
NK117(she)001:21392: de yang phar phyin bcu'i dri ma bcu sel ba la ltos nas sa bcur bzhag kyang /
NK117(she)001:21393: phyin bcu rang rang gtso bor spyod bzhin lhag ma rnams kyang sgrub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21394: de'ang bsgom lam chung 'bring che gsum gyis dbye bas dgu ste /
NK117(she)001:21395: chung ngu'i chung ngu sa gnyis pa dri ma med
NK117(she)001:21396: pa ni tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa
NK117(she)001:21397: sogs 'og ma kun la de'i 'gres kyis sa bcu
NK117(she)001:21398: dang phyin bcu sbyor shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:21399: chung ngu'i 'bring sa gsum pa 'od byed pa /
NK117(she)001:21400: chung ngu'i chen po sa bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21401: de gsum ka'i rnam smin ni /
NK117(she)001:21402: dang pos gser gyi 'khor los bsgyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21403: gnyis pas lha'i dbang po brgya byin /
NK117(she)001:21404: gsum pas mtshe ma'i lha rgyal gyi skye ba 'dzin to //
NK117(she)001:21405: 'bring gi chung ngus lnga pa sbyang dka' ba /
NK117(she)001:21406: 'bring gi 'bring sa drug pa mngon du gyur pa /
NK117(she)001:21407: 'bring gi chen po sa bdun pa ring du song ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21411: gsum pas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi rgyal por 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:21412: chen po'i chung ngu sa brgyad pa mi g.yo ba /
NK117(she)001:21413: chen po'i 'bring sa dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros /
NK117(she)001:21414: chen po'i chen po sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin /
NK117(she)001:21415: de gsum gyi dang pos lha chen tshangs pa /
NK117(she)001:21416: gnyis pas tshangs pa chen po /
NK117(she)001:21417: gsum pas gnas gtsang lha'i bdag por 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:21418: de las gnyis pa'i skabs yon tan stong phrag bcu gnyis dang /
NK117(she)001:21420: bzhi par bye ba phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:21421: lnga par bye ba stong phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:21422: drug par bye ba 'bum phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:21423: bdun par bye ba phrag khrig 'bum phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:21424: brgyad par stong chen 'bum phrag gcig gi rdul dang
NK117(she)001:21425: mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhal blta ba la sogs
NK117(she)001:21427: dgu par stong chen grangs med pa 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i yon tan thob /
NK117(she)001:21428: bcu par sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod du med pa'i
NK117(she)001:21429: yang brjod du med pa'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam
NK117(she)001:21430: pa'i rdul phra rab snyed kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhal
NK117(she)001:21431: blta ba sogs yon tan bcu gnyis po skad cig
NK117(she)001:21432: gcig la mngon du byed do //
NK117(she)001:21433: gong du sa bcu'i yon tan bshad pa'i skabs su
NK117(she)001:21434: 'khor los bsgyur ba la sogs pa'i rim pas 'phags
NK117(she)001:21435: pa'i lha'i rgyal po rnams kyi skye srid 'dzin par
NK117(she)001:21436: bshad kyang gnas rigs de dag gi rgyal po yin
NK117(she)001:21437: tshad pa de dag la gnas pas ma khyab ste
NK117(she)001:21438: / so skye bsod nams rlabs chen bsags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21439: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa yang de ltar snang bas 'gro don mdzad pa'ang yod do //
NK117(she)001:21440: de yang sa dang po yan chad nas tshe la
NK117(she)001:21441: dbang thob pas skye 'chi'i re dogs rang mtshan pa
NK117(she)001:21442: med kyang 'gro ngor ltar snang tsam du skye rga
NK117(she)001:21443: na 'chi'i tshul ston par yang gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:21444: lam lnga'i mthar thug mi slob pa'i lam ni bslab bya rnams zad pa'i dus te /
NK117(she)001:21445: nyan thos ltar na 'dzam gling gi rgyal rigs sam bram ze'i rigs las sangs rgya bar 'dod cing /
NK117(she)001:21446: theg pa chen po ba ltar na gtsang ris lnga
NK117(she)001:21447: 'das pa na dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min nyan
NK117(she)001:21448: thos 'phags pa rnams skye bar mi nus pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:21449: yod pas der sangs rgyas nas gdod sprul pa 'dzam
NK117(she)001:21450: gling du sangs rgyas pa'i tshul ston par bzhed do
NK117(she)001:21451: // mi slob pa'i lam de'i ngo bo ni sku
NK117(she)001:21452: gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid yin la sa'i ngos
NK117(she)001:21453: nas brjod na bcu gcig kun tu 'od de rgyu'i
NK117(she)001:21454: theg pa'i rtse mo sprul sku'i sa mthar thug go
NK117(she)001:21455: // // yang slob dpon zhi ba 'tshos phar phyin
NK117(she)001:21456: rang lam gyis kyang sngags kyi rdo rje 'dzin par
NK117(she)001:21457: 'dod pa ni spyi don tsam mo //
NK117(she)001:21458: de yang mdo sngags kyi sangs rgyas gnyis rnam pa'i cha nas mi mtshungs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21460: phrin las dang zhing dang spyod yul dang /
NK117(she)001:21461: sa lam gyi rnam bzhag sogs kyi khyad par dbye
NK117(she)001:21462: yang don la dpags na chos kyi dbyings ni yongs
NK117(she)001:21464: de la re zhig rdo rje theg pa'i sa'i khyad par ni /
NK117(she)001:21475: so so'i bdag nyid dag pa'i sa ste bcu gnyis su bshad ched ni rigs lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:21477: thabs shes gnyis la grags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21478: de las ma chags pa'i shes rab dang mi dmigs pa'i thugs rjer ldan pa ni /
NK117(she)001:21479: bcu gnyis ma chags pad+ma can dang /
NK117(she)001:21480: de'i byin rlabs las rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas
NK117(she)001:21481: pa rtsol med lhun grub tu 'byung bas bcu gsum
NK117(she)001:21482: pa yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK117(she)001:21488: mee tri pas phar phyin theg pa'i rang lam gyis
NK117(she)001:21489: sangs rgyas mi thob kyang sngags kyi lam stegs su
NK117(she)001:21491: n+aa ro pas phar phyin theg pa bas sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:21492: thob kyang sngags dang de gnyis kyi khyad par ni
NK117(she)001:21493: / sa bcu gcig pas da dung sngags lam la
NK117(she)001:21494: zhugs nas myur lam gyis sangs rgyas bsgrub dgos par
NK117(she)001:21495: / bzhed do // 'di ltar rgyal ba rnams kyi
NK117(she)001:21496: rdo rje gsum gyi rang bzhin ni byang chub kyi
NK117(she)001:21497: / bzhed do // sems yin la / de ni rigs kyi sems dang /
NK117(she)001:21499: 'bras bu'i sems rnams so so ma yin te chos nyid kun tu 'gro ba rigs par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:21500: sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin ni bsam gyis mi khyab
NK117(she)001:21501: pa'i phyir bsam pas gzhal du mi rung bar bshad
NK117(she)001:21502: do // de ltar chos dkon mchog gi yon tan shes pa des rgyal ba'i bstan pa shes shing /
NK117(she)001:21503: de shes pas grub mtha' yang shes la /
NK117(she)001:21504: des 'khor ba las gang gis skyob pa'i mtshan nyid kyang shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21506: dge 'dun ngo bo rig grol gnyis ldan te //
NK117(she)001:21507: nyan rang zhugs gnas skyes bu zung bzhi'am //
NK117(she)001:21508: ya brgyad rgyal sras sar gnas mtha' dag pa'i //
NK117(she)001:21509: rang sa'i yon tan brjod kyis mi lang yang //
NK117(she)001:21510: lam dang skyob pa'i ngo bo dam pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:21511: chos ni ston pa las byung de bsgrub pa'i //
NK117(she)001:21512: grogs sam bslab pa'i rten gnas dge 'dun phyir //
NK117(she)001:21513: dkon mchog gsum zhes skyabs kyi yul du grub //
NK117(she)001:21514: ces pa ni de la dge 'dun gyi ngo bo rig grol gyi yon tan brgyad ldan te /
NK117(she)001:21515: de yang ji lta ba rig pa'i yon tan /
NK117(she)001:21516: ji snyed pa rig pa'i yon tan /
NK117(she)001:21517: nang ye shes gzigs pa'i rig pa'i yon tan dang gsum /
NK117(she)001:21518: de'i steng du spang bya chags sgrib las grol ba'i yon tan /
NK117(she)001:21519: thogs sgrib las grol ba'i yon tan /
NK117(she)001:21520: dman sgrib las grol ba'i yon tan /
NK117(she)001:21521: dbye gzhi rig pa'i yon tan /
NK117(she)001:21522: grol ba'i yon tan gnyis bsnan pas brgyad do //
NK117(she)001:21523: de brgyad du tshang ba ni 'phags pa phyir mi
NK117(she)001:21524: ldog pa'i dge 'dun yin pas dge 'dun gyi ngo
NK117(she)001:21526: nyan rang gi rig grol las dman pas de'i yan lag lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:21527: nyan thos ni ston pas kun tu sbyor ba gsum spangs pas rgyun du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK117(she)001:21528: zhes pa ni dug gsum gnyen pos bcil te zhi
NK117(she)001:21529: gnas rtse gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin la mi g.yeng
NK117(she)001:21530: ba'o // 'dod pa'i 'dod chags srabs pas lan cig phyir 'ong ba'i 'bras bu'o //
NK117(she)001:21531: 'og ma'i cha can gyi kun tu sbyor ba lnga
NK117(she)001:21532: ni dug lnga rang rgyud la lnga gnyen pos spong
NK117(she)001:21534: bla ma'i cha can gyi kun tu sbyor ba lnga
NK117(she)001:21535: ni spang gnyen gnyis su 'dzin pa lnga dang bral
NK117(she)001:21537: 'di ltar rgyun zhugs zhugs gnas gnyis /
NK117(she)001:21540: dgra bcom zhugs gnas gnyis te ya brgyad yin la /
NK117(she)001:21541: gnyis re sbrel na zung bzhi'o //
NK117(she)001:21542: rang rgyal la'ang zhugs gnas brgyad yod de nyan thos
NK117(she)001:21543: las 'phags pa'i khyad par ni kun 'byung ba'i chos
NK117(she)001:21544: de dag thams cad 'gog pa'i chos can du shes
NK117(she)001:21546: de yan phyi'i dge 'dun yin la nang gi dge
NK117(she)001:21547: 'dun ni rgyal sras sar gnas mtha' dag pa zhes
NK117(she)001:21551: las las skyes pa'i dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma ye shes kyi spyan ldan rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:21552: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang rdo rje rin chen
NK117(she)001:21553: pad+ma las kyi rigs te 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK117(she)001:21557: lhun grub rig 'dzin te sa dang 'bras bur gnas pa'i rig 'dzin gyi tshogs rnams so //
NK117(she)001:21559: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis shes bya thams cad la
NK117(she)001:21560: chags thogs med par khyab pa nor bu lta bu
NK117(she)001:21561: dkon pa dang / 'gro ba rnams la bu gcig
NK117(she)001:21562: par ltar brtse ba'i thugs rje dang ldan pas phyogs
NK117(she)001:21563: ris kyi dri ma med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21564: 'dod pas zil gyis non pa'i 'gro ba mtha' dag 'dul ba'i nus pa che ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21565: 'jig rten spyi'i rgyan mchog tu gyur pa'i yon tan zad mi shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21566: zab cing rgya che ba'i chos nyid 'gro ba kun
NK117(she)001:21567: la sman pa'i phrin las 'ba' zhig tu shar ba
NK117(she)001:21568: nam yang bslu ba med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21569: sngon phug ron gcig khras ded pa sh+aa ri'i bu'i phag tu gab kyang skrag cing sngangs la /
NK117(she)001:21570: sangs rgyas kyi sku grib tu phyin pas 'jigs skrag dang ya nga ba med pa'i don ni /
NK117(she)001:21571: sh+aa ri'i bu ni bskal pa drug cu'i bar du
NK117(she)001:21572: dka' ba spyad kyang byams snying rje chung ba'i skyon
NK117(she)001:21573: dang / sangs rgyas ni de las lhag pa'i bskal
NK117(she)001:21574: pa grangs med gsum gyi bar du tshogs gnyis bsags
NK117(she)001:21575: pas khyad par 'phags pa dang byams snying rje bsam
NK117(she)001:21576: gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pas 'phags pa'i phyir
NK117(she)001:21577: dang / ro // dper na lhas sbyin gyis dkon
NK117(she)001:21578: mchog gsum la skyabs su song ba yang dag pa'i
NK117(she)001:21580: de ni rgyun du rnyed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21582: grags pa'i phyir thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes can
NK117(she)001:21583: du tshul 'chos shing sangs rgyas la'ang skur pa 'debs
NK117(she)001:21584: pa sogs kyis mtshams med pa'i dmyal bar song mod
NK117(she)001:21585: kyang mchog gsum la skyabs su song ba'i mthus sdug
NK117(she)001:21586: bsngal yang zhing chung la thar pa'i skabs kyang yod
NK117(she)001:21588: rgyal po ma skyes dgras mtshams med pa'i sdig pa
NK117(she)001:21589: byas bzhin de'i rnam smin gyis mtshams med pa'i dmyal
NK117(she)001:21590: bar lhung bar rigs pa la /
NK117(she)001:21591: dad pa'i sems kyis sangs rgyas la skyabs su song
NK117(she)001:21592: bas mtshams med pa'i sdig pa myong rgyu zhag bdun
NK117(she)001:21593: gyi zad pa nas dkon mchog gsum zhes skyabs kyi
NK117(she)001:21596: de la rgyu dang 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro yi //
NK117(she)001:21597: dam bca' gnyis las dus gzhan 'grub 'dod rgyu //
NK117(she)001:21598: da ltar 'grub pa rang sems 'bras bu'i skyabs //
NK117(she)001:21599: rdo rje theg pa dag gi khyad chos yin //
NK117(she)001:21600: rgyu yi yul ni dkon mchog rnam pa gsum //
NK117(she)001:21601: sngags su de yi ngo bo bla mar 'dus //
NK117(she)001:21602: zhes pa ni de la phar phyin theg pas dus
NK117(she)001:21603: gzhan bskal pa grangs med gsum la sogs pa'i mthar
NK117(she)001:21604: sangs rgyas thob par dmigs nas gzhan rgyud la byon
NK117(she)001:21605: zin pa'i dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su song bas
NK117(she)001:21606: sangs rgyas 'thob pa'i rgyu byed pas na rgyu'i skyabs
NK117(she)001:21607: 'gro zhes bya'o // skyabs su 'gro yul de dag
NK117(she)001:21608: gi spangs rtogs kyi ye shes 'byung 'gyur la rang
NK117(she)001:21609: rgyud du smin par 'dod pa ni 'bras bu'i skyabs
NK117(she)001:21610: 'gro zhes bya'o // 'agro'o // khyad par rdo rje
NK117(she)001:21611: theg pa ba ltar na rang gi sems kyi de
NK117(she)001:21612: nyid mthong bar 'dod nas mchog gsum gzhan nas mi
NK117(she)001:21613: 'tshol bar rig pa sku gsum gyi bdag nyid gsal
NK117(she)001:21614: gdab cing de'i ngang du mnyam par 'jog pa ni
NK117(she)001:21616: rgyu phar phyin theg pa'i skabs sangs rgyas gtso bor 'dzin gyi /
NK117(she)001:21617: sngags bla med la bla ma kho na gtso bor bshad do //
NK117(she)001:21619: nyi tshe mchog dang bla na med pa yi //
NK117(she)001:21620: kun slong gsum las skyes bu chung ngu ni //
NK117(she)001:21621: ngan 'gro la 'jigs mngon mtho'i bar du 'gro //
NK117(she)001:21622: 'bring gnyis srid pas 'jigs nas thar pa gnyer //
NK117(she)001:21623: gnas skabs ji srid 'tsho dang mthar thug ni //
NK117(she)001:21624: nyan rang 'bras bu thob pa'i bar du 'gro //
NK117(she)001:21625: chen po gzhan don spang ba'i zhi bdes 'jigs //
NK117(she)001:21626: 'khor ba dbugs 'byin chen po la bsgral phyir //
NK117(she)001:21627: byang chub bar 'gro de yang rang gi sems //
NK117(she)001:21628: bral thob bslu ba spangs pa 'bras bu'i skyabs //
NK117(she)001:21629: zhes pa ni de la skyes bu chung ngu ni
NK117(she)001:21630: tshe 'di don du gnyer ba min kyang phyi ma
NK117(she)001:21632: skyes bu 'bring ni srid pa'i gnas mtho dman thams
NK117(she)001:21633: cad sdug bsngal du shes bzhin de las thar bar
NK117(she)001:21634: 'dod cing rang kho na sangs rgyas pa'i thabs la
NK117(she)001:21635: dmigs te skyabs su 'gro zhing gnas skabs ji srid
NK117(she)001:21636: 'tsho'i bar dang mthar thug nyan rang gi 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:21638: skyes bu chen po ni gzhan don spang ba'i zhi
NK117(she)001:21639: bde la 'jigs shing 'gro ba yongs sdug bsngal thams
NK117(she)001:21640: cad zad par bya ba'i phyir mchog gsum la skyabs
NK117(she)001:21641: su 'gro ba'o // dus kyang byang chub snying po'i
NK117(she)001:21642: bar ram sangs rgyas kyi ye shes rang rgyud la
NK117(she)001:21643: grub nas bral thob dang bslu ba spangs pa 'bras
NK117(she)001:21644: bu'i skyabs gnas la reg pa'i bar ro //
NK117(she)001:21646: lam dus sangs rgyas rnams ni sems can gyi //
NK117(she)001:21647: khams la thugs rje dus las yol ba med //
NK117(she)001:21648: ba spu'i khung bu gcig gi yon tan kyang //
NK117(she)001:21649: mtha' dag brjod pas ma thug nam mkha' lding //
NK117(she)001:21650: bya lam grub mtha' ma snyogs slar 'bab 'dra //
NK117(she)001:21651: zhes pa ni de la rmi lam gyi lam /
NK117(she)001:21655: rgyu dang 'bras bu so sor ma nges pa'i lam
NK117(she)001:21656: ste rgyud lnga'i bsdus pa'i 'gro ba yongs la snying
NK117(she)001:21657: rje chen pos phan 'dogs pa la snyel ba med
NK117(she)001:21658: pa sangs rgyas kyi phrin las kyi yon tan yin
NK117(she)001:21659: zhing / sangs rgyas kyi mkhyen brtse nus gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:21660: mdzad phrin ni 'gro ba'i khams la phan pa rgyun
NK117(she)001:21661: chags su 'brel bas na nam yang bslu ba med
NK117(she)001:21662: pa yin la rgyal ba'i ba spu'i khung bu gcig
NK117(she)001:21663: gi yon tan mtha' dag brjod pas mthar thug pa
NK117(she)001:21664: med pa'i dpe bya dar la bab pa zhig gis
NK117(she)001:21665: nam mkha'i mtha' btsal bas ma rnyed nas thang chad
NK117(she)001:21666: de slar 'bab pa dang 'dra zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21668: 'di na 'khor ba'i 'khor lor yang na yang //
NK117(she)001:21669: brgyud de las ngan bsags pa'i mtshang can rnams //
NK117(she)001:21670: 'khor los bsgyur dang dbang phyug la sogs pa //
NK117(she)001:21671: skyabs gzhan gang gis bslu bar mthong nas ni //
NK117(she)001:21672: 'jigs dang dad dang snying rje rnam gsum gyis //
NK117(she)001:21673: gzhan don sems pa skyes bu chen po'i blos //
NK117(she)001:21674: dkon mchog rjes su dran pas skyabs su 'gro //
NK117(she)001:21675: zhes pa ni de yang 'jig rten na 'khor ba
NK117(she)001:21676: rigs drug 'khor lor 'khor ba lta bu la yang
NK117(she)001:21677: nas yang du brgyud de nyon mongs brgyad khri'i las
NK117(she)001:21678: ngan bsags pa'i mtshang can rnams /
NK117(she)001:21679: 'khor los bsgyur rgyal dang dbang phyug la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:21680: la skyabs btsal yang dkon mchog gsum la gtogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:21681: gzhan mthu bo che gang gis kyang bslu bar mthong
NK117(she)001:21682: nas gzhan don spang ba'i 'jigs pa dang mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:21683: la snying nas dad pa dang ris med kyi snying
NK117(she)001:21684: rje rnam pa gsum gyis gzhan don kho na sems
NK117(she)001:21685: pa skyes bu chen po'i blos dkon mchog gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:21686: yon tan rjes su dran pas skyabs su 'gro dgos
NK117(she)001:21688: ji ltar nam mkha' tshad gzung med pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:21689: dkon mchog la brten dkar nag las 'bras kyi //
NK117(she)001:21690: pha mtha' mi dpogs skyabs song gzugs gyur na //
NK117(she)001:21691: nam mkha'i snod kyis brten par nus ma yin //
NK117(she)001:21692: nang pa'i khyur 'gro sdom pa mtha' dag brten //
NK117(she)001:21693: sdig sgrib 'dzad cing gnod pa'i tshogs kyis spong //
NK117(she)001:21694: ngan 'gro'i g.yang bsrung dkon mchog gsum mi 'bral //
NK117(she)001:21695: phun sum tshogs pa mthong ba'i chos la 'ong //
NK117(she)001:21696: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs gzugs kyi sku gnyis 'grub //
NK117(she)001:21697: ces pa ni 'di ltar nam mkha' tshad bzung med
NK117(she)001:21698: pa ltar dkon mchog gsum la brten pa'i rnam dkar
NK117(she)001:21699: dang nag po sdig pa'i las dang 'bras bu gnyis
NK117(she)001:21700: kyi pha mtha' sus kyang mi dpogs shing mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:21701: rin po cher skyabs su song ba'i phan yon gzugs
NK117(she)001:21702: dang rjes su grub pa zhig yin na nam mkha'
NK117(she)001:21703: 'di snod kyi dngos por gyur kyang shong bar dka'
NK117(she)001:21704: bas na brten par nus ma yin zhes dang /
NK117(she)001:21705: skyabs su song ba'i dgos ched kyang /
NK117(she)001:21707: skyabs su song ma thag tu mchog gsum gyi sde tshan du tshud pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21708: sdom pa thams cad kyi rtsa bar 'gyur zhing sngon
NK117(she)001:21709: bsags pa'i las sgrib dang sdig pa rnams kyang la
NK117(she)001:21710: la ni bsrab cing la la ni 'dzad pa dang
NK117(she)001:21711: nyer 'tshe'i tshogs kyis spong ba yang sngon sgrub pa
NK117(she)001:21712: po zhig la rkun po zhig gis rku ru phyin
NK117(she)001:21713: pa na sgrub pos rkun po la khyod rang lag
NK117(she)001:21714: pa yar skyongs dang chas ka rnams gtad byas pas
NK117(she)001:21715: khos bden par 'khrul nas de ltar byas pas des
NK117(she)001:21716: de'i lag pa bzung nas ber kas mgo la lan
NK117(she)001:21717: gsum brdeg pa dang chabs gcig mchog gsum la skyabs
NK117(she)001:21718: 'gro byas 'phral kho na tshas gdung bzhin bros nas
NK117(she)001:21719: zam zur zhig tu gab nas bsdad cing khos yang
NK117(she)001:21720: mchog gsum la dad pas ma yin kyang sngon ma'i
NK117(she)001:21721: lad mo'i kha 'chal gyis mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro
NK117(she)001:21723: pha ri nas mi ma yin mang po zam thog
NK117(she)001:21724: nas 'ongs tshe skyabs 'gro'i sgra tshor ba dang bros
NK117(she)001:21725: pa lta bu'o // 'khor ba dang ngan song la
NK117(she)001:21726: sogs mi mthun pa'i phyogs mtha' dag las skyob pa
NK117(she)001:21727: dang mchog gsum skyabs su rnyed pa la dga' ba
NK117(she)001:21728: bsgoms rjes bsngo smon dang 'brel na sdig pa 'dzad
NK117(she)001:21729: cing dge ba 'phel bas tshe rabs thams cad du
NK117(she)001:21730: dkon mchog gsum dang mi 'bral zhing srid dang zhi
NK117(she)001:21731: ba'i phun sum 'tshogs pa mtha' dag mthong ba'i chos
NK117(she)001:21732: la 'byung ba dang gnas skabs su rgyu'i skyabs 'gros
NK117(she)001:21733: bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs shing mthar thug gzugs sku
NK117(she)001:21734: rnam pa gnyis rdzogs zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21736: 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro bslu ba med pa ni //
NK117(she)001:21737: rnam thar sgo gsum smon pa med pa'i dbyings //
NK117(she)001:21738: gnas lugs rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa yin //
NK117(she)001:21739: ye shes tshogs rdzogs dag pa gnyis ldan 'thob //
NK117(she)001:21740: ces pa ni de la phar phyin theg pa bas
NK117(she)001:21741: 'byung 'gyur gyi char rang rgyud la 'grub rung gi
NK117(she)001:21742: sangs rgyas la dmigs te smon pa ni 'bras bu'i
NK117(she)001:21743: skyabs 'gror 'dod kyang gzhan don la dmigs pa ni
NK117(she)001:21744: ma yin zhing / 'dir ni chos sku de yang gzhan rgyud la byon zin pa de rgyu dang /
NK117(she)001:21745: 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro bslu ba med pa ni rang
NK117(she)001:21746: gi sems nyid chos sku'i rang bzhin spros pa thams
NK117(she)001:21747: cad dang bral ba ni sangs rgyas 'gyur ba med
NK117(she)001:21748: cing dri mas ma gos pa ni dam chos /
NK117(she)001:21749: yon tan thams cad lhun grub tu rdzogs pa dge
NK117(she)001:21750: 'dun zhes ngo bo'i cha nas rnam thar sgo gsum
NK117(she)001:21751: gyi bzhugs tshul chen po yul mchog gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:21752: yul can bdag sogs 'gro ba zhes skyabs su 'gro
NK117(she)001:21753: bya 'gro byed kyi tha snyad thams cad smon pa
NK117(she)001:21754: med pa'i dbyings su zhi ba ni 'bras bu'i skyabs
NK117(she)001:21755: 'gro rang sems kyi gnas lugs 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK117(she)001:21756: rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa yin zhes pa /
NK117(she)001:21757: de lta bu rtogs pas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs
NK117(she)001:21758: nas ye nas dag pa'i ngo bo dri bral dang
NK117(she)001:21759: glo bur sgrib gnyis kyi bag chags gnyis ka dag
NK117(she)001:21760: pa'i dag pa gnyis ldan thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21761: de yang skyabs su dkon mchog gsum snying thag pa
NK117(she)001:21762: nas 'dzin snyam pa'i sgo nas sdom pa blangs pa
NK117(she)001:21763: lus dang srog la thug kyang mi 'dor ba gal
NK117(she)001:21764: che zhing / de la spang bya gsum bsgrub bya
NK117(she)001:21765: gsum cha mthun gsum bcas shes bzhin blang dor tshul
NK117(she)001:21766: bzhin byed pa gal che ste /
NK117(she)001:21767: rang nyid dkon mchog gsum la ci tsam gus pa
NK117(she)001:21768: de tsam du 'gro ba gzhan dag bdag la gus
NK117(she)001:21769: pa ni las 'bras bslu ba med pa'i phyir ro
NK117(she)001:21771: bslab bya rgyu 'bras gnyis las dang po ni //
NK117(she)001:21772: mnga' ris bya dag'i slad du smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:21773: srog gi phyir yang dkon mchog gtong ba min //
NK117(she)001:21774: de yi ngo bo bla mar skyabs song nas //
NK117(she)001:21775: dam pa bslu dang mi snyan sgrog pa spang //
NK117(she)001:21776: de bzhin sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK117(she)001:21777: skyabs su song nas rim bzhin bdag nyid ni //
NK117(she)001:21778: 'khor bar 'khor ba'i lha la phyag mi 'tshal //
NK117(she)001:21779: gzhan la mi 'tshe mu stegs can mi 'grogs //
NK117(she)001:21780: dkon mchog rten la dad pas bsnyen bkur zhing //
NK117(she)001:21781: nyin mtshan brjed pa spangs nas skyabs su 'gro //
NK117(she)001:21782: zhes pa ni skyabs 'gro la bslab bya gnyis yod pa'i dang po rgyu'i skyabs 'gro'i blang dor ni /
NK117(she)001:21783: mchog gsum rin po cher snying nas skyabs su song
NK117(she)001:21784: ba'i gang zag zhig la gzhan rgyal po sogs dbang
NK117(she)001:21785: chen zhig gis khyod kyis skyabs 'gro 'di zhog dang
NK117(she)001:21786: mnga' ris la dbang bskur ram zas nor longs spyod
NK117(she)001:21787: kyi bya dga' ci tsam ster zer yang mi gtong
NK117(she)001:21789: skyabs 'gro mi gtong na srog gcod par nges kyang mi gtong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21790: mchog gsum gyi ngo bo bla ma las gzhan pa'i
NK117(she)001:21791: sangs rgyas rnams ni mkhyen brtse nus gsum gyi thugs
NK117(she)001:21792: rje che yang rang la chos ston pa'i skal ba
NK117(she)001:21794: chos kyi tshig don sogs bla ma la ma bsten
NK117(she)001:21795: par rang stobs kyis phan par ma nus tshe mchog
NK117(she)001:21796: gsum gyi ngo bo bla ma ste de'i sku dge
NK117(she)001:21797: 'dun gsung dam chos thugs sangs rgyas yin pas na
NK117(she)001:21798: bla ma dam pa bslu zhing mi snyan pa sgrog
NK117(she)001:21799: pa tsam yang spang dgos zhes gdams pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21800: de bzhin du sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la
NK117(she)001:21801: skyabs su song nas rim bzhin bdag nyid dang slob
NK117(she)001:21802: bu sogs / 'khor bar 'khor ba'i lha'i gtso bo
NK117(she)001:21803: rnams dang yul lha sogs la phyag mi 'tshal ba
NK117(she)001:21804: dang gzhan sems can su la'ang gnod 'tshe mi byed
NK117(she)001:21805: cing mu stegs can zhes pa las rgyu 'bras la
NK117(she)001:21806: smod pa dag dang mi 'grogs pa ni spang bya
NK117(she)001:21807: bu sogs / gsum mo // sku gsung thugs rten
NK117(she)001:21808: chung ngu tsam la'ang dad pas bsnyen bkur zhing nyin
NK117(she)001:21809: mtshan kun tu mchog gsum mi brjed bzhin du skyabs
NK117(she)001:21812: 'bras bu'i bslab bya thub pa chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:21813: bral thob spangs pa'i dbyings la byang chub pas //
NK117(she)001:21814: skyob dang bskyab byar mi 'dzin tha snyad las //
NK117(she)001:21815: 'das phyir gtong rgyu'ang btags pa bla dwags yin //
NK117(she)001:21816: zhes pa ni de la sems kyi ngo bo rang
NK117(she)001:21817: stobs kyis rig nas dkon mchog gsum rgyud gzhan las
NK117(she)001:21818: byung ba ma yin par rtogs pa ni 'bras bu'i
NK117(she)001:21819: skyabs 'gro dang / sems byung don gyi khyad par
NK117(she)001:21820: me long la gzugs brnyan sna tshogs su 'char ba'i
NK117(she)001:21821: rang bzhin shes pa lta bu ni rgyu'i skyabs 'agro'o
NK117(she)001:21822: skyabs 'gro dang / // des na 'bras bu'i bslab
NK117(she)001:21823: bya thub pa chos kyi sku ni sems dang sems
NK117(she)001:21824: byung dbyings su zhi ba'i tshe skyob byed dkon mchog
NK117(she)001:21825: dang bskyab bya sems can du blta ba gnyis ka
NK117(she)001:21826: med pas bslab bya btang mtshams kyang tha snyad tsam
NK117(she)001:21827: skyabs 'gro dang / // du zad do // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:21828: rgyu'i gtong mtshams skyabs 'gro mtshan nyid pa //
NK117(she)001:21829: 'gro ba'i yul la log lta skyes pas gtong //
NK117(she)001:21830: bslab pa nyams na dman par ltung ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:21831: rma yi bag bzhin bsgrims te bsrung bar bya //
NK117(she)001:21832: zhes pa ni de la rgyu'i skyabs 'gro'i sdom pa
NK117(she)001:21833: gtong mtshams ni dkon mchog gsum la log lta skyes
NK117(she)001:21834: te snying nas spangs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21835: skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya phul bas gtong ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21836: de yang skyabs su 'gro ba'i bslab pa nyams na
NK117(she)001:21837: skyabs med mgon med kyi rigs sam phyi rol pa'i
NK117(she)001:21838: lugs sogs dman par ltung ba'i phyir lus smas pa'i
NK117(she)001:21839: rma'i bag bzhin bsgrims te bslab pa bsrung bar bya'o
NK117(she)001:21842: las kyi lce spyang gdug pas skabs btsal rnams //
NK117(she)001:21843: tshig don 'dzol ba'i yid gnyis snod ngan du //
NK117(she)001:21844: bslu ba med pa'i nges shes bri ba'i rtags //
NK117(she)001:21845: yi dwags la brten tshe 'di nyid la nyams //
NK117(she)001:21846: zhes pa ni bod 'dir dkon mchog gi mtshan 'dod
NK117(she)001:21847: rgyal du sgrog cing kha tshig tsam gyi dad pa
NK117(she)001:21848: las / snying nas ma yin skyon gyis tshogs bsags kyang grags pa'i rjes su 'brang zhing /
NK117(she)001:21849: las ngan gyi rgyu las lus ngan mi dge ba'i
NK117(she)001:21850: rten du gyur pa'i ce spyang gdug pa can gzhan
NK117(she)001:21851: srog la 'tshe ba'i skabs btsal ba lta bu rnams
NK117(she)001:21852: ni / tshig tsam du mchog gsum la dad bardzu
NK117(she)001:21853: byas kyang don la yi dwags mthu bo che 'ga'
NK117(she)001:21854: la blo rtse gtad nas kha zhe gnyis 'dzol ba'i
NK117(she)001:21855: yid gnyis kyi snod ngan du bslu ba med pa'i
NK117(she)001:21856: bcud blugs kyang yid ches kyi nges shes bri ba'i
NK117(she)001:21857: ni / rtags su / mchog gsum las 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:21858: gyi lha 'dre dga' bar sems pas skyabs yul gyi
NK117(she)001:21859: thugs rje'i dpyang thag chad nas tshe 'di nyid la
NK117(she)001:21862: 'di na sa dang nam mkha' ri rab rnams //
NK117(she)001:21863: yan man gnas 'gyur nyi zla thang lhung srid //
NK117(she)001:21864: dkon mchog gsum gyis bslu bar mi srid pa'i //
NK117(she)001:21865: nges shes brtan pa kun tu don yod yin //
NK117(she)001:21866: zhes pa ni 'jig rten 'di na 'byung ba chags
NK117(she)001:21867: 'jig gi rkyen las sa dang nam mkha' ri rab
NK117(she)001:21868: rnams gnas yul go log tu 'gyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:21869: nyi zla yang so na mi gnas pa ltar srid kyang /
NK117(she)001:21870: dkon mchog gsum gyis bslu bar mi srid pa'i don
NK117(she)001:21871: la nges shes dang mos gus brtan pa ni 'phral
NK117(she)001:21872: phugs kun tu don chen po yod pa yin mod
NK117(she)001:21873: kyang blun rmongs thos pa nyung ba la las mchog
NK117(she)001:21874: gsum gyi thugs rjes rang gi las ngan slong ba
NK117(she)001:21875: mi shes bzhin the tshom za ba mi rigs te
NK117(she)001:21876: / da lta mchog gsum la dad bzhin rnam dkar
NK117(she)001:21877: nan tan bsgrubs pa la mi 'dod pa mang du
NK117(she)001:21878: 'byung ba phyi ma sdug bsngal chen po myong rgyu
NK117(she)001:21879: da lta nas zad pa'i rtags su ston pas gsungs
NK117(she)001:21880: / te / rab 'byor 'di ltar sems can de
NK117(she)001:21881: dag tshe rabs snga ma'i mi dge ba'i las ngan
NK117(she)001:21882: song du skye bar 'gyur na gang dag tshe 'di
NK117(she)001:21883: nyid la mnar bas tshe rabs snga ma'i mi dge
NK117(she)001:21884: ba'i las de dag byang bar 'gyur te sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:21885: kyi byang chub kyang thob par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:21886: zhes rdo rje gcod pa las gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:21887: yang de nyid go ldog ste sdig pa'i las tshan
NK117(she)001:21888: po che bsags pa dag tshe 'dir bde skyid phun
NK117(she)001:21889: sum 'tshogs pa ni skye ba sngon ma'i dge rtsa
NK117(she)001:21890: kun tshe 'dir smin bzhin zad nas shi ma thag
NK117(she)001:21891: tu ngan song gi sdug bsngal myong ba'i rtags su
NK117(she)001:21892: bshad de / sngon nyi 'og gi yul du sdig
NK117(she)001:21893: pa kho na la spyod pa'i sdig can tshan gcig
NK117(she)001:21894: yod pa la tshe rabs sngon gyi dge rtsa rnams
NK117(she)001:21895: dus der smin cing zad pa'i rtags su zhag bdun
NK117(she)001:21898: de nas rin po che'i bar gong bzhin bab mthar
NK117(she)001:21899: bye tshan gyi char bab pa dang chabs cig ri
NK117(she)001:21900: thams cad thug chom du 'ur nas dus gcig tu
NK117(she)001:21902: spyir sdig can la la rgyu gzhan med bzhin 'chi
NK117(she)001:21903: kha mi 'dod pa 'byung ba ni sngon gyi dge
NK117(she)001:21904: ba'i 'bras bus mi lus thob kyang de'i bsod nams
NK117(she)001:21905: zad nas phyi ma'i sdug bsngal gyi sngon bsu ma
NK117(she)001:21906: shi'i sngon nas slebs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21907: dge ba can la de ltar byung na las ngan zad pa'i rtags su shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:21908: de'i phyir rgyu 'bras la yid ches shing mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:21909: la snying thag pa nas dad pa rnams ni mi
NK117(she)001:21910: lus rin po che rnyed pa mchog dang ldan pa
NK117(she)001:21912: rmi lam na'ang dkon mchog mthong ba dang //
NK117(she)001:21913: bag yod dran zhing yon tan kun gyis 'byor //
NK117(she)001:21914: tshe rabs dran zhing bar do bgrod par bla //
NK117(she)001:21915: lus can kun gyi dpung dang gnyen du 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:21917: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:21918: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:21919: lde mig las le'u drug pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:21920: de ltar skyabs su song nas theg chen dngos la 'jug pa ni /
NK117(she)001:21922: theg dman rdzing bur byang chub sems kyi khams //
NK117(she)001:21923: rigs las nyams pa nyan rang skyes bu'i sems //
NK117(she)001:21924: stong nyid snying rje'i ded dpon mthus sad nas //
NK117(she)001:21925: theg chen rgya mtsho kun mkhyen gling du 'gro //
NK117(she)001:21926: zhes pa ni de yang theg dman gyi lam gzhan phan gyi yur bar mi rgyu bar /
NK117(she)001:21927: rdzing bu'i 'khyil chu lta bu'i zhi bde'i mal du
NK117(she)001:21928: byang chub sems kyi mthu nyams pa de mthar rgyal
NK117(she)001:21929: ba'i thugs rjes bskul bas gdod rigs sad nas theg
NK117(she)001:21930: chen gyi lam la 'jug dgos pas na blo ldan
NK117(she)001:21931: rnams kyi lam la 'jug ngogs ni theg chen kho
NK117(she)001:21932: na yin te / der zhugs phyin kun mkhyen gyi gling du 'gro zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21934: sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa rnam pa lnga'i //
NK117(she)001:21935: ngo bo lung du ma bstan lcags khams su //
NK117(she)001:21936: rnam par nyams pa thabs shes gser 'gyur rtsis //
NK117(she)001:21937: thebs pa'i mod la rin thang chen por byed //
NK117(she)001:21938: ces pa ni 'di ltar sbyin pa la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:21939: thabs kyi cha lnga po yang shes rab kyis ma
NK117(she)001:21940: zin bar du byang chub chen por lung du ma
NK117(she)001:21941: bstan pa'i lcags khams lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:21942: de yang thabs byang chub kyi sems dang shes rab
NK117(she)001:21943: stong nyid zung du 'brel ba gser 'gyur gyi rtsi
NK117(she)001:21944: lta bus thebs pa'i mod la rin thang chen po
NK117(she)001:21945: sangs rgyas kyi rgyu ma nor ba byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21947: gang phyir snying rje'i thabs dang stong nyid kyi //
NK117(she)001:21948: shes rab zung du 'jug pa'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:21949: sbyor ba tshad med bzhi pa'i sa mkhan gyi //
NK117(she)001:21950: smon 'jug gnyis dang bslab bya slob las skye //
NK117(she)001:21951: zhes pa ni de la snying rjes ni zhi ba'i mtha' dang /
NK117(she)001:21952: shes rab kyis srid pa'i mtha' ste gnyis po 'gog ces pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21953: 'dir las dang po pa la sbyor ba tshad med
NK117(she)001:21954: bzhis sa mkhan lta bu byas nas smon 'jug gnyis
NK117(she)001:21955: dang bslab bya bslabs pa las skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:21958: byams pa'i ngo bo gzhan bde 'dod pa yin //
NK117(she)001:21959: sdug pa'i ma yis bu la ji bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:21960: lus dang longs spyod dge ba kun spangs nas //
NK117(she)001:21961: gzhan la phan 'dogs gnod pa bzod la bslab //
NK117(she)001:21962: ces pa ni de la byams pa ni 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:21963: gnas mtho dman kun pha ma'i rang bzhin du shes
NK117(she)001:21964: pas ma dang bu'i 'du shes kyis gnod 'tshe cung
NK117(she)001:21965: zad kyang med bzhin byams par byed pa ni sems
NK117(she)001:21966: can la dmigs pa'i byams pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21967: sa dang po dang bdun pa'i bar gyi byang sems
NK117(she)001:21968: rnams ni chos rnams rang bzhin med kyang 'gro rnams
NK117(she)001:21969: dngos por zhen nas sdug bsngal la spyod pa 'di
NK117(she)001:21970: rnams la chos kyis phan gdags shing chos nyid rtogs
NK117(she)001:21971: par brtson pa ni chos la dmigs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21972: sa brgyad pa yan chad ni dmigs med kyi byams
NK117(she)001:21973: pa ste rnam rtog bral yang nor bu bzhin dang
NK117(she)001:21974: / rgyal ba rnams kyi sngon smon gyis 'gro ba'i
NK117(she)001:21975: khams la byams pa chen po lhun grub tu 'byung
NK117(she)001:21977: de la byams pa'i ngo bo ni gzhan bde bar
NK117(she)001:21978: 'dod pa yin la de'i dpe ni snying du sdug
NK117(she)001:21979: pa ma yis bu la brtse ba ji bzhin dang
NK117(she)001:21980: / rang gi lus dang longs spyod dge ba sogs
NK117(she)001:21981: kun spangs nas gzhan la phan 'dogs kho na las
NK117(she)001:21982: log sgrub dang gnod pa bzod pa la bslabs pa'o
NK117(she)001:21983: / // de yang sems can la dmigs pa ni phyi rol pa dang mtshungs shing /
NK117(she)001:21984: chos la dmigs pa ni nyan rang bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:21985: dmigs pa med pa ni de dag las 'phags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:21987: snying rje'i ngo bo gzhan gyi sdug bsngal la //
NK117(she)001:21988: bzod mi phod pa'i sems stobs drag po dang //
NK117(she)001:21989: 'gro drug mtha' dag sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyi //
NK117(she)001:21990: mtha' la gcur mthong mchi ma slong ba yin //
NK117(she)001:21991: zhes pa ni de yang 'gro rnams sdug bsngal gyis
NK117(she)001:21992: mnar ba dang de'i rgyu mi dge ba la spyod
NK117(she)001:21993: pa dang / de gnyis ka'i blang dor la rmongs
NK117(she)001:21994: pa gsum la snying rje skye bzhin du de dag
NK117(she)001:21995: gi sdug bsngal gyi khur rang gis khyer ba ni
NK117(she)001:21996: snying rje'i ngo bo yin zhing de dag gi sdug
NK117(she)001:21997: bsngal bzod mi phod pa'i sems stobs drag po bskyed
NK117(she)001:21998: nas phan thabs dang du len pa dang /
NK117(she)001:21999: 'gro ba rigs drug po mtha' dag sdug bsngal gyi
NK117(she)001:22000: rgyu dang 'bras bu la spyod pa na rngon pas
NK117(she)001:22001: ri dwags mtha' la gcur ba ltar mthong nas snying
NK117(she)001:22002: rje shas mi bzod pa'i mchi ma slong ba yin
NK117(she)001:22004: dga' ba'i ngo bo gzhan dag phun tshogs la //
NK117(she)001:22005: spro ba'i sems 'jug kun la legs smon bsgom //
NK117(she)001:22006: rang rang mthu yis thob la dga' byed cing //
NK117(she)001:22007: phyin chad de dang mi 'bral smon pa yin //
NK117(she)001:22008: zhes pa ni de la dga' ba'i ngo bo ni
NK117(she)001:22009: gzhan dag zang zing dang chos dang bde 'byor dang
NK117(she)001:22010: ldan pa la mi dga' ba med cing spro ba'i
NK117(she)001:22011: sems 'jug bzhin kun la de bzhin 'byor ba'i legs
NK117(she)001:22013: rang yang byams pa dang snying rje'i skyon med la
NK117(she)001:22014: brtson nus bzhin 'gro don 'grub pa la nga rgyal
NK117(she)001:22016: gzhan chos dang zang zing phun sum tshogs pa rang
NK117(she)001:22017: rang gi sngon dkar po rnam par 'phel ba'i mthus
NK117(she)001:22018: thob pa la dga' bar byed cing phyin chad de
NK117(she)001:22019: lta bu'i dga' bde phun sum tshogs pa dang mi
NK117(she)001:22020: 'bral ba'i smon sems byas na dge bar 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:22022: btang snyoms ngo bo byams sdang 'bral ba ste //
NK117(she)001:22023: phyogs dang ris chad mnyam pa nyid brdal nas //
NK117(she)001:22024: dgra dang gnyen dang bar ma'i 'du shes gsum //
NK117(she)001:22025: phan 'dogs yul la mnyam par rab tu spyod //
NK117(she)001:22026: rnam pa'i dmigs bcas dmigs med rtsi yis sbyar //
NK117(she)001:22027: zhes pa ni 'di ltar btang snyoms kyi ngo bo
NK117(she)001:22028: ni gong gsal gyi tshad med pa gsum po de
NK117(she)001:22029: sgom pa'i yul la byams pa'i gnyen dang sdang ba'i
NK117(she)001:22030: dgra gnyis kar chags sdang bral ba ste /
NK117(she)001:22031: mthun phyogs dang 'gal phyogs ris su ma chad pa'i
NK117(she)001:22032: mnyam pa nyid du brdal nas dgra dang gnyen dang
NK117(she)001:22033: bar ma gsum la mdza' 'khon bar ma'i 'du shes
NK117(she)001:22034: gsum spangs nas phan 'dogs yul la bsam sbyor mnyam
NK117(she)001:22036: rnam pas dmigs bcas ni lus ngag gi las dang
NK117(she)001:22037: dmigs med ni bsam pa'i las kyi rtsi yis sbyar
NK117(she)001:22038: nas mthun par bya zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22040: 'dod pa'i byams pa ser sna'i snying rje dang //
NK117(she)001:22041: nga rgyal dga' ba gti mug btang snyoms dang //
NK117(she)001:22042: thar pa'i lam min tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhi'i //
NK117(she)001:22043: phyogs dang nye ba dmigs bcas rnam par spang //
NK117(she)001:22044: zhes pa ni de la rang gi bu dang nye
NK117(she)001:22045: du mdza' bshes sogs la byams shing gzhan la cang
NK117(she)001:22046: mi sems pa ni byams pa ltar yang ngo bo
NK117(she)001:22047: 'dod chags so // de bzhin du rang gis bdag
NK117(she)001:22048: pa'i rta khal sogs snying rje nas 'khol mi 'jug
NK117(she)001:22049: cing gzhan dag de las ldog pa ni snying rje
NK117(she)001:22051: rang dang rang phyogs phun sum tshogs pa dang bde
NK117(she)001:22052: zhing skyid pa la dga' ba bsgom zhing gzhan la
NK117(she)001:22053: de ltar ma yin na dga' bar bardzusa pa'i nga
NK117(she)001:22054: rgyal dang phrag dog la'ang nye'o //
NK117(she)001:22055: gzhan la phan gnod gang yang mi byed par kha
NK117(she)001:22056: rog tu sdod pa kho na ni btang snyoms 'dra
NK117(she)001:22057: yang gti mug gi sa pa yin pas thar lam
NK117(she)001:22058: rnal mar mi 'gro ba'i skyon ni tshangs pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:22059: pa bzhi zhes 'jig rten mes po'i lugs kyi tshad
NK117(she)001:22060: med bzhi yin par bstan nas de'i phyogs dang nye
NK117(she)001:22061: ba dmigs bcas rnam par spangs dgos par gdams pa'o
NK117(she)001:22063: 'di na zhi ba'i lam dang 'brel ba yi //
NK117(she)001:22064: dmigs pa'i yul ni sems can thams cad kyang //
NK117(she)001:22065: snang la rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid kyi //
NK117(she)001:22066: rnam pa'i bsgom tshul stobs su gyur pa las //
NK117(she)001:22067: byang chub sems gnyis skye ba'i rgyur 'gro bas //
NK117(she)001:22068: khyad chos ldan pa'i tshad med bzhi ru 'dod //
NK117(she)001:22069: ces pa ni 'di na zhi ba'i lam dang 'brel
NK117(she)001:22070: ba'i tshad med bzhi ni dmigs pa'i yul sems can
NK117(she)001:22071: thams cad la khyad med du byas kyang /
NK117(she)001:22072: de la bden zhen dang dngos 'dzin sogs ma yin
NK117(she)001:22073: par snang la rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid sgyu
NK117(she)001:22074: ma lta bu'i rtsis zin pa ni rnam pa'i bsgom
NK117(she)001:22075: tshul de nyid gegs dang gol sa med par stobs
NK117(she)001:22076: su gyur pa de las byang chub kyi sems gnyis
NK117(she)001:22077: skye ba'i rgyur 'gro ba yin pas 'jig rten pa'i
NK117(she)001:22078: sgom lugs las khyad chos ldan pa spyan ras gzigs
NK117(she)001:22079: kyi tshad med bzhi lta bur 'dod ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22081: sgom tshul go rim can dang nges pa med //
NK117(she)001:22082: dmigs pa'i yul gang skye bar sla la gtad //
NK117(she)001:22083: 'on kyang byams bsgoms chags pa'i rten gyur na //
NK117(she)001:22084: nye ring bral ba'i btang snyoms bsgom par spo //
NK117(she)001:22085: zhes pa ni byams pa bsgoms pa de rang gi
NK117(she)001:22086: gnyen bshes lta bu'i phyogs ris can du shor nas
NK117(she)001:22087: chags pa'i rten du gyur na btang snyoms bsgoms pas
NK117(she)001:22090: de nyid rmongs nas lung ma bstan gyur na //
NK117(she)001:22091: snying rjer spos pas sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras 'gog /
NK117(she)001:22092: ces pa ni btang snyoms kyi sems de phan med
NK117(she)001:22093: gnod med lung ma bstan du gyur na snying rje
NK117(she)001:22094: chen po bskyed pas btang snyoms tha mal pa 'gog
NK117(she)001:22096: snying rje stobs zhan ris su chad pa na //
NK117(she)001:22097: dga' bar spos pas dman sems skye ba 'gog /
NK117(she)001:22098: ces pa ni snying rje yang nyes can kho na
NK117(she)001:22099: lta bu las kun la mi sgom pa'i nyi tshe
NK117(she)001:22100: ba phyogs lhung can du gyur na dga' ba bsgoms
NK117(she)001:22101: pas dman sems kyi gnyen por 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:22103: dga' bas sems rgod spros pa'i yul gyur na //
NK117(she)001:22104: byams sogs mtha' dbus barjesa nas spel mar bsgom //
NK117(she)001:22105: zhes pa ni gzhan gyi bde 'byor la dga' ba bsgoms pas sems g.yeng skyon du gyur na /
NK117(she)001:22106: byams pa dang dga' ba snying rje dang btang snyoms
NK117(she)001:22107: spel mar bsgom pa dang thod rgal du bsgom pa
NK117(she)001:22108: sogs kyis gegs las grol bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:22110: de ltar bsgoms pas rnam smin mngon par mtho //
NK117(she)001:22111: 'dod pa'i lha mi'i lus dang nges legs gnyis //
NK117(she)001:22112: rgyu mthun byed pas de 'dra myong bas na //
NK117(she)001:22113: mi mthun phyogs dang bral zhing bde ba 'thob //
NK117(she)001:22114: dbang gis yid 'ong bde dag'i yul la spyod //
NK117(she)001:22115: byed pa bzhi po stobs su gyur pa yi //
NK117(she)001:22116: don gnyis 'byor pa'i yon tan 'thob 'gyur te //
NK117(she)001:22117: zhes pa ni de ltar bsgoms pas rnam smin gyi
NK117(she)001:22118: 'bras bus gnas skabs su lha mi'i lus rten 'grub
NK117(she)001:22119: cing tshogs gnyis rdzogs shing gzhan la'ang phan pa dang
NK117(she)001:22120: / mthar thug nges legs kyi 'bras bu lhun gyis 'grub par 'gyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22121: byed pa rgyu mthun gyis rtag tu tshad med bzhi bsgom par skye zhing /
NK117(she)001:22122: myong ba rgyu mthun gyis gzhan la gnod 'tshe dang
NK117(she)001:22123: chags sdang sogs bral ba'i bde ba la reg par
NK117(she)001:22125: byams pas yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22127: dga' bas sman shing me tog la sogs pas 'byor pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22128: btang snyoms kyis skye dgu mdza' zhing dga' ba'i yul la spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22129: skyes bu byed pa'i 'bras bu ni tshad med bzhi
NK117(she)001:22130: po bsgoms pas rang rang gi byed pa bzhi po
NK117(she)001:22131: ches cher 'phel te rgyal sras rnams la rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:22132: du rtag par skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22133: goms pa las skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22134: yul mthong ba las skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22135: mi mthun pa'i phyogs nyams pa las skye ba la
NK117(she)001:22136: sogs pa bsod nams rgya chen po 'thob cing rang
NK117(she)001:22137: gzhan gyi don gnyis 'grub pa'i yon tan 'thob pa'o
NK117(she)001:22139: byams pa 'byongs pas 'gro la bu ltar brtse //
NK117(she)001:22140: zhe sdang med cing gzhan gyi yid du 'ong //
NK117(she)001:22141: byams pa'i ngo bo stong la rang bzhin med //
NK117(she)001:22142: me long ye shes longs spyod rdzogs pa 'thob //
NK117(she)001:22143: ces pa ni de la byams pas sems kyi rgyud
NK117(she)001:22144: brlan pas 'gro ba kun la ma bu'i 'du shes
NK117(she)001:22145: kyis zhe sdang gi sems zhi bar 'gyur zhing byams
NK117(she)001:22146: pa'i ngo bo yang stong la rang bzhin med pas
NK117(she)001:22147: me long lta bu'i ye shes mngon du gyur nas
NK117(she)001:22148: mtshan dpe rgya mtsho lta bu'i bdag nyid longs sku
NK117(she)001:22151: snying rje 'byongs pas gzhan gyi sdug bsngal kyang //
NK117(she)001:22152: bdag gi khur 'gro 'tshe ba bral ba'i sems //
NK117(she)001:22153: 'dod chags dang bral stong nyid snying rjer 'brel //
NK117(she)001:22154: sor rtog ye shes chos kyi sku ru 'grub //
NK117(she)001:22155: ces pa ni de yang snying rje bsgoms pa ji
NK117(she)001:22156: bzhin 'byongs tshe gzhan gyi sdug bsngal yang rang thog
NK117(she)001:22157: tu len nus pa bu gcig po na ba'i ma
NK117(she)001:22158: bzhin rang yid la mi byed par sems can gyi
NK117(she)001:22159: nad gdon sdug bsngal bdag gis khur ba la sems
NK117(she)001:22160: mi zhum zhing 'tshe ba dngos su byed pa smos
NK117(she)001:22161: ci sems pa'ang mi 'gyu ba ni 'dod chags dang
NK117(she)001:22162: bral zhing stong pa nyid ji bzhin rtogs pa'i rtsal
NK117(she)001:22163: snang snying rjer shar ba zung du 'brel ba'i 'bras
NK117(she)001:22164: bu so sor rtog pa'i ye shes chos kyi sku
NK117(she)001:22165: ru lhun gyis grub pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:22168: dga' ba 'byongs pas phrag dog rtsa ba chod //
NK117(she)001:22169: 'byor pa brtan cing zhi bde rgyun mi 'chad //
NK117(she)001:22170: bsam gtan dga' ba dmigs pa med pa dang //
NK117(she)001:22171: bya grub ye shes sprul pa'i sku mchog thob //
NK117(she)001:22172: ces pa ni de la dga' ba ni rang sems la zug rngu med pa ste /
NK117(she)001:22173: de nyid 'byongs pa'i tshad ni gzhan gyi bde 'byor
NK117(she)001:22174: sogs la phrag dog gi rtsa ba chod nas dga'
NK117(she)001:22176: de'i dge 'bras kyis rang nyid 'byor pa brtan cing zhi bde'i rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22177: bsam gtan gyi dga' ba yang rim bzhin thob kyang
NK117(she)001:22178: dmigs pa med bzhin phrag dog gnas su dag pa
NK117(she)001:22179: bya grub ye shes thob cing sprul sku'i mdzad phrin
NK117(she)001:22182: btang snyoms 'byongs pas bdag gzhan dgra gnyen mnyam //
NK117(she)001:22183: nga rgyal med cing zab zhi'i rtogs pa skye //
NK117(she)001:22184: rmongs pa med cing chos dbyings ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:22185: ngo bo nyid sku mngon du 'thob par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:22186: zhes pa ni 'di ltar btang snyoms bsgoms pa mthar
NK117(she)001:22187: phyin tshe mdza' 'khon bar ma gsum la phan 'dogs
NK117(she)001:22188: rgyu mnyam zhing / rang nyid la bzang rloms sogs
NK117(she)001:22189: kyi nga rgyal med cing sems kyi rang bzhin zab
NK117(she)001:22190: pa dang zhi ba'i dbyings su gnyis 'dzin rnams btang
NK117(she)001:22191: snyoms pa'i rtogs pa skye zhing rmongs pa'i rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:22192: gti mug gi khams gnas su dag nas chos kyi
NK117(she)001:22193: dbyings kyi ye shes dang ngo bo nyid sku 'thob
NK117(she)001:22194: rgyu mnyam zhing / par 'gyur ro // zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22196: de lta'i tshad med bzhi yi yon tan ni //
NK117(she)001:22197: rgyu 'bras shin tu mtha' yas bslu ba med //
NK117(she)001:22198: lam ngan gzhan gyi grub mtha' srid pa'i rgyu //
NK117(she)001:22199: stong nyid snying rjer 'gal la mi bsten par //
NK117(she)001:22200: thar lam dri med rgyal sras dam pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:22201: rnyog pa zhi ba'i dge la goms 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:22202: zhes pa ni 'di ltar tshad med bzhi po bsgoms
NK117(she)001:22203: pa'i yon tan ni thar par 'gro ba'i lam ste
NK117(she)001:22204: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka shin tu mtha' yas te rgyu'i
NK117(she)001:22205: theg par sku gnyis skyed byed tshogs gnyis su 'dod
NK117(she)001:22206: pa dang / sngags su dag bya'i sgrib pa gnyis tshogs gnyis kyi rang bzhin /
NK117(she)001:22207: thabs shes kyis sbyangs pa de rkyen du 'dod pas
NK117(she)001:22208: don stong nyid snying rje zung 'jug bsgrub pa la
NK117(she)001:22209: mdo mthun cing / khyad par 'khor lo tha mar
NK117(she)001:22210: yon tan ye ldan yin phyir gsar byung mi 'dod
NK117(she)001:22211: mdo mthun cing / la / sngags kyi sde snod
NK117(she)001:22212: las kyang 'gro rnams gzhi'i dus rang bzhin gyi dkyil
NK117(she)001:22213: 'khor dam pa'i chos nyid du gnas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22214: lam yang tshogs gnyis dang thabs shes ngo bo gcig
NK117(she)001:22215: la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes tha mi dad
NK117(she)001:22216: pa'i de lugs su slob pa las /
NK117(she)001:22217: lam ngan phyi rol pa'i lha mi'i grub mtha' sogs
NK117(she)001:22218: la zhugs pa ni srid pa'i rgyu yin pas na
NK117(she)001:22219: nang pa'i lugs bzang dri ma med pa las gzhan
NK117(she)001:22220: pas stong nyid snying rje 'gal ba can gyi gzhung
NK117(she)001:22222: 'dir thar pa dri med ni theg chen gyi lam
NK117(she)001:22223: thabs shes zung 'jug yin pa de'i mi mthun phyogs
NK117(she)001:22224: kyi rnyog pa zhi ba'i rang bzhin can yin pas
NK117(she)001:22225: der zhugs na myang ngan las 'das pa'i sar phyin
NK117(she)001:22227: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:22228: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:22229: lde mig las le'u bdun pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:22230: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:22232: rnyed pa gang gi don la yon gyi mchog /
NK117(she)001:22233: tshad med rnam bzhis thob pa'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:22234: smon 'jug shing rta'i sgyu thabs la drangs pas //
NK117(she)001:22235: zhi bde'i lta ba ngan pa nyams par byed //
NK117(she)001:22236: ces rnyed pa don du gnyer ba de nyid 'grub
NK117(she)001:22237: pa'i ched du yon nam barngana pa ster ba bzhin
NK117(she)001:22238: / tshad med pa rnam pa bzhis rgyu byas nas
NK117(she)001:22239: thob pa'i 'bras bu ni byang chub kyi sems rin
NK117(she)001:22241: ston pas bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs gnyis
NK117(she)001:22242: kyi phan yon la dpyad pas kyang 'di las lhag
NK117(she)001:22243: pa ma gzigs bzhin sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob
NK117(she)001:22244: pa la smon pa dang de'i thabs la 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:22245: ni shing rta'i sgyu thabs la drangs pa lta bu
NK117(she)001:22246: yin pas des nyan rang gi zhi bde'i lta ba
NK117(she)001:22247: ngan pa nyams nas g.yo sgyu bral ba'i lhag bsam
NK117(she)001:22248: 'phel bar byed pas de kho na la bslab par
NK117(she)001:22251: sdig sdug 'khor ba'i btson rar bcings rnams kyang //
NK117(she)001:22252: byang chub sems bskyed mod la rgyal sras kyi //
NK117(she)001:22253: ming gi cod pan 'thob la rab dga' nas //
NK117(she)001:22254: 'jig rten lha mir bcas kyang bsti stang byed //
NK117(she)001:22255: ces pa ni 'di ltar zhe sdang gi rgyus srog
NK117(she)001:22256: bcad pa la sogs pa'i sdig pa dang des bskyed
NK117(she)001:22257: pa'i rigs drug gi sdug bsngal gyi btson rar bcings
NK117(she)001:22258: pa rnams kyang rang bde don gnyer las log ste
NK117(she)001:22259: gzhan don sgrub phyir byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK117(she)001:22260: pa'i mod la rgyal ba rnams kyi sras kyi ming
NK117(she)001:22261: gi cod pan thob pa la rab tu dga' nas
NK117(she)001:22262: 'jig rten na mngon par mtho ba'i lha dang mir
NK117(she)001:22263: bcas pas kyang bsti stang byed pa'i gnas su gyur
NK117(she)001:22264: pa'o // 'o na sa dang po ma thob par
NK117(she)001:22265: byang chub kyi sems thob par ma bshad pas nyon
NK117(she)001:22266: mongs kyi khrod na gnas pa'i so skye la skye
NK117(she)001:22267: bar rung ngam dogs na de ni chos la dmigs
NK117(she)001:22268: pa dang 'di ni yang dag par blangs pa brda
NK117(she)001:22269: can la dgongs pas 'phags pa ma yin kyang skye
NK117(she)001:22270: ba zab mo'i mdo sde rnams las bshad pas so
NK117(she)001:22272: las nyon mun nag 'khrigs pa'i sprin bar nas //
NK117(she)001:22273: gtum po'i glog 'od 'khyug lta'i dge ba la //
NK117(she)001:22274: skabs 'gar goms pa'i bsod nams tsam po ba //
NK117(she)001:22275: chu shing bzhin du 'bras bus rtsa ba smad //
NK117(she)001:22276: ces pa ni 'di ltar byang chub sems kyis ma zin pa'i dge bas ni lha mi'am /
NK117(she)001:22277: nyan rang gi 'bras bu tsam zhig thob nas dge
NK117(she)001:22278: 'bras 'dzad pa ste 'jig rten na las dang nyon
NK117(she)001:22279: mongs pa mun nag 'khrigs pa lta bu'i sprin gyi
NK117(she)001:22280: bar nas dam pa gsum gyis ma zin pa'i gtum
NK117(she)001:22281: po'i glog 'od 'khyug pa lta bu'i dge ba tsam
NK117(she)001:22282: po ba la skabs 'gar goms pa'i bsod nams kyi
NK117(she)001:22283: gzugs brnyan ni chu shing gi rigs rnams 'bras bu
NK117(she)001:22284: smin pa dang rtsa ba skam pa ltar 'gyur zhes
NK117(she)001:22285: pa dang / gzhan yang dam pa gsum gyis ma
NK117(she)001:22286: zin pa'i phar phyin drug dang rim pa gnyis sogs
NK117(she)001:22287: la brtson 'grus bskyed kyang de dang mtshungs par gsungs
NK117(she)001:22289: sa bzhi bzang pos bsten pa'i zhing sa la //
NK117(she)001:22290: dge ba'i lo tog phun sum tshogs pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:22291: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing srid pa na //
NK117(she)001:22292: 'bras bu mang zhing zhi ba'i bar du 'phel //
NK117(she)001:22293: zhes pa ni sa gzhi bzang po skyon bral gyis
NK117(she)001:22294: bsten pa'i zhing sa gshin po lta bu'i rnam gsum
NK117(she)001:22295: dad pa'i gzhi la dge 'bras smin pa lo tog
NK117(she)001:22296: phun sum tshogs pa ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:22297: khyad par dpag bsam ljon pa ni bskal pa'i bar
NK117(she)001:22298: du 'bras bu je 'phel du 'gro ba ltar byang
NK117(she)001:22299: chub sems kyis zin pa'i dge 'bras kyang srid pa
NK117(she)001:22300: ji srid par chud mi za zhing zhi ba ste
NK117(she)001:22301: sangs rgyas kyi bar du 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:22303: las nyon 'du byed sdug bsngal kun gyi snod //
NK117(she)001:22304: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho rnam rtog rba rlabs can //
NK117(she)001:22305: sems can rnams kyis khyim ltar rab bzung las //
NK117(she)001:22306: gdon pa'i snying stobs chen po sems bskyed yin //
NK117(she)001:22307: zhes pa ni 'di ltar las dang nyon mongs yongs
