NK117(she)001:22308: su 'du byed kyi bdag po sdug bsngal kun gyi
NK117(she)001:22309: snod du gyur pa'i 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho chen po'i
NK117(she)001:22310: rang bzhin ni kun tu rtog pa'i dba' rlabs drag
NK117(she)001:22311: pos thar pa'i gru gzings bshig pa can yin yang
NK117(she)001:22312: / sems can blun rmongs rnams ni de la khyim
NK117(she)001:22313: ltar dga' zhing rab tu bzung bas thar pa'i go
NK117(she)001:22314: skabs dka' ba las gdon par nus pa'i snying stobs
NK117(she)001:22315: ni sems bskyed kho na las gzhan ci yang med
NK117(she)001:22317: gang la rang don sems pa yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:22318: bkres pa zas dang skom pa chur gdung bzhin //
NK117(she)001:22319: sems can 'ba' zhig don du sangs rgyas kyi //
NK117(she)001:22320: go 'phang gnyer la byang chub sems zhes grags //
NK117(she)001:22321: zhes pa ni 'dir gang la zhes skyes bu chen
NK117(she)001:22322: po rnams la rang don sems nas gzhan don yal
NK117(she)001:22323: bar dor ba yod pa ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:22324: bkres pas zas 'tshol ba dang skom pa chur gdung
NK117(she)001:22325: ba bzhin du phar phyin drug dang rim gnyis la
NK117(she)001:22326: rtag par brtson pa yang sems can 'ba' zhig la
NK117(she)001:22327: phan pa'i don du sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang gnyer
NK117(she)001:22328: ba la byang chub sems zhes grags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22329: de ltar ma yin pas tha snyad kyi shes bya
NK117(she)001:22330: dang blun sgom gyi go yul tsam du nges pa'i
NK117(she)001:22331: don zab mo rtogs so snyam pa sogs yon tan
NK117(she)001:22332: gyi rnam pa gzhan yod kyang theg dman par ltung
NK117(she)001:22333: ba'o // byams snying rje nyi tshe ba nyan rang la'ang yod kyang /
NK117(she)001:22334: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam dang bsngo ba ma bshad do //
NK117(she)001:22336: de'ang 'bras bur dam bca' smon pa'i sems //
NK117(she)001:22337: bslab bya bdag gzhan mnyam dang barje ba dang //
NK117(she)001:22338: bdag bas gzhan gces gsum du bzhag pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:22339: bslab pa'i mdo bsdus yin gyis de'i ngo bo //
NK117(she)001:22340: byams sogs tshad med bzhi la yang dag gnas //
NK117(she)001:22341: rgyu la dam bca' 'jug pa'i sems yin te //
NK117(she)001:22342: de yi bslab bya pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK117(she)001:22343: spyod yul yongs su dag pa rnams la bsten //
NK117(she)001:22344: zhes pa ni de la 'bras bur dam bca' ste
NK117(she)001:22345: sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs rgyas thob
NK117(she)001:22346: par bya snyam nas de'i bslab bya slob pa smon
NK117(she)001:22348: de ni bdag gzhan khyad med du sdug bsngal 'gog
NK117(she)001:22349: cing bde ba la sbyor ba bdag gzhan mnyam pa
NK117(she)001:22350: dang / barje ba ni bdag gi dge ba dang
NK117(she)001:22351: bde ba sems can la gtong zhing sems can gyi
NK117(she)001:22352: sdug bsngal rang gis len pa yin kyang sbyor bas
NK117(she)001:22353: bslabs na bsam pas de ltar slob cing bdag bas
NK117(she)001:22355: byang chub kyi bslab pa zhugs nas sangs rgyas bar
NK117(she)001:22356: rang don cung zad kyang mi gnyer bar ngan song
NK117(she)001:22357: gi 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i ched du gnas ngan
NK117(she)001:22358: rnams su bskal pa nas bskal pa'i bar du gnas
NK117(she)001:22359: dgos kyang skyo ngal mi byed pa gsum ni bslab
NK117(she)001:22360: pa'i mdor bsdus tsam yin gyis de'i ngo bo ni
NK117(she)001:22361: byams pa tshad med pa sogs bzhi po la yang
NK117(she)001:22362: dag par gnas zhes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22363: rgyu la dam bca' ba ni sangs rgyas pa'i thabs
NK117(she)001:22364: la 'jug pa'i sems yin te de'i bslab bya ni
NK117(she)001:22365: pha rol tu phyin pa drug yin la /
NK117(she)001:22366: spyod yul yongs su dag pa ste rgyu 'bras gtso bor byed pa rnams la bsten //
NK117(she)001:22369: dbye ba'i sgo nas skye 'phags sems bskyed gnyis //
NK117(she)001:22370: bslab pa gsum la ltos pa'i sems bskyed gsum //
NK117(she)001:22371: khyad par tshogs sbyor lam na mos pas spyod //
NK117(she)001:22372: dang po'i sa nas bdun par lhag bsam dag /
NK117(she)001:22373: dag pa gsum na rnam par smin pa dang //
NK117(she)001:22374: sangs rgyas sa na sgrib pa spangs te bzhi //
NK117(she)001:22375: de bzhin lam lnga'i rjes 'gro sems bskyed lnga //
NK117(she)001:22376: pha rol phyin pa drug ltos de snyed grangs //
NK117(she)001:22377: sa mtshams dbye ba nyi shu rtsa gnyis sogs //
NK117(she)001:22378: bsam pas smon dang 'jug pas khyab la 'du //
NK117(she)001:22379: zhes pa ni de ltar smon 'jug gnyis po de'ang so skye dang 'phags pa'i sems bskyed gnyis dang /
NK117(she)001:22382: sems can don byed gsum ni bslab pa gsum la ltos pa'i sems bskyed gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:22383: khyad par tshogs sbyor gyi lam pa la tshogs brgyad
NK117(she)001:22384: bag chags dang bcas pas rang ngo'i khams nyi ma
NK117(she)001:22385: lta bu bsgribs nas mi mthong ste mos pas spyod
NK117(she)001:22387: sa dang po nas bdun pa'i bar du nyon mongs
NK117(she)001:22388: pa can gyi yid log pas yon tan brgya phrag
NK117(she)001:22389: mngon du gyur cing khams kyi sgrib pa phyogs gcig
NK117(she)001:22390: dag pas ye shes kyi mthong ba cung zhig gsal
NK117(she)001:22391: bas lhag bsam dag pa ces brjod do //
NK117(she)001:22392: dag pa gsum du sgo lnga dang kun gzhi'i rnam
NK117(she)001:22393: shes log tshul ni sa brgyad par yid shes log
NK117(she)001:22394: pas rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK117(she)001:22395: dgu par sgo lnga'i rnam shes log pas zhing khams dag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22396: bcu par kun gzhi'i rnam shes log pas ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22397: smon lam dang yon tan rgya che ba'i phyir rnam par smin pa'i sems bskyed ces bya'o //
NK117(she)001:22398: sangs rgyas kyi sa na sgrib pa thams cad spangs pa'i don dam pa'i sems bskyed do //
NK117(she)001:22399: de bzhin du tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi slob pa'i
NK117(she)001:22400: lam lnga dang rjes su mthun pa'i sems bskyed lnga
NK117(she)001:22401: dang / pha rol tu phyin pa drug la ltos pa'i sems bskyed tshul drug /
NK117(she)001:22402: sa mtshams dbye ba nyer gnyis sogs bshad pa ni
NK117(she)001:22403: bsam pas smon pa dang 'brel ba'i 'jug pas khyab
NK117(she)001:22405: sa mtshams kyi dbye bas nyi shu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK117(she)001:22407: de yang sa gser zla ba med //
NK117(she)001:22408: gter dang rin chen 'byung gnas mtsho //
NK117(she)001:22409: rdo rje ri sman bshes gnyen dang //
NK117(she)001:22410: yid bzhin nor bu nyi ma glu //
NK117(she)001:22411: rgyal po'i mdzod dang lam po che //
NK117(she)001:22412: bzhon pa bkod ma'i chu dang ni //
NK117(she)001:22413: sgra snyan chu bo sprin rnams kyis //
NK117(she)001:22414: rnam pa nyi shu rtsa ga nyis so //
NK117(she)001:22415: smon pa'i sems rnam pa gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:22416: 'jug pa'i sems rnam pa bcu dgur bshad pa ni
NK117(she)001:22417: tshogs lam nas sa bcu pa'i bar yin la sa
NK117(she)001:22418: bcu gcig pa sangs rgyas kyi sa yin pas de
NK117(she)001:22421: gang zhig rang nyid legs pa don gnyer nas //
NK117(she)001:22422: rtag tu gcod pa med pa'i sgo 'phar nang //
NK117(she)001:22423: slong ba'i yid la 'khrugs pa mi ster ba //
NK117(she)001:22424: de la gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin zhes //
NK117(she)001:22425: basngagasa par 'os na mtha' dag sems can don //
NK117(she)001:22426: phan pa'i smon sems thang gcig skyes pas kyang //
NK117(she)001:22427: ngan song sgo gcod lha mi'i gnas rigs su //
NK117(she)001:22428: bde ba bsten pa'i yon tan zad mi shes //
NK117(she)001:22429: zhes pa ni gang su zhig rang nyid legs pa
NK117(she)001:22430: don du gnyer nas sbyin pa la brtson pa dag
NK117(she)001:22431: rtag tu gcod pa med pa'i mdzod khang gi sgo
NK117(she)001:22432: 'phar nang nas slong ba'i yid la 'dod pa 'gog
NK117(she)001:22433: pas 'khrugs pa mi ster ba de lta bu la
NK117(she)001:22434: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin zhes basngagasa brjod kyi
NK117(she)001:22436: mtha' dag sems can gyi don du phan pa'i smon
NK117(she)001:22437: sems thang cig skyes pas kyang ngan song gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:22438: sgo gcod cing lha dang mi'i gnas rigs su skyes
NK117(she)001:22439: nas bde ba bsten pa'i yon tan ni snga ma
NK117(she)001:22440: las 'phags shing zad mi shes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22443: khyad par 'jug pa'i yon tan mtha' yas te //
NK117(she)001:22444: dngos su sbyor bas khyab pa'i cho ga la //
NK117(she)001:22445: gang nas bzung ste ldog pa med pa'i sems //
NK117(she)001:22446: 'gro sgrol dam bca' shin tu yid brtan pa //
NK117(she)001:22447: de nas bzung ste bag med gnyid log kyang //
NK117(she)001:22448: bsod nams rgyun chags nyid du 'brel 'gyur ba //
NK117(she)001:22449: spyod pa'i sa las 'thad pa dang bcas bshad //
NK117(she)001:22450: ces pa ni khyad par zhes smon pa las kyang
NK117(she)001:22451: 'jug pa'i yon tan mtha' yas par gsungs shing de
NK117(she)001:22452: la dngos su sbyor bas khyab pa'i cho ga la
NK117(she)001:22453: zhugs pa gang nas bzung ste ldog pa med pa'i
NK117(she)001:22454: sems bskyed 'gro rnams sgrol ba'i dam bcar shin tu
NK117(she)001:22455: yid brtan pa blangs bzhin ma nyams pa de nas
NK117(she)001:22456: bzung ste bag med lung ma bstan nam gnyid log
NK117(she)001:22457: pa sogs dran pa nyams kyang bsod nams rgyun chags
NK117(she)001:22458: nyid du 'brel bar 'gyur ba theg pa chen po'i
NK117(she)001:22459: spyod pa'i sa las 'thad pa dang bcas te bshad
NK117(she)001:22461: bskal pa mang po'i tshogs kyang 'dums par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:22462: phyugs dang glang po shing rta nyi zla sogs //
NK117(she)001:22463: bgrod pa'i brtul zhugs myur bul mtha' yas ltar //
NK117(she)001:22464: blo stobs chen po'i thabs brtson shes rab kyis //
NK117(she)001:22465: grangs med gsum gyi dam bzhag 'jig pa yin //
NK117(she)001:22466: zhes pa ni de skad du dbang po rnon po ni bskal pa grangs med pa gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:22468: dbang rtul grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum gyi sangs
NK117(she)001:22469: rgya bar gsungs na'ang theg pa chen po'i lam la
NK117(she)001:22470: nges par zhugs pa dag gis ni bskal pa mang
NK117(she)001:22471: po'i tshogs kyang sems bskyed kyi 'phen pa re res
NK117(she)001:22472: 'dums par 'gyur ba'i dpe dang sems bskyed che chung
NK117(she)001:22474: phyugs kyi shing rta lta bu dang gcig /
NK117(she)001:22475: de bzhin du glang po lta bu dang gnyis /
NK117(she)001:22476: nyi zla lta bur 'gro ba dang gsum /
NK117(she)001:22477: nyan thos kyi rdzu 'phrul lta bus 'gro ba dang bzhi /
NK117(she)001:22478: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdzu 'phrul lta bus 'gro ba dang lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:22479: dang po de ni theg chen gyi lam la zhugs
NK117(she)001:22480: lo tsam byas kyang de bzhin du mi slob par
NK117(she)001:22481: nyan rang gi gzhung la slob par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22483: gang dag theg chen gyi lam du zhugs nas de'i
NK117(she)001:22484: gzhung la bslab sbyang yang byed nyan thos kyi gzhung
NK117(she)001:22485: yang mi 'dor zhing gnyis ka lhan cig tu nyams
NK117(she)001:22487: gsum pa ni byang chub tu sems bskyed nas nyan
NK117(she)001:22488: thos kyi gzhung la yid cung zad kyang mi ston
NK117(she)001:22489: par theg pa chen po'i gzhung kho na nyams su
NK117(she)001:22491: theg chen gyi lam du zhugs nas de kho na
NK117(she)001:22492: la yi dam byas kyang gzhan rjes su mi 'dzin
NK117(she)001:22493: pa dag go // lnga pa ni /
NK117(she)001:22494: theg chen gyi lam du zhugs nas de'i gzhung bzhin
NK117(she)001:22495: nyams su len cing gzhan yang de la 'god par
NK117(she)001:22497: de lta bu'i sangs rgyas kyi sa lam bgrod pa'i
NK117(she)001:22498: brtul zhugs la myur bul mtha' yas pa yod cing
NK117(she)001:22499: / de yang blo stobs chen po'i thabs mang la
NK117(she)001:22500: brtson nus pa dang shes rab kyi rtsal gyis theg
NK117(she)001:22501: chen ltar grangs med gsum gyi mthar sangs rgyas thob
NK117(she)001:22502: pa'i dam bzhag 'jig pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:22504: ji ltar sa bon sa la lhung ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:22505: sems mchog bskyed pa mi gtso skyes pa gtso //
NK117(she)001:22506: zhes pa ni so so skye bo'i rgyud la byang
NK117(she)001:22507: chub kyi sa bon bzhag pa tsam yin gyis de'i
NK117(she)001:22508: dpe ni ji ltar sa bon sa la lhung ba
NK117(she)001:22509: la myu gu smin dgos na'ang de'i gegs theg dman
NK117(she)001:22510: lam gyi byed pas sems mchog bskyed pa kho na
NK117(she)001:22511: las skyes pa nyid gtso che zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22512: ded dpon snying rje chen pos mi nag mdung thung
NK117(she)001:22513: can bsad pas bskal pa bzhi khri'i tshogs 'dum pa
NK117(she)001:22514: dang / bram ze khye'u skar ma la dga' bas
NK117(she)001:22515: tshong dpon gyi bu mo 'dod pas gzir te lceb
NK117(she)001:22516: dang / par brtsam pa / srog la bskyab phyir
NK117(she)001:22517: tshangs spyod btang bas bskal pa nyi khri'i tshogs 'dums
NK117(she)001:22518: pa bzhin grangs med mang por thogs par ma nges
NK117(she)001:22521: stobs gsum las ni byang chub sems skye bas //
NK117(she)001:22522: snying rje che dang tshogs bsags skyabs su 'gro //
NK117(she)001:22523: bsam dang sbyor ba rgyu yi stobs su bshad //
NK117(she)001:22524: ces pa ni de yang bsam pa'i stobs snying rje
NK117(she)001:22525: chen po la blo 'byongs pas sbyor ba'i tshogs bsags
NK117(she)001:22526: pa rgyu'i stobs skyabs 'gro khyad par can byas pa
NK117(she)001:22527: las skye ba'o // khyad par bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK117(she)001:22528: la brten nas theg pa chen po'i sems skye bar
NK117(she)001:22529: yang sngon sangs rgyas grags pa tha ga par gyur
NK117(she)001:22530: tshe sangs rgyas glog gi sgron ma la ras kyi
NK117(she)001:22532: bde gshegs 'od 'phro can sprang por gyur tshe sangs
NK117(she)001:22533: rgyas 'od mtha' yas la rtsi'i sgron me phul nas
NK117(she)001:22534: thugs bskyed pa sogs la bsam par bya ba ni
NK117(she)001:22535: gal che zhing / dus rnams kun tu yan lag
NK117(she)001:22536: bdun pa sogs tshogs bsag gi rim pa mtha' ma
NK117(she)001:22537: bkag pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:22539: rten gyi gang zag rnam pa gnyis bstan te //
NK117(she)001:22540: so thar rigs bdun gang rung sdom ldan nam //
NK117(she)001:22541: dkon mchog t+aa lar bsam pa'i rten gtso ba'i //
NK117(she)001:22542: rjes phyogs dbu ma'i lam srol 'jug pa yangs //
NK117(she)001:22543: zhes pa ni spyir sems bskyed tsam theg pa che
NK117(she)001:22544: chung gnyis kar yod kyang de'i cho ga spyod pa
NK117(she)001:22545: med do // 'di theg pa chen po la sems tsam pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22546: dbu ma pa'i lugs gnyis las sngon ma ltar na
NK117(she)001:22547: so thar rigs bdun gang rung gcig tshang dgos pa
NK117(she)001:22548: dang rjes ma ltar na srog gcod pa kho na
NK117(she)001:22549: spangs nus pa la dad pa dang snying rje yod
NK117(she)001:22550: na byang chub sems bskyed kyi bslab pa 'bogs pa
NK117(she)001:22553: tshogs bsag pa ni lhag par skye ba'i thabs //
NK117(she)001:22554: rgyu ni kun kyang bde gshegs snying po can //
NK117(she)001:22555: rkyen ni dge ba'i bshes la rab bsten pa //
NK117(she)001:22556: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i bla ma mchog /
NK117(she)001:22557: byang chub sems kyi thugs rgyud gang ba des //
NK117(she)001:22558: zhes pa ni de yang dge tshul gyi sdom pa mkhan slob las skyes /
NK117(she)001:22559: dge slong gi sdom pa dad pa'i dge 'dun las skye /
NK117(she)001:22560: byang chub kyi sems rin po che tshogs bsags pa
NK117(she)001:22561: kho na las skye bar gsungs pas dkon mchog mchod
NK117(she)001:22562: pa g.yo zol med par gang yod bsham dgos pa
NK117(she)001:22563: yang / sngon jo bo d+ai pam ka ra la
NK117(she)001:22564: bod ston tshos sems bskyed zhus tshe mchod pa chung
NK117(she)001:22565: ba la ma mnyes nas lan gnyis su bzhugs khang
NK117(she)001:22566: du gshegs mthar yod dgu spungs nas mchod par bshams
NK117(she)001:22567: tshe da dung yang rung tsam las ma gsungs /
NK117(she)001:22568: des na rang gi longs spyod cha gsum bgos pa'i cha gnyis dkon mchog spyi dang bla ma /
NK117(she)001:22569: gcig ni rang gis spyod du rung bar bshad pa'i
NK117(she)001:22570: phyir tshogs bsag la 'bungs pa ni byang chub kyi
NK117(she)001:22571: sems lhag par skye ba'i thabs su gsungs pa dang
NK117(she)001:22572: / de yang rgyu ni sems can kun kyang bde
NK117(she)001:22573: bar gshegs pa'i snying po 'o ma la mar gyis
NK117(she)001:22574: khyab pa bzhin yod pa can yin kyang rkyen ni
NK117(she)001:22575: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la rab tu gus pa'i sgo
NK117(she)001:22577: yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i bla ma bstan 'gror
NK117(she)001:22578: phan pa mchog dang ldan zhing khyad par byang chub
NK117(she)001:22579: kyi sems rin po che thugs rgyud gang ba de
NK117(she)001:22580: lta bu las bslab sdom blang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:22581: de ma rnyed na sangs rgyas dang byang sems rnams
NK117(she)001:22582: mdun mkhar bzhugs pa yid la byas te blang du
NK117(she)001:22584: de ltar blangs pas dngul chu gser du snang ba
NK117(she)001:22585: srang gcig gis lcags srang stong gser du bsgyur ba
NK117(she)001:22586: bzhin / byang chub sems bskyed dngul chu'i mchog lta
NK117(she)001:22587: bu des las dang nyon mongs pa lcags khams lta
NK117(she)001:22588: bu rnams ma lus par zad par byed do //
NK117(she)001:22590: thog mtha' bar du dge ba'i chos rnams dang //
NK117(she)001:22591: rgyan dang sdong po bkod las legs gsungs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:22592: byang chub sems kyi yon tan dpag yas brjod //
NK117(she)001:22593: ces pa ni 'dir blo sbyang ba'i phyir thog mar dge ba 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs la skyo ba /
NK117(she)001:22594: bar du dge ba thar pa'i phan yon la spro ba /
NK117(she)001:22595: tha mar dge ba stong nyid snying rjes rgyud legs
NK117(she)001:22596: par sbyangs pa theg chen la spro ba dag la
NK117(she)001:22597: sngon du rgyan dang sdong po bkod pa las legs
NK117(she)001:22598: par gsungs pa'i byang chub sems kyi yon tan dpag
NK117(she)001:22599: tu med pa brjod dgos par gsungs kyang mdor na
NK117(she)001:22600: sangs rgyas kyi chos thams cad dang sangs rgyas kyi
NK117(she)001:22601: yon tan thams cad dril ba dang byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:22602: kyi yon tan dang phan yon mnyam par gsungs pa
NK117(she)001:22603: dang / dper na rgya mtsho chen po ba dang
NK117(she)001:22604: ma he dang ra'i 'o ma sogs kyis yongs su
NK117(she)001:22605: bltams pa'i nang du seng+ge'i 'o ma thigs pa gcig
NK117(she)001:22606: blugs pas 'o ma gzhan ma thams cad 'bros shing
NK117(she)001:22607: 'gyes nas 'dur mi btub pa bzhin du bskal pa
NK117(she)001:22608: dpag med nas bsags pa'i las nyon thams cad byang
NK117(she)001:22609: chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i mthus 'bros shing 'gyes
NK117(she)001:22610: nas nyes byas kyi rnam smin dang theg dman gyi
NK117(she)001:22611: bsam sbyor 'du bar mi byed do //
NK117(she)001:22612: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa'i shing rta'i nang du
NK117(she)001:22613: zhugs te 'dod yon lnga la longs spyod pa zhig
NK117(she)001:22614: gi shing rta 'dren mkhan gzhan med na de bzhin
NK117(she)001:22615: gshegs pas kyang 'dren du rung zhing /
NK117(she)001:22616: nyan thos mchog gnyis lta bu yin kyang de ltar mi rung ngo //
NK117(she)001:22617: de ci'i phyir zhe na byang chub sems dpa' las
NK117(she)001:22618: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams skyes shing de las ni
NK117(she)001:22619: nyan rang rnams skye bas khyad par ro //
NK117(she)001:22621: skyang nul mdzes sdug ngom pa'i gnas khang yang //
NK117(she)001:22622: gur gum spos chus bran bcas gdong bkru zhing //
NK117(she)001:22623: dkon mchog 'ba' zhig yid la sems pa yi //
NK117(she)001:22624: mchod tshogs phru ma 'debs la dga' zhing dgod //
NK117(she)001:22625: ces pa ni de yang sdig pa'i skyon dang bral
NK117(she)001:22626: zhing dge ba'i dpal yon ldan pa'i gnas khang byi
NK117(she)001:22627: dor dang / skyang nul mdzes sdug ngom pa ste
NK117(she)001:22628: gur gum spos chu ba byung bran bcas gdong bkru
NK117(she)001:22629: zhes legs par byugs nas 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi
NK117(she)001:22630: skyon dang ma 'dres par dkon mchog gsum 'ba' zhig
NK117(she)001:22631: mchod pa la dga' ba dang spro ba'i sems kyis
NK117(she)001:22632: dngos su 'byor ba'i mchod pa sna lnga sogs dngos
NK117(she)001:22633: gtsang gya nom pa ser snas cung zad kyang ma
NK117(she)001:22634: sbags pa'i rigs dang de las kyang blos dpag med
NK117(she)001:22635: du sprul nas mchod pa'i tshogs phru ma 'debs zhes
NK117(she)001:22636: mngon du bstar 'jig rten na lha mi'i sgar chen
NK117(she)001:22637: thang du lhags pa lta bu'i bkrag dang gzi 'od
NK117(she)001:22638: dpag tu med pa bshams pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22640: dam tshig gzugs brnyan mtha' dag der bos nas //
NK117(she)001:22641: ye shes sems dpa'i dgug gzhug cho ga ni //
NK117(she)001:22642: mdza' gcugs dam bca' dran pa las myur bas //
NK117(she)001:22643: rgyal rnams zhing khams gzhan du gzigs pa yol //
NK117(she)001:22644: zhes pa ni gnas khang der dam tshig gi gzugs
NK117(she)001:22645: brnyan mtha' dag ni sku gsung thugs rten gang yod
NK117(she)001:22646: rnams spyan drangs la bzhugs gsol nas ye shes sems
NK117(she)001:22647: dpa'i dgug gzhug cho ga ni /
NK117(she)001:22648: spyan 'dren gyi tshig gang rung gis kha tsam ma yin par snying nas dad pas spyan drangs na /
NK117(she)001:22649: rang nyid la mdza' zhing gcugs pa'i snying mthun gyi
NK117(she)001:22650: grogs dang dus btab pa'i dam bca' dran pa las
NK117(she)001:22651: myur bas bdag kho nar brtse ba'i thugs kyis dgongs
NK117(she)001:22652: nas byon pa las rgyal ba rnams zhing khams gzhan
NK117(she)001:22653: du gzigs pa bshol ba la yol zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22654: 'dir rtsa 'grel lhan du bsdebs pa la /
NK117(she)001:22655: gang zhig zhes ma lus mi lus lus pa med
NK117(she)001:22656: pa'i sems can thams cad kyi mgon dang dpung gnyen
NK117(she)001:22657: du gyur kyang thar lam la bar du gcod pa'i
NK117(she)001:22658: bdud kyi sde tshogs yongs kyi dgrar gyur pa ni
NK117(she)001:22659: ji lta ba don dam dang ji snyed pa kun
NK117(she)001:22660: rdzob kyi chos rnams chags thogs med par mkhyen cing
NK117(she)001:22662: bdud bzhi bcom zhing phar drug dang ldan pa'i rgyal
NK117(she)001:22663: ba rnams bdag gi sdum pa ste gnas khang 'dir
NK117(she)001:22664: mchis su gsol ni 'byon par bskul nas /
NK117(she)001:22665: de yang las dang rdzu 'phrul gyis sprul pa ma
NK117(she)001:22666: yin zhing rnam gsum dad pa'i blo yis rgyal ba
NK117(she)001:22667: 'khor bcas pa'i 'byon pa'i shul te lam bar du
NK117(she)001:22668: khrus kyi khang bu brtsegs pa dri bsung 'thul ba
NK117(she)001:22669: can dang / der yang kha dog sna tshogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:22670: shel dang nor bu'i rigs kyis gzhi da nga ka
NK117(she)001:22671: ba la sogs dang ldan zhing /
NK117(she)001:22672: g.yu dmar dang mu tig gi bla bre dpyangs pa'i gnas khang der su zhig bzhugs su gsol na /
NK117(she)001:22673: bde gshegs rgyal ba rnams dang rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa rnams la /
NK117(she)001:22674: dri bzangs kyi spos chu sna tshogs kyis gang ba'i
NK117(she)001:22675: nor bu'i bum pa nas khrus kyi rim gro ba
NK117(she)001:22676: ste sri zhu bgyid pa'i smin legs ma ni lha
NK117(she)001:22677: mi'i bu mo mdzes ma'i tshogs kyis /
NK117(she)001:22678: glu dang rol mo'i 'gyur ba gcig las gcig lhag pa 'gran pa la brtson pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:22679: nye reg ste khrus kyi cho ga la mkhas pa'i
NK117(she)001:22680: ri dwags mig dkyus ring ba dag gis dril phyis
NK117(she)001:22681: lha'i dar pany+tsa li ka lta bu'i sku mnye'i ste
NK117(she)001:22682: snga ma khrus byas pa'i gnas rnams phyi zhing sri
NK117(she)001:22683: zhus g.yeng ba'ang / dar kha dog gcig kho nar
NK117(she)001:22684: mi gnas te dbang po'i mtshon zhes pa 'ja' tshon
NK117(she)001:22685: kha dog sna tshogs pa lta bu /
NK117(she)001:22686: de yang thags su btags pa lta bu'i tha mal
NK117(she)001:22687: gyi skyon med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sprul pa'i
NK117(she)001:22688: lha rdzas de nyid yul gang las na rang sems
NK117(she)001:22689: kyi rtsal du shar ba rtsal gyis nyo zhes pa
NK117(she)001:22690: dang / lha'i dpag bsam gyi shing las gang 'dod
NK117(she)001:22691: kyi zas gos 'byung ba yin na de la ljon
NK117(she)001:22692: pas btsong ba'i pany+tsa li zhes nyo tshong gis thob
NK117(she)001:22693: pa'i tha snyad kyis btags nas /
NK117(she)001:22694: de yang lcid kyi skyon spangs shing srab 'jam yang
NK117(she)001:22695: ba'i yon tan dang ldan pa'i gos kyi mchog de
NK117(she)001:22696: lta bu la / dri bzang dang spos chus bgos shing byugs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22697: gzhan yang sems dpa' chen po la 'os pa'i rin
NK117(she)001:22698: thang gzhal du med pa la brjod la khrel ba'i
NK117(she)001:22699: rin po che'i rgyan gyi bye brag phyag zhabs rnams
NK117(she)001:22700: su gdu bu dpung rgyan snyan cha dar gyi cod
NK117(she)001:22702: 'dod pa'i yon tan spangs pa'i thub pa'i dbang pos
NK117(she)001:22703: kyang bkren ldan zhes yi dwags kyi 'gro ba lta
NK117(she)001:22704: bu bdag cag bsod nams bsags pa'i slad du bdag
NK117(she)001:22705: gir bzhes nas tshogs rdzogs par gsol ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22706: 'jig rten dbang phyug la sogs nye ba'i sras chen
NK117(she)001:22707: brgyad dang ngan song kun 'dren la sogs pa bskal
NK117(she)001:22708: bzang gi sems dpa' bcu drug rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:22709: khyim pa'i tshul 'dzin pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chos
NK117(she)001:22710: 'phags dang rtag tu ngu li tsa bi dri ma
NK117(she)001:22711: med par grags pa dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul
NK117(she)001:22713: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i khams gcig car du
NK117(she)001:22714: khyab pa'i dri'i bzhon pa ste rlung la 'khyud pa'i
NK117(she)001:22715: tsan+d+hana spos kyi bsung zhim dris gang la bgos na
NK117(she)001:22716: / bsod nams bye ba'i 'byung gnas rgyal ba rnams
NK117(she)001:22717: kyis mtshan dpe'i byad ces sku'i dkyil 'khor gser sbyangs
NK117(she)001:22718: kyi brtan pa 'phrog nus pa de la byugs par
NK117(she)001:22719: / bgyi / tshad med bzhi ni btang snyoms yangs
NK117(she)001:22720: pa shel gyi sa gzhi lta bu la byams pa
NK117(she)001:22721: tshad med pa'i pad+mo'i ge sar stong brdal bar /
NK117(she)001:22722: snying rje tshad med pa'i nyi zla bkrag tu 'tsher
NK117(she)001:22723: ba bstar lha'i dga' ba chen po bcom ldan 'das
NK117(she)001:22724: 'khor dang bcas pa bzhugs su gsol zhes brjod la
NK117(she)001:22726: mchong rgyug dang 'gyel bub sogs bab col gyi goms
NK117(she)001:22727: pa 'dor len ma yin pa'i lus gus btud kyi
NK117(she)001:22728: rnam pas / snying khar gus pa dang bcas pa'i
NK117(she)001:22729: mngon rtogs ngom pa ji lta bu zhe na me
NK117(she)001:22730: tog sna tshogs kyi yu ba chun por byas pa
NK117(she)001:22731: la dog pa'i dang rab bzung snyims pa'i snod ni
NK117(she)001:22732: lag pa gnyis thal mo sbyar ba ga'u chung gi
NK117(she)001:22733: brtul zhugs 'dzin pa yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22735: rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa la sogs bde
NK117(she)001:22736: gshegs rnams kyi yon tan mtha' dag gnas kyis bskal
NK117(she)001:22737: nas gzhan du bgrod ma nus pa bzhin du /
NK117(she)001:22738: bdag gi dad pa'i skyed mos tshal 'di nyid du
NK117(she)001:22739: 'ongs pa'i mod sdug bsngal la skyo ba ltar min
NK117(she)001:22740: pa'i dad pas bskyed pas lus kyi ba spu yang
NK117(she)001:22742: yan lag bdun pa'i dang po phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK117(she)001:22744: ston zla gsar pa la gzhon pa'i tha snyad dang
NK117(she)001:22745: de nyid khrus la 'jug pa zhes gzugs brnyan rdzing
NK117(she)001:22746: bu'i nang du snang yul der /
NK117(she)001:22747: rma bya'i bu mo zhes de la pho med pa
NK117(she)001:22748: shugs kyis bstan nas chu de'i nang du de nyid
NK117(she)001:22749: 'jo sgeg rol pa lta bu'i bdag lus lang tsho'i
NK117(she)001:22750: grangs snyed rdul gyi rnam grangs dang shin tu 'khrul
NK117(she)001:22751: pa skyed byed phyag gis brel zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22753: ljon shing sa la bsnyal ba bzhin lus sa la
NK117(she)001:22754: bag yod par brkyang la mar me mdzad kyi brkyang
NK117(she)001:22755: phyag ces bya'o // de la mgo bo sa la
NK117(she)001:22756: smad gzhan yan lag bzhi po shugs la smad pa
NK117(she)001:22759: spyi mgrin snying ga gsum du thal mo 'jog pa
NK117(she)001:22760: dang lhan cig dkon mchog gsum la dmigs nas sngon
NK117(she)001:22761: bzhin bya ba dang de ltar lan gsum ldab pa
NK117(she)001:22762: la phyag dgu phrugs su 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22763: yang na bla ma lta bur dang po mjal ma thag dang /
NK117(she)001:22764: de nas phyag rten phul mthar dang /
NK117(she)001:22765: de nas snyun smod de smon bzhin yan lag lnga
NK117(she)001:22766: phyag lan gsum gsum dgu 'tshal ba la'ang dgu phrug
NK117(she)001:22767: zer ro // mchod pa'i yan lag ni /
NK117(she)001:22769: gtong ba'i yan lag ni yar mchod mar sbyin gnyis
NK117(she)001:22770: ka yin te rdzogs pa'i zhes ser snas ma bcings
NK117(she)001:22772: des kyang mtshon par mi nus pa la dpe med
NK117(she)001:22773: ces sngon ma las 'phags pa ni yid kyis sprul
NK117(she)001:22775: de'i bla na mchod pa gzhan mchis pa ma yin pa mchod pa'i sprin rgya mtsho /
NK117(she)001:22776: 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i yon la zhes gang
NK117(she)001:22777: gi mchod pa 'gran du yod pa srid khams na
NK117(she)001:22778: med kyang sems stobs chen pos de ltar spro nus
NK117(she)001:22779: pas phrag dog bgyid ces tha snyad smos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22780: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22782: sems can la snying rje bsgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:22783: chos bsgrub pa dang bzhi po yang bla na med pa'i mchod par bzhag pa yod do //
NK117(she)001:22784: sdig bshags kyi yan lag ni /
NK117(she)001:22785: mu cor smra ba'i las dang zhes pa ni kha
NK117(she)001:22786: ni sdig pa'i sgo yin pas ngag gi mi dge
NK117(she)001:22787: ba la mu cor smra ba'i las dang zhes rjes
NK117(she)001:22788: su smin rgyu dang bag chags ni rin po che
NK117(she)001:22789: dang g.ya' bzhin 'bral med du gnas pa de sdig
NK117(she)001:22790: pa'i sa bon ltar yod pa de nyid dge ba
NK117(she)001:22791: bcu sgrub pa la 'jigs shing skrag nas gzhan du
NK117(she)001:22792: bros pa lta bu'i mi dge ba'i gzugs de nyid
NK117(she)001:22793: re zhig cig dge ba nyi tshe bas zil gyis
NK117(she)001:22794: non nas srid pa'i mun nag ste nyon mongs pa
NK117(she)001:22795: brgyad khri srab mo ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:22796: shin tu stug po'i gnas su sbas pa la 'chab pa de kun gzhan gyis bkru ru med kyang /
NK117(she)001:22797: stobs bzhi'i nyin byed 'bar bas sbyangs shing bshags te
NK117(she)001:22798: sngon mi dge ba'i las byas pa la gnong zhing
NK117(she)001:22799: 'gyod pa dang 'jigs shing ngo tsha bar byed pa
NK117(she)001:22800: ni rnam par sun 'byin pa'i stobs dang /
NK117(she)001:22801: rang nyid gnyen po zhan pa'i skyon gyis nyon mongs
NK117(she)001:22802: pa'i dbang du shor nas sngon mi dge ba la
NK117(she)001:22803: spyod kyang de las shin tu mang ba'i dge stobs
NK117(she)001:22804: rgya chen po bskyed pa ni gnyen po kun tu
NK117(she)001:22805: spyod pa'i stobs / sngon mi dge ba byas pa
NK117(she)001:22806: la shin tu 'gyod pas slar sdom pa blangs nas
NK117(she)001:22807: srog la babs kyang sdig pa mi byed pa ni
NK117(she)001:22808: nyes pa las ldog pa'i sor chud pa'i stobs /
NK117(she)001:22809: sdig pa bshags pa'i ched du sgo gsum gyi dge
NK117(she)001:22810: ba bsgrubs tshad dang khyad par mchog gsum la skyabs
NK117(she)001:22811: 'gro dang byang chub kyi sems rin po che bsgoms
NK117(she)001:22812: pas sdig pa zad par byed cing /
NK117(she)001:22813: de las kyang pha ma dang rang sangs rgyas bsad
NK117(she)001:22814: pa yang stong pa nyid bsgoms pas 'dag par gsungs
NK117(she)001:22815: pa yang sdig pa 'dus byas yin pa'i phyir ro
NK117(she)001:22817: sbyor ba sngon 'gro'i skabs chags sdang rmongs gsum gang
NK117(she)001:22818: gis kyang bdag nyid kyi sems ma 'khrugs bzhin du
NK117(she)001:22819: bsam pa'i khyad par gcig gis zhes dge sgrub sdig
NK117(she)001:22821: de yang gzhan phyogs dang ris su ma chad pa'i
NK117(she)001:22822: rnam dkar gyi dge ba la snying thag pa nas
NK117(she)001:22823: dga' zhing spro bar gyur na de'i bsod nams yud
NK117(she)001:22824: tsam la rang gis thob pa la 'phrog pa'i chom
NK117(she)001:22825: rkun gyi brtul zhugs lta bu dper sbyar ba ste
NK117(she)001:22826: rjes su yi rang kho nas de ltar byas pa
NK117(she)001:22828: sngon ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis ston
NK117(she)001:22829: pa 'khor dang bcas pa nyin zhag sbrel nas bsnyen
NK117(she)001:22830: bkur ba'i tshe grong mtha' sprang po zhig gis rjes
NK117(she)001:22831: su yi rang rgya chen byas pa /
NK117(she)001:22832: ston pa dus gsum mkhyen pas rgyal po la da
NK117(she)001:22833: lam gyi bsngo ba 'di rgyal po khyod kyi bsod
NK117(she)001:22835: khyod kyis rnam dkar bgyis pa 'di'i stobs kyis gzhan
NK117(she)001:22836: zhig la khyod las lhag pa'i bsod nams 'thob pa
NK117(she)001:22837: la bsngo zhes bka' bstsal pas /
NK117(she)001:22838: bdag gi dge bas gzhan zhig bsod nams che bar
NK117(she)001:22839: gyur na de la sngos shig zhus pas dbul po'i
NK117(she)001:22840: ming nas smos te bsngo ba mdzad pa yang rjes
NK117(she)001:22841: su yi rang gi phan yon yin no //
NK117(she)001:22843: thar med 'khor ba'i spyod pa ni ma dul ba
NK117(she)001:22844: ma zhi ba ma bsdams pa sogs sdig pa dang
NK117(she)001:22845: g.yo sgyu kho nas bslad pa /
NK117(she)001:22846: mchod sbyin la lcags kyi pha gu bzhin du sra
NK117(she)001:22847: ba ser sna sogs la goms pa brtas pa rdo
NK117(she)001:22848: rje 'dag pa ltar mkhregs pa nges 'byung dang dad
NK117(she)001:22849: pa la tha rgod ltar rengs par gyur pa de
NK117(she)001:22850: lta bu ni / gzhan gang gis kyang gdul thabs
NK117(she)001:22851: brtan pa bral ba de la'ang drang nges ldem dgongs
NK117(she)001:22852: chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bsdu ba'i
NK117(she)001:22853: gang la gang 'dul gyi rtsibs rnon po mngon mtho
NK117(she)001:22854: dang nges legs kyi mu khyud las 'da' ba med
NK117(she)001:22855: pa de bskor bar bskul ba'o //
NK117(she)001:22857: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba dang de sras
NK117(she)001:22858: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis spangs par gyur na
NK117(she)001:22859: ston pa dang bstan pa gnyis ka med par 'gyur
NK117(she)001:22860: zhing de med na rgyu 'bras kyi blang dor mi
NK117(she)001:22861: shes pa'i 'gro ba rigs drug po 'dis sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:22862: kho na la spyod pa'i gnas skabs kyi rten tsam
NK117(she)001:22864: de rnams thar pa dang rnam mkhyen gyi go 'phang la 'god pa'i ched du /
NK117(she)001:22865: sku mya ngan las 'da' ba ma yin pa'i gdan
NK117(she)001:22866: khri la bzhugs pa'i yon du dngos po kun gyi
NK117(she)001:22867: rin thang gcig tu dril te spungs na bdag sogs
NK117(she)001:22868: 'gro ba'i ched du yun ring bzhugs par gsol ba
NK117(she)001:22869: btab na de'i rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bur bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:22870: kyang dus min 'chi bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:22872: 'dir yang srid pa'i bde 'bras la dmigs pa la
NK117(she)001:22873: bdag tu blta bas 'dar ba'i zhes 'jig rten chos
NK117(she)001:22874: brgyad kyi bsam pas rnam dkar gyi las ltar snang
NK117(she)001:22875: ba yang srid par lan cig smin nas mngon mtho'i
NK117(she)001:22876: lus rten tsam thob nas myur du 'dzad pa yin
NK117(she)001:22877: kyang cho nge ste de'i grags pa sgrog pa la
NK117(she)001:22879: byang chub bsngo ba'i thabs zab mo dang ldan na
NK117(she)001:22880: lcags la gser 'gyur gyi rtsis thebs pa bzhin mi
NK117(she)001:22881: gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyur 'gyur bar
NK117(she)001:22882: nges na / 'di lta bu'i 'phags chos dpag tu
NK117(she)001:22883: med pa ni nyan rang dang phyi rol pa su
NK117(she)001:22884: la yang med pas na ston pa gzhan gyi lugs
NK117(she)001:22886: de'i phyir na dge ba sngon byas dang byed 'gyur thams cad bsngo bar gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22887: rang gi bsod nams longs spyod la chog shes yod
NK117(she)001:22888: pa la bdud rtsi'i btung bas zhes de'i ma ngom
NK117(she)001:22889: nas mchod sbyin sogs gtong ba'i las la ma brtson
NK117(she)001:22890: na / skyes bu'i yid la ma bzung ba'i mchod sprin ni yid sprul kho na ste /
NK117(she)001:22891: de ni dngos 'byor ser snas bcings te gtong mi
NK117(she)001:22892: bra bzhin du yid sprul tsam la bstod basngagasa brjod
NK117(she)001:22893: cing rloms par byed pa tsam ni tshig gi pha
NK117(she)001:22894: mthar 'khyams pa ste tshig tsam du zad par gyur
NK117(she)001:22895: pa la skrag par gyur nas dngos 'byor gtong ba
NK117(she)001:22897: bdag gis gces par bzung ba'i lus 'di yang stan du 'bul ba la'ang do gal bgyid ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22898: yang 'di ltar dkon mchog gsum gyi 'bangs sam g.yog
NK117(she)001:22899: tu dam bcas pa'i chos 'dod gang zhig thugs rje'i
NK117(she)001:22900: grib bsil du bsti bas me tog sad ser gyi
NK117(she)001:22901: 'jigs pa dang bral bzhin 'jo sgegs kyi lang tsho
NK117(she)001:22902: ngom pa can lta bu de ni rnam pa kun
NK117(she)001:22903: tu 'khrugs pa'i zhi zhing dul ba ma yin pa'i
NK117(she)001:22904: gshin rje'i pho nya'i mdun sar dkon mchog dran pa'i
NK117(she)001:22905: mod la 'jigs skrag skye ba'i mngon rtogs kyi khro
NK117(she)001:22906: gnyer 'jig par byed pa'i rin thang zad mi shes
NK117(she)001:22908: yang de'i phyir na skye ba kun tu gti mug
NK117(she)001:22909: gi mthus non pa'i sdig pa dang ldan pa bdag
NK117(she)001:22910: ni / byi dor shin tu bsten pa'i dwangs shel
NK117(she)001:22911: bzang po ltar du bsod nams ma yin pa'i rnyog
NK117(she)001:22912: ma mtha' dag dwangs pa'i sems kyi nang du brda
NK117(she)001:22913: can cho ga las thob pa'i byang chub sems bskyed
NK117(she)001:22914: cho gas thob pa'i gzugs brnyan ngom zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22916: nyon mongs pa'i nyes pa brgya phrag g.yang sar lhung
NK117(she)001:22917: ba'i dam sdom nyams pa'i gang zag dug gsum dang
NK117(she)001:22918: dug lnga'i rims kyis shin tu btab pa'i nad pa
NK117(she)001:22920: gso dpyad de sman pa phal pa'i mdun sar dbugs
NK117(she)001:22921: mi phyin te des 'du ba rnam bzhi la phan
NK117(she)001:22922: srid kyang / nyon mongs kyis gdung ba'i nad sel
NK117(she)001:22923: mi nus na sman pa mchog ces dkon mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:22924: la skyabs su lhag par dong zhes snying nas skyabs
NK117(she)001:22925: srid kyang / su 'gro ba'o // yang bsod nams
NK117(she)001:22926: kyi mthus bskyed pas dad pa dang mos pa mchog
NK117(she)001:22927: dang ldan pa gang gi slad du gnas khang 'dir
NK117(she)001:22928: ston pa gtso 'khor rnams gshegs nas kyang /
NK117(she)001:22929: sems can gyi khams dang dbang po la dgongs pa'i
NK117(she)001:22930: ston pa'i zhal skyin mchog ni theg pa chen po'i
NK117(she)001:22931: skyes bu 'ba' zhig yin pas de nyid tshogs kyi
NK117(she)001:22932: dbus na lham mer mdzes pa la /
NK117(she)001:22933: zhes sdom pa blang ba'i yul byang sems 'phags pa
NK117(she)001:22934: 'ba' zhig gi dbus na bzhugs pa la dang ba
NK117(she)001:22935: 'dren cing dad pa bskyed par bya dgos zhes pa'o
NK117(she)001:22936: // yang byang chub sems bskyed kyi bslab pa zhu
NK117(she)001:22937: ba'i sngon du skyabs su 'gro ba gsum gyi gzhi
NK117(she)001:22938: bcas la dgongs su gsol ba lan gsum gyis yul
NK117(she)001:22939: mchog gsum la snyan gsan phab pa sngon du 'gro
NK117(she)001:22940: ba dang chabs cig sems bskyed zhu yul gyi bla
NK117(she)001:22941: ma'i dgongs pa sad par byas nas /
NK117(she)001:22942: bslab sdom ji ltar blang na bdud sde'i g.yul las
NK117(she)001:22943: rgyal ba'i sangs rgyas rnams dang de dag gi gdung
NK117(she)001:22944: byang chub sems bskyed kyi bslab pa 'dzin pa'i rgyal
NK117(she)001:22945: sras 'phags pa'i tshogs dang bcas pa'i thugs bskyed dang
NK117(she)001:22946: bslab pa'i brtul zhugs kha tsam ma yin par yang
NK117(she)001:22947: dag par blang ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:22948: de yang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa'i zug rngu ste
NK117(she)001:22949: rab tu gdung ba srin bu'i kha chus rang nyid
NK117(she)001:22950: 'ching ba lta bu dum bur bcad par gyur kyang
NK117(she)001:22951: / shes sgrib ste lta sgom yul dang yul can
NK117(she)001:22952: du bzung zhing ro myong ba ltar yid la bcags
NK117(she)001:22953: shing zhen pa'i thos dang rang rgyal dgra bcom pa
NK117(she)001:22954: dag rang nyid thar pa gnyer las gzhan don mi
NK117(she)001:22955: sems pa'i rigs rnams gang las ma bsgral na rang
NK117(she)001:22956: don yid byed las ma bsgral ba theg chen gyi
NK117(she)001:22957: sar bkod pa la bsgral zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22958: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gnyis ka'i 'ching ba kun
NK117(she)001:22959: nas dkris pa'i 'jig rten mes po tshangs pa mar
NK117(she)001:22960: bzung nas lam la ma zhugs pa'i so so skye
NK117(she)001:22962: slob lam bzhi dang 'phags pa'i bden pa mthong ba'i
NK117(she)001:22963: bar la gnas pa'i sems can ma grol ba de
NK117(she)001:22964: dag rnams lha mi'i sems 'dzin las grol nas nyan
NK117(she)001:22965: rang gi dgra bcom la 'god par bya ba dang
NK117(she)001:22966: / mtho ris rnam gsum las shin tu sdug bsngal
NK117(she)001:22967: drag pos mnar ba'i gdung shugs rgya che zhing rgyun
NK117(she)001:22968: ring ba las bde ba'i dbugs 'byin thob pa med
NK117(she)001:22969: pa'i ngan song gsum por bsti ba'i 'gro ba mtha'
NK117(she)001:22970: / dag kyang / dbugs 'byin chen po'i zhes lha dang mi'i gnas yul la sbyar ba dang /
NK117(she)001:22971: mdor na 'khor ba'i rten cing 'brel 'byung bcu gnyis
NK117(she)001:22972: kyi dpe ni zo chu'i 'khyud mo'i chu 'thags kyi
NK117(she)001:22973: 'khor lo ltar rgyun chad med par 'khor ba'i rgyar
NK117(she)001:22974: chud pa'i sems can yod do cog mi gnas pa'i
NK117(she)001:22975: ye shes mya ngan zhes 'khor ba'i sa las 'das
NK117(she)001:22976: pa'i grong khyer mchog ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i go
NK117(she)001:22977: 'phang yin te / der 'god par byed pa'i thabs
NK117(she)001:22978: kyi cho gas bzung ba'i brjod pa 'di lta bu
NK117(she)001:22979: 'phang yin te / ni / sngon tshe byon pa'i
NK117(she)001:22980: rgyal dang de sras rnams kyi thugs rgyud la ya
NK117(she)001:22981: yo dang kyag kyog med pa'i drang por srong ba
NK117(she)001:22982: ste de rnams kyi lugs la brten par bgyid do
NK117(she)001:22985: zur du bkod pa ltar shes par bya ba kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:22987: byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i bslab pa blang phan du lan gcig ma yin par /
NK117(she)001:22988: rtag par rgyun du nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum
NK117(she)001:22989: byang chub smon pa dang 'jug pa'i sems gnyis bskyed
NK117(she)001:22990: pa la nan tan bya dgos zhes bstan nas /
NK117(she)001:22991: yang rang nyid kyi dad pa dang 'dun pa'i rtse
NK117(she)001:22992: mo la byin rlabs dang dpal yon kun kyang de'i
NK117(she)001:22993: rkyen gyis chags par byed pas /
NK117(she)001:22994: dgongs su gsol ba dang pos smon pa thob cing /
NK117(she)001:22995: de bzhin du gnyis pas 'jug pa dang gsum pas gnyis ka brtan par thob pa ni /
NK117(she)001:22996: rgya mtsho'i sprin gyi bzhed pa zhes de nyid kyis gsungs pa bla na med pa yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:22997: yang sngon chad gzhan gyi don la dmigs pa'i sems
NK117(she)001:22998: bskyed pa smos ci dgos rang gi don du sems
NK117(she)001:22999: bskyed dgos pa rmi lam tsam du'ang ma myong ba'i
NK117(she)001:23000: da lam yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che
NK117(she)001:23001: lta bu'i sems kyi khyad par 'phags pa'i go 'phang
NK117(she)001:23002: la bkod pa'i thabs zab mo 'di'i yon tan gyis
NK117(she)001:23003: / bdag gi srid pa zhes mi lus thob pa
NK117(she)001:23004: tsam la bstod basngagasa brjod kyang rin thang de tsam
NK117(she)001:23005: med la byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i yon
NK117(she)001:23006: tan dang 'bras bu ni dpag tu med do zhes
NK117(she)001:23007: / pa'o // yang rgyal bu rkang 'khyams pa rgyal
NK117(she)001:23008: po'i rigs las gang su dag ji zhig cho zhes
NK117(she)001:23009: zhang phyogs dang rigs pha phyogs kyis mngon par mtho
NK117(she)001:23010: ba'i dpal yon gyis lhag par phyug pa'i btsun pa'i
NK117(she)001:23011: gnas thob pa ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK117(she)001:23012: rgyal ba kun gyi sras su dus de ring nas
NK117(she)001:23013: gyur pas byang chub sems dpa' zhes ming gi cod
NK117(she)001:23014: pan mgo bor thob pas rab tu dga' bar byas
NK117(she)001:23016: yang 'di ltar sa 'og sa steng sa bla ste
NK117(she)001:23017: srid pa gsum gyi bdag po byas pa'i lha'i gtso
NK117(she)001:23018: bo rnams dang de nyid kyis dpal yon byin lta'i
NK117(she)001:23019: ma h+aa tsi na rgyal po sogs dang des kyang
NK117(she)001:23020: gzhan la rmongs pa'i bla dwags ta le bla ma
NK117(she)001:23022: tsang kyon sogs dpyangs zhes btags pa la'ang dga' bar byed na /
NK117(she)001:23023: de las khyad par bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'phags
NK117(she)001:23024: pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i gnas sam go sa thob
NK117(she)001:23025: pa de ring tsam du zad pas /
NK117(she)001:23026: 'di lta bu'i dpal dang yon tan dpag tu med
NK117(she)001:23027: pa'i byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i bslab pa
NK117(she)001:23028: blangs pa la dga' ba'i 'khri shing ste sar nyal
NK117(she)001:23029: ba'i rkang 'thung dag yar slong ba la lha yang
NK117(she)001:23030: phyogs par gyur to zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23031: yang de ltar byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i phan yon ni /
NK117(she)001:23032: 'chi bdag 'joms pa'i bdud rtsi mi zad pa'i gter lta bu /
NK117(she)001:23033: 'gro ba rnams kyi lugs zung gi dbul ba sel
NK117(she)001:23034: ba'i nor bu rin po che lta bu dang bzhi
NK117(she)001:23035: brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel ba'i sman mchog lta bu
NK117(she)001:23036: / srid pa mchog dman kun tu rgyu ba'i lam
NK117(she)001:23037: yun ring bas ngal zhing dub pa'i mgron po'i ngal
NK117(she)001:23039: bdag ni dus de ring nas byang chub mchog tu
NK117(she)001:23040: sems bskyed pa 'di'i mthus 'gro ba yongs kyi nye
NK117(she)001:23041: bar 'tsho ba'i byed por gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23042: mdor na rang don du bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed du dge rtsa byas pa las /
NK117(she)001:23043: dmigs pa med pas skad cig gcig la sems bskyed
NK117(she)001:23044: pa bsod nams che zhes yum bsdus las gsungs so
NK117(she)001:23045: // yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags
NK117(she)001:23046: 'byed byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po
NK117(she)001:23047: che'i lde mig las le'u brgyad pa'i skabs so ////
NK117(she)001:23048: da ni byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'i gzhung bstan pa /
NK117(she)001:23050: sngon chad legs par ma brtags bab col gyi //
NK117(she)001:23051: dam bca' gtong la'ang yid gnyis gnas mchi na //
NK117(she)001:23052: rgyal dang de sras rnams kyi shes rab mthus //
NK117(she)001:23053: gdon mi za bar brtags pa'i blang dor gnas //
NK117(she)001:23054: btang na bdag gis sems can kun bslus pas //
NK117(she)001:23055: mu mtha' med pa'i ngan 'gror 'khyams par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:23056: de phyir sems can gcig gi bde ba'ang //
NK117(she)001:23057: bshig nas bdag nyid nyams pa'i las mi bgyid //
NK117(she)001:23058: ces pa ni 'jig rten na gnas skabs kyi bya
NK117(she)001:23059: ba che chung gang yin kyang 'byung 'gyur gyi nyes
NK117(she)001:23060: dmigs la sngon chad legs par ma brtags bab col
NK117(she)001:23061: te deng dus kyi ser skya pho mo gshin por
NK117(she)001:23062: 'dre rlangs 'debs pa lta bus mtshon gzhan phan gyi
NK117(she)001:23063: dam bca' blangs pa khyad du bsad nas gzhan gnod
NK117(she)001:23064: kyi bsam sbyor kho na la brtson pa 'di tshos
NK117(she)001:23065: rang gzhan gang la'ang mi phan steng du gnod pa'i
NK117(she)001:23066: las la 'jug pa 'di 'dra'i skyon gyis rang gi
NK117(she)001:23067: sdom pa gsum ka dang khyad par byang sems kyi
NK117(she)001:23068: bslab pa gtong nges pa la yid gnyis kyi gnas
NK117(she)001:23069: mchi na / rgyal ba kun dang de sras byang
NK117(she)001:23070: chub sems dpa' rnams kyis shes rab kyi mthus legs
NK117(she)001:23071: par brtags shing dpyad nas 'phral phugs kun gyi bde
NK117(she)001:23072: legs dang yon tan gyi 'byung gnas ni gdon mi
NK117(she)001:23073: za bar theg pa chen po'i spyod pa nyid du
NK117(she)001:23074: bstan pa yin na de ltar brtags pa'i don 'bras
NK117(she)001:23075: su blang dor gyi gnas rnams 'dzol nas sems bskyed
NK117(she)001:23076: kyi bslab pa btang na bdag gis zhes gtong ba
NK117(she)001:23077: pos sems can kun bslus pa'i nyes pa 'go zhing
NK117(she)001:23078: de ltar na gang zag de srid pa phyi ma
NK117(she)001:23079: mu mtha' med pa'i ngan 'gror 'khyams par 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:23080: las 'os med na sems can la gnod pa'i kha
NK117(she)001:23081: na ma tho ba la 'dzem pa shin tu gal
NK117(she)001:23082: mchi na / che ste / bla na med pa'i
NK117(she)001:23083: bde ba ni sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul las
NK117(she)001:23084: med kyang bar du bde ba ste /
NK117(she)001:23085: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal la ngal gso ba'i stegs lta bu ni byang chub kyi sems rin po che'o //
NK117(she)001:23086: de bas na de nyid mi nyams pa'i thabs la brtson pa gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:23088: ltung dang byang chub sems stobs gnyis kar ldan //
NK117(she)001:23089: 'khor bar res kyi 'dre byed gang yin pa //
NK117(she)001:23090: sa thob pa la yun ring thogs 'gyur na //
NK117(she)001:23091: bslab bya gtong ba'i skyes bu smyon pa yin //
NK117(she)001:23092: zhes pa ni de la ngan song du ltung nges
NK117(she)001:23093: kyi las dang byang chub kyi sems stobs gnyis kar
NK117(she)001:23094: ldan pa dag 'khor bar yang res mos kyis 'dre
NK117(she)001:23095: bar byed pa gang yin pa de ni sa dang
NK117(she)001:23096: po sogs 'thob pa la yun ring du thogs par
NK117(she)001:23097: 'gyur na bslab bya blangs nas gtong ba'i skyes bu
NK117(she)001:23098: de ni smyon pa yin zhes smad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23100: gang zhig gnod pa'i rgyu 'bras chung ngu la'ang //
NK117(she)001:23101: khros pa'i nga rgyal shin tu bdo ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:23102: mda' mdung mtshon gyi chad pa bzod byas nas //
NK117(she)001:23103: don ma 'grub par phyir phyogs mi byed na //
NK117(she)001:23104: rnam pa kun tu bdag la dgrar gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:23105: nyon mongs stobs chen 'di dang g.yul sprad nas //
NK117(she)001:23106: 'khon du bzung ba'i cho ga ma zhig par //
NK117(she)001:23107: bslab pa bsrung ba'i brtul zhugs su zhig gtong //
NK117(she)001:23108: zhes pa ni 'jig rten na gang su zhig la
NK117(she)001:23109: gnod pa'i rgyu 'bras chung ngu tsam la'ang khros pa'i
NK117(she)001:23110: nga rgyal shin tu bdo ba ste bzod du med
NK117(she)001:23111: pa rnams ni lus srog la phangs pa med bzhin
NK117(she)001:23112: mda' mdung sogs mtshon gyi chad pa rtsub mo bzod
NK117(she)001:23113: par byas nas rang nyid kyis dmigs pa'i gnod 'tshe
NK117(she)001:23114: sbyor ba'i don de ma 'grub bar du phyir phyogs
NK117(she)001:23116: de las rnam pa kun tu bdag la dgrar gyur
NK117(she)001:23117: nges pa'i nyon mongs pa dug lnga dug gsum sogs
NK117(she)001:23118: stobs chen po yod pa 'di dag dang g.yul sprad
NK117(she)001:23119: pa lta bu'i spang gnyen gnyis 'gran nas 'khon du
NK117(she)001:23120: bzung ba'i cho ga ma zhig bar du byang chub
NK117(she)001:23121: sems dpa'i bslab pa bsrung ba'i brtul zhugs te spyod
NK117(she)001:23122: pa de nyid su zhig gis gtong phod mi gtong
NK117(she)001:23125: 'di na nyon mongs btson rar bsdams pa yi //
NK117(she)001:23126: bdag gi tshod kyang rig par mi 'gyur na //
NK117(she)001:23127: mtha' dag 'gro ba de las dbugs 'byin zhing //
NK117(she)001:23128: sgrol ba'i brtan pa mi nyams ga la zhig /
NK117(she)001:23129: ces pa ni de la nyon mongs pa dag ni
NK117(she)001:23130: phyi'i yul dang nang du dbang po dang bar zhes
NK117(she)001:23131: gang na'ang mi gnas kyang kun rtog las glo bur
NK117(she)001:23132: du byung zhing kun rtog de la'ang yul med na
NK117(she)001:23133: nyon mongs pa gzugs can ma yin pas rten dang
NK117(she)001:23135: rang bzhin du sems can thams cad 'di'i btson rar
NK117(she)001:23136: bsdams pa'i phyir gti mug la sogs pa'i rgyus bdag
NK117(she)001:23137: gi tshod kyang rig par mi 'gyur na mtha' dag
NK117(she)001:23138: 'gro ba de las dbugs 'byin zhing sgrol ba'i brtan
NK117(she)001:23139: pa mi nyams pa lta ga la zhig /
NK117(she)001:23140: khyad par sems can gyi don mi nus pas rang
NK117(she)001:23141: don sgrub blo'i zhi bde skyes pa ni sems bskyed
NK117(she)001:23143: bag yod shes bzhin ldan pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK117(she)001:23144: byang chub sems kyi myu gu bskyed sla bas //
NK117(she)001:23145: mi nyams bzung zhing dri ma sbyong ba dang //
NK117(she)001:23146: spel ba'i thabs la nan tan bgyid 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:23147: zhes pa ni bag yod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23148: dran pa dang shes bzhin rgyun chags su ldan pa
NK117(she)001:23149: ni sa gzhi lta bu la byang chub sems kyi
NK117(she)001:23150: sa bon btab na myu gu bskyed sla bas /
NK117(she)001:23151: theg chen gyi lam der zhugs pa'i bslab pa rnams
NK117(she)001:23152: mi nyams par bzung zhing de'i mi mthun phyogs kyi
NK117(she)001:23153: dri ma rnams rim bzhin sbyong ba dang byang chub
NK117(she)001:23154: kyi sems rin po che spel ba'i thabs la nan
NK117(she)001:23158: khyad par ltung ba'i rab 'byed nyi shu ni //
NK117(she)001:23159: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog la sogs rgyal po'i lnga //
NK117(she)001:23160: grong dang grong rdal 'joms sogs blon po'i lnga //
NK117(she)001:23161: blo ma sbyangs la stong nyid ston pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:23162: phal pa'i brgyad dang smon 'jug gtong rnams spangs //
NK117(she)001:23163: zhes pa ni rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur
NK117(she)001:23164: ba zhes mi dpon du gyur nas chab 'bangs la
NK117(she)001:23166: mchod rten dang dge 'dun gyi rdzas yo byad sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:23167: dge 'dun spyi la 'bul rgyu'i ma phul ba 'phrog
NK117(she)001:23168: gam 'phrog tu 'jug pa ni ltung ba dang po'o
NK117(she)001:23169: // gang yang nyan thos kyi lam la dad nas der zhugs pa dag de las bzlog pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23170: theg pa chen po la dad nas der zhugs pa'ang de las bzlog pa ni gnyis pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23171: gang yang rab tu byung bar mos te rtags dang cho ga ldan min su yang rung ste /
NK117(she)001:23172: bslab pa bzung min dang tshul khrims 'chal min la ma ltos te /
NK117(she)001:23173: de'i zas gos nor sogs 'phrog pa nas srog la 'tshe ba'i bar gyi log sbyor dang /
NK117(she)001:23174: lus la chad pa dang gzhur brdegs byed pa sogs ni gsum pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23175: rgyal rigs su yang bsam bzhin du ma dang pha dang nyan thos dgra bcom pa gsod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23176: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23177: ched du bsams te sangs rgyas kyi sku dngos ma
NK117(she)001:23178: yin kyang sku gzugs kyi rnam pa gang yang rung
NK117(she)001:23179: ba la ngan sems kyis khrag 'byin pa ni de
NK117(she)001:23180: nyid bshig pa'i las byed pa sogs ni bzhi pa'o
NK117(she)001:23181: // rgyal rigs gang yang 'jig rten gyi bde sdug
NK117(she)001:23182: thams cad rgyu las byung bar mi 'dod cing phyi
NK117(she)001:23183: ma'i don la g.yel te rang dang gzhan rnams mi
NK117(she)001:23184: dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam yang dag pa la
NK117(she)001:23185: 'jug pa'i thabs la dkri bar byed pa ni lnga
NK117(she)001:23186: // pa'o // blon po su yang rung ste mchod
NK117(she)001:23187: rten dang dge 'dun gyi dang phyogs bzhi'i dge 'dun
NK117(she)001:23188: gyi rdzas 'phrog pa 'di ni dang po'o //
NK117(she)001:23192: yul 'khor 'joms par byed pa ni gnyis pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23193: yang blon pos nyan rang dang theg chen gyi gzhung
NK117(she)001:23194: la dad pa las bzlog ste spongs shing 'gog tu
NK117(she)001:23196: yang blon pos sangs rgyas kyi phyir rab tu byung
NK117(she)001:23197: ba su yang tshul khrims ldan min la ma ltos
NK117(she)001:23198: te / de'i gos ngur smrig 'phrog gam khyim du
NK117(she)001:23199: gnas par byed dam btson rar 'jug gam nor rdzas
NK117(she)001:23200: 'phrog cing srog dang bral ba'i bar du byed pa
NK117(she)001:23202: yang blon po mtshams med pa lnga'i las byed pa ni lnga pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23203: zhes grong gi khyim gcig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23204: ljongs ni mi rigs bzhi tshang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23205: grong khyer ni bzo sna bco brgyad yod pa /
NK117(she)001:23206: grong rdal ni tshong pa mang po 'du yul /
NK117(she)001:23207: yul 'khor ni yul che chung mang po 'dzom gnas so //
NK117(she)001:23209: stong pa nyid tshig lam du 'khrul nas skrag pa
NK117(she)001:23210: skye ba'i blo dman la'ang sgra ji bzhin par ston
NK117(she)001:23211: pa dang / theg chen gyi rigs lam der zhugs
NK117(she)001:23212: pa dag nyan thos kyi bcas pa gzugs can la
NK117(she)001:23213: bstod basngagasa brjod nas theg dman gyi sde snod la
NK117(she)001:23215: nyan thos kyi rigs can gdod nas theg chen gyi
NK117(she)001:23216: skal ba dman zhing so so thar pa la dga'
NK117(she)001:23217: ba dag theg chen la bstod cing basngagasa nas de
NK117(she)001:23218: nyid la btsan thabs kyis 'jug par byas pas gnyis
NK117(she)001:23219: ka ma yin par 'chos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23220: las dang po pa'i kun slong dman pa'i cha nas
NK117(she)001:23221: theg chen gyi bsam sbyor ma lobs pa yang nyan
NK117(she)001:23222: rang gi lam mi 'dod bzhin du 'dor du 'jug
NK117(she)001:23223: pa / rnyed pa dang bkur sti don du gnyer
NK117(she)001:23224: ba'i ched du bdag la bstod cing gzhan la phrag
NK117(she)001:23225: dog gi sgo nas smod pa dang gzhan gyis bdag
NK117(she)001:23226: 'gran zla med pa'i yon gnas su 'dzin du re
NK117(she)001:23227: nas lkog gyur gyi gnas rnams ma rtogs bzhin du
NK117(she)001:23228: rtogs so zhes mi chos bla ma'i rdzun gyis gzhan
NK117(she)001:23229: mgo bskor ba'i rigs dang rgyal po sogs dbang shed
NK117(she)001:23230: che ba'i rigs la bcar nas dge sbyong gi nor
NK117(she)001:23231: rdzas 'phrog cing brdeg btsog bgyid pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23232: mchog gsum gzhan gyi zhabs 'brings su gyur nas bkur
NK117(she)001:23233: sti dang rim gro byed pa ngag thabs sna tshogs
NK117(she)001:23234: kyis phrog nas rang phyogs la sbyar zhing dkor la
NK117(she)001:23235: ji mi snyam par longs spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23236: spong ba bsam gtan pa zhes sgom bsgrub la rtse
NK117(she)001:23237: gcig tu brtson pa dag gi bza' btung longs spyod
NK117(she)001:23238: las phris te thos bsam gyis rnam par g.yeng ba
NK117(she)001:23239: dang klog pa kha ton byed pa la ster zhing
NK117(she)001:23240: chos bzhin spyod pa'i rnal 'byor 'dor du 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:23241: dang brgyad do // de'i steng du nyan rang gi
NK117(she)001:23242: lam la blo phyogs te sems can thams cad kyi
NK117(she)001:23243: don du sangs rgyas bsgrub pa'i smon sems btang ba
NK117(she)001:23244: dang brgyad do // dang / rnam dkar gyi dge
NK117(she)001:23245: ba la mi sbyor ba la 'jug sems btang ba
NK117(she)001:23248: nag po'i chos bzhi ltung ba lnga gnyis brgyad zhes pa la /
NK117(she)001:23249: lnga lnga brgya zer ba gad mo'i gnas so //
NK117(she)001:23250: yan lag gi nyes byas brgyad cu ni bslab btus su blta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:23251: 'dir ni 'phags pa klu sgrub kyi rjes su 'brangs
NK117(she)001:23252: nas rgyud dag pa rnams las skye bar bzhed cing
NK117(she)001:23253: bsrung bya yang rtsa ltung nyi shu de bsrungs shing
NK117(she)001:23254: nyams na 'chos thabs kyang 'di bzhin te /
NK117(she)001:23256: mdor na rmi lam sdig pa mthong na yang //
NK117(she)001:23257: de ma thag tu phung po gsum pas bshags //
NK117(she)001:23258: rten gzhi smon sems shor dang 'gal zla byung //
NK117(she)001:23259: spong rkyen bslab pa phul ba gsum dag las //
NK117(she)001:23260: thun tshod las nyams shor na 'gyod sems kyis //
NK117(she)001:23261: skya rengs mdun du nam mkha'i snying po la //
NK117(she)001:23262: bos nas yan lag bdun pas ltung ba ldang //
NK117(she)001:23263: zhes pa ni mdor dril na rmi lam du sems
NK117(she)001:23264: bskyed nyams pa'i bsam sbyor la 'jug pa'i sdig pa'i
NK117(she)001:23265: las byed pa mthong na yang gnyid las sad pa'i
NK117(she)001:23266: de ma thag tu phung po gsum pas bshag dgos
NK117(she)001:23267: par gsungs pas na nyin par nyams na bshags pa
NK117(she)001:23269: byang chub kyi sems brten pa'i gzhi smon sems shor
NK117(she)001:23270: ba dang 'gal zla rtsa ltung bco brgyad po gang
NK117(she)001:23271: rung byung ba / spong ba'i rkyen gzhan don du
NK117(she)001:23272: sangs rgyas bsgrubs pas skyo zhing sun nas bslab pa
NK117(she)001:23273: phul zhing phyin chad rang don las gzhan don yal
NK117(she)001:23274: bar dor ba gsum gyis byang chub sems kyi bslab
NK117(she)001:23275: pa gtong bar bshad pa ltar nyin thun gsum mtshan
NK117(she)001:23276: thun gsum du bcad pa'i drug cha so so ma
NK117(she)001:23277: yol gong nas gnyen pos slebs na tshul khrims rgyun
NK117(she)001:23279: rang don las gzhan don du sangs rgyas bsgrub mi
NK117(she)001:23280: nus so snyam ma thag tu sems bskyed spangs pas
NK117(she)001:23281: thun tshod la ma ltos so //
NK117(she)001:23282: thun tshad las thal nas nyams par gyur pa dag
NK117(she)001:23283: nyes ltung 'chags pa kho na yid la byed bzhin
NK117(she)001:23284: 'gyod pa dang ldan pas tho rangs khar khrus dang
NK117(she)001:23285: gtsang sbra la gnas pas spos btul skya rengs kyi
NK117(she)001:23286: mdun du nam mkha'i snying po la bos nas yan
NK117(she)001:23287: lag bdun pa btang bas ltung ba las ldang bar
NK117(she)001:23288: 'gyur ro // byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa nyams
NK117(she)001:23289: pa bshags pa'i cho ga logs su bkod pa ltar
NK117(she)001:23290: lag len la thebs par bya ba gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:23291: byang chub sems dpa' bzang skyong dang dri ma med
NK117(she)001:23292: par grags pa la sogs khyim pa'i gzugs can du
NK117(she)001:23293: bstan nas de dag gi sde snod dang rjes su
NK117(she)001:23294: 'brel bar ji skad bstan pa bzhin du dbu ma'i
NK117(she)001:23295: lta ba yang dag par 'dzin pa slob dpon klu
NK117(she)001:23296: sgrub dang / rgyal sras zhi ba lhas srol gtod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23297: yang bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba yin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23298: rigs dang mi ldan pa dag gzugs can gyi sdom
NK117(she)001:23299: pas rgyud 'dul ba gtso bor byed pa'i ched du
NK117(she)001:23300: slob dpon thogs med sku mched kyis mdo sde'i rgyan
NK117(she)001:23301: las rab tu byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' mchog
NK117(she)001:23302: tu gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas sems tsam pa'i
NK117(she)001:23303: lta ba 'dzin pa'i lugs kyi sems bskyed pa gnyis
NK117(she)001:23306: yang na so sor thar pa'i bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23308: sems can kun la mnyam pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23310: mkhon 'dzin med pa rnam gsum gyis tshul khrims bsrung
NK117(she)001:23311: zhing srid pa'i rnam smin thams cad mi blta bar
NK117(she)001:23312: bsrung ngo // zhes gsungs pa'i don shes na phyogs lhung gi rnam rtog zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:23314: bdag bde gzhan la yang dag spo ba dang //
NK117(she)001:23315: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal bdag gis khur bzod pa'i //
NK117(she)001:23316: gtong len snying stobs rmad byung 'du byed cing //
NK117(she)001:23317: byang chub bar du mi 'bral phyi phyir smon //
NK117(she)001:23318: zhes pa ni de la smon 'jug las 'da' bar mi byed pa ni sems bzung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:23319: de yang bdag gi bde ba gzhan la spo ba
NK117(she)001:23320: dang gzhan gyi sdug bsngal khur bzod pa'i zhes pa
NK117(she)001:23321: ni rlung phyir dbyung ba'i tshe rang gi bde skyid
NK117(she)001:23322: dang gzhan gyi sdug bsngal rang gis len par bya'o
NK117(she)001:23323: // de ltar rang bde gzhan la gtong ba dang
NK117(she)001:23324: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal rang gis len pa'i snying stobs
NK117(she)001:23325: rmad du byung ba 'du bar byed cing /
NK117(she)001:23326: byang chub bar du byang chub kyi sems dang mi 'bral bar phyi phyir smon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23328: smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med bzhi po yang //
NK117(she)001:23329: byas pa drin du gzo las byams pa skye //
NK117(she)001:23330: byams las snying rje de las byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:23331: skye ba tshad ma'i lung gis yang dag 'grub //
NK117(she)001:23332: ces pa ni de yang byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa smon 'jug gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:23333: dang po smon pa'i bslab bya tshad med pa bzhi po la yang /
NK117(she)001:23334: mas dka' las chen pos srog bskyabs pa la sogs
NK117(she)001:23335: byas pa drin du gzo ba la bsams pas byams
NK117(she)001:23337: byams pas gnod 'tshe med kyang phan mi thogs pa
NK117(she)001:23338: la bsams te snying rje skye zhing de'i sna drangs
NK117(she)001:23339: nas dga' ba dang btang snyoms sogs rim bzhin skye
NK117(she)001:23340: zhing de las kyang byang chub kyi sems skye bar
NK117(she)001:23341: nges pa tshad ma'i lung gis yang dag par 'grub
NK117(she)001:23342: bo zhes pa'o // de yang b+ham ga la'i pan+di tas /
NK117(she)001:23348: brtse ba'i snying rje chen po /
NK117(she)001:23349: rang 'bras bla na med pa nyid de rgyu 'bras man ngag bdun ldan du bzhed do //
NK117(she)001:23351: btsas ma thag pa'i skyes bu bzhin ngan de //
NK117(she)001:23352: ma yi pang pas khrus khang ltar byas nas //
NK117(she)001:23353: mi gtsang mtha' dag lag pas nye reg byas //
NK117(she)001:23354: nu zhos bsnyen bkur lus kyi reg byas g.yogs //
NK117(she)001:23355: bu chung na las bdag nyid 'chi bar 'dams //
NK117(she)001:23356: sdig sdug gtam ngan mtha' dag bsran nus pa'i //
NK117(she)001:23357: drin dang rim gro khyad du gsod byed na //
NK117(she)001:23358: de las cho ga 'khrugs pa su zhig yod //
NK117(she)001:23359: ces pa ni de ltar ma byas res kyi btsas
NK117(she)001:23360: ma thag pa'i sems can nyam chung ba de tsham
NK117(she)001:23362: pang pas ni khrus khang ltar byas /
NK117(she)001:23363: mi gtsang ba thams cad lag pas phyis /
NK117(she)001:23365: sha drod la bcangs nas grang reg sogs skyob par byas so //
NK117(she)001:23366: brtse sems kyis rang srog las gces par byas shing /
NK117(she)001:23368: bu'i don du sdig pa dang sdug bsngal dang gtam
NK117(she)001:23369: ngan mtha' dag bzod nus pa'i drin dang rim gro
NK117(she)001:23370: khyad du gsod par byed na bzang lan ngan gyis
NK117(she)001:23371: 'jal ba ste / de las cho ga 'khrugs pa
NK117(she)001:23372: zhes lag len nor ba su zhig yod ces med
NK117(she)001:23373: 'jal ba ste / par bstan pa'o // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:23374: sa 'di rir bcas bdag gi khur ma yin //
NK117(she)001:23375: byas pa mi gzo'i khur chen dug ldan gyi //
NK117(she)001:23376: bza' ba khong du chud pa'i skye bo bzhin //
NK117(she)001:23377: zhes pa ni sa 'di ri dang bcas pa bdag gi khur dgos pa ma yin kyang /
NK117(she)001:23378: ma'i drin lan khyad gsod lta bu'i byas pa mi
NK117(she)001:23379: gzo ba'i drin lan log 'jal ni khur du shin
NK117(she)001:23380: tu lci ste dper na 'chi nges kyi bza' ba
NK117(she)001:23381: dug can khong du chud pa'i skye bo bzhin no
NK117(she)001:23383: de phyir pha mtha' yas pa'i sems can kun //
NK117(she)001:23384: ma ru gyur nas phan btags dam pa'i drin //
NK117(she)001:23385: dran pas byams sogs bzhi po gong 'phel zhing //
NK117(she)001:23386: byas pa shes dang drin du gzo ba yi //
NK117(she)001:23387: skyes bu gang la 'phags pa'i nor gyis bsnyen //
NK117(she)001:23388: zhes pa ni 'di ltar pha mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK117(she)001:23389: can kun te nam mkha' la mtha' med pa ltar
NK117(she)001:23390: sems can la mtha' med pas na /
NK117(she)001:23391: de dag thams cad ma ru ma gyur pa gcig
NK117(she)001:23392: kyang med cing de ltar ma bur gyur nas phan
NK117(she)001:23393: dpag med btags pa la dam pa'i ste de lta
NK117(she)001:23394: bu'i drin de ma dran na mi rung bas /
NK117(she)001:23395: dran pas byams sogs tshad med bzhi po gong 'phel
NK117(she)001:23396: du 'gyur zhing byas pa shes pa dang phan btags
NK117(she)001:23397: pa la drin du gzo ba sogs phan 'dogs la
NK117(she)001:23398: brtson pa'i skyes bu gang su zhig kyang de nyid
NK117(she)001:23399: la 'phags pa'i nor gyis bsnyen zhes pa 'phags pa'i
NK117(she)001:23400: nor bdun gyis rim gyis phyug pa 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:23403: smon sems ston ka'i zla ba lta bu la //
NK117(she)001:23404: sgra gcan gdong bas thu ba'i mi mthun phyogs //
NK117(she)001:23405: nag po'i chos bzhi ring du bskrad par bya //
NK117(she)001:23406: zhes pa ni de yang smon sems ston ka'i zla
NK117(she)001:23407: ba lta bu 'gal zla sgra gcan gyi gdong pa
NK117(she)001:23408: bas thu ba'i gzhan phan sems bskyed kyi mi mthun
NK117(she)001:23409: phyogs ni nag po'i chos bzhi bya ba'i kha na
NK117(she)001:23410: ma tho ba'i sdig sems bzhi yin pas de dag
NK117(she)001:23411: nye bar mi len bzhin ring du bskrad par bya'o
NK117(she)001:23412: // mtshan nyid theg pa ni sngags lam la ltos na drang don yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:23413: mdo las rang sangs rgyas mang po theg chen la
NK117(she)001:23414: zhugs kyang sa brgyad thob nas phyir log par gsungs
NK117(she)001:23416: mchod 'os bslu dang gzhan gyi bsod nams la //
NK117(she)001:23417: the tshom bskyed nas 'gyod pa'i gnas la sbyar //
NK117(she)001:23418: dam pa rnams la bskur zhing mi snyan sgrog /
NK117(she)001:23419: g.yo dang sgyus spyod gzhan dag mgo bo bskor //
NK117(she)001:23420: chos bzhi gang rung nyams myong smon sems shor //
NK117(she)001:23421: 'gyod dang gnyen pos ma slebs thun tshod 'das //
NK117(she)001:23422: de yi mod la sems bskyed 'chor ba yin //
NK117(she)001:23423: zhes pa ni de yang mchod 'os bla ma dang /
NK117(she)001:23426: sbyin gnas yon tan ldan pa dag mgo bo bskor ba'o //
NK117(she)001:23427: gang zag 'du bar spyod pa dang byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:23428: bskyed 'dzin pa dang zab mo'i don sgom pa dang
NK117(she)001:23429: / bskyed rdzogs bzlas brjod la zhugs /
NK117(she)001:23430: thar pa dang bsod nams cha mthun gyi las la
NK117(she)001:23431: brtson pa la 'gyod pa bskyed du gzhug pa dang
NK117(she)001:23432: / mchod sbyin dang phyag skor sogs la smad de
NK117(she)001:23433: 'jig rten gyi tshong so nam sogs la bstod basngagasa
NK117(she)001:23434: brjod nas the tshom bskyed du 'jug pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23435: bskur 'debs kyi yul sems bskyed zhu yul sogs yin
NK117(she)001:23436: la mi snyan sgrog pa ni 'dis mi dge ba
NK117(she)001:23437: 'di dang 'di spyod do zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:23438: g.yo ni rang gi nyes pa thabs kyis mi mngon
NK117(she)001:23439: par byed pa dang sgyu ni rang la yon tan
NK117(she)001:23440: med bzhin du yod bardzu byed cing de gnyis 'brel
NK117(she)001:23441: bas gzhan dag mgo bo bskor ba dang bre srang
NK117(she)001:23442: sogs la g.yo sgyu byed pa yang de dang mtshungs
NK117(she)001:23443: so // de lta bu'i chos bzhi po gang rung
NK117(she)001:23444: nyams su myong bar byas pa'i mod la smon sems
NK117(she)001:23445: shor ba yin la der 'gyod sems dang gnyen pos
NK117(she)001:23446: ma slebs par thun tshod 'das na de'i mod la
NK117(she)001:23447: zhes de ma thag tu sems bskyed 'chor ba yin
NK117(she)001:23449: gnyen por che ba dkar po'i chos bzhi ni //
NK117(she)001:23450: srog la bab kyang bsam bzhin brdzun mi smra //
NK117(she)001:23451: rgyal sras rnams la ston par gus shing basngagasa //
NK117(she)001:23452: g.yo sgyu med pas sems can thams cad gnyer //
NK117(she)001:23453: mtha' dag byang chub lam la dkri ba'o //
NK117(she)001:23454: zhes pa ni sems can su la'ang shes bzhin du rdzun mi smra ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23455: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la sangs rgyas kyi
NK117(she)001:23456: 'du shes bskyed dgos par gsungs pa ji bzhin shes
NK117(she)001:23457: dka' yang rigs sad pa'i rtags su yang dag pa'i
NK117(she)001:23458: lta ba la gnas shing gzhan don kho na brtson
NK117(she)001:23459: pa gzhan gyis bsgyur du med pa'i lhag bsam can
NK117(she)001:23460: dang / gzhan yang shan pa dang smad 'tshong ma
NK117(she)001:23461: dang dud 'gro sogs lus rten mchog dman la ma
NK117(she)001:23462: ltos par byang chub sems dpa'i rigs yod pa gang
NK117(she)001:23463: la gang 'dul gyi ched yin pas 'gro ba su
NK117(she)001:23464: la'ang bsam sbyor gang thad nas gnod 'tshe med bzhin
NK117(she)001:23465: dag snang sbyang dgos pa yang gnad kyi dam pa'o
NK117(she)001:23467: sems can rnams la phan 'dod kyi lhag bsam dang
NK117(she)001:23468: ldan pa ni rang skyon sbed pa'i g.yo dang gzhan
NK117(she)001:23469: mgo bskor ba'i sgyu med pa'i bsam sbyor drang po
NK117(she)001:23470: la spyod pa'o // bzhi pa ni /
NK117(she)001:23471: rang gi nus pa'i tshod dang bstun te sems can
NK117(she)001:23472: rnams rmongs pa'i dbang gis rang don la basngagasa shing
NK117(she)001:23473: gzhan don la g.yel ba dag blo mthu bskyed de
NK117(she)001:23474: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa la bskul bar
NK117(she)001:23475: bya'o // de'i mi mthun phyogs ni bzhi yin te /
NK117(she)001:23476: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK117(she)001:23477: rnyed dang bkur stir chags pa yi //
NK117(she)001:23478: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:23479: sdug bsngal mgon med gyur pa la //
NK117(she)001:23480: ser snas chos nor mi ster dang //
NK117(she)001:23481: gzhan gyis bshags kyang mi nyan par //
NK117(she)001:23482: khro bas gzhan la 'tshog pa dang //
NK117(she)001:23483: theg pa chen po spong byed cing //
NK117(she)001:23485: khyad par nag po'i chos bzhi la yan lag bzhi tshang na kun dkris chen po yin te /
NK117(she)001:23486: nyes spyod gang yin pa de rgyun du spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23487: de la ngo tsha dang khrel med pa /
NK117(she)001:23488: mgu zhing dga' bar byed pa de'i nyes dmigs la
NK117(she)001:23489: mi 'gyod pa'i steng du yon tan du blta ba
NK117(she)001:23490: ste yan lag bzhi tshang na kun dkris chen po
NK117(she)001:23491: / khrel dang ngo tsha skyes nas gzhan gyis ldog tu rung ba kun dkris 'bring /
NK117(she)001:23492: yan lag re re'ang gzhan la ma ltos par rang gis ldog pa chung ngu'o //
NK117(she)001:23493: de la zag pa dang kun dkris ni gcig yin te /
NK117(she)001:23494: de 'bring gis spyad pas pham 'dra'am pham par yang
NK117(she)001:23495: bshad pas gang zag gsum yan chad la bshags dgos
NK117(she)001:23496: shing chung ngus spyad pa'i rtsa ltung dang gzhan nyes
NK117(she)001:23497: byas phra ba rnams ni gang zag gcig gi drung
NK117(she)001:23498: du nyes byas brjod nas bshags par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:23499: bshags yul ma rnyed na rgyal ba sras bcas dmigs pa'i yul du byas la bshags shing bsdams pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23501: brtan bya'i sgo nas bsrung ba'i 'du shes bzhi //
NK117(she)001:23502: dge ba'i bshes la sangs rgyas 'du shes dang //
NK117(she)001:23503: des bstan chos la lam gyi 'du shes dang //
NK117(she)001:23504: de sgrub rnams la grogs kyi 'du shes dang //
NK117(she)001:23505: sems can kun la bu gcig 'du shes te //
NK117(she)001:23506: 'di dag smon pa'i bslab bya yang dag go //
NK117(she)001:23507: zhes pa ni byang chub smon pa'i sems bskyed pa
NK117(she)001:23508: brtan par bya ba'i sgo nas bsrung ba'i 'du shes
NK117(she)001:23509: bzhi yod de / dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes dang /
NK117(she)001:23510: des bstan pa'i chos la lam gyi 'du shes dang /
NK117(she)001:23511: de sgrub par byed pa rnams la grogs kyi 'du shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23512: sems can thams cad kun la bu gcig po'i 'du
NK117(she)001:23513: shes te 'di dag bzhi po ni smon pa'i bslab
NK117(she)001:23516: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug las //
NK117(she)001:23517: dang po lnga ni bsod nams dam pa'i tshogs //
NK117(she)001:23518: phyi ma gcig ni ye shes tshogs chen te //
NK117(she)001:23519: gnyis la ma bsten sangs rgyas yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:23520: thabs stobs smon lam ye shes bsnan pas bcu //
NK117(she)001:23521: zhes pa ni 'di ltar phar phyin drug po ni dge ba chos sdud dang /
NK117(she)001:23522: khyim gnas la bzod pa gtong ba tshul khrims so //
NK117(she)001:23523: tshul khrims ni dge bsnyen te sdig pa las ldog pa'i don to //
NK117(she)001:23524: dge sdud kyi gtso bo ni sdom dang des pa ste bsam gtan la sogs lhag bsam rnams so //
NK117(she)001:23525: spang bya sgrib pa'i gnyen por ltos nas bcur phye ba ste /
NK117(she)001:23526: ser sna 'chal tshul khong khro le lo rnam g.yeng shes 'chal thabs rmongs pa stobs la sgrib pa /
NK117(she)001:23527: smon don mi 'grub pa shes sgrib dang bcu'o //
NK117(she)001:23528: drug ltar na sbyin sogs lnga po bsod nams dang shes rab ni ye shes kyi tshogs so //
NK117(she)001:23529: de la theg pa chen po pas bsgrub bya ni
NK117(she)001:23530: de kho na nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis 'khor
NK117(she)001:23531: ba la mi gnas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23532: snying rje chen po dang 'brel ba'i thabs kyis myang
NK117(she)001:23533: 'das la mi gnas pa ste mi gnas pa'i mya
NK117(she)001:23536: blo stobs mthu yis sgrub byed rgyal sras gsum //
NK117(she)001:23537: rang don sngon byas 'gro ba sgrol 'dod pa //
NK117(she)001:23538: rgyal po lta bu'i 'dod chen sems bskyed dang //
NK117(she)001:23539: rang dang 'gro ba stabs cig sgrol 'dod pa //
NK117(she)001:23540: gru pa lta bu ye shes dam pa'i sems //
NK117(she)001:23541: 'gro ba sngon bsgral rjes la zhi 'dod pa //
NK117(she)001:23542: skyong byed lta bu'i dpe med sems bskyed de //
NK117(she)001:23543: rtul pos grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:23544: 'bring pos bdun dang rnon pos gsum na grol //
NK117(she)001:23545: zhes blo stobs chung ngu dang 'bring dang chen po
NK117(she)001:23546: gsum gyi rang rang gi mthus bsgrub par byed pa
NK117(she)001:23547: rgyal sras rnam pa gsum ni /
NK117(she)001:23548: dbang po rtul po rang don sngon du byas nas
NK117(she)001:23549: slar 'gro ba rnams sgrol bar 'dod pa rgyal po
NK117(she)001:23550: lta bu'i 'dod chen sems bskyed dang /
NK117(she)001:23551: rang dang 'gro ba stabs gcig tu sgrol ba ste
NK117(she)001:23552: sangs rgyas par 'dod pa gru pa dang mgron po
NK117(she)001:23553: mnyam du chu'i phar khar phyin pa lta bu ye
NK117(she)001:23554: shes dam pa'i sems zhes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23555: 'gro ba rnams sngon du bsgral ba ste sems can
NK117(she)001:23556: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi sa la ma bkod par
NK117(she)001:23557: rang don mi bsgrub cing rjes su rang nyid zhi
NK117(she)001:23558: bar 'dod pa skyong byed lta bu ni dpe med
NK117(she)001:23560: rtul po sngon du rang nyid sangs rgyas par byas
NK117(she)001:23561: nas rjes su sems can gyi don byed 'dod pas
NK117(she)001:23562: ni bskal pa grangs med sum cu rtsa gsum dang
NK117(she)001:23563: / 'bring pos rang gzhan gnyis mnyam du sangs rgya
NK117(she)001:23564: bar 'dod nas dam chos bsgrubs pas kyang grangs med
NK117(she)001:23565: / bdun / chen pos sems can thams cad sangs
NK117(she)001:23566: rgyas kyi sa la ma bkod par rang don mi
NK117(she)001:23567: gnyer ba grangs med gsum nas sangs rgyas par gsungs
NK117(she)001:23568: pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas bslab bya
NK117(she)001:23569: la bslab shing nus pa rdzogs kyang /
NK117(she)001:23570: sa bcu'i sems dpa'i tshul gyis 'gro don mdzad pa
NK117(she)001:23571: la 'khor ba ji srid bar sangs mi rgya ba
NK117(she)001:23572: rigs gsum mgon po lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:23573: 'dir 'dul ba dang sngags kyi lam ni sngon la
NK117(she)001:23574: sdom pa bzung nas gdod bslab bya mnyam du rung
NK117(she)001:23575: la byang chub sems dpa'i lam ni sngon du bslab
NK117(she)001:23576: bya shes par byas nas dad cing bsgrub nus pa'i
NK117(she)001:23577: tshe bslab bya yang dag par blang zhes gsungs so
NK117(she)001:23578: // sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa'i mtshan nyid ston pa ni /
NK117(she)001:23580: sbyin pa'i ngo bo chags pa med pa ste //
NK117(she)001:23581: dbye na chos dang zang zing mi 'jigs gsum //
NK117(she)001:23582: zang zing la'ang rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK117(she)001:23583: gtong dang gtong ba che dang shin tu gtong //
NK117(she)001:23584: gtong ba zhes bya zas gos shing rta dang //
NK117(she)001:23585: glang po yul khams gzhan la byin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23586: gtong ba chen po bu dag bu mo dang //
NK117(she)001:23587: khyim thab gtong yin shin tu gtong ba ni //
NK117(she)001:23588: bya daka'i gnas te mgo dang yan lag gtong //
NK117(she)001:23589: zhes pa ni de la sbyin pa'i ngo bo ni
NK117(she)001:23590: chags dang bral ba ste rang gi longs spyod la
NK117(she)001:23591: zhen cing chags pa'i gnyen po'o //
NK117(she)001:23592: dbye na chos dang zang zing dang mi 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23593: de yang sngon khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi
NK117(she)001:23594: sbyin pa la 'gran btsal ba zhig gis de'i do
NK117(she)001:23596: zas nor gang yod spangs nas rab 'byung byas pas
NK117(she)001:23597: ston pas mgon med zas sbyin las lhag par lung
NK117(she)001:23599: ko sa la'i rgyal pos dge sbyong bzhi la zan dron gcig sbyin pas rgyal srid thob pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23600: tshong dpon zil gyis mi non pa slong ba pos bslangs tshe med ces zer mi nus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23601: rang khyim nas gzhan gyis brkus na'ang dga' ba sgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23602: de nyid dbul por gyur tshe r+ts+wa 'tshong byas pa'i rin sbyin par gtong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23603: shi bi'i rgyal pos gtan pa med pa'i sbyin gtong
NK117(she)001:23604: gi khang bu brtsigs nas mchod sbyin la 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:23606: rtsa bar chos sngon du byas kyang 'dir gzhan gnyis
NK117(she)001:23607: sngon du byas pa la dang po zang zing la
NK117(she)001:23608: gtong ba dang / gtong ba chen po dang /
NK117(she)001:23610: de la gtong dang zhes zas gos che chung nor rdzas rta glang gi bar sbyin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23612: bu pho bu mo khyim thab slong na byin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23613: de yang rgyal po thams cad sgrol la phrag dog
NK117(she)001:23614: gi sgo nas rgyal po gzhan gyis g.yo sgyu kho
