NK117(she)001:23615: nas thams cad sgrol gyi bu bu mo mchis brang
NK117(she)001:23616: bcas bslangs pas de dag la yid shin tu gcugs
NK117(she)001:23617: pa'i sdug bsngal gyi tshor bas snying 'gas pa ltar
NK117(she)001:23618: du gyur na'ang gtong sems las ldog pa med pa'i
NK117(she)001:23619: sems kyis byin pa ltar bdag cag gis mchod sbyin
NK117(she)001:23620: byed tshe snying las dang 'jungs sems la khrel brtas
NK117(she)001:23621: nas dam bca' ba la goms par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:23622: shin tu gtong ba ni bya dka' ba'i gnas te /
NK117(she)001:23623: mgo dang mig dang lag pa dang rkang pa la sogs pa gtong ba'o //
NK117(she)001:23624: de yang bdag cag gi ston pa sa spyod dpal
NK117(she)001:23625: gyi sder gyur tshe rked skabs man chad chad pa'i
NK117(she)001:23626: slong ba po la sog le rnon pos rang gi
NK117(she)001:23627: rked pa 'breg tu bcug nas byin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23628: rgyal po zla 'od du gyur tshe bram ze drag
NK117(she)001:23629: po'i mig la mgo bcad nas byin pa la sogs
NK117(she)001:23630: la bsams nas sbyin pa la brtson 'tshal lo //
NK117(she)001:23632: 'di na thog mar goms su 'jug pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:23633: ser snas bsdams pa'i skyes bu'i lag pa ni //
NK117(she)001:23634: gcig nas gcig shos sbyin par bsam pa'i sems //
NK117(she)001:23635: yang yang spos pas tshod ma la sogs la //
NK117(she)001:23636: brkam chags 'jig pa stobs su gyur la bslab //
NK117(she)001:23637: ces pa ni de la thog ma nas ser snas
NK117(she)001:23638: 'ching ba dag ni sngon khyim bdag 'jur gegs can
NK117(she)001:23639: zhig la rang gi lag pa gcig tu dngos po
NK117(she)001:23640: cung zad cig bzung ba gcig shos slong ba po
NK117(she)001:23641: yin 'dun gyis de la sbyin tshul yang yang bslabs
NK117(she)001:23642: mthar sbyin pa rgya chen gtong nus pa byung ba
NK117(she)001:23643: ltar bdag nyid kyang tshod ma la sogs dngos po
NK117(she)001:23644: chung ngu sbyin pa la goms su bcug pas brkam
NK117(she)001:23645: chags 'jig pa stobs su gyur pa la bslab dgos
NK117(she)001:23648: mi 'jigs sbyin pa gzhan gyi srog bsrung dang //
NK117(she)001:23649: 'jigs pa'i yul bsgral dbugs 'byin gnas la dgod //
NK117(she)001:23650: ces pa ni de la mi 'jigs pa'i ngo bo
NK117(she)001:23651: ni 'jigs pas skrag cing rtabs par gyur pa rnams
NK117(she)001:23652: dbugs 'byin chen po'i gnas la sbyar ba ste 'jigs
NK117(she)001:23653: pa med pa'i sar bsgral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:23654: de bas byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis gtong ba
NK117(she)001:23655: dang thabs la mkhas pa dang rang gi zho sha
NK117(she)001:23656: las su 'khor bar byas nas gzhan la mi 'jigs
NK117(she)001:23657: pa sbyin pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:23659: mi nus bzhin du bab col cho ga yi //
NK117(she)001:23660: rnam par sbyar ba'i sbyin pa'ang smad pa ste //
NK117(she)001:23661: snying rje'i bsam pa shin tu ma dag par //
NK117(she)001:23662: lus dang srog gtong bslab btus nyid las bkag /
NK117(she)001:23663: ces pa ni de yang yar mchod mar sbyin spyi
NK117(she)001:23664: dang khyad par lus ril po'i cha shas snying thag
NK117(she)001:23665: pa nas gtong mi nus bzhin du bab col cho
NK117(she)001:23666: ga yi zhes pa chos brgyad kyi kun slong ngan
NK117(she)001:23667: pas gzhan gyis bstod basngagasa dang grags pa don du
NK117(she)001:23668: gnyer nas sbyin gtong gi rnam par sbyar ba'i sbyin
NK117(she)001:23669: pa'ang rnam smin dman pa'i phyir smad pa ste /
NK117(she)001:23670: de'i phyir na snying rje'i bsam pa shin tu ma
NK117(she)001:23671: dag gi bar du lus srog gtong ba'ang bslab btus
NK117(she)001:23672: nyid las bkag pa'i don ni /
NK117(she)001:23673: gtong ba chen po dang shin tu gtong ba ni
NK117(she)001:23674: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa dag
NK117(she)001:23677: kha na ma thos bskrun pa'i sbyin pa yang //
NK117(she)001:23678: gnas min smad pa'i gnas te bdog pa la //
NK117(she)001:23679: zhen pa btang ba sbyin pa'i tshad du bzhed //
NK117(she)001:23680: ces pa ni de la kha na ma thos bskrun
NK117(she)001:23681: pa'i sbyin pa ni gtong ba po'i sgo gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:23682: bsam sbyor ma dag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23683: sbyin rgyu'i rdzas rku 'phrog bcom gsum gyis thob pa'i nor rdzas sam /
NK117(she)001:23684: gzhan gyi srog 'phrog nus pa'i mtshon cha rdzas la
NK117(she)001:23685: sogs pa dang sha chang yang mi phan zhing gnod
NK117(she)001:23687: dbul phongs bor nas che btsan phyug sogs 'dzom pa
NK117(she)001:23688: la ster ba sogs ni gnas min smad pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:23690: de las rang nyid la zas nor che chung gang
NK117(she)001:23691: bdog pa de yis chog shes pa skyes nas zhen
NK117(she)001:23692: pa btang ba yang mchod pa dang sbyin pa'i tshad
NK117(she)001:23693: du bzhed pa'o // de ltar zang zing dang mi
NK117(she)001:23694: 'jigs pa'i sbyin pa chos sbyin gyi sngon 'gror song
NK117(she)001:23695: nas chos sbyin la 'jug pa ni /
NK117(she)001:23697: chos kyi sbyin pa rnam pa gsum las dngos //
NK117(she)001:23698: mos pas spyod pa ji bzhin 'doms par dka' //
NK117(she)001:23699: rang gi nyon mongs bsal ba'i cho ga dang //
NK117(she)001:23700: byams dang snying rjes gsung rab bklag pa yis //
NK117(she)001:23701: dkar po'i phyogs kyi rgyud grol smon lam gdab /
NK117(she)001:23702: rang rgyud grol nas 'gro ba'i skal ba dang //
NK117(she)001:23703: rang bzhin 'tshams pas gzhan don gtso bor bya //
NK117(she)001:23704: zhes pa ni de la chos kyi sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK117(she)001:23705: snag smyug dang glegs bam sbyin pa chung ngu /
NK117(she)001:23706: rang skal dang 'tshams pa'i nyan rang dang theg chen gyi chos ston pa 'bring /
NK117(she)001:23707: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos ston pa chen po'o //
NK117(she)001:23708: de yang mos pas spyod pa rnams gzhan la chos
NK117(she)001:23709: ston du re ba long ba'i lam sna long bas
NK117(she)001:23710: khrid pa ltar yin pas ji bzhin 'doms par dka'
NK117(she)001:23711: na / de las rang gi nyon mongs bsal ba'i
NK117(she)001:23712: cho ga dug gsum gyi kun rtog la gnyen po
NK117(she)001:23713: spyi dang bye brag pa bstan zhing byams dang snying
NK117(she)001:23714: rjes 'gro rnams blos mi gtong bzhin du rgyal ba'i
NK117(she)001:23715: gsung rab bklags pa sogs kyis dkar po'i phyogs kyi
NK117(she)001:23716: rang rgyud grol ba'i smon lam gdab pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23717: rang rgyud grol nas 'gro ba'i skal ba dang rang
NK117(she)001:23718: bzhin 'tshams pas gang la gang 'dul gyis gzhan don
NK117(she)001:23720: de yang rab tu byung ba dag gis nor rdzas
NK117(she)001:23721: sogs btsal zhing bsags pa'i dngos pos sbyin pa don
NK117(she)001:23722: du gnyer ba ma yin mod kyang /
NK117(she)001:23723: sngon gyi sbyin 'bras kyi rang bzhin du nor rdzas
NK117(she)001:23724: sogs byung ba mchod sbyin byed du mi rung ba
NK117(she)001:23726: gang gi phyir na sngon mgon po klu sgrub kyis
NK117(she)001:23727: dge 'dun mang po la 'tsho ba sbyar ba dang
NK117(she)001:23728: / slob dpon dpa' bos sngon gyi bsod nams kyis
NK117(she)001:23729: nyin rer bsod nams rgya chen po rnyed pa dge
NK117(she)001:23730: 'dun thams cad kyi 'tsho bar sbyor ba bzhin no
NK117(she)001:23731: / // de ltar sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin
NK117(she)001:23732: pa de thams cad kyang dam pa drug ldan du
NK117(she)001:23734: kun slong byang chub kyi sems la brten pa ni rten dam pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23735: spyi dang bye brag gi sbyin pa gang yin kyang
NK117(she)001:23736: de'i bsam pa ma dor ba dngos po dam pa
NK117(she)001:23737: dang / sems can thams cad la 'phral phugs kun
NK117(she)001:23738: tu phan pa'i phyir gtong ba ni ched du bya
NK117(she)001:23739: dang / ba dam pa / rnam par mi rtog
NK117(she)001:23740: pa'i ye shes kyis zin pa ni thabs la mkhas
NK117(she)001:23741: dang / ba dam pa / pa dam pa /
NK117(she)001:23742: sbyin pa btang ba'i dge ba rdzogs byang du bsngo
NK117(she)001:23743: ba'i bsngo ba dam pas zin pa /
NK117(she)001:23744: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gnyis 'gog pa'i rnam par dag par dam pas zin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23745: des na mthon po'i sbyin pa la slob tshul rnams
NK117(she)001:23746: ni re zhig smon pa'i yul du byas nas lus
NK117(she)001:23747: dang longs spyod bdog pa thams cad la phangs sems
NK117(she)001:23748: dang dman dang 'tshe sems cung zad tsam med par
NK117(she)001:23749: gtong sems rgya chen po dang 'brel ba'i byang chub
NK117(she)001:23750: thob pa'i smon lam gdab pa ni gtong ba thams
NK117(she)001:23753: tshul khrims ngo bo mi mthun sdom pa ste //
NK117(she)001:23754: dbye na nyes spyod sdom dang dge chos sdud //
NK117(she)001:23755: sems can don byed rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NK117(she)001:23756: sgo gsum mi dge sdom pa nyes spyod sdom //
NK117(she)001:23757: pha rol phyin pa drug ldan dge chos sdud //
NK117(she)001:23758: gzhan la phan gdags sems can don byed yin //
NK117(she)001:23759: zhes pa ni de la sgo gsum gyi spang bya
NK117(she)001:23760: thams cad bsdams nas gzhan gnod gzhi bcas la spong
NK117(she)001:23761: sems brtan pa ni tshul khrims kyi ngo bo yin
NK117(she)001:23762: no // dbye na nyes spyod sdom pa ni spyir mi dge ba bcu spang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23763: bye brag lus ngag gi las bdun spang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:23764: dge ba chos sdud ni phyin drug la sogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:23765: dge ba'i las bslab bya khyad chos bzhi dang ldan
NK117(she)001:23767: de bzhi ni rang rang gi mi mthun phyogs dang bral ba /
NK117(she)001:23768: 'khor gsum rnam par mi rtog pa'i shes rab kyis
NK117(she)001:23769: zin pa gzhan gyi 'dod don rdzogs par byed pa
NK117(she)001:23770: / 'bras bus gdul bya byang chub gsum du smin par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23771: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims ni pha rol
NK117(she)001:23772: tu phyin pa drug ka'i ngo bor gnas pas kun
NK117(she)001:23773: kyang rang rgyud la ma skyes pa bskyed cing /
NK117(she)001:23774: skyes pa gong nas gong du 'phel bar byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23775: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK117(she)001:23776: dngos sam brgyud nas gzhan gyi don la rnam pa
NK117(she)001:23777: thams cad du 'jug pa'i sems mtshungs ldan dang bcas
NK117(she)001:23778: pa'o // de la thog mar zang zing gi sbyin
NK117(she)001:23779: pas 'gro rnams legs par bsdus nas snyan par smra
NK117(she)001:23780: ba'i gtam gyis gdul bya'i yid drangs shing chos la
NK117(she)001:23782: de ltar gzhan dag thabs gang gis lam la 'dzud
NK117(she)001:23783: pa'i don mthun pa la bdag nyid kyang gnas dgos
NK117(she)001:23784: so // de yang sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis ni mi dge ba las sems bsrung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23785: dge ba'i chos sdud ni dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon par bsgrub pa yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:23786: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims kyis ni gzhan la phan pa lhur byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23788: nang gses so sor thar las byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:23789: khyad par bzhi yi sgo nas 'phags pa ste //
NK117(she)001:23790: so thar gzhan gnod gzhi bcas ldog pa tsam //
NK117(she)001:23791: byang sems de yi steng du phan 'dogs bsnon //
NK117(she)001:23792: so thar spang ba bdun bsdus lus ngag gtso //
NK117(she)001:23793: byang sems spang ba bcu ka gtso bor byed //
NK117(she)001:23794: ces pa ni de la so thar gyi bcas pa
NK117(she)001:23795: rnams byang sems kyi sdom ldan dag gi bslab bya'i
NK117(she)001:23797: byang sems ma yin pa'i rab byung rnams la bslab
NK117(she)001:23798: bya bsnon pa'i tshul gyis 'phags chos su bsgrub pa
NK117(she)001:23799: ste / 'di ltar so thar ni rang rgyud kyi
NK117(she)001:23800: nyes spyod sdom pas gzhan gnod gzhi bcas las ldog
NK117(she)001:23801: ste / pa tsam dang / byang sems ni gzhan
NK117(she)001:23802: la mi 'tshe ba'i steng du phan 'dogs pa yang
NK117(she)001:23803: ste / pa tsam dang / bsnon pa ste / nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK117(she)001:23805: sems can don byed gsum ka dang ldan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23806: so thar ni lus kyi gsum ngag gi bzhi ste spangs pa bdun gtsor byed la /
NK117(she)001:23807: byang sems ni kun slong dang bcas pa'i spang ba bcu ka gtso bor byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23809: khyad par bslab pa'i gnas ni so thar skabs //
NK117(she)001:23810: gzhan gyi don du bcas pa mi 'dral la //
NK117(she)001:23811: byang chub sems dpa' gzhan gyi don 'gyur na //
NK117(she)001:23812: lus ngag gnyis kyi mi dge rnam pa bdun //
NK117(she)001:23813: gzhan don 'gyur dang 'gyur bar shes pa dang //
NK117(she)001:23814: rang gi dge tshogs mi sgrib 'phel ba yi //
NK117(she)001:23815: gnas skabs gsum brtags gnang ba'i skabs yod do //
NK117(she)001:23816: sems stobs chen pos mi nag mdung thung can //
NK117(she)001:23817: bram ze'i khye'u skar ma dper mtshon nas //
NK117(she)001:23818: rnam pa'i nyes pa'ang don la dge ba yin //
NK117(she)001:23819: rgyu 'bras mthu can bsam pas byas pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:23820: yid kyi gsum la gnang ba'i skabs med do //
NK117(she)001:23821: zhes pa ni de yang so thar ni gzhan don du 'gyur yang bcas pa mi 'dral la /
NK117(she)001:23822: byang sems ni gzhan don du 'gyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23824: rang gi dge ba gong 'phel dang gsum brtags nas
NK117(she)001:23825: gnang ba'i skabs yod kyang lus ngag gi mi dge
NK117(she)001:23826: ba bdun po las yid kyi gsum ni nam yang
NK117(she)001:23827: spyod du chog par ma gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:23828: lus ngag gi mi dge ba bdun ji ltar gnang na /
NK117(she)001:23829: tshong pa mang po'i srog skyob pa'i phyir ded dpon
NK117(she)001:23830: snying rje chen pos mi nag mdung thung can bsad
NK117(she)001:23831: pa lta bu ni gzhan phan kho nas dang du
NK117(she)001:23832: blangs pa dang / longs spyod 'byor pa phun sum
NK117(she)001:23833: tshogs kyang mchod sbyin mi nus pa la brkus shing
NK117(she)001:23834: phrogs nas bkres pas nyam thag pa la sbyin pa
NK117(she)001:23835: blangs pa dang / dang / bram ze khye'u skar
NK117(she)001:23836: ma la dga' ba lo brgyad khri nyis stong la
NK117(she)001:23837: nags khrod du tshangs par spyad pa'i mthar grong khyer
NK117(she)001:23838: du bsod snyoms la byon pa /
NK117(she)001:23839: tshong dpon gyi bu mo zhig 'dod pas gdungs nas
NK117(she)001:23840: bram ze chags spyod la bskul yang ma nyan par
NK117(she)001:23841: dus de nyid du 'chi bar brtsams pa la snying
NK117(she)001:23842: rje dbang gis chags pa spyad pas tshangs pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:23844: gsod nges pa de las phyir rdzun smra ba mi bdag mchod sbyin byed lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:23845: sdig grogs kyi dbang gis ngan 'gror 'khrid pa las ldog phyir phra mas dbye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23846: mya ngan las skyob phyir ram chos la 'jug phyir ngag 'khyal gyis 'brid pa /
NK117(she)001:23847: sdig pa las bzlog phyir tshig rtsub smra ba sogs
NK117(she)001:23848: kyis mtshon pas gzhan don kho nas mi dge ba
NK117(she)001:23849: la spyod pa thams cad do //
NK117(she)001:23850: de bas na theg dman gyi sde snod las bkag pa dag /
NK117(she)001:23851: theg pa chen po nas gnang ba dag 'gro ba'i
NK117(she)001:23852: blo rim dang nus pa la dgongs pa nyid du
NK117(she)001:23854: de lta na'ang rgyal sras sdom pa la //
NK117(she)001:23855: rang don zhi bde gnyer dang bya dka' spang //
NK117(she)001:23856: gzhan phyir phan pa mi bsgrub gang dang gang //
NK117(she)001:23857: ltung ba'i rgyu ru gcig par gsungs pa yin //
NK117(she)001:23858: zhes pa ni de la gnang bkag gi gnas gang
NK117(she)001:23859: la'ang rang rang gi blo mthu la dpags nas dgag
NK117(she)001:23860: sgrub rigs ma brtags par rgyal sras byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:23861: dpa'i sdom pa blang ba bzhin du rang don zhi
NK117(she)001:23863: bya dka' ba spangs nas gzhan gyi phyir phan 'dogs
NK117(she)001:23864: mi sgrub gang dang gang yin yang rung ste ltung
NK117(she)001:23865: ba'i rgyu ru 'gyur ba la gcig par gsungs pa'o
NK117(she)001:23866: // 'di ltar sdom pa'i tshul khrims la zhe sdang gis gzhan srog gcod pa ltung ba /
NK117(she)001:23867: phan sems kyis yin na ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK117(she)001:23868: snying rjes mi gsod pa ltung med /
NK117(she)001:23869: gzhan la phan kyang mi gsod pa ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK117(she)001:23871: ser snas mi ster ba ltung ba /
NK117(she)001:23872: phan sems kyis mi ster ba ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK117(she)001:23873: bsam pa dag pas ster ba ltung med /
NK117(she)001:23874: gzhan gnod kyi phyir ster ba ltung med kyi gzugs brnyan no //
NK117(she)001:23876: nad par phan mi 'dogs pa ltung ba /
NK117(she)001:23877: don chen bsgrub pa'i ched du de las ldog pa ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan /
NK117(she)001:23878: brtse sems kyis nad g.yog byed pa ltung med /
NK117(she)001:23879: de la nad g.yog yod bzhin du rang gi dge
NK117(she)001:23880: sbyor bshol nas nad g.yog la 'jug pa ltung med
NK117(she)001:23882: rnam dkar dang ma 'brel bar sa brko r+ts+wa 'dreg sogs don med kyi las byed pa nyes byas /
NK117(she)001:23883: dge ba'i phyogs yin na ltung med /
NK117(she)001:23884: dran pas ma zin bzhin pa la ri mo 'bri ba sogs phyogs mthun /
NK117(she)001:23885: dran dang shes bzhin gyis zin par bya ba bslab bya /
NK117(she)001:23886: bslab bya dran nas phyir 'chos shing ldog pa phyir bcos te lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:23888: dang po'i las can byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK117(she)001:23889: blo ni gong nas gong du spyod gtso bas //
NK117(she)001:23890: thog mar sdom pa'i tshul khrims ma dag par //
NK117(she)001:23891: gzhan gnyis gtso bor gnyer na bar chad mang //
NK117(she)001:23892: rab tu byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' ni //
NK117(she)001:23893: khyad par can du mdo sde'i rgyan las bshad //
NK117(she)001:23894: ces pa ni de la so skye rnams kyang nyon
NK117(she)001:23895: mongs pa la skyon dang nyes dmigs su shes nas
NK117(she)001:23896: khyim med par rab tu byung ste dge slong gi
NK117(she)001:23897: rten la sdom pa'i tshul khrims dag par bya ste
NK117(she)001:23898: / ci'i phyir na las dang po pas dge ba
NK117(she)001:23899: chos sdud dang sems can don byed gnyis sgra ji
NK117(she)001:23900: bzhin pa stobs su 'gyur dka' bas rang gi nyon
NK117(she)001:23901: mongs pa bsrung ba gal che zhes gsungs pas so
NK117(she)001:23902: / // tshul khrims rnam pa gsum po de las
NK117(she)001:23903: dang po'i las can byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni
NK117(she)001:23904: sngon du sdom pa'i tshul khrims brtan par byas nas
NK117(she)001:23905: / // / rim bzhin blo gong nas gong du
NK117(she)001:23906: spyod pa gtso che bas kun gyi thog mar sdom
NK117(she)001:23907: pa'i tshul khrims ma dag bar du gzhan dge ba
NK117(she)001:23908: chos sdud dang sems can don byed gnyis gtso bor
NK117(she)001:23909: gnyer na bar chad mang bar 'gyur bas na /
NK117(she)001:23910: rab tu byung ba'i byang chub sems dpa' ni khyim
NK117(she)001:23911: pa las khyad par can du mdo sde rgyan las
NK117(she)001:23912: bshad ces pa'o // de bas na las dang po
NK117(she)001:23913: pas so so thar pa'i sdom pa ni nyan thos
NK117(she)001:23914: kyi yin pas nyan chung snyam du bltas nas byang
NK117(she)001:23915: chub sems dpa'i bslab bya bslab par 'dod pa ni
NK117(she)001:23917: de'i phyir byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i tshul khrims nyams na sdom pa thams cad nyams pa'o //
NK117(she)001:23918: de bas na las dang po pa'i byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:23919: dpa' rnams kyi nyes spyod dang ring bar 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:23920: la dgongs nas rab tu byung ba'i byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:23923: byang chub sems dpa' rang sa'i sdom pa la //
NK117(she)001:23924: so thar mtshan nyid cho gas gsal ba med //
NK117(she)001:23925: sbyangs pa sngon song sems stobs chen po ni //
NK117(she)001:23926: bsam pa'i rten gtso in+d+ra b+hu ti bzhin //
NK117(she)001:23927: zhes pa ni de la byang chub sems dpa' rang
NK117(she)001:23928: sa'i sdom pa zhes theg chen kho na'i gzhung na
NK117(she)001:23929: so thar mtshan nyid pa ltar 'dul sdom gyi cho
NK117(she)001:23931: sbyangs pa sngon song zhes pa skye mang gong nas
NK117(she)001:23932: theg pa chen po la goms pa'i sems stobs chen
NK117(she)001:23933: po ni bsam pa'i rten gtso bo las lus ngag
NK117(she)001:23934: gi bya ba so thar dang 'gal yang de'i skyon
NK117(she)001:23935: du 'gyur mi nus pa in+d+ra b+hu ti bzhin no
NK117(she)001:23938: gang zhig khyim pa'i phyogs la rten pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:23939: dge bsnyen dang ni bsnyen gnas sdom pa'i steng //
NK117(she)001:23940: smon 'jug byang chub sems gnyis rtag tu bsrung //
NK117(she)001:23941: rab tu byung rnams dge slong dge tshul dang //
NK117(she)001:23942: dge slob ma yi sdom pa gang yin steng //
NK117(she)001:23943: smon 'jug gnyis bsrung rang sa'i tshul khrims yin //
NK117(she)001:23944: zhes pa ni gang zhig khyim pa'i phyogs la zhes
NK117(she)001:23945: dge tshul dang dge slong ma yin pa'i sdom pa
NK117(she)001:23946: dman pa'i phyogs la rten pa rnams ni dge bsnyen
NK117(she)001:23947: rigs rnam pa lnga gang rung dang nya stong tshes
NK117(she)001:23948: brgyad sogs la dus khrims yan lag brgyad pa ste
NK117(she)001:23949: bsnyen gnas sdom pa'i steng du smon pa dang 'jug
NK117(she)001:23950: pa'i byang chub kyi sems gnyis res 'ga' tsam ma
NK117(she)001:23951: yin pa rtag pa rgyun du bsrung zhing /
NK117(she)001:23952: rab tu byung ba rnams la'ang dge slong dang dge
NK117(she)001:23953: tshul dang dge slob ma yi sdom pa gang yin
NK117(she)001:23954: gyi steng du / smon 'jug gnyis kyi bslab bya
NK117(she)001:23955: ji bzhin du bsrung ba rang sa'i tshul khrims yin
NK117(she)001:23956: gyi steng du / zhes pa'o // byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:23957: dpa'i tshul khrims kyi sdom pa ni khyim pa'i phyogs
NK117(she)001:23958: la rten pa'i bsnyen gnas dang /
NK117(she)001:23959: dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis dang /
NK117(she)001:23963: dge slob ma ste so thar rigs brgyad po gang
NK117(she)001:23964: rung gi steng du smon 'jug gnyis dang ldan pa'o
NK117(she)001:23965: // spyir sdom pa skye ba'i rten ma yin pa ni /
NK117(she)001:23972: rgyal pos ma gnang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:23973: bya rog skrod mi nus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:23975: skra ser lag rdum sogs lus la skyon chags pa rnams ni dor bya'o //
NK117(she)001:23977: dbye na dge bsnyen rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK117(she)001:23978: sna gcig bsrung ba srog gcod lta bu spang //
NK117(she)001:23979: de steng ma byin len spang phyogs gcig ldan //
NK117(she)001:23980: de steng rdzun smra spang ba phal cher bsrung //
NK117(she)001:23981: de steng 'dod log chang dang bcas spang na //
NK117(she)001:23982: yongs rdzogs bsrung ba'i dge bsnyen dag tu 'dod //
NK117(she)001:23983: rtsa bzhi chang dang lnga ka spang ba la //
NK117(she)001:23984: tshangs par spyod pa'i dge bsnyen zhes su grags //
NK117(she)001:23985: zhes pa ni de la rtsa bzhi gang rung gcig bsrung ba sna gcig /
NK117(she)001:23986: yang gcig bsnan pa phyogs gcig bsrung ba /
NK117(she)001:23988: rtsa ba gnyis chang bcas bsrung ba yongs rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:23989: rtsa bzhi chang bcas lnga ka bsrung ba tshangs spyod dge bsnyen no //
NK117(she)001:23991: rab tu byung ba'i bslab pa'i gnas bcu las //
NK117(she)001:23992: gser dngul len pa bu smad gso phyir gnang //
NK117(she)001:23993: gar phreng gnyis po mtshang chung gcig tu bgrang //
NK117(she)001:23994: yan lag brgyad pa'i khrims zhes grags pa gang //
NK117(she)001:23995: bsrung mtshams med par rtag tu bsrung ba de //
NK117(she)001:23996: tsan+d+ra go mi lta bu'i dge bsnyen yin //
NK117(she)001:23997: zhes pa ni rab tu byung ba'i bslab pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:23998: bcu yod pa las gser dngul len pa gnang don
NK117(she)001:23999: bu smad gso ba'i phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:24000: gar 'cham dang rin po che'i phreng bas spud pa
NK117(she)001:24001: gnyis mtshang skyon chung bas gcig tu bgrang ba la
NK117(she)001:24002: yan lag brgyad pa'i khrims zhes grags pa gang nyid
NK117(she)001:24003: bsrung min res 'ga' tsam ma yin par dus mtshams
NK117(she)001:24004: med par rtag tu bsrung ba de ni /
NK117(she)001:24005: 'phags yul gyi tsan+d+ra go mi lta bu'i dge bsnyen yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24006: khyim pa rnams kyis nya stong brgyad gsum dang dus
NK117(she)001:24007: chen bzhi sogs la bsrung rgyu'i yan lag brgyad pa'i
NK117(she)001:24008: dus khrims dang / de las kyang tshangs spyod dge
NK117(she)001:24009: bsnyen ni bud med spangs pas khyim pa'ang min la
NK117(she)001:24010: dus khrims dang / / rab byung gi rtags ma blangs pas de yang ma yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:24011: slob dpon tsan+d+ra go mi yang so sor thar pa'i sdom pa 'di tsam la brten par snang ngo //
NK117(she)001:24012: skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen ni /
NK117(she)001:24014: gang zhig sangs rgyas skyabs 'gro ba //
NK117(she)001:24015: de ni yang dag dge bsnyen no //
NK117(she)001:24016: zhes gsungs pas mchog gsum skyabs su bzung phyin yang dag pa'i dge bsnyen no //
NK117(she)001:24017: de la yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi spang bya ni rtsa ba bzhi chang dang lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:24018: skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen la spang bya gsum /
NK117(she)001:24022: bsnyen par rdzogs ma rdzogs gnyis las dang po la bar ma dang dge tshul gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:24023: dang po la skyabs 'gro 'dor ba mkhan slob la ma gus pa /
NK117(she)001:24024: khyim pa'i rtags len pa rab byung gi rtags spong ba rnams so //
NK117(she)001:24026: dge tshul srog gcod gzhan gyi nor 'phrog dang //
NK117(she)001:24027: mi tshangs spyod rdzun bcos pa'i chang la sogs //
NK117(she)001:24028: gar sogs phreng sogs mal chen mtho ba dang //
NK117(she)001:24029: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul len pa spang //
NK117(she)001:24030: bslab pa'i gnas bcu 'dzin pa khyad par yin //
NK117(she)001:24031: zhes pa ni dge tshul la dngos bstan spang bya rags gtogs bcu bshad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24032: shugs la so sor phra zhib sgo nas dbye ba gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:24033: de dag rnams bsdu na tshul khrims bag yod brtul zhugs kyi yan lag gsum du 'adu'o //
NK117(she)001:24034: 'di dag gi yin lugs rgyas pa 'grel chen du blta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:24036: dge slob ma ni de steng skyes pa la //
NK117(she)001:24037: reg pa la sogs spong byed bcu gnyis kyi //
NK117(she)001:24038: gnyen po dang bcas bud med nyon mongs pas //
NK117(she)001:24039: lo gnyis la sogs thub bam mi thub brtag /
NK117(she)001:24040: ces pa ni dge slob ma ni dge tshul gyi
NK117(she)001:24041: bslab gzhi bcu thob pa'i steng du dge slob ma'i
NK117(she)001:24043: de'ang sngon ma'i steng du skyes pa la reg pa
NK117(she)001:24044: la sogs spong byed bcu gnyis kyi gnyen po bsten
NK117(she)001:24045: pa'i thabs dang bcas pas bud med nyon mongs pas
NK117(she)001:24046: chags pa spangs nus min lo gnyis la sogs su
NK117(she)001:24047: sdom pa thub bam mi thub brtag ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24048: de'ang spong byed bcu gnyis ni rtsa ba'i chos drug dang /
NK117(she)001:24049: rjes mthun gyi chos drug dang bcu gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:24050: nyes med bdun yang dge slob ma la'o //
NK117(she)001:24052: dge slong rtsa ba'i pham pa bzhi dag dang //
NK117(she)001:24053: lhag ma bcu gsum pham ltung sum cu dang //
NK117(she)001:24054: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24055: sor bshags sde bzhi nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis //
NK117(she)001:24056: nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa gsum rnam grangs dang //
NK117(she)001:24057: zhes pa ni de la dge slong gi rtsa ba'i pham pa bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:24058: mi tshangs spyod dang ma byin len dang /
NK117(she)001:24059: srog gcod pa dang rdzun smra ba dang bzhi'o //
NK117(she)001:24060: de'i steng du dge 'dun la lhag ma bcu gsum yod pa yang /
NK117(she)001:24061: rang gi khu ba 'byin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24062: 'dzin pa'i reg pa'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24063: 'khrig tshig smra ba'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24064: bsnyen bkur basngagasa pa'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24065: smyan byed pa'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24067: khang chen gyi dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24068: gzhi med kyi dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24069: bag tsam gyi dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24070: dbyen byed pa'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24071: rjes phyogs kyi dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24072: khyim sun 'byin pa'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24073: bka' blo mi bde ba'i dge 'dun lhag ma /
NK117(she)001:24074: sngon ma'i bzhi dang bcas pa bcu bdun no //
NK117(she)001:24082: slong ba'i rig pa'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24083: dpags pa slong ba'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24084: so so nas dpags pa slong ba'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24086: srin bal gyi gdan gyi spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24087: bal nag gi gdan gyi spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24088: cha gnyis bsres pa'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24091: lam du bal 'thogs pa'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24093: rin po che la reg pa'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24094: mngon mtshan can gyi spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24095: nyo tshong byed pa'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24096: lhung bzed zhag bcu 'chang ba'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24097: lhung bzed lhag po 'tshol ba'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24099: thags pa bskyed pa'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24101: brtad pa las byung ba'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24104: bsngosa pa gzhan du bsgyur ba'i spang ba /
NK117(she)001:24105: bsog 'jog gi spang ba ste sum cu'o //
NK117(she)001:24106: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa ni /
NK117(she)001:24108: 1 de nas rim bzhin skyon brjod pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24111: 4 bud med la chos bstan pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24112: 5 bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa dang lhan cig chos 'don pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24114: 7 mi chos bla ma dbyen byed pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24119: 12 bsgo ba rna la gzon pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24126: 19 rim pa lhag par rtsig pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24127: 20 dge slong ma la chos ston pa'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24128: 21 nyi ma nub kyi bar chos ston pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24133: 26 dge slong ma dang lhan cig grur 'jug pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24134: 27 dben pa skyabs yod du 'jug pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24137: 30 yang yang bza' ba'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24140: 33 spangs pa bza' ba'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24143: 36 dus ma yin par bza' ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24145: 38 byin len ma byas par bza' ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24146: 39 zas bsod pa slong ba'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24147: 40 srog chags dang bcas pa chu la longs spyod pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24150: nyal po byed pa'i khyim du 'greng ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24151: 43 gces bu la zas byin pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24153: 45 dmag gi nang du gnas pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24163: 55 spangs pa rjes su phyogs pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24164: 56 dge tshul bsnyil ba sdud pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24166: 58 rin po che la reg pa'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24172: 64 bud med dang lhan cig tu nyal ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24173: 65 dngangs par byed pa'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24174: 66 dge slong la mtho 'tsham pa'i bsam pa 'jigs pa sna tshogs ston pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24176: 67 sbyin pas nye bar 'tsho ba'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24178: 69 bud med dang lhan cig tu 'gro ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24179: 70 bud med dang lhan cig tu rgyang grags las 'das par lam du 'gro ba'o //
NK117(she)001:24180: rkun po dang lhan cig lam du 'gro ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24181: 71 gzhan gyi dngos po brkus pa'i gang zag dang
NK117(she)001:24182: lhan cig tu rgyang grags las 'das par 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:24183: / nyi shu ma lon par bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24185: 73 'gron du gnyer las ring du 'dug pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24186: 74 bslab pa nye bar 'jog pa spong ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24193: 81 rgyal po'i pho brang du nub mo 'gro ba'i /
NK117(she)001:24197: 85 shing bal gyis bgos par byed pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24198: 86 gding ba tshad lhag byed pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24199: 87 g.yan pa dgab pa tshad las lhag pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24200: 88 dbyar gyi gos ras chen tshad las lhag pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24201: 89 chos gos tshad las lhag par byed pa'i ltung byed /
NK117(she)001:24203: dge slong mar zas len pa'i sor bshags /
NK117(she)001:24204: dge slong mas rang nyid 'tsho ba'i ched du bsod snyoms slong ba /
NK117(she)001:24205: gral rim du ma phebs par 'grim du 'jug pa la bzlog pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24206: bslab pa hral te khyim du 'jug pa'i /
NK117(she)001:24207: nags brtags pa las gyur pa'i sor bshags rnams so //
NK117(she)001:24208: nyes byas pa brgya dang bcu gnyis yod pa'i sde tshan brgyad las sham thabs kyi bdun /
NK117(she)001:24209: khyim du 'gro ba la shin tu bsdams pa lnga /
NK117(she)001:24215: zas bza' ba'i sde tshan drug go //
NK117(she)001:24219: lhung bzed kyi sde tshan la 'phya ba sogs ni bzhi'o //
NK117(she)001:24221: chos bshad pa'i sde tshan la 'greng ba sogs ni drug go //
NK117(she)001:24222: mgo bo g.yogs pa sogs ni lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:24226: sgrub pa'i sde tshan ni bzhi'o //
NK117(she)001:24227: de ltar dge slong gi sdom pa ni nyis brgya
NK117(she)001:24228: dang lnga bcu rtsa gsum gyi rnam grangs su bsdus
NK117(she)001:24229: so // dge 'dun lhag ma'i ltung ba 'di ltung
NK117(she)001:24230: ba gang byung yang mal stan dang kha zas la
NK117(she)001:24231: sogs pa dge 'dun rgan po dang bar ma dang
NK117(she)001:24232: gzhon nu'i rjes la lhag mar byed pas na dge
NK117(she)001:24233: so // 'dun lhag ma'o // sor bshags ni rang
NK117(she)001:24234: rang so sor bshags par bya ba 'os pa yin
NK117(she)001:24235: so // 'dun lhag ma'o // pas so // mdor
NK117(she)001:24236: na dge slong la khrims nyis brgya dang lnga bcu
NK117(she)001:24237: rtsa gsum yod par shes 'dod pa dag bden gnyis
NK117(she)001:24238: shing rta la blta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:24240: dge slong ma la sum brgya drug cu bzhi //
NK117(she)001:24241: so so'i rtsa ba bzhi brgyad pham pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24242: nyes byas sbom po phyogs mthun khyad par yod //
NK117(she)001:24243: pham pas sdom pa rtsa nas gtong ba yin //
NK117(she)001:24244: phyin chad sor chud rung dang mi rung mtshams //
NK117(she)001:24245: 'chab sems skyes dang ma skyes dag la rag /
NK117(she)001:24246: ces pa ni de la dge slong ma la pham pa brgyad lhag ma nyi shu /
NK117(she)001:24247: spang ltung sum cu so gsum /
NK117(she)001:24248: ltung byed brgya dang dgu bcu /
NK117(she)001:24249: sor bshags bcu gcig nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis te
NK117(she)001:24250: dge slong las brgya dang bcu gcig lhag pa las
NK117(she)001:24251: pham pa brgyad ni dge slong dang thun mong ba
NK117(she)001:24252: bzhi po'i steng / skyes pa la reg pa /
NK117(she)001:24254: 'chab pa bzlog pa bsnan pas brgyad do //
NK117(she)001:24255: de lhag ma nyi shu sogs kyang 'grel chen du gsal lo //
NK117(she)001:24256: de ltar dge slong pha ma sus kyang pham pas
NK117(she)001:24257: sdom pa'i rtsa ba 'jig pa dang yan lag ma
NK117(she)001:24258: tshang na pham 'dra'i nyes byas dang /
NK117(she)001:24259: de yang gsor rung min ni 'chab sems skyes min gyis dabye'o //
NK117(she)001:24261: bsrung bya mi shes bsrung bar rlom pa mtshar //
NK117(she)001:24262: ltung ba shes pa tsam gyi gso sbyong sla //
NK117(she)001:24263: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi'i dang po'ang //
NK117(she)001:24264: mi shes pa zhes thog med bzhed pa yin //
NK117(she)001:24265: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya gzhi gsum cho ga dang //
NK117(she)001:24266: bcu bdun bslab bya 'jug pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK117(she)001:24267: zhes pa ni de yang so sor thar pa'i dang
NK117(she)001:24268: po dge bsnyen dang dge tshul dge slong sogs kyi
NK117(she)001:24269: bsrung bya rnams ji bzhin shes shing blang dor rnams
NK117(she)001:24270: ma 'dzol ba zhig dgos kyang mi shes bzhin du
NK117(she)001:24271: bsrung bar rlom pa ni byis pa chung ngu zhig
NK117(she)001:24272: gis stobs rtsal ldan pa gyad kyi lad mo byed
NK117(she)001:24273: pa 'dra mo ni mtshar ba'i gnas tsam las don
NK117(she)001:24274: thog tu khel ba ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:24275: des na ltung ba'i skyon shes pa tsam gyis nyams
NK117(she)001:24276: pa gso zhing nyes pa sbyong bar sla zhes pa
NK117(she)001:24277: dang / de la ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi ni ltung min shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24278: bslab pa phul lam 'bul rgyu'i brda' sprad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24280: mtshan gnyis gcig car byung ngam lan gsum gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24281: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya gzhi gsum cho ga ni gso sbyong dang /
NK117(she)001:24282: dbyar gnas dang dgag dbye ste gsum du rgyas 'grel las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:24283: bcu bdun bslab bya 'jug pa'i tshul khrims kyang pham
NK117(she)001:24284: lhag bdun po spang blang 'dzol med dgos pa dang
NK117(she)001:24285: / de'i yan lag gi gtso bo sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis ni /
NK117(she)001:24287: phyag dar khrod pa nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:24291: zas phyis mi len pa nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:24292: chos gos gsum pa nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:24294: gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:24297: bla gab med pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:24299: 'di na pham lhag bcu bdun ma gtogs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:24300: mi rung longs spyod byin gyis rlob pa ni //
NK117(she)001:24301: dus ma yin par kha zas spyod dgos na //
NK117(she)001:24302: sgra mi snyan pa'i gling du mos pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24303: de bzhin khrus la nad pa gos lhag gam //
NK117(she)001:24304: rung ba ma yin bgo ba dkar po dang //
NK117(she)001:24305: ko lpags sogs la phongs pas nyam thag par //
NK117(she)001:24306: srog bsrung slad du gnang ba yin snyam dang //
NK117(she)001:24307: rin po cher reg dkon mchog mchod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24308: sems can gso ba'i slad du gnang bar bsgom //
NK117(she)001:24309: gnang med bkag pa med pa rjes mthun brtsi //
NK117(she)001:24310: zhes pa ni 'di na pham pa bzhi dang lhag
NK117(she)001:24311: ma bcu gsum bsdoms pas bcu bdun po de ma
NK117(she)001:24312: gtogs pa'i / mi rung ba'i bza' btung gos sogs longs spyod byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK117(she)001:24313: dus ma yin par kha zas btung ba sogs la
NK117(she)001:24314: spyod dgos pa byung na sgra mi snyan pa'i gling
NK117(she)001:24315: du mos nas longs spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24316: de bzhin du khrus byed pa la nad par mos
NK117(she)001:24317: pa dang gos lhag gam gyon du rung ba ma
NK117(she)001:24318: yin pa bgo ba dkar po'am ko lpags sogs la
NK117(she)001:24319: spyod dgos byung na phongs pas nyam thag par srog
NK117(she)001:24320: bsrung ba'i slad du gnang ba yin snyam dang rin
NK117(she)001:24321: po cher reg dgos pa byung na dkon mchog gsum
NK117(she)001:24322: mchod pa'i don yin pa dang sems can gso ba'i
NK117(she)001:24323: slad du gnang bar bsgom zhing gnang ba yang med
NK117(she)001:24324: la bkag pa yang med pa dag la gang nye
NK117(she)001:24325: dang rjes su mthun par rtsi dgos zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24327: thams cad yod smra phal chen sde pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24328: gnas brtan pa dang mang pos bkur ba ste //
NK117(she)001:24329: sde pa bzhi ka'i bslab pa thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:24330: ston pa'i bcas pas ma khyab mi srid pas //
NK117(she)001:24331: bslab pa kun la dbang thob byed pa yin //
NK117(she)001:24332: zhes pa ni thams cad yod par smra ba dang /
NK117(she)001:24334: gnas brtan pa dang mang pos bkur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:24335: de las dang po la gyes pa bdun ni gzhi yod pa /
NK117(she)001:24338: mang du thos par smra ba pa /
NK117(she)001:24340: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde dang bdun no //
NK117(she)001:24341: phal chen pa ni bram ze 'od srung chen po'i brgyud pa ste de las gyes pa lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:24346: 'jig rten las 'das par smra ba'i sde'o //
NK117(she)001:24348: rigs smyig ma mkhan k+aa t+ya na'i brgyud pa /
NK117(she)001:24349: de las gyes pa gsum rgyal byed tshal na gnas pa'i sde /
NK117(she)001:24350: 'jigs med ri la gnas pa'i sde /
NK117(she)001:24351: gtsug lag khang la gnas pa'i sde'o //
NK117(she)001:24352: 'dreg mkhan gyi rigs nye bar 'khor ba'i brgyud pa /
NK117(she)001:24353: de las gyes pa gsum ni /
NK117(she)001:24356: gnas ma bu'i sde spyi dril bas nyan thos sde brgyad de /
NK117(she)001:24357: de dag rnam pa mi mthun kyang rab byung ste
NK117(she)001:24358: lnga'i spyod pa dang 'brel zhing ston pa'i bcas pas
NK117(she)001:24359: ma khyab pa ni srid pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:24360: de ltar ston pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas so thar
NK117(she)001:24361: gyi bslab sdom ji bzhin blangs pa tshul bzhin ma
NK117(she)001:24362: bsrungs na rtsa ltung lta bu'i ngos nas 'chab med
NK117(she)001:24363: la bslab pa sbyin nas phyir bcos su yod kyang
NK117(she)001:24364: / so thar gyi rang 'bras mthar thug dgra bcom
NK117(she)001:24365: pa'i go 'phang ma thob bar du pham pa'i dngos
NK117(she)001:24366: gzhi lhag med du zad mi nus pas rnam grol
NK117(she)001:24367: thob pa la yun ring 'gyang ba nyid de /
NK117(she)001:24369: dam chos thos par mi 'gyur la //
NK117(she)001:24370: thos pa myur du brjed par 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:24371: sa lam rtogs pa yongs mi skye //
NK117(she)001:24373: bsrung ba'i phan yon ni tshe 'dir nad dang rgyal po'i chad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24374: phongs pa las thar ba sogs phan yon mang zhing /
NK117(she)001:24375: phan yon de dag don gnyer gyi ched du bslab
NK117(she)001:24376: pa blang na 'jigs skyob kyi tshul khrims dang phyi
NK117(she)001:24377: ma lha mi'i bde 'bras tsam don du gnyer nas
NK117(she)001:24378: bslab pa blang na legs smon te /
NK117(she)001:24379: de gnyis pos 'khor ba las thar ba ma yin kyang gnas skabs kyi bde 'bras tsam thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24380: 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin du shes bzhin
NK117(she)001:24381: nges 'byung gi bsam pas bslab sdom blang ba nyan
NK117(she)001:24382: thos rang sa'i grub mtha' yin la /
NK117(she)001:24383: theg chen sems bskyed kyis zin na re re thar
NK117(she)001:24384: pa rigs brgyad gang yin kyang byang chub sems dpa'i
NK117(she)001:24386: de yang da lta bstan pa mar 'grib la nye
NK117(she)001:24387: ba'i dus 'dir bstan pa la zhugs par rloms pa
NK117(she)001:24388: dag kyang ma dul zhing ma bsdams pa /
NK117(she)001:24390: khyim pa'i rjes su zhugs pa la dga' ba'i dus
NK117(she)001:24391: 'dir nyin zhag gcig gi bar du bslab pa sna
NK117(she)001:24392: tshogs bsrung ba'i phan yon kyang bskal pa yar dar
NK117(she)001:24393: la bslab pa yongs su rdzogs pa bsrungs pa dang
NK117(she)001:24394: mnyam zhes gsungs pas na deng dus bsnyen gnas dang
NK117(she)001:24395: bsnyung gnas sogs kyang khyad gsod mi byed cing nyams
NK117(she)001:24396: len byed pa gal shin tu che'o //
NK117(she)001:24398: mya ngan 'da' bar bsngo bas lhag pa'i khrims //
NK117(she)001:24399: gzhan la phan pa bsgrub pas byang sdom la //
NK117(she)001:24400: dbang bskur rnal ma thob na sngags sdom ste //
NK117(she)001:24401: gsum rdzogs bslab bya yon tan mtha' dag mang //
NK117(she)001:24402: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du //
NK117(she)001:24403: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la gnas pa yin //
NK117(she)001:24404: nang 'gal byung na gong ma gtsor bton pa //
NK117(she)001:24405: sngon byon mkhas grub rnams kyi lugs la grags //
NK117(she)001:24406: 'og ma'i rnam pa 'gal ba ltar snang yang //
NK117(she)001:24407: gnod pa spong dang phan 'dogs dgos pa mthun //
NK117(she)001:24408: gang zhig 'gal na gnang bar mi srid la //
NK117(she)001:24409: gnang na 'gal bar mi srid de chos can //
NK117(she)001:24410: zhes pa ni de la sems rgyud nyon mongs dang
NK117(she)001:24411: mi dge ba'i phyogs las spong sems kyis sdom zhing
NK117(she)001:24412: nyan thos kyi byang chub la dmigs pa ni so
NK117(she)001:24413: thar dang / dge ba'i chos mtha' dag rgyun chags
NK117(she)001:24414: par sdud cing gzhan phan bsgrub pa ni byang sdom
NK117(she)001:24415: thar dang / / de'i steng du sngags kyi dbang skur rnal ma thob na sngags sdom ste /
NK117(she)001:24416: de yang mya ngan las 'da' bar bsngosa pas lhag pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK117(she)001:24417: gzhan la phan pa bsgrub pas byang chub sems dpa'i
NK117(she)001:24418: sdom pa gsum ka rdzogs pa dag la bslab bya
NK117(she)001:24419: dang yon tan mtha' dag mang zhing /
NK117(she)001:24420: de dag ngo bo gcig na'ang ldog pa tha dad
NK117(she)001:24421: du yod cing gang zag gcig gi rgyud la gnas
NK117(she)001:24422: pa so sor gnas pa yin zhing nang 'gal byung
NK117(she)001:24423: na gong ma'i gong ma gtsor bor bton zhes pa
NK117(she)001:24424: sngon byon gyi mkhas grub rnams kyi lugs la grags
NK117(she)001:24425: pa yin zhing / 'og ma so thar dang 'gal
NK117(she)001:24426: ba ltar snang yang gong ma dang mthun te gnod
NK117(she)001:24427: pa spang ba dang phan 'dogs pa dgos pa mthun
NK117(she)001:24428: zhing gang zhig gsum ka dang 'gal na gnang ba
NK117(she)001:24429: gtan nas mi srid la gnang phyin 'gal bar mi
NK117(she)001:24430: srid pa de chos can zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24432: 'di ltar nyan thos pa la ltung ba dang //
NK117(she)001:24433: byang chub sems dpar phyogs mthun nyes byas su //
NK117(she)001:24434: 'gyur ba'i myos byed sngags kyi dam rdzas su //
NK117(she)001:24435: spyod pa'i skyes bu'i rtog tshogs lhar shar bas //
NK117(she)001:24436: gzhi dang bsam pa gnyis ka gzhan du 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:24437: dge slong ma yin byang chub sems dpa' min //
NK117(she)001:24438: thabs bral chags sred nyon mongs mthus non min //
NK117(she)001:24439: snang ba mtha' dag lha dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK117(she)001:24440: spyad bya'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:24441: 'du shes gnas 'gyur gang la gnang ba yin //
NK117(she)001:24442: so so thar dang byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK117(she)001:24443: dge slong dang ni dge 'dun la byin las //
NK117(she)001:24444: yi dam la phul tshogs kyang yar ldan 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:24445: bslab pa'i cha shas gzhan la'ang de yis 'gre //
NK117(she)001:24446: zhes pa ni 'di ltar chang gi btung ba ni
NK117(she)001:24447: nyan thos pa la ltung ba dang byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:24448: dpa' la'ang phyogs mthun du nyes byas su 'gyur ba'i
NK117(she)001:24449: myos byed kyang sngags kyi skabs su dam tshig gi
NK117(she)001:24451: de ltar tshul bzhin spyod pa'i skyes bu rim gnyis
NK117(she)001:24452: la goms pa dag gi rtog tshogs lhar shar bas
NK117(she)001:24453: na gzhi dang bsam pa gnyis ka tha mal las
NK117(she)001:24454: gnas 'gyur phyir / so so thar pa'i dge tshul
NK117(she)001:24455: slong dang byang sems 'dul 'dzin pa gnyis ka ma
NK117(she)001:24456: gnas 'gyur phyir / yin zhing / de bzhin du
NK117(she)001:24457: thabs dang bral bzhin chags sred dang nyon mongs kho
NK117(she)001:24458: nas mthus non pa yang min zhing /
NK117(she)001:24459: snang ba mtha' dag lha dang dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK117(she)001:24460: zhing spyad bya'i myos byed rdzas kyang bdud rtsi'i rang
NK117(she)001:24461: bzhin las tha mal gyi 'dzin rtog 'du shes gnas
NK117(she)001:24462: 'gyur ba gang la'ang gnang ba yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:24463: de'i don yang so so thar pa dang byang chub
NK117(she)001:24464: sems dpa'i dge slong dang ni dge 'dun bsam spyod
NK117(she)001:24465: tha mal las ma 'gyur ba'i tshogs la byin pa
NK117(she)001:24466: las yi dam gyi lha la phul bas tshogs kyang
NK117(she)001:24467: yar ldan du 'gyur zhing bslab pa'i cha shas gzhan
NK117(she)001:24468: rnams la'ang de'i 'gres kyis shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:24471: 'on kyang rang ldog ma 'dres dgag dgos tshang //
NK117(she)001:24472: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yon tan yar ldan pas //
NK117(she)001:24473: gnad kyis mi 'gal dus skabs gtsor spyod do //
NK117(she)001:24474: zhes pa ni de la rang ldog ma 'dres pa ni /
NK117(she)001:24475: sdom pa gsum po blang ba'i yul len pa'i bsam pa /
NK117(she)001:24476: len byed kyi cho ga rnams rang rang gi ldog
NK117(she)001:24477: pa ma 'dres pa'i sgo nas dus tha dad du
NK117(she)001:24478: nges pa kho na yin phyir rang rang gi ldog
NK117(she)001:24479: pa gzhi mthun pa ma yin zhing mtshan nyid so
NK117(she)001:24480: sor 'dzin pas rang ldog ma 'dres pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24482: dgag bya ni nyon mongs pa dang dgos pa ni
NK117(she)001:24483: des mi 'ching bar rang lam so sor gcig pa'i
NK117(she)001:24486: sngags su lam du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24487: de yang nyan thos kyi ni phyi gzung ba'i yul rags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24488: nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa rgyun dang bcas pa
NK117(she)001:24489: rang bzhin med par rtogs pas 'khor ba las nges
NK117(she)001:24490: par 'byung yang / gzung yul rdul phra rab dang
NK117(she)001:24491: 'dzin sems kyi shes pa skad cig ma don dam
NK117(she)001:24492: du 'dod pas nyon mongs pa dgra bzhin spong ba
NK117(she)001:24493: par 'byung yang / dang / byang chub sems dpa'
NK117(she)001:24494: ni nang 'dzin pa'i shes pa rkyen gyis 'khrul pa'i
NK117(she)001:24495: snang ba tsam las don la bden grub ma yin
NK117(she)001:24496: par 'byung yang / dang / kyang / phyi yul du 'dogs pa ni kun brtags dang /
NK117(she)001:24498: yongs grub rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis yul shes gnyis skye med du shes nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24499: rnam rtog chos nyid du sbyong bsgyur byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24500: rdo rje'i theg pa ni nyon mongs rnam rtog lha
NK117(she)001:24501: dang ye shes su bsgyur ba la mi rmongs pa
NK117(she)001:24502: dang / khyad par chos nyid kyi don rnal ma
NK117(she)001:24503: mthong bas spang blang las 'das pa'i don rtogs pa'o
NK117(she)001:24504: dang / // mdor na nyan thos pa bden gnyis
NK117(she)001:24505: rdzas yod du blta bas so thar gyis spong ba
NK117(she)001:24506: dang / // dang / byang sems kyi kun rdzob
NK117(she)001:24507: rdzas yod du blta ba stong nyid snying rjes sbyang
NK117(she)001:24508: dang / // dang / ba dang / sngags kyi
NK117(she)001:24509: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du dag cing grol bas
NK117(she)001:24510: de gsum kas rgyud gcig de'i mi dge sdom par
NK117(she)001:24511: dang / // dang / ba dang / gcig go
NK117(she)001:24512: // de yang las dang po pas rnal 'byor pa'i
NK117(she)001:24514: rnal 'byor pas grub pa'i bya ba mi bya /
NK117(she)001:24515: grub pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:24516: zhes pa'ang gal shin tu che'o //
NK117(she)001:24518: grub pa'i mtha' la dpyad pa zhugs pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:24519: gnas 'gyur ngo bo gcig tu 'dod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24520: gcig la gzhi mi mthun du 'dod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24521: gsum ka rdzas 'gal gong 'phel 'dod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24522: gtong thob mtshams nas rnam par dbye ba dang //
NK117(she)001:24523: dong rtse brtsegs bzhin ma 'dres 'dod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24524: nyi zla skar gsum rim can tshogs pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:24525: rang 'od ma nyams nus pa'i khyad zhugs 'dod //
NK117(she)001:24526: ces pa ni de la grub pa'i mtha' so so
NK117(she)001:24527: rang rang gi dpyad pa zhugs pa rnams kyis sdom
NK117(she)001:24528: pa 'og ma gong mar gnas 'gyur dang de yang
NK117(she)001:24529: ngo bo gcig tu 'dod pa yongs grub chen po'i
NK117(she)001:24530: rtogs pas rgyud grol ba ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:24531: gcig la gzhi mi mthun pa'ang shes rab kyi don
NK117(she)001:24532: gcig tu yod kyang 'du shes kyi cha nas gzhi
NK117(she)001:24535: sdom gsum rdzogs pa'i gang zag de dngos kyi blo'i
NK117(she)001:24536: rim pa las rang rang so so na yod do
NK117(she)001:24537: snyam byed kyi shes ngor rdzas 'gal bas gong ma'i
NK117(she)001:24538: thabs shes kyis 'og ma'i sdom pa dang 'gal ba'i
NK117(she)001:24539: chos can zin gyis mi non par gsungs pa dang
NK117(she)001:24540: / gtong thob mtshams nas rnam par dbye ba ni /
NK117(she)001:24541: blo chung dag grol du 'dzin pa'i gang zag drang
NK117(she)001:24542: srong nyi ma'i shing rta can lta bu don zab
NK117(she)001:24543: mo ring du gyur pa rnams rjes su bzung phyir
NK117(she)001:24544: / thog mar de skad brjod pas gdod sngags la 'jug pa'i rgyur gsungs pa lta bu ste /
NK117(she)001:24545: dgos dbang rab tu byung ba spyod pa lhod pa
NK117(she)001:24546: dag la dgongs nas gsang ba dang sher ye'i dbang
NK117(she)001:24547: bskur tshangs spyod la bkag pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:24548: zhes pa ltar gnas dus kyi dgag bya dmigs bsal
NK117(she)001:24549: la nges pa kun nas kun tu de ltar 'dod
NK117(she)001:24550: nas sdom pa gong ma thob phyin 'og ma gtong
NK117(she)001:24551: ba'i shes byed dgod na ni sngags kyi dge slong
NK117(she)001:24552: rdor 'dzin mi 'byung zhing dbang bzhi ma tshang na
NK117(she)001:24553: sangs rgyas mi thob pa dang 'gal lo //
NK117(she)001:24554: dong rtse brtsegs ltar gsum ka rdzas ma 'dres par 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24555: bcas khrims mi srid du sems pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24557: smon pa la ltos pa'i bar du dang po rgyu
NK117(she)001:24558: tshogs gcig las skyes pa bar du 'gal ba ltag
NK117(she)001:24559: mi sprod pa / tha mar sgrub sde gcig pa
NK117(she)001:24560: sde chos gsum tshang bas rdzas ldog dang dus gsum
NK117(she)001:24561: du gcig pa med pas 'thad du rung ngo //
NK117(she)001:24562: nyi zla skar gsum 'tshogs pa'i dpes nus stobs che
NK117(she)001:24563: chung gi 'og ma bag la zha bar 'dod pa'i
NK117(she)001:24564: don yang slob dpon chen po bi ma las /
NK117(she)001:24565: sems kyis las de bya ba'i sems de la ngo
NK117(she)001:24566: bo nyid med par rtogs pa'i phyir ram chos thams
NK117(she)001:24567: cad ngo bo nyid med par bsgoms na tshul khrims
NK117(she)001:24568: rnam par dag pa kho na yin par rigs par
NK117(she)001:24570: de sogs rnam pa'i khas blangs mtha' dag kyang //
NK117(she)001:24571: cho ga'i dus ltar rang ldog ma 'dres dang //
NK117(she)001:24572: bsrung mtshams dus na dgag dgos tshang ba dang //
NK117(she)001:24573: gnas 'gyur ngo bo ye shes mthus byed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:24574: spyir btang dmigs bsal phyed pa khyad par yin //
NK117(she)001:24575: zhes pa ni de sogs zhes rnam pa'i khas blangs
NK117(she)001:24576: mtha' dag yod kyang sdom gsum so so'i cho ga'i
NK117(she)001:24577: dus ltar rang ldog ste rang rang gi lugs ma
NK117(she)001:24578: 'dres pa dang dge bsnyen dge tshul dge slong gsum
NK117(she)001:24579: gyi bsrung mtshams so so'i dus na dgag bya'i nyon
NK117(she)001:24580: mongs dang dgos bya'i sdom pa rtsa lag thams cad
NK117(she)001:24581: tshang ba dang / de yang sdom pa gnas 'gyur
NK117(she)001:24582: min gang zag la rag las shing de'i ngo bo
NK117(she)001:24583: ye shes kyi mthus byed pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:24584: spyir btang dang dmigs bsal gnyis kyi bye brag phyed pa khyad par yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24585: de la sdom pa gsum ni bcas pa'i ltung ba
NK117(she)001:24586: yin la sdom pa med na bsod nams dang ltung
NK117(she)001:24587: ba gnyis ka med cing sdom pas ma bsdams pa
NK117(she)001:24588: la bar ma dge ba ste 'khor ba las mi
NK117(she)001:24590: gleng gzhi gnas 'gyur 'dod la phyir bcos med //
NK117(she)001:24591: so thar ngos nas byung ba'i ltung ba gcig /
NK117(she)001:24592: rang ngos 'chos na gnas 'gyur zin pas 'gal //
NK117(she)001:24593: gong ma'i ngos nas 'chos na de nyid la //
NK117(she)001:24594: ltung ba ma byung phyir bcos mi dgos bsnyon //
NK117(she)001:24595: zhes pa ni gleng gzhi gnas 'gyur 'dod pa'i lugs
NK117(she)001:24596: ltar na de la phyir bcos kyi dgos pa med
NK117(she)001:24597: pa'i don yang / so thar ngos nas byung ba'i
NK117(she)001:24598: ltung ba gang rung gcig byung na de nyid so
NK117(she)001:24599: thar rang ngo nas 'chos dgos zer na 'og ma'i
NK117(she)001:24600: sdom pa de nyid gong mar gnas 'gyur zin pas
NK117(she)001:24601: phyir bcos byed pa 'gal zhing gong ma'i ngos nas
NK117(she)001:24602: 'chos na so thar gyi sdom pa nyams kyang gong
NK117(she)001:24603: ma la ltung ba ma byung bas phyir bcos mi
NK117(she)001:24605: 'di ltar las byed pa po ni sems /
NK117(she)001:24606: de nyid dge ba dang mi dge ba ni las /
NK117(she)001:24607: las bzang ngan las bde sdug 'byung bas de dag
NK117(she)001:24608: blang dor byed pa'i thabs ni sdom pa yin na
NK117(she)001:24609: lam zhugs kyi gang zag gsum ldan dge slong rdor
NK117(she)001:24610: 'dzin du khas 'che ba tsam spyi'i rnams kyi ngos
NK117(she)001:24611: nas sdom gsum mtshan nyid so sor 'dzin cing rang
NK117(she)001:24612: ldog ma 'dres par yod pas gleng gzhi thams cad
NK117(she)001:24613: nas thams cad du gang zag sdom gsum nod tshad
NK117(she)001:24614: kyi rgyud la gnas 'gyur mnyam brdal du med de
NK117(she)001:24616: rag rdo dang zha ne la so sor byung bzhin
NK117(she)001:24617: 'og ma gong mar gnas 'gyur te sngags gcig pu
NK117(she)001:24618: bsrungs pas chog zer ba yang mi 'thad de /
NK117(she)001:24619: 'og ma khyad du gsod pa ltung ba dang sdom pa thams cad bsrung bar bshad pas gnod do //
NK117(she)001:24621: lus ngag las skyes sdom pa gzugs can nam //
NK117(she)001:24622: spong sems rgyun chags sa bon bden zhen ldan //
NK117(she)001:24623: bsgyur dang lam 'khyer thabs kyis ma zin par //
NK117(she)001:24624: theg chen lam zhugs dbang bskur nod na'ang //
NK117(she)001:24625: gnas 'gyur thob pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa min //
NK117(she)001:24626: zhes pa ni so sor thar pa pa'i sdom pa
NK117(she)001:24627: lus dang ngag las skyes pa yin phyir gzugs can
NK117(she)001:24628: nam chags sdang sogs nyes byas spong sems rgyun chags
NK117(she)001:24629: kyi dpe sa bon sa la btab pa bzhin bden
NK117(she)001:24630: par zhen pa'i skyon dang ldan pa dag byang sems
NK117(she)001:24631: ltar snang ba rmi lam dang sgyu mar bsgyur ba
NK117(she)001:24632: dang nyon mongs lam khyer sngags gzhung ltar thabs kyis
NK117(she)001:24634: theg chen lam du zhugs nas dbang bzhi bskur ba nod par gyur na'ang /
NK117(she)001:24635: 'og ma gong mar gnas 'gyur sgra ji bzhin thob pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa min no //
NK117(she)001:24637: sdom pa dag par byed pa 'du shes te //
NK117(she)001:24638: 'du shes dag byed lha yi rnal 'byor yin //
NK117(she)001:24639: de nyid dag byed ye shes la goms na //
NK117(she)001:24640: bcas pa'i ltung ba chos can skyes 'jig can //
NK117(she)001:24641: rang mtshan mi 'dzin thob dang shor ba med //
NK117(she)001:24642: thog mtha' bar du 'gal bar mi gnas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:24643: ngo bo kun rdzob yin pas gnas 'gyur grub //
NK117(she)001:24644: ces pa ni rang nyid kyi 'du shes ma dag
NK117(she)001:24645: pa dag par byed pa bskyed rim lha yi rnal
NK117(she)001:24646: 'byor yin par bstan nas de nyid kyang dag byed
NK117(she)001:24647: kyi ye shes la goms par gyur na /
NK117(she)001:24648: bcas pa'i ltung ba ni lus ngag ga las chos
NK117(she)001:24649: can skye 'jig can yin pas rang mtshan te dngos
NK117(she)001:24650: po dang mtshan mar mi 'dzin pa'i phyir bsrungs pas
NK117(she)001:24651: thob rgyu dang ma bsrung bas shor ba gang yang
NK117(she)001:24652: med cing / thog ma dang tha ma bar pa
NK117(she)001:24653: zhes dus gsum gyi gnas gang du'ang 'gal ba mi
NK117(she)001:24654: gnas pa'i phyir ngo bo kun rdzob ces bden pa
NK117(she)001:24655: ma yin pas gnas 'gyur grub ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24657: gzhi dang bsam pa gnyis ka mngon gyur ldan //
NK117(she)001:24658: mos pas spyod pa'i sdom pa gsum ldan la //
NK117(she)001:24659: gnas na bye brag bsrungs na 'chol bar bsrung //
NK117(she)001:24660: ldan na yar ldan 'chos na rang sa nas //
NK117(she)001:24661: nyams pa khol bur phyung ba'i phyir bcos grub //
NK117(she)001:24662: ci phyir nyes pa bskyed na gang yang 'gog /
NK117(she)001:24663: dge dang yon tan bskyed na gnang ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:24664: gnang bkag tshig gi lam na gnas pa min //
NK117(she)001:24665: gang zag rgyud dang 'brel nas grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24666: zhes pa ni de la dge bsnyen dang dge tshul
NK117(she)001:24667: dge slong byang sems rnams so sor yin par shes
NK117(she)001:24668: pa dang bsam pa yang de dag rang rang gi
NK117(she)001:24669: blang dor la bslabs pa gnyis ka ni lkog tu
NK117(she)001:24670: ma gyur cing mngon du gyur par ldan cing /
NK117(she)001:24671: de dag la mos pas spyod pa tsam gyi sdom
NK117(she)001:24672: pa gsum dang ldan pa rnams la so thar byang
NK117(she)001:24673: sems sngags gsum gnas na bye brag so so dang
NK117(she)001:24674: bsrungs na 'chol ba ste bsrung gang dka' ba de
NK117(she)001:24675: lhag par bsrungs la gzhan gnyis kyang byi dor byed
NK117(she)001:24676: bzhin bsrung ba'o // gsum po ma nyams par ldan
NK117(she)001:24677: na yar ldan de rim bzhin je bzang lta bu
NK117(she)001:24678: dang nyams pa 'chos na gsum po gang gi ngos
NK117(she)001:24679: nas nyes pa byung ba khol bur phyung nas so
NK117(she)001:24680: so'i gzhung bzhin phyir bcos byas pas chog par grub
NK117(she)001:24681: bzhin bsrung ba'o // cing / ci phyir zhe na /
NK117(she)001:24682: nyes pa 'phel zhing bskyed na de'i rgyu rkyen gang
NK117(she)001:24683: yang 'gog cing dge ba gong 'phel dang yon tan
NK117(she)001:24684: bskyed na bkag pa ltar yang gnang ba'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:24685: mdor na gnang bkag tshig gi lam kho na la
NK117(she)001:24686: gnas pa ma yin zhing gang zag gi dbang po'i
NK117(she)001:24687: mchog dman gyi rgyu dang 'brel nas grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24688: de yang tshogs lam du nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK117(she)001:24689: sbyor lam du dge ba chos sdud /
NK117(she)001:24690: mthong lam du sems can don byed gtso bor byed dgos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24692: pha rol phyin pa drug dang tshogs gnyis kyi //
NK117(she)001:24693: yonatana ma skyes skyed par byed pa dang //
NK117(she)001:24694: skyes pa spel la dge ba chos sdud kyi //
NK117(she)001:24695: tshul khrims zhes bya sems kyi bslab pas bsdus //
NK117(she)001:24696: byams dang snying rjes zin pa'i dge ba ni //
NK117(she)001:24697: gang du sems can don byed sbyin pa yin //
NK117(she)001:24698: de la rang 'dod med pa tshul khrims la //
NK117(she)001:24699: gzhan don skyo ngal med pa bzod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24700: lhag par spro bzhin 'jug pa brtson 'grus te //
NK117(she)001:24701: sems can don la rtse gcig bsam gtan dang //
NK117(she)001:24702: dngos mtshan zhen pa spangs pa shes rab ste //
NK117(she)001:24703: pha rol phyin drug nam yang 'du 'bral med //
NK117(she)001:24704: spyod lam rnam bzhi kun la dran shes ldan //
NK117(she)001:24705: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i dge tshogs kyi //
NK117(she)001:24706: gom pa'i 'degs 'jog dag kyang phyin drug lam //
NK117(she)001:24707: rtsol med 'jug pas tshogs rdzogs shin tu myur //
NK117(she)001:24708: zhes pa ni de yang pha rol tu phyin pa drug ni /
NK117(she)001:24709: sems can gyi don byed pa ni sbyin pa /
NK117(she)001:24710: de la rang 'dod kyi kun slong med pa tshul khrims /
NK117(she)001:24711: gzhan don sgrub pa la mi skyo ba bzod pa /
NK117(she)001:24713: de la mi g.yeng ba bsam gtan /
NK117(she)001:24714: de dag la dngos mtshan du mi 'dzin pa shes rab ste /
NK117(she)001:24715: de dag kyang don la mi sems pa ni sbyin pa /
NK117(she)001:24717: ci yang bye brag mi phyed pa ni bzod pa /
NK117(she)001:24718: blang dor med pa ni brtson 'grus /
NK117(she)001:24719: ma chags pa ni bsam gtan /
NK117(she)001:24720: mi gnyis pa ni shes rab bo //
NK117(she)001:24721: tshogs gnyis kyi rgyu bsod nams dang 'bras bu ye
NK117(she)001:24722: shes kyi yon tan ma skyes pa skyed par byed
NK117(she)001:24723: pa dang skyes pa spel ba la dge ba chos
NK117(she)001:24724: sdud kyi tshul khrims zhes bya ste sems kyi bslab
NK117(she)001:24726: byams dang snying rjes zin pa'i dge ba che phra
NK117(she)001:24727: gang yin kyang gang du sems can don byed kyi
NK117(she)001:24728: sbyin pa'o // de la rang 'dod med pa tshul
NK117(she)001:24729: khrims man chad nas pha rol phyin drug nam yang
NK117(she)001:24730: 'du 'bral med kyi bar rtsa ba ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:24731: spyod lam rnam bzhi ni za nyal 'gro 'chags gang
NK117(she)001:24732: gi skabs su'ang kun la dran pa dang shes bzhin
NK117(she)001:24733: ldan pa dang sgo gsum gyi spyod yul yongs su
NK117(she)001:24734: dag pa'i zhes byang chub sems kyis zin pa'i dge
NK117(she)001:24735: tshogs kyis gom pa'i 'degs 'jog dag kyang phar phyin
NK117(she)001:24736: drug gi lam du 'gro ba la 'bad rtsol gyis
NK117(she)001:24737: ngal ba med bzhin 'jug pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa
NK117(she)001:24739: phyin drug gi mi mthun phyogs sdug ni /
NK117(she)001:24740: khyad du gsod pa'i sems dang /
NK117(she)001:24741: le lo dang ldan pa'i sems /
NK117(she)001:24743: btsal bas yongs su skyo ba'i sems dang /
NK117(she)001:24744: bar chad dang ldan pa'i sems rnams dang bral ba ni gal che bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:24745: skabs 'dir spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i dge bar
NK117(she)001:24746: sdud pa'i tshul phal po che las gsungs pa 'grel
NK117(she)001:24747: chen du bkod pa la blta bar bya zhing /
NK117(she)001:24748: sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i sgo nas rang gi lus
NK117(she)001:24749: longs spyod dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas pa sems
NK117(she)001:24750: can thams cad la dngos sam brgyud nas gtong ba
NK117(she)001:24753: spel ba bzhis byang sems kyi sdom pa kun bsdu zhing /
NK117(she)001:24754: de yang las dang po dang /
NK117(she)001:24756: ma dag sa bdun la gnas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24757: dag pa sa gsum la gnas pa rnams rim gyis thob par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:24759: thabs la mkhas pas dngos sam brgyud ma nas //
NK117(she)001:24760: sems can kun la phan pa lhur byed cing //
NK117(she)001:24761: sbyin dang snyan smra don spyod don mthun dang //
NK117(she)001:24762: dge ba chos sdud tshul khrims sgo 'phar yangs //
NK117(she)001:24763: zhes pa ni gzhan don sgrub pa'i thabs la mkhas
NK117(she)001:24764: pas dngos sam brgyud ma nas sems can kun la
NK117(she)001:24765: nye ring cung zad kyang med pa phan pa kho
NK117(she)001:24766: na lhur byed cing mkho ba sbyin pa dang snyan
NK117(she)001:24767: par smra ba dang gdul bya'i don la spyod pa
NK117(she)001:24768: dang gzhan sgrub pa la bskul ba dang chos don
NK117(she)001:24769: dang mthun par bya ba rnams dge ba chos sdud
NK117(she)001:24770: kyi tshul khrims zhes spyod yul la khyad par med
NK117(she)001:24771: bzhin sgo 'phar mi dog la yangs zhes de nyid
NK117(she)001:24772: lhur byed cing gzhan phan kho nas de dag gi
NK117(she)001:24775: gang la brtag pa drug tu gsungs pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:24776: rang gi chos la 'byor rgud brtag par 'du //
NK117(she)001:24777: rang nyid chos lam ma nyams gzhan don bya //
NK117(she)001:24778: rang don nyams pa'i so skyes 'khrul pa brtag /
NK117(she)001:24779: ces pa ni sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims
NK117(she)001:24780: la gang la zhes de la brtag pa drug tu
NK117(she)001:24781: gsungs pa yin kyang rang gi chos la 'byor pa
NK117(she)001:24782: dang rgud pa brtag pa la don 'du ba'o //
NK117(she)001:24783: de yang rang nyid chos ma nyams bzhin du gzhan don ci nus bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:24784: rang don gyi chos sgrub pa las nyams pa'i so so'i skye bo'i 'khrul pa brtag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24785: bdag nyid kyi bslab pa'i gnas ma nyams bzhin gzhan phan rgya chen 'grub na de nyid gtsor bya /
NK117(she)001:24786: so skye dus su slar sems can gyi don 'grub
NK117(she)001:24787: pa'i ched du rang gi 'khrul pa bsam la shes
NK117(she)001:24788: rab kyis brtags nas nyams pa bsrung ba la gtso
NK117(she)001:24789: bor bya zhing snying rjes gzhan don yang zhar la
NK117(she)001:24790: bsgrub par bya ba nyid do //
NK117(she)001:24792: gzhan la phan pa rlabs chen 'grub srid na //
NK117(she)001:24793: bcas pa chung ngu bag yangs gnang ba'i skabs //
NK117(she)001:24794: yod de grong khyer phyir na grong brdal dang //
NK117(she)001:24795: bdag phyir sa gtong chos phyir bdag kyang gtong //
NK117(she)001:24796: zhes pa ni de yang don 'bras chung ngu'i phyir
NK117(she)001:24797: don chen po btang ba ma yin te gzhan la
NK117(she)001:24798: phan pa rlabs po che 'grub srid na bcas pa
NK117(she)001:24799: chung ngu bag yangs su gnang ba'i skabs yod de
NK117(she)001:24800: grong khyer la phan phyir grong rdal gtong ba dang
NK117(she)001:24801: / bdag gi phyir sa gtong zhing chos mi spang phyir bdag lus kyi gces 'dzin kyang gtong /
NK117(she)001:24802: don bsdu na tshul khrims gsum po la brten nas
NK117(she)001:24803: bslab gsum bsgrub cing spangs rtogs kyi 'bras bur sangs
NK117(she)001:24804: rgya ba ste / 'di ltar sdom pa'i tshul khrims
NK117(she)001:24805: kyis spangs pa phun sun tshogs pa sgrib gnyis bag
NK117(she)001:24806: chags dang bcas pa spong bar byed do //
NK117(she)001:24807: dge ba chos sdud kyis ni rtogs pa phun sun
NK117(she)001:24808: tshogs pa ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa mkhyen
NK117(she)001:24809: pa thob pa'o // sems can don byed kyis ni
NK117(she)001:24810: phrin las phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyu bsgrub cing don
NK117(she)001:24813: 'di na mi mjed bzod pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK117(she)001:24814: chos kyi dri bzang rgyas pa rab bsrung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:24815: dka' ba dang len bzod pa ji mi snyam //
NK117(she)001:24816: zab mo'i don la mi skrag rnam pa gsum //
NK117(she)001:24817: zhes pa ni tshe 'di'i snang ngo na mi mjed
NK117(she)001:24818: ces bzod pa sgom pa po dang bzod rgyu'i khro
NK117(she)001:24819: sdang gnyis mnyam pa nyid du gdal ba sa gzhi
NK117(she)001:24820: lta bu la dam pa'i chos kyi dri bzang rgyas
NK117(she)001:24821: pa lta bu rab tu bsrung ba'i dka' ba dang
NK117(she)001:24822: du len pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24823: gzhan gyis gnod pa la ci mi snyam pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24824: zab mo'i don la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa dang gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:24825: dang po ni rang don du sangs rgyas dang gzhan
NK117(she)001:24826: don du phan pa bsgrub pa gnyis car gyi don
NK117(she)001:24827: du dka' ba dang du len nus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24828: gnyis pa ni gzhan gyis bdag la dngos dang brgyud
NK117(she)001:24829: nas log sgrub dang gnod 'tshe ci ltar byas kyang
NK117(she)001:24832: chos la sems pa'i mos pa rkyen gang gis kyang
NK117(she)001:24833: mi 'phrogs shing zab mo'i don la mi skrag pa
NK117(she)001:24834: ni dmigs med kyi bzod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24836: yid ni shin tu rengs byas zhe sdang gi //
NK117(she)001:24837: sdig pa'i mngon rtogs mun pa'i 'khri shing can //
NK117(she)001:24838: thar med dmyal bar 'dzul la skrag pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:24839: nam yang khro ba'i go skabs dbye mi bgyid //
NK117(she)001:24840: ces pa ni 'di ltar tha mal rang rgyud ldan
NK117(she)001:24841: gyi yid ni ma zhi bas shin tu rengs pas
NK117(she)001:24842: byas pa'i zhe sdang gi sems sdig pa'i mngon rtogs
NK117(she)001:24843: mun pa'i 'khri shing 'khril ba lta bu can ni
NK117(she)001:24844: thar med dmyal bar 'dzul ba las 'os med pa
NK117(she)001:24845: dag la skrag pa skye ba'i blo gros can rnams
NK117(she)001:24846: ni / dus nam du'ang khro ba'i go skabs dbye bar mi bgyid ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24848: gnod pa'i yul ni nags kyi tsher ma bzhin //
NK117(she)001:24849: gdul gyis mi lang kun nas 'phel ba can //
NK117(she)001:24850: 'khon dang khro ba'i byed po gcig btul na //
NK117(she)001:24851: bzod pa'i dka' thub bdag la mdza' bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:24852: zhes pa ni rang nyid la gnod pa'i yul gang
NK117(she)001:24853: yin pa de ni dper na nags kyi tsher ma
NK117(she)001:24854: bgrangs yas bzhin 'dul bar brtsams kyang gdul gyis mi
NK117(she)001:24855: langs te phyir zhing kun nas 'phel ba can yin
NK117(she)001:24856: na / de bas rang nyid kyi 'khon sems dang
NK117(she)001:24857: khro ba'i byed po gcig ces pa bdag tu 'dzin
NK117(she)001:24858: pa 'di btul nus na bzod pa'i dka' thub de
NK117(she)001:24859: bdag la mdza' bshes bzhin du 'gyur te dper na
NK117(she)001:24860: sa steng kun ko bas g.yogs par mi ldang yang
NK117(she)001:24861: lham mthil gyi ko bas sa gzhi yod do cog
NK117(she)001:24862: g.yogs pa dang mtshungs te rang nyid bzod pa'i go
NK117(she)001:24863: cha dang ldan na dgra kun thub pa dang 'dra'o
NK117(she)001:24865: reg pa shin tu rtsub pa'i tshig gi mdas //
NK117(she)001:24866: skyes bu'i snying la zug pa cang mchi'am //
NK117(she)001:24867: de nyid dang du blang ba'i nyer len gyis //
NK117(she)001:24868: phan tshun rten dang brten par 'khrugs shing mnar //
NK117(she)001:24869: zhes pa reg pa shin tu rtsub pa gzugs kyis
NK117(she)001:24870: ma yin zhing dngos med tshig gi mdas zhes dpe
NK117(she)001:24871: sbyar nas de nyid skyes bu tshig rtsub brdeg yul
NK117(she)001:24872: gyi snying la zug pa ci yang 'dug gam zhib
NK117(she)001:24874: tshig dngos med de nyid dang du blangs nas bdag
NK117(she)001:24875: gir byas pa'i nyer len gyis phan chad kyi sems
NK117(she)001:24876: 'khrugs yul gzhan du gyur pa dang tshur ngos kyi
NK117(she)001:24877: rang gnyis rten dang brten par bcas pa 'khrugs shing
NK117(she)001:24878: mnar zhes sdug bsngal ba yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24880: 'di na gnod pa'i rgyu 'bras mtha' yas pa //
NK117(she)001:24881: bdag nyid las byung sgra dang brag cha bzhin //
NK117(she)001:24882: bdag nyid ma byung gnod pa'i yul med pas //
NK117(she)001:24883: rang gi sngon byas rkyen gyis bos la ltos //
NK117(she)001:24884: zhes pa de la da lta'i dus 'di na gnod
NK117(she)001:24885: pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu mtha' yas pa yang bdag
NK117(she)001:24886: nyid las byung zhing sgra grags rkyen gyis brag cha
NK117(she)001:24887: grags par 'khrul pa bzhin bdag nyid ma byung na
NK117(she)001:24888: gnod pa'i yul 'byung bzhi sogs la sems med pas
NK117(she)001:24889: de dag la phan gnod gang yang med pa bzhin
NK117(she)001:24890: rang bdag 'dzin dang bcas pa'i dbang gi sngon 'gro
NK117(she)001:24891: byas rkyen gyis bos pa lta bu la ltos dang
NK117(she)001:24893: gang zag bzod ldan ni phyi mar dgra med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:24895: bde ba dang yid mi bde ba mang bar mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:24896: 'gyod pa med bzhin dus byed par 'gyur ba /
NK117(she)001:24897: bde 'gro lha gnas su skye bar 'gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:24899: brtags na gnod chen ma yin phan chen te //
NK117(she)001:24900: gang la brten nas bzod pa'i gru gzings dang //
NK117(she)001:24901: byang chub sems kyi nor bu thob 'gyur na //
NK117(she)001:24902: de 'dra'i gnod pa dam pa'i chos ltar mchod //
NK117(she)001:24903: ces pa ni de yang khro sdang la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:24904: ma brtags tshe gnod pa chen po'i rgyu rkyen ltar
NK117(she)001:24905: 'dug kyang legs par brtags na de ltar ma yin
NK117(she)001:24906: te bzod pa bsgoms pa'i yul du phan chen du
NK117(she)001:24907: 'gyur te / gang la brten nas bzod pa'i brtul
NK117(she)001:24908: zhugs gru gzings lta bur zhugs te 'khor ba'i rgya
NK117(she)001:24909: mtsho brgal nas byang chub sems kyi nor bu nges
NK117(she)001:24911: de 'dra ba'i gnod pa byed mkhan su yang rung
NK117(she)001:24912: ste dam pa'i chos ltar mchod dgos pa'i dpe sngon
NK117(she)001:24913: jo bo rje khong khro shin tu che ba'i a
NK117(she)001:24914: tsa ra zhig g.yog tu khrid nas kho bos bzod
NK117(she)001:24915: pa'i rten du 'di ka shin tu dgos zhes pa
NK117(she)001:24917: shin tu brtags na gnod pa'i ngo bo la //
NK117(she)001:24918: mtshan nyid med de chu yi ri mo bzhin //
NK117(she)001:24919: rnam rtog khro gnyer rtsub mo zhig pa'i mod //
NK117(she)001:24920: mkha' bzhin rnam par stong la thob shor med //
NK117(she)001:24921: ces pa ni de la shin tu brtags na zhes
NK117(she)001:24922: sems nyid bdag med la bdag tu bzung zhing snang
NK117(she)001:24923: ba gzhan med la gzhan du bzung rkyen gyis phan
NK117(she)001:24924: gnod kyi rnam par shar ba yin gyi ngo ba
NK117(she)001:24925: la brtag tshe / mtshan nyid 'di 'dra zhes dngos
NK117(she)001:24926: por grub pa med de dper na chu la ri
NK117(she)001:24927: mo bris kyang 'phral mar rang dag la 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:24928: bzhin du rnam rtog khro ba'i mngon rtogs chu'i gnyer
NK117(she)001:24929: ma ltar zhig pa'i mod la khro sdang skye ba'i
NK117(she)001:24930: la brtag tshe / yul dang / khro mkhan bdag
NK117(she)001:24931: gnyis nam mkha' bzhin du rnam par stong par gyur
NK117(she)001:24932: tshe thob pa dang shor ba'i tha snyad las 'das
NK117(she)001:24933: la brtag tshe / yul dang / pa'o // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:24934: gang zhig bzod pa'i dka' thub gsum nyams na //
NK117(she)001:24935: sbyin sogs pha rol phyin pa gzhan lnga yang //
NK117(she)001:24936: phyi mtha' dgra yis bskor ba'i bshul lam bzhin //
NK117(she)001:24937: 'dod pa'i gnas su phyin dka' blo stobs bskyed //
NK117(she)001:24938: ces pa ni gang ci'i phyir na bzod pa'i dka' thub gsum ni chos phyir dka' spyod bzod pa /
NK117(she)001:24939: gzhan gyi gnod pa la ci mi snyam pa'i bzod pa /
NK117(she)001:24940: zab mo'i don la mi skrag pa'i bzod pa ste /
NK117(she)001:24941: rnam pa gsum po de nyams par gyur na /
NK117(she)001:24942: sbyin pa la sogs pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa
NK117(she)001:24943: gzhan lnga po yang phyi mtha' dgras bskor ba'i bshul
NK117(she)001:24944: lam bzhin du nye zho med pa zhig dka' zhing
NK117(she)001:24945: thar pa dang rnam mkhyen gyi gnas su phyin dka'
NK117(she)001:24946: bas byang chub mchog tu blo stobs chen po bskyed
NK117(she)001:24947: par bya ba gal chen du gsungs pa yang /
NK117(she)001:24948: bcom ldan 'das kyis khong khros ni bskal pa stong
NK117(she)001:24949: du bsags pa'i bsod nams 'joms par byed cing rang
NK117(she)001:24950: gzhan gnyis ka'i dge rtsa bsreg par 'gyur bas na
NK117(she)001:24951: zhe sdang zhing khong khro ba spang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:24953: dus las yol ba med pa'i brtson 'grus kyi //
NK117(she)001:24954: rang dbang nyid du dge ba'i chos mtha' dag /
NK117(she)001:24955: skyed mos tshal du ngang pa 'gro ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:24956: le lo'i g.yang la bskyud pa med par 'jug /
NK117(she)001:24957: ces pa ni dge ba sgrub pa'i blo nam skyes
NK117(she)001:24958: tshe dus de las shol 'gyangs sogs kyis yol ba
NK117(she)001:24959: med pa'i brtson pa lhur len zhing kha tsam ma
NK117(she)001:24960: yin par snying nas 'grus stobs kyi rang dbang nyid
NK117(she)001:24961: du dge ba'i chos mtha' ma bkag pa dag la
NK117(she)001:24962: spyod pa'i dpe skyed mos tshal du ngang pa dga'
NK117(she)001:24963: spro'i blos 'gro ba'am 'jug pa bzhin du /
NK117(she)001:24964: le lo zhes bag med spyod pas bar chad kyi
NK117(she)001:24965: g.yang sa la bskyud pa med par te dge blo
NK117(she)001:24966: brjed pa med par 'jug ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:24968: bya ba ngan na 'du 'dzi'i thag pas dkris //
NK117(she)001:24969: sgyid lug mthus non sbyor bas nus pa'ang btang //
NK117(she)001:24970: bdag nyid brnyas nas sems zhum brtul zhugs blangs //
NK117(she)001:24971: de 'dra'i gang zag nyes pa'i gzings la zhon //
NK117(she)001:24972: zhes pa ni de la le lo dang snyom las
NK117(she)001:24973: kyis phyin drug gi blang dor 'dzol ba la bya
NK117(she)001:24974: ba ngan zhen dang 'du 'dzi ni 'jig rten gyi
NK117(she)001:24975: bya las sna tshogs kyi thag pas dkris pa ltar
NK117(she)001:24976: gyur zhing rnam dkar sgrub rgyu khur du song skyon
NK117(she)001:24977: gyis 'di ltar mi nus so snyam nas sgyid lug
NK117(she)001:24978: pa'i mthus non nas sbyor ba'i brtson 'grus kyi nus
NK117(she)001:24979: pa'ang btang zhing bdag nyid kyis byang chub bsgrub mi
NK117(she)001:24980: nus snyam bzhin brnyas nas sems zhum pa'i brtul zhugs
NK117(she)001:24981: dang du blangs shing theg dman la zhugs pa'ang tha
NK117(she)001:24982: mal du sdod pa gang yang rung ste de 'dra'i
NK117(she)001:24983: gang zag de ni nyes pa'i gzings la zhon zhes
NK117(she)001:24986: bdud bzhi 'joms pa go cha'i brtson 'grus dang //
NK117(she)001:24987: sa bcu'i lam 'gro sbyor ba'i brtson 'grus dang //
NK117(she)001:24988: mi 'gong mi ldog chog shes med pa yi //
NK117(she)001:24989: brtson 'grus can gyis smon pa'i don kun 'grub //
NK117(she)001:24990: ces pa ni de yang lha'i bu'i bdud 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:24991: chos brgyad kyi dbang du gyur nas phyi ma'i don
NK117(she)001:24993: nyon mongs pa dug lnga dang dug gsum sogs brgyad
NK117(she)001:24994: khri bzhi stong gis rnam par g.yengs nas sems rnal
NK117(she)001:24996: rang nyid kyi phung po lnga la bdag tu bzung
NK117(she)001:24997: bas bde sdug dang re dogs kyi dbang du gyur
NK117(she)001:24998: pa dang / chos sgrub blo tsam zhig yod kyang
NK117(she)001:24999: 'dod pa thog tu ma khel bar le los bar
NK117(she)001:25000: du bcad nas lnga lam du zhugs pa rnams 'joms
NK117(she)001:25001: par byed pa go cha'i brtson 'grus dang /
NK117(she)001:25002: sa bcu'i lam bgrod par byed pa la sbyor ba'i brtson 'grus /
NK117(she)001:25003: sems can gyi don sgrub dka' ba thog tu bab
NK117(she)001:25004: tshe mi 'gong zhes pa de nyid bzhag nas rang
NK117(she)001:25005: gi nus tshod tsam la mi 'jug cing dka' ba
NK117(she)001:25006: dang du blang ngal ba khyad du gsod dgos pa
NK117(she)001:25007: dang mi ldog ces pa yang 'gro don bgyid dka'
NK117(she)001:25008: ba dang 'phrad tshe skyo sun gyis rang don bsgrub
NK117(she)001:25009: pa la 'jug pa rnams skyon yin pa ngos bzung
NK117(she)001:25010: nas / chog shes med pa zhes tshe rabs nas
NK117(she)001:25011: tshe rabs bskal pa nas bskal pa'i bar du rang
NK117(she)001:25012: don yid la mi 'gyu bar gzhan don sgrub pa
NK117(she)001:25013: la lhod pa bral ba'i brtson 'grus can gang su
NK117(she)001:25014: yang rung ba rnams kyis ji ltar smon pa'i don
NK117(she)001:25016: phar phyin lam ni lus srog yang yang gtong dgos
NK117(she)001:25017: pa dang de las ldog mi rung ba sogs kyi
NK117(she)001:25018: skrag mod kyang gang zag yang rang rang gi blo
NK117(she)001:25019: stobs dang bstun nas rim pas goms su 'jug dgos
NK117(she)001:25020: par gsungs shing brtson 'grus gal shin tu che dgos
NK117(she)001:25021: pa yang 'byon 'gyur gyi rgyal ba byams pas ston
NK117(she)001:25022: pa'i sngon du sems bskyed kyang brtson 'grus la khyad
NK117(she)001:25023: zhugs nas sngon du zas gtsang sras po sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:25024: pa bzhin brtson 'grus stobs bskyed par gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:25026: bdag gi tshe ni nyin mo'i mthar gyur te //
NK117(she)001:25027: myur ba myur bar 'chi ba'i mun nag gis //
NK117(she)001:25028: gtugs na 'khor ba'i spyod pa rgyu skar las //
