NK117(she)001:25029: rnam grangs mang ba de yi dbugs mi phyin //
NK117(she)001:25030: zhes pa ni 'di ltar 'gro ba'i tshe ni nyi
NK117(she)001:25031: ma nub kha lta bu'i mthar gyur te myur bar
NK117(she)001:25032: myur bar 'chi ba'i mngon rtogs mun nag gis gtugs
NK117(she)001:25033: par gyur na 'khor ba'i spyod pa rgyu skar las
NK117(she)001:25034: grangs mang ba de yis dbugs mi phyin zhes gtan
NK117(she)001:25035: bde ster mi nus pa'i smad tshig go //
NK117(she)001:25036: der ma zad lus kyi nyes skyon rgyal po gsal
NK117(she)001:25037: rgyal la gsungs pa 'di ltar mi rtag pa mi
NK117(she)001:25038: brtan pa yid brtan du mi rung ba sogs mang
NK117(she)001:25039: du gsungs mthar brtson 'grus kyi mi mthun phyogs le
NK117(she)001:25040: lo'i gnyen por mi rtag pa dran dgos pa man
NK117(she)001:25041: ngag gi dam pa yin par bstan to //
NK117(she)001:25043: le lo'i rnyog pa dwangs pa'i brtson 'grus kyi //
NK117(she)001:25044: dal 'bab phyogs lhung ston pa ma yin par //
NK117(she)001:25045: rnam pa kun mkhyen rgya mtshor phyin de srid //
NK117(she)001:25046: g.yo zhing myur ba'i brtul zhugs nyams mi bgyid //
NK117(she)001:25047: ces pa ni de la chu klung ni rnyog pa'i
NK117(she)001:25048: dris bslad bzhin brtson 'grus kyi 'gal zla le lo
NK117(she)001:25049: yin pas de lta'i skyon dang bral ba'i brtson 'grus
NK117(she)001:25050: lhod pa med pa'i dpe'i dal 'bab ste chu klung
NK117(she)001:25051: chen po phyogs ga shed nas 'gog tu yod pa
NK117(she)001:25052: ston pa ma yin par rnam pa kun mkhyen sangs
NK117(she)001:25053: rgyas kyi go 'phang rgya mtsho lta bur ma phyin
NK117(she)001:25055: chu klung de nyid g.yo zhing myur ba'i brtul zhugs
NK117(she)001:25056: las mi nyams pa ltar bdag kyang brtson 'grus nyams
NK117(she)001:25059: brtson 'grus ni sde tshan gcig par bzhag kyang don
NK117(she)001:25060: la pha rol tu phyin pa drug gi grogs yin
NK117(she)001:25061: pas de med na gzhan rnams kyang nyams pa'i skyon
NK117(she)001:25062: du 'gyur zhing de dang ldan na drug po mthar
NK117(she)001:25064: bsam gtan gyi sngon du gnas kyi yon tan bshad pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25066: nags tshal me tog 'khrigs pa'i sman ljongs ni //
NK117(she)001:25067: ngang pa shin tu zhi bas brten byas shing //
NK117(she)001:25068: blta na sdug pa brag ri'i pha gu dang //
NK117(she)001:25069: rta babs ri dwags gzhon nus mdzes pa yod //
NK117(she)001:25070: ces pa ni bsam gtan bsgom yul gyi gnas khyim sogs brel g.yengs che ba ma yin te /
NK117(she)001:25071: nags tshal me tog 'khrigs pa'i sman ljongs sogs ni
NK117(she)001:25072: ngang pa rtsub spyod dang bral zhing shin tu zhi
NK117(she)001:25073: bas brten par byas shing der blta na sdug pa
NK117(she)001:25074: brag ri'i pha gu dang rta babs ri dwags gzhon
NK117(she)001:25075: nus mdzes par byas pa rang byung lhun grub kyi
NK117(she)001:25076: tshul du yod cing der ma zad //
NK117(she)001:25078: dga' ba'i nags tshal lha mo'i rked chings ni //
NK117(she)001:25079: shing bal gzhon nu'i dra phyed g.yo ba na //
NK117(she)001:25080: dogs pas skrags pa min pa'i khu byug rnams //
NK117(she)001:25081: 'khor bar skyo ba'i gtam gyi spring yig 'grem //
NK117(she)001:25082: zhes pa de yang shin tu nyams dga' ba'i nams
NK117(she)001:25083: tshal lha mo'i rked chings lta bu ni shing bal
NK117(she)001:25084: gzhon nu'i dra phyed g.yo ba na /
NK117(she)001:25085: 'jigs skrag gi dogs nas sngar skad 'byin pa lta
NK117(she)001:25086: bu ma yin pa'i khu byug rnams ni 'khor bar
NK117(she)001:25087: skyo ba'i gtam gyi spring yig 'grem pa lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:25088: nges 'byung gi bskul ma 'debs pa'i grogs byed pa
NK117(she)001:25090: de lta bu'i gnas su 'gro bar bskul ba ni /
NK117(she)001:25092: de ru gshegs shig bsam gtan 'dod pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:25093: longs spyod sprin gyi bla re'i nang shed na //
NK117(she)001:25094: tshe srog rol pa'i glog ni g.yo zhing 'dar //
NK117(she)001:25095: 'gyur dang sdug bsngal 'du byed chom rkun dkyu //
NK117(she)001:25096: phung krol bskyed pa'i chu klung ca co can //
NK117(she)001:25097: gsog dang bsrung dang spel ba'i 'dod pas 'khrugs //
NK117(she)001:25098: khengs dang 'jungs dang ser snas tshe gtugs nas //
NK117(she)001:25099: ngan 'gro'i chu gter mu mtha' med par 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:25100: zhes pa ni gnas dben pa de lta bu ru
NK117(she)001:25101: gshegs shig bsam gtan sgom du 'dod pa khyed rnams
NK117(she)001:25103: de ltar ma yin pas 'jig rten chos brgyad kyis
NK117(she)001:25104: bskrun pa'i longs spyod sprin gyi bla re bres pa
NK117(she)001:25105: lta bu'i nang shed na tshe srog mi rtag cing
NK117(she)001:25106: 'gyur sla ba'i dpe rol pa'i glog ni g.yo zhing
NK117(she)001:25108: 'gyur ba dang sdug bsngal dang 'du byed gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:25109: chom rkun dkyu zhes pa glags blta zhing skabs tshol
NK117(she)001:25110: bas phung dkrol bskyed pa'i dpe chu klung ca co
NK117(she)001:25111: can gyi 'gram du bsti ba'i rna ba rgyun du
NK117(she)001:25112: gtser ba bzhin / nor rdzas gsog pa dang de
NK117(she)001:25113: nyid bsrung zhing spel bar dka' bas 'dod pas sems
NK117(she)001:25114: 'khrugs pa dang 'byor pas khengs shing mchod sbyin la
NK117(she)001:25115: 'jungs pa dang ser snas mi tshe zad par byas
NK117(she)001:25116: pa la gtugs na zhes ngan 'gro'i chu gter mu
NK117(she)001:25117: mtha' med par 'khyams pa'i rgyur 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:25120: g.yo sgyu'i char sprin gnag pa'i rin thang can //
NK117(she)001:25121: nor ni ji tsam 'byor bzhin sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK117(she)001:25122: yo byad bsnyungs rnams dgra rkun 'tshe bas spong //
NK117(she)001:25123: chog shes thob pa 'byor pa'i rtse mor 'gro //
NK117(she)001:25124: zhes pa ni de yang g.yo ni kha zhe mi
NK117(she)001:25125: mtshungs pa'i sems gya gyu ba can yin la sgyu
NK117(she)001:25126: ni gzhan bslu ba'i bsam pa kho na ste de
NK117(she)001:25127: gnyis kyis bsgrubs pa'i zas nor ni rnam smin char
NK117(she)001:25128: sprin ltar gnag cing sdig sdug gi rin thang shin
NK117(she)001:25129: tu che ba can yin pas de lta bu'i nor
NK117(she)001:25130: de ni ci tsam 'byor bzhin sdug bsngal bskyed pa'i
NK117(she)001:25132: yo byad bsnyungs rnams te zas nor nyung ngu las
NK117(she)001:25133: med na dgra rkun gyis 'tshe bas spong zhing chog
NK117(she)001:25134: shes thob pa ni 'byor pa phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:25137: so so'i skye bo'i rang bzhin byis pa ste //
NK117(she)001:25138: byis pa rnams ni nyes pa'i sprin gyis 'khrigs //
NK117(she)001:25139: bdag nyid bstod cing gzhan la mi snyan sgrog /
NK117(she)001:25140: nyon mongs sbrul lce rtsub mo'i nyam bag bsten //
NK117(she)001:25141: dpal 'byor g.yo ba gang la'ang rtag par sems //
NK117(she)001:25142: byas pa mi gzo mgu ba'i gzugs brnyan 'khyog /'khon gyi me lce phra ma'i rlung gis bskyod //
NK117(she)001:25143: spre'u bzhin du gnod pa sna tshogs ster //
NK117(she)001:25144: chu srin bzhin du sdig pa'i lto ba yangs //
NK117(she)001:25145: sbrul gdug bzhin du su dang phrad pa 'joms //
NK117(she)001:25146: me bzhin dge ba'i ljon shing bsreg 'gyur ba'i //
NK117(she)001:25147: byis pa'i grogs las ring du bsring bar bya //
NK117(she)001:25148: zhes pa ni de la so so'i skye bo ste
NK117(she)001:25149: 'phags pa ma yin pa'i rigs rnams ni bgrang bya
NK117(she)001:25151: de lta bu'i byis pa'i sems ldan gyi rgan gzhon
NK117(she)001:25152: su yang rung ste de dag gi bsam spyod ni
NK117(she)001:25153: nyes skyon gyi sprin gyis 'khrigs shing bdag bstod cing
NK117(she)001:25154: gzhan dag smod pa la sogs mi snyan pa sgrog
NK117(she)001:25155: pa dang / nyon mongs kyi sgo nas sbrul lce
NK117(she)001:25156: rtsub mo'i nyam zhes bsam ngan gyi bag ste dri
NK117(she)001:25157: mas bgos shing dpal 'byor mi rtag cing g.yo ba
NK117(she)001:25158: sogs gang la'ang rnam par sems pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25159: phan btags pa la byas pa mi gzo zhing mgu
NK117(she)001:25160: dka' bas bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan 'khyog por ston pa
NK117(she)001:25161: dang / rang phyogs gzhan phyogs gang yang rung ste
NK117(she)001:25162: bsam ngan gyi me phra ma'i rlung gis bskyod nas
NK117(she)001:25164: de yang spyod lam dang rnam 'gyur mi brtan te
NK117(she)001:25165: spre'u bzhin du gnod pa sna tshogs ster ba dang
NK117(she)001:25166: / srog gcod la sogs la cang mi sems pa
NK117(she)001:25167: chu srin bzhin du sdig pa'i lto ba yangs pa
NK117(she)001:25168: mi dge ba'i las la cung zad kyang mi 'dzems
NK117(she)001:25169: / shing // dug sbrul gdug pa can su dang
NK117(she)001:25170: 'phrad kyang 'joms pa ltar dgra gnyen su yang phung
NK117(she)001:25171: du 'jug cing me bzhin dge ba'i ljon shing gzhan
NK117(she)001:25172: gyi gsos su gyur pa yang bsreg par 'gyur ba'i
NK117(she)001:25173: byis pa'i grogs rnam dkar gyi bar chod byed cing
NK117(she)001:25174: rang dbang 'phrog pa'i rigs su yang ring du bsring
NK117(she)001:25177: yul ni drug las thu ste rnam smin rtsub //
NK117(she)001:25178: spyad pa'i mod la bda' ba'i ro bro yang //
NK117(she)001:25179: tshe rabs gcig min skye ba thams cad du //
NK117(she)001:25180: gsang sngags mchog dang sman gyis gsor mi rung //
NK117(she)001:25181: gang zhig sems kyi glang po ma dul bar //
NK117(she)001:25182: bslu ba'i rdzu 'phrul yul las che ba med //
NK117(she)001:25183: phung po'i 'du byed khyogs la bzhag de srid //
NK117(she)001:25184: zhi ba'i nags mthongs dag la bsnyen par mdzod //
NK117(she)001:25185: ces pa ni tshogs drug gi yul du gyur pa
NK117(she)001:25186: rnams ni chags sdang rmongs gsum kho na skyed byed
NK117(she)001:25187: kyi rgyu yin pas btsan dug las kyang thu ste
NK117(she)001:25188: mthong chos su rnam smin rtsub mo mi mngon zhing
NK117(she)001:25189: / spyad pa'i mod la bda' ba'i ro bro ba
NK117(she)001:25190: ltar snang yang tshe rabs gcig kho na tsam min
NK117(she)001:25191: zhing skye ba thams cad du gsang sngags mchog dang
NK117(she)001:25192: sman dpyad sogs kyis gsor mi rung na /
NK117(she)001:25193: gang zhig sems kyi glang po che rlangs po'i spyod
NK117(she)001:25194: pa dang ma bral ba 'di ma dul gyi bar
NK117(she)001:25195: du bslu ba'i rdzu 'phrul yul drug las che ba
NK117(she)001:25196: med phyir gzugs tshor ba 'du shes sogs kyi phung
NK117(she)001:25197: po'i 'du byed khyogs la bzhag pa de srid du
NK117(she)001:25198: rtog tshogs zhi ba'i nags mthongs sogs dben pa dag
NK117(she)001:25199: la brten par mdzod ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25201: bas mtha' 'brog ni yid 'ong skyo shas 'phel //
NK117(she)001:25202: tshong dang so nam sdig pa'i grogs kyis spangs //
NK117(she)001:25203: dpya dang khral dang zho shas 'tshos mi gdung //
NK117(she)001:25204: bya dang ri dwags mi snyan sgrog pa med //
NK117(she)001:25205: chu gtsang 'bras bu'i nyer spyod rgya che la //
NK117(she)001:25206: brag ri'i phug dang lo ma'i khang bzang yangs //
NK117(she)001:25207: ljon pa'i grib bsil 'grogs na bde ba dang //
NK117(she)001:25208: nam zhig bdag ni lhan cig gnas 'gyur bsam //
NK117(she)001:25209: zhes pa ni de la grong zad pa'i mur thug
NK117(she)001:25210: pa la bas mtha' dang 'brog dgon pa ni grong
NK117(she)001:25211: pa las bral ba'i rgyang grags tsam gyi sa la
NK117(she)001:25213: de lta bu'i gnas ni yid du 'ong zhing skyo shas 'phel ba dang /
NK117(she)001:25214: tshong dang so nam dang sdig pa'i grogs po rnams
NK117(she)001:25215: kyis spangs shing dpya dang khral 'dus sogs lus bkol
NK117(she)001:25216: ba'i zho shas 'tsho bas mi gdung zhing bya dang
NK117(she)001:25217: ri dwags sogs kyis mi snyan pa sgrog pa med
NK117(she)001:25218: cing chu gtsang dang 'bras bu sogs nyer spyod rgya
NK117(she)001:25219: che la brag ri'i phug pa dang lo ma'i khang
NK117(she)001:25220: bzang yangs shing ljon pa'i grib bsil 'grogs na bde
NK117(she)001:25221: ba dang nam zhig bdag ni lhan cig gnas par
NK117(she)001:25224: de na dus bzhi'i mgron po gsar pa yis //
NK117(she)001:25225: 'pho 'gyur mngon rtogs ngom pa'i nags tshal rnams //
NK117(she)001:25226: rang nyid nyon mongs ma yin gtan tshigs su //
NK117(she)001:25227: gom bdun phyogs pa'i bsod nams sgrog la ltos //
NK117(she)001:25228: zhes pa ni 'du 'dzis dben pa'i gnas de na
NK117(she)001:25229: dus bzhi ste dbyar dgun ston dpyid bzhi'i mgron po
NK117(she)001:25230: gsar pa'i 'pho 'gyur gyi mngon rtogs ngom pa'i nags
NK117(she)001:25231: tshal rnams ni rang nyid nyon mongs 'phel ba'i gnas
NK117(she)001:25232: ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs su dgon par gom bdun
NK117(she)001:25233: phyogs pa'i bsod nams mdo rgyud man ngag kun nas
NK117(she)001:25234: sgrog pa la ltos la der gshegs nas sgrub la
NK117(she)001:25235: brtson na phan yon rnams thob bo //
NK117(she)001:25238: gang du bsam gtan shin tu brtan pa ni //
NK117(she)001:25239: lhag pa sems kyi bslab pa'i mtshan nyid de //
NK117(she)001:25240: rten cing 'brel 'byung lus kyi cho ga ni //
NK117(she)001:25241: rnam snang chos bdun sems kyi srog shing can //
NK117(she)001:25242: gcig las gnyis pa min pa'i mnyam bzhag brtson //
NK117(she)001:25243: dmigs pa gang yang rung ba'i 'dzin dpyad kyis //
NK117(she)001:25244: yid ni dge ba'i don la rnam par bcing //
NK117(she)001:25245: spros pa'i snang ba chos nyid gcig tu nub //
NK117(she)001:25246: snang yul ma 'gags der 'dzin med pa yin //
NK117(she)001:25247: shes pa yul la mi rtog mnyam bzhag la //
NK117(she)001:25248: ngo bo gcig pa'i rjes thob lhag mthong ste //
NK117(she)001:25249: zhes pa ni gong du bstan pa'i dben gnas gang
NK117(she)001:25250: du bsam gtan te ting nge 'dzin shin tu brtan
NK117(she)001:25251: par gyur pa ni lhag pa sems kyi bslab pa'i
NK117(she)001:25252: mtshan nyid yin te 'di ltar rten cing 'brel bar
NK117(she)001:25253: 'byung ba'i lus kyi sdod tshul gyi cho ga ni
NK117(she)001:25254: / rkang pa rdo rje'i skyil krung lag gnyis mnyam
NK117(she)001:25255: bzhag sogs rnam snang chos bdun la sems kyi srog
NK117(she)001:25256: shing can ni gcig las gnyis pa min pa'i mnyam
NK117(she)001:25257: bzhag la rtag par brtson zhing dmigs pa gang yang
NK117(she)001:25258: rung ba la ma yengs pa'i 'dzin dpyad kyis lus
NK117(she)001:25259: dang ngag dang yid ni dge ba'i don la rnam
NK117(she)001:25260: par bcings shing spros pa'i snang ba tshogs drug gi
NK117(she)001:25261: yul du gyur pa thams cad chos nyid gcig tu
NK117(she)001:25262: nub cing snang ba'i yul tshogs ma 'gags kyang der
NK117(she)001:25263: / 'dzin med pa'o // de yang bsgrub gzhi ni
NK117(she)001:25264: sems yin te de'i rang bzhin ni dkon brtsegs las
NK117(she)001:25265: 'od srungs sems ni yongs su btsal na mi rnyed
NK117(she)001:25266: / 'dzin med pa'o // do // gang ma rnyed pa de ni mi dmigs so //
NK117(she)001:25267: gang mi dmigs pa de ni 'das ma 'ongs da lta gsum sogs gang ci yang ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:25268: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyas 'grel las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:25270: dbye na byis pa nyer spyod don rab 'byed //
NK117(she)001:25271: de bzhin gshegs daka'i bsam gtan rnam gsum las //
NK117(she)001:25272: rtog dpyod yod med mu bzhi'i bsam gtan bzhi //
NK117(she)001:25273: de bzhin gzugs med bzhi ste rnam pa'i grangs //
NK117(she)001:25274: lam ma zhugs pa'i rgyud kyi ting 'dzin ni //
NK117(she)001:25275: bsam gtan gzugs med byis pa nyer spyod yin //
NK117(she)001:25276: lam zhugs tshogs dang sbyor ba'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK117(she)001:25277: thar lam mngon byed don rab 'byed par grags //
NK117(she)001:25278: dang po'i sa yin 'phags pa'i ting 'dzin te //
NK117(she)001:25279: zag pa med pas de bzhin gshegs dge yin //
NK117(she)001:25280: zhes pa ni de yang bsam gtan la dbye na
NK117(she)001:25281: byis pa nyer spyod ni lam du ma zhugs pa'i
NK117(she)001:25282: rgyud kyi ting nge 'dzin bsam gtan dang gzugs med
NK117(she)001:25283: pa rnams la yod de 'jig rten pa'i lam mo
NK117(she)001:25284: // don rab 'byed pa ni lam zhugs tshogs sbyor
NK117(she)001:25285: gyi ting nge 'dzin gyis thar lam mngon du byed
NK117(she)001:25286: // pa'o // de bzhin gshegs dge ni sa dang
NK117(she)001:25287: po yan chad 'phags pa'i rgyud kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK117(she)001:25289: de lta'i bsam gtan rnam pa gsum la'ang /
NK117(she)001:25291: kun kyang ngo bo nang du sems 'dzin la //
NK117(she)001:25292: rgyu ni dran pa rgyun chags brtson 'grus can //
NK117(she)001:25293: rnam par g.yeng na slar yang de la bslan //
NK117(she)001:25294: byed las bde ba bskyed cing rdzu 'phrul 'grub //
NK117(she)001:25295: 'bras bu mngon shes la sogs thob pa yin //
NK117(she)001:25296: zhes pa ni de la bsam gtan gyi ngo bo
NK117(she)001:25297: ni sems nang du rtse gcig tu gnas pa dran
NK117(she)001:25298: pas rgyun du bskyangs shing brtson 'grus kyi rkyen la
NK117(she)001:25300: rnam pa ste phyi'i snang ba dang nang gi rnam
NK117(she)001:25301: rtog gis kha khrid de g.yeng na slar yang dran
NK117(she)001:25302: shes kyi 'dzin pa mi lhod cing slar yang de
NK117(she)001:25303: la ste sngar gyi bsam gtan la bslan par byed
NK117(she)001:25304: pa'o // de ltar 'bad pas byed las kyis gnas
NK117(she)001:25305: skabs su sgo gsum la bde ba bskyed cing rdzu
NK117(she)001:25307: mthar thug 'bras bu mngon shes thob par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25308: de lta bu'i bsam gtan gyi gegs su che ba rnams spang dgos te /
NK117(she)001:25309: las su bya ba'i dngos po la dga' zhing chags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25310: bre mo'i gtam dang gnyid dang zang zing tshol ba /
NK117(she)001:25311: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya rnams la rtog dpyod dang bcas te dga' zhing chags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25312: de dag rnams spangs nas sems mi g.yeng ba'i thabs
NK117(she)001:25313: la 'bungs nas thun mong gi bsam gtan bsgrub par
NK117(she)001:25315: bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdogs rtog cing dpyod //
NK117(she)001:25316: dngos gzhi rtog pa med la dpyod pa tsam //
NK117(she)001:25317: lhag ma gsum por rtog dpyod gnyis ka med //
NK117(she)001:25318: snga ma snga mas phyi ma'i nyer bsdogs byed //
NK117(she)001:25319: 'phags pa'i lam gyi brten gzhi zhes su grags //
NK117(she)001:25320: zhes pa ni de yang gzugs dang gzugs med la
NK117(she)001:25321: spyod pa gnyis las dang po ni slob pa dang
NK117(she)001:25322: so so skye bo rnams kyi bsam gtan bzhi dang
NK117(she)001:25323: de'i nyer bsdogs de la snyoms 'jug rnams kyang /
NK117(she)001:25324: smon sems dang bcas pa ma yin pas srid pa'i rgyu btang snyoms kyi tshor ba dang /
NK117(she)001:25325: de la 'di ltar ro snyam pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25326: de la yang dpyod par byed pa bcas bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdogs te sta gon yin no //
NK117(she)001:25327: de yang 'dod sred dang sdig chos las 'das shing /
NK117(she)001:25329: dga' bde nyams su myong ba ni bsam gtan dang
NK117(she)001:25330: po dang de nyid la 'di ltar ro snyam pa'i
NK117(she)001:25332: yid dpyod yod pa bsam gtan dang po'i sems khyad par can no //
NK117(she)001:25333: de yang rtog dpyod gnyis kar bral zhing sngon ma'i
NK117(she)001:25334: sred zhen dang mi ldan yang dga' bde dang yongs
NK117(she)001:25335: su dang bar gyur pa ni bsam gtan gnyis pa'o
NK117(she)001:25336: // bsam gtan gnyis pa'i sred zhen dang bral nas bde ba dang /
NK117(she)001:25338: dran shes dang ma bral ba la bsam gtan gsum pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25339: yang bsam gtan gsum pa'i sred zhen dang bral nas
NK117(she)001:25340: bde sdug gnyis ka'i rtog dpyod bral bzhin dran shes
NK117(she)001:25341: dang ldan par gyur pa la bsam gtan bzhi pa'o
NK117(she)001:25342: // bsam gtan phyi ma phyi ma'i nyer bsdogs snga ma snga mas byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25343: de bzhin du gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:25344: 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug dgu po ni 'phags pa'i lam gyi rten gzhi tsam yin no //
NK117(she)001:25346: yon tan thams cad bskyed pa'i bsam gtan ni //
NK117(she)001:25347: snying rje dang ni ye shes dam pas zin //
NK117(she)001:25348: ting 'dzin mang ldan rnam pa thams cad bsgrub //
NK117(she)001:25349: blo rdzas gcig pa'i mnyam rjes gzung 'dzin spong //
NK117(she)001:25350: mnyam gzhag las langs rjes thob rgya yan pa //
NK117(she)001:25351: sa bdun tshun chad kun na yod pa yin //
NK117(she)001:25352: zhes pa de yang theg pa chen po'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:25353: thams cad bskyed pa'i bsam gtan ni snying rje dang
NK117(she)001:25354: ni ye shes dam pas zin bzhin ting nge 'dzin
NK117(she)001:25355: mang po dang ldan zhing rnam pa thams cad bsgrub
NK117(she)001:25356: pa dang / blo rdzas gcig pa'i mnyam gzhag dang
NK117(she)001:25357: rjes thob gnyis su bzung ba dang 'dzin pa spong
NK117(she)001:25358: zhing mnyam gzhag las langs tshe rjes thob rgya yan
NK117(she)001:25359: pa ste dran yengs kyi dbye ba sa bdun tshun
NK117(she)001:25360: chad kun na yod par bstan to //
NK117(she)001:25361: de yang ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo thams cad zhi
NK117(she)001:25362: lhag zung 'brel gyis bsdus phyir zhi gnas brtan par
NK117(she)001:25363: ma gyur pa'i lhag mthong ni rlung gseb kyi mar
NK117(she)001:25365: lhag mthong med pa'i zhi gnas rkyang pas sgrib pa
NK117(she)001:25366: mtha' dag gcod mi nus shing bsam gtan bzhi dang
NK117(she)001:25367: gzugs med kyi zhi gnas kyis srid rtser 'khor ba
NK117(she)001:25368: bzhin no // de la zhi gnas rnam rtog gi rlung gis sems g.yo ba 'gags par byed la /
NK117(she)001:25369: lhag mthong gis ni rmongs pa dang 'jigs tshogs la
NK117(she)001:25370: blta ba sogs phas rgol gyi lta ngan pa rnams
NK117(she)001:25371: gnon par byed cing grub mtha' ngan pa dang lung
NK117(she)001:25372: ma bstan gyis bardzi bar mi nus so //
NK117(she)001:25373: de yang nyan thos rnams ni ting nge 'dzin shas che la shes rab chung ngo //
NK117(she)001:25374: byang chub sems dpa' ni de las ldog cing sangs
NK117(she)001:25375: rgyas ni gnyis ka cha mnyam pa las thams cad
NK117(she)001:25376: gzigs so // de bas na shin tu mnyam par
NK117(she)001:25377: bzhag tshe chos rnams mkha' dbyings ltar 'od gsal la
NK117(she)001:25378: go 'byed pa'i cha de lhag mthong skyon med yin
NK117(she)001:25379: gzigs so // la / rnam pa du ma'i dmigs
NK117(she)001:25380: pa can sems kyi rnam g.yeng ngan pa'i rtog dpyod
NK117(she)001:25381: rnon po ni so sor rtog pa'i shes rab ma
NK117(she)001:25382: gzigs so // la / yin no // de la
NK117(she)001:25383: gnyis chos thams cad kyi dbus dang dbus tsam du'ang
NK117(she)001:25384: mi 'dzin pa'i shes rab zab mo dang de'i rtsal
NK117(she)001:25385: las 'gro la dmigs pa'i snying rje chen po ni
NK117(she)001:25386: gzigs so // la / yin no // thabs so
NK117(she)001:25387: // de yang mnyam gzhag tu bsam gtan gyi ngo
NK117(she)001:25389: shes rab kyi ngo bo lhag mthong gi ye shes
NK117(she)001:25390: kyis tshogs bsgrub pa gnyis ka'i chings su brtson 'grus
NK117(she)001:25391: kyi pha rol phyin pa bcings na bsam gtan des
NK117(she)001:25392: rnam pa thams cad kyi mchog dang ldan pa bsgrub
NK117(she)001:25394: de nyid kyang phar phyin drug dang ma bral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:25395: da ni phar phyin lnga ka'i 'bras bu shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25397: lhag pa shes rab bslab pa'i nges 'byed ni //
NK117(she)001:25398: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor ba las skyes shing //
NK117(she)001:25399: dngos dang rjes las byung ba'i shes rab bam //
NK117(she)001:25400: thos dang bsam pa sgom pa las byung ba'i //
NK117(she)001:25401: shes rab gsum gyis lhag mthong yang dag 'grub //
NK117(she)001:25402: ces pa ni de la chos mngon pa'i sde snod
NK117(she)001:25403: kyi brjod bya'i don ma 'khrul par rab tu 'byed
NK117(she)001:25404: pa ni lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa'i ngo
NK117(she)001:25405: bo yin zhing / de'i nges 'byed ni ting nge
NK117(she)001:25406: 'dzin gyi sbyor ba ste bsam gtan las skyes sgrib
NK117(she)001:25407: pa thams cad dang bral ba'i shes rab dngos sam
NK117(she)001:25408: bo yin zhing / / dman pa'i shes rab dang /
NK117(she)001:25409: thos pa dang bsam pa dang bsgom pa las byung
NK117(she)001:25410: ba'i shes rab gsum gyis lhag mthong yang dag pa
NK117(she)001:25412: nyon mongs tshogs 'joms chos dang chos can shes //
NK117(she)001:25413: srid pa'i grong las mya ngan med par 'da' //
NK117(she)001:25414: sbyin sogs rnam pa drug po'ang gong nas gong //
NK117(she)001:25415: khyad zhugs shes rab pha rol phyin la brten //
NK117(she)001:25416: zhes pa ni 'di ltar shes rab gsum gyis don
NK117(she)001:25417: la brtson pa des nyon mongs pa rnams dngos dang
NK117(she)001:25418: rgyud nas 'joms par byed cing chos nyid zab mo
NK117(she)001:25419: dang chos can 'khrul ngor snang ba yongs kyi gnas
NK117(she)001:25421: de ltar shes pas srid pa'i grong mya ngan gyis
NK117(she)001:25422: non pa dag la'ang dub kha med par yongs su
NK117(she)001:25423: 'da' zhing sbyin pa la sogs phar phyin rnam pa
NK117(she)001:25424: drug po'ang gong nas gong du khyad zhugs pa ste
NK117(she)001:25425: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i 'phags chos
NK117(she)001:25426: la brten nas 'bras bu thob pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:25427: mdor na rgyu 'bras bslu med la nges pa rnyed pa dang chos dang chos min 'byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25428: ston pa dang bstan pa'i yon tan la nges shes
NK117(she)001:25429: skye ba dang yon tan thams cad dge ba'i bshes
NK117(she)001:25430: gnyen la rag las pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25431: 'jig rten gyi spyod pa dang mthar thug la skyo
NK117(she)001:25432: bar 'gyur ba rten cing 'brel 'byung la nges pa
NK117(she)001:25433: brtan pa dang / theg pa gong 'og dang bden
NK117(she)001:25434: gnyis dang drang nges gnyis mdo sngags gnyis kyi gnang
NK117(she)001:25435: bkag la gang zag gzhan la 'gal yang shes rab
NK117(she)001:25436: can la mi 'gal ba sogs 'phags chos mang ngo
NK117(she)001:25437: brtan pa dang / // sngon gyi sbyin 'bras las
NK117(she)001:25438: rgyal po sogs kyi gnas thob kyang shes rab med
NK117(she)001:25439: na myur du nyams dma' bar 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:25441: de'ang 'di na so so'i skye bo'i sar //
NK117(she)001:25442: thos pa las byung shes rab ma bsten na //
NK117(she)001:25443: bsam dang bsgom pa'i yon tan gnas min 'khyams //
NK117(she)001:25444: thos pa'i shes rab kun gyi rgyu ru gsungs //
NK117(she)001:25445: zhes pa ni de la gang zag gang gi rgyud
NK117(she)001:25446: 'phags pa yin na sngon goms stobs kyis thos bsam
NK117(she)001:25447: gyi don shes sla srid kyang so so yang dag
NK117(she)001:25448: rig pa bzhi ma thob bar brtson pa gal che'o
NK117(she)001:25449: // de'ang 'di na so so'i skye bo ni sems
NK117(she)001:25450: nyon mongs pa can yin na de lta'i dman sar
NK117(she)001:25451: gnas skabs thos pa las byung ba'i shes rab ma
NK117(she)001:25452: bsten na bsam pa dang bsgom pa'i shes rab gnas
NK117(she)001:25453: min du 'khyams pa ni byis pa shed ma byed
NK117(she)001:25454: pas mi chen gyi lad mo byas pa dang 'dra
NK117(she)001:25455: bas thos pa'i shes rab kun gyi rgyu ru gsungs
NK117(she)001:25457: de'i phyir na bstan la ma dad pa rnams tshar gcad phyir sgra dang gtan tshigs rig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25458: dad pa can rnams rjes su bzung phyir bzo dang
NK117(she)001:25459: gso ba rig pa dang rang nyid kyis kun shes
NK117(she)001:25460: par bya phyir nang rig pa 'tshol ba rnams yin
NK117(she)001:25461: la de thams cad sangs rgyas thob pa'i phyir du
NK117(she)001:25462: yin na der 'thus mod kyi don la bdag med
NK117(she)001:25463: pa'i de kho na nyid spyi dang mngon gyur gyi
NK117(she)001:25464: sgo nas ma nor bar ston phyir drang nges gnyis
NK117(she)001:25467: gzhal bya'i chos la 'jal byed shes rab kyis //
NK117(she)001:25468: drang nges gnyis dang ldem dgongs rnam bzhir gzhal //
NK117(she)001:25469: chos rnams kun gyi ngo bo de bzhin nyid //
NK117(she)001:25470: rnam thar gsum du gnas pa nges don yin //
NK117(she)001:25471: chos can snang tshod lam la 'jug pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:25472: rigs pas gzhal nas sgro btags drang ba'i lam //
NK117(she)001:25473: gnyis po drang don gang la rton mi rton //
NK117(she)001:25474: shes de gsung rab blta ba'i lde mig yin //
NK117(she)001:25475: zhes pa ni de la gzhal bya'i chos ni 'khor
NK117(she)001:25476: 'das su 'dzin pa'i kun rdzob kyi yul du gyur
NK117(she)001:25477: pa rnams yin la de nyid shes byed dam 'jal
NK117(she)001:25478: byed shes rab kyis ji ltar gzhal na /
NK117(she)001:25479: drang nges gnyis dang ldem dgongs gnyis te rnam pa
NK117(she)001:25480: bzhir gzhal ba la chos rnams kun gyi dbyings sam
NK117(she)001:25481: ngo bo de bzhin nyid yin la de'i gnas lugs
NK117(she)001:25482: ni rnam thar sgo gsum ste /
NK117(she)001:25483: rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:25486: tshul de ltar du gnas pa de la nges don
NK117(she)001:25487: zhes dngos po dang mtshan ma med pa la tha
NK117(she)001:25488: snyad tsam du de ltar btags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25489: de yang chos can zhes 'khrul ngor snang tshod kyi
NK117(she)001:25490: lam du 'jug pa'i phyir rigs pas gzhal nas sgro
NK117(she)001:25491: btags pa tsam las don la reg ma nus pa
NK117(she)001:25492: gang yin pa de ni drang ba'i lam mo //
NK117(she)001:25493: de gnyis pos drang nges gang la rton ma rton
NK117(she)001:25494: zhes phal skad du gang la don mi don shes
NK117(she)001:25495: pa / de ni gsung rab thams cad la blta ba'i lde mig yin zhes stangs bcad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25496: de yang mdo sde gang dag lam la 'jug phyir bstan pa thams cad drang don dang /
NK117(she)001:25497: 'bras bu la 'jug phyir bstan pa thams cad nges don zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:25498: de yang zhib tu dbye na don la rton gyis tshig la mi rton pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25499: ye shes la rton gyis rnam shes la mi rton pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25500: nges don la rton gyis drang don la mi rton pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25501: chos nyid la rton gyis gang zag la mi rton pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25502: de la tshig ni 'jig rten pa'i chos rnams dang don ni de las 'das pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25503: rnam shes ni gzugs dang 'du shes 'du byed rnams la nye bar 'gro zhing gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25504: ye shes ni gzugs tshor 'du shes 'du byed bzhi
NK117(she)001:25505: la gnas pa'i rnam shes kyi phung po yongs su
NK117(she)001:25506: shes pa'o // mdor na gshis kyi gnas lugs gtso
NK117(she)001:25507: bor ston pa rnams la nges don gyi mdo sde
NK117(she)001:25508: shes pa'o // dang / gshis la 'jug thabs kyi
NK117(she)001:25509: lam bstan pa rnams la drang don gyi chos zhes
NK117(she)001:25510: shes pa'o // dang / pa'o // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:25511: de dag rang bzhin gsal bar bya ba dang //
NK117(she)001:25512: don gyi dgongs pa rtogs par bya ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:25513: dgongs ldem gnyis bshad dang po dgongs pa ni //
NK117(she)001:25514: cung zad sgro btags bshad du yang yod la //
NK117(she)001:25515: gdul bya'i yul rnams re zhig kha drang ba //
NK117(she)001:25516: gcig pu'i slad du'ang ma yin dgos ched dang //
NK117(she)001:25517: bcas nas dgongs pa rnam bzhir ston pa ste //
NK117(she)001:25518: zhes pa ni de dag ste gong du bshad pa
NK117(she)001:25519: rnams kyi rang bzhin gsal bar bya ba dang don
NK117(she)001:25520: gyi dgongs pa rtogs par bya ba'i phyir dgongs pa
NK117(she)001:25521: can dang ldem por dgongs pa gnyis bshad pa'i dang
NK117(she)001:25522: po dgongs pa can ni spyir dmigs pa'i don gcig
NK117(she)001:25523: yid yul du bzhag kyang phyir mi mngon par byed
NK117(she)001:25525: de la cung zad sgro btags nas bshad du yang
NK117(she)001:25526: yod la zhes pa ni yid la bzhag pa'i gnad
NK117(she)001:25527: de la sbas par mngon sum du bstan pa ma
NK117(she)001:25528: yin kyang zur tsam bstan nas gnad gab pa lta
NK117(she)001:25529: bu'o // de yang gdul bya'i yul zhes gzhan rnams
NK117(she)001:25530: re zhig ste 'phral du kha drang ba gcig pu'i
NK117(she)001:25531: slad du'ang ma yin zhing dgos ched khyad par ba
NK117(she)001:25532: dang bcas nas dgongs pa rnam pa bzhir ston pa
NK117(she)001:25534: mnyam pa nyid dgongs 'gal ba'ang gcig tu bstan //
NK117(she)001:25535: don gzhan la dgongs dpyad na ma grub bstan //
NK117(she)001:25536: dus gzhan la dgongs 'bad med 'tshang rgya bstan //
NK117(she)001:25537: gang zag la dgongs de de'i mchog 'dzin smad //
NK117(she)001:25538: ces pa ni de yang mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa ste tshur mthong snang ngor 'khor 'das dang /
NK117(she)001:25539: bzang ngan sogs gnyis 'dzin gyi yul dang yul can
NK117(she)001:25540: du gyur pa'i 'gal chos rnams kyang don dam rtogs
NK117(she)001:25541: pa'i rnal 'byor pas 'gal min chos kyi dbyings spros
NK117(she)001:25542: pa dang bral bar ro gcig tu bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25543: don gzhan la dgongs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25544: kun brtags mtshan nyid ngo bo nyid med de nges don du ma grub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25545: gzhan dbang skye ba ngo bo nyid med de mu bzhi las skye ba ma grub cing /
NK117(she)001:25546: yongs grub ni don dam pa'i ngo bo nyid med
NK117(she)001:25547: de spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir ro
NK117(she)001:25548: // dus gzhan la dgongs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25549: gang yang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam 'di //
NK117(she)001:25550: 'chang ba dang ni bston nam klog na yang //
NK117(she)001:25551: de yi rnam par smin pa sangs rgyas mkhyen //
NK117(she)001:25552: byang chub mchog la som nyi ma byed cig /
NK117(she)001:25553: ces pas mtshon rgyu rkyen gzhan la mi ltos par
NK117(she)001:25554: byang chub la reg par mi 'gyur yang sngon du
NK117(she)001:25555: dge tshogs mang du song ba zhig nam zhig 'tshang
NK117(she)001:25556: rgya ba'i gru'i kha lo pa lta bur 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:25558: gang zag la dgongs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25559: gang zag so so'i rang nyams su myong ba'i phar
NK117(she)001:25560: phyin drug gam gzhan yang dmigs bcas dang dmigs med
NK117(she)001:25561: du rloms pa'i chos gang la yang mchog 'dzin byed
NK117(she)001:25562: pa dag smod pa'i don yang /
NK117(she)001:25563: mdo las phar phyin drug la mngon par zhen pa yang bdud kyi las so //
NK117(she)001:25566: ldem por dgongs pa gdul bya gang zhig gi //
NK117(she)001:25567: blo la mi chud yid gnyis gnas thob rnams //
NK117(she)001:25568: de nyid dga' ba'i ming dang cha ldan gyi //
NK117(she)001:25569: rnam par kyog nas yang dag lam gzud phyir //
NK117(she)001:25570: tshig mthun don mi mthun par bshad pa ste //
NK117(she)001:25571: zhes pa ni de la ldem por dgongs pa ni
NK117(she)001:25572: gdul bya gang yang rung ba zhig 'dul ba'i skabs
NK117(she)001:25573: su babs pa na de nyid rigs dman par gyur
NK117(she)001:25574: nas theg chen phar phyin nam sngags la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:25575: blo la mi chud cing yid gnyis kyi gnas su
NK117(she)001:25576: gyur nas dman sems thob pa rnams kyang de nyid
NK117(she)001:25577: dga' ba'i ming theg dman dang cha ldan gyi rnam
NK117(she)001:25578: par kyog nas yang dag pa'i lam du gzud phyir
NK117(she)001:25579: tshig rgyu'i theg pa dang mthun par bcos nas don
NK117(she)001:25580: theg chen rnam gnyis dang mthun par bshad pas tshig
NK117(she)001:25581: mthun don mi mthun pa 'byung ste 'di ltar /
NK117(she)001:25582: sngon rgyal po ma skyes dgras rang gi yab rgyal
NK117(she)001:25583: po gzugs can snying po bsad pa sogs mtshams med
NK117(she)001:25584: kyi las byas pa la dus re zhig gi tshe
NK117(she)001:25585: rgyal po 'gyod pa skyes nas rang gi khyim na
NK117(she)001:25587: nyan thos chen po dag lhung bzed dang lag pa bkru ba rigs nas /
NK117(she)001:25588: rgyal po chos nyan pa'i phyir 'jam dpal gzhon nur
NK117(she)001:25589: gyur pa'i mdun du 'dug ste 'jam dpal bdag gi
NK117(she)001:25590: 'gyod pa bsal du gsol zhes zhus pas /
NK117(she)001:25591: 'jam dpal gyis rgyal po chen po khyod kyi 'gyod
NK117(she)001:25592: pa ni sangs rgyas gang ga'i klung gi bye ma
NK117(she)001:25593: snyed kyis kyang bsal bar mi nus so //
NK117(she)001:25595: rgyal po skyabs ma rnyed nas sa la 'gyel bar 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:25596: de nas gnas brtan 'od srung chen pos rgyal po la ni 'di skad ces smras so //
NK117(she)001:25597: rgyal po chen po 'phags pa 'jam dpal ni ldem po ngag tu ston pa la mkhas kyis /
NK117(she)001:25598: ma 'jigs ma skrag par don 'di ci la dgongs
NK117(she)001:25599: te gsungs zhes dris dang gdod 'gyod pa bsal ba'i
NK117(she)001:25600: thabs ston to // zhes pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:25602: dbye na zhugs pa mtshan nyid gnyen po bsgyur //
NK117(she)001:25603: zhugs pa ldem dgongs gang zhig nyan thos dag /
NK117(she)001:25604: stong pas skrag nas theg chen spong ba la //
NK117(she)001:25605: gzugs yod smos pas grub par go nas 'jug /
NK117(she)001:25606: snang tshod rmi lam lta bur dgongs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25607: mtshan nyid ldem dgongs ngo bo nyid med don //
NK117(she)001:25608: shes pa'i don du rim bzhin kun brtags dang //
NK117(she)001:25609: gzhan dbang yongs grub rnam pa gsum dag las //
NK117(she)001:25610: dang por mtshan nyid ngo bo nyid med dang //
NK117(she)001:25611: gnyis par skye ba ngo bo nyid med dang //
NK117(she)001:25612: gsum par don dam ngo bo nyid med pas //
NK117(she)001:25613: chos rnams brjod pa zab pa dag tu ston //
NK117(she)001:25614: gnyen po ldem dgongs gzhan gyi log rtog ldog /
NK117(she)001:25615: sku tshe rigs dang sku bong tshad kyis min //
NK117(she)001:25616: sangs rgyas thams cad gzugs sku chos skur mnyam //
NK117(she)001:25617: tshogs kyi yul la'ang mnyam pa lta bur dgongs //
NK117(she)001:25618: bsgyur ba ldem dgongs gsad bya ma yin pa'i //
NK117(she)001:25619: pha ma gsad dang de bzhin bcom bya min //
NK117(she)001:25620: rgyal po dang ni gtsang sbra can gnyis bcom //
NK117(she)001:25621: sred len kun gzhi sogs la btags pa'i don //
NK117(she)001:25622: rnal mar bzung na nor ba chen po'o //
NK117(she)001:25623: zhes pa ni de la zhugs pa ldem dgongs ni /
NK117(she)001:25624: nyan thos pa dag chos kyi bdag med thos pas skrag pa yod de /
NK117(she)001:25625: sngon jo bo rje bod na bzhugs dus 'phags yul
NK117(she)001:25626: gyi dge slong sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis la
NK117(she)001:25627: gnas pa ga nyis chos zhur byung tshe jo bos
NK117(she)001:25628: gang zag gi bdag med gsungs tshe de gnyis dad
NK117(she)001:25629: chos kyi bdag med gsungs tshe de skad mi gsung
NK117(she)001:25630: bar zhu zhes dang 'jigs 'jigs zer ba dang /
NK117(she)001:25631: sher snying gsungs tshe rna ba dgab par jo bos
NK117(she)001:25632: byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems med na bsrung
NK117(she)001:25633: sdom gcig pos gang la yang mi phyin zhes gsungs
NK117(she)001:25634: / de lta bu'i gang zag theg chen la gzhug pa'i don du mdo las /
NK117(she)001:25636: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pa ltar gzugs yod
NK117(she)001:25637: ces smos pas nyan pa po skrag pa mi skye
NK117(she)001:25638: zhing 'chad pa pos snang tshod la rmi lam ltar
NK117(she)001:25640: mtshan nyid ldem por dgongs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25641: ngo bo nyid med pa ste kun brtags la mtshan nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:25642: gzhan dbang la skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:25643: yongs grub la don dam ngo bo nyid med par
NK117(she)001:25644: gsungs pas chos rnams brjod pa zab par bstan pa'o
NK117(she)001:25646: sangs rgyas stong rtsa'i nang nas sh+aakya thub pa ni
NK117(she)001:25647: sku gzugs chung zhing 'od 'dom gang ba 'dus pa
NK117(she)001:25648: nyung ba sku tshe thung ba la sogs pas sangs
NK117(she)001:25649: rgyas gzhan las ma dman pa zhig go snyam pa'i
NK117(she)001:25650: log rtog ldog pa la dgongs te rnam snang gangs
NK117(she)001:25651: chen mtsho'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi
NK117(she)001:25652: zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i tshul bshad nas sangs
NK117(she)001:25653: rgyas thams cad kyi sprul gzhi bdag nyid yin par
NK117(she)001:25654: zhal gyis bzhes pa lta bu ste /
NK117(she)001:25655: nyan pa pos gzugs sku'i rang bzhin gcig tu mnyam
NK117(she)001:25656: par go zhing 'chad pa pos rang don du tshogs
NK117(she)001:25657: rdzogs pa dang chos sku thub par mnyam /
NK117(she)001:25658: gzhan don du 'gro don mdzad par dus mnyam pa gsum la dgongs so //
NK117(she)001:25659: bsgyur ba ldem por dgongs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:25660: dge sbyong go bo ta ma ni ma bskul yang
NK117(she)001:25661: chos 'chad do zer ba'i dpya ba bsal ba dang
NK117(she)001:25662: / lo drug dka' spyad kho nas khyad par thob
NK117(she)001:25663: na de nyid gting dpag chung ngo snyam pa bsal
NK117(she)001:25664: / ba'i phyir / zab mo chags bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK117(she)001:25665: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos shig bdag gis rnyed //
NK117(she)001:25666: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'gyur te //
NK117(she)001:25667: bdag nyid gcig pu nags su bsgom par bya //
NK117(she)001:25668: zhes gsungs nas chos nyid de shin tu rtogs par dka' ba ston pa lta bu dang /
NK117(she)001:25669: khyad par don tshig gnyis 'gal bar bsgyur nas gsungs pa'i tshul /
NK117(she)001:25670: ngas me tog zla mdzes bsad de la sogs pa gsungs pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:25672: pha dang ma ni gsad bya zhing //
NK117(she)001:25673: rgyal po gtsang sbra can gnyis dang //
NK117(she)001:25674: yul 'khor skor bcas bcom pa na //
NK117(she)001:25675: mi de dag pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:25676: zhes pa lta bu 'di ltar 'khor bar 'du byed pa'i rtsa ba sred pa ni pha dang /
NK117(she)001:25678: kun gzhi ni bag chags sna tshogs pa'i rten du
NK117(she)001:25679: gyur pa'i rgyal po dang bram ze 'jigs tshogs la
NK117(she)001:25680: blta ba / dge sbyong tshul khrims dang brtul zhugs
NK117(she)001:25681: la mchog 'dzin gyi blta ba'i gtsang sbra can gnyis
NK117(she)001:25682: blta ba / so // nang gi skye mched gzung
NK117(she)001:25683: 'dzin gyis bsdus pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad ni yul
NK117(she)001:25684: 'khor te de dag bcom pa'i tha snyad kyis rang
NK117(she)001:25685: rgyud la mi gnas par dag pa'i tshe 'tshang rgya
NK117(she)001:25686: ba la sbyar ba dngos bstan du 'khrul na nor
NK117(she)001:25687: blta ba / so // ba chen po'o // de yang zhugs pa ldem por dgongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25690: bsgyur ba ldem dgongs bzhi'i grangs su bsdu'o //
NK117(she)001:25692: mdor na dgongs dang ldem po'i khyad par ni //
NK117(she)001:25693: dgongs pa yid la rnam par bzhag pa tsam //
NK117(she)001:25694: yin gyis pha rol bzung la ltos pa min //
NK117(she)001:25695: ldem por dgongs pa pha rol bzung ba la //
NK117(she)001:25696: ltos pa'i rnam 'byed gsung rab blta ba'i mig /
NK117(she)001:25697: ces pa ni de la dgongs pa ni yid la
NK117(she)001:25698: rnam par bzhag pa tsam yin gyi pha rol bzung
NK117(she)001:25699: ba la ltos pa ma yin zhing ldem dgongs ni
NK117(she)001:25700: pha rol bzung ba la ltos pa'i rnam 'byed ni
NK117(she)001:25701: gsung rab blta ba'i mig yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25702: de yang gdul bya'i snod dang sbyar nas 'byung ba'i
NK117(she)001:25703: tshul khong du chud pa'i blo chen rnams la 'gal
NK117(she)001:25706: gzhal bya'i ngos nas rgyal bas chos kyi sgo //
NK117(she)001:25707: brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa mtha' dag don //
NK117(she)001:25708: 'jig rten kun rdzob pa dang don dam ste //
NK117(she)001:25709: bden pa gnyis las gsum pa ma mchis so //
NK117(she)001:25710: zhes pa ni de la gzhal bya'am 'jal rgyu'i ngos
NK117(she)001:25711: nas rgyal bas chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi
NK117(she)001:25712: stong gsungs pa yang nyon mongs pa dug gsum gdul
NK117(she)001:25713: phyir 'dul ba dang mdo sde dang mngon pa sde
NK117(she)001:25714: snod gsum dang / mngon rtogs bslab pa gsum mam
NK117(she)001:25715: grangs rgya che ba'i ngos nas gsungs pa mtha' dag
NK117(she)001:25716: snang lugs kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis las gzhan
NK117(she)001:25717: pa bden pa gsum pa med do //
NK117(she)001:25719: kun rdzob pa la snang lugs rnam pa gnyis //
NK117(she)001:25720: 'khrul shes ngo la snang ba ji snyed kyi //
NK117(she)001:25721: snang tshod nyid dang mthun par don byed rnams //
NK117(she)001:25722: yang dag kun rdzob nyid de snang na'ang //
NK117(she)001:25723: don mi byed la log pa'i kun rdzob grags //
NK117(she)001:25724: zhes pa ni de la sems kyi rnam shes tshogs
NK117(she)001:25725: brgyad kyis bskyed pa'i 'khrul pa'i snang ngor shar ba
NK117(she)001:25726: dang de la 'dzin pa skyes pa dang mdor na
NK117(she)001:25727: 'khrul pa'i shes par shar ba thams cad kun rdzob
NK117(she)001:25728: yin te / de la'ang snang lugs rnam pa gnyis
NK117(she)001:25729: te 'khrul ba'i shes pa'i snang ba ji snyed cig
NK117(she)001:25730: yod pa kun gyi snang tshod nyid dang mthun par
NK117(she)001:25731: don byed pa rnams la yang dag kun rdzob nyid
NK117(she)001:25732: de dper na dge sdig gnyis dngos su spyad pas
NK117(she)001:25733: 'phral phugs bde sdug gi rgyur 'gyur ba sogs dang
NK117(she)001:25734: yin te / / dbang lnga'i sgor snang na'ang don byed mi nus pa /
NK117(she)001:25735: chu nang du shar ba'i zla gzugs dang ri mo'i mar mes mun pa sel mi nus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25736: rol mo'i bye brag sna tshogs ri mor bris pa rna bar grags ma nus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25737: bdug spos sna tshogs kyi gzugs brnyan snang la bro mi btub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25738: bza' btung gi snang brnyan sna tshogs lce la myong
NK117(she)001:25739: mi nus pa sogs la log pa'i kun rdzob ces
NK117(she)001:25740: grags so // de lta bu'i kun rdzob gnyis po
NK117(she)001:25741: la yang dag dang log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis su
NK117(she)001:25742: gsungs kyang gshis thog nas gzhal na so so ma
NK117(she)001:25743: grags so // yin te / bag chags dang 'khrul
NK117(she)001:25744: ngor skyes pa mnyam pa dang dbang yul so sor
NK117(she)001:25745: snang ba yang mnyam gzhag gi re zhig 'khrul ngor
NK117(she)001:25746: snang tshe kun rdzob gnyis po mig shes kyi yul
NK117(she)001:25747: du yod na yod mnyam med na med mnyam du
NK117(she)001:25748: gcig pas rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25749: khyad par 'phags pa'i ye shes thob tshe bden zhen
NK117(she)001:25750: dang bcas pa'i sems rtog dang snang ba thams cad
NK117(she)001:25752: bden zhen med pa'i 'char sgo dang snang ba thams cad yang dag kun rdzob tu 'thad do //
NK117(she)001:25754: don dam bden pa gshis kyi bzhugs tshul te //
NK117(she)001:25755: 'khor ba dang ni mya ngan 'das pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:25756: ngo bo gnyis med gdod nas bsam brjod 'das //
NK117(she)001:25757: rtogs dang ma rtogs blo yis ma bzhag go //
NK117(she)001:25758: zhes pa ni de la don dam bden pa ni
NK117(she)001:25759: kun gzhi'i gshis kyi gnas lugs rang bzhin gyi zhi
NK117(she)001:25760: ba spros pa med pa gcig pa dang tha dad
NK117(she)001:25761: pa las 'das shing 'khor 'das dang chos so cog
NK117(she)001:25762: gdod nas ngo bo nyid med pas so so skye
NK117(she)001:25763: bo'i rtogs ma rtogs kyi blos bzhag tu med do
NK117(she)001:25764: // de ltar bden gnyis ni sems can gyi don
NK117(she)001:25765: du thabs la mkhas pa'i tshul du gsungs pa yin
NK117(she)001:25766: // gyi / dngos po'i cha nas tha dad yod pa ma yin pa'i tshul /
NK117(she)001:25768: bden gnyis 'dres pa'i snang stong zung 'jug ni //
NK117(she)001:25769: rdzing bur zhugs pa'i zla ba'i skye mched bzhin //
NK117(she)001:25770: snang ba'i cha nas kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK117(she)001:25771: rang bzhin ma grub don dam bden pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25772: zhes pa ni de ltar kun rdzob kyi gnas lugs
NK117(she)001:25773: rdzing bur zla gzugs shar ba ltar mig shes la
NK117(she)001:25774: snang ba kun rdzob zol zog tu grub kyang /
NK117(she)001:25775: zla ba dngos ma yin pas don dam du mnyam
NK117(she)001:25776: zhing bden gnyis 'dres pa'i snang ba tshogs drug gi
NK117(she)001:25777: yul du gyur pa rnams dang stong pa de dag
NK117(she)001:25778: gi dbyings rang bzhin gyis stong pa ni bshad ma
NK117(she)001:25779: thag pa'i rdzing bur zhugs pa'i zla ba'i skye mched
NK117(she)001:25780: gsal ba ltar snang ba'i cha nas kun rdzob bden
NK117(she)001:25781: pa dang / rang bzhin ma grub pa la don dam bden pa zhes zlos nas 'grel lo //
NK117(she)001:25783: yul lnga'i shes pa tshon ris ma 'dres ltar //
NK117(she)001:25784: gzugs sogs 'dod pa'i longs spyod cha bzung ba //
NK117(she)001:25785: de la der 'dzin dgag bsgrub blo rtog gi //
NK117(she)001:25786: 'khrul snang sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad nyid du brtag /
NK117(she)001:25787: ces pa ni de la yul lnga ni gzugs sgra
NK117(she)001:25788: dri ro reg bya ste de la sems zhugs nas
NK117(she)001:25789: so sor rnam par rtog cing dgag bsgrub kyi blo
NK117(she)001:25790: rtog tu shar ba'i 'khrul pa'i shes pa 'ja' tshon
NK117(she)001:25791: gyi ri mo ma 'dres pa ltar gzugs sogs 'dod
NK117(she)001:25792: pa'i longs spyod kyi cha bzung ba /
NK117(she)001:25793: de dag la der 'dzin gyi dgag sgrub dang blo
NK117(she)001:25794: rtog gi cha thams cad 'khrul snang sgyu ma'i dpe
NK117(she)001:25795: brgyad nyid du brtag cing goms tshe srid pa'i grong
NK117(she)001:25796: las 'das shing thar pa'i sa dang nye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:25798: mthar thug blo yis rnam par dpyad bzod na //
NK117(she)001:25799: don dam ma yin blo ni kun rdzob phyir //
NK117(she)001:25800: gcig dang du mar 'gal ba'i mtshan nyid rnams //
NK117(she)001:25801: blo yi yul na nam yang gnas ma myong //
NK117(she)001:25802: zhes pa ni de yang mthar thug ste don dam
NK117(she)001:25803: bden pa dngos ni blo yis rnam par dpyad bzod
NK117(she)001:25804: na blos btags pa yin pas don dam ma yin
NK117(she)001:25805: zhing blo ni kun rdzob 'khrul pa'i cha yin pa'i
NK117(she)001:25806: phyir dngos rdzas gcig kyang med par nges na du
NK117(she)001:25807: ma yod pa ga la rigs te tha snyad thams
NK117(she)001:25808: cad dang 'gal ba'i mtshan nyid rnams ni gtan la
NK117(she)001:25810: blo yi yul na nam yang gnas ma myong ste rmi lam gyi gnas grogs dang mtshungs so //
NK117(she)001:25812: re zhig grub pa'i mtha' yi rnam bzhag ni //
NK117(she)001:25813: shes pa'i don dam blo yis dpyad pa dang //
NK117(she)001:25814: dngos po'i don dam tho bas bcom pa yi //
NK117(she)001:25815: rdul phran cha med nyan thos sde pa'i lugs //
NK117(she)001:25816: zhes pa ni de yang re zhig ste 'phral tshig
NK117(she)001:25817: tsam du grub pa'i mtha' yi rnam par bzhag na
NK117(she)001:25818: nyan thos pa la bye mdo gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:25819: dang po ni rang rig tha snyad tsam du'ang khas
NK117(she)001:25820: mi len zhing lam theg dman du zhugs pa ni
NK117(she)001:25822: des ni gzhi'i chos shes pa'i don dam la blo
NK117(she)001:25823: ngo'i dpyad pa zhugs pa dang dngos po'i don dam
NK117(she)001:25824: tho bas bcom pa sogs kyis gnod mi nus te
NK117(she)001:25825: / shes pa'i rgyun dang dngos po'i rags pa ni kun rdzob shes pa'i skad cig ma dang /
NK117(she)001:25826: dngos po'i rdul phran cha med pa ni don dam
NK117(she)001:25827: du 'dod cing 'di ltar dngos po'i rnam pa gser
NK117(she)001:25828: dngul zangs lcags sa rdo sogs gzugs dang rdzas kyi
NK117(she)001:25829: rnam pa gang yang rung ba zhig ma nyams par
NK117(she)001:25830: yod dus 'di dang 'adi'o snyam pa'i blo skye yang
NK117(she)001:25831: / dngos rdzas de tho ba dang gtun bu sogs
NK117(she)001:25832: kyis bcom nas rdul phran byas tshe dpyad pa'i rnam
NK117(she)001:25833: pa de med pas der 'dzin gyi blo rags pa
NK117(she)001:25835: don dam bden pa ni rdul phran phra rab gnyen
NK117(she)001:25836: pos bcom pa dang rigs pas gzhig ste bsal yang
NK117(she)001:25837: ngar 'dzin gyi blo 'dor du mi rung ba'i chos
NK117(she)001:25838: rnams ni don dam pa'i dngos por 'dod de mtshan
NK117(she)001:25839: gzhi rdul phran cha med dang /
NK117(she)001:25840: shes pa skad cig cha med dang /
NK117(she)001:25841: 'dus ma byas kyi chos rnams so //
NK117(she)001:25842: de'ang kun rdzob dang btags yod gcig la /
NK117(she)001:25843: don dam dang rdzas yod gcig tu 'dod do //
NK117(she)001:25844: grub mtha' 'dis ni mu stegs pa rnams 'dod pa'i
NK117(she)001:25845: gang zag gi bdag bkag nas bdag med par khas
NK117(she)001:25846: blangs shing / dus gsum yang rdzas grub dang dngos
NK117(she)001:25847: por 'dod pas med par mi 'gyur ba sogs rags
NK117(she)001:25848: blangs shing / pa yin la / kha che bye
NK117(she)001:25849: smra ni mdo sde pa dang mthun te las kyi
NK117(she)001:25850: rgyun khas len pa'i khyad par ro //
NK117(she)001:25851: lam gyi rnam bzhag ni bden pa bzhi'i rnam pa
NK117(she)001:25852: mi rtag pa sogs bcu drug po la dmigs nas
NK117(she)001:25853: lam lnga'i rnam bzhag tsam byed kyang /
NK117(she)001:25854: sa bcu'i rnam bzhag ni mi 'dod do //
NK117(she)001:25856: theg dman gyi bsam sbyor rgyud la skyes pa ni theg dman pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25857: theg chen gyi bsam sbyor rgyud la skyes pa ni theg chen pa yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:25858: de gnyis gang yang rgyud la ma skyes na de gnyis gang yang ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:25859: de yang theg dman bye brag tu smra ba ni /
NK117(she)001:25860: shes pa sems dang sems byung gnyis /
NK117(she)001:25861: yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya ste lnga de
NK117(she)001:25862: dag gi shes pa lnga dang bcu po skye 'jig
NK117(she)001:25864: nam mkha' dang 'gog pa rnam gnyis te 'dus ma byas gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:25865: 'das pa dang ma 'ongs kyi dngos po rnams rang rang so so rdzas grub tu 'dod cing /
NK117(she)001:25866: bden grub kyi cha re yang yod par 'dod la
NK117(she)001:25867: rig pa'i dngos po dang rgyun gyi dngos po sogs
NK117(she)001:25869: 'di'i nang tshan kha che bye brag smra ba sogs 'dus byas skad cig gis 'jig pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25870: gang zag gi bdag ni blos btags pa tsam las rdzas su med par 'dod /
NK117(she)001:25871: mang pos bkur ba'i sde pa sogs ni 'dus byas
NK117(she)001:25872: mthar 'jig pa yin kyang skad cig gis 'jig pa
NK117(she)001:25873: min zer zhing rgyun gyi dngos po yang ci rigs
NK117(she)001:25874: par 'dod la / phyi pa rnams kyis btags pa'i
NK117(she)001:25875: bdag rtag pa gcig pu rang dbang can de 'dra
NK117(she)001:25876: med kyang spyir nga bdag tsam zhig rdzas grub dang
NK117(she)001:25878: 'di la bdag lta'i skyon gyis thar lam med pa
NK117(she)001:25879: 'dra yang mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro dang thar pa
NK117(she)001:25880: 'dod pa'i tshul khrims dang thos bsam sgom gsum yod
NK117(she)001:25881: pas rim pas thar pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:25882: bye smra 'di ni mngon pa sde bdun bkar 'dod
NK117(she)001:25883: cing lta grub rnams bstan bcos kyi lugs su khas
NK117(she)001:25884: len dgos par bzhed cing bstan bcos kyang bye brag
NK117(she)001:25885: tu bshad pa la ngos 'dzin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25887: don byed nus pa gang yin de 'dir ni //
NK117(she)001:25888: don dam yod yin gzhan ni kun rdzob yod //
NK117(she)001:25889: de yang rang spyi'i mtshan nyid kyis bshad pa //
NK117(she)001:25890: mdo sde pa'i lugs ngo bo rtog ger mthun //
NK117(she)001:25891: zhes pa ni 'di ltar bden zhen gyi ngo bo
NK117(she)001:25892: nas phyi don dang rang rig gnyis ka khas len
NK117(she)001:25893: pa'i theg dman gyi grub mtha' brjod pa la zhugs
NK117(she)001:25894: pa'i gang zag de ni mdo sde pa'i mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:25895: de dbye na lung dang rig pa'i rjes 'brang gnyis
NK117(she)001:25896: las / dang po ni bye brag smra ba rnams
NK117(she)001:25897: kyis bkar 'dod pa'i mngon pa sde bdun po sh+aa
NK117(she)001:25898: ri'i bu la sogs pa'i dgra bcom pa bdun po'i
NK117(she)001:25899: bstan bcos su 'dod nas grub mtha' de 'dzin pa
NK117(she)001:25900: las / yin la / phyi ma ni tshad ma
NK117(she)001:25901: sde bdun la sogs nas bshad cing mdo sde la
NK117(she)001:25902: brten nas grub mtha' smra ba'o //
NK117(she)001:25903: gzhi kun rdzob bden pa gang gi bden par 'jog
NK117(she)001:25904: pa mi rtog pas btags pa'i blo kun rdzob pa
NK117(she)001:25905: ste / des don rang mtshan gyi gnas lugs mthong ba la sgrib pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:25906: 'di ltar sems la rnam par rtog pa shar ba'i snang yul la spyi mtshan gyis khyab pa ste /
NK117(she)001:25907: spyi mtshan dang dngos med kyi chos dang bden pa
NK117(she)001:25908: kun rdzob pa rnams tha dad du med pa'i yin
NK117(she)001:25909: khyab mnyam la / mngon sum pa'i snang ba ste
NK117(she)001:25910: tshogs drug gi yul la rang mtshan gyis khyab cing
NK117(she)001:25911: khyab mnyam la / / rang mtshan dang /
NK117(she)001:25912: dngos po dang don dam bden pa rnams yin khyab mnyam du 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25913: mdor na spyi mtshan la sogs pa sngon ma rnams kun rdzob bden pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25914: rang mtshan la sogs phyi ma la don dam bden pa zhes mdo sde pa'i 'dod lugs so //
NK117(she)001:25915: de yang go bde bar brjod na nam mkha' sogs
NK117(she)001:25916: 'dus ma byas gsum dang yul gzugs sogs bcu skye
NK117(she)001:25917: 'jig sogs ldan min 'du byed rnams ni btags yod
NK117(she)001:25918: ces blos btags pa tsam yin pas bden par med
NK117(she)001:25919: cing / gzugs sogs la rags rgyun dang shes pa
NK117(she)001:25920: la rgyun bden par ma grub 'das ma 'ongs kyi
NK117(she)001:25921: chos kyang btags yod tsam yin la da lta ba'i
NK117(she)001:25923: shes pa skad cig ma tsam cha med bden grub yin /
NK117(she)001:25924: mig gis gzugs de ma mthong mig shes kyis kyang
NK117(she)001:25925: gzugs dngos su mi mthong ste mig shes la gzugs
NK117(she)001:25926: snang shar ba de gzugs kyi rnam par grags pa
NK117(she)001:25927: shes par gyur pa de yin la rnam par 'char
NK117(she)001:25928: ba de la rnam pa gtod byed gzugs sogs phyi
NK117(she)001:25930: mngon pa sde bdun sogs ni bka' ma yin zhing
NK117(she)001:25931: bye brag bshad pa sogs la 'khrul pa yod pas
NK117(she)001:25932: grub mtha' ni mdo sde dang bstun dgos par 'dod
NK117(she)001:25933: do // bye mdo gnyis kas sangs rgyas kyi bka'
NK117(she)001:25934: ni nyan thos kyi ched du gsungs pa'i sde snod
NK117(she)001:25936: sher phyin sogs theg chen gyi mdor grags pa 'di
NK117(she)001:25937: rnams rgyal ba'i bka' ma yin zhing theg pa che
NK117(she)001:25938: chung gi khyad par ni gang zag gi ngos nas
NK117(she)001:25939: phye ba yin gyis gsung rab tha dad pa med
NK117(she)001:25941: de yang nyan thos la sprul pa'i nyan thos ni
NK117(she)001:25942: mchog zung dang rab 'byor ma 'gag pa la sogs
NK117(she)001:25943: pa / lhas sbyin dang drug sde yang sprul par bsdu ba yod do //
NK117(she)001:25944: nyan thos zhi ba bgrod pa ni rang lam nas ji ltar bshad pa ltar 'jug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25945: grub mtha' 'dzin pa ni theg chen pas nyan thos kyi grub mtha' 'dzin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25946: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'gyur ba ni sbyor lam bzod pa thob nas so //
NK117(she)001:25947: de'ang nyan thos la so skye dang theg chen gnyis
NK117(she)001:25948: las 'phags pa rgyun zhugs dang phyir 'ong gnyis 'dod
NK117(she)001:25949: khams su lus rten mtshan nyid pa bzung nas theg
NK117(she)001:25950: chen gyi spyod pa bsgrub la /
NK117(she)001:25951: phyir mi 'ong ni sprul pa'i lus kyi gzhan don byed cing /
NK117(she)001:25952: lhag med myang 'das kyi sa zhing dag par skyes
NK117(she)001:25953: pa sangs rgyas kyis bskul nas gzhan don byed pa'o
NK117(she)001:25956: gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i yul yul can //
NK117(she)001:25957: kun rdzob bden pa nyid de gang las gzhan //
NK117(she)001:25958: gnyis med shes pa don dam bden pa ru //
NK117(she)001:25959: 'dod pa sems tsam pa yi grub pa'i mtha' //
NK117(she)001:25960: zhes pa ni de la phyi don med kyang bden
NK117(she)001:25961: grub khas len pa'i nang pa'i grub mtha' smra ba
NK117(she)001:25964: dbye na so skye rgyud kyi dbang por mngon sum
NK117(she)001:25965: snang ba'i gzugs snang rags par gsal ba 'di dag
NK117(she)001:25966: snang ba ltar du grub par khas len pa ni
NK117(she)001:25968: ma grub par 'dod pa ni rnam rdzun pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25969: mdor bsdu na gzung 'dzin gnyis snang gi yul dang yul can ni kun rdzob bden pa dang /
NK117(she)001:25970: gnyis med du shes pa ni don dam bden par 'dod do //
NK117(she)001:25971: de'ang rnam shes tshogs brgyad khas len pa dag ni
NK117(she)001:25972: kun gzhi'i rnam shes sgo lnga'i yid dang bcas par
NK117(she)001:25973: ma 'gyur pa'i shes pa'i ngo bo ma bsgribs lung
NK117(she)001:25974: ma bstan du byung ba'i gtso bo yid kyi rnam
NK117(she)001:25976: de dgra bcom pa'i rgyud la'ang yod pas bsgribs lung ma bstan pa yin /
NK117(she)001:25977: dge rtsa chad pa'i rgyud la'ang yod pas dge ba ma yin /
NK117(she)001:25978: gzugs med kyi rgyud la yod pas mi dge ba'ang ma yin /
NK117(she)001:25979: nyon yid ni dmigs pa'i cha nas kun gzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:25980: rnam pa'i cha nas rang sems pa'i ngo bo bsgribs lung du ma bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:25981: go bder brjod na sems tsam pa ni gzugs sgra
NK117(she)001:25982: dri ro reg bya sogs tshogs drug gi yul rnams
NK117(she)001:25983: rmi lam gyi skabs ltar shes pa gcig pu de
NK117(she)001:25984: / de dang der 'dzin ma yin gyi phyi rol na de ltar grub pa med de /
NK117(she)001:25985: gzugs la mtshon na mig dbang ni mig gi rnam par snang ba'i sems yin la /
NK117(she)001:25986: gzugs su snang ba yang de ltar gyi rnam par
NK117(she)001:25987: snang ba'i sems yin pas gzugs rang mtshan pa med
NK117(she)001:25988: cing yul la mig gi rnam shes skyes par snang
NK117(she)001:25990: dbang po dang shes pa gzugs gsum ka so sor
NK117(she)001:25991: snang ba ni 'khrul pa yin la shes pa'i ngo
NK117(she)001:25992: bo rdzas gcig pas mig shes kyis gzugs mthong yang
NK117(she)001:25993: shes pa rang gis rang mthong ba yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:25994: gzugs kyi rnam pa 'char ba'i rgyu shes pa las
NK117(she)001:25995: gzhan phyi rol du rnam pa gtod byed gzugs su
NK117(she)001:25996: grub pa gtan nas med do //
NK117(she)001:25997: 'on kyang brtag dpyad ma byas pa'i ngor mig gis
NK117(she)001:25998: gzugs mthong zhes sogs 'dod kyang de ltar ma grub
NK117(she)001:25999: ste / gzugs su snang ba'i shes pa de ni
NK117(she)001:26000: bden par grub bo zhes zer zhing rnam shes sogs
NK117(she)001:26001: shes pa thams cad kyi ngo bo bden par grub
NK117(she)001:26002: ste / la / yul phyi rol na yod par
NK117(she)001:26003: snang ba gzung cha dang rig pa nang na yod
NK117(she)001:26004: pa ltar snang ba 'dzin cha ste de gnyis 'khrul
NK117(she)001:26005: pa yin phyir gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa
NK117(she)001:26007: gzung 'dzin gnyis tha dad ma grub pas gnyis med
NK117(she)001:26008: kyi go chod pa dang rnam shes kyi rang ngo
NK117(she)001:26009: tsam ye shes su 'dod kyang gzung 'dzin ma khegs
NK117(she)001:26010: te / gzung 'dzin gnyis rdzas gzhan med pa tsam
NK117(she)001:26011: las 'dzin pa rang ngos na yod par khas blangs
NK117(she)001:26013: de'ang shes bya'i chos rnams kun brtags gzhan dbang yongs
NK117(she)001:26014: grub gsum las kun rdzob pa'i chos rnams thams cad
NK117(she)001:26015: ni kun brtags dang gzhan dbang du 'du la /
NK117(she)001:26016: don dam ni yongs grub tu 'du bas chos kyi bdag med kyang de rang yin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26017: gang zag gi bdag med kun brtags su 'dod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26018: dbu ma la rang rgyud pa dang thal 'gyur gnyis las dang po ni /
NK117(she)001:26020: ji ltar snang ba thams cad kun rdzob tu //
NK117(she)001:26021: grub pa sgyu ma lta bu'i mtshan nyid de //
NK117(she)001:26022: don dam grub pa med pa nam mkha' ltar //
NK117(she)001:26023: 'dod pa dbu ma rang rgyud pa yi lugs //
NK117(she)001:26024: zhes pa ni de yang ji ltar snang ba'i cha
NK117(she)001:26025: thams cad kun rdzob kyi cha nas sgyu mar snang
NK117(she)001:26026: yang / don dam par bden par ma grub pa
NK117(she)001:26027: nam mkha' ltar 'dod cing gdags gzhi'i ngos nas chos
NK117(she)001:26028: thams cad blo la ltos nas bden gnyis su 'jog
NK117(she)001:26029: pa de yang gshis la bden par ma grub bzhin
NK117(she)001:26030: du tha snyad kyi cha nas rang gi mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:26031: du grub par 'dod pas rang rgyud pa zhes bya'o
NK117(she)001:26032: yang / // de la'ang re zhig yongs su grags pa'i tshul bzhis rig par bya ste /
NK117(she)001:26038: chos can dngos po tsam yang don dam par bdag
NK117(she)001:26039: gzhan dang rgyu med pa las ma skyes pa de
NK117(she)001:26040: / skye ba'i dngos po mtha' dag gis stong ste
NK117(she)001:26041: don spyi tsam la dngos po med pa bzhin no
NK117(she)001:26043: chos can snang ba rten 'brel 'di yang don dam
NK117(she)001:26044: par rgyu la 'bras bu yod med skye ba gsum
NK117(she)001:26045: kas stong pa ste dper na dngos po med kyang
NK117(she)001:26046: ngo bo nyid kyis mtshon par byas pa bzhin no
NK117(she)001:26048: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka dpyad nas 'gog pa ste dper
NK117(she)001:26049: na dngos po med pa la nam mkha' zhes gdags
NK117(she)001:26050: pa bzhin no // bzhi pa la gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:26051: ma yin dgag ni rten 'brel chen mo rang gi ngo bo dpyad nas 'gog pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26052: med dgag kyang gcig dang du bral lo //
NK117(she)001:26053: de yang rten cing 'brel 'byung de nyid skye 'gag
NK117(she)001:26054: la sogs pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral bas rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:26055: gyis stong ste dper na smig rgyu ltar snang ba'i
NK117(she)001:26057: 'di yang mdor bsdus ltar 'god na gzugs sems gnyis
NK117(she)001:26058: dang ldan min 'du byed de 'dus byas kyi dngos
NK117(she)001:26059: po thams cad dang nam mkha' sogs 'dus ma byas
NK117(she)001:26060: dang dngos med thams cad ni kun rdzob yin la
NK117(she)001:26061: / de rnams kyi rang bzhin bden med tsam ni
NK117(she)001:26062: don dam yin zhing de gnyis ngo bo gcig dang
NK117(she)001:26063: tha dad gang du yang brjod du med cing rnam
NK117(she)001:26064: bzhag tsam tha dad de don dam dbyings kyi ngo
NK117(she)001:26065: bo na gang yang med pas spros bral nam mkha'i
NK117(she)001:26066: / dpes bstan / kun rdzob snang dus na bden
NK117(she)001:26067: pas stong yang snang ba ma 'gag pa sgyu ma'i
NK117(she)001:26068: / dpes bstan / dpes bstan / de gnyis kar
NK117(she)001:26069: yod med yin min sogs spros pa thams cad las
NK117(she)001:26071: da ni dbu ma thal 'gyur pa'i tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:26073: 'di ltar snang ba nyid ni kun rdzob dang //
NK117(she)001:26074: stong pa don dam zhes bya tha snyad kyi //
NK117(she)001:26075: btags pa gang yang spros pa'i mtha' dang bral //
NK117(she)001:26076: snang dus nyid nas skye 'gag 'gro 'ong med //
NK117(she)001:26077: gzhan dbang dngos por 'dod pa'i kun rdzob kyang //
NK117(she)001:26078: de yi grub pa'i mtha' ru khas ma blangs //
NK117(she)001:26079: de ni thal 'gyur shing rta'i srol 'byed che //
NK117(she)001:26080: klu dbang zla ba grags pa'i khyad chos yin //
NK117(she)001:26081: 'dir ni 'og ma'i rnam pa thams cad la //
NK117(she)001:26082: brtsad cing brtags pas gong ma nor mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:26083: zhes pa ni 'di ltar snang ba nyid kun rdzob
NK117(she)001:26084: dang stong pa nyid don dam zhes bya ba la
NK117(she)001:26085: sogs pa ni thos bsam las byung ba'i shes pas
NK117(she)001:26086: chos thams cad bden gnyis kyi tshul du slob par
NK117(she)001:26087: ston pa ste / tshur rol mthong ba'i blo can
NK117(she)001:26088: bden pa ma mthong ba rnams kyi ngor tha snyad
NK117(she)001:26089: la brten nas zhen pa'i bsam pas sbyar ba tsam
NK117(she)001:26090: ston pa ste / mo // bden gnyis kyang yang
NK117(she)001:26091: dag par na gcig yin na don dam yang kun
NK117(she)001:26092: rdzob ltar 'gyur ba can dang dri bcas su 'gyur
NK117(she)001:26093: ston pa ste / mo // ba'i skyon dang /
NK117(she)001:26094: tha dad yin na kun rdzob la gzugs sgra dri
NK117(she)001:26095: ro reg bya sogs 'dus byas kyi yul dang yul
NK117(she)001:26096: can sna tshogs yod pa bzhin don dam la'ang de
NK117(she)001:26097: ltar yod dgos pas chos kyi dbyings su mi 'gyur
NK117(she)001:26098: bas na gcig dang tha dad gang du'ang grub pa
NK117(she)001:26099: ston pa ste / mo // ba'i skyon dang /
NK117(she)001:26100: med do // brdar btags kyi grub mtha' 'dis ni
NK117(she)001:26101: gzhan gyi dam bca' 'gog cing rang rgyud kyi gtan
NK117(she)001:26102: tshigs khas len thams cad dang bral bas pha rol
NK117(she)001:26103: gyi dam bca' 'gog pa'i 'gal chos thal 'gyur gyi
NK117(she)001:26104: sgo nas gtso bor byed pas thal 'gyur pa zhes
NK117(she)001:26105: ston pa ste / mo // ba'i skyon dang /
NK117(she)001:26106: med do // bya'o // 'di'i lugs la sems tsam
NK117(she)001:26107: man chad du 'dod pa'i 'dus ma byas gsum sogs
NK117(she)001:26108: 'dus ma byas btags pa ba dngos med rnams dang
NK117(she)001:26109: ston pa ste / mo // ba'i skyon dang /
NK117(she)001:26110: med do // bya'o // / gzugs sogs phyi don
NK117(she)001:26111: du grags pa dang rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad
NK117(she)001:26112: sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig sogs mdor na gzhi
NK117(she)001:26113: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang gnas skabs lam gyis
NK117(she)001:26114: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad dang /
NK117(she)001:26115: 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyis bsdus pa'i nang nas gsar
NK117(she)001:26116: du byung ba'i cha rnams dang gdul bya gzhan snang
NK117(she)001:26117: gis bsdus pa ste snang grags kyi chos sam /
NK117(she)001:26118: chos chos nyid kyi zlas phye ba'i chos sam /
NK117(she)001:26119: gzung 'dzin gyis bsdus pa'i chos sogs /
NK117(she)001:26120: don dam gtan la 'beb pa'i skabs 'dir dngos po
NK117(she)001:26121: dngos med thams cad 'dus byas dang glo bur bar
NK117(she)001:26122: bzhag pa de rnams ni bden med yin la dbyings
NK117(she)001:26123: su gcig dang gnyis su med pa'i ye shes rang
NK117(she)001:26124: rig rang gsal ni don dam bden pa chos nyid
NK117(she)001:26126: 'di ni rig pas dpyad bzod bden grub kho na
NK117(she)001:26127: ste rgya gar du dbu ma chen po dang bod
NK117(she)001:26128: yul 'dir gzhan stong dbu ma zhes smra'o //
NK117(she)001:26129: dbu ma phal pa'i rang stong pa rnams kyi 'dod
NK117(she)001:26130: pa'i nam mkha' lta bu de ni rnam par dpyad
NK117(she)001:26131: na dngos med yin pa'i phyir don dam bden par
NK117(she)001:26132: mi 'dod do // de bas na grub pa'i mtha'
NK117(she)001:26133: 'dir ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin skye ba
NK117(she)001:26134: med la chos nyid spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang
NK117(she)001:26135: bral bas snang ba'i dus tsam nas ma skyes pa
NK117(she)001:26136: mi 'dod do // dang / ma 'gags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26137: gzod ma nas zhi ba dang /
NK117(she)001:26138: rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pas khas len
NK117(she)001:26139: pa'i kun rdzob tsam yang 'gog cing gshis thog tu
NK117(she)001:26140: gtan la phebs pa la dbu ma'i lta bar 'dod
NK117(she)001:26141: kyi / gtan la 'bebs yul gyi stong nyid mtha'
NK117(she)001:26142: bral dbu ma'i lta bar 'dod na ni mtha' bzhi
NK117(she)001:26143: po de ka mthar 'dzin gyi lta bar 'gyur bas
NK117(she)001:26144: mtha' dang mthar 'dzin gyi khyad par ma phyed pa
NK117(she)001:26146: rang rang 'dod zhen gyis sbyar ltos grub kyi //
NK117(she)001:26147: grub pa'i mtha' yi mtshan nyid nyams 'og chud //
NK117(she)001:26148: de las dngos dang dngos 'dra dngos min gyi //
NK117(she)001:26149: mtshan nyid legs par 'byed pa'i shes rab kyang //
NK117(she)001:26150: thos la brten 'byung de yi nyon mongs bcil //
NK117(she)001:26151: nyon mongs med la bdud kyis glags mi rnyed //
NK117(she)001:26152: ces de la spyir 'phags bod kun dang khyad par
NK117(she)001:26153: bod 'dir so so'i skye bo phal gyi rang rang
NK117(she)001:26154: gi 'dod zhen gyis sbyar ba'i gzhung la ltos pa'i
NK117(she)001:26155: lta grub kyi skyon mang ba yang 'phags yul na'ang
NK117(she)001:26156: theg chen bka' min par bsgrags shing /
NK117(she)001:26157: ston pas stong nyid zab mo ston pa la lung
NK117(she)001:26158: du bstan pa 'phags mchog klu sgrub sogs kyang chos
NK117(she)001:26159: log mkhan du bsgrags pa byung bar nges na /
NK117(she)001:26160: da lta'i dus na rang rang gi kun 'byung rnam
NK117(she)001:26161: pa tha dad pa bskyed cing bskrun pa'i grub mtha'
NK117(she)001:26162: mang zhing / de thams cad kyang rang rang gi
NK117(she)001:26163: blo nus dang rjes su mthun pa'i rgyal ba'i phrin
NK117(she)001:26164: las sems can la phan pa can yin par stangs
NK117(she)001:26165: bcad na phyogs lhung dang ring bar cis mi 'gyur
NK117(she)001:26166: mang zhing / / 'on kyang grub pa'i mtha' yi
NK117(she)001:26167: mtshan nyid nyams 'og tu chud pa gal che zhing
NK117(she)001:26168: mang zhing / / / de las kyang dngos po
NK117(she)001:26169: gshis kyi gnas lugs ji lta ba dang de dang
NK117(she)001:26170: 'dra tsam pa dang dngos min yin lugs ngom pa
NK117(she)001:26171: bcas kyi mtshan nyid legs par 'byed pa'i shes rab
NK117(she)001:26172: nyid kyang thos pa la brten nas 'byung zhing de
NK117(she)001:26173: yis nyon mongs pa'i dgra tshogs bcil zhing ye shes
NK117(she)001:26174: mngon du byed cing nyon mongs med par gyur pa
NK117(she)001:26175: la bdud sde'i dpung tshogs kyis glags kyang mi rnyed
NK117(she)001:26178: 'dir gang bzung na gshis kyi bzhugs tshul la //
NK117(she)001:26179: smra bsam brjod med don dam bden pa yin //
NK117(she)001:26180: blo yi cha nas smra bsam brjod pa ru //
NK117(she)001:26181: brtags shing snang ba kun rdzob bden pa'i char //
NK117(she)001:26182: bzhag nas bden gnyis rtogs bya rtogs byed las //
NK117(she)001:26183: 'das pa sus kyang mngon du byar med la //
NK117(she)001:26184: bltar med thob dang ma thob gnyis ka med //
NK117(she)001:26185: stong pa nyid dang nges par rjes mthun pa'i //
NK117(she)001:26186: blo skyes pa la rtogs pa'i bla dwags btags //
NK117(she)001:26187: zhes pa ni de la gzhung 'dir gang bzung na gshis kyi bzhugs tshul te /
NK117(she)001:26188: sems nyid kyi gnas lugs gtan la phab pa la /
NK117(she)001:26189: smra bsam brjod du med pa don dam pa'i bden
NK117(she)001:26190: pa yin kyang blo yi cha nas gzhal na smra
NK117(she)001:26191: rgyu dang bsam brjod yod par sgro btags shing snang
NK117(she)001:26192: ba'i dngos po kun rdzob bden pa'i char bzhag nas
NK117(she)001:26193: brgal brtags shing snang ba'i dngos po kun rdzob bden
NK117(she)001:26194: pa'i char bzhag nas brgal brtags byed mod kyang bden
NK117(she)001:26195: gnyis rtogs bya rtogs byed las 'das pa'i don sus
NK117(she)001:26196: kyang mngon du byar med la /
NK117(she)001:26197: de lta'i gnas tshul la bltar med cing thob rgyu
NK117(she)001:26198: dang ma thob rgyu gnyis ka med par rtogs tshe
NK117(she)001:26199: stong pa nyid dang nges par rjes su mthun pa'i
NK117(she)001:26200: blo skyes pa la rtogs pa'i bla dwags te tha
NK117(she)001:26201: snyad btags pa tsam du zad do //
NK117(she)001:26202: de la sa dang po 'phags pa'i mnyam gzhag dang
NK117(she)001:26203: sangs rgyas kyi sa na shes bya shes byed la
NK117(she)001:26204: sogs pa'i yul yul can gyi shes bya rang rgyud
NK117(she)001:26205: pa gang yang ma grub pas gzung 'dzin las rnam
NK117(she)001:26206: par 'das pa ste yul can ye shes kyi 'jug
NK117(she)001:26207: pa'ang zhi ba de'i tshe sems dang sems las byung
NK117(she)001:26208: ba'i 'jug pa thams cad rgyud chad de /
NK117(she)001:26209: smra bsam brjod du med pa'i chos nyid rtogs pa ni don dam pa'i bden pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26212: chos rnams ma lus kun gyi mdzod //
NK117(she)001:26213: gang la bsam pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK117(she)001:26214: yang dag 'jug pa lde mig yin //
NK117(she)001:26215: zhes pa ni chos rnams gang zhig rten cing 'brel
NK117(she)001:26216: bar 'byung ba rnams ni 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams
NK117(she)001:26217: ma lus kun gyi mdzod yin bzhin gang la bsam
NK117(she)001:26218: pa'i shes rab kyis thos bsam sgom gsum la yang
NK117(she)001:26219: dag par 'jug pa ni chos rnams kyi sgo lcags
NK117(she)001:26220: 'byed pa'i lde mig lta bu yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26221: de bas na bsam pa'i shes rab kyis rig pa
NK117(she)001:26222: dang lung gis brtags la yang dag pa'i don ni
NK117(she)001:26223: nges par 'byed pa'i cha dang mthun pa'i shes rab
NK117(she)001:26224: zab mo rtog ge'i spyod yul las 'das pa kho
NK117(she)001:26225: na yin na de'i rang bzhin bye brag phyed par
NK117(she)001:26226: byas la mngon sum bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:26229: gang nas kyang ni ma 'ongs la //
NK117(she)001:26230: gang du'ang ma song mi gnas pa //
NK117(she)001:26231: gshis la gnas pa'i rten cing 'brel //
NK117(she)001:26232: chos can nyid kyang skye 'gag ltar //
NK117(she)001:26233: snang dus nyid nas stong par shar //
NK117(she)001:26234: spros pa'i mtha' la mi gnas pa //
NK117(she)001:26235: dbu ma'i rang bzhin nyid du bstan //
NK117(she)001:26236: zhes pa ni dbang po drug gi yul du snang
NK117(she)001:26237: ba'i bslu zhing rdzun pa'i rigs dang srid pa g.yo
NK117(she)001:26238: zhing 'du byed pa 'khor ba ni kun 'byung rang
NK117(she)001:26239: rgyud ldan myang 'das yang rang bzhin gyi chos nyid
NK117(she)001:26240: la ming gi gdags pa nyid de /
NK117(she)001:26241: 'di ltar chos can dang chos nyid du snang ba'i
NK117(she)001:26242: chos thams cad dang po gang nas kyang 'ongs pa
NK117(she)001:26243: med pas ma skyes pa zhes bya ste 'das pa
NK117(she)001:26244: ma yin bar du gang du'ang gnas pa med pas
NK117(she)001:26245: rang bzhin ma mchis pa ste da lta ba ma
NK117(she)001:26246: yin tha mar gang du 'gro ba'ang med pas mi
NK117(she)001:26247: 'byung ba ste ma 'ongs pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:26249: dag dang ma dag glo bur ba //
NK117(she)001:26250: don la med kyang med bzhin snang //
NK117(she)001:26251: kun tu btags pas nye bar len //
NK117(she)001:26252: rtog cing dpyad pas mtha' bzhi byung //
NK117(she)001:26253: yod dang med dang rtag 'chad dang //
NK117(she)001:26254: dbus la gnas pa'ang mkhas pa min //
NK117(she)001:26255: zhes pa ni de yang dag pa myang 'das dang
NK117(she)001:26256: ma dag pa 'khor ba gnyis ka glo bur 'khrul
NK117(she)001:26257: pa'i snang bar shar ba tsam las don la med
NK117(she)001:26258: kyang / med bzhin du snang ba kun tu brtags
NK117(she)001:26259: pas nye bar len bzhin gshis kyi gnas lugs la
NK117(she)001:26260: rtog cing dpyad pas mtha' bzhir lta ba zhes phyi
NK117(she)001:26261: rol pa'i lta log sum brgya drug cu'i rtsa ba
NK117(she)001:26262: kyang / lta bu dang / nang pa yin kyang
NK117(she)001:26263: de rjes 'brangs pa 'ga' dang 'ga' yis lta sgom
NK117(she)001:26264: nor ba'i skyon gyis sems nyid la yod 'dzin dang
NK117(she)001:26265: med 'dzin dang rtag par lta ba dang chad par
NK117(she)001:26266: lta ba sogs kyi skyon chags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26267: phal cher mtha' bzhir ma lhungs par rloms kyang dbus
NK117(she)001:26268: la gnas pa ste dbu ma khas blangs nas mchog
NK117(she)001:26269: 'dzin gyi lta ba dregs shing 'khun pa dag mkhas
NK117(she)001:26270: pa'i bya ba min zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26272: ji ltar dar gyi srin bu bzhin //
NK117(she)001:26273: 'dod pa'i grub mthas rang nyid bcings //
NK117(she)001:26274: 'di na blo yis btags pa'i chos //
NK117(she)001:26276: don gcig ma yin tha dad min //
NK117(she)001:26277: rtag pa ma yin chad pa min //
NK117(she)001:26278: spros pa mtha' dag nyer zhi ba'i //
NK117(she)001:26279: rang bzhin nyid du shes pa ni //
NK117(she)001:26280: bsam byung shes rab ngo bo yin //
NK117(she)001:26281: zhes pa ni de la dpe ji ltar na dar
NK117(she)001:26282: gyi srin bu ste sdom gyi kha chus rgya bres
NK117(she)001:26283: nas der rang nyid thogs pa bzhin du chos nyid
NK117(she)001:26284: bsam gyis mi khyab pa bsam yod brjod yod du
NK117(she)001:26285: 'dod pa'i grub mthas rang nyid bcings shing 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:26286: 'dam la bying ba yin mod kyang 'jig rten 'di
NK117(she)001:26287: na blo yis btags pa'i chos thams cad thog mar
NK117(she)001:26288: skye ba med pa bar du 'gag pa med pa
NK117(she)001:26289: mthar gnas pa dang 'gro ba dang 'ong ba sogs
NK117(she)001:26290: ma yin zhing / don gcig ma yin zhing tha
NK117(she)001:26291: dad kyang min pa rtag pa ma yin la chad
NK117(she)001:26292: pa'ang min pa bsam brjod las 'das pas spros pa
NK117(she)001:26293: mtha' dag nye bar zhi ba'i rang bzhin stong pa
NK117(she)001:26294: nyid du shes pa ni thos pa'i don la mno
NK117(she)001:26295: bsam gzhig pa las byung ba'i shes rab kyi ngo
NK117(she)001:26298: snang yul sa chu me rlung mkha' //
NK117(she)001:26299: ri dang nags tshal khang bu brtsegs //
NK117(she)001:26300: 'dus byas rgyu las thams cad skyes //
NK117(she)001:26302: zhes pa ni 'di ltar snang ba'i yul ni phyi
NK117(she)001:26303: 'byung lnga dang de la brten pa'i ri dang nags
NK117(she)001:26304: tshal sbra khang sogs sdod yul gyi rten dang de
NK117(she)001:26305: la brten pa'i mi nor sogs 'dus byas pa kun
NK117(she)001:26306: rgyu las thams cad skyes pa ni 'khor ba rten
NK117(she)001:26308: 'di ltar lang gshegs sogs zab mo'i mdo sde dag
NK117(she)001:26309: las kun gzhi'i rnam shes dgongs pa can gyi gsungs
NK117(she)001:26310: pa des thog mar phyi rol pa'i lugs bsal ba'i
NK117(she)001:26312: phyi nas zab mo'i don rig pa rnams kyis kun
NK117(she)001:26313: gzhi'i rnam shes yod par 'dzin pa spong ba nyid
NK117(she)001:26314: de / 'dir re zhig 'khor ba'i rten cing 'brel
NK117(she)001:26315: 'byung can dag ni shes pa rtog med yengs thabs
NK117(she)001:26316: kyi dus snang yul tshogs drug 'dzin pa'i kun gzhi
NK117(she)001:26317: de / dang / gsal snang la der 'dzin mi
NK117(she)001:26318: 'jug pa de'i rnam shes de sgo lnga'i yul la
NK117(she)001:26319: dgag bsgrub gzung 'dzin du rten cing 'brel bas rnam
NK117(she)001:26320: shes tshogs drug nyon yid dang bdun du btags pa'i
NK117(she)001:26321: 'khrul ngo la 'khrul snang shar ba mtha' dag ni
NK117(she)001:26322: phyi'i rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ste gcig la
NK117(she)001:26323: gcig ltos kyi tshul du byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26326: ma rig pa las 'du byed de //
NK117(she)001:26327: de bzhin gcig la gcig brten gyis //
NK117(she)001:26328: rga shi'i bar du 'brel ba ni //
NK117(she)001:26330: zhes pa ni 'dir nyan thos theg pa'i lugs ltar 'chad na /
NK117(she)001:26331: tshe snga ma'i nyon mongs pa spyod dus kyi phung po lnga ni ma rig pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26332: de bzhin du snga ma'i las gsag dus kyi phung po lnga ni 'du byed /
