NK117(she)001:26333: de'i 'gres kyis ma'i mngal du nying mtshams sbyor dus kyi phung po lnga ni rnam shes so //
NK117(she)001:26334: mer mer po sogs 'gyur ba'i gnas skabs lnga nyams
NK117(she)001:26335: su myong nas dbang po'i sgo ma dod bar gyi
NK117(she)001:26336: phung po lnga ni ming gzugs so //
NK117(she)001:26337: sgo dod nas yul la spyod mi nus bar gyi phung po lnga ni skye mched drug go //
NK117(she)001:26338: dbang po yul la sad nas bde sdug gi bye
NK117(she)001:26339: brag mi shes pa'i bar gyi phung po lnga ni
NK117(she)001:26340: reg pa'o // bde sdug stangs phyed pa nas 'khrig
NK117(she)001:26341: pa bsten mi nus bar gyi phung po lnga ni
NK117(she)001:26342: reg pa'o // tshor ba'o // 'khrig pa bsten nus
NK117(she)001:26343: pa nas 'dod yul dang du ma blang bar gyi
NK117(she)001:26344: phung po lnga ni sred pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26345: 'dod yul dang du blangs pa'i gnas skabs kyi phung po lnga ni len pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26346: de nas las gsog pa'i gnas skabs phung po lnga ni srid pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26347: tshe phyi ma'i thog mar ma'i mngal nas byung ba'i bar gyi phung po lnga ni skye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26348: de nas phyi ma'i ming gzugs skye mched drug reg sred tshor ba bzhi po ni rga shi'o //
NK117(she)001:26349: de lta'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis la skad cig dang rgyun chags gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:26350: bya rdzogs kyi skad cig ni bdag gzhan gyi dbang
NK117(she)001:26351: gis srog gcod dus sdig to'i sems de ni ma
NK117(she)001:26352: rig pa / de'i las la 'jug pa 'du byed /
NK117(she)001:26353: de dus kyi rnam rig ni rnam shes /
NK117(she)001:26354: rang bzhin gyi ming gzugs dang skye mched drug /
NK117(she)001:26355: mtshon bsnun pa reg pa des sdug bsngal ba ni tshor ba /
NK117(she)001:26356: de la phyir zhing dga' ba sred pa /
NK117(she)001:26357: de nas skye ba phyi mar 'jug pas len pa /
NK117(she)001:26358: de las phung po lnga'i cha ldan srid pa /
NK117(she)001:26359: de las da lta dang phyi ma'i cha skye ba
NK117(she)001:26360: de'i cha'i rga shi ste bya ba gcig mgo brtsams
NK117(she)001:26361: nas rdzogs pa'i bar gyi skad cig la tshang ba'o
NK117(she)001:26362: // yang shes bya la shes pa wal gyis 'jug pa la dus matha'i skad cig dang /
NK117(she)001:26363: de lta bu'i yun brgya nyi shu la de'i skad cig ste rnam grangs gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:26366: lam dang 'bras bu gnyis su gnas //
NK117(she)001:26368: lugs su 'jug pa bcu gnyis kyi //
NK117(she)001:26369: rtsa ba ma rig chen po ni //
NK117(she)001:26370: rig pa'i ye shes kyis ldog pas //
NK117(she)001:26371: 'du byed la sogs gzhan rnams kyang //
NK117(she)001:26372: lugs ldog srid pa'i rtsa ba chad //
NK117(she)001:26374: mtshan nyid mthong ba'i skyes bu yis //
NK117(she)001:26375: sdug bsngal shes shing kun 'byung spong //
NK117(she)001:26376: 'gog pa mngon gyur lam mchog mthong //
NK117(she)001:26377: zhes pa ni de la 'khor ba ni mya ngan
NK117(she)001:26378: gyi sa dang de las 'das pa ni thar pa
NK117(she)001:26379: dang rnam mkhyen gyi lam yin phyir de'i rten cing
NK117(she)001:26380: 'brel 'byung ni lam lnga dang 'bras bu sku gsum
NK117(she)001:26381: gnyis su gnas la lam ni 'khor bar rten cing
NK117(she)001:26382: 'brel 'byung ltar te lugs su 'jug pa bcu gnyis
NK117(she)001:26383: kyi rtsa ba ma rig pa chen po de ni
NK117(she)001:26384: 'khor ba'i rgyu'i sa bon yin kyang de nyid rig
NK117(she)001:26385: pa'i ye shes kyis ldog pas 'du byed la sogs
NK117(she)001:26386: gzhan rnams kyang rim pa bzhin du lugs las ldog
NK117(she)001:26387: ste srid pa'i rtsa ba chad nas slar 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:26388: don dang / de ltar rten cing 'brel 'byung gi
NK117(she)001:26389: mtshan nyid de rgyu mtshan ji bzhin mthong ba'i skyes
NK117(she)001:26390: bu blo ldan de yis sdug bsngal gyi bden pa
NK117(she)001:26391: shes shing de'i rgyu kun 'byung gi bden pa las
NK117(she)001:26392: nyon spong ba'i thabs la brtson na 'gog pa ste
NK117(she)001:26393: nyon mongs rgyun chad tshe bden pa mngon du gyur
NK117(she)001:26394: zhing lam mchog ces 'bras bzang mthong ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26396: de ltar snang ba skye med du //
NK117(she)001:26397: bsam pas gtan la phab pa de'i //
NK117(she)001:26398: rang bzhin shes pa'i chos nyid la //
NK117(she)001:26399: bsgom pa'i shes rab ces su grags //
NK117(she)001:26400: zhes pa ni de ltar zhes gong bzhin du snang
NK117(she)001:26401: ba skye 'gag med par bsam pas gtan la phab
NK117(she)001:26402: pa de'i rang bzhin ni smra bsam brjod med yin
NK117(she)001:26403: pa shes pa'i chos nyid nyams su len pa la
NK117(she)001:26404: bsgom pa'i shes rab ces su grags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26405: de phyir bsgom pa'i shes rab ni chos la bdag
NK117(she)001:26406: med par mthong zhing rang bzhin med pa'i don la
NK117(she)001:26407: rang bzhin gyis rnal du 'byor pas snang ba med
NK117(she)001:26408: pa'i ye shes mthong ba nyid yin te /
NK117(she)001:26409: de la dngos por yod med sogs yid byed kyi
NK117(she)001:26410: blos bsgom du med kyang gdod nas rang bzhin gyis
NK117(she)001:26411: shin tu rnam par grol ba'i shes rab kyi dbyings
NK117(she)001:26412: la dran pa nye bar 'jog pa la bsgom pa'i
NK117(she)001:26415: nam mkha' rnam par dag pa'i dbyings //
NK117(she)001:26416: bsgom pa'i don dang ro gcig pa //
NK117(she)001:26417: de la gzugs sogs phung po lnga //
NK117(she)001:26418: tshogs brgyad kun kyang yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:26419: zhes pa ni 'di ltar sems nyid kyi gnas lugs
NK117(she)001:26420: nam mkha' rnam par dag pa'i dbyings lta bu ste
NK117(she)001:26421: bsgom pa'i don dang ro gcig pa de la gzugs
NK117(she)001:26422: sgra dri ro reg bya sogs phung po lnga dang
NK117(she)001:26423: tshogs brgyad kun kyang yod pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:26425: med ces blo yis bkag pa na //
NK117(she)001:26426: shes rab nyid dang lhag par 'gal //
NK117(she)001:26427: cang med chad pa nyid ma yin //
NK117(she)001:26428: sku dang ye shes kun gyi mdzod //
NK117(she)001:26429: ces pa ni 'di ltar yod mtha' bkag nas med
NK117(she)001:26430: pa zhig glo bur du bsgom pa byar med de
NK117(she)001:26431: / don la med ces blo yis bkag par gyur
NK117(she)001:26432: na shes rab nyid dang lhag par 'gal bas cang
NK117(she)001:26433: med kyi stong par bzung na chad par 'gyur bas
NK117(she)001:26434: de nyid kyang ma yin te sku dang ye shes
NK117(she)001:26435: kun gyi mdzod yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26437: rang bzhin nyid du rnam dag pa'i //
NK117(she)001:26438: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK117(she)001:26439: blta zhes bya ba'ang kun rdzob ste //
NK117(she)001:26440: ngang las ma g.yos bsgom pa'i mchog /
NK117(she)001:26441: de yi mdun na blo dang ni //
NK117(she)001:26442: yid byed thams cad gnas pa min //
NK117(she)001:26443: shes rab de 'drar yongs shes na //
NK117(she)001:26444: thabs kyis rnam par grol bar 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:26445: shes rab med pa'i thabs kyis ni //
NK117(she)001:26446: bcings pa nyid las grol ba med //
NK117(she)001:26447: ces pa ni de la byang chub sems dpa' rnams
NK117(she)001:26448: kyi lam ni shes rab kyi stobs kyis 'khor bar
NK117(she)001:26449: mi lhung la thabs kyi stobs kyis myang 'das kyi
NK117(she)001:26452: shes rab med pa'i thabs dang thabs dang bral ba'i
NK117(she)001:26453: shes rab kyis ni bcings pa nyid las grol ba
NK117(she)001:26454: med do // de lta bu'i thabs shes 'brel ba'i
NK117(she)001:26455: lam 'dis ni sgro skur gyi mtha' spangs pa'i dbu
NK117(she)001:26457: 'di ltar shes rab can gyis ni sgro 'dogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:26458: mtha' spangs la thabs kyis ni skur ba'i mtha' spong
NK117(she)001:26460: gang du stong nyid snying rje gnyis //
NK117(she)001:26461: rgyud la bsten pa tshogs lam che //
NK117(she)001:26462: sbyor lam chos mchog man chad du //
NK117(she)001:26463: mnyam rjes stong dang snying rjer 'char //
NK117(she)001:26464: zhes pa ni 'di ltar mnyam bzhag tu stong nyid
NK117(she)001:26465: dang rjes thob snying rje'i snying po can gyi sbyin
NK117(she)001:26466: pa la sogs pa tshogs zung yongs su bsgrub pa
NK117(she)001:26467: la 'jug pa ni tshogs lam ste /
NK117(she)001:26468: theg chen gyi sems bskyed gsar du skyes pa'i rten
NK117(she)001:26469: gang yin pa des theg chen sems bskyed dang por
NK117(she)001:26470: thob nas tshogs lam chung ngur 'jug nus pa yin
NK117(she)001:26471: la bsgom tshul bye brag pa'i cha nas tshogs lam
NK117(she)001:26472: la che 'bring chung gsum yod pa'i chung ngur dran
NK117(she)001:26474: lus dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK117(she)001:26475: mnyam bzhag tu nam mkha' ltar sgom zhing /
NK117(she)001:26476: rjes thob tu mi gtsang ba dang sgyu ma ltar bsgom pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26477: tshor ba dran pa nyer bzhag ni mnyam bzhag tu ma skyes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26478: rjes thob tu tshor ba mtha' dag sgyu ma dang chu shing ltar snying po med par bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:26479: sems dran pa nyer bzhag ni mnyam bzhag tu rang
NK117(she)001:26480: bzhin gyis stong pa dang rjes thob tu mi 'gag
NK117(she)001:26481: pa mi gnas par bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:26482: chos dran pa nyer bzhag ni mnyam bzhag tu mnyam pa nyid /
NK117(she)001:26483: rjes thob tu sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad la sogs par bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:26484: tshogs lam 'bring du mi dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams mi bskyed /
NK117(she)001:26485: skyes pa rgyun bcad pa'i phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:26486: dge chos rnams ma skyes pa bskyed /
NK117(she)001:26487: skyes pa gong du spel ba'i phyir brtson pas 'jug cing gnyen po bdag med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26488: sgyu ma'am rmi lam la sogs pa bsgom mo //
NK117(she)001:26489: tshogs lam chen por rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi
NK117(she)001:26490: ni 'dun pa brtson 'grus sems pa dpyod pa'i ting
NK117(she)001:26491: 'dzin bzhi'i rdzu 'phrul dang mngon shes dang spyan la
NK117(she)001:26492: sogs bsam gtan gyi sems las su rung stobs kyis
NK117(she)001:26493: 'grub pas na rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa zhes bya'o
NK117(she)001:26494: // de'i rjes la rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK117(she)001:26495: shes mthong lam myur du sbyor ba'i lam ste lus
NK117(she)001:26496: kyis rten 'gro ba lnga gang rung la bsam pa'i
NK117(she)001:26497: rten bsam gtan sa drug pa gang rung yin no
NK117(she)001:26498: // // de yang drod rtse gnyis su dad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26502: shes rab ste dbang po lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:26503: bzod chos gnyis su dad pas yid ches brtson 'grus
NK117(she)001:26504: kyis spro dran pas mi brjed ting 'dzin gyi rtse
NK117(she)001:26505: gcig shes rab kyis rang bzhin shes pa'i tshul gyis
NK117(she)001:26506: bsgom pa'o // de'ang nges par 'byed pa'i cha bzhi
NK117(she)001:26507: la che 'bring chen po'i dbye bas bcu gnyis gnas
NK117(she)001:26508: tshul sogs rgyas 'grel las blta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:26509: 'di man chad kyi ye shes kyi ngo bo mnyam
NK117(she)001:26510: bzhag gi cha ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK117(she)001:26511: shes stong nyid dang de las langs pa'i rjes thob
NK117(she)001:26512: ni snying rje chen po'i cha rtog bcas rtog med
NK117(she)001:26515: mthong lam thob nas gnyis po ni //
NK117(she)001:26517: rab tu dga' ba dang po'i sar //
NK117(she)001:26518: chos nyid bden pa mngon sum mthong //
NK117(she)001:26519: zhes pa ni mthong lam thob par gyur pa de'i
NK117(she)001:26520: tshe stong nyid snying rje gnyis po zung du 'jug
NK117(she)001:26521: cing tshur 'du ba dang phar 'bral rgyu gang yang
NK117(she)001:26522: med cing rab tu dga' ba zhes dang po'i sar
NK117(she)001:26523: sleb tshe chos nyid kyi bden pa mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:26526: de nas 'phags pa'i sgom lam du //
NK117(she)001:26527: sa bcu rgyun gyi mtha' ma la //
NK117(she)001:26528: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK117(she)001:26529: shes sgrib bcom nas mngon byang chub //
NK117(she)001:26530: ces pa ni de yang mthong lam rdzogs nas 'phags
NK117(she)001:26531: pa'i sgom lam du sa bcu chos kyi sprin thob
NK117(she)001:26532: nas de'i rgyun gyi mtha' ma la rdo rje lta
NK117(she)001:26533: bu'i ting 'dzin thob pa'i stobs kyis shes bya'i sgrib
NK117(she)001:26534: pa ma lus pa bcom nas mngon par byang chub
NK117(she)001:26535: pa zhes sangs rgyas kyi go sar slebs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26536: de la sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi
NK117(she)001:26537: ngos 'dzin dang dbye ba yon tan sogs bshad pa
NK117(she)001:26538: rgyas pa 'grel chen las shes par bya zhing /
NK117(she)001:26539: 'dir sa bcad ma stong tsam du cung zad bri na /
NK117(she)001:26540: sa dang po skad cig snga phyi med bzhin du sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal blta ba dang /
NK117(she)001:26541: ting nge 'dzin brgya thob pa zhing khams brgyar 'gro
NK117(she)001:26542: ba sems can brgya skyong bzhin chos sgor 'jug par
NK117(she)001:26543: byed pa bskal brgyar 'jug cing lus brgya rab tu
NK117(she)001:26544: ston par byed pa rgyal ba'i sras kyang brgya yi
NK117(she)001:26545: grangs tshang rab tu ston pa sogs yon tan brgya
NK117(she)001:26546: phrag bcu ga nyis mngon du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26547: de bzhin du sa gnyis par stong phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:26549: bzhi par bye ba brgya phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:26550: lnga par bye ba stong phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:26551: drug par bye ba khrag khrig bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:26552: bdun par khrag khrig 'bum phrag bcu gnyis /
NK117(she)001:26553: brgyad par stong chen 'bum phrag gcig gi rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK117(she)001:26554: dgu par 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK117(she)001:26555: bcu par brjod du med pa'i grangs dang mnyam pa'i
NK117(she)001:26556: sangs rgyas kyi zhal blta ba dang chos nyan pa
NK117(she)001:26557: dang zhing g.yo bar byed pa dang 'od kyis gsal
NK117(she)001:26558: bar byed pa dang zhing de dag tu 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:26559: dang / sems can smin par byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26560: chos sgo 'byed pa dang ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par 'jog pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26561: dus skad cig gcig bskal pa du mar ston cing /
NK117(she)001:26562: bskal pa du ma skad cig ma gcig tu ston pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26563: sngon dang phyi ma'i mtha' de snyed la gzigs pa 'jug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26564: rang lus sangs rgyas kyi sku du mar 'phrul pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26565: de re re la'ang 'khor du mas bskor bar ston
NK117(she)001:26566: pa rnams skad cig snga phyi med par 'byung ngo
NK117(she)001:26567: // de lta'i yon tan yang khams kyi steng gi
NK117(she)001:26568: sgrib pa bral stobs las sngon med gsar du mthong
NK117(she)001:26569: // ba'am / de las ldog pa'i khyad par bde
NK117(she)001:26570: gshegs snying po drang nges gnyis su 'dod pa'i phyogs
NK117(she)001:26572: slob dpon zla grags kyis bde gshegs snying po drang don du bshad cing /
NK117(she)001:26573: rgyud bla ma'i dgongs pa'ang dgongs gzhi stong nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:26574: dgos pa skyon lnga spang phyir 'dod phyogs su bslan
NK117(she)001:26575: na tshogs brgyad dang 'brel ba'i dpyad pa rnon pos
NK117(she)001:26576: phyir mi ldog pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo'i gtam drang
NK117(she)001:26577: don du khas len pa rnams la bde ste /
NK117(she)001:26578: de'i dgongs gzhi chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba nyid de /
NK117(she)001:26581: sems zhum sems can dman la brnyas pa yang //
NK117(she)001:26582: yang dag mi 'dzin yang dag chos la bskur //
NK117(she)001:26583: bdag chags lhag pa'i skyon lnga gang dag la //
NK117(she)001:26584: yod pa de dag spong ba'i don du gsungs //
NK117(she)001:26585: zhes pas nyes pa lnga bsal zhing bdag la mngon
NK117(she)001:26586: par zhen pa drang ba'i phyir 'gro rgyud la rtag
NK117(she)001:26587: brtan ther zug gi sku bzhugs so'i sgras tshig tsam
NK117(she)001:26588: la rton pa dag mu stegs byed kyi bdag dang
NK117(she)001:26590: ma 'ongs pa'i dus na bla med kyi byang chub
NK117(she)001:26591: yod phyir sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin zhes bya ba'o
NK117(she)001:26592: // sems can rnams la da lta nyon mongs pa rnams yod phyir mtshan dpe dngos su med do //
NK117(she)001:26593: de dag ni 'khor lo bar pa'i ched du byas
NK117(she)001:26594: pa'i gdul byas 'khor lo tha ma la ltos mi
NK117(she)001:26595: dgos par rnam thar sgo gsum gyi dgongs pa rang
NK117(she)001:26596: stobs kyis dpyad nus la tha ma'i ched du bya
NK117(she)001:26597: ba'i gdul byas de ltar dpyod par mi nus shing
NK117(she)001:26598: 'khor lo tha ma la brten nas bar pa'i dgongs
NK117(she)001:26599: pa tshol dgos par 'dod cing de gnyis la dbang
NK117(she)001:26600: po rno rtul gyi khyad par 'byed kyang /
NK117(she)001:26601: khyad gzhi de ni yang dag par mi rung ste
NK117(she)001:26602: 'khor lo tha ma'i gdul bya yin tshad dbang rtul
NK117(she)001:26603: yin pa cis grub phar phyin drug la spyod cing
NK117(she)001:26604: bsgrub pa dang ldan pa'i byang sems rnams ni de
NK117(she)001:26605: bzhin gshegs pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro ba can yin
NK117(she)001:26606: phyir de las mgyogs pa gzhan med do //
NK117(she)001:26607: 'di ltar sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi
NK117(she)001:26608: byang sems rnams kyi sbyin pa la sogs pa'i spyod
NK117(she)001:26609: pa rnams 'byung zhing lhag ma rnams kun tu mi
NK117(she)001:26610: spyod pa ni ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:26611: de'ang phung po lnga sogs kyi chos thams cad bden
NK117(she)001:26612: par grub mnyam du bstan nas gang zag gi bdag
NK117(she)001:26613: med ston par 'khor lo dang po dang /
NK117(she)001:26614: chos rnams ma grub mnyam du bstan nas chos kyi
NK117(she)001:26615: bdag med ston pa 'khor lo bar pa dang kun
NK117(she)001:26616: brtags don dam par ma grub cing gzhan dbang dang
NK117(she)001:26617: yongs grub don dam par grub pa'i khyad par phye
NK117(she)001:26618: nas ston pa'i 'khor lo tha ma gsum las dang
NK117(she)001:26619: po drang don yin par theg chen pa gnyis ka
NK117(she)001:26620: mthun la 'khor lo gzhan gnyis la rnam rig pas
NK117(she)001:26622: dbu ma pas bar pa nges don du 'dod pa'i
NK117(she)001:26623: lugs 'di ni rgyu'i theg pa'i skabs yin pa sor
NK117(she)001:26625: don la nges don gyi mdo sde dang rnal 'byor
NK117(she)001:26626: chen po'i don smra bsam las 'das pa la lam
NK117(she)001:26627: dus kyi tha snyad kyis thug pa med kyang /
NK117(she)001:26628: so so'i skye bo rnams drang ba'i phyir rim gyis
NK117(she)001:26629: bkri ba la ltos nas gsungs pa'i don 'gal med
NK117(she)001:26630: du bsdu shes pa gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:26631: de yang tha snyad tsam gyi sgo nas bshad pa'i
NK117(she)001:26632: grub mtha' ni blo'i ri mo yin pas don dam
NK117(she)001:26633: bden pa la bzhag pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:26634: sa bcu'i yon tan 'chad skabs phyi ma'i skye srid
NK117(she)001:26635: sogs dang de dag gi dbye ba bcas zhib par
NK117(she)001:26637: de ltar bslab bya mthar thug nas slob tu med pa ni mi slob pa'i lam ste /
NK117(she)001:26639: mnyam par ma bzhag med pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:26640: rgyal ba'i ma 'dres chos bco brgyad //
NK117(she)001:26641: stobs bcu dang ni mi 'jigs bzhi //
NK117(she)001:26642: mtha' dag mngon gyur sangs rgyas yin //
NK117(she)001:26643: 'di ltar pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK117(she)001:26644: rgyal ba kun gyi gzhung lam ste //
NK117(she)001:26645: lta bas ma rmongs spyod pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:26647: zhes pa ni de yang thugs mnyam par ma bzhag
NK117(she)001:26648: pa med pa sogs rgyal ba'i ma 'dres pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:26649: bco brgyad dang stobs bcu dang ni mi 'jigs pa
NK117(she)001:26650: bzhi mtha' dag gab pa'i tshul du ma yin cing
NK117(she)001:26651: mngon du gyur pa ni sangs rgyas kho na'i khyad
NK117(she)001:26652: chos yin no // 'di ltar pha rol du phyin pa drug po ni /
NK117(she)001:26653: dus gsum du byon pa dang bzhugs pa dang 'byon
NK117(she)001:26654: 'gyur gyi rgyal ba kun gyi gzhung lam chen po
NK117(she)001:26655: ste / de ltar lta bas ma rmongs pas phyogs
NK117(she)001:26656: gang du'ang ma lhungs shing ris su ma chad pas
NK117(she)001:26657: tha snyad kyi grub mtha' las grol /
NK117(she)001:26658: spyod pa'ang shin tu rnam dag ste lam dus sde
NK117(she)001:26659: snod gsum nas ji ltar bshad pa bzhin blang dor
NK117(she)001:26660: tshul bzhin du thabs shes zung 'jug gi ngang nas
NK117(she)001:26661: bsgrubs pa dag 'og min sku gsum gyi sa la
NK117(she)001:26665: rten chos sku longs sku sprul sku gsum /
NK117(she)001:26668: de la chos sku ni dbyings dang ye shes gnyis
NK117(she)001:26669: su ma phyed pa'i rang bzhin gyis zung du 'jug
NK117(she)001:26670: cing dri ma thams cad dang bral ba'i rnam byang
NK117(she)001:26671: chen po'i khams nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:26672: de nyid rtog pa med pa'i chos nyid la mnyam
NK117(she)001:26673: par bzhag pa'i shes rab kyis mthong ba yin no
NK117(she)001:26674: // longs sku ni 'khor ba'i cha 'dus byas pa
NK117(she)001:26675: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kun gzhi dang bcas pa dbyings
NK117(she)001:26676: su nub pa'i stobs kyis bzhag pa'i gzhi'i gnas lugs
NK117(she)001:26677: kyi snang cha'i yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs pa ni
NK117(she)001:26678: nges pa lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26679: sprul sku ni chos sku'i gdangs longs sku'i rnam par
NK117(she)001:26680: rol pa'i ngang nas de nyid las gdul bya'i ngor
NK117(she)001:26681: gang la gang 'dul du 'byung ba'i rgya che ba'i
NK117(she)001:26683: de yang gdul bya yod na 'dul byed yod pa'i
NK117(she)001:26684: dpe 'char gzhi'i chu che chung gang yod kyi ngogs
NK117(she)001:26685: su zla gzugs snang ba dang 'dra yang /
NK117(she)001:26686: gdul bya med tshe sangs rgyas yod kyang de nyid
NK117(she)001:26687: bskrun pa'i dge ba med na sa bon rul ba
NK117(she)001:26688: spel du mi rung ba dang chos mtshungs so //
NK117(she)001:26690: bzo sprul sku ni lug ma jo sh+aakya sogs phyag mchod kyi gnas su gyur pa rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:26691: khang par bris sku thang kha sogs dang glegs bam rnams kyang der bsdu'o //
NK117(she)001:26692: gzhan yang gnas ri rnams la rang byung 'bur dod
NK117(she)001:26693: sogs phyag skor mchod 'bul gyi gnas su gyur pa'i
NK117(she)001:26694: tshogs gnyis bsag yul thams cad do //
NK117(she)001:26696: srog chags nges pa sprul nas nad bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:26698: rta rgyal ba la ha dang /
NK117(she)001:26699: seng+ge ral pa can gyis tshong pa bskyabs nus pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:26700: mchog gi sprul sku ni ston pa sh+aakya thub pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:26701: brten pa'i ye shes ni chos nyid ji lta ba dang /
NK117(she)001:26702: shes bya ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26703: de yang dbye na ye shes lngar gsungs pa'ang /
NK117(she)001:26704: kun gzhi dbyings su nub pa chos dbyings dang /
NK117(she)001:26705: kun gzhi'i rnam shes dbyings su nub pa me long /
NK117(she)001:26706: yid shes dbyings su nub pa mnyam nyid /
NK117(she)001:26707: nyon yid dbyings su nub pa sor rtog /
NK117(she)001:26708: sgo lnga'i rnam shes dbyings su nub pa ni bya grub ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:26709: de'i tshe ye shes dang shes bya mkhyen pa'i tshul
NK117(she)001:26710: yang rang snang la ltos na 'khrul pa gtan nas
NK117(she)001:26711: spang phyir shes bya'i spros pa dang des bskyed pa'i
NK117(she)001:26712: ye shes rang mtshan pa yod pa ma yin te
NK117(she)001:26713: stong ngos chos sku'i ye shes yod med gnyis ka
NK117(she)001:26714: ma grub pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhes bya
NK117(she)001:26715: la / gzhan snang la ltos nas thugs rjes 'jug
NK117(she)001:26716: pa dang ye shes kyi 'char tshul de dag gi
NK117(she)001:26717: rgyu 'bras mtha' dag 'gags pa med bzhin mkhyen pa'o
NK117(she)001:26718: la / // 'di la gzhan dag rig pa ni
NK117(she)001:26719: ma rig pa'i khyab byed can yin la khyab byed
NK117(she)001:26720: ma rig pa ldog pas khyab bya rig pa ldog
NK117(she)001:26721: pa'i phyir ye shes nyid kyang med par grub bo
NK117(she)001:26723: chad par smra ba rgyang 'phen pa'i lugs yin te
NK117(she)001:26724: spang bya las 'das shing sems sems byung kun gzhi
NK117(she)001:26725: tshogs brgyad kyis bsdus pa rig pa ye shes kyi
NK117(she)001:26726: steng du 'gag pa'i don yin no //
NK117(she)001:26727: rig pa ma rig pa'i rten yin kyang khyab byed
NK117(she)001:26728: ma yin pas ma rig pa log pa tsam gyis
NK117(she)001:26729: rig pa log par yang mi 'gyur te /
NK117(she)001:26730: sems byung 'gags pas sems 'gag pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:26731: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu dang /
NK117(she)001:26733: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad thams
NK117(she)001:26734: cad mkhyen pa'i rang bzhin le'u drug pa las bshad
NK117(she)001:26735: zin cing gzhung 'di nyid kyi rgyas 'grel kho na
NK117(she)001:26736: las rtogs par bya dgos so //
NK117(she)001:26737: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:26738: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:26739: lde mig las le'u dgu pa'i skabs rdzogs pa yin
NK117(she)001:26740: gyis / rgyu mtshan nyid kyis theg pa la yongs
NK117(she)001:26741: su grags pa'i rgya chen spyod pa dang zab mo
NK117(she)001:26742: lta ba'i grub pa'i mtha' legs par gtan la phab
NK117(she)001:26743: pa las tshig 'grel nyung ngu 'di ni byis pas
NK117(she)001:26744: me tog brgyus pa ltar rang dang skal mnyam rnams
NK117(she)001:26746: mdo 'grel 'di nyid kyi mjug tu 2yab rje grub
NK117(she)001:26747: pa'i dbang phyug gang gi zhal snga nas kyi mdzad
NK117(she)001:26748: byang 'di ltar / nying 'khrul lam du dpal ldan n+aa ga rdzus //
NK117(she)001:26749: bshes spring lung gis zab dang rgya che'i don //
NK117(she)001:26750: bdag rgyud bde gshegs snying po la sbyar ba //
NK117(she)001:26751: 'dis kyang rgyal bstan mi nub dpal du shog /
NK117(she)001:26752: sa skya bdag po rin po che ngag dbang kun
NK117(she)001:26753: dga' blo gros sangs rgyas bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan dpal
NK117(she)001:26754: bzang pos bstan pa 'ba' zhig thugs la bcangs nas
NK117(she)001:26756: rin chen gnyis pa'i rta rmig /
NK117(she)001:26757: nang mdzod sna lnga'i skyes dang bcas te bkas bskul ba las /
NK117(she)001:26758: dben pa'i ri ngogs na gnas pa'i gtsug lag khang
NK117(she)001:26759: pad+ma 'od gling zhes bya bar rdzogs chen pa rang
NK117(she)001:26760: byung rdo rje mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer gyis zin ris
NK117(she)001:26761: su btab pa'i yi ge pa ni dge slong rnal
NK117(she)001:26762: 'byor spyod pa chos rje brag pa'o ////
NK117(she)001:26767: /// yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:26768: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs las sngags 'grel
NK117(she)001:26769: nor bu'i phreng ba bzhugs so //
NK117(she)001:26770: 'khor 'das chos rnams byed po thabs mchog kun bzang yab //
NK117(she)001:26771: gang zhig bya ba'i yum gyur shes rab kun bzang mo //
NK117(she)001:26772: stangs dpyal zung gis bskrun pa'i srid dang zhi ba'i khams //
NK117(she)001:26773: bde gshegs snying por gcig pas phyag 'tshal gnyis 'dzin bral //
NK117(she)001:26774: sngon dus chos rgyal mes dbon rnam gsum gyis //
NK117(she)001:26775: spyan drangs snga 'gyur 'od zer 'bum ldan dal //
NK117(she)001:26776: phyis byon 'ga' yis chos spong chu 'dzin gyis //
NK117(she)001:26777: bsgrib pa'i sta gon mngon du gyur pa'i tshe //
NK117(she)001:26778: dri med bshes gnyen klong chen rab 'byams kyi //
NK117(she)001:26779: mkhyen brtse nus pa'i brgal brtags 'thor rlung gis //
NK117(she)001:26780: mi mthun chu 'dzin bskrad pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK117(she)001:26781: slar yang 'od zer stong ldan gzhung 'di 'bar //
NK117(she)001:26782: deng dus khams 'dir mdo sngags ma nges pa'i //
NK117(she)001:26783: chos tshul mang yang dbye bsal su yis nus //
NK117(she)001:26784: 'on kyang rang nus tshod kyi sems dge bas //
NK117(she)001:26785: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i bsdus 'grel blta bder 'god //
NK117(she)001:26786: da ni dbang po shin tu rnon po'i don du gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa bshad pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:26788: byang chub sems dpa' sngags kyi theg pa la //
NK117(she)001:26789: 'bras bu'am ni rdo rje'i theg pa dang //
NK117(she)001:26790: thabs kyi theg pa rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK117(she)001:26791: sde snod ces grags rgyud las khyad par 'phags //
NK117(she)001:26792: zhes pa de yang byang chub sems dpa'i bsam spyod
NK117(she)001:26793: dang bral ba'i sngags kyi gzugs brnyan la spyod pa
NK117(she)001:26794: ni r+au tra'i rgyu las ma 'das pa sngags gzhung
NK117(she)001:26796: de ltar ma yin pa'i sems bskyed dang ldan pa'i sngags kyi theg pa la /
NK117(she)001:26797: 'bras bu'i theg pa'am zhes pa ni 'bras bu bde
NK117(she)001:26798: gshegs snying pos 'gro ba yongs la til la mar
NK117(she)001:26799: khus khyab pa bzhin khyab pa de ni sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:26800: zhes bya ba de yin kyang glo bur gyi dri
NK117(she)001:26801: mas bsgribs nas rang zhal ma mthong ba de bsal
NK117(she)001:26802: ma thag tu nyi ma sprin rum nas thon pa
NK117(she)001:26804: rdo rje'i theg pa dang zhes pa rdo rje'i ni
NK117(she)001:26805: 'dir don dam chos nyid kyi rdo rje chos bdun
NK117(she)001:26806: dang ldan pa de yin te /
NK117(she)001:26807: de gnyis gang smos kyang rung zhing theg pa ni
NK117(she)001:26808: glang po che la sogs dud 'gro stobs chen gyis
NK117(she)001:26809: khur chen po theg pa ltar 'dir yang rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:26810: theg pa bas snang srid 'khor 'das thams cad theg
NK117(she)001:26811: pas so // 'khor ba'i chos myang 'das su bsgyur
NK117(she)001:26812: ba'i thabs kyi theg pa'am rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde
NK117(she)001:26813: snod ces yongs su grags pa 'di nyid rgyu'i theg
NK117(she)001:26814: pa las khyad par du ma'i sgo nas 'phags tshul
NK117(she)001:26815: shes pa yang gal che bas rgyas 'grel blta ba'i
NK117(she)001:26818: rgyun chags ngos nas gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud //
NK117(she)001:26819: rim gnyis la brten thabs dang shes rab 'brel //
NK117(she)001:26820: dka' thub mthu yis mi gdung 'jug sgo yangs //
NK117(she)001:26821: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas brtul zhugs myur //
NK117(she)001:26822: zhes pa ni 'di ltar rgyud ces pa rgyun chags
NK117(she)001:26823: yin te de la tan+t+ra san ta zhes bya ste
NK117(she)001:26824: sngags rgyud rnams la zhi ba sogs las phra mo
NK117(she)001:26825: bsgrub chog dang / mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul sogs
NK117(she)001:26826: thun mong gi dngos grub chen po bsgrub chog dang
NK117(she)001:26827: bsgrub chog dang / / mi gnas pa'i mya ngan
NK117(she)001:26828: las 'das pa'i bsgrub chog sogs mang po dang 'brel
NK117(she)001:26830: de yang gzhi'i rgyud bde gshegs snying po /
NK117(she)001:26831: lam gyi rgyud bskyed rdzogs bsgom bzlas /
NK117(she)001:26832: 'bras bu'i rgyud sku dang ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:26833: de yang rim pa gnyis la brten pas thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel zhing /
NK117(she)001:26834: dgung lto bcag pa dang smyung bar gnas pa sogs
NK117(she)001:26835: dka' thub mthu yis mi gdung bas sngags lam 'jug
NK117(she)001:26837: dbang po rtul po dang 'bring dang rnon po gsum
NK117(she)001:26838: las rjes ma'i dbang du byas pa'i lam mchog bla
NK117(she)001:26839: na med pa yin pas brtul zhugs myur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26840: de yang dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs
NK117(she)001:26841: pa dam par gyur pas skal med dang blo ma
NK117(she)001:26842: sbyangs pa dag gis rtogs par dka' bar gsang ba
NK117(she)001:26843: dang / 'jig rten pa dang theg dman rnams kyi
NK117(she)001:26844: spyod yul du mi rung bas gsang bar bya zhing
NK117(she)001:26845: dang / / sbas nas 'grub pa yin pa'i phyir yang gsang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26846: de lta bu'i gsang sngags de ni thabs mang bas
NK117(she)001:26847: rang rang gi nyon mongs pa gang yin pa de
NK117(she)001:26848: nyid kyi rigs shes par byas nas de'i sbyong byed
NK117(she)001:26849: lha sngags la brten pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK117(she)001:26850: 'du shes bsgyur ba'i thabs mkhas kyi spyod pas zin
NK117(she)001:26851: pa sogs sgo mang po la brten nas rang grol
NK117(she)001:26852: zhing gzhan rjes su 'dzin pa'i thabs yod pas thabs
NK117(she)001:26853: mang ba dang / dka' thub dang sdom pa'i kun
NK117(she)001:26854: spyod kyis mi gdung bar ji ltar 'dod pa'i lam
NK117(she)001:26855: la bkrir yod cing ngal bas bsgrub mi dgos par
NK117(she)001:26856: nyon mongs pa gdul ba'i thabs zab la rgya che
NK117(she)001:26857: ba mang pos rang gzhan grol bar nus pas dka'
NK117(she)001:26858: mang ba dang / ba med pa / mtshams med
NK117(she)001:26859: lnga la sogs mi dge ba'i las ci tsam spyad
NK117(she)001:26860: kyang mi gos par 'gro ba 'dren pa'i thabs la
NK117(she)001:26861: mang ba dang / ba med pa / mkhas pa
NK117(she)001:26862: / mtshan nyid theg pa ltar sa dang pha rol
NK117(she)001:26863: tu phyin pa'i spyod pa rgya chen pos yun ring
NK117(she)001:26864: po bsgrub mi dgos shing mthong chos la myur du
NK117(she)001:26865: bsgrub pa'i thabs yod pas myur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26867: dus la dgongs pa rdzogs ldan gsum ldan dang //
NK117(she)001:26868: gnyis ldan dang ni rtsod par ldan pa bzhi //
NK117(she)001:26869: rigs la dgongs pa bram ze'i rje'u rigs //
NK117(she)001:26870: rgyal po dang ni dmangs sam gdol pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26871: dbang por dgongs pa rtul 'bring rnon dang mchog /
NK117(she)001:26872: ces pa ni de yang dus la dgongs te gsungs
NK117(she)001:26873: pa ni rdzogs ldan gyi dus su bya rgyud gsum
NK117(she)001:26874: ldan la spyod rgyud gnyis ldan la rnal 'byor rgyud
NK117(she)001:26875: / rtsod ldan la bla med gsungs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26876: rigs la dgongs pa bram ze la bya rgyud /
NK117(she)001:26879: dmangs sam gdol pa bla med rgyud do //
NK117(she)001:26880: dbang po rtul 'bring rnon po gsum yang de'i 'gres so //
NK117(she)001:26882: chos ni bya spyod rnal 'byor bla na med //
NK117(she)001:26883: dang po gsum ni gsang sngags phyi pa ste //
NK117(she)001:26884: thub pas dngos gsungs mtshan nyid theg pa dang //
NK117(she)001:26885: gtsang sbra sdom pa'i kun spyod phal cher mtshungs //
NK117(she)001:26886: rtsod pa'i dus dang 'gal ba'i 'dod chags kyi //
NK117(she)001:26887: kun spyod lam byed lha yang zung 'brel min //
NK117(she)001:26888: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la longs mi spyod //
NK117(she)001:26889: ces pa ni de yang rgyud sde bzhir grangs nges pa'i kri ya dang /
NK117(she)001:26891: yo ga ste spyi rgyud gsum po de ni thub
NK117(she)001:26892: pa chags bral gyi rnam pas gsungs shing mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:26893: theg pa ltar gtsang rtsog dang spong len mang zhing
NK117(she)001:26894: kun spyod phal cher theg dman dang mtshungs shing rtsod
NK117(she)001:26895: pa'i dus su pho mo gnyis mkhyud kyi 'dod chags
NK117(she)001:26896: yin la de dang 'gal ba'i kun spyod lam du
NK117(she)001:26897: byed cing lha yang yab yum zung 'brel bsgom pa
NK117(she)001:26898: min pa dang / sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga sogs
NK117(she)001:26899: nang gi dam rdzas la spyod par mi nus so
NK117(she)001:26901: dbye na bya ba dang ni spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK117(she)001:26902: sems dpa' sems ma rig sngags gzungs sngags lha //
NK117(she)001:26903: bya bas rje khol spyod pas spun grogs tshul //
NK117(she)001:26904: bya bas rje khol rnam par bsgrub pa'ang //
NK117(she)001:26905: bdag bskyed med pa rang nyid dman par bzhag /
NK117(she)001:26906: la lar yod de gtso bor mdun bskyed ston //
NK117(she)001:26907: phyi yi bya ba khrus dang gtsang sbra gtso //
NK117(she)001:26908: mchog dman tshul du bsgrubs nas dngos grub 'dod //
NK117(she)001:26909: ces pa ni de'ang bya ba dang spyod pa'i rgyud
NK117(she)001:26910: ni sems dpa' sems ma rig sngags dang gzung sngags
NK117(she)001:26911: kyi lha de dag bya bas rje khol dang spyod
NK117(she)001:26912: pas spun grogs kyi tshul du bsgrub tshul gnyis yod
NK117(she)001:26913: pa la / spyir sngags kyi dbye ba la rig
NK117(she)001:26914: sngags dang gzungs sngags dang gsang sngags zhes pa gsum
NK117(she)001:26917: gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo gsum du gnas te rig sngags ni thabs kyi ngo bo dang /
NK117(she)001:26918: gzugs sngags ni shes rab kyi ngo bo yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:26919: gsang sngags ni gnyis med kyi ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:26920: de yang phyi lus ngag gi spyod pa gtso bor
NK117(she)001:26921: ston pa bya ba'i rgyud dang spyod rgyud spun nam
NK117(she)001:26922: grogs po'i tshul du bsgrub dgos pa la /
NK117(she)001:26923: bya bas mdun bskyed rje dang rang nyid bran khol gyi rnam par bsgrub pa la'ang /
NK117(she)001:26924: phal cher bdag bskyed med cing rang nyid dman par bzhag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:26925: la lar bdag bskyed yod kyang gtso bor mdun bskyed ston cing /
NK117(she)001:26926: phyi'i bya ba khrus dang gtsang sbra gtsor byed la
NK117(she)001:26927: lha nyid mchog dang rang nyid dman tshul du bsgrubs
NK117(she)001:26930: bya ba thabs dang rang gi rnal 'byor la //
NK117(she)001:26931: cha mnyam spyod pas spyod pa'i rgyud du grags //
NK117(she)001:26932: rang nyid dam tshig sems dpa'i mdun bzhugs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:26933: ye shes lha las spun ltar dngos grub len //
NK117(she)001:26934: zhes pa ni de yang phyi'i bya ba gtsang sbra
NK117(she)001:26935: sogs thabs dang nang gi rnal 'byor la brtson pa
NK117(she)001:26936: cha mnyam spyod pas spyod pa'i rgyud du grags shing
NK117(she)001:26937: rang nyid dam tshig sems dpa'i mdun na bzhugs pa'i
NK117(she)001:26938: ye shes kyi lha la spun grogs ltar bsgrubs nas
NK117(she)001:26941: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi gru chad man chad la //
NK117(she)001:26942: bkod pa chen po longs spyod rdzogs pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:26943: bstan yang zung 'brel ma yin bskyed dang rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:26944: thabs dang shes rab rim can so so ba //
NK117(she)001:26945: rnal 'byor gtsor spyod lus ngag grogs su ston //
NK117(she)001:26946: ye shes dgug bstim phyag rgya bzhi yis bcing //
NK117(she)001:26947: dam ye gcig pa'i ngang nas dngos grub blang //
NK117(she)001:26948: bzlas pa'i mtha' la gshegs gsol bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26949: zhes pa ni de la rtsa rgyud de nyid 'dus pa /
NK117(she)001:26950: bshad rgyud rdo rje rtse mo /
NK117(she)001:26951: cha mthun gyi rgyud dpal mchog dang po sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:26953: khams gsum rnam rgyal dang ngan song sbyong ba dang
NK117(she)001:26954: don grub ste dum bu bzhir grags pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK117(she)001:26955: gyi gru chad la bkod pa chen po longs spyod
NK117(she)001:26956: rdzogs pa ltar bstan kyang de dag gi lha yang
NK117(she)001:26957: thabs shes zung 'brel can ma yin cing chos thams
NK117(she)001:26958: cad bdag med pa'i rang bzhin stong nyid du rtogs
NK117(she)001:26959: pa'i ye shes kyi byin rlabs kun rdzob tsam du
NK117(she)001:26960: rdo rje dbyings sogs pa'i lhar btags pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26961: 'di'i lugs ni yab yum rim pa ltar bzhugs pa'am
NK117(she)001:26962: so sor bzhugs shing nang ting nge 'dzin gtsor spyod
NK117(she)001:26963: cing lus ngag gi spyod pa grogs su ston cing
NK117(she)001:26964: bdag dam tshig pa la lha ye shes pa dgug
NK117(she)001:26965: cing bstim zhing phyag rgya bzhi yis bcings mthar dam
NK117(she)001:26966: ye ro gcig pa'i ngang nas dngos grub blang ba
NK117(she)001:26967: dang bzlas pa'i mtha' la gshegs gsol bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:26968: de yang gong du dum bu bzhir dbye skabs dang
NK117(she)001:26969: po ni de bzhin gshegs pa dang rnam snang gi
NK117(she)001:26970: rigs so // gnyis pa ni rdo rje'i rigs so //
NK117(she)001:26972: bzhi pa ni rin po che'i rigs su bstan pa
NK117(she)001:26973: yang 'gro ba'i bsam pa rdzogs par byed pa'i rin
NK117(she)001:26974: po che'i rigs yin la las su bya ba'i sgo
NK117(she)001:26975: nas las kyi rigs yin phyir las dang byed pa
NK117(she)001:26976: po gnyis gcig tu sdud tshul sangs rgyas gsang bas
NK117(she)001:26977: bshad do // dum bu dang po gdul bya gti mug can 'dul phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:26980: bzhi pa ser sna can 'dul ba'i phyir bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:26981: 'di dag gi bshad pa rgyas pa ni yi ges 'jigs so //
NK117(she)001:26982: de yang 'bras bu'i phyag rgya bzhi thob pa'i thabs
NK117(she)001:26983: su dam rgya chos rgya las rgya phyag rgya chen
NK117(she)001:26988: phyag chen sku ste rang rang gi rigs dang sbyar
NK117(she)001:26989: ba'i gtso che chung gis rgyas gdab pa las sbyang
NK117(she)001:26990: gzhi sgrub pa po'i sgo gsum bya ba dang bzhi
NK117(she)001:26991: po de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba gsum phrin las
NK117(she)001:26992: dang bcas par bsgrub pa ni sbyangs 'bras so //
NK117(she)001:26994: bla na med pa gsang sngags nang pa ni //
NK117(she)001:26995: bskyed dang rdzogs dang zung du 'jug pa las //
NK117(she)001:26996: pha rgyud ma rgyud gnyis med rgyud du bzhag /
NK117(she)001:26997: lha ni 'khril sbyor dam rdzas khyad par spyod //
NK117(she)001:26998: gtsang rtsog spong len med pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK117(she)001:26999: zhes pa ni de la rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud
NK117(she)001:27000: 'di ni ngo bo'i sgo nas thabs shes sam bskyed
NK117(she)001:27001: rdzogs ga nyis med du 'dod kyang /
NK117(she)001:27002: kun rdzob tu rnam par dbye ba tsam gyi cha
NK117(she)001:27003: nas brjod na dkyil 'khor gang du lha pho shas
NK117(she)001:27004: che zhing dar dang rat+na'i rgyan mang ba pha rgyud
NK117(she)001:27005: do // mo shas che zhing gcer bu rus rgyan
NK117(she)001:27006: dang g.yang gzhi thal chen gyis byugs pa sogs ma
NK117(she)001:27007: do // rgyud do // de las khyad par dal
NK117(she)001:27008: gyi lha'i gtso bo go 'pho ba gtso mo mi
NK117(she)001:27010: de bzhin du gtso mo 'pho la gtso bo mi 'pho ba ma rgyud /
NK117(she)001:27011: 'di ltar dbang phyug ma gcig po rigs lnga gang
NK117(she)001:27012: bsgrub kyi gtso bo dang stangs dpyal du 'gyur zhing
NK117(she)001:27013: / pha rgyud du ni thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa spros pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27014: rdzogs rim rlung gtsor 'don la ma rgyud du ni
NK117(she)001:27015: rdzogs rim thig le 'ba' zhig gtso bor byed do
NK117(she)001:27016: // de gnyis ka cha mnyam du ston pa la
NK117(she)001:27017: gnyis med kyi rgyud ces btags kyang rgyud thams cad
NK117(she)001:27018: thabs shes gnyis med kyi rgyud yin par 'dus so
NK117(she)001:27019: // // nang rgyud 'di'i khyad par ni phyi pa ltar tshangs spyod kyi dka' thub dang /
NK117(she)001:27020: gtsang dme sogs kyi blang dor mang pos gdung ba
NK117(she)001:27021: ma yin par chos mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig
NK117(she)001:27022: la lta bas phye ba ni bla med kyi khyad
NK117(she)001:27024: rnal 'byor chen po pha rgyud thabs kyi lam //
NK117(she)001:27025: bskyed rim gtsor byas rlung lnga dag par byed //
NK117(she)001:27026: rjes su rnal 'byor ma rgyud shes rab lam //
NK117(she)001:27027: rdzogs rim gtsor byed khams la zhu bde bskyed //
NK117(she)001:27028: shin tu rnal 'byor gnyis med ye shes lam //
NK117(she)001:27029: gcig dang du bral 'od gsal chen por sbyor //
NK117(she)001:27030: zhes pa ni de la gsang sngags bla med 'dir
NK117(she)001:27031: sdug bsngal bden pa'i rang bzhin glo bur gyi dri
NK117(she)001:27032: ma dang bcas pa rgyu 'bras kyis slongs pa'i srid
NK117(she)001:27033: pa skye ba'i rim pa gang yin pa'i 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:27034: 'dra 'bag bskyed rim gyis sbyangs shing dag par byed
NK117(she)001:27036: kun 'byung gi chos las nyon gyi rnam par shar
NK117(she)001:27037: ba'i rigs rgyun sdug bsngal bden pa'i chos nyid 'bras
NK117(she)001:27038: bu sangs rgyas kyi rnam par thar pa'i 'dra 'bag
NK117(she)001:27039: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsgyur te bsgoms
NK117(she)001:27041: de yang sbyang bya glo bur kun brtags la bltos nas bskyed rim dang /
NK117(she)001:27042: gzhan dbang la bltos nas rdzogs rim dang /
NK117(she)001:27043: yongs grub dang mthun par rdzogs pa chen po lam du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27044: 'di ltar pha rgyud rnams ni bskyed rim thabs su
NK117(she)001:27045: byas nas 'byung lnga'i rlung dag pas 'khrul snang zhing
NK117(she)001:27046: khams su dag par byed cing gsal stong zung du
NK117(she)001:27047: 'jug pa'i dngos grub rnam gnyis sgrub par byed do
NK117(she)001:27048: // shes rab ma rgyud las ni bskyed rim gtsor
NK117(she)001:27049: mi 'don par khams bde ba chen po b+ha ga'i
NK117(she)001:27050: dkyil 'khor las rang lus thabs ldan la sngon du
NK117(she)001:27051: goms nas gzhan lus phyag rgya chen po las dga'
NK117(she)001:27052: bzhi'i ye shes bde ba chen pos byang chub bsgrub
NK117(she)001:27053: // pa yin zhing / gnyis med kyi rgyud shin
NK117(she)001:27054: tu rnal 'byor las ni gcig dang du bral gyi
NK117(she)001:27055: chos nyid gtsor byed pas phung po'i snyigs ma dwangs
NK117(she)001:27058: kun gyi gnad du khams drug ldan pa'i lus //
NK117(she)001:27059: phung po khams dang skye mched rtsa thig rlung //
NK117(she)001:27060: las su rang lus bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gsum //
NK117(she)001:27061: yon tan kun skyed rdo rje theg pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:27062: zhes pa ni de yang sa chu me rlung nam
NK117(she)001:27063: mkha' ste 'byung lnga dang de dag gi dbyings rang
NK117(she)001:27064: bzhin gyi stong pa la ye shes kyi khams te
NK117(she)001:27065: drug tu dabye'o // de la gzugs tshor 'du shes
NK117(she)001:27066: 'du byed lnga ni phung po dang khams kyang sha
NK117(she)001:27067: khrag drod dbugs khong pa'i nang gi stong cha'o //
NK117(she)001:27068: de dag la brten pa'i gnas pa rtsa g.yo ba
NK117(she)001:27069: rlung bkod pa byang chub kyi sems gsum las su
NK117(she)001:27070: rung ba ste sbyangs pa stobs su gyur tshe bskyed
NK117(she)001:27071: pa dang rdzogs pa dang de gnyis zung 'jug gsum
NK117(she)001:27072: lam du longs shing sa dang lam gyi yon tan
NK117(she)001:27073: kun bskyed nus pa rdo rje'i lam mchog tu gyur
NK117(she)001:27075: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK117(she)001:27076: lta bas thag bcad bsgoms pas nyams su blang //
NK117(she)001:27077: spyod pas la dor 'bras bus don gnyis bsgrub //
NK117(she)001:27078: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rgyud la yang dag brten //
NK117(she)001:27079: zhes pa ni 'di ltar rdo rje'i theg pa'i nye
NK117(she)001:27080: lam zab mo'i skabs su chos rnams dbyings nas sangs
NK117(she)001:27081: rgyas pa'i rang bzhin lta bas gtan la 'bebs pas
NK117(she)001:27082: bden pa dbyer med gzhi rang bzhin yongs grub tu
NK117(she)001:27083: ldan pa'i ngang du sgra rtog dang zhen yul gyi
NK117(she)001:27085: bden gnyis kyis rjes su dpags pa'i rnam grangs pa'i
NK117(she)001:27086: don dam tsam ma yin par gnas lugs phyag rgya
NK117(she)001:27087: chen mo'i dbang las byung ba'i dpe'i ye shes sam
NK117(she)001:27088: / rim gnyis kyi thabs dang shes rab zung du
NK117(she)001:27089: 'brel ba'i 'du 'phrod la brten nas myang 'das kyi
NK117(she)001:27090: rgyud kyi rang byung gi ye shes mngon sum du
NK117(she)001:27092: de'ang rgyu'am gzhi'i rgyud ni 'gro ba'i kun gzhi tshogs
NK117(she)001:27093: bdun gyi sbubs na bde gshegs snying po nyi ma
NK117(she)001:27094: sprin gyis bsgribs pa lta bur gnas so //
NK117(she)001:27095: thams sam lam gyi rgyud ni sbyang gzhi de nyid
NK117(she)001:27096: kyi dri ma thabs mang 'phrul gyis sbyangs nas rang
NK117(she)001:27097: gi rang bzhin ci yin pa mngon du byed pa'o
NK117(she)001:27098: // 'bras bu'i rgyud ni sbyang gzhi de nyid sbyong
NK117(she)001:27099: byed kyi thabs zab mos sbyangs pas sgrib byed dang
NK117(she)001:27100: bral te 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27101: de yang man ni sgra'i dbyings de kho na nyid shes pa'i shes rab dang /
NK117(she)001:27102: t+r+aa ya ni 'jig rten skyob pa'i snying rje chen
NK117(she)001:27103: po ste de gnyis dbyer med pa gsang sngags so
NK117(she)001:27104: // gsang sngags zhes pa'ang skal dman gyis thos su
NK117(she)001:27105: mi rung ba gsang dgos pa dang sngags ni dug
NK117(she)001:27106: la sngags kyis btab pa'i 'tsho byed kyi sman du
NK117(she)001:27107: 'gyur ba ltar nyon mongs rang grol gyi lam la
NK117(she)001:27108: zhugs pa'i stobs kyis dug lngas 'ching bar mi nus
NK117(she)001:27109: pa rma byas dug la spyod pa'i ro nus mdzes
NK117(she)001:27110: rgyan du gyur pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:27112: 'jug pa'i sgo ni smin par byed pa'i dbang //
NK117(she)001:27113: grol bar byed pa bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gnyis //
NK117(she)001:27114: mthun pa'i grogs su dam tshig spyod pa gsum //
NK117(she)001:27115: sngags kyi lam mchog rnal mar nges pa las //
NK117(she)001:27116: zhes rdo rje'i theg pa'i lam yongs su rdzogs pa ni smin grol gnyis dang rim gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:27117: de'i grogs su gyur pa ni dam tshig rnam par dag pa kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:27119: dang po dbang bskur ma thob dngos grub med //
NK117(she)001:27120: bye ma btsir las zhun mar 'dod pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:27121: 'chad nyan bsgom la brtson kyang dmyal bar 'gro //
NK117(she)001:27122: dbang thob skyes bu rgyal ba'i sras su 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:27123: dkyil 'khor mthong bas sdig las rnam par grol //
NK117(she)001:27124: gtsang ma'i rigs skye skye ba bdun dag na //
NK117(she)001:27125: nges par 'grub cing sa bcu 'thob par bshad //
NK117(she)001:27126: ces pa ni mdor na rdo rje'i theg pa'i spyi
NK117(she)001:27127: chings ni dbang bskur ba kho na yin pas dbang
NK117(she)001:27128: bskur tshul bzhin zhus te dam tshig bsrung ba gal
NK117(she)001:27129: che zhing de ltar ma byas na sngags lam la
NK117(she)001:27130: thos bsam sgom gsum 'chad nyan sogs ji lta bu
NK117(she)001:27131: byed kyang bye ma btsir nas mar khu 'dod pa'am
NK117(she)001:27132: sa bon ma btab par myu gu re ba bzhin
NK117(she)001:27133: no // de ltar dngos grub mi thob par ma
NK117(she)001:27134: zad gsang sgrogs kyi nyes pas sems can dmyal ba
NK117(she)001:27135: chen por 'gro bar soms la sngags lam la 'jug
NK117(she)001:27136: pa'i sngon du dbang bskur tshul bzhin thob nas dam
NK117(she)001:27137: tshig ma nyams par bsrungs na skyes bu de nyid
NK117(she)001:27138: rgyal ba'i sras su skye bar 'gyur zhing dkyil 'khor
NK117(she)001:27139: mthong bas kyang sngon bsags kyi sdig pa las rnam
NK117(she)001:27140: par grol nas gtsang ma'i rigs te gtsang ris kyi
NK117(she)001:27141: lhar skye zhing de'i skye ba bdun dag na sangs
NK117(she)001:27142: rgyas nges par 'grub cing sa bcu 'thob par bshad
NK117(she)001:27144: dbang bskur slob dpon rim gnyis gdengs dang bral //
NK117(she)001:27145: bsti gnas dkor spyod ma bsdams khyim la chags //
NK117(she)001:27146: snying rje chung dang rtog ges zil non des //
NK117(she)001:27147: dbang bskur byas kyang be'u sbrel g.yang sar ltung //
NK117(she)001:27148: zhes pa ni de yang dbang bskur ba'i slob dpon
NK117(she)001:27149: ni bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim gnyis gang la'ang sbyangs
NK117(she)001:27150: pa mthar phyin ma byas pas lta sgom gdengs dang
NK117(she)001:27151: bral zhing / rang gi yul 'brog ci 'dra yin
NK117(she)001:27152: yang rung ste bsti gnas te sdod gnas de nyid
NK117(she)001:27153: mi nyams pa'i ched du dkor rdzas la bag med
NK117(she)001:27154: du spyod cing sdom pa gsum gyis ma bsdams pa'i
NK117(she)001:27155: khyim la chags shing zhen pa can dang /
NK117(she)001:27156: 'gro phan gyi snying rje chung ba dang tha snyad
NK117(she)001:27157: kyi tshig la grims pa'i rtog ge bas zil gyis
NK117(she)001:27158: non nas de'i rjes su 'brangs shing dbang du gyur
NK117(she)001:27159: pa de lta bus dbang bskur byas kyang thob la
NK117(she)001:27160: ma smin tsam du ma zad dpon slob gnyis ka
NK117(she)001:27161: be'u sbrel g.yang sar lhung ba ltar 'gyur bas spang
NK117(she)001:27163: phyi nang gsang ba'i de nyid rnam pa bcu //
NK117(she)001:27164: rig cing rang nyid grol ba'i bla ma yis //
NK117(she)001:27165: dad dang ngo tsha shes pa'i slob ma'i rgyud //
NK117(she)001:27166: brtags la dbang bskur rim pas sbyin par bya //
NK117(she)001:27167: zhes pa ni de yang dbang bskur thob cing dam
NK117(she)001:27168: tshig ma nyams pa'i phyi nang gsang ba'i de nyid
NK117(she)001:27169: rnam pa bcu la dbang 'byor ba dag bsten par
NK117(she)001:27170: bya ba ste / dang po ni dkyil 'khor gyi
NK117(she)001:27171: bya ba la mkhas pa dang ting 'dzin dang phyag
NK117(she)001:27172: rgya dang stangs stabs dang 'dug stangs dang bzlas brjod
NK117(she)001:27173: sbyin sreg mchod pa las sbyor dang slar sdud pa
NK117(she)001:27174: yi rnam pa ni phyi'i de nyid bcu'o //
NK117(she)001:27175: khro bcu la sogs pa'i bsrung 'khor bsgoms pas phyir bzlog pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27176: bris pas bsrung 'khor gyis phyir bzlog pa gsang dbang
NK117(she)001:27177: sher ye'i dbang gnyis la brten pa'i sbyor ba mthun
NK117(she)001:27178: dbye bsad sgrol / gtor ma'i cho ga rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:27179: bzlas pa lha ma grub na drag shul bsgrub pa'i
NK117(she)001:27180: cho ga'am spogs chog gis lha bsad pa rab gnas
NK117(she)001:27181: dang dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i cho ga yang 'khor ba
NK117(she)001:27182: dang mthun par sbyar nas chags spyod dang mngal 'byin
NK117(she)001:27183: srid na rang gi chos nyid la ngo tsha zhing
NK117(she)001:27184: gsang sbed dgos rigs mtha' dag nyams su bstar bas
NK117(she)001:27185: na gsang ba'i de nyid bcu'o //
NK117(she)001:27186: de tsam gyi tshig dang gzugs brnyan shes kyang mi
NK117(she)001:27187: chog par 'jig rten pa'i kun rtog gi sems nyer
NK117(she)001:27188: len gyi phung po lnga las yang dag par 'das
NK117(she)001:27189: pas rtogs pas bdag rgyud grol ba la brten pa
NK117(she)001:27190: gal che'o // de lta na'ang sangs rgyas rnams ni
NK117(she)001:27191: sems can gdul ba'i thabs la mkhas shing thugs rje
NK117(she)001:27192: dang ldan pa yin pas nges pa'i don du slob
NK117(she)001:27193: dpon yang mtha' gcig tu mi bzung ste dper na
NK117(she)001:27194: rgyal po zas gtsang ma dge slong 'char ka la
NK117(she)001:27196: rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti chags bral la mi ston
NK117(she)001:27197: pa ston pa chags can gyi rnam par bsgyur nas
NK117(she)001:27198: gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27199: slob ma btsun tshugs brtas shing blo chung ba drang
NK117(she)001:27200: srong nyi ma'i shing rta lta bu rgyu 'bras dag
NK117(she)001:27201: grol du 'dzin pa la dge slong rdo rje 'dzin
NK117(she)001:27202: pa dgos pa gsungs pa ltar de la slob ma
NK117(she)001:27203: yang dad pa dang ngo tsha khrel yod ldan pa
NK117(she)001:27205: de yang sngags sdom bzung mi nus pa'i rigs la dbang gi dngos rjes rnams bshol bar bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:27207: bsnyen pa dang ni sa yi cho ga dang //
NK117(she)001:27208: sta gon dang ni slob ma 'jug cing smin //
NK117(she)001:27209: mngon rtogs bzhi po re re nyid la yang //
NK117(she)001:27210: bzhi bzhir rdzogs pa'i yan lag ma tshang na //
NK117(she)001:27211: cho ga nyams pas smin par nus ma yin //
NK117(she)001:27212: zhes pa ni de la so skye rgyud ldan gyi
NK117(she)001:27213: slob dpon gyis ni cho ga phra mo nyams pas
NK117(she)001:27214: kyang dngos grub la sgrib par byed na /
NK117(she)001:27215: cho ga'i rtsa ba nyams na byin rlabs mi 'byung
NK117(she)001:27216: bas thog mar rang rgyud dag par byed pa'i bsnyen
NK117(she)001:27217: pa dang sa bdag gis bzung ba'i gzhi la som
NK117(she)001:27218: nyi mi dgos pa'i sa chog dang /
NK117(she)001:27219: dkyil 'khor dang slob ma'i las la btsan thabs su
NK117(she)001:27220: mi 'jug pa sta gon 'jug pa sngon du btang
NK117(she)001:27222: sa chog gi yan lag bzhi'am lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:27228: khang pa rnying pa sogs su sa brtag pa mi dgos pas bzhir gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:27229: sa brtag pa'i tshe gseg ma dang ngam grog dang
NK117(she)001:27230: khung bu dang grog mkhar dang tsha sgo can dang
NK117(she)001:27231: thal ba dang rdul dang skra dang srin bu dang
NK117(she)001:27232: srog chags mang ba rnams spang ngo //
NK117(she)001:27233: 'on kyang sa brtag pa dang brkos nas sbyang ba la gzab mi dgos pa'i gnas bcu ni /
NK117(she)001:27234: drang srong gi bsti gnas dang ba lang sogs phyugs
NK117(she)001:27235: lhas phug pa dang ri rtse sa gzhi gang zhig
NK117(she)001:27236: gzhan gyis 'thas pa khang pa dang rdo leb kyi
NK117(she)001:27237: steng / mchod rten drung dang 'bab chu'i gling mtsho'i 'gram rnams so //
NK117(she)001:27238: gzhan yang gtsug lag khang dang tshal dang dur khrod la sogs kyang de dang mtshungs so //
NK117(she)001:27239: brtag sbyangs nan du dgos pa'i gnas su brkos dong dgang nas brtag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27240: de bzhin du chus bkang nas brtag pa sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:27241: kha dog gi sgo nas brtag pa sogs kyang dgos par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:27242: sa blang ba ni gnas yul de'i bdag po'i gzugs
NK117(she)001:27243: can gyi rgyal po sogs la rin dngos dang gzugs
NK117(she)001:27244: med pa'i lha mo la nyer spyod dang gtor ma
NK117(she)001:27245: zhing skyong la sogs pa la dkar dmar phud dang
NK117(she)001:27246: gtor mas barngana la tshig gis bkrol nas rang dbang
NK117(she)001:27247: bar bya ba'o // sbyang ba ni /
NK117(she)001:27248: lto 'phye'i brtag pa dang de'i lus la thig gdab
NK117(she)001:27249: nas brtsi zhing rko mkhan nyid gnod sems bral ba'i
NK117(she)001:27250: ngang nas rang nyid bgegs mthar byed dang tog rtse
NK117(she)001:27251: rdo rjes mtshan pas phyag char bsams la mchan 'og
NK117(she)001:27252: dang lto ba gnyis su brko ba'o //
NK117(she)001:27253: de ltar brkos pa'i sar phub ma dang /
NK117(she)001:27254: rdo dang gyo mo sol ba /
NK117(she)001:27255: tsher ma la sogs bsal la bcag go //
NK117(she)001:27256: de'ang zug rngu ji ltar bsal ba tsam gyis dngos grub nye ba yin zhes bshad do //
NK117(she)001:27257: sa cung zad brkos pa las gzhung nas gsungs pa
NK117(she)001:27258: ltar brko ru thog khel ma byung tshe ha na
NK117(she)001:27259: ha na kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK117(she)001:27260: ces bzlas nas sbyangs pas kyang rung zhing /
NK117(she)001:27261: slar yang zug rngu bsal ba la gtogs pa'i brkos
NK117(she)001:27262: pa dang bkra shis pa'i sa gzhan dri bzang gi
NK117(she)001:27263: chus bran pa blugs nas legs par bcags la dkyil
NK117(she)001:27264: 'khor so so'i gzhung ltar bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:27265: dkyil 'khor gyi che chung chag tshad mtshan nyid sogs
NK117(she)001:27266: rang rang gi gzhung nas bshad pa ltar bya zhing
NK117(she)001:27267: / dal zhing spro na bum gter 'jug par bya zhing /
NK117(she)001:27268: dkyus ma tsam la las sngags bzlas pa'i chu dang ba byung gis kyang bran zhing byugs /
NK117(she)001:27269: lag mthil g.yas pa sa la bzhag pas bskor zhing /
NK117(she)001:27270: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK117(she)001:27271: ces bzlas pas lag pa las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis ma dag pa thams cad sbyangs /
NK117(she)001:27273: zhes pas sa phyogs kyi dngos po thams cad nam mkhar byas /
NK117(she)001:27274: sor mo rnams rdo rje rtse lngar bsam zhing sar brdeg /
NK117(she)001:27275: me di ni badz+r+ai b+ha wa badz+ra b+han+d+ha h'u /
NK117(she)001:27276: ha na ha na badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK117(she)001:27277: ces brjod pas sa gzhi thams cad rdo rje'i rang bzhin du bcings /
NK117(she)001:27278: +aahh+aum sho d+ha ya sho d+ha ya rak+sha rak+sha h+aum
NK117(she)001:27279: h+aum phatah ces brjod pas nyes skyon rnams sbyangs shing
NK117(she)001:27281: sa lha la mchod gtor phul la 'bru gsum dang yig brgya bzlas pa sogs bya zhing /
NK117(she)001:27282: mthar sbyang bya'i sa dang sbyong byed thams cad chos nyid gcig tu mnyam par bzhag go //
NK117(she)001:27283: dal rnying par tshon gyis bzhengs na mi mngon pa la blang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:27284: rdzas sngags ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba dang bzung ba bsrung ba bzhi rnams bya zhing /
NK117(she)001:27285: ras bris la bzung bsrung tsam gyis chog go //
NK117(she)001:27286: lha'i rnal 'byor la gnas bzhin langs nas rkang pa
NK117(she)001:27287: byin gyis brlabs nas rdo rje rtse gcig pa dang
NK117(she)001:27288: / gsum pa lnga pa sna tshogs rdo rje ste
NK117(she)001:27289: rkang pa'i stangs stabs bzhis sa la rdo rje bri
NK117(she)001:27290: / ba dang / rdo rje'i mig gnyis kyis mdun
NK117(she)001:27291: rgyab tu blta zhing mngon phyogs phyir phyogs gnyis gnyis
NK117(she)001:27292: blta zhing shar dang lhor g.yas brkyang g.yon brkyang nub
NK117(she)001:27293: tu sa ga byang du zlum po /
NK117(she)001:27294: dbus su mnyam pa dang kha sbyor sogs stangs stabs
NK117(she)001:27295: brgyad dang gar dgu'i nyams kyi rnam 'gyur la sogs
NK117(she)001:27296: bya ba'o // spyi tsam du ni sa bzung ba'i slad du /
NK117(she)001:27297: pra na ma mi sarba ta th+aa ga t+aa na zhes pas rgyal ba rnams la phyag byas la /
NK117(she)001:27298: ma rig pa dang bdu da dbang du song ba rnams la snying rje'i sems kyis bltas te /
NK117(she)001:27299: de dag bsal phyir rdor dril 'dzin pas khro bo'i nga rgyal du langs te /
NK117(she)001:27300: mig g.yas g.yon nyi zla mig 'bras las me 'bar bas phyogs kun tu blta zhing /
NK117(she)001:27301: h'u glu dang rdo rje'i rkang stabs kyis gyad 'gros
NK117(she)001:27302: su bskor zhing rkang 'og nas bskal me lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:27303: 'od zer byung bas gnod byed rnams byer bar bsams
NK117(she)001:27304: nas rdor dril dpung 'gor phyar bzhin thod dbyug dang
NK117(she)001:27305: 'khor lo dang / mda' dang lcags kyu zhags pa
NK117(she)001:27306: sogs kyi rgya dang bcas te brdeg tshul dang chabs
NK117(she)001:27307: cig gtso sngags gang yin dang sum b+ha nis bgegs
NK117(she)001:27308: bskrad pas kyang 'thus par gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:27309: de nas dkyil 'khor bya ba'i gzhi dri dang bdud
NK117(she)001:27310: rtsi lngas byugs sgo zur rnams nas me tog spos
NK117(she)001:27311: sogs kyis mchod cing gzhi de thal mos bkab tshul
NK117(she)001:27312: gyis lha gang yin gyi gtso sngags dang yig brgya
NK117(she)001:27313: bdun bzla bzhin mngon rtogs bsgoms nas spro bsdu bya
NK117(she)001:27316: de lta bu'i las kyis dam la mi 'du ba'i
NK117(she)001:27317: gnod sems 'chang ba rnams bkug nas khro bcu'i phur
NK117(she)001:27318: bus gdab pa la sa bsrung zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27319: de ltar sa brtag blang sogs yan lag bzhi'am lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:27324: slob ma sta gon rnams so //
NK117(she)001:27325: de la dkyil 'khor ni 'byor pa che na dpag
NK117(she)001:27326: tshad tsam yang rung la chung na lag mthil tsam
NK117(she)001:27327: du bri ba'am yid kyis bris kyang chog par gsungs
NK117(she)001:27328: so // de ltar bris la thig gi bya ba dang /
NK117(she)001:27329: thig skud dang tshon sogs zhib par bri rgyu yi ges 'jigs nas bzhag go //
NK117(she)001:27330: spyir ye thig ni nam mkha' dang sa gzhi gnyis
NK117(she)001:27331: ka la byed dgos shing ye thig sngon la btab
NK117(she)001:27332: pas rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar
NK117(she)001:27333: gyur pa de'i gzugs brnyan gnyis pa zhig me long
NK117(she)001:27334: snang bzhin sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du bltar mngon pa'i
NK117(she)001:27335: ched du yin te sku gsum gyi sprul gazhi'ang chos
NK117(she)001:27336: sku spros bral yin zhing de'i gdangs las longs sku
NK117(she)001:27337: dang de las sprul skur 'char ba dang sgo mthun
NK117(she)001:27338: pa'o // thig gis ni dkyil 'khor gyi mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:27339: gtan la 'bebs phyir yin pas snga 'gyur bka' gter
NK117(she)001:27340: gang yin gyi ring lugs dkyil 'khor gyi bkod pa
NK117(she)001:27341: mi 'dra ba mang du yod pa ltar rang rang
NK117(she)001:27342: gi gzhung bzhin shes dgos pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:27343: lha sta gon dang bum pa sta gon gnyis spyir gzhung bzhin dang bye brag bum rdzas ni /
NK117(she)001:27344: nas 'bras gro til mon sran lnga ni 'bru lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:27348: tsan dan dkar dmar rnams ni dri lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:27352: byi ru mu men lnga ni rin po che lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:27354: sbrang rtsi bu ram til mar rnams snying po lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:27355: kan+da k+aa ri sle tres shu dag dkar po chu srin sder mo dbang lag lnga sman lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:27356: de lta'i nyer lnga po de ni sngags phyi rgyud gsum gyis so //
NK117(she)001:27357: de'i steng du sha lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga bsnan
NK117(she)001:27358: pa'i rdzas so lnga ni bla med kho nas so
NK117(she)001:27359: // dang po nyer lnga ni rim par snang mthar
NK117(she)001:27360: don grub rin 'byung mi bskyod pa rnam snang lnga'i
NK117(she)001:27362: bla med kyi bdud rtsi lnga la pany+tsa a mri
NK117(she)001:27363: ta +aahh+aum dang sha lnga la pany+tsa m+aam sa +aahh+aum
NK117(she)001:27364: gis blugs pa'i mgul chings ni phyi rgyud la sku
NK117(she)001:27365: gsum mtshon phyir srog gsum dang bla med la sku
NK117(she)001:27366: lnga mtshon pa'i srog lnga dang zhu bde'i ye shes
NK117(she)001:27367: mtshon pas bdun du yang bshad do //
NK117(she)001:27368: phyi rgyud gsum la kha rgyan du d+aur wa dang
NK117(she)001:27369: rgya gzhung 'ga' na a mra sogs shing la bshad
NK117(she)001:27370: cing phur rgyud la la na shug pa'i ldem bu'ang
NK117(she)001:27371: bshad cing drag po'i rdzas kyang bshad pa dang yal
NK117(she)001:27372: ga bzang pos brgyan zhes pa'ang yod pas shing kho
NK117(she)001:27373: nar ngos bzung ba tsam yang ma yin te /
NK117(she)001:27374: ldum bu dang shing gi yal 'dab gnyis su phye ba yang shes dgos so //
NK117(she)001:27375: dag sbyor ni sngags phyi rgyud ltar na bum pa'i phyi dbyibs kha dog kha rgyan dang mgul chings /
NK117(she)001:27376: dung zhal dri zhim gyi chu push+pe dkar pos brgyan
NK117(she)001:27377: pa'i mchod yon dang bcas pa'i steng du gzungs rdor
NK117(she)001:27378: me tog gi phreng ba can sogs phyir snang ba'i
NK117(she)001:27379: dngos po rnams sprul skur mtshon la /
NK117(she)001:27380: bcud nyer lnga blugs pas 'gro ba rnams kyi tshogs
NK117(she)001:27381: rdzogs nas longs spyod 'phel bas longs skur mtshon pa
NK117(she)001:27382: dang bum nang gi bsil ba'i ngo bos nyon mongs
NK117(she)001:27383: pa'i tsha gdung bcil bas ni chos skur mtshon la
NK117(she)001:27384: / lha bsgom pa ni ngo bo nyid sku ste
NK117(she)001:27385: sku bzhir mtshon pas byang chub kyi chos rnams rang
NK117(she)001:27387: nang rgyud ltar na bum pa lha'i gnas dang kha
NK117(she)001:27388: rgyan sogs chas rgyan thams cad thugs rje chen po'i
NK117(she)001:27389: rtags sman lnga thugs rje byang chub kyi sems dang
NK117(she)001:27390: 'bru lnga lha'i rang bzhin rin chen lnga sku'i 'od
NK117(she)001:27391: snying po lnga ye shes thugs kyi dbyings spos sogs
NK117(she)001:27392: tshul khrims yon tan rgyal zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:27393: de ltar bum pa grangs nges yod na sgo mtshams
NK117(she)001:27394: brgyad du dri'i man+dala re re'i steng du bum pa
NK117(she)001:27395: brgyad dang gtso bum ni dbus su bzhag go //
NK117(she)001:27396: rnam rgyal gcig las med na lha thams cad der bskyed cing /
NK117(she)001:27397: las bum ni shar sgo'i g.yon du 'god pa rgya gar ba'i lugs so //
NK117(she)001:27398: rnam rgyal gdan khrir 'god pa la lung rig gis gnod chen yod ces bshad pa'ang snang ngo //
NK117(she)001:27399: 'di ltar dbang rdzas rnams dkyil 'khor bdag po zhes
NK117(she)001:27400: bla ma dang dbyer med gtso bo'i thugs ka nas
NK117(she)001:27402: dbang lha glo bur byon pa'i phyag mtshan du shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:27403: lha bskyed pa'i gnas bum pa kho na dang de'i
NK117(she)001:27404: steng gi dung zhal lam thod phor ni mchod yon
NK117(she)001:27405: 'bul ba'i snod kho na yin no //
NK117(she)001:27406: de yang lha bum pa'i nang du bskyed pa 'dra
NK117(she)001:27407: yang phyi rgyud gsum la ye shes pa gshegs gsol
NK117(she)001:27408: bya ba dang / bla med la dam ye gnyis
NK117(she)001:27409: med bde stong chen po'i ngang du 'od zhu ba'i
NK117(she)001:27410: bya ba dang / khyad par ro // bla med
NK117(she)001:27411: kyi skabs 'dir rnam bum gyi steng gi dung zhal
NK117(she)001:27412: sogs su dri bzang gi chu bdud rtsi lngas sbags
NK117(she)001:27413: pa badz+ra a mri ta de ka tha h+aum dang
NK117(she)001:27414: 'bru gsum lan bdun gyis ye shes kyi bdud rtsir
NK117(she)001:27415: byin gyis brlabs pas chu rdul phra rab rnams rdo
NK117(she)001:27416: rje'i rang bzhin du mos pa de nyid bzlas pa'i
NK117(she)001:27417: mthar mchod yon du phul rkyen gyis lha 'od zhu
NK117(she)001:27418: bya ba dang / khyad par ro // bya ba'o
NK117(she)001:27419: // las bum gyi lha mi bzhu bar bgegs bzlog
NK117(she)001:27420: pa'i phrin las bcol ba yang bshad do //
NK117(she)001:27421: bum par lha tshogs gsal ba la snying ga'i sa
NK117(she)001:27422: bon las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis ye shes pa
NK117(she)001:27423: spyan drangs te dam ye gnyis med la mchod bstod
NK117(she)001:27424: bya tshul bla med kyi lugs so //
NK117(she)001:27426: sngon nas slob dpon rang nyid las dbang thob cing
NK117(she)001:27427: rang gi sgrub grogs su gyur pa'i bskyed rdzogs sgom
NK117(she)001:27428: bzlas sogs la sngon goms yod cing dam tshig dang
NK117(she)001:27429: ldan pa zhig rang nyid kyi zhal tshab tu mnga'
NK117(she)001:27430: gsol ba la sgo'i slob dpon zhes bya ste dbang
NK117(she)001:27431: rdzas 'degs 'jog sogs byed du bcug kyang rung ba
NK117(she)001:27432: las de ltar ma yin pas mi rung bar rgyud
NK117(she)001:27434: slob ma'i grangs tshad kyang phyi rgyud las nyer lnga man chad gsungs kyang rnam snang mngon byang las /
NK117(she)001:27435: grangs bcad mi dgos par gsungs pa yang slob ma
NK117(she)001:27436: mtshan nyid tshang ba ni shin tu dkon na mngas
NK117(she)001:27437: kyis dogs pa dang nyung yang skyon med dkon pa'i
NK117(she)001:27438: phyir mang nyung dpyad mi dgos pa'i mtha' bsdus pa
NK117(she)001:27439: rgyud las gsungs pa 'di lta ste /
NK117(she)001:27440: slob ma phan tshun nang mi mthun pa mi bzung
NK117(she)001:27441: zhing gcig la gcig sems bzang ba zhi dul ldan
NK117(she)001:27442: zhing bla ma la phan pa bzung ngo zhes pa
NK117(she)001:27443: ni don bsdus nges par bya dgos so //
NK117(she)001:27444: gzhan yang 'gro khams mtha' yas pa bsgral ba'i sems
NK117(she)001:27445: bskyed kyis dkyil 'khor gyi tshon rtsi mthong ba'i phan
NK117(she)001:27446: yon gsungs pa la bsams te theg chen gyi bsam
NK117(she)001:27449: slob dpon snying rje chen po dang ldan pas sems
NK117(she)001:27450: can gyi khams ma lus pa bsgral ba la yi
NK117(she)001:27451: dam bca' ba kho nar bya ste /
NK117(she)001:27452: des byang chub sems kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'i phyir sems
NK117(she)001:27453: can tshad med pa rnams yongs su bzung bar bya'o
NK117(she)001:27455: yang sta gon gyi tshe stes dbang gis 'du bar
NK117(she)001:27456: ma nus kyang dngos gzhi dbang zhu ba'i mos 'dun
NK117(she)001:27457: drag po yod rigs sta gon gyi tshe tshang nus
NK117(she)001:27458: pa'am ma slebs pa dag gi gzugs brnyan nam de'i
NK117(she)001:27459: skyin po gzhug kyang chog par gsungs pas deng dus
NK117(she)001:27460: dbang zhabs su gyon pa bzhag srol 'dug pa'ang dad
NK117(she)001:27461: pa'i mngon rtogs lags pas rung ngam snyam mo //
NK117(she)001:27462: spyir yang sta gon gyi bya ba ma byas pa'i
NK117(she)001:27463: slob ma la dbang gcig car du bskur ba bkag
NK117(she)001:27464: phyir dbang gi dkyil 'khor yol bas bsgrib pa sogs
NK117(she)001:27465: mi mthong ba'i thabs kyang dgos par bshad do //
NK117(she)001:27466: dngos gzhi dbang bskur ba la sdom bzung dang /
NK117(she)001:27467: ltas brtags phyi nang gnyis kyi dang po blo bcos
NK117(she)001:27468: pa ni khrus byas gos gsar bgos man+dala phul pus
NK117(she)001:27469: btsugs thal sbyar du 'dug pa la phyi rgyud kyi
NK117(she)001:27470: don bkral nas bshad pa ste /
NK117(she)001:27471: gsang sngags don du gnyer ba dag gis tshe 'di
NK117(she)001:27472: dang phyi ma'i mngon mtho thob par 'dod pa dang
NK117(she)001:27473: / de gnyis ka ma yin pas 'jig rten pha
NK117(she)001:27474: rol ni 'das pa ste nges legs kyi yon tan
NK117(she)001:27475: don du gnyer zhing bsgrub byar bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27476: dbang dngos gzhi'i thog mar rdo rje slob dpon gyi
NK117(she)001:27477: rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur phyir bla ma'i sras su
NK117(she)001:27478: bsgrub pa ste phyi mthun du slob dpon dkyil 'khor
NK117(she)001:27479: bdag por snying ga'i sa bon gyi 'od kyis slob
NK117(she)001:27481: rnam shes h+aum yig sogs kyi rnam pas kha nas
NK117(she)001:27482: drangs rdo rje'i lam nas yum mkhar dbab pa lha'i
NK117(she)001:27483: rnam par gyur pa la rang gi snying ga'i 'od
NK117(she)001:27484: kyis gdan gsum tshang ba'i lha tshogs spyan drangs zhal
NK117(she)001:27485: nas zhugs / rjes chags kyi mes zhu bas bde
NK117(she)001:27486: chen byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur de ma thag
NK117(she)001:27487: yum mkha' nas bton te dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor
NK117(she)001:27488: bzhag pa'i dmigs pa ni slob dpon nyid kyis bya
NK117(she)001:27489: ste slob ma la bu zhes pa'i dngos don la
NK117(she)001:27490: nas zhugs / sbyor ba'o // de nas bla ma
NK117(she)001:27491: la dga' ba chen po zhes badz+ra d+h+aa ra'i mtshan
NK117(she)001:27492: nas bos te khyod kho na bdag gi ston pa
NK117(she)001:27493: gcig pur bas so zhes pa la sogs /
NK117(she)001:27494: gdab pa'i don sngags dang rgyud dang phyag rgya bzhi sogs kyi dam tshig dang /
NK117(she)001:27495: smon 'jug gnyis skyabs 'gro bcas bdag la stsol zhes
NK117(she)001:27496: pa rnams skas them bzhin bgrod tshul gyis bslab sdom
NK117(she)001:27497: rnams rim par sbyin zhing sdom pa dang dam tshig
NK117(she)001:27498: 'bogs pa po'i slob dpon rgyud dag pa'i thabs la
NK117(she)001:27499: 'bad par ma byas na gzhan gyis rdo rje slob
NK117(she)001:27500: dpon du bkur ba tsam gyis khengs pa mi bskyed
NK117(she)001:27501: de / so skye dam bca' ni gzhan gyis bsnyen
NK117(she)001:27502: bkur la brten nas nyams pa snang ba'i phyir ro
NK117(she)001:27503: de / // de nas las sngags dang chus bsrung
NK117(she)001:27504: la slob ma lhar bskyed pa'i gnas gsum du g.yas
NK117(she)001:27505: rdo rje'i khu tshur dang bcas pa'i dri chus yas
NK117(she)001:27506: sam mas rim nas reg cing phyag mtshan gsum la
NK117(she)001:27507: gnas pa'i 'bru gsum bsgoms nas sgo gsum byin gyis
NK117(she)001:27508: brlab pa sogs byas nas 'dod lngas mchod cing deng
NK117(she)001:27509: nas bzung ste 'dod yon la spyod pa'i sred len
NK117(she)001:27510: las grol te sgyu ma lta bu'i mchod pas bsod
NK117(she)001:27511: nams su 'gyur bar gyis zhes brjod do //
NK117(she)001:27512: de nas ngag sgrib sbyong phyir so shing dor ba'i dal gru bzhi pa ba byung gis byugs pa'am /
NK117(she)001:27513: pad+ma 'dab brgyad dri'i me tog gi tshom bu can nyer bsdogs byas la /
NK117(she)001:27514: 'o ma can gyi shing skyon dang bral ba rten
NK117(she)001:27516: pa'i brdar sor bcu gnyis pa zur gsum du byas
NK117(she)001:27517: pa dri bzang gi chus bkru bdug pas bdug rtser
NK117(she)001:27518: me tog gi phreng ba dang srad bu dmar pos
NK117(she)001:27519: bcings pa nyid a mri ta bzlas pas byin gyis
NK117(she)001:27520: brlabs pa de nyid ngag sgrib bsal ba dang /
NK117(she)001:27521: dngos grub kyi ltas brtag pa'i ched du slob ma'i
NK117(she)001:27522: lag par gtad pa yang kha byang du phyogs te
NK117(she)001:27523: 'dor tshe mthe bo gnyis kyi bar du rtse mo'i
NK117(she)001:27524: me tog bzung tshul dang zur gsum gyi dbal so
NK117(she)001:27525: rtsa bar ngos bzung bas so bru ba'i stangs ka
NK117(she)001:27526: dang bcas te 'dor ba'i tshe sngags dang bcas pas
NK117(she)001:27527: 'bor dgos shing / de yang 'dor yul ba byung
NK117(she)001:27528: gis sbags yod na so shing rtse mo gyen thur
NK117(she)001:27529: sogs ci 'drar babs kyang tshug ger sdod mod kyang
NK117(she)001:27530: 'bor dgos shing / / ba byung gis ma sbags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27531: nas tshom la'ang spyod lam ma bzo skyon gyi so
NK117(she)001:27532: shing steng du nyal stabs tsam las 'os ma mchis
NK117(she)001:27533: kyang rtsa ba'i dbal so rang la ma bstan pa
NK117(she)001:27534: gal che'o // de yang dpon slob zung gi byang
NK117(she)001:27535: phyogs su bltas te so shing 'dor na bkra shis
NK117(she)001:27536: pa'i phyogs yin pa'i bzang bar bshad do //
NK117(she)001:27537: 'dor tshe dngos grub kyi ltas brtag pa'i 'dun pas /
NK117(she)001:27539: zhes brjod pa dang stabs cig 'dor ba'i sngags don ni /
NK117(she)001:27540: ni sku lnga'am gsum mtshon la /
NK117(she)001:27542: ha sa ni bzhad pa ham ni de'i dbyings so //
NK117(she)001:27543: 'di gtam rgyud dang sbyar na de bzhin gshegs pa
NK117(she)001:27544: rdo rje bzhad pa slob lam la gnas skabs 'byung
NK117(she)001:27545: 'gyur la dgongs pas slob dpon dang pha ma sogs
NK117(she)001:27546: slar dud 'gro'i lus rten bzung ba'i sha zos pa'i
NK117(she)001:27547: nyes pa dang / de'i rnam smin gyis dbang thob
NK117(she)001:27548: pa'i bkag byed pa bsal ba'i ched du gang des
NK117(she)001:27549: mtshan sngags kyis btab pas so shing gis so brus
NK117(she)001:27550: pa'i nyes tshogs dag cing dbang snod du rung ba'i
NK117(she)001:27551: smon lam btab pa sogs kyi don shes par yang
NK117(she)001:27552: nyes pa dang / bya'o // de nas yid sgrib dag phyir khyor chu byin pa ni /
NK117(she)001:27553: dung chos sogs su dri bzang gi chu blugs pa
NK117(she)001:27554: bam zhu ba'i chur bsam la bgegs dgra'i sngags lan
NK117(she)001:27555: bdun gyis brlabs nas khyor ba g.yas g.yon gang rung
NK117(she)001:27556: du lan gsum sbyin par gsungs bzhin /
NK117(she)001:27557: h+r+aihbi shud d+he d+harma p+aa sa ni tsa s+ya sho
NK117(she)001:27558: d+ha ya sarba bi kalpana a pa na ya h+aum
NK117(she)001:27559: phatah h+r+aih sogs ni chos thams cad rnam par dag
NK117(she)001:27560: pa yin pas phung khams kyi bdag 'dzin can 'di'i
NK117(she)001:27561: sdig pa rnam par sbyongs shig /
NK117(she)001:27562: rnam par rtog pa thams cad bsal bar mdzod cig /
NK117(she)001:27563: ces lan gsum btung du bcug pa'i lhag ma dpung
NK117(she)001:27564: pa g.yon pa'i rgyab tu dor bas yid sgrib dag
NK117(she)001:27565: par bsam mo // 'di'i don yang gong bzhin de
NK117(she)001:27566: bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje chos byang chub sems dpa'i
NK117(she)001:27567: spyod pa la gzhol tshe ma 'ongs pa'i dus smin
NK117(she)001:27568: byed kyi dbang bskur skabs su gang gi mtshan sngags
NK117(she)001:27569: kyis brlabs pa'i chu byin pas yid sgrib rnam rtog
NK117(she)001:27570: bsal bar mdzod ces byung ba bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:27571: de nas lus sgrib dag phyir bsrung skud dmar po
NK117(she)001:27572: slob bu'i lus tshad gsum lteb bam khru gang sor
NK117(she)001:27573: bzhi yang bshad pas gang yang rung bar mdud pa
NK117(she)001:27574: gsum mam drug tu byas la h+aum las byung ba'i
NK117(she)001:27575: bsrung skud du dmigs nas las chus bsang bzhin bgegs
NK117(she)001:27576: dgra'i sngags bdun gyis brlabs nas khams dkar dmar gyi
NK117(she)001:27577: cha'i bar chad bsrung phyir pho mo'i dpung pa g.yon
NK117(she)001:27578: dang g.yas pa rim pa gnyis su bcings pa ni
NK117(she)001:27579: nyin mtshan nam phyi nang gi bar chos bsrung ched
NK117(she)001:27580: yin pas / bud+d+ha mee tri rak+sha rak+sha sar+b+aana s+w+aa h+aa /
NK117(she)001:27581: zhes bzla bzhin par rdo rje rgya gram gyi tshul
NK117(she)001:27582: du reg nas lus rdo rje'i go chas g.yogs par
NK117(she)001:27583: bsgom mo // de yang sngon de bzhin gshegs pa
NK117(she)001:27584: rdo rje'i bsrung ba slob lam du gnas tshe gong
NK117(she)001:27585: bzhin gang gis mtshan sngags kyis btab pa'i bsrung skud
NK117(she)001:27586: bcings pa dag la smin lam gyi dbang skal che
NK117(she)001:27587: phra'i rten 'brel ji bzhin mngon pa'i smon lam btab
NK117(she)001:27588: bsgom mo // pa ltar ro // yang rmi lam mi 'khrugs shing gsal ba'i ched du /
NK117(she)001:27589: ku sha sbyin pa'i don ni sngon bdag cag gi
NK117(she)001:27590: ston pas r+ts+wa 'tshong gi khye'u bkra shis la r+ts+wa
NK117(she)001:27591: ku sha'i chun po blangs te gdan du bting ba'i
NK117(she)001:27592: steng du mngon sangs rgyas pa bzhin du deng 'dir
NK117(she)001:27593: slob bur / d+h+aihyiga las byung ba'i ku sha ring ba'i phon po stan dang /
NK117(she)001:27594: thung ngu'i chun po sngas kyi ched du gtad la
NK117(she)001:27595: d+h+aihyiga dang 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis brlabs pa sbyin bzhin
NK117(she)001:27597: zhes pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje rnon
NK117(she)001:27598: po theg chen gyi bslab pa la slob tshe 'byung
NK117(she)001:27599: 'gyur gyi dus 'gro ba gang zhig smin lam du
NK117(she)001:27600: 'jug tshe skal pa bzang ngan gyi dge mtshan gyi
NK117(she)001:27601: rmi lam brtags tshe gang gi mtshan sngags kyis brlabs
NK117(she)001:27602: pa'i ku sha'i sngas stan la brten na dge min
NK117(she)001:27603: gyi ltas gsal por mthong bar smon pa bzhin no
NK117(she)001:27604: // de bzhin du rmis ltas brtags pa yang mtshan
NK117(she)001:27605: thun dum bu bzhi ru bgos pa'i dang po'i gang
NK117(she)001:27609: bzhi pa bden par 'jam dpal rtsa rgyud las gsungs /
NK117(she)001:27610: rmi lam bzang ngan gyi ltas ni gsang dgos las gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK117(she)001:27611: rang gi slob dpon gyis phyag cha gnang ba rmis na thugs kyi dngos grub dang /
NK117(she)001:27612: b+han+d+ha lag tu thogs pa dang dmag dpon byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27613: sku la rgyan cha 'dogs pa ni sku'i dngos grub dang /
NK117(she)001:27614: gser g.yu lus la 'dogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27615: zangs lcags sogs rin chen bcings pa ni yon tan gyi dngos grub bo //
NK117(she)001:27617: me tog thogs pa nyi zla shar ba yang dngos grub kyi rtags su bshad cing /
NK117(she)001:27618: mda' gzhu dang go mtshon thogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27619: rtsi shing mang po bsdu ba /
NK117(she)001:27620: nam mkha' la 'phur ba sogs phrin las dngos grub thob pa'i rtags la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27621: ngan rtags rmis na tshogs gtor dang /
NK117(she)001:27623: las thams cad pa'i sngags sbyin sreg srung 'khor sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:27624: khyad par bdag med kyi don bsgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27625: rmi lam sogs sgyu ma'i dpes bzlog par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:27626: de nas spro ba bskyed pa ni rnam snang mngon byang las gsungs pas /
NK117(she)001:27629: de bzhin gshegs par 'gyur ba yin //
NK117(she)001:27630: zhes pa'i bar gyi rkang pa sum cu so gnyis po'i 'grel pa gzhung tshig gis shes nus so //
