NK117(she)001:27631: 'di la gzhan dag dkyil 'khor mthong yang chos gsum
NK117(she)001:27632: dang mi ldan na sdig pa mi 'byung zhes 'chad
NK117(she)001:27633: mod / de lta na sngon 'gro'i chos gsum kho na'i nus pa yin par 'gyur bas /
NK117(she)001:27634: dkyil 'khor 'di 'dra mthong ba'i mod la sdig pa
NK117(she)001:27635: thams cad zad par 'gyur zhes gsungs pa la snying
NK117(she)001:27636: po med par 'phangs pa'i skyon yod pa'i phyir ro
NK117(she)001:27637: // des na bum pa sta gon dang slob ma
NK117(she)001:27638: sta gon ni ras bris la brten pa nyid legs
NK117(she)001:27639: // so // de ltar dbang gi nyer bsdogs sam
NK117(she)001:27640: sta gon gyi rim pa sngon du btang nas lhag
NK117(she)001:27641: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du bya ba'i thig
NK117(she)001:27642: gi rim pa ni rgyas 'grel du blta bar bya'o
NK117(she)001:27643: // so // // thig gi rim pa yongs su
NK117(she)001:27644: rdzogs par gyur tshe bum pa dgod par bya ste
NK117(she)001:27645: // so // // / sngar lhag gnas byas pa'i
NK117(she)001:27646: bum pa rnams slob dpon rdo rje sems dpa'i nga
NK117(she)001:27647: rgyal la gnas shing rdor dril dang bcas h+aum bzhi'i
NK117(she)001:27648: sngags zlo bzhin par spos rol gyis sna drangs te
NK117(she)001:27649: dal la g.yas skor gsum byas nas rnam bum gtso
NK117(she)001:27650: bo'i mdun nam lha snam mam shar sgo'i phyi rol
NK117(she)001:27652: bum pa gzhan brgyad dam gang yod rnams lha so so'i mdun nam /
NK117(she)001:27653: sgo mtshams brgyad dam nyung na shar sgo'i g.yon logs sam /
NK117(she)001:27654: rdo rje'i ra ba'i nang khongs su tshud par bzhag go //
NK117(she)001:27655: las bum rang mdun du bum gdan la bzhag /
NK117(she)001:27656: dal gyi phyogs bzhir shar nas rim bzhin sher phyin ting 'dzin rgyal po /
NK117(she)001:27657: sdong po bkod pa gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams 'don du gzhug go //
NK117(she)001:27658: nang gi phyogs kun tu mchod pa'i rdzas sna tshogs
NK117(she)001:27659: mtha' ma bkag par 'god cing h+aum dang gtso bo'i
NK117(she)001:27660: sngags badz+ra s+pha ra na kham btags pas 'bul /
NK117(she)001:27661: phyogs skyong rnams mnyes phyir phyogs bzhi dang mtshams bzhi ba dan bco lnga gzug pa'ang /
NK117(she)001:27662: shar phyogs su dbang po la ser po /
NK117(she)001:27664: nyi zla ser dang dkar po /
NK117(she)001:27667: srin po dud kha rnams so so'i phyogs mdog /
NK117(she)001:27668: nub tu chu lha dkar po /
NK117(she)001:27670: thag bzangs ris la nag po /
NK117(she)001:27671: nub byang du rlung lha'i ljang gu /
NK117(she)001:27672: byang du lus ngan po'i ser po /
NK117(she)001:27674: byang shar du dbang ldan la dkar po'o //
NK117(she)001:27675: de nas slob dpon khrus byas /
NK117(she)001:27677: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i chas su zhugs nas /
NK117(she)001:27678: phyi rol par gtor ma byin la bskrad /
NK117(she)001:27679: phur bus gdab cing srung 'khor bsgom pas mtshams bcad /
NK117(she)001:27680: bgegs dgra'i sngags bzlas pa'i chus dkyil 'khor la bsangs
NK117(she)001:27681: shing bsrungs nas rdor dril 'dzin pas dal gyi shar
NK117(she)001:27683: dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa la bdag mdun so sor bsgrub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27684: lhan cig bsgrub tshul gnyis las /
NK117(she)001:27686: bdag gi rnal 'byor bzlas pa'i bar sgrub thabs bzhin
NK117(she)001:27687: byas mthar nyer bsdu rdzogs rim bcas byed rgyu dang
NK117(she)001:27689: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos la sogs
NK117(she)001:27690: kyis ting nge 'dzin gnyis mtshams sbyor nas rten brten
NK117(she)001:27691: pa'i bskyed chog rnams rdor sems sgyu 'phrul gyi bdag
NK117(she)001:27692: sras kyi cho ga bzhin la /
NK117(she)001:27693: gzhan sras kyi cho ga bsgrub tshul gnyis 'grel chen
NK117(she)001:27694: phyogs bcu'i mun sel gyi le'u dgu pa ltar shes
NK117(she)001:27696: 'og tu bskyed rim gyi skabs su'ang 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:27698: dkyil 'khor bsangs sbyang byas nas 'byung ba rim brtsegs
NK117(she)001:27699: nas bzung dkyil 'khor bskyed pa bcas grub nas lha
NK117(she)001:27700: rnams mngon sum par dmigs pa la rdo rje shugs
NK117(she)001:27701: kyis 'jug pas dal du zhugs nas sgrub tshul yang
NK117(she)001:27703: mchog tu bde ba'i sems ni sogs rkang pa gnyis
NK117(she)001:27704: kyi mthar sngags dang 'bul tshig gis me tog phreng
NK117(she)001:27705: ba phul bas / bdag la'ang phreng ba'i dbang bskur bar bsams te mgo bor bcing bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:27706: de nas mchod yon phul la nub sgo sogs su
NK117(she)001:27707: song ste h+aum mdzad kyi nga rgyal la gnas pas
NK117(she)001:27708: h+aum brjod cing gar dang bcas te sgo ba bzhi
NK117(she)001:27710: de dag gi shar sgo sogs rim gyis phye bar
NK117(she)001:27711: bsam la rdo rje khu tshur bcings te phyag rgya
NK117(she)001:27712: dang sngags kyis 'jug pas zhugs nas stangs dpyal sbyor
NK117(she)001:27713: ba dang ye shes pa dgug gzhug sogs 'dus pa'i
NK117(she)001:27714: le'u bzhi pa las gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:27715: gzhan yang rdul tshon gyi dal bsang sbyangs bskyed bstims
NK117(she)001:27716: sogs gsar rnying so so'i lugs mang du yod kyang
NK117(she)001:27717: rang rang so so'i gzhung ltar byed pa dang sngags
NK117(she)001:27718: 'grel gyi gzhung bzhin nyams 'og tu tshud par bya'o
NK117(she)001:27719: // bdag mdun tha mi dad du byed tshe /
NK117(she)001:27720: bsgrub gzhi nga yir 'dzin pa dang gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis /
NK117(she)001:27721: sgrub chos ting 'dzin gsum nas cho ga'i yan lag
NK117(she)001:27722: rdzogs pa'i bar rnams kun 'byung gis bskyed pa'i rim
NK117(she)001:27723: can yin na phyi rol gyi yul rnams dbyings dang
NK117(she)001:27724: dbyings kyi rang bzhin du shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27725: rdzas dang dngos po rnams byang chub sems su shes
NK117(she)001:27726: pa'i dus na ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rig pa
NK117(she)001:27727: rang snang ba'i ngo bo nyid la gcig dang tha
NK117(she)001:27728: dad pa'am bdag gzhan du ris chad med pa'i rang
NK117(she)001:27729: bzhin dbyer med kyi dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis
NK117(she)001:27730: grub pa'o // tshul 'di lta bu khongs su ma
NK117(she)001:27731: chud pa dag bdag mdun dbyer med du bsgrub pa'i
NK117(she)001:27732: phyogs la klan ka byed pa ni rnal 'byor dbang
NK117(she)001:27734: ma he'i lha sogs kyi dkyil chog kyang ma mthong bar zad do //
NK117(she)001:27735: des na las dang po pa zhes pa ni /
NK117(she)001:27736: lha yongs su ma gyur pa'i gang zag rnams yin
NK117(she)001:27737: pas bdag mdun tha dad pa'i go don 'byor ba
NK117(she)001:27739: de kho na nyid mthong ba rnams kyis ni chos
NK117(she)001:27740: thams cad gdod nas rdzas 'gal ba ma yin pa'i
NK117(she)001:27741: rang bzhin shes nas bdag mdun du dbye ba'i rnam
NK117(she)001:27742: rtog du ma ro gcig tu bsdus nas snang srid
NK117(she)001:27743: 'khor 'das thams cad dkyil 'khor gcig gi rten dang
NK117(she)001:27744: brten pa'i rang bzhin du rdzogs par gsal btab nas
NK117(she)001:27746: dbang bskur rab gnas sogs dgos ched dmigs bsal gyi
NK117(she)001:27747: tshe bdag mdun cha gnyis su dbye tshul shes par
NK117(she)001:27748: byas dal bsgrub pa'i las rim la 'jug /
NK117(she)001:27749: chad lhag la sogs pa'i nyes pa bsal don du me la brten nas me lha tshim pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27750: me lhar brten nas lha tshogs tshim pa'i thabs su sbyin bsreg gal che zhing /
NK117(she)001:27751: de yang mtshan ma ngan tshe zhi /
NK117(she)001:27752: rab gnas sogs kyi tshe rgyas pa /
NK117(she)001:27754: sta gon gyi skabs sogs bar chad kyi ltas byung na drag po'o //
NK117(she)001:27755: sgrub tshul de lta bu ras bris kyi dal la'ang
NK117(she)001:27756: mi rung ba ma yin kyang rdul tshon gyi dkyil
NK117(she)001:27757: 'khor las bya ba nyung ba'i skabs yin pas cho
NK117(she)001:27758: ga'i yan lag dmigs bsal rnams ma grub kyang chog
NK117(she)001:27759: go // de la bris sku'i ye shes pa la
NK117(she)001:27760: 'byin 'jug byed pa sogs ni lhag gnas byas pa'i
NK117(she)001:27761: 'gal zlar 'gyur ba'i kun tu rtog pa'i gzhan dbang
NK117(she)001:27763: rdul tshon dang ras bris kyi dal gnyis ka las
NK117(she)001:27764: khyad par du gyur pa ni zab mo lus kyi
NK117(she)001:27766: bya spyod gnyis su ma grags shing /
NK117(she)001:27767: rnal 'byor rgyud du'ang gsal bar ma bstan pas /
NK117(she)001:27769: rjes su rnal 'byor kho na'i khyad chos so //
NK117(she)001:27770: de'i khyad gzhi yang tshon dkyil gnyis ni gsar byung
NK117(she)001:27771: du bsgrub cing dmigs pa'i rnam pa kha phyir bltas
NK117(she)001:27772: kyis sgro btags pas dman la /
NK117(she)001:27773: lus dkyil ni phung khams skye mched sogs lha'i bdag nyid du phyi gzugs las 'das par yod do //
NK117(she)001:27774: rdo rje'i lus grub pa tsam nas de ltar du
NK117(she)001:27775: gnas pa'i rnam pa sgyu tsam du mthong ba de
NK117(she)001:27776: nyid la dmigs shing kha nang blta ba'i rnal 'byor
NK117(she)001:27777: gtso che bas 'bras bu myur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:27778: de'ang thog mar tshon dkyil gnyis gang rung ltar dbang
NK117(she)001:27779: bskur nod nas rim pa gnyis la nges pa thob
NK117(she)001:27780: pa dag la ni rnam pa dngos bstan kho na
NK117(she)001:27781: la ma ltos te rang bzhin shes pas sbas don
NK117(she)001:27782: du ngo bo nyid du yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:27783: gal te rim gnyis la ma goms pas ni slob
NK117(she)001:27784: ma dal der 'jug kyang lus yongs su gyur pa
NK117(she)001:27785: las rten dang / rtsa khams rnams las brten pa'i
NK117(she)001:27786: lha tshogs bsgom mthar cha gnyis su phye nas lus
NK117(she)001:27787: dkyil du gzhug bya 'jug byed dmigs kyang mi rigs
NK117(she)001:27789: lus dkyil yang dngos gnas la 'thad du mi rung
NK117(she)001:27790: ste lus dal du sgom rgyu'ang so so'i dod thub
NK117(she)001:27791: tsam las rnam pa bsgyur nas /
NK117(she)001:27792: yan lag rta babs dang rna ba ri dwags su
NK117(she)001:27793: byed pa dras shing drubs pa'i tshem bu lta bu
NK117(she)001:27794: ni rig pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:27795: de ltar bskyed gzhi tshon dkyil gnyis dang lus dkyil
NK117(she)001:27796: bcas pas lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK117(she)001:27797: ltar bsgrub na rdo rje slob dpon gyi spangs rtogs
NK117(she)001:27798: mchog dman dang sbyar nas dbye tshul gsum du nges
NK117(she)001:27799: te / slob dpon sangs rgyas kyi sar bzhugs pa
NK117(she)001:27800: dag gis slob ma sa bcu rgyun matha'i byang sems
NK117(she)001:27801: la 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur bas sa bcu
NK117(she)001:27802: gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa bcu gsum pa rnams
NK117(she)001:27803: rdzogs nas zung 'jug ngo bo nyid sku 'thob par
NK117(she)001:27804: te / byed do // slob dpon mthar lam pa
NK117(she)001:27805: gcig gis slob ma mthong sgom la gnas pa la
NK117(she)001:27806: dbyings rig sprul pa'i dal mkha' khyab bam dpag tshad
NK117(she)001:27807: kyi bar bsgoms nas gzhug pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27808: slob dpon 'phags lam du bzhugs pas slob ma bden
NK117(she)001:27809: mthong tshogs sbyor gyi yon tan mthar phyin pa dag
NK117(she)001:27810: la rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor rgyang grags tsam
NK117(she)001:27811: pa'i bar sprul te slob ma gzhug pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27812: lar yang slob dpon gyi ting 'dzin gyi nus stobs
NK117(she)001:27813: dang slob ma'i las 'phro dag stobs kho na la
NK117(she)001:27814: rag las so // dal der 'jug mi nus na
NK117(she)001:27815: slob dpon sbyor lam gyi bar chad med lam thob
NK117(she)001:27816: rag las so // pa'am / g.yo thob goms brtan
NK117(she)001:27817: gyi ting 'dzin tshad du phyin pa dag gis slob
NK117(she)001:27818: ma shes rab dang dam can skal ba rab la
NK117(she)001:27819: rag las so // pa'am / lus dkyil / 'bring la chu tshon /
NK117(she)001:27820: tha ma rdul tshon te bum dbang gi dal dang /
NK117(she)001:27821: dbang gong ma gsum la kun rdzob byang sems /
NK117(she)001:27822: yum mkha' don dam byang sems te rang byung gi
NK117(she)001:27823: dal gsum la brten nas dbang bskur ba yin no
NK117(she)001:27824: // de ltar rgyu dbang gi dus su bum dbang
NK117(she)001:27825: rdul tshon gyi dal las gzhan du mi rung ba'i
NK117(she)001:27826: tshul slob dpon so skye'i rgyud ldan la rung gis
NK117(she)001:27827: // / mthong lam skyes pa yan la ni de
NK117(she)001:27828: ltar du bzung na nyes pa chen po'i rgyur 'gyur
NK117(she)001:27829: // / ro // lar yang rdul tshon la sogs
NK117(she)001:27830: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rnams chos mig rdul
NK117(she)001:27831: bral thob pa'i slob dpon dag la rang gzhan gyi
NK117(she)001:27833: sems can gyi rnam rtog 'dul ba'i rten 'brel la dgongs nas gsungs pa nyid de /
NK117(she)001:27834: don la dbang bskur byed la ltos na bsgrub byar gyur pa'i dmigs pa'i rten dang /
NK117(she)001:27835: bskur yul ltos na rmongs pa'i gzhan dbang gis rang sems kyi chos nyid dang /
NK117(she)001:27836: phung khams skye mched rnams de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying
NK117(she)001:27837: po can gyi rten dang brten pa'i rang bzhin du
NK117(she)001:27838: yod pa las kha phyir phyogs kyi ma rig 'dzin
NK117(she)001:27839: pas sgrib pa rnams la rang ngo'i yon tan gang
NK117(she)001:27840: yin pa brda dang don rtags kyis mtshon nas mngon
NK117(she)001:27841: sum par ston pa'i thabs kyi yan lag tsam las
NK117(she)001:27842: gtso bor mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i rdzas dang dngos po
NK117(she)001:27843: nyid kyis ni yang dag pa nyid du mi grub
NK117(she)001:27844: pas shu nya ta la sogs pa'i sngags kyis stong
NK117(she)001:27845: par sbyangs nas ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam 'phrul gyis
NK117(she)001:27846: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa sogs
NK117(she)001:27847: cho ga gang yin ltar gzhung bsrangs nas bskyed rim
NK117(she)001:27848: bzlas sgom rdzogs rim sogs la nan tan bskyed dgos
NK117(she)001:27849: pa yin no // lar yang gzhung dang gang zag
NK117(she)001:27850: khyad par can la rmongs par bltas nas chos spang
NK117(she)001:27851: gi las kyis 'gog pa ni nyes dmigs chen po
NK117(she)001:27853: dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon dag gis gzhan snang
NK117(she)001:27854: la bltar mi mngon pa ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam
NK117(she)001:27855: par 'phrul pa rgya mtsho las g.yo ba med pa'i
NK117(she)001:27856: dkyil 'khor 'dod rgyal ba sna tshogs su slob ma
NK117(she)001:27857: smin pa'i mngon sum tshad ma rtog ge'i rigs pas
NK117(she)001:27858: bzlog pa ma yin pas mnyam par bzhag pa'i sems
NK117(she)001:27860: 'di ltar byang shar sham+b+ha lar 'jam dbyangs grags pas
NK117(she)001:27861: blos slong gi dkyil 'khor du tshangs pa'i drang srong
NK117(she)001:27862: bye ba phrag phyed bzhi bcug ste smin par byas
NK117(she)001:27863: pa'i phyir / rnam pa gru bzhi pa kho nar ma nges te /
NK117(she)001:27864: dus 'khor 'khor lo sdom chen gyi dal zlum po sgo brgyad du snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:27865: sgo can kho nar yang ma nges te shes rab
NK117(she)001:27866: ma rgyud dag zur gsum chos 'byung gi rnam pa
NK117(she)001:27867: can dang / gzhan yang pad+ma 'dab brgyad la sogs
NK117(she)001:27868: dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor sgo dang rta babs
NK117(she)001:27869: la sogs pa'i rnam pa ma rdzogs pa mang du
NK117(she)001:27870: snang bas de dag kyang dkyil 'khor de dang de'i
NK117(she)001:27871: bdag pos mngon sum du bstan cing byin gyis brlabs
NK117(she)001:27872: can dang / pa'i phyir dang / lha tshogs mang nyung yang ma nges de bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:27873: spyir de bzhin gshegs pa rnams gnyug mar gnas pa'i
NK117(she)001:27874: gzhal med khang ni rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga
NK117(she)001:27875: nyid na / de'i rang bzhin ni rnam thar sgo
NK117(she)001:27876: gsum las 'da' ba ma yin pa mtshon phyir chos
NK117(she)001:27878: ma bstan kyang rung ste gnas nyi tshe bar rgya
NK117(she)001:27879: yongs su chad pa'i phyogs su ma lhung zhing mkha'
NK117(she)001:27880: khyab kyi b+ha ga shes rab kyi pha rol du
NK117(she)001:27881: phyin pa'i gnas su grub pa gang zhig re zhig
NK117(she)001:27882: gdul bya 'dul byed dang bstun nas dam tshig chen
NK117(she)001:27883: po'i gzhal med khang gru bzhi pa la sogs par
NK117(she)001:27884: byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshul rgyud las bstan pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27885: de bas na rgyu dus kyi dkyil 'khor gru bzhi
NK117(she)001:27886: sgo snam rta babs dang bcas pa'i rnam pa rdzogs
NK117(she)001:27887: par bstan pa de'ang rgyu'i theg pa dang bstun nas
NK117(she)001:27888: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi la sogs pa
NK117(she)001:27889: byang chos so bdun dang dag pa sbyor ba las
NK117(she)001:27891: lam bden thams cad ni 'dus byas /
NK117(she)001:27892: 'dus byas kun rdzob las 'da' ba med pas /
NK117(she)001:27893: kun rdzob kyi chos rnams don dam bden pa'i ngo
NK117(she)001:27894: bo nyid rnam thar sgo gsum du ston phyir rdo
NK117(she)001:27895: rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga'am gzugs brnyan du mtshon la
NK117(she)001:27896: / so bdun kyang sngags lam du yul dang /
NK117(she)001:27897: rtsa dang khams so so nas so bdun du bshad
NK117(she)001:27898: sbyar gyi dag pa'ang don dam par bde stong gnyis
NK117(she)001:27899: su med pa'i bdag nyid can yin pa gang zhig
NK117(she)001:27900: e wam gyi yi ge'i brda las rten dang brten
NK117(she)001:27901: pa'i dkyil 'khor du mtshon pa'i tshul 'jam dpal sgyu
NK117(she)001:27902: 'phrul d+r+wa ba las bstan pa ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:27903: dus kyi 'khor lo mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho sogs nas
NK117(she)001:27904: e wam gyi yi ge sgrub tshul mang du gsungs
NK117(she)001:27905: pas / dal so so'i mtshon don la dgongs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27906: dngos grub thob pa'i slob dpon gyi cha nas phyogs gcig tu bzung bar mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:27907: 'on kyang dbang bzhi pa'i dngos don ma rtogs shing
NK117(she)001:27908: sgra spyi'i rang bzhin lha dang dal gyi dbyibs dang
NK117(she)001:27909: rnam pa'i brtul zhugs mchog tu 'dzin pa las ma
NK117(she)001:27910: grol ba'i byis pa slob dpon gyi gzugs su 'chos
NK117(she)001:27911: pa dag gis rang rang gzhung nas bshad pa'i cho
NK117(she)001:27912: ga'i yan lag nyams na slob ma smin par mi
NK117(she)001:27913: nus pa ni don la gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:27914: bum sgrub ni so so'i rang gzhung ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:27915: bzhi pa'i yan lag bzhi ni /
NK117(she)001:27917: slob ma gzhug par gnang ba nod pa /
NK117(she)001:27918: nod nas slob ma dal du gzhug pa zhugs pa la dbang bskur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:27920: bgegs gtor byin la bgegs dang phral /
NK117(she)001:27922: gos rgyan dmar pos spras la dal gyi shar sgor 'dug ste me tog thogs la /
NK117(she)001:27924: sogs nas sngags kyi thog mtha' gnyis gong bzhin du
NK117(she)001:27925: +aa dang h+aum dang s+w+aa dang h+aa rnams sbyar ro
NK117(she)001:27926: // des rang bzhin gyi dal gyi lha rnams kyi
NK117(she)001:27927: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dang dbyer med
NK117(she)001:27928: // du bltas la / badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum gis dam ye bsres zhing /
NK117(she)001:27929: badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam gyis brtan par byas /
NK117(she)001:27930: badz+ra sa ma ya hos dbang du gyur zhing dgyes pa bskyed /
NK117(she)001:27931: dzahh+aum bam hohgasala brtan gyi tshad brgyad thob pa'i dal dang tha mi dad du gyur par blta'o //
NK117(she)001:27932: go 'phang mthon por son pa'i slob dpon gyis ni
NK117(she)001:27933: nang ye shes kyi dal du 'jug pa 'di tsam
NK117(she)001:27934: gyis kyang dam tshig gi dal du 'jug pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:27935: rnams nyams su myong ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:27936: de yang dal du 'jug pa'i don ni ye shes
NK117(she)001:27937: pa dang bdag nyid dbyer med du bya ba'i don
NK117(she)001:27938: no // de lta na'ang so skye'i slob dpon rnams
NK117(she)001:27939: ni nyams chag dang bcas pa rtog sgrib can yin
NK117(she)001:27940: pas dad 'dun rnam dag gis dal du 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:27943: snod kyis ma smin pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27944: de bzhin du cho gas ma smin pa /
NK117(she)001:27945: cho ga ma rdzogs pas ma smin pa /
NK117(she)001:27946: zab mos 'jigs nas ma smin pa bzhir 'phags pa
NK117(she)001:27947: yab sras bzhed pas slob dpon rang la rtsa ltung
NK117(she)001:27948: yod na slob bu la sngags sdom mi skye bas
NK117(she)001:27949: so // des na he ru ka 'dus pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27952: rim gsal sogs don mthun par /
NK117(she)001:27953: slob ma 'jug pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK117(she)001:27954: dang por slob dpon 'jug par bya //
NK117(she)001:27955: zhes pas slob ma la bskul ba ltar rang nyid
NK117(she)001:27956: kyis rig pa bde gshegs snying po'i ngo bo nyid
NK117(she)001:27957: bla ma dang dal gyi lha tshogs su shes pa
NK117(she)001:27958: dang rnam smin bag chags kyi lus rten glo bur
NK117(she)001:27959: du skye ba'i kun rtog dang bcas pa slob bu'i
NK117(she)001:27961: yang na rgyu dbang thob pa'i bla mas las kyi
NK117(she)001:27962: slob dpon mdzad par mos kyang rung zhes slob dpon
NK117(she)001:27963: pad+mas gsungs so // de nas slob ma 'jug pa'i
NK117(she)001:27964: ched du dal gyi lha la slob dpon gyis gnang
NK117(she)001:27966: rdo rje ye shes ni chos thams cad kyi de
NK117(she)001:27967: kho na nyid yin bzhin de la bstod tshig sngon
NK117(she)001:27968: du btang nas tshul de lta bu'i dngos grub slob
NK117(she)001:27969: ma la byin pa'i ched du dmigs nas rdo rje
NK117(she)001:27970: ye shes 'thob byed pa'i sogs dang /
NK117(she)001:27971: bden pa gang gis sogs nas /
NK117(she)001:27972: kun gyis sgrib med mthong bar shog dang yan lan gsum brjod do //
NK117(she)001:27973: de ni thabs shes zung 'jug yin pa'i bdag nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK117(she)001:27974: de yang rgyu ni chos kyi dbyings la thos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27976: bsgom pa'i shes rab las yang dag par 'byung ngo //
NK117(she)001:27977: de kho na nyid kyi snying po'am de bzhin nyid
NK117(she)001:27978: ni ye shes su kun tu bzang po ste dal
NK117(she)001:27979: gyi rten brten par bcas pa'i spro gzhi yin no
NK117(she)001:27980: // don dam bden pa las dal gyi gzugs brnyan du snang zhing bkod pa las /
NK117(she)001:27981: de dang de'i skur blta ba ni gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:27982: de lta bu'i dal ni gsang sngags zab mo'i nus
NK117(she)001:27983: pas sdig pa bsal ba la brten nas slob ma
NK117(she)001:27984: kun gyis sgrib med de mthong bar shog cig ces
NK117(she)001:27985: so // de nas lhag gnas byas pa'i slob ma rnams phyi rol du las chus bkru /
NK117(she)001:27986: las sngags bzlas pa'i gos dmar ram /
NK117(she)001:27988: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nut+ta ra bo d+hi a lam k+aa ra sogs kyis smad g.yogs dang /
NK117(she)001:27989: badz+ra rak+sha ham gis stod g.yogs dgab /
NK117(she)001:27990: badz+ra ush+ni shas gtsug tor bskon /
NK117(she)001:27991: dal mthong ba re zhig bsgrib pa dang /
NK117(she)001:27992: ma rig pas ldongs pa'i mtshon byed du dar ras dmar pos gdong bcings te /
NK117(she)001:27994: h+aum zhes pas kyang rung ngo //
NK117(she)001:27995: a kham bi ras me tog gtad cing nub nas
NK117(she)001:27996: g.yas skor gyi rgyal ba rigs bzhi dang dbus kyi
NK117(she)001:27997: mi bskyod pa'i sa bon las skyes pa'i push+pe ma
NK117(she)001:27998: le rang rang skyed byed kyi yig 'brus mtshan pa
NK117(she)001:28000: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dri ba dang lan ldon bya /
NK117(she)001:28001: de nas sgo'i slob dpon nam las slob kyis rdo
NK117(she)001:28002: rje bzung bzhin pa la slob ma yang 'chang bcug
NK117(she)001:28003: nas dal gyi yol ba dang nye bar khrid la
NK117(she)001:28004: dal gyi phyogs bzhi nas phyag 'tshal tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:28006: gnyis pa rdor thal snying kha dang /
NK117(she)001:28008: bzhi pa spyi bo nas phab ste snying gar spyi bo sa la reg tshul bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28009: de dang chabs cig sarba bud+d+ha p+au dza karma ne +aat+ma nam ni t+y+aa ta y+aa mi /
NK117(she)001:28010: zhes rigs bzhi'i rgyal ba rnams bos nas lus dbul du bcug /
NK117(she)001:28011: ci'i phyir dbul na rgyal ba rnams la mchod cing bsnyen bkur dang /
NK117(she)001:28014: mchod pa'i las kyi don du'o //
NK117(she)001:28015: de nas phyi rol par gtor ma byin nas bi shwa badz+ra la sogs sam /
NK117(she)001:28017: lag sor bcu rigs lnga yab yum du bskyed la
NK117(she)001:28018: bden pa bdar nas bsnol ba'i sbyor mtshams nas byung
NK117(she)001:28019: ba'i byang sems kyi 'od zer gyis slob ma'i sgrib
NK117(she)001:28020: tshogs bral 'od du zhu nas dngul chu ltar gyur
NK117(she)001:28021: pa de rnam snang du bskyed la gnas gsum du
NK117(she)001:28022: 'bru gsum gyis go bgos shing bsrung ngo //
NK117(she)001:28023: de rjes bla mas k+aa ya sid+d+hi sogs gnas gsum 'bru gsum bzhag la 'du 'phro dang /
NK117(she)001:28024: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sogs sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig sbyin /
NK117(she)001:28025: khyad par gsang chen thabs la mkhas pa'i theg pa chen po'i rigs nges par byed la /
NK117(she)001:28026: rgyal ba rnams dang mi 'bral zhing bdud rnams zil
NK117(she)001:28027: gyis gnon pa'i phan yon dang yang ldan pa thams
NK117(she)001:28028: cad rnal 'byor gyi sems bskyed pa nyid rang sngags
NK117(she)001:28029: kyis go bar bya ba ni /
NK117(she)001:28030: sarba yo ga tsit+ta ut+p+aa ta ya mi /
NK117(she)001:28031: zhes 'don du 'jug cing sgom don la /
NK117(she)001:28032: snying gar kun rdzob byang sems zla gdan la don
NK117(she)001:28033: dam byang sems stong nyid kyi rdo rje rtse lnga
NK117(she)001:28034: pas rgyas btab pas byang chub las phyir mi ldog
NK117(she)001:28036: de'i rjes su rdo rje me tog dang bcas pas snying gar reg la /
NK117(she)001:28037: su ra sa ma ya s+t+wam hohsid+da badz+ra ya th+aa su kham /
NK117(she)001:28038: zhes ba de ba'i dam tshig 'dus pa'i bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:28039: dngos grub ji ltar ba'i bde ba zhes pa'i sngags
NK117(she)001:28040: don gyis rdor sems kyi rang bzhin du byas nas
NK117(she)001:28041: me tog la sogs pas mchod /
NK117(she)001:28042: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK117(she)001:28045: dam tshig nyams shing slar gso 'dun med pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28046: nyan rang sogs sngags la mi dad pas ma 'dres pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28047: med pa ni skye bo phal pa dag gzhan dag ni tshig gis go bar nus so //
NK117(she)001:28048: de nas slob dpon gyis slob ma dgug cing /
NK117(she)001:28049: +aa kham b+ai ra h+aum gis yol ba'i nang du khrid la /
NK117(she)001:28050: ma h+aa ra ta su dri d+ha su to sh+yo
NK117(she)001:28051: su po sh+yo badz+ra sa t+wa a d+ya sid+d+h+ya m+aam
NK117(she)001:28052: zhes pas dal la bskor du gzhug go //
NK117(she)001:28053: de nas dam la bzhag pa la'ang /
NK117(she)001:28056: gnyis ka thun mong ste gsum gyi sgo nas dam la bzhag pa gzhung so sor shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28057: de ltar dam tshig bsgrag bzung dang 'brel bar thabs spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28058: shes rab lta ba'i phyogs gnyis zung 'brel gyi sgo
NK117(she)001:28059: nas 'dod yon la spyod kyang nyes skyon gyis mi
NK117(she)001:28061: de nas lha dang skal ba mnyam phyir me tog
NK117(she)001:28062: dor tshul dang ltas bzang ngan brtags pa sogs gzhung
NK117(she)001:28063: ltar ro // de yang rdul tshon dngos sam der
NK117(she)001:28064: skabs ma phyed na chos rnams 'dun pa'i rjes su
NK117(she)001:28065: 'brang ba yin pas man+dala gyi re kha tshom bu
NK117(she)001:28066: can la dor rung bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:28067: de nas gsang ba'i 'jug pa ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK117(she)001:28068: pra we shas ma rig sgo nga'i sbubs dral phyir
NK117(she)001:28069: khog pa kha phye bar bsam la a we sha
NK117(she)001:28070: mang du brjod cing lta ba'i gdengs bskyed nas rigs
NK117(she)001:28071: dang mthun pa'i lha thim pa dbyer med du bsam
NK117(she)001:28072: nas 'beb sngags dang rol mo 'khrol ba sogs dbang
NK117(she)001:28073: gzhung ltar shes par bya ba nyid do //
NK117(she)001:28074: de yang ye shes pa phebs rtags spros bral zag
NK117(she)001:28075: med kyi sems gzhi'i rgyud du gyur pa la dbang
NK117(she)001:28076: las byung ba'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28077: de yang ye shes 'bebs pa po lta sgom gyi gdengs dang ldan pa zhig gal che zhing /
NK117(she)001:28078: gzhan yang ye shes dbab tshul rdzas yo byad bskyed bstim spog chog sogs kyang gzhung ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:28079: de nas mig dbye ba'i dmigs pa tshigs bcad sngags bcas kyis mig dbye tshul /
NK117(she)001:28080: spyan 'dren nas dal gyi phyogs bzhi nas phyag 'tshal
NK117(she)001:28081: mthar lha ngo bstan pa sogs zhib rgyas 'grel chen
NK117(she)001:28082: du blta bar bya ba nyid do //
NK117(she)001:28083: de yan chad ni 'jug pa'i cho ga ste /
NK117(she)001:28084: de yang me tog dor ba yan phyi 'jug dang /
NK117(she)001:28085: mig dar bsal nas dkyil 'khor bstan pa sogs nang 'jug go //
NK117(she)001:28086: de dag gi spyi don ni thog mar sa gzhi
NK117(she)001:28087: mnyam pa ni chos thams cad mnyam par rtogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:28088: rten 'brel lo // de nas dkyil 'khor che chung
NK117(she)001:28089: gi tshad rig pas dpogs pa ni rjes la thob
NK117(she)001:28090: pa'i shes rab bskyed pa mtshon la /
NK117(she)001:28091: de nas thig gdab pa ni rig pa'i chos nyid dkyil 'khor las gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:28092: tshon dbye ba ni rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28093: de la rnam pa dgod pa ni snang grags rig pa dkyil 'khor gsum du rgyas 'debs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28094: de la rab tu gnas nas bsgrub cing mchod pa
NK117(she)001:28095: ni sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor lhun rdzogs
NK117(she)001:28096: su byed pa'o // skabs de dang der sbyin sreg
NK117(she)001:28097: bya ba ni bde ba chen po'i don rgyud la
NK117(she)001:28098: sbyin zhing rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs bsreg pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28099: de nas dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ni lha dang bskal pa mnyam par bsgrub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28100: de nas slob ma 'jug pa ni dngos grub la nye bar bsnyen pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28101: bzhi pa zhugs pa la dbang bskur ba chos kyi rgyal po'i go 'phang sbyin pa la gnyis /
NK117(she)001:28102: dbang spyi'i rnam par bzhag pa mdor bstan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28103: dbang bzhi'i ngo bo bye brag tu brjod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28106: rgyud sde so so'i dbang gi rigs dbye la //
NK117(she)001:28107: bya ba'i rgyud la chu dang cod pan gnyis //
NK117(she)001:28108: spyod pa'i rgyud la de steng rdo rje ming //
NK117(she)001:28109: rnal 'byor rgyud la rig pa'i dbang lnga dang //
NK117(she)001:28110: gsang ba bka' yi dbang dang mtha' rten rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:28111: bla med bum gsang shes rab tshig dbang bzhi //
NK117(she)001:28112: theg pa'i rtse mo'i rim pa bye brag pa //
NK117(she)001:28113: spros dang spros med shin tu rab spros med //
NK117(she)001:28114: spyir na dbang gi dbye bsdu mtha' yas kyang //
NK117(she)001:28115: sa zin 'jog mtshams rnam pa bzhi po yin //
NK117(she)001:28116: zhes pa ni de yang phyi rgyud gsum dang nang
NK117(she)001:28117: rgyud gsum so so'i dbang gis rigs kyi dbye ba
NK117(she)001:28118: la / bya rgyud la chu dbang dang cod pan tsam dang /
NK117(she)001:28119: gzhan rnams yan lag lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:28120: spyod rgyud ni de'i steng du rdo rje ming dbang
NK117(she)001:28121: bsnan zhing yan lag mang nyung slob dpon so so'i
NK117(she)001:28124: rigs bsdus che chung gang yin kyang rigs dbang lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:28125: gsang dbang dang bka' dbang bcas pa slob ma'i dbang dang /
NK117(she)001:28126: mtha' rten slob dpon gyi dbang la sogs pa yo
NK117(she)001:28127: ga phyi'i dbang bcu dang bcu gsum sogs sbyong rgyud
NK117(she)001:28128: dang rdo rje 'byung ba sogs las shes dgos so
NK117(she)001:28129: // 'di'i gsang dbang ni lha dang dal gyi de
NK117(she)001:28130: kho na nyid dang slob dpon gyi las ston pa
NK117(she)001:28132: rnal 'byor rgyud la lar sher dbang gsungs pa yang ming tsam yin gyis bla med dang mi 'dra'o //
NK117(she)001:28133: des na dbang gong ma gsum ni bla med kho na'i khyad chos yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:28134: de yang gsang 'dus snga 'gyur phyi 'gyur gnyis dang
NK117(she)001:28135: zla gsang thig le sogs nas bum gsang sher ye
NK117(she)001:28137: dus 'khor las byis pa 'jug pa'i dbang bdun dang
NK117(she)001:28138: dbang gong ma la 'jig rten pa gsum dang de
NK117(she)001:28139: las 'das pa gcig ste bcu gcig go //
NK117(she)001:28140: de yang snga 'gyur la'ang slob ma dang dbang rdzas
NK117(she)001:28141: rigs kyi lha so sor bskyed pa ma yin par
NK117(she)001:28142: lhag pa'i lha 'ba' zhig tu dran par bya ba'ang
NK117(she)001:28143: yod do // rdor sems sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK117(she)001:28145: gsang ba byang sems kyi gsum ste bco brgyad do //
NK117(she)001:28146: phan pa'i dbang bcu'i nang du rnal 'byor phyi pa las gsungs pa'i bum pa /
NK117(she)001:28150: phyag rgya dang lnga ni dngos su 'du zhing /
NK117(she)001:28151: gzungs ni nyan pa'i dbang dang /
NK117(she)001:28154: 'khor los bsgyur ba ni rdo rje rgyal po sogs
NK117(she)001:28155: rgyud nas 'du ba kho na yin pas na rgyud
NK117(she)001:28156: sde spyi la grags pa'i rig pa'i dbang lnga po
NK117(she)001:28157: ni rigs bsdus pa'i chings so //
NK117(she)001:28158: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu
NK117(she)001:28159: ni dad ldan snod rung la ster ba yin la
NK117(she)001:28160: / nang nus pa'i dbang lnga ni brtson 'grus can la sbyin pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28161: de yang bdag don la brtson pa can la nyan sgom gnyis /
NK117(she)001:28162: gzhan don la brtson pa can la 'chad 'phrin gnyis /
NK117(she)001:28163: gnyis ka'i don du rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang sbyin no //
NK117(she)001:28164: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum ni brtul zhugs can la ster dgos te /
NK117(she)001:28165: de yang spyod pa'i brtul zhugs can la gsang dbang /
NK117(she)001:28166: rig pa'i brtul zhugs can la sher ye /
NK117(she)001:28167: mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can la dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang ster ro //
NK117(she)001:28168: 'di ltar sangs rgyas rnams ni 'gro phan kho na'i
NK117(she)001:28169: ched yin na theg chen gyi chos lam na skal
NK117(she)001:28170: med yal bar 'dor dgos pa ma bshad phyir snying
NK117(she)001:28171: rjes gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams pa'i bcud ma blugs
NK117(she)001:28172: na seng+ge'i 'o ma snod ngan gyis mi thub pa
NK117(she)001:28173: ltar snod bcud ma brtags na mi rung bar gsungs
NK117(she)001:28174: so // khyad par sems phyogs la byin dbang rgyun
NK117(she)001:28175: chad med pa chu rgyun lta bu'i rgyud rdzogs pa
NK117(she)001:28176: rang byung gi spros bcas spyi'i dbang rnam par bzhag
NK117(she)001:28177: so // pa dang / bye brag dang /
NK117(she)001:28178: gsum pa'i don 'bras ngos bzung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:28179: dang po khrus dbang nas rin po che'i 'khor lo'i bar du'o //
NK117(she)001:28180: gnyis pa phyi nang gsang gsum dang yongs su rdzogs
NK117(she)001:28181: pa bzhin rim dgu'i theg pa'i dbang ston pa yang
NK117(she)001:28182: so so'i sgos chos nas 'dra mthun btus pa ma
NK117(she)001:28183: yin mod kyi / sngags lam thabs mang ltar so
NK117(she)001:28184: so'i rigs 'dra'i yon tan mngon sum du skye ba'i
NK117(she)001:28186: nyan thos kyi skra bregs pa /
NK117(she)001:28187: stod smad kyi g.yogs dang chos gos dang /
NK117(she)001:28188: dge tshul slong gi sdom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28190: lhung bzed sbyin pa sogs ni phyi'o //
NK117(she)001:28191: nang rang rgyal dang gsang ba byang sems te rgyu'i
NK117(she)001:28192: theg pa gsum gyi dbang rdzogs pas rgyu byang chub
NK117(she)001:28193: kyi sems brtan / rkyen kun rdzob byang sems las su rung /
NK117(she)001:28194: chos kyi bya ba'i rgyu'i sa bon rnams la dbang bas na dbang zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28195: de nas sngags phyi pa'i theg pa gsum gyi dbang
NK117(she)001:28196: rdzogs par byas pas lam byang chub kyi sems la
NK117(she)001:28197: dbang zhing / de'ang chu cod pan /
NK117(she)001:28198: rdor dril gyi dbang bskur bas 'bras bu byang chub kyi sems la dbang bas na dbang zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28199: sngags nang pa gsum las phyi bskyed pa ma h+aa
NK117(she)001:28200: yo ga'i dus su bum dbang yan lag dang bcas
NK117(she)001:28201: pa byas pas phan pa dang nus pa'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:28203: nang lung a nu'i dus nang dang gsang ba'i sgra don gyis /
NK117(she)001:28204: sbas pa rig ma'i dbang gis kun rdzob byang sems
NK117(she)001:28205: la longs spyod cing zhu bde'i ye shes la dbang
NK117(she)001:28207: gsang ba rdzogs pa chen po'i spros bcas kyi dbang gi dus na ni /
NK117(she)001:28208: phyi bum pa la brten pa rma bya dang me
NK117(she)001:28209: long sogs khyad par gyi rdzas bdun gyis srid pa
NK117(she)001:28210: bdun gyi rgyun 'gags par byed do //
NK117(she)001:28211: nang bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad dang sna bdun la brten nas gnas skabs su 'dod yon dang /
NK117(she)001:28212: mthar thug sems dang ye shes la dbang bas so //
NK117(she)001:28213: spros med gsang ba la brten nas bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:28214: b+han+d+ha dang dbang chen gyi sku sogs mchog gi rdzas
NK117(she)001:28215: bdun sbyin pas nang srid pa'i 'khor lo bdun rgyun
NK117(she)001:28216: 'chad do // spros bcas kyi spros med sher ye
NK117(she)001:28217: rig ma la brten pa'i tshe sin+du ra dang me
NK117(she)001:28218: long yu ba can la sogs snying rje'i rdzas bdun
NK117(she)001:28219: la brten nas gsang gnas sogs gnas gsum du bskur
NK117(she)001:28220: bas gsang ba sems 'jug pa'i las bdun rgyun chad
NK117(she)001:28221: 'chad do // / rdo rje gsum dang gnyis med kyi ye shes la brtan pa thob /
NK117(she)001:28222: de yang gsang sher gnyis rgyu 'bras su bstan nas gsum par bzhag go //
NK117(she)001:28223: spros bcas kyi yongs rdzogs byang sems kyi dal la
NK117(she)001:28224: brten nas spangs rtogs sogs te dmigs med kyi rdzas
NK117(she)001:28225: bdun la brten nas bskur bas khams gsum du 'jug
NK117(she)001:28226: pa'i sbyor ba bdun rgyun chad do //
NK117(she)001:28227: gsum pa sher dbang ni 'og tu ston pas mtshon no //
NK117(she)001:28228: spros med la phyi nang gsang ba yongs rdzogs bzhi las /
NK117(she)001:28229: phyi man+dala dang bum pa la brten nas sku gsung
NK117(she)001:28230: thugs kyi yi ge 'khor los dag par byed do
NK117(she)001:28231: // nang gi chos rnams skye med sogs bum gnas nges pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28232: gsang ba ni dngos rnams shar grol ris med chen por mtshon pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28233: yongs su rdzogs pa'i chos rnams bdag med sogs ni tshig dbang ngo //
NK117(she)001:28234: shin tu spros med kyi dbang la yang phyi 'khor 'das ru shan dbye ba /
NK117(she)001:28235: nang ye shes nyer lnga la spyod don du man+dala phul nas gsol ba gdab pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:28236: gsang ba ni phyogs bzhi'i mkha' nas sems nyid kyi sgor 'jug go //
NK117(she)001:28237: yongs rdzogs ni nam mkha' rgya che ba'i sgras sems la mtha' dbus med par bstan to //
NK117(she)001:28238: rab tu spros med ni phyi 'dug stangs nang lta
NK117(she)001:28239: stangs gsang ba de gnyis bstun nas sangs rgyas kyi
NK117(she)001:28241: yongs rdzogs ni song zhig sogs kyi brda don spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28242: de dag gi dag bya dag 'bras sogs rgyas 'grel las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28243: de dag gi tshul ni bla ma'i zhal las byung
NK117(she)001:28244: ba'i dbang ni dbang chog sgra ji bzhin par ltos
NK117(she)001:28245: pa dag dang / yi dam gyi byin rlabs la
NK117(she)001:28246: brten pa'i dbang ni rgyal po dza'i khang thog tu
NK117(she)001:28247: po ti'i char babs pa lta bu'o //
NK117(she)001:28248: rdo rje mkha' 'gros lung bstan pa'i dbang ni klu
NK117(she)001:28249: sgrub dang 'gro bzang gis o rgyan d+har+m+aa gany+dzo nas
NK117(she)001:28250: brtag gnyis dang ma h+aa ma ya brkus nas bros
NK117(she)001:28251: par mkha' 'gro mas rjes bsnyegs te zin tshe chos
NK117(she)001:28252: de'i bdag po gyis la shod cig byas pas thob
NK117(she)001:28253: pa lta bu'o // rang gi sems kyi rtsal gyis
NK117(she)001:28254: thob pa ni chos nyid kyi lta bas thob pa
NK117(she)001:28255: rig pa'i dbang ste de la brten nas slob mar
NK117(she)001:28256: dngos grub thob pa ni dbang 'bras so //
NK117(she)001:28257: 'di dag ni jo bo'i dam tshig bsdus pa las bstan to //
NK117(she)001:28258: de ltar rgyud sde so so'i rang lugs kyi dbang
NK117(she)001:28259: gi dbye bsdu mtha' gcig tu ma nges shing gdul
NK117(she)001:28260: bya'i khams dang bsam pa dbang po /
NK117(she)001:28262: nyon mongs sogs kyi gnyen por gsungs pa rnams kyang dbang bzhir ma 'dus pa med la /
NK117(she)001:28263: 'di ltar phyi nam zla dus bzhi /
NK117(she)001:28264: nang sgo gsum dang cha mnyam dang bzhi /
NK117(she)001:28265: don dam par skye ba dang /
NK117(she)001:28267: yod med rtag chad mu bzhi sbyor phyir bum gsang
NK117(she)001:28268: sher ye tshig dbang rin po che ste bzhis dag
NK117(she)001:28269: par sbyangs shing tshogs sbyor mthong bsgom bzhi bgrod nas
NK117(she)001:28270: sku bzhi thob par bya phyir gong nas gong du
NK117(she)001:28271: lha khyad zhugs pa'i dbang bzhi byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:28272: de yang phar phyin du rten de nyid la mthong
NK117(she)001:28273: spangs spong bzhin dang mthong lam skye rung la smin
NK117(she)001:28274: pa'i tshad du bzhag pa bzhin sngags lam du bar
NK117(she)001:28275: chad med pa'i dbang du byas nas tshe 'di nyid
NK117(she)001:28276: la spang thob gnyis la rang dbang bsgyur phyir rgyud
NK117(she)001:28277: smin pa'i tshad du bzhag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28279: gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu dbang bzhi ru //
NK117(she)001:28280: gdod nas grub pa rtsa rlung thig le'i rten //
NK117(she)001:28281: rang chas nyid de mtshungs par ldan pa dang //
NK117(she)001:28282: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni rnam gnyis las //
NK117(she)001:28283: snod du rung ba'i slob bu rgyu yi rkyen //
NK117(she)001:28284: lta dgongs ldan pa'i slob dpon bdag po'i rkyen //
NK117(she)001:28285: nus pa'i cho ga mkhyen pa dmigs pa'i rkyen //
NK117(she)001:28286: rten cing 'brel 'byung de ma thag pa'i rkyen //
NK117(she)001:28287: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi tshogs las dbang bskur 'grub //
NK117(she)001:28288: ces pa ni de la sngags kyi theg pa bla
NK117(she)001:28289: na med pa ni gzhi rang bzhin lhun grub kyi
NK117(she)001:28290: dal du phung khams skye mched kyi rten brten pa'i
NK117(she)001:28291: rang bzhin du rdzogs par rang la yod pa gang
NK117(she)001:28292: zhig dbang gi lam du thabs la brten nas smin
NK117(she)001:28293: rung du byas nas bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug pas
NK117(she)001:28294: 'bras bu rnal 'byor rang gi sa thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28295: de la dbang gi rten ni yid kyi lus can
NK117(she)001:28296: gzugs med dang 'dod sred rags pa bcom pa'i bsam
NK117(she)001:28297: gtan bzhi / khams gcig nas lnga'i bar las mi
NK117(she)001:28298: ldan pa'i gnas rigs nyi shu rnams dbang bskur yul
NK117(she)001:28299: gtan bzhi / ma yin zhing / dbang bskur yul
NK117(she)001:28300: gyi rten ni khams drug dag ldan gyi rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:28301: lus rtsa rlung thig le'i rkyen ldan mi lus kho
NK117(she)001:28302: gtan bzhi / ma yin zhing / na'o // de
NK117(she)001:28303: yang dam pa'i rigs can lngar gtogs pa dang nyan
NK117(she)001:28304: rang dgra bcom lhag med pa 'ga' zhig yid lus
NK117(she)001:28305: kyis sngags la 'jug pa ni bems po'i khyad par
NK117(she)001:28306: can yin pas ma nges so //
NK117(she)001:28307: lha dang lha min sgra mi snyan gsum ni 'bras
NK117(she)001:28308: bur spyod pas rgyud dman la gling gsum du skyes
NK117(she)001:28309: pa'i khams drug ldan ni khyad par ba dang /
NK117(she)001:28310: de las kyang 'dzam bu'i gling pa ni las kyi sa par grags pas mchog yin no //
NK117(she)001:28311: de yang bde gshegs snying po ni mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu yin te /
NK117(she)001:28312: de med na bsgrub mi nus so //
NK117(she)001:28313: des na slob ma'i rgyud kyi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu
NK117(she)001:28314: thabs la brten nas 'bras bur 'byin pa rdo rje
NK117(she)001:28315: slob dpon gyi rtog tshogs su snang ba kun rdzob
NK117(she)001:28316: kyi bden par dag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis slob
NK117(she)001:28317: ma'i rgyud dag par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28318: de yang dbang bskur bya'i slob ma snod du rung ba rgyu'i rkyen yin te /
NK117(she)001:28319: 'di ltar dngos grub thob byed kyi gtso bo ni
NK117(she)001:28320: dad dam gnyis yin zhing de ltar mi ldan na
NK117(she)001:28322: skur byed slob dpon yang bdag dang /
NK117(she)001:28326: 'phro 'du rnams kyi de kho na nyid de sngags
NK117(she)001:28327: kyi yan lag lnga'i sbyor ba la mkhas pa bdag
NK117(she)001:28328: po'i rkyen / dngos grub thob cing mkhas pa'i bla
NK117(she)001:28329: ma rnams kyi man ngag ji lta ba'i dbang chog
NK117(she)001:28330: ma nor ba shes pa dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK117(she)001:28331: bum dbang sogs snga ma snga mas phyi ma phyi
NK117(she)001:28332: ma'i go phye nas rtogs pa dang shes rab gnyis
NK117(she)001:28333: po'i mthu byin gyis slob mar phan 'dogs shing dbang
NK117(she)001:28334: so so'i go brda 'phrod par byed pa de ma
NK117(she)001:28336: de lta'i rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi 'tshogs pa la
NK117(she)001:28337: brten nas dngos grub thob rung gi nus pa rgyud
NK117(she)001:28338: la smin na lam 'bras kyi chos rnams kun gyi
NK117(she)001:28339: yon tan bskyed nas rtogs pa'i dbang mchog thob par
NK117(she)001:28340: nges so // de'ang gsang ba sgyu 'phrul ba'i lugs
NK117(she)001:28341: kyi phan nus kyi dbang bco lnga dang gsang dbang
NK117(she)001:28342: gsum rlung sems rtsa dang thig le'i rang bzhin dang
NK117(she)001:28343: dag bya dag byed du sbyar ba'i tshul /
NK117(she)001:28345: gnyen po drang nges sgo nas bzhag pa ni //
NK117(she)001:28346: lus kyi gtso bor gyur pa rtsa yin te //
NK117(she)001:28347: rtsa yi rnam pa yi ge'i gzugs su gnas //
NK117(she)001:28348: de la rlung brten rlung la khams rnams brten //
NK117(she)001:28349: khams la don dam byang chub sems brten bzhi //
NK117(she)001:28350: zhes pa ni spyir 'gro rnams rang rang gi las
NK117(she)001:28351: dang 'khrul pa'i dbang gis rigs drug tu 'khor ba
NK117(she)001:28352: las / mtho ris kyi rten khams drug ldan rnams
NK117(she)001:28353: ni mngal gnas 'dzin pa'i thog mar mig gnyis dang
NK117(she)001:28355: de las lus yongs bskyed pas na gnas pa rtsa ni /
NK117(she)001:28356: lus kyi dag bya'i gtso bo yin pas de'i gnyen por sku rdo rje bum pa'i dbang /
NK117(she)001:28357: der g.yo byed kyi rlung brten nas byed las sna
NK117(she)001:28358: tshogs su shar ba ni ngag gi dag bya'i gtso
NK117(she)001:28359: bo de'i gnyen por gsung rdo rje gsang ba'i dbang
NK117(she)001:28360: / de la bkod pa byang sems kyi khams dwangs
NK117(she)001:28361: ma chen po brten pas rtsa yur ba lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:28362: nang du khams rags pa chu rgyun 'dra ba de
NK117(she)001:28363: rlung gis bskyod nas 'gro 'ong du gnas pa de'i
NK117(she)001:28364: gnyen por thig le bde ba chen por dag cing
NK117(she)001:28365: smin pa thugs rdo rje sher ye'i dbang ngo //
NK117(she)001:28366: de dang rjes mthun don dam byang sems kyang rlung
NK117(she)001:28367: gi chas khur nas skyon yod sna tshogs bskyed pa
NK117(she)001:28368: ni yid kyi dag bya yin no //
NK117(she)001:28369: de'i gnyen por ye shes rdo rje'i dbang bzhi pas
NK117(she)001:28370: sems dag cing smin par byed pas dbang bzhir byung
NK117(she)001:28371: ba'o // de la sngags ni 'dod yon gyi lam
NK117(she)001:28372: yin pas gnas rigs so so'i 'dod yon rnam bzhi'i
NK117(she)001:28373: dag byed kyi ngos nas dbang bzhir nges pa la
NK117(she)001:28374: dang po bum dbang ston pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:28376: 'dod pa'i khams kyi gang zag rang rgyud pa //
NK117(she)001:28377: kun la 'dod chags rnam bzhir gnas pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:28378: dag bya dag byed la brten nges pa yang //
NK117(she)001:28379: dang po bltas pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags ni //
NK117(she)001:28380: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed pa la gnas pa ste //
NK117(she)001:28381: rdul tshon dkyil 'khor la brten bum pa'i dbang //
NK117(she)001:28382: bskur bas gtso bor lus kyi sgrib pa dag /
NK117(she)001:28383: snod bcud brtan g.yo phung khams skye mched kun //
NK117(she)001:28384: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor gcig tu shar //
NK117(she)001:28385: snang stong zung 'jug ngo bo nyid gsum gyi //
NK117(she)001:28386: grub mtha' 'khor 'das gnyis med chen po la //
NK117(she)001:28387: 'da' ka 'od kyi gong bu sgra yis 'pho //
NK117(she)001:28388: rtsa yi 'gros thim bskyed rim sprul pa'i sku //
NK117(she)001:28389: mkha' khyab sku yi rdo rje 'dus ma byas //
NK117(she)001:28390: zhes pa de yang gzhan 'phrul dbang byed rnams ni
NK117(she)001:28391: gcig la gcig pa'i 'dod chags kyis gdung bar byed
NK117(she)001:28392: pa dag byed bum dbang gzugs brnyan thabs kyi dal
NK117(she)001:28393: rdul tshon nam chu tshon gyi dal du brten nas
NK117(she)001:28394: bskur ba'o // de yang sngon goms kyi skal ba
NK117(she)001:28395: can kha cig la lus dkyil yang mchog tu basngagasa
NK117(she)001:28396: te bum dbang phyag rgya'i lus dang bum pa de'i
NK117(she)001:28397: nu ma la dus 'khor nas bstan pa ltar ro
NK117(she)001:28398: bskur ba'o // // 'on kyang gang zag gi bye
NK117(she)001:28399: brag la ltos nas 'jug tshul sna tshogs yod kyang
NK117(she)001:28400: snyigs dus 'dir 'phags pa'i rgyud ldan gyi bla ma
NK117(she)001:28401: bskur ba'o // // dang / slob ma las sad
NK117(she)001:28402: gcig car ba dkon na tshon dkyil gnyis la blo
NK117(she)001:28403: bskur ba'o // // dang / khel bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28404: bskur tshul ni man+dala dbul ba sogs sngon 'gro rnams
NK117(she)001:28405: dbang gzhung so so'i lugs ltar dang /
NK117(she)001:28407: sdig pa sbyang ba sogs rab gnas bzhin byed pa'ang yod la /
NK117(she)001:28408: gsol ba gdab tshul khyab che ba ni /
NK117(she)001:28409: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK117(she)001:28411: tshig dang po rdo rje 'chang ste des mi bskyod
NK117(she)001:28412: pa sogs la tshig gnyis pa mchod pa chen po
NK117(she)001:28413: dbang gi bya ba ji ltar bstsal ba ltar du
NK117(she)001:28414: / tshig gsum pa bdag kyang 'khor ba las yongs
NK117(she)001:28415: su bsgral ba'i phyir tshig bzhi pa slob dpon rdo
NK117(she)001:28416: rje 'chang dang dbyer med pa la bos nas deng
NK117(she)001:28417: bdag la dbang bskur ba da lta nyid du stsol
NK117(she)001:28418: / zhes pa'o // de nas dal gyi shar phyogs
NK117(she)001:28419: su khrus dkyil sna tshogs pad+mas mtshan pa'am sgo mu
NK117(she)001:28420: khyud gcig pa nub bstan 'dab brgyad can phyogs bzhir
NK117(she)001:28421: rigs lnga dang mtshams bzhir yum bzhi'i mtshan ma tshon
NK117(she)001:28422: nam 'bras phye'i khu bas bris steng 'dab brgyad dam
NK117(she)001:28423: zla dkyil bris pas bkab par slob ma bzhag gam
NK117(she)001:28426: sku rdo rje sprul sku ngo bo bla ma dang
NK117(she)001:28427: dbyer med pa'i dal gyi lhas bum dbang bskur ba'i
NK117(she)001:28428: dgongs pa gtad nas thugs ka sogs nas rigs lnga
NK117(she)001:28429: so so'i ngo bo nyid kyi dbang rdzas rnams byung
NK117(she)001:28430: bar mos bzhin slob ma lhag lha gang yin du
NK117(she)001:28432: spro na slob ma sngar ltar nang dbang bskur ba'i
NK117(she)001:28433: dmigs pas rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkhar bzhag
NK117(she)001:28434: la dmigs med kyi ngang nas dbang rdzas lhar bskyed
NK117(she)001:28435: nas dbang bskur ba'i ched du slob dpon gyis /
NK117(she)001:28436: rdo rje can gyis sangs rgyas la sogs sho lo
NK117(she)001:28437: ka de 'don pa dang mnyam du snying ga'i 'od
NK117(she)001:28438: kyis phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas gdan gsum tshang
NK117(she)001:28439: ba'i dal gyi rnam par spyan drangs pas dbang gi
NK117(she)001:28440: bya ba byed par mos pa'i lugs kyang yod de
NK117(she)001:28443: gshegs pa lnga dang gshegs ma lnga /
NK117(she)001:28446: dus bzhi rnams gnas su dag pa'i bsdoms pa'i byang
NK117(she)001:28447: sems stangs dpyal brgyad gnyis ni skye mched sems dpa'
NK117(she)001:28448: sems ma'i gdan / yan lag bzhi ni lus kyi rnam shes dang /
NK117(she)001:28451: reg shes bzhi dag pa sgo ba bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:28452: yan lag khro bo khro mo'i gdan sogs zhes pa
NK117(she)001:28453: ni rgyu dus kyi phung khams skye mched yan lag
NK117(she)001:28454: dang bcas pa 'bras bu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du
NK117(she)001:28455: snang ba lha sum cu so bzhi ste /
NK117(she)001:28456: de yang gshegs pa lngas dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa mdzad /
NK117(she)001:28457: gshegs ma lngas bum pa yo bar bzung ste dbang bskur gyi las la bzhengs /
NK117(she)001:28458: sems dpa' stangs dpyal bcu drug gis bkra shis gang
NK117(she)001:28459: zhig sogs kyis me tog 'thor bzhin shis pa brjod
NK117(she)001:28460: / sgo srung pho mo brgyad kyis bgegs bskrad par
NK117(she)001:28461: mos shing dbang gi gsham du lha rnams slob mar
NK117(she)001:28462: / bstim mo // gzhan yang dbang lha gsar du
NK117(she)001:28463: spyan drangs kyang mtha' gcig tu gdan gsum tshang ba
NK117(she)001:28464: kho nar ma nges pa yod de /
NK117(she)001:28465: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las til gyi gang bu bzhin gang sogs gsungs pas so //
NK117(she)001:28466: de la dbang bskur rdo rje chen po ste zhes tshig rkang bzhi'i don ni /
NK117(she)001:28467: rim bzhin dang po ni 'dor du mi rung zhing
NK117(she)001:28468: gzhom gzhig bral ba dang chen po ste de'i bla
NK117(she)001:28469: na gzhan med pa'i phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:28470: khyad par chen po sgras khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa'i rgyal por gyur pas so //
NK117(she)001:28471: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs kyi gsang gsum
NK117(she)001:28472: gyi yon tan gang yin pa'i gnas las byung ba'i
NK117(she)001:28473: smin byed kyi thabs zab mo 'di ni deng khyod
NK117(she)001:28476: tshig 'di ni rig dbang lnga ka'i mgor sbyar ba'ang yod de /
NK117(she)001:28477: de'ang dbang lha gsar du spyan drangs pa las thob
NK117(she)001:28478: pa yin na rdul tshon gyi dal las dbang thob
NK117(she)001:28480: de dang dbyer med pa'i bla mas dbang bskur ba'i dgongs pa gtad pas thob dgos pa ste /
NK117(she)001:28481: dper na ston pa ting nge 'dzin la bzhugs te
NK117(she)001:28482: dgongs pa gtad pa'i mthus spyan ras gzigs dang shwa
NK117(she)001:28483: ri'i bu gnyis dri ba dang lan ldon tshul gyis
NK117(she)001:28484: sher snying byung ba ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:28485: des na chos thams cad rgyal ba'i dgongs rgyud gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28486: don de'i phyir na ma rig pa lnga yongs su gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28487: rig pa'i chos nyid rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid du sad par byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28488: de'ang chu dbang gis dri ma 'khrud pa /
NK117(she)001:28490: rdor dril gtod pa ming gdags pa lnga po ni skyed byed 'grub pa'i rgyu yin la /
NK117(she)001:28491: dbang gi ngo bo ni chu dbang la mtshon na
NK117(she)001:28492: slob ma dang dbang rdzas gnyis ka mi bskyod par
NK117(she)001:28493: gsal bzhin bum chus gtor blud byas pas de'i rgyud
NK117(she)001:28494: kyi rnam shes kyi phung po dang zhe sdang sbyong
NK117(she)001:28495: zhing me long ye shes mngon du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28496: de'i 'gres kyis dbang rdzas dang slob ma rigs bzhir
NK117(she)001:28497: bskyed cing dbang rdzas bzhi gtad pas bskur yul de'i
NK117(she)001:28498: rgyud kyi phung po dang nyon mongs pa sbyong zhing
NK117(she)001:28499: ye shes mngon du byed pa sogs bsgyur kha shes
NK117(she)001:28500: par bya ba'o // dmigs bsal ni me tog gang
NK117(she)001:28501: la phog pa'i lhar bskyed nas rang gi lha zhu
NK117(she)001:28502: ba'i bum chu spyi bor gtor zhing phyi nang gi
NK117(she)001:28503: dri ma 'khrud par byas pas de'i rgyud kyi dag
NK117(she)001:28504: bya dag 'bras kyang lha de dang de'i rigs dang
NK117(she)001:28505: ye shes la sbyor tshul gong ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:28506: de'ang de bzhin gshegs pa la phog na rin chen gyi cod pan nam dbu rgyan /
NK117(she)001:28507: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdo rje dang /
NK117(she)001:28508: dril bu dang ming de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la de lnga'i cod pan /
NK117(she)001:28510: des mtshon pa'i dril bu dang ming /
NK117(she)001:28511: rdo rje'i rigs la sangs rgyas lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:28515: pad+ma'i rigs la 'od dpag med dang pad+ma'i phreng ba'i cod pan /
NK117(she)001:28516: rdo rje pad+ma dang dril bu dang ming /
NK117(she)001:28517: nor bu'i rigs la rin chen myu gu'i cod pan dang ming /
NK117(she)001:28518: rdo rje rin chen dang dril bu dang ming /
NK117(she)001:28519: las kyi rigs la sna tshogs rdo rje cod pan dang /
NK117(she)001:28520: sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu dang ming gis dbang bskur /
NK117(she)001:28521: de'ang ming dbang ni me tog phog pa'i ming gi mgor /
NK117(she)001:28523: zhes bde ba'i sgra dang dpal dang rdo rje'i mgo can du gdags shing /
NK117(she)001:28524: rdor dril mgo thog tu bzung nas lan gsum brjod pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:28525: de ltar rig dbang lnga thob pas rigs su skyes
NK117(she)001:28526: pa'i phyir rigs kyi bya ba las mi 'gong zhing
NK117(she)001:28527: de'i yan lag gi dam tshig drang nges gnyis las
NK117(she)001:28529: khyod kyis srog chags gsad mi byed //
NK117(she)001:28530: ces pa la sogs bslab pa'i gzhi lnga la bslab pa bla med dang thun mong yin no //
NK117(she)001:28531: dbang bar byed pa'i cha nas phung po lnga dang
NK117(she)001:28532: 'byung ba lnga gnas 'gyur thob pa'i 'bras bu de
NK117(she)001:28533: bzhin gshegs pa lnga'i spangs rtogs kyi rang bzhin la
NK117(she)001:28534: sbyor ba'o // de lta na'ang mthar gyi ni go
NK117(she)001:28535: ba de tsam gyis nyon mongs dang ma rig pa'i
NK117(she)001:28536: cha bzlog mi nus te gnyis su snang ba ma
NK117(she)001:28538: 'di ltar chu dbang la mtshon na sbyang gzhi'i rnam shes dang /
NK117(she)001:28539: zhe sdang glo bur bas bslad pa'i blo'i 'dzin stangs
NK117(she)001:28540: kyis bzung ba las yul thog tu ye nas grub
NK117(she)001:28541: ma myong ste / 'khor ba ni 'khrul snang gis bskyed pa /
NK117(she)001:28543: tho yor mir bzung ba ltar rnam shes kyi phung
NK117(she)001:28544: po yang mtshan nyid kyis ma grub bzhin du grub
NK117(she)001:28545: pa ltar snang ba'i chos nyid kyi mtshang rig pa
NK117(she)001:28546: ni rgyal ba ma bskyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28547: zhe sdang yang 'khrul pas btags pa las don la
NK117(she)001:28548: grub pa med pa ni rnam kun mchog ldan gyi
NK117(she)001:28549: mkhyen cha tsam du ji snyed pa'i chos ston pa
NK117(she)001:28550: me long lta bu'i ye shes zhes rnam grangs pa'i
NK117(she)001:28551: don dam gyis btags pa'i sbyang gzhi sbyong byed yin
NK117(she)001:28552: te / don la chos rnams ngo bo nyid med
NK117(she)001:28553: pa'am rab tu mi gnas par grub pas sbyang gzhi
NK117(she)001:28554: sbyangs 'bras gnyis kar bzhag tu med kyang /
NK117(she)001:28555: re zhig byis pa rnams skrag pa spang phyir rigs
NK117(she)001:28556: lnga dang ye shes lnga'i rnam par bzhag pa tsam
NK117(she)001:28557: las blo ngos nas gzhal yul las 'das pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28558: 'di ltar ma shes na sngags lam ni drang don
NK117(she)001:28559: gyi kha drang ba tsam ma yin par rgya che
NK117(she)001:28560: ba'i rang bzhin du bshad pa'ang de kho na nyid
NK117(she)001:28561: 'ba' zhig tu 'bab cing de'i lam gyi lus yongs
NK117(she)001:28562: rdzogs dbang gi rang bzhin la rdzogs pa mi shes
NK117(she)001:28563: so // de ltar rig dbang lnga'i steng du brtul zhugs kyi dbang lung bstan dang /
NK117(she)001:28564: dbugs dbyung dang rjes gnang dang bcas slob ma'i dbang drug go //
NK117(she)001:28565: thabs de las byung ba'i rdo rje slob dpon gyi
NK117(she)001:28566: dbang ni de ltar du thob pa gang zhig sngar
NK117(she)001:28567: lhag gnas kyi skabs slob dpon gyi sdom pa byin
NK117(she)001:28569: min na skabs 'dir gzhan don la rjes su gnang
NK117(she)001:28570: ba'i mthu bskyed phyir bum dbang gtso bor bya ba
NK117(she)001:28571: dang / dam tshig gsum 'dzin pa gtso bor bya
NK117(she)001:28572: ba gnyis las phyi ma 'di 'thad kyi phyir mi
NK117(she)001:28573: ldog pa'i dbang zhes pa'i phyir /
NK117(she)001:28574: mdo lam du ma nges pa'i rigs can yang sbyor
NK117(she)001:28575: lam thob pa na phyir mi ldog par bshad pa
NK117(she)001:28576: bzhin no // de yang thugs kyi dam tshig rdo rje gsor ba dang /
NK117(she)001:28578: gnyis kas 'khyud rgya bya ba ste de gsum las
NK117(she)001:28579: byung ba'i bde stong gi ting 'dzin gyi khyad par
NK117(she)001:28580: rig dbang lnga lta bu'i rigs nyi tshe ba'i 'khyud
NK117(she)001:28581: rgya'i bde ba tsam ma yin par rigs kun gyi
NK117(she)001:28582: khyab byed rdo rje 'chang yab yum sbyor ba'i bde
NK117(she)001:28583: stong gi ye shes la yab kyis blta ba dang
NK117(she)001:28584: yum gyis dgod pa'i sgo nas sems gtad pa ni
NK117(she)001:28585: / bla med kyi bskur tshul te dbang stegs la
NK117(she)001:28586: bzhag nas lha lus la bkod de dam tshig gsum
NK117(she)001:28587: / bzung ba / dbang lha spyan drangs nas bum
NK117(she)001:28588: chus dbang bskur rjes dbang lha bstims nas rigs bdag
NK117(she)001:28589: gi rgyas 'debs byas la mchod pas zhal bsro /
NK117(she)001:28590: lha dang dal dang slob dpon gyi de kho na nyid bstan /
NK117(she)001:28592: ming dbang bskur nas mig thur dang me long sogs
NK117(she)001:28593: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i rjes
NK117(she)001:28594: gnang / chos 'khor bskor ba'i rjes su gnang ba sogs ni yan lag yin no //
NK117(she)001:28595: de yang thugs kyi rang bzhin brjod pa don gyi e wam dang /
NK117(she)001:28596: dril bu'i sgra las thams cad mkhyen pa'i brjod pa rdzogs pa sgra'i e wam /
NK117(she)001:28597: kha sbyor gzugs kyi e wam gyi rang bzhin rtogs
NK117(she)001:28598: na dam tshig gsum sgra ji bzhin par gyur nas
NK117(she)001:28599: bum dbang la dbang bzhi'i gnad rdzogs par song bas
NK117(she)001:28600: / rab gnas kyi lha la ye shes pa gzhug
NK117(she)001:28601: pa dang dbang chog gis gzhan rjes su 'dzin pa
NK117(she)001:28602: / dang / rgyud bshad pa tshogs kyi dpon du
NK117(she)001:28603: 'gyur ba slob ma bsdu ba sogs la dbang ba'o
NK117(she)001:28604: / dang / // 'chad tshul de'i dbang gong ma
NK117(she)001:28605: gsum ma thob par bla med kyi nyan bshad dang
NK117(she)001:28606: bskyed rdzogs zab mo bsgom par mi dbang bar 'dod
NK117(she)001:28607: pa ni dpyad bzod pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:28608: de lta bu'i bum dbang ni ri mo dang lus dkyil gnyis su 'thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28609: phan yon ni lus kyi sgrib tshogs 'dag cing phung po'i bdud bcom pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28610: las gang la dbang na bskyed rim gyi snod du
NK117(she)001:28611: rung zhing phung khams skye mched rang rgyud du 'dzin
NK117(she)001:28612: pa las grol / chos can kun rdzob pa las dben par byed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28613: sbyin sreg sogs phrin las kyi yan lag la dbang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:28614: de'ang rang yul phung khams skye mched dang bcas gdan
NK117(she)001:28615: gsum dang der 'phros rdo rje dbyings kyi lha lnga
NK117(she)001:28616: bcu / dam pa rigs brgya sogs dag bya dag
NK117(she)001:28617: 'bras kyi lha'i 'khor lo dbyings kyi lam du bsgoms
NK117(she)001:28618: pas gzugs thams cad snang stong /
NK117(she)001:28620: sems rig stong zung 'jug tu shar ba de la
NK117(she)001:28621: gsal ba'i cha nas snang phyogs kyi ngo bo bskyed
NK117(she)001:28622: pa dang / rang bzhin med pa'i cha nas stong phyogs kyi ngo bo rdzogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28623: lhun grub kyi cha nas bskyed rdzogs dbyer med chen
NK117(she)001:28624: por blta ba ngo bo nyid gsum gyi phyi don
NK117(she)001:28626: dal rang gnas la sgrib pa bsal ba ste /
NK117(she)001:28627: 'dod yon thams cad tha mal du ma gol ba yul snang yum /
NK117(she)001:28628: bza' btung rgyan gos sogs yab tu snang ba zung 'jug tu dang du blang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28629: de ltar bum dbang gis lus rags pa /
NK117(she)001:28630: skyed byed kyi rtsa'i 'gros rnams dag pas shin sbyangs
NK117(she)001:28631: kyi yon tan thob nas rdos bcas la thogs pa
NK117(she)001:28632: med / khams ldog pas chu bo gyen la ldog /
NK117(she)001:28633: rdul dbu mar 'chings pas nyi ma gte bar 'dzin /
NK117(she)001:28635: du ma gcig stong gsum yungs 'brur chud pa ste
NK117(she)001:28636: 'das pa'i sa drug dang grub mtha' 'khor 'das gnyis
NK117(she)001:28638: gal te grub mtha' ma snyogs na snang ba bsgyur ba'i dang /
NK117(she)001:28640: sgras 'pho ba'i 'da' ka gsum gyis 'pho ba'i phyi ma dngos su smos pa ste /
NK117(she)001:28641: 'bras bu sku rdo rje sprul pa'i sku la sbyor ba'o //
NK117(she)001:28642: bum dbang gi dam tshig ni rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:28643: sbom po brgyad bsrung ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:28645: b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor la brten gsang dbang bskur //
NK117(she)001:28646: dgod pas tshim pa 'phrul dag'i 'dod chags dang //
NK117(she)001:28647: ngag gi sgrib sbyangs bdag byin rlobs pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:28648: gtum mos gzung 'dzin ro rkyang dbu mar 'dzud //
NK117(she)001:28649: rang byung ye shes grub mtha' ma 'dres rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:28650: 'da' ka dpe yi 'od gsal chen po'i ngang //
NK117(she)001:28651: yi ge'i 'gros thim longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur //
NK117(she)001:28652: yan lag drug cur rdzogs pa'i gsung rdo rje //
NK117(she)001:28653: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dgod pa'i tshim pa'i 'dod chags ni lha 'phrul dga' ba la yod pas /
NK117(she)001:28654: dag bya de la dag byed gsang dbang ni rig
NK117(she)001:28655: ma'i b+ha ga'i dal la brten nas bskur ba rdor
NK117(she)001:28656: sems sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang dus 'khor zung las
NK117(she)001:28657: gsungs so // de ltar 'thad pa ni dngul chu
NK117(she)001:28658: med par gser 'gyur mi 'grub pa ltar zhu ba
NK117(she)001:28660: bde ba med pa'i zhu ba yang med la kun+d+ha ni rtsa rnams kyis bsdams pa ltar gnas shing /
NK117(she)001:28661: de 'ju thabs ni gzhon nu mar sbyor ba kho na las gzhan med do //
NK117(she)001:28662: de yang slob dpon yab yum gyi lus dkyil gdan
NK117(she)001:28663: gsum lha'i dal du bsgrub cing gsal ba dbang blang
NK117(she)001:28664: ba'i yul yin phyir de'i sbyor dngos rjes kyi rim
NK117(she)001:28665: pa zhib pa rgyas 'grel las shes par bya dgos
NK117(she)001:28666: shing / de lta bu'i gsang dbang gi thabs las
NK117(she)001:28667: byung ba'i kun rdzob byang sems ni gdan gsum lha
NK117(she)001:28668: tshogs zhu ba'i khu ba yin phyir skal med rnams
NK117(she)001:28669: kyi thos su'ang mi rung ngo //
NK117(she)001:28670: dgos ched nang gi 'byung ba rlung khams la 'dres
NK117(she)001:28671: pas chan la phabs kyis thebs pa ltar gsung rdo
NK117(she)001:28672: rje longs sku'i spangs rtogs kyi nus pa khyad par
NK117(she)001:28673: can bzhag pas na dbang zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:28674: de ltar rlung gnad bzhi dang rnal 'byor bzhi sogs
NK117(she)001:28675: myur ba bdun gyi man ngag la brten nas nyams
NK117(she)001:28676: su blangs pas rlung la brten nas rtsa mdud grol
NK117(she)001:28678: 'khrul 'khor gyis rtsa gnas kun tu byang sems kyis khyab pas yi ge'i 'gros thim /
NK117(she)001:28679: lta ba rang byung gi ye shes skye /
NK117(she)001:28680: de yang shes sgrib dang bcas pa'i cha nas ting
NK117(she)001:28681: nge 'dzin nam s+n+rel gzhi sogs rang byung gi bsam
NK117(she)001:28682: gtan bzhi'i rang bzhin du 'chad pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28683: de'i grub mtha' ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa ni
NK117(she)001:28684: sa bdun pa nas bcu pa'i bar la ngag dag
NK117(she)001:28685: pa a k+sha lnga bcu la dbang bas rigs drug
NK117(she)001:28686: gi skad dang brda' 'phrod chos kyang de'i skad du
NK117(she)001:28687: ston / dgu par so so yang dag rig bzhi
NK117(she)001:28688: la dbang bas chos thams cad kyi de nyid rig
NK117(she)001:28689: ston / / gal te grub mtha' ma rnyogs na 'da' ka ma dpe'i 'od gsal ni /
NK117(she)001:28690: 'chi kha'i sdud rim gyis rkyen byas te rlung thams
NK117(she)001:28691: cad dbu mar tshud nas rnam par mi rtog ting
NK117(she)001:28693: gsung rdo rje longs spyod rdzogs pa 'grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28694: gsang dbang gi dam tshig tu sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga brten zhing rig ma mi spang /
NK117(she)001:28696: bla ma mi smod pa rnams yin no //
NK117(she)001:28698: gdan gsum mngon rtogs ngom pa'i mdzes ma yi //
NK117(she)001:28699: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten sher dbang gi //
NK117(she)001:28700: lag bcangs tshim pa dga' ldan 'dod chags dag /
NK117(she)001:28701: yid kyi sgrib sbyang snang mched thob gsum dang //
NK117(she)001:28702: dga' bzhi'i ye shes khams kyi zhu bdes 'grub //
NK117(she)001:28703: grub mtha' bde stong dbyer med nyams su myong //
NK117(she)001:28704: 'da' ka der snang ma grub rdo rje sems //
NK117(she)001:28705: snying ga'i rtsa mdud grol ba dpe'i ye shes //
NK117(she)001:28706: mkha' khyab thugs kyi rdo rje dwangs ma'i sku //
NK117(she)001:28707: zhes pa ni de la lha dga' ldan pa rnams
NK117(she)001:28708: ni lag bcangs 'dod pas gdung bas de'i gnyen por
NK117(she)001:28710: de yang rdo rje'i theg par rig ma'i phung khams
NK117(she)001:28711: skye mched yan lag dang bcas pa gdan gsum lha'i
NK117(she)001:28712: dkyil 'khor yin par gsungs bzhin de nyid mngon sum
NK117(she)001:28713: du nges pa'i mdzes ma yi zhes spyad bya bud
NK117(she)001:28714: med kyi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i sher
NK117(she)001:28715: dbang gis / lag bcangs kyis tshim pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28716: dga' ldan du skye ba'i las dang 'dod chags dag go //
NK117(she)001:28717: yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs shing snang mched thob gsum
NK117(she)001:28718: dang dga' ba mchog dga' khyad dga' dga' bral bzhi'i
NK117(she)001:28719: ye shes khams dkar po zhu ba'i bde bas 'grub
NK117(she)001:28720: cing / grub mtha' bde stong dbyer med du nyams su myong zhing /
NK117(she)001:28721: 'da' ka de dang der snang ba'i gzung 'dzin ma
NK117(she)001:28722: grub pa'i rdo rje ni rang gi sems nyid ye
NK117(she)001:28724: de nyid snying ga'i rtsa mdud grol ba dpe'i ye
NK117(she)001:28725: shes ni rig ma las rnyed pa'i bde stong zung
NK117(she)001:28726: 'jug yin la / de ni nam mkha' khyab pa'i thugs kyi rdo rje ni /
NK117(she)001:28727: dwangs ma ste gzhon nu bum pa'i sku'o //
NK117(she)001:28728: de la lha dga' ldan pa dag lag bcangs kyi
NK117(she)001:28729: 'dod pas gdung bar byed pas de'i gnyen por dbang
NK117(she)001:28731: de yang rig ma'i thabs kyi cho ga sgra ji
NK117(she)001:28732: bzhin pa lam du lhongs shing de nyid rig pa
NK117(she)001:28733: rnams ni sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ma nor ba
NK117(she)001:28734: mngon sum du mthong zhing ston pa'i thabs kyi mthar
NK117(she)001:28735: thug pa 'di las gzhan med do //
NK117(she)001:28736: de yang tshangs spyod kyi rten ldan sogs la sher
NK117(she)001:28737: dbang sgra ji bzhin par bskur du mi rung ba
NK117(she)001:28738: yang / byang chub lam sgron sogs las gsungs mod kyang /
NK117(she)001:28739: de ni rim gnyis kyi de kho na nyid la nang byan ma chud cing /
NK117(she)001:28740: dman lam gyi brtul zhugs la mchog tu 'dzin pas
NK117(she)001:28741: gsang ba dang sher dbang gnyis blangs na ngo tsha
NK117(she)001:28742: khrel yod gnyis nyams so snyam nas 'gyod par 'gyur
NK117(she)001:28743: te / dper na sher phyin nyan pas nyan thos mang po khrag skyugs te shi ba bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:28744: rim gnyis dang mi ldan pa dag ni sngags kyi
NK117(she)001:28745: gzugs brnyan la phas pham pas ngan song du 'gro
NK117(she)001:28746: bas na spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel ba shin
NK117(she)001:28747: tu gal che'o // 'on kyang yid kyis btags pa
NK117(she)001:28748: tsam ni mi 'gog pas tshig tsam gyi dbang bskur
NK117(she)001:28749: bar byang chub sems 'grel las bshad do //
NK117(she)001:28750: yang kha cig lung de gnyis la khungs byas nas
NK117(she)001:28751: dge slong la dmigs bsal gzhan med bzhin du mchog
NK117(she)001:28752: dbang gong ma gtan 'gog pa'ang skyon che ste /
NK117(she)001:28753: de ltar na rab byung gis sngags kyi zab lam
NK117(she)001:28754: bkag pas sdom gsum gnad kyi mi 'gal zhing yar
NK117(she)001:28755: ldan du 'gyur ba las log ste /
NK117(she)001:28756: theg pa che chung dgra gshed ltar 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK117(she)001:28757: dus 'khor las dge slong la yum gyis 'khyud pa'i dbang gsungs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28758: rab byung mchog dbang gi snod khyad 'phags yin pa /
NK117(she)001:28760: dge slong dang dge tshul gnyis kar yum yod par bstan pa ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:28761: de bzhin du dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pa sngags
NK117(she)001:28762: 'chang mchog tu gsungs pa yang bum dbang cha lag
NK117(she)001:28763: bcas thob pa tsam ma yin te /
NK117(she)001:28764: des rgyud sde zab mo nyan bshad /
NK117(she)001:28765: rdzogs rim zab mo sgom pa la mi dbang bar gsungs pa'i don yang ldog par 'gyur zhing /
NK117(she)001:28766: rab byung thams cad sngags lam gyi snod du mi rung bar song bas /
NK117(she)001:28767: slob dpon n+aa gardzu na dang /
NK117(she)001:28770: sangs rgyas ye shes la sogs pa'ang sngags lam nas
NK117(she)001:28771: dngos grub brnyes nas grub brgya'i gral du bzhugs pa'ang
NK117(she)001:28773: de bas na 'du shes gsum dang mi ldan pa la gsang dbang bkag la /
NK117(she)001:28774: de'i steng du 'dzag pa'i gnyen po med pa la sher dbang bkag gis /
NK117(she)001:28775: gal te bzod pa chung ngu thob kyi bar bsring
NK117(she)001:28776: dgos na de'i lam rtags ji bzhin skyes pa deng
NK117(she)001:28777: dus dkon pas rab byung thams cad sngags kyi snod
NK117(she)001:28778: ma yin par 'gyur bas rtsa ltung la rin thang
NK117(she)001:28779: chen po byed pa nyid do //
NK117(she)001:28780: de la gsum pa'i dbang ni yum gyi b+ha ga'i dal du bskur ba yin pas de la'ang /
NK117(she)001:28783: bslab bya'i sgo nas snod ldan du bsgrub pa /
NK117(she)001:28784: slob mar gtad nas go bar bya ba /
NK117(she)001:28785: rtsa bslang nas sbyor thabs bshad pa dang blta ba
NK117(she)001:28786: bzhi dang sbyar nas dbang don ngos bzung ba dang
NK117(she)001:28787: / 'pho med kyi don la sbyar nas yin tshul ltar ldog cing dgram pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28788: de ltar sher dbang gis sgrib pa gang 'dag na brnab sems 'dag tshul sngar bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:28789: ye shes kyi sgrib pa ste shes sgrib rags pa dang /
NK117(she)001:28790: gnas skabs bzhi las gnyid 'thug gi dang /
NK117(she)001:28791: tshogs drug rags pa 'gags pa'i rnam rtog yin pas yid kyi thig le dang /
NK117(she)001:28792: 'chi bdag gi bdud sogs nyes pa'i tshogs 'joms pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28793: de'i grub mtha' ni bde stong dbyer med du rtogs
NK117(she)001:28794: pas sa bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:28795: skabs dang skal ba mnyam zhing /
NK117(she)001:28796: grub mtha' ma snyogs na 'da' ka'i tshe sdud rim gyis rtsa mdud dral bas /
NK117(she)001:28797: don dam byang chub sems kyi rten khams kyi thig
NK117(she)001:28798: le kun rdzob pa rnams lhan cig tu tshogs shing
NK117(she)001:28799: / dbu mar cung zad zhugs pas der snang ma
NK117(she)001:28800: grub pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' mthong bar 'gyur te
NK117(she)001:28801: / / de la rdo rje ni stong pa /
NK117(she)001:28802: sems dpa' ni bde ba ste rdo rje lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:28803: ting 'dzin gyi bde stong nyams su myong nas bar
NK117(she)001:28804: do med pa mthar thug gi 'bras bu thugs rdo
NK117(she)001:28805: rje chos sku'i rang bzhin 'grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28807: na ri dang bral ba la sher dbang gi sdom pa med cing /
NK117(she)001:28808: brtson pa yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK117(she)001:28809: zhes gsungs pas sngags gzhung gi zab khyad du shes
NK117(she)001:28810: rab kyi rang bzhin mo rigs la bsnyen bkur bya
NK117(she)001:28811: ba sogs gal che tshul gsungs bzhin shes par bya'o
NK117(she)001:28813: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas //
NK117(she)001:28814: gsum pa'i nyams myong tshig gis mtshon pa'i dbang //
NK117(she)001:28815: 'thab bral man chod 'khyud sbyor 'dod chags dang //
NK117(she)001:28816: sgo gsum sgrib dag tha dad 'dzin pa sbyang //
NK117(she)001:28817: stong pa'i thig le rig pa'i snying po can //
NK117(she)001:28818: grub mtha' bsam mi khyab pa'i ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:28819: 'da' ka gsang chen phyag rgya chen po la //
NK117(she)001:28820: 'bras bu mkha' khyab ngo bo nyid sku'o //
NK117(she)001:28821: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la brten nas //
NK117(she)001:28822: zhes pa bla ma yab yum sbyor ba'i khu ba
NK117(she)001:28823: slob bu'i ngag tu blud nas gsang ba'i dbang thob
NK117(she)001:28824: par byas mthar gsum pa'i dbang ni rig ma mtshan
NK117(she)001:28825: ldan slob bur gzhung rnam dag ltar gtad par sbyor
NK117(she)001:28826: ba byas pas dga' bzhi'i ye shes nyams su myong
NK117(she)001:28827: ba dpe'i ye shes dang de'i rang bzhin dpe las
NK117(she)001:28828: 'das pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bor bzhag
NK117(she)001:28829: nas tshig gis mtshon pa'i dbang bskur ba yang /
NK117(she)001:28830: lha 'thab bral man chad ni gnyis 'khyud kyi 'dod
NK117(she)001:28831: chags kyis gdung bar byed pa'i de'i gnyen por tshig
NK117(she)001:28832: dbang rin po che bskur bas sgo gsum gyi sgrib
NK117(she)001:28833: pa dag cing tha dad du 'dzin pa'i dri ma
NK117(she)001:28834: sbyang / stong pa'i thig le ste spros bral ka
NK117(she)001:28835: dag rig pa'i snying po can sgra ji bzhin par
NK117(she)001:28836: sbyang / rtogs tshe / grub mtha' bsam gyis mi
NK117(she)001:28837: khyab pa'i ye shes te 'da' ka ma gsang chen
NK117(she)001:28838: phyag rgya chen po ni 'khor 'das gnyis su med
NK117(she)001:28839: sbyang / rtogs tshe / pa la / 'bras bu mkha' khyab ste /
NK117(she)001:28840: nam mkhas gar khyab chos sku dang longs skus khyab
NK117(she)001:28841: pa la ngo bo nyid sku zhes sgro btags pa
NK117(she)001:28842: tsam mo // dbang gsum pa'i dus na sna tshogs
NK117(she)001:28843: gzugs can ma las rnyed pa'i dpe'i lhan skyes de
NK117(she)001:28844: ni don dam byang sems kyi myu gu lta bu
NK117(she)001:28845: tsam mo // yin no // de yang phar phyin
NK117(she)001:28846: theg pa man chad du de kho na nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:28847: don rjes dpag tsam las ston ma nus pa /
NK117(she)001:28848: sngags su thabs la brten nas sgrib gnyis bag chags
NK117(she)001:28849: dang bcas pa bcom nas don dam sgra ji bzhin
NK117(she)001:28850: par rtogs par 'gyur ba ni 'pho med kyi zhu
NK117(she)001:28851: bde las skyes pa yin phyir mtha' gang du'ang ma
NK117(she)001:28852: lhung la / 'dzag med bde chen gyi ros yid
NK117(she)001:28853: kyi dri ma bkrus pas dbang po'i duhkha'i grong khyer
NK117(she)001:28855: dwangs mas lus yongs khyab pas rnam thar bzhi ldan
NK117(she)001:28856: gyi bde chen nam bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i de
NK117(she)001:28857: bzhin nyid kyi lhums su zhugs pa dbang bzhi pa'i
NK117(she)001:28858: ngo bo'o // de'ang re zhig tshig gis mtshon nas
NK117(she)001:28859: de'i rang bzhin go bar bya dgos pas tshig dbang
NK117(she)001:28860: ngo bo'o // ngo // de ltar dbang bzhi pa
NK117(she)001:28861: tshig dbang rin po che thob pas lta ba rang
NK117(she)001:28862: byung gi ye shes mthong lam gyi bden pa mngon
NK117(she)001:28863: sum du ston pa'i gnas lugs bsam gyis mi khyab
NK117(she)001:28864: ngo bo'o // ngo // pa dang / stong nyid
NK117(she)001:28865: kyi thig le rig pa'i ye shes kyi snying po
NK117(she)001:28866: can thod rgal la sogs pa don dam 'od gsal
NK117(she)001:28867: gyi rdzogs rim bsgom pa la dbang /
NK117(she)001:28868: sgo gsum tha dad du 'dzin pa'i sems kyi dri
NK117(she)001:28869: ma shin tu phra ba cha mnyam par sbyong zhing
NK117(she)001:28871: gnas skabs bzhi las snyoms 'jug gi gnas skabs dang /
NK117(she)001:28872: de'ang 'dzag bde'i sred pa yin pas khu rdul rlung gsum las 'khor ba'i sgo gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:28873: bde sdug btang snyoms gsum 'char bas khu rdul rlung gsum la cha mnyam du 'jug pa'i sems dang /
NK117(she)001:28874: shes sgrib ches phra ba 'pho ba'i bag chags kyi cha dang bcas pa sbyong ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:28875: de'i grub mtha' bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni bde
NK117(she)001:28876: stong gi ye shes rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'o
NK117(she)001:28877: // grub mtha' ma rnyogs na 'da' ka ma phyag rgya chen pos 'pho ba sbyang ba dang /
NK117(she)001:28879: las la sbyar ba gsum yin no //
NK117(she)001:28880: mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni dbang gi sa bon
NK117(she)001:28881: rgyud la thebs pa de rim gnyis kyis sad par
NK117(she)001:28882: byas pas mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i stong gzugs phyag
NK117(she)001:28883: rgya chen po ye shes kyi rlung rig las grub
NK117(she)001:28884: pa'i mtshan dpe'i bdag nyid can lhan skyes ye shes
NK117(she)001:28885: ngo bo nyid kyi sku 'grub pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28886: dbang bzhi pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK117(she)001:28887: khyod kyis srog chags gsad par bya /
NK117(she)001:28891: bzhi po ma tha' drug gi tshul du shes dgos so //
NK117(she)001:28893: sgra don sbyar na a b+hi sh+ainy+tsa'i sgras //
NK117(she)001:28894: glo bur dri ma gtor dang sheka tas //
NK117(she)001:28895: skal ba blugs pa rnam pa gnyis su 'grub //
NK117(she)001:28896: ces pa ni de la sgra don sbyar na ste
NK117(she)001:28897: a b+hi mngon par dang sh+ainy+tsa'i sgras dbang bskur ba
NK117(she)001:28898: ste / de'ang glo bur gyi dri ma gtor ba
NK117(she)001:28899: dang sheka tas skal ba blugs pa rnam pa gnyis
NK117(she)001:28900: ste / su 'grub pa'o // de la dbang gi sgra bshad ni snod du rung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:28901: lugs su blugs pa'i rnam pa ltar sgom rung dang /
NK117(she)001:28902: 'bras bu ye shes kyi nus pa khyad par rgyud la blugs pa ltar 'jog pas na dbang /
NK117(she)001:28903: dri ma dag par byed pas na gtor ba'i don du 'jog pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28905: dbang mchog rang la gnas pa khams drug gi //
NK117(she)001:28906: rten dang 'byor pa rgyu yi dbang yin te //
NK117(she)001:28907: slob dpon nyid kyis cho gas bskur ba dang //
NK117(she)001:28908: rang gi dmigs pas 'dris pa lam gyi dbang //
NK117(she)001:28909: rgyu dus 'od zer chen po'i dbang bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:28910: rang sems sku bzhir smin pa 'bras bu'i dbang //
NK117(she)001:28911: dbang bzhi rdzogs tshe rig 'dzin sdom pa 'a thob //
NK117(she)001:28912: ces pa ni de la dbang mchog rang la gnas
