NK117(she)001:28913: pa ste sems ni ming bzhi'i phung po can ye
NK117(she)001:28915: phung po'i rten ni 'byung ba lnga /
NK117(she)001:28917: rtsa'i brten pa srog gi rlung /
NK117(she)001:28918: rlung gi brten pa byang chub kyi sems yin pa'i dpe /
NK117(she)001:28919: sman gyi ro dang nus pa dang dri dang /
NK117(she)001:28920: zhu rjes lta bur gcig la gcig brten pa'o //
NK117(she)001:28921: snying po can la dbang gi rang bzhin gdod nas gnas pa yang /
NK117(she)001:28922: rgyu dus kyi phung lnga rigs lnga /
NK117(she)001:28924: skye mched sems dpa' sems ma sogs gdan gsum lha'i
NK117(she)001:28925: rnam par 'gyur ba can gyi dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor
NK117(she)001:28926: lor rdzogs pa ni bum dbang gi rang bzhin du
NK117(she)001:28927: yod pa'o // de bas na lam bsgom pa'i sngon
NK117(she)001:28928: du 'gro ba can bum dbang gi sa bon lus
NK117(she)001:28929: kyi rtsa'i gtso bo rnams ye nas sprul skur gnas
NK117(she)001:28930: pas de'i glo bur ba'i dri ma dag byed bum
NK117(she)001:28931: dbang bskur ba ni lam gyi dbang yin la /
NK117(she)001:28932: de bzhin du gsang dbang gi sa bon dag yi
NK117(she)001:28933: ge'i rang bzhin longs skur gnas pa de'i glo bur
NK117(she)001:28934: ba'i dri ma dag byed gsang dbang dang /
NK117(she)001:28935: sher dbang gi sa bon kun rdzob byang sems dang
NK117(she)001:28936: rten dang brten par 'brel ba sems nyid bde chen
NK117(she)001:28937: chos sku'i rang bzhin du gnas pa de'i glo bur
NK117(she)001:28938: ba'i dri ma dag byed sher dbang ste shes rab
NK117(she)001:28939: ni lhan cig skyes pa'i lta ba dang ye shes
NK117(she)001:28940: ni de'i rang bzhin shes pa'i lhag mthong ngo //
NK117(she)001:28941: dbang bzhi pa'i sa bon da lta ba ltar mi
NK117(she)001:28942: mngon kyang bde stong gi myong zhen dang bcas pa'i
NK117(she)001:28943: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes gnas pa de'i glo
NK117(she)001:28944: bur ba'i dri ma tshig dbang gis dag par byed
NK117(she)001:28945: pas rlung sems dwangs pa'i ye shes rig stong mtha'
NK117(she)001:28946: bral rnam thar gsum gyi mtshan nyid can gyi nus
NK117(she)001:28947: pa rgyud la 'jog pa'i dbang bzhi pa'am /
NK117(she)001:28948: de'ang gzhan du cho ga la brten te bla mas
NK117(she)001:28949: slob mar bskur ba ni gzhi lam gnyis ka'i dbang
NK117(she)001:28952: rnal 'byor zab mo'i dbang bzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:28953: byin rlabs 'pho ba'i rgyun la goms su 'jug cing
NK117(she)001:28954: dad pas nan tan du bya ba thams cad lam
NK117(she)001:28955: dbang yin la / rgyu dus na rang rig la
NK117(she)001:28956: ye ldan gyi dbang gi de nyid nyi ma'i dal
NK117(she)001:28957: lta bu de tshogs brgyad kyi dri ma glo bur
NK117(she)001:28958: ba sprin sbubs lta bus bsgribs pa lam dus kyi
NK117(she)001:28959: dbang gi byed las kyis dri ma thams cad bsal
NK117(she)001:28960: nas gnas skabs kyi yon tan rgya chen po dang
NK117(she)001:28961: dbang yin la / / rgyu dus nas rang sems
NK117(she)001:28962: sku bzhir sbyor ba'i 'bras dus kyi 'od zer chen
NK117(she)001:28963: po'i rang bzhin du thob pa'ang yod pa'i phyir 'bras
NK117(she)001:28964: bu'i dbang zhes bya ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:28965: de la sngags kyi dbang bskur thob cing dam sdom
NK117(she)001:28966: rnam par dag pa rnams ni rim gnyis kyi rten
NK117(she)001:28967: 'brel las 'bad pa chung ngus kyang tshe 'di nyid
NK117(she)001:28968: la dngos grub thob pa ni sngags kyis btab pas
NK117(she)001:28969: sa bon yud tsam la smin pa ma sha'i sbyor
NK117(she)001:28970: ba bzhin no // de ltar dbang bzhi mtha' rten
NK117(she)001:28971: bcas rdzogs tshe sngags kyi sdom pa'ang thob pa yin
NK117(she)001:28972: ba bzhin no // te / de'ang slob ma'i sgo
NK117(she)001:28973: gsum rdo rje gsum du byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus
NK117(she)001:28974: nas brtsams te rgyud sde 'og ma gsum la dngos
NK117(she)001:28975: gzhi rdzogs nas slob dpon gyi dbang bskur ba'i mtha'
NK117(she)001:28976: ba bzhin no // te / dang / bla med
NK117(she)001:28977: la bum dbang gi mthar bskyed rim gyi sngags sdom
NK117(she)001:28978: ba bzhin no // te / dang / dngos bstan
NK117(she)001:28979: dang / dbang gong ma gsum la'ang de'i ldog chas
NK117(she)001:28980: phye ba'i dam tshig gsar thob re re ste /
NK117(she)001:28981: ngo bo gcig pa'i cha nas sdom pa yang bzhag
NK117(she)001:28982: tu rung ba rnams thob pa'i mtshams skabs 'di yin
NK117(she)001:28983: pas na rang rang la ltos pa'i yon tan dang
NK117(she)001:28984: / rtsa ltung gnyis ka bskyed pa'i rten du song ba'o //
NK117(she)001:28985: de nas dam tshig khas blang ba bcas song mthar /
NK117(she)001:28986: mos gus chen pos lus longs spyod /
NK117(she)001:28987: sa gzhi sogs rang la bdog dgu yongs su 'bul bar bagyi'o //
NK117(she)001:28989: dbang thob skyes bu tha ba'i skyon sbyangs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:28990: zhing sar sa bon bzhag pa ji bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:28991: sgrib pa gnyis dang sku bzhi mngon du byed //
NK117(she)001:28992: ces pa ni 'di ltar rdo rje slob dpon mtshan
NK117(she)001:28993: nyid dang ldan pa la slob ma dad dam ldan
NK117(she)001:28994: pas dbang bskur rdzogs par nod pa'i de ma thag
NK117(she)001:28995: thar pa'i lam sna zin cing rgyal ba'i sras su
NK117(she)001:28996: 'gyur ba'i dpe zhing sar sa bon bzhag pa ji
NK117(she)001:28997: lta ba bzhin du nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang
NK117(she)001:28998: shes bya'i sgrib pa gnyis dag nas sprul sku dang
NK117(she)001:28999: longs sku dang chos sku ngo bo nyid sku ste
NK117(she)001:29000: sku bzhi'i 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29002: gnyis pa lam la bskyed rdzogs rnam gnyis las //
NK117(she)001:29003: dang po bskyed rim skye gnas rnam pa bzhi'i //
NK117(she)001:29004: bag chags sbyong phyir de dang mthun par ston //
NK117(she)001:29005: bskyed tshul 'khor ba'i rnam pa dang mthun pas //
NK117(she)001:29006: srid pa gsum po ma lus sbyong zhing dag /
NK117(she)001:29007: mya ngan 'das dang bzhugs tshul mthun pa yi //
NK117(she)001:29008: lha yi rnam pas 'bras bu gzhi la rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:29009: gnyis ka'ang rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i smin byed du //
NK117(she)001:29010: 'gro ba'i dag rdzogs smin gsum spyi la gces //
NK117(she)001:29011: zhes pa ni de yang sngon du dbang song nas
NK117(she)001:29012: gnyis pa lam la bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim
NK117(she)001:29014: dang po bskyed rim la skye gnas rnam pa bzhi'i
NK117(she)001:29015: bag chags sbyong phyir de dang der mthun par ston
NK117(she)001:29016: pa ni 'og nas rim bzhin shes par bya la
NK117(she)001:29017: / bskyed tshul 'khor ba'i rnam pa dang mthun pas
NK117(she)001:29018: srid pa bar do'i ming bzhi'i phung po mngal du
NK117(she)001:29019: tshud pa nas bzung ste skye rga na 'chi sogs
NK117(she)001:29020: srid pa gsum po ma lus kyi bag chags sbyong
NK117(she)001:29022: de dag pas mya ngan las 'das pa sangs rgyas
NK117(she)001:29023: rnams dang bzhugs tshul mthun pa'i lha'i rnam pas 'bras
NK117(she)001:29025: de ltar 'khor 'das gnyis ka dang mthun pa'i bskyed
NK117(she)001:29026: rim ni rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i smin par byed pa'i
NK117(she)001:29027: thabs su 'gro bas 'khor ba'i skyon dag cing myang
NK117(she)001:29028: 'das kyi yon tan rdzogs pa'i smin byed gsum po
NK117(she)001:29030: de la theg chen gyi spyad pa spyod pa'i skyes
NK117(she)001:29031: bu chen po gnyis kyis gnyer bya ni sems can
NK117(she)001:29032: gyi don du gzugs sku bsgrub pa kho na yin
NK117(she)001:29033: la / de 'thob thabs ni sngags lam du dam sdom dag par byed pa gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:29034: de yang 'bras rgyud mngon du byed pa la nyer len gyi rgyu dang /
NK117(she)001:29035: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen gnyis 'tshogs dgos pas nyer len ni gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:29036: byed can ni thabs sam lam rgyud yin pas 'khor
NK117(she)001:29037: 'das lam gsum gzhi lam 'bras rgyud du 'dus so
NK117(she)001:29038: // de'ang rang bzhin lhan skyes kyi dus gsal ba ni 'khor ba /
NK117(she)001:29042: de la rang bzhin med pa ni myang 'das /
NK117(she)001:29045: kun la lam gyi man ngag thabs rgyud sbyar bas
NK117(she)001:29046: thabs dang rgyu 'bras kyi rgyud de gsum du gnas
NK117(she)001:29047: pa'o // de la sems can thams cad la rang
NK117(she)001:29048: chas su ldan pa'i sems kyi rang bzhin bde gshegs
NK117(she)001:29049: snying po rtogs na sangs rgyas dang /
NK117(she)001:29050: ma rtogs na 'khor ba'i rgyu byed pa ni gzhi'i rgyud dang /
NK117(she)001:29051: ngo bo nyid dang 'ching grol med pa'i cha nas
NK117(she)001:29052: don gyi gnas lugs rnam pa dri ma dang ma
NK117(she)001:29053: bral yang rang ngo des gos ma myong ba bde
NK117(she)001:29054: gshegs snying po / mtshan nyid med pa'i chos sku
NK117(she)001:29055: dang rang bzhin gyi gdangs ma 'gags pa'i cha nas
NK117(she)001:29056: gzugs sku'i yon tan rten du gnas pa gang zhig
NK117(she)001:29057: lam dus su byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK117(she)001:29058: bden pa dbyer med dang rang byung gi ye shes
NK117(she)001:29059: la sogs pa'i tha snyad sna tshogs su chags pa'o
NK117(she)001:29060: // zhes pa ltar lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen gdams
NK117(she)001:29061: ngag bar ma chad pa'i thabs kyi rgyud la brten
NK117(she)001:29062: nas glo bur gyi dri ma sbyangs pas /
NK117(she)001:29063: yongs su dag pa'i zhing khams na sku dang ye
NK117(she)001:29064: shes kyi bkod pa sna tshogs su snang ba ni
NK117(she)001:29065: gzhan gyis mi 'phrogs pa 'bras bu'i rgyud ces bya'o
NK117(she)001:29066: // de yang rgyal ba'i bka' dri ma med pa'i lung tshad ma dang /
NK117(she)001:29067: mkhas pas nyams su blangs shing grol ba'i dpang po yod pa'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK117(she)001:29068: gnyis ka dang rjes su mthun pa'i rig pa tshad ma ste gsum gyis gtan la phab dgos so //
NK117(she)001:29069: da ni so so'i rang bzhin bshad pa la rdzogs
NK117(she)001:29070: rim gyi rtogs pa khyad par can ma rnyed bar
NK117(she)001:29071: du bskyed rim la brten nas rtog pas rtog pa
NK117(she)001:29073: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud kyi dgongs pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:29075: ji ltar sgong skyes lan gnyis skye ba ltar //
NK117(she)001:29076: bdag sras gzhan sras rnam pa gnyis su bskyed //
NK117(she)001:29077: bdag gi sras su gzhan bya ba la lnga //
NK117(she)001:29078: sa bon las ni gtso bo bskyed pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29079: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bkug nas mkhar bstim dang //
NK117(she)001:29080: sems can bkug nas sgrib pa sbyang ba dang //
NK117(she)001:29081: gnyis su med la che ba bskyed pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29082: mkha' nas bton nas gdan la 'god pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29083: gzhan gyi sras su bdag bya ba la brgyad //
NK117(she)001:29084: sgo nga smin pa de dang der gyur bzhin //
NK117(she)001:29085: gtso bo 'od zhu sa bon gyur pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29086: de las yab yum skye mched rdzogs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29087: yab kyi rtog pa yi ger gyur pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29088: yum las 'od 'phro lha la gsol gdab dang //
NK117(she)001:29089: kun kyang rang bstim nga rgyal bzung ba dang //
NK117(she)001:29090: snyoms par zhugs nas mkha' ru dkyil 'khor bskyed //
NK117(she)001:29091: rtog pa zhe gnyis lhar gsal phyir gdon dang //
NK117(she)001:29092: phyag rgya bzhi yis bcings dang rgyas gdab bo //
NK117(she)001:29093: zhes pa ni ji ltar 'dab chags la sogs dang
NK117(she)001:29094: po sgo nga dang de nas bya ru 'gyur zhing
NK117(she)001:29095: lan gnyis su skye ba ltar bdag sras gzhan sras
NK117(she)001:29096: rnam pa gnyis su bskyed pa ste /
NK117(she)001:29097: de'ang bsgrub gzhi'i rnam smin gyi lus ting 'dzin gsum
NK117(she)001:29098: gyi man ngag la brten nas nam mkhar rgyu'i rdo
NK117(she)001:29099: rje 'dzin pa yab yum du bskyed cing de'i mkha'
NK117(she)001:29100: gsang du phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams spyan drangs nas
NK117(she)001:29101: bdag gi sras su bya ba'i sa bon du bsgrub
NK117(she)001:29102: pa dang / sems can rnams bkug nas sgrib pa
NK117(she)001:29103: sbyangs te 'khor 'das ro gcig tu zhu ba dang
NK117(she)001:29104: pa dang / / gnyis med kyi rang bzhin la che ba brjod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29105: de'i rkyen gyis 'bras bu'i rdo rje 'dzin par bzhengs
NK117(she)001:29106: pa'i mkha' gsang nas 'khor rnams bton te dal du
NK117(she)001:29107: dgod pa la bdag gi sras su sangs rgyas byas
NK117(she)001:29108: pa zhes bya'o // gzhan gyi sras su bdag bya ba la brgyad de /
NK117(she)001:29109: gtso bo yab yum zhu ste rgyu'i sa bon du gyur pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29110: de las yab yum du bskyed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29111: yab kyi rtog tshogs las yi ge bskyed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29113: lha la gsol ba gdab pa dang dkyil 'khor thams
NK117(she)001:29114: cad bdag yab yum la bstim pas ye shes par
NK117(she)001:29116: yab yum sbyor ba bya zhing mkha' ru dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29117: bdag gi rtog pa zhe gnyis lha skur gyur te phyir gdon pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29118: ye shes pa spyan drang zhing rgyas gdab pa la sogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29120: bsdu na thog mar rang nyid lhar gsal bas //
NK117(she)001:29121: mdun mkhar dkyil 'khor gsal btab rgyun bshags bya //
NK117(she)001:29122: gnyis ka mi dmigs ngang nas lha so so'i //
NK117(she)001:29123: dkyil 'khor mngon rtogs ji bzhin bsgom pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29124: zhes pa ni de yang thog mar rang nyid gzhung
NK117(she)001:29125: gang yin gyi lhar gsal bzhin pas mdun mkhar dal
NK117(she)001:29126: gyi lha gtso 'khor rnams gsal btab la rgyun bshags
NK117(she)001:29127: yan lag bdun pa'am brgyad pa bcu pa gang yin
NK117(she)001:29128: byas mthar bdag dang tshogs zhing gnyis mi dmigs par
NK117(she)001:29129: bzhag pa'i ngang nas lha zhi ba dang khro bo
NK117(she)001:29130: gang yin so so'i dkyil 'khor gyi rten dang brten
NK117(she)001:29131: pa'i mngon rtogs ji bzhin bsgom pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29133: mngal skyes sbyong phyir mngon byang bzhi'am lnga //
NK117(she)001:29134: dang po khrag 'thung gal po'i dgongs pa ste //
NK117(she)001:29135: 'chi srid bar dor bcas pa stong nyid sems //
NK117(she)001:29136: dri za nye bar len pa'i rnam shes ni //
NK117(she)001:29137: lha yi sa bon gyis sbyang de nyid kyang //
NK117(she)001:29138: khu rdul rlung dang 'dres pa'i mer mer nur //
NK117(she)001:29139: sa bon nyid las phyag mtshan gyur pas sbyong //
NK117(she)001:29140: ltar dang mkhrang gyur phyag mtshan 'od gong gyur //
NK117(she)001:29141: khyab 'jug nya dang rus sbal dbang po rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:29142: lha yi rnam par gyur nas sbyang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:29143: zhes pa ni de yang mngal skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim la mngon byang bzhi'am lnga ste /
NK117(she)001:29144: dang po ni he ru ka gal po'i dgongs pa
NK117(she)001:29145: ste 'chi kha ma'i srid pa bar do dang bcas
NK117(she)001:29146: pa stong nyid kyi sems bza' btung spyod du med
NK117(she)001:29147: cing dri za dang nye bar len pa'i rnam par
NK117(she)001:29148: shes pa ni lha'i sa bon gyis sbyang zhing de
NK117(she)001:29149: nyid kyang khu ba dang rdul gnyis rlung dang gsum
NK117(she)001:29150: po 'dres pa'i mer mer dang nur nur po rnams
NK117(she)001:29151: / sa bon nyid las phyag mtshan du gyur pas sbyong zhing /
NK117(she)001:29152: ltar ltar dang mkhrang gyur phyag mtshan 'od gong du
NK117(she)001:29153: gyur pas sbyangs nas khyab 'jug nya dang rus sbal
NK117(she)001:29154: sogs su gnas 'gyur mthar dbang po rdzogs pa dang
NK117(she)001:29155: bcas lha'i rnam par gyur nas sbyang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:29157: de la bsdus pa'i cho ga gsum bskyed ni //
NK117(she)001:29158: phyag rgya sku la yig 'bru gsung rdo rje //
NK117(she)001:29159: thugs ni phyag mtshan nyid du sbyor ba la //
NK117(she)001:29160: rdo rje'i cho ga gsum zhes pha rgyud lugs //
NK117(she)001:29161: zhes pa ni de la rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs
NK117(she)001:29162: rdo rje'i ngo bo rtse lnga pa dang gsung rdo
NK117(she)001:29163: rje'i ngo bo +aahh+aum la sogs sa bon sku rdo
NK117(she)001:29164: rje'i ngo bo lha'i rnam pa thams cad rdzogs par
NK117(she)001:29165: bsgoms pas sbyang gzhi'i sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du
NK117(she)001:29167: rdo rje'i cho ga gsum gyi dang pos mngal du
NK117(she)001:29168: khams dkar dmar tshogs pa la dri za'i rnam shes
NK117(she)001:29169: zhugs pa / gnyis pas khu khrag sems gsum 'dres
NK117(she)001:29170: nas 'gyur ba'i gnas skabs lnga nyams su myong ba
NK117(she)001:29171: zhugs pa / / gsum pas byung ba byer sdud
NK117(she)001:29172: kyis lus yongs su grub nas btsas pa sbyong la
NK117(she)001:29173: zhugs pa / / / 'bras dus sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du bsgrub pa'i rten 'brel bsgrig go //
NK117(she)001:29175: bar ma do nas lus 'tshol tshogs kyi lam //
NK117(she)001:29176: mngal du rnam shes 'jug pa sbyor lam ste //
NK117(she)001:29177: lhums zhugs byang chub lnga po mthong bsgom dang //
NK117(she)001:29178: zla ba bcu ni sa dang rab sbyar nas //
NK117(she)001:29179: btsa' ba mi slob lam gyur sprul pa'i sku //
NK117(she)001:29180: zhes pa ni de yang bar ma do nas gzhan
NK117(she)001:29181: don gyi sems bskyed dang ldan pas lus tshol ba
NK117(she)001:29182: tshogs lam / mngal sgo 'dams nas lus len pa la sbyor lam /
NK117(she)001:29183: mngal du 'jug pa'i byed las rang rgyud pa rnams sbyang ba mthong sgom gyi lam /
NK117(she)001:29184: zla ba bcu sa bcur mtshon nas lhag lha gang
NK117(she)001:29185: yin gyi skur bzhengs nas skye ba sprul pa'i skur
NK117(she)001:29186: 'grub pa'o // mngon byang gi ngo bo skye gnas bzhi dang mthun par sbyar na /
NK117(she)001:29187: mngon byang lnga'i dang po gnyis kyis pha ma'i khu khrag tshogs pa /
NK117(she)001:29188: gsum pas dri za'i rnam shes zhugs pa /
NK117(she)001:29189: bzhi pas de gsum 'dres nas 'gyur ba'i gnas skabs rnams myong ba /
NK117(she)001:29190: lnga pas mngal gyi gnas skabs rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29192: mngon byang dang po zla ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK117(she)001:29193: mngal skyes khu ba drod gsher skyes kyi gsher //
NK117(she)001:29194: sgong skyes pha dang bardzusa skyes stong pa'i cha //
NK117(she)001:29195: zhes pa ni de la sbyang bya phung po lnga las gzugs phung /
NK117(she)001:29203: sbyong byed ni rnam snang gi ngo bo +aa li
NK117(she)001:29204: las byung ba'i mngon byang dang po zla ba'i dal
NK117(she)001:29205: du bsgom pa rnam pa lam byed /
NK117(she)001:29206: de'i ngo bo chos rnams me long gi gzugs ltar
NK117(she)001:29207: snang bas me long lta bu'i ye shes su mos
NK117(she)001:29208: pa ni mos pa lam byed /
NK117(she)001:29209: de'ang chos sku'i ye shes sgrib med du gsal ba ni 'bras bu lam byed /
NK117(she)001:29210: lam byed gsum la brten nas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:29211: rten 'brel du 'gyur ba ni byin rlabs lam byed
NK117(she)001:29213: de bzhin gnyis pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor yang //
NK117(she)001:29214: mngal skyes rdul dang drod gsher skyes kyi drod //
NK117(she)001:29215: sgong skyes ma dang bardzusa skyes gsal ba'i cha //
NK117(she)001:29216: zhes pa ni de ltar sbyang bya tshor ba dang nam mkha'i khams /
NK117(she)001:29217: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid de ser sna nga rgyal /
NK117(she)001:29218: mngal sgong drod rdzus bzhi'i ma'i khams dang cha drod dang gsal cha rnams so //
NK117(she)001:29219: sbyong byed ni rin 'byung gi ngo bo k+aa li
NK117(she)001:29220: las byung ba'i nyi ma'i dal du bsgom pa ni
NK117(she)001:29221: rnam pa / ngo bo chos rnams mnyam nyid du
NK117(she)001:29222: rtogs pa'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa
NK117(she)001:29223: rnam pa / / de'ang 'khor 'das kyi rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:29224: gcig par rtogs pa'i ye shes sgrib med du gsal
NK117(she)001:29225: bas na 'bras bu lam byed dang gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:29227: mngon byang gsum pa sa bon phyag mtshan bcas //
NK117(she)001:29228: khu rdul gnyis bar rnam shes zhugs pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29229: skye gnas bzhi po'i bar do'i rnam shes sbyong //
NK117(she)001:29230: zhes pa ni de la gong ma'i 'gres kyis /
NK117(she)001:29231: sbyang bya 'du shes dang rlung khams /
NK117(she)001:29233: 'dod chags skye gnas bzhi ka'i dri za nye bar len pa'i rnam shes so //
NK117(she)001:29234: sbyong byed a mi t+aa b+ha'i ngo bo sa bon phyag mtshan bcas par bsgom pa ni rnam pa /
NK117(she)001:29235: de'i ngo bo chos rnams ma 'dres pa rtogs pa'i ye shes su mos pa ni mos pa /
NK117(she)001:29236: de'ang chos kun ma bsgribs par gsal zhing mkhyen pa'i
NK117(she)001:29237: ye shes so sor rtog pa ni 'bras bu dang
NK117(she)001:29238: gsum po lam du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29240: mngon byang bzhi pa rnam gsum gcig tu 'dres //
NK117(she)001:29241: khu rdul sems gsum ro gcig 'dres pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29242: drod gsher skyes kyi drod dang rnam shes dang //
NK117(she)001:29243: bardzusa skyes gsal la stong pa'i cha tsam dang //
NK117(she)001:29244: bar srid 'dres pa'i cha rnams sbyong ba yin //
NK117(she)001:29245: zhes pa ni de la sbyang bya 'du byed dang rlung gi khams /
NK117(she)001:29246: bya ba sgo lnga'i rnam shes /
NK117(she)001:29247: phrag dog skyes gnas bzhir 'jug pa'i tshul gyi mngal skyes /
NK117(she)001:29248: sgong skyes ltar na rnam shes dang khu rdul 'dres pa /
NK117(she)001:29249: drod gsher gyi drod dang rnam shes 'dres pa bardzusa
NK117(she)001:29250: skyes kyi gsal la stong pa tsam dang bar srid
NK117(she)001:29252: sbyong byed ni don 'grub kyi ngo bo nyi zla
NK117(she)001:29253: phyag mtshan sa bon dang bcas pa 'dres pa'i thig
NK117(she)001:29254: le gong bu'i rnam pa can du bsgom pa ni
NK117(she)001:29255: rnam pa / de'i ngo bo rgyal ba kun gyi
NK117(she)001:29256: mdzad pa ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i ye shes su
NK117(she)001:29258: des 'gro ba kun gyi bya ba thams cad grub
NK117(she)001:29259: pa'i ye shes ni 'bras bu lam byed dang gsum
NK117(she)001:29261: mngon byang lnga pa sku ru grub pa ni //
NK117(she)001:29262: skye gnas bzhi po'i skye mched yongs rdzogs nas //
NK117(she)001:29263: rags pa'i yul la dbang po sad pa yi //
NK117(she)001:29264: 'khor ba'i rnam pa cha dang bcas pa sbyong //
NK117(she)001:29265: khams dang phung po rnam par shes pa'i tshogs //
NK117(she)001:29266: gnas su dag pa gdan gsum tshang ba'i lha //
NK117(she)001:29267: mya ngan 'das dang bzhugs tshul mthun pa ni //
NK117(she)001:29268: rgyu las 'bras bu'i he ru ka nyid do //
NK117(she)001:29269: zhes pa ni de la sbyang bya rnam shes kyi phung po dang sa khams /
NK117(she)001:29270: yid dang bcas pa'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi chos nyid du 'dzin pa'i cha /
NK117(she)001:29272: skye gnas bzhi'i lus grub pa'i gnas skabs rnams so //
NK117(she)001:29273: sbyong byed ni mi bskyod pa'i ngo bo rgyu'i he
NK117(she)001:29274: ru ka yab yum du bskyed pa ni sku'i rnam
NK117(she)001:29275: pa / btsas nas dbang po la sad pas 'khor ba'i rnam pa cha dang bcas pa sbyangs la /
NK117(she)001:29276: de'ang lha'i rnam pa de la yan lag nying lag
NK117(she)001:29277: sogs yongs su rdzogs pa ltar ye shes la yon
NK117(she)001:29278: tan thams cad rdzogs pa mos pa /
NK117(she)001:29279: de'i ngo bo chos dbyings ye shes su ro gcig pa ni 'bras bu lam byed dang gsum mo //
NK117(she)001:29280: gnyis pa rang 'bras sngags kyi yon tan bskyed tshul ni /
NK117(she)001:29284: nyon mongs pa'i cha bcas mngon byang lnga'i sbyong byed
NK117(she)001:29285: kyis sbyangs mthar rgyu'i rdo rje 'dzin par rdzogs pa
NK117(she)001:29286: ni mngal skyes ltar na pha ma mtshon pa'i sbyang
NK117(she)001:29287: gzhi yin la / de'i ngang las rgyu rdo rje
NK117(she)001:29288: 'dzin pa yab yum thig ler zhu ba ni bar
NK117(she)001:29290: de las zhu ba glus bskul gyi sgras phung khams /
NK117(she)001:29291: skye mched gnas su dag pa la gdan gsum tshang
NK117(she)001:29292: ba'i lha'i ngo bo 'bras bu'i rdo rje 'dzin par
NK117(she)001:29293: bzhengs pa ni pha ma gnyis kyi bur gyur pa'i
NK117(she)001:29295: de'ang mtshan dpe'i bdag nyid du bzhengs nas gzhan la
NK117(she)001:29296: phan pa rgya chen grub pa ni myang 'das dang
NK117(she)001:29298: de'ang nyi zla'i bar du sa bon dang mtshan ma'i rnam pa zhu ba sgong skyes /
NK117(she)001:29299: mngon byang lngas bskyed zhu ba 'khor gyi lha mo'i
NK117(she)001:29300: glus bskul rkyen gyis bzhengs pa mngal skyes sbyong tshul
NK117(she)001:29302: khu rdul rlung gsum sems dang bcas pa'i cha //
NK117(she)001:29303: rnam par dag pas rdzogs rim smin byed 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:29304: 'di ltar khams dkar dmar gyi rten gnyis la brten
NK117(she)001:29305: pa'i tshul du 'brel ba'i rnam shes sems kyi rang
NK117(she)001:29306: bzhin rgyu dus na dbang gis smin par byas pa
NK117(she)001:29307: gang zhig / rtog bcas kyi lam bskyed rim gyi
NK117(she)001:29308: dus su mngon byang lnga la brten nas bsgoms pas
NK117(she)001:29309: rdzogs rim gyi smin byed du 'gro ba yin te
NK117(she)001:29310: gang zhig / / ci'i phyir na de'i dus na'ang
NK117(she)001:29311: gnad du bsnun pa'i gtso bo ni khams dkar dmar
NK117(she)001:29312: gnyis dang rnam par shes pa gsum yin pa'i phyir
NK117(she)001:29313: gang zhig / / ro // de dag gi byed las kyi khyad par dag rdzogs smin gsum ni /
NK117(she)001:29314: mngon byang so so'i rang bzhin rgyu 'bras 'brel pa
NK117(she)001:29315: can yin pas 'khor ba dang mthun pa'i rnam pa
NK117(she)001:29316: lam byed kyi sbyang bya srid pa'i rang bzhin sbyong
NK117(she)001:29318: rgyal ba'i bzhugs tshul dang mthun pa'i mos pa lam
NK117(she)001:29319: byed kyis so so'i ye shes su rdzogs par byed
NK117(she)001:29320: / gnyis ka rdzogs rim gyi smin byed du 'gro
NK117(she)001:29321: ba'i 'bras bu lam byed kyi mtshan dpe'i bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:29324: drod gsher skyes ni gnyis po 'dus pa las //
NK117(she)001:29325: rnam shes zhugs pa'i mod la gzugs grub bzhin //
NK117(she)001:29326: lha yi mtshan dang mngon rtogs dran tsam la //
NK117(she)001:29327: phyag rgya rdzogs pa'i bskyed rim tshang bar bsgom //
NK117(she)001:29328: zhes pa ni de'ang mngal sgong zung gi bag chags
NK117(she)001:29329: sbyong ba'i bskyed rim la goms pa rnams kyis ni
NK117(she)001:29330: drod gsher skyes sbyong ba a nu ltar gtso che
NK117(she)001:29332: mngon byang lnga la sogs pa'i spros pa la ma
NK117(she)001:29333: brten par lha so so'i snying po brjod pa tsam
NK117(she)001:29334: gyis shes rab kun tu bzang mo'i klong las kun
NK117(she)001:29335: rdzob bden pa'i cha lha skur rdzogs pa ni drod
NK117(she)001:29336: gsher skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim bde stong dbyer med
NK117(she)001:29338: bardzusa te skye ba skad cig dran rdzogs te //
NK117(she)001:29339: ming dang gzugs la ma brten wal gyis gsal //
NK117(she)001:29340: zhes pa ni 'di ltar lha gang yin de'i rnam
NK117(she)001:29341: pa'am snying po dran pa'i mod la skad cig dran
NK117(she)001:29342: rdzogs su bskyed pa chu las nya 'gyu ba bzhin
NK117(she)001:29343: no // de la kha cig bskyed tshul 'di la
NK117(she)001:29344: bskyed rim gyi yan lag ma tshang zhes dgag pa
NK117(she)001:29346: de lta na bardzusa skyes la'ang mngal 'byin gyi gnas
NK117(she)001:29347: skabs sogs kyi yan lag rnams sbyar dgos phyir dang
NK117(she)001:29348: / gzhan yang sbyong tshul bzhi med na 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:29349: 'dra 'bag bzhi lam du byas par ga la 'gyur
NK117(she)001:29350: / / gal te mngon byang so so'i skabs su
NK117(she)001:29351: skye gnas bzhi ga'i bag chags sbyong bas so zer
NK117(she)001:29352: / / na / skabs de'i mngon byang dang po
NK117(she)001:29353: ltar na bardzusa skyes kyi sbyang bya stong pa'i cha
NK117(she)001:29354: tsam las med pas der sbyar 'os pa'i 'thad pa
NK117(she)001:29355: / / na / de ci yin / gcig car 'jug pa'i sbyor ba ni /
NK117(she)001:29356: mngon brjod bla ma dang sdom 'byung las bstan pa la blta bar byos shig /
NK117(she)001:29358: bsgom tshul bzhi po'ang dang po'i las can la //
NK117(she)001:29359: sgong skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim gtso bor bsgom //
NK117(she)001:29360: rim bzhin goms pa brtan dang brtan pa che //
NK117(she)001:29361: shin tu brtan pa'i mthu dang mthun par slob //
NK117(she)001:29362: ces pa ni de la rim gnyis la ma goms
NK117(she)001:29363: pa dag dang po sgrub chen bka' brgyad ltar sgong
NK117(she)001:29364: skyes sbyong ba'i bskyed rim gtso bor bsgoms nas de
NK117(she)001:29365: la rim bzhin goms pa brtan pas bskyed rim las
NK117(she)001:29367: shin tu brtan pas bskyed rim la rang dbang thob
NK117(she)001:29368: pa'i mthu dang ldan pa'i dus su drod gsher skyes
NK117(she)001:29369: dang bardzusa skyes dang mthun par slob ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29370: de'ang rang rang gi sde pas bardzusa skyes sbyang ba
NK117(she)001:29371: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi bskyed rim du 'dod pa
NK117(she)001:29373: de ni 'phags lam gyi rdzogs rim mos spyod las
NK117(she)001:29374: 'phags pa yin pas de la bskyed rim gyi grub
NK117(she)001:29377: kun kyang de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:29378: spros pa kun dang bral ba'i shes rab gdangs //
NK117(she)001:29379: kun snang snying rje'i 'phen pas bskyed rim du //
NK117(she)001:29380: shar ba thabs kyi lam mchog ma nor zhing //
NK117(she)001:29381: snang dus nyid nas rang bzhin ma grub pa //
NK117(she)001:29382: zab mo snang stong thabs shes 'brel ba'i lam //
NK117(she)001:29383: zhes pa ni 'di ltar bskyed pa'i rim pa kun
NK117(she)001:29384: kyang de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin spros pa
NK117(she)001:29385: kun dang bral ba'i dbyings de nyid stong pa phyang
NK117(she)001:29386: chad ma yin zhing shes rab kyi gdangs 'gag pa
NK117(she)001:29387: med pa las kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK117(she)001:29388: snying rje chen po'i rtsal gyis 'phen pas bskyed pa'i
NK117(she)001:29389: rim pa ru shar ba thabs kyi lam mchog ma
NK117(she)001:29390: nor ba yin zhing snang ba'i dus nyid nas rang
NK117(she)001:29391: bzhin ma grub pas ngo bo stong pa yin phyir
NK117(she)001:29392: / zab mo snang ba dang stong pa gnyis dbyer med thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i lam mo //
NK117(she)001:29393: de nyid dbang dus su byin rlabs 'pho ba'i stobs kyis sam /
NK117(she)001:29394: gsum pa'i dpe'i ye shes la brten nas rgyud la skyes na cho ga las thob pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29395: gzhan mdo lam du thos bsam la brten nas sam
NK117(she)001:29396: gal te sngags lam la brten pa gang zhig rgyud
NK117(she)001:29397: bshad pa dang man ngag bstan pa las rig par
NK117(she)001:29398: bya dgos so // de yang gdod ma'i sems nyid
NK117(she)001:29399: de ni stong pa chos sku'i snying po can yin
NK117(she)001:29400: pas nam mkha' ltar go phyed pa /
NK117(she)001:29401: gsal ba longs sku'i rang bzhin can yin pas nyi zla ltar rang 'od gsal ba /
NK117(she)001:29402: 'char tshul sprul sku'i bdag nyid can yin pas nor
NK117(she)001:29403: bu bzhin dgos dgu lhun grub bde gshegs snying po'am
NK117(she)001:29404: / rgyal ba sku gsum gyi 'char gzhir ye nas rang chas su yod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29405: de ltar ngo bo bzhugs tshul la 'khrul pa med
NK117(she)001:29406: bzhin glo bur ba'i bdag rtog gis srid pa'i nyes
NK117(she)001:29407: dmigs kyi dbus su khrid cing gnas rigs drug por
NK117(she)001:29408: log rtog gis kun nas brtags kyang rang gi rang
NK117(she)001:29409: bzhin la nyams pa rdul tsam med do //
NK117(she)001:29410: gnas lugs de sgra ji bzhin par rtogs na 'phags
NK117(she)001:29411: pa'i bden pa mthong ba yin pas bskyed rim la
NK117(she)001:29412: che thang du dgos pa min par yang gsungs so
NK117(she)001:29413: // de'ang dang po'i las can la rdzogs rim 'grub pa'i rgyu ru gal chen du gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:29414: bskyed gzhi de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin de
NK117(she)001:29415: so skye'i sa la rjes dpag tsam yin pas chos
NK117(she)001:29416: thams cad bsam du med pa'i de kho na nyid
NK117(she)001:29417: kyi gzugs brnyan tsam du snang bas ting nge 'dzin
NK117(she)001:29418: ltar gyur pa'i gdangs snying rje chen por shar ba
NK117(she)001:29419: mos spyod kyi sems bskyed la kun snang gi ting
NK117(she)001:29420: nge 'dzin du btags nas de'i 'phen pas bskyed rim
NK117(she)001:29421: gyi rgyu tshogs bsgrub pa ni thabs lam ma nor
NK117(she)001:29423: de las 'gal ba'i dmigs bcas bskyed rim ni //
NK117(she)001:29424: mu stegs byed dang gdon gyi rigs la'ang yod //
NK117(she)001:29425: ces pa ni spyir ting 'dzin rnam gsum sogs dang 'gal ba'i dmigs bcas kyi bskyed rim ni /
NK117(she)001:29426: mu stegs byed de phyi rol pa'i grub mtha' 'dzin
NK117(she)001:29427: pa 'ga' dang gdon gyi rigs phal cher la'ang yod
NK117(she)001:29428: ces pa'o // spyir mu stegs byed la la dge
NK117(she)001:29429: ba bsgrub pa yod kyang de'i rgyud sdom pas ma
NK117(she)001:29430: bsdams pa'i skyon gyis bar ma dge ba tsam las
NK117(she)001:29431: ces pa'o // med do // rig 'dzin gyi sdom
NK117(she)001:29432: pa bral ba'i bskyed rim sogs gsang sngags lam gyis
NK117(she)001:29433: kyang 'tshang rgya bar mi nus la /
NK117(she)001:29434: khyad par bskyed rim so so'i sbyang gzhi sbyong byed
NK117(she)001:29435: kyi rten 'byung la rmongs pa rnam pa thams cad
NK117(she)001:29436: du shes rab bral ba'i lam snang phyogs kyi kha
NK117(she)001:29437: dog dang dbyibs tsam la zhen pa'i bskyed rim ni
NK117(she)001:29438: phyi rol pa dang yi dwags mthu bo che rnams
NK117(she)001:29439: la'ang yod de / mu stegs byed kyi gsang sngags
NK117(she)001:29440: kyi grub 'bras dang bde 'gro'i lus rten la bskyed
NK117(she)001:29441: rim rang rgyud du spyad pa'i goms pa mngon du
NK117(she)001:29442: brtas pa'i gdon gyi rnam 'gyur las kyang shes so
NK117(she)001:29443: la'ang yod de / // tshul bzhin grub pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK117(she)001:29445: sngags su byang chub sems dpa'i mthong lam la //
NK117(she)001:29446: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub ces //
NK117(she)001:29447: shin tu grags pa mngon du byed pa'i thabs //
NK117(she)001:29448: snang cha lha skur gsal ba bsod nams tshogs //
NK117(she)001:29449: de la rang bzhin ma grub ye shes te //
NK117(she)001:29450: tshogs gnyis nye rgyur bsten pa'i dbang rnon ni //
NK117(she)001:29451: lam lngar 'brel ba rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'i //
NK117(she)001:29452: them skas nyid la nges pa lnga ldan sogs //
NK117(she)001:29453: sku lnga'i zhing du mig 'phrul lta bur 'gro //
NK117(she)001:29454: zhes pa ni de'ang theg chen gyi rigs gnyis las thabs sam lam yang gnyis su bstan te /
NK117(she)001:29455: gang zag 'dod yon la mi sred pa rnams la byang sems theg pa gsungs shing /
NK117(she)001:29456: 'dod yon spang mi nus pa rnams la sngags gsungs
NK117(she)001:29457: pa bzhin mthong lam ma skyes bar du lam de
NK117(she)001:29458: gnyis so so'i rigs kyi nus pa gsos btab nas
NK117(she)001:29459: sbyangs pa las / nam zhig skyes pa na ngo
NK117(she)001:29460: bo la gnyis su med pas byang chub sems dpa'i
NK117(she)001:29461: sa las ni mthong lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK117(she)001:29462: ye shes su grags la sngags su phyag rgya chen
NK117(she)001:29463: po mchog gi dngos grub ces su grags pa gang
NK117(she)001:29464: sbyangs pa las / zhig / mtshan nyid theg pa
NK117(she)001:29465: ltar spang gnyen so sor byed pa'i dka' thub kyis
NK117(she)001:29466: yun ring du mi gdung bar snang cha lha'i skur
NK117(she)001:29467: gsal ba rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK117(she)001:29468: de la rang bzhin ma grub ye shes kyi tshogs
NK117(she)001:29469: te tshogs chen gnyis po de sangs rgyas dang nye
NK117(she)001:29470: ba'i rgyur bsten pa'i dbang rnon rnams ni tshogs sbyor
NK117(she)001:29471: mthong sgom mi slob pa'i lam lngar 'brel ba rnam
NK117(she)001:29472: smin tshe dbang phyag chen lhun grub ste /
NK117(she)001:29473: rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'i them skas nyid las /
NK117(she)001:29474: gnas nges pa 'og min chos dbyings /
NK117(she)001:29475: ston pa nges pa rigs lnga gangs chen mtsho dang /
NK117(she)001:29476: 'khor nges pa nyid las mi gzhan pa /
NK117(she)001:29477: chos nges pa sgra tshig brjod pa dang bral ba /
NK117(she)001:29478: dus nges pa dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dus
NK117(she)001:29479: rnams tshang bar sprul sku longs sku chos sku ngo
NK117(she)001:29480: bo nyid sku mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku ste sku
NK117(she)001:29481: lnga'i zhing du tha mal gyi 'gros kyis ma yin
NK117(she)001:29482: par mig 'phrul lta bur 'gro zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29483: de yang bdag dam tshig pa bskyed pa la ye
NK117(she)001:29484: shes pa dgug gzhug gis gcig tu 'dres pa la
NK117(she)001:29485: sbyor ba'i ting 'dzin nam snyoms 'jug gi tha snyad
NK117(she)001:29486: thob la / 'khor gyi lha rnams rdzogs par bskyed pa la dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog dang /
NK117(she)001:29487: mchod bstod phrin las sogs la las rgyal mchog go //
NK117(she)001:29488: spyir rigs bdag gi rgyas 'debs pa ni sngags kyi gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi mtshon don te /
NK117(she)001:29489: de la mi bskyod pas rigs gzhan bzhi la rgyas 'debs pa ni /
NK117(she)001:29490: de ni sems kyi ngo bo nyid yin la /
NK117(she)001:29491: gzugs sogs ming bzhi'i phung po sems tsam gyi las
NK117(she)001:29492: su zad pas de dag kyang sems su shes par
NK117(she)001:29493: bya ba'i don du rgyas gdab pa ni rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:29494: la rang bzhin gyi rgya zhes kyang bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29495: dbye na gtso bo yab yum rang sems su shes
NK117(she)001:29496: pa la yid kyi ngo bo mi bskyod pas rgyas
NK117(she)001:29497: 'debs pa ni ngo bo la ngo bo nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:29498: rgya / lus kyi ngo bo rnam snang la sems
NK117(she)001:29499: rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pas rgyas
NK117(she)001:29500: 'debs pa ni lus la sems kyi rgya /
NK117(she)001:29501: yid dag pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pa la /
NK117(she)001:29502: lus dag pa rnam snang gis rgyas 'debs pa sems la lus kyi rgya /
NK117(she)001:29503: rgyu 'dod chags dag pa'i ngo bo 'od dpag la
NK117(she)001:29504: 'bras bu ser sna dag pa'i rin 'byung gi rgyas
NK117(she)001:29505: 'debs pa ni rgyu la 'bras bu'i rgya /
NK117(she)001:29506: 'bras bu phrag dog dag pa'i ngo bo don grub
NK117(she)001:29507: la rgyu 'dod chags dag pa'i 'od dpag med kyis
NK117(she)001:29508: rgyas 'debs pa ni 'bras bu la rgyu'i rgya'o //
NK117(she)001:29509: spyir 'khor ba'i phung khams skye mched lhar bsgom pa ni kun brtags la gzhan dbang gi rgya /
NK117(she)001:29510: lha yongs kyi spyi bo rigs bdag gis rgyas gdab pa ni gzhan dbang la gzhan dbang gi rgya /
NK117(she)001:29511: rigs bdag rnams kyi gtsug tu rang rang gi rigs
NK117(she)001:29512: kyi phyag mtshan gyis rgyas gdab pa ni gzhan dbang
NK117(she)001:29513: la yongs grub kyi rgya ste /
NK117(she)001:29514: de ltar mig la rnam snang /
NK117(she)001:29523: reg bya dang chos la mi bskyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29525: chu dang nam mkha' la mi bskyod pa /
NK117(she)001:29527: rlung don grub ste so so'i yon tan gyi cha
NK117(she)001:29528: dang byed las dang mthun pa'i dag la sbyar ro
NK117(she)001:29529: // de ltar bskyed rim gyi sbyor dngos rjes gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:29530: lam de la brten nas sa lam bgrod tshul dang
NK117(she)001:29531: 'bras bu thob tshul sogs rgyas 'grel dang 'og min
NK117(she)001:29532: bgrod pa'i them skas sogs su shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29534: gnyis pa rdzogs pa'i rim pa nyid la yang //
NK117(she)001:29535: pha rgyud rnams las 'byung ba lnga yi rlung //
NK117(she)001:29536: rnam par dag pa'i gsal stong ye shes bskyed //
NK117(she)001:29537: ma rgyud rnams las khams la zhu bde yis //
NK117(she)001:29538: ye shes bskyed phyir rang lus thabs ldan dang //
NK117(she)001:29539: gzhan lus la brten dga' bzhi'i ye shes bskyed //
NK117(she)001:29540: gnyis med rgyud las gcig dang du bral gyi //
NK117(she)001:29541: thig le chen po'i 'od gsal gtsor byed las //
NK117(she)001:29542: zhes pa ni de yang spyir tha mal 'khrul 'byams
NK117(she)001:29543: kyi kun rtog lha sngags ting nge 'dzin gyi rol
NK117(she)001:29544: par bsgyur nas rtog pas rtog pa dag par bsgyur
NK117(she)001:29546: rdzogs pa'i rim pa nyid la'ang dpal gsang ba 'dus
NK117(she)001:29547: pa dang gshin rje'i gshed la sogs rnal 'byor chen
NK117(she)001:29548: po'i rgyud rnams las ni 'byung lnga'i rlung la gnad
NK117(she)001:29549: du bsnun nas zab gsal lam gsal stong rnam par
NK117(she)001:29550: mi rtog pa'i ye shes la gtso bor dmigs nas
NK117(she)001:29551: dngos grub sgrub par byed do //
NK117(she)001:29552: de la'ang gsang 'dus la 'phags lugs dang ye shes zhabs lugs tha dad pa las /
NK117(she)001:29553: snga ma la bden gnyis kyi rdzogs rim dang dben
NK117(she)001:29554: gsum gyi rdzogs rim gnyis su 'dod pas sngon du
NK117(she)001:29555: rang byin gyis brlab pa sgyu ma'i lus kun rdzob
NK117(she)001:29556: kyi bden pa thob dgos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29557: yang shes rab ma'i rgyud yang phur dang /
NK117(she)001:29558: kun 'dus rig pa 'khor lo sdom pa /
NK117(she)001:29559: dgyes rdor sogs rjes su rnal 'byor rnams las ni
NK117(she)001:29560: khams byang chub kyi sems thig le'i rnal 'byor gtso
NK117(she)001:29561: bor byed cing / khyad par gzhan lus la brten
NK117(she)001:29562: nas dga' bzhi'i ye shes kyi zhu bde 'dren pas
NK117(she)001:29563: bde stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i rdzogs rim gtso
NK117(she)001:29568: gzhan yang ma rgyud du grags pa rnams las /
NK117(she)001:29569: dang po snying ga'i thig ler dmigs nas 'byung lnga'i
NK117(she)001:29570: kha dog dang sbyar ba'i rlung 'byung 'jug gis sgrib
NK117(she)001:29571: pa sbyongs shing dngos grub bsdu ba dang /
NK117(she)001:29572: gnyis pa 'khor lo lnga'i phyag mtshan dmigs pa /
NK117(she)001:29573: gsum pa 'khor lo bzhir dga' bzhi'i ye shes ngos 'dzin pa /
NK117(she)001:29574: bzhi pa rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan skur gyur pa las bdud rtsi 'bebs shing gtum mo dang bsre ba /
NK117(she)001:29575: lnga pa snying ga nas 'od zer spros nas brtan g.yo 'od du bzhu ba rnams so //
NK117(she)001:29576: gnyis su med pa'i rgyud rdor sems sgyu 'phrul dra
NK117(she)001:29577: ba dus kyi 'khor lo sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor sogs
NK117(she)001:29578: las ni rtsa thig rlung gsum gyi zhu bde drangs
NK117(she)001:29581: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i thig le chen po'i rnal
NK117(she)001:29582: 'byor gcig dang du bral gyi 'od gsal chen po'i
NK117(she)001:29583: rdzogs rim gsum du 'dod pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:29584: dus 'khor gyi yan lag drug ni /
NK117(she)001:29589: rjes su dran pa dang ting nge 'dzin rnams so //
NK117(she)001:29590: de ni gal po las kyang bshad cing /
NK117(she)001:29591: de'i du ba sogs stong gzugs ni sprul skur gyur la /
NK117(she)001:29593: de la rang bzhin med pa don dam bden pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29595: dngos po thams cad rnam bral ba'i //
NK117(she)001:29596: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK117(she)001:29597: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
NK117(she)001:29598: chos bdag med pa mnyam nyid pas //
NK117(she)001:29599: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NK117(she)001:29600: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:29603: snga ma gnyis ni snang bcas dmigs pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:29604: phyi ma gcig ni snang med 'od gsal te //
NK117(she)001:29605: dang po'i phyogs la gnas pa rtsa dang ni //
NK117(she)001:29606: g.yo ba rlung la bkod pa byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:29607: gsum du gnas pa rdo rje phung po'i grong //
NK117(she)001:29608: zhes pa ni de la phyogs dang po snang bcas
NK117(she)001:29609: rdzogs rim gyi mtshan nyid ni rtsa rlung thig le
NK117(she)001:29610: gsum la gnad du bsnun pa kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:29611: de'ang rtsa gtso bo gsum dang 'khor lo lnga /
NK117(she)001:29612: byed las kyi sgo nas bzhag na rtsa stong phrag
NK117(she)001:29613: bdun cu rtsa gnyis su yod pa sangs rgyas thod
NK117(she)001:29615: de yang rnam par 'gyur ba lha'i bdag nyid du
NK117(she)001:29616: g.yo med du gnas pa la gnas pa rtsa zhes
NK117(she)001:29617: bya'o // de la gnad du bsnun pa'i gtso bo
NK117(she)001:29618: lhan cig skyes pa'i bde ba ster zhing sems can
NK117(she)001:29619: gyi srog tu gyur pa ni a wa d+hu ti'o
NK117(she)001:29620: bya'o // // de lta bu'i rtsa rnams dang rten dang brten pa'i tshul du 'brel ba'i rlung ni /
NK117(she)001:29623: bskyed pa'i byed las can rnam shes kyi bzhon par 'gyur la /
NK117(she)001:29624: khams gsum kun kyang rlung gis 'du byed pa'i phyir g.yo ba rlung zhes brjod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29625: de ltar rtsa rlung gnyis kar brten pa ni bkod pa byang chub sems kyi thig le nyid de /
NK117(she)001:29626: dbye na rtsa ba spros bral gyi thig le /
NK117(she)001:29627: 'khrul pa ma rig pa'i thig le /
NK117(she)001:29628: khams lnga rdzas kyi thig le ste gsum las /
NK117(she)001:29629: dang po ni skye 'gag gnas gsum bral ba'i byang chub kyi sems so //
NK117(she)001:29630: gnyis pa ni ma rig pa /
NK117(she)001:29631: 'du byed rnam shes kyis kun nas brtags shing ming
NK117(she)001:29632: bzhi las 'gyur ba rtogs pa sngags kyi thig le
NK117(she)001:29633: dang / de las gzhan dbang yid kyi nus pa can la rlung gi thig le zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29634: de bas na rnam par shes pa'i rten ni khams byang chub kyi sems yin no //
NK117(she)001:29635: de nyid ma rig pa dang 'brel bas 'khor ba mu mtha' med par bskyed la /
NK117(she)001:29636: thabs kyis zin pas de'i gnyen por song ste mya ngan las 'das par nye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:29637: de ltar rtsa thig rlung gsum rten cing 'brel 'byung
NK117(she)001:29638: du 'tshogs pas gling gsum gyi rten la khams drug
NK117(she)001:29639: ldan gyi mchog gi rdo rje'i lus zhes gsungs la
NK117(she)001:29640: / khyad par 'dzam bu'i gling pa ni dge sdig
NK117(she)001:29641: gi 'bras bu tshe 'dir smin par nges pas na
NK117(she)001:29642: / / las kyi sa pa zhes grags pas nye rgyu'i spyod pa la slob pa yin te /
NK117(she)001:29643: gzhan du bde 'gro yin yang lha dang lha min
NK117(she)001:29644: sgra mi snyan gsum 'bras bu la spyod pas rgyu
NK117(she)001:29647: mi yi mngal gnas 'dzin pa'i thog ma ru //
NK117(she)001:29648: mig gnyis dang ni lte ba'i rtsa mdud chags //
NK117(she)001:29649: de las lus bskyed dwangs mar gyur pa yi //
NK117(she)001:29650: rtsa gsum ka ba lta bur gnas pa'i nang //
NK117(she)001:29651: phyi ru lus ngag nang du nyon mongs gsum //
NK117(she)001:29652: gsang ba sku gsung thugs kyi rten byed pa'i //
NK117(she)001:29653: yi ge gsum gnas dbu ma'i yas mar sna //
NK117(she)001:29654: tshangs pa'i sgo dang gsang gnas gnyis la zug /
NK117(she)001:29655: g.yas g.yon ro rkyang dkar dang dmar ba nyid //
NK117(she)001:29656: bud med nyid la ldog pas rkyang ma g.yas //
NK117(she)001:29657: dbu ma sngo skyar gnyis pos lug rgyud du //
NK117(she)001:29658: mdud pa nyi shu rtsa gcig byas pa la //
NK117(she)001:29659: zhes pa ni de la kun gzhi'i srog rlung dang
NK117(she)001:29660: bcas pa'i bar srid kyi rnam shes khams gsum du
NK117(she)001:29662: 'du shes dang rnam shes kyis nam mkha' mtha' yas
NK117(she)001:29663: sogs su skye ba ni gzugs med khams te yid
NK117(she)001:29664: kyi lus so // bsam gtan bzhi por skye ba
NK117(she)001:29665: ni gzugs khams pa ste 'dod sred rags pa bcom
NK117(she)001:29667: mdor na khams lnga ldan pa'i gnas rigs nyi shu
NK117(she)001:29668: por skyes pa dag ni ma rig pa skye dang
NK117(she)001:29669: bcas pa'o // 'dod khams rigs drug ni 'byung lnga
NK117(she)001:29670: dang ye shes kyi khams te drug ldan zhing phra
NK117(she)001:29671: rags kyi khyad par can skye gnas bzhi dang ldan
NK117(she)001:29672: bcas pa'o // pa'o // 'dir shar lho nub gsum
NK117(she)001:29673: du skye ba'i mi rnams mngal gnas 'dzin pa'i thog
NK117(she)001:29674: mar mig gnyis dang lte ba'i rtsa mdud chags shing
NK117(she)001:29675: bcas pa'o // pa'o // / de las dwangs mar
NK117(she)001:29676: gyur pa gnas tshul dang mthun pa'i dbu ma sngo
NK117(she)001:29677: skya srog rlung dang bcas pa'i yar mar gyi sna
NK117(she)001:29678: gnyis spyi gtsug dang gsang bar zug pa'i yas snar
NK117(she)001:29680: mas snar ma'i rdul a thung du gnas pa'i bar
NK117(she)001:29681: na kun gzhi'i rten srog rlung gnas te mkha' bzhin
NK117(she)001:29682: no // de yang lte 'og man du dung can
NK117(she)001:29683: te dkar cha 'bab cing bde ba bskyed pa'i rtsa'o
NK117(she)001:29684: no // // bud med la rigs can lngas gtums
NK117(she)001:29685: pas sa bon dngos su mi 'dzag cing reg pa'i
NK117(she)001:29686: bde ba phyir zhing 'phel bas lang tsho rgud kyang
NK117(she)001:29688: dbu ma'i g.yas su ro ma dkar mo gnas pas
NK117(she)001:29689: lus dang byang sems bskyed cing khrag dang dri chen
NK117(she)001:29691: g.yon rkyang ma dmar pos ni ngag dang khrag bskyed cing dri chu 'byin sdom gyi las byed /
NK117(she)001:29692: bud med la rtsa gnyis po go ldog tu gnas so //
NK117(she)001:29693: mdor na lus grub phyin rtsa grub cing rtsa grub
NK117(she)001:29694: na rlung dang ye shes sogs kyang grub pas thabs
NK117(she)001:29695: lam zab mo'i gnad kyis grol ba la rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:29696: lus kyi gnas lugs shes dgos pa'i tshul thal 'gyur
NK117(she)001:29697: dang / bi ma la'i dum dum khrigs /
NK117(she)001:29698: rtsa 'khor gyi rang bzhin rgyas par phye ba theg mchog mdzod sogs su shes par bya zhing /
NK117(she)001:29699: gzhan yang rtsa rlung thig le'i gnas tshul rgyas pa
NK117(she)001:29700: dang de dag la brten nas grub gnyis sgrub tshul
NK117(she)001:29701: skyon yon sogs rgyas 'grel du blta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29703: rim bzhin sku gsung thugs sam sku bzhi lnga //
NK117(she)001:29704: phyin drug grangs kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab rnams //
NK117(she)001:29705: phri bsnan gyur pa sbyang gzhi sbyong byed tshul //
NK117(she)001:29706: lte bar drug cu rtsa bzhi mgrin pa la //
NK117(she)001:29707: brgyad tshan gnyis dang snying gar rtsa 'dab brgyad //
NK117(she)001:29708: spyi bor sum cu rtsa gnyis bde skyong na //
NK117(she)001:29709: bdun cu rtsa gnyis de bzhin gtsug tor la //
NK117(she)001:29710: nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lo zhes su grags //
NK117(she)001:29711: 'khor lo re dang so so'i bar mtshams su //
NK117(she)001:29712: 'pho ba bcu gnyis rlung gi dus sbyor dang //
NK117(she)001:29713: de bzhin rten cing 'brel 'byung bcu gnyis gnas //
NK117(she)001:29714: khams la 'pho ba spangs pa'i lugs ldog 'gros //
NK117(she)001:29715: gsang gnas ye shes 'khor lor phyin pa dang //
NK117(she)001:29716: rlung gi 'pho ba gcig dang rten 'brel gcig /'gags nas dang po'i sa yi rtogs pa 'char //
NK117(she)001:29717: rim bzhin nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lo'i bar //
NK117(she)001:29718: rlung dang rten 'brel re re'i cha ldog pas //
NK117(she)001:29719: sa ni bcu gnyis rab tu rdzogs pa'i mthar //
NK117(she)001:29720: thig le nam mkha'i khams dang 'dres pa'i tshe //
NK117(she)001:29721: mngon par 'tshang rgya dang po'i sangs rgyas lugs //
NK117(she)001:29722: zhes pa ni de yang 'khor lo la brten pa'i srog shing lta bu ni dbu ma yin kyang /
NK117(she)001:29723: de nyid dngos por med par 'dod pa yang mi
NK117(she)001:29724: rigs te med na gnad du bsnun pa'i yon tan
NK117(she)001:29725: kyang spangs pa'i skyon yod do //
NK117(she)001:29726: yang kha cig srog rtsa la dbu mar 'dod kyang
NK117(she)001:29727: der rlung sems 'dus na smyo ba'i skyon las yon
NK117(she)001:29729: la la rgyungs pa la 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:29730: dbu ma las rtsa 'dab gyes tshul sogs kyi rnam bzhag dang 'gal lo //
NK117(she)001:29731: don la srog rtsa la ma ltos pa'i dbu ma
NK117(she)001:29732: gsar du 'chos kyang srog rtsa rang rgyud par rlung
NK117(she)001:29734: de'i dbyings su dmigs pa'i chos nyid kyi dbu mar skyon de 'dra ga la 'du /
NK117(she)001:29735: de ltar yin tshul bram ze chen pos rlung dang 'gyu ba rtsal chen srog rtsar bcud nas /
NK117(she)001:29736: tha mal shes pa ngang gis 'gag par 'gyur /
NK117(she)001:29738: de lta bu'ang tha snyad tsam ste dbu ma ni
NK117(she)001:29739: bsgoms pa las byung ba'i rtsa yin pas mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:29740: bzhi ldan du bshad kyang kun gzhi srog rlung dang
NK117(she)001:29741: bcas pa'i rten ni de yin pas spang du'ang mi
NK117(she)001:29742: rung ste srog rtsa bcad nas gnad 'chad pa zhes
NK117(she)001:29744: de'ang gnas tshul gyi ngos nas srog 'dzin pa'i rtsa
NK117(she)001:29745: dbus su mtshan nyid bzhi ldan 'od gsal ba'i rang
NK117(she)001:29746: ba zhin thogs reg dang bral ba zhig lus sems
NK117(she)001:29747: dbugs gsum so sor ma gyes par rtsa de nyid
NK117(she)001:29748: yod pas med pa'ang ma yin la /
NK117(she)001:29749: dbugs yal ba'i tshe de dang lhan cig bltar mi mngon pas dngos po dang bral ba'o //
NK117(she)001:29750: de la a wa d+hu ti /
NK117(she)001:29753: sgra gcan mun pa sogs su grags la /
NK117(she)001:29756: dung can ma sogs ni gzugs can gyi rtsa yin yang dbu mar ming du btags pa tsam mo //
NK117(she)001:29757: don dam dbu ma ni gang la gnad du bsnun pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo nyid yin te /
NK117(she)001:29758: de yang tshig tsam du zad pas ngo bo nyid med pa zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29759: de las gnas pa srog gi rtsa dbu ma dang
NK117(she)001:29760: g.yas g.yon na ro rkyang dang rtsa'i 'khor lo yang
NK117(she)001:29761: / lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK117(she)001:29762: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi bcu drug /
NK117(she)001:29764: spyi bo bde chen gyi sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK117(she)001:29765: gsang gnas bde skyong gi bdun cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK117(she)001:29766: de dag gi sku bzhi dang lnga sogs kyi dag
NK117(she)001:29767: pa dang sbyar ba dang sbyang gzhi sbyong byed kyi
NK117(she)001:29768: dbang du na gtsug tor nam mkha'i 'khor lo bsnan
NK117(she)001:29769: pa'o // de'ang 'khor lo drug dang so so'i bar
NK117(she)001:29770: te bcu gnyis la rlung gi 'pho ba bcu gnyis
NK117(she)001:29771: dang rten 'brel bcu gnyis yod pa'i byed pa bcings
NK117(she)001:29772: pa na khams kyi rnam par 'gyur ba mi brtan
NK117(she)001:29773: par 'dzag med du 'chings nas 'pho ba spangs te
NK117(she)001:29774: lugs las ldog pa'i gsang gnas ye shes 'khor lor
NK117(she)001:29775: phyin tshe las rlung 'pho ba gcig 'gags cing rten
NK117(she)001:29776: 'brel gcig 'dag sa dang po'i rtogs pa skye /
NK117(she)001:29777: de bzhin du 'khor lo re dang bar mtshams re'i
NK117(she)001:29778: gnas su rlung gi 'pho ba re dang rten 'brel
NK117(she)001:29779: re nas sa gnyis pa sogs bgrod /
NK117(she)001:29780: mthar gtsug tor nam mkha'i khams kyi 'khor lor phyin
NK117(she)001:29781: tshe las rlung 'pho ba bcu gnyis po thams cad
NK117(she)001:29782: 'gag cing rten 'byung bcu gnyis po dag nas sangs
NK117(she)001:29783: rgyas kyi go 'phang mngon du byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29785: de dang rnam grangs mthun pa'i rtsa 'dab la //
NK117(she)001:29786: sbyang gzhir gnas pa'i rigs drug sa bon rnams //
NK117(she)001:29787: sbyong byed rig pa'i skyes bu rnam drug dang //
NK117(she)001:29788: pha rol phyin pa drug gis sbyangs pa las //
NK117(she)001:29789: tha dad pa yi ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK117(she)001:29790: bsam gyis mi khyab gcig dang drug 'thob bo //
NK117(she)001:29791: zhes pa ni rnam pa thams cad du bla mar mos gus dang /
NK117(she)001:29792: rdzogs rim gyi smin byed bskyed rim lam du song
NK117(she)001:29793: ba las tshogs gnyis rdzogs nas rlung sems las su
NK117(she)001:29794: rung bas sbyang bya rigs drug gi sa bon rnams
NK117(she)001:29795: sbyong byed thub drug gam phyin drug gi rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:29796: 'khor lo drug tu rgyu ba'i rlung sems thig le
NK117(she)001:29797: dang bcas pa la gnad du bsnun nas sbyangs pas
NK117(she)001:29798: 'khor lo drug dang so so'i bar stong ste rlung
NK117(she)001:29799: dag pas sa bcu gnyis bgrod cing sbyangs 'bras ye
NK117(she)001:29800: shes drug thob nas mthar thug ye shes chen po'i
NK117(she)001:29801: sa bcu gsum pa rdzogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29803: de bzhin snying ga zhi ba'i 'khor lo dang //
NK117(she)001:29804: spyi gtsug khro bo'i 'khor lo rnam gnyis la //
NK117(she)001:29805: lha dang rnam grangs mnyam pa'i rtsa 'dab dang //
NK117(she)001:29806: thabs grol steng 'og lam gyi sgo gnyis su //
NK117(she)001:29807: 'dod pa rgyud kyi rgyal po sgyu 'phrul lugs //
NK117(she)001:29808: zhes pa ni de la sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud kyi
NK117(she)001:29809: lugs la ni 'khor lo gnyis te snying ga zhi
NK117(she)001:29810: ba dang / spyi gtsug khro bo'i 'khor lo'o //
NK117(she)001:29811: de gnyis la snying gar zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa
NK117(she)001:29812: gnyis dang dung khang na khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa
NK117(she)001:29813: brgyad de dam pa rigs brgya'i bdag nyid do //
NK117(she)001:29814: yang 'khor lo drug la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi
NK117(she)001:29815: sbyor bas dga' bzhi'i ye shes bskyed pa la 'khor
NK117(she)001:29816: lo bzhi'i rtsa 'dab gong ltar la lte ba'i dbus
NK117(she)001:29817: su a thung bsgoms pas sa'i dwangs ma zin /
NK117(she)001:29818: snying ga'i dbus su thig le bam dang bcas pa bsgoms pas chu'i dwangs ma zin /
NK117(she)001:29819: mgrin pa'i dbus su yi ge a dang bcas pa bsgoms pas me'i dwangs ma zin /
NK117(she)001:29820: spyi bo'i dbus su ham dang bcas pa bsgoms pas chu'i dwangs ma zin /
NK117(she)001:29821: de yang sgrom mdo rlung gi tsakra bskyed pas sum
NK117(she)001:29822: mdo me'i tsakra te 'khor lo bzhi'i thig le zhu
NK117(she)001:29823: ba las rlung gi dwangs ma zin /
NK117(she)001:29824: dga' bzhi dang 'brel ba'i bde ba'i ye shes rgyud
NK117(she)001:29825: la skyes pa la steng sgo rnam grol gyi lam
NK117(she)001:29827: snying lte mgrin pa spyi bo'i tsakra bzhir kun tu bzang po'i /
NK117(she)001:29830: khyab gdal chen po'i man ngag bzhis bstan to //
NK117(she)001:29831: 'og sgo khams su rol pa'i man ngag la nam mkha' shes rab /
NK117(she)001:29833: de gnyis kyi rol pas rtsa khams nas zhu bde
NK117(she)001:29834: 'dren pa dang rdo rje nor bur bcing ba dang
NK117(she)001:29835: / yum gyi mkhar spro ba sogs 'grel chen du gsal lo //
NK117(she)001:29837: g.yo ba rlung la 'gyu ba che chung gnyis //
NK117(she)001:29838: che ba nyin zhag phrugs gcig dag la ni //
NK117(she)001:29839: nyi khri chig stong drug brgya'i grangs su 'gyu //
NK117(she)001:29840: chung ba kun rtog brgyad khri bzhi stong gi //
NK117(she)001:29841: grangs dang mnyam pa'i bzhon pa lta bur gnas //
NK117(she)001:29842: zhes pa ni de yang g.yo ba rlung la skyes
NK117(she)001:29843: bu dar babs nad med cig nyin zhag rer nyi
NK117(she)001:29844: khri chig stong drug brgya rgyu ba 'gyu ba chen
NK117(she)001:29846: de la rgas pa rnams la lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyis ma tshang la /
NK117(she)001:29847: byis par sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis ma tshang ngo //
NK117(she)001:29848: 'gyu ba chung ngu ni kun rtog gtso che ba'i
NK117(she)001:29849: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong grangs dang mnyam
NK117(she)001:29850: pas de dag gi bzhon par gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:29852: rtsa ba'i rlung ni srog 'dzin me mnyam dang //
NK117(she)001:29853: khyab byed gyen rgyu thur sel lngar gnas pa'i //
NK117(she)001:29854: byed las rim bzhin srog brten me drod bskyed //
NK117(she)001:29855: lus nyams brtas dang dbugs kyi 'gro 'ong dang //
NK117(she)001:29856: 'gro 'dug bshang gci 'phen pa'i bya ba byed //
NK117(she)001:29857: de'ang pho rlung gyen rgyu stod na gnas //
NK117(she)001:29858: mo rlung thur sel smad dang ma ning mnyam //
NK117(she)001:29859: nang gi rlung ni 'byung lnga'i kha dog can //
NK117(she)001:29860: phung po khams dang skye mched gnas pa'i rten //
NK117(she)001:29861: dug lnga dang ni ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK117(she)001:29862: rgyu 'bras lta bur mched pa'i rten byed do //
NK117(she)001:29863: zhes pa ni de la rtsa ba'i rlung lnga las
NK117(she)001:29864: srog 'dzin snying gar gnas te srog brten par byed
NK117(she)001:29865: do // me mnyam lto bar gnas te drod 'bebs /
NK117(she)001:29866: khyab byed lus spyir gnas te nyams brtas par byed /
NK117(she)001:29867: gyen rgyu ro stod na gnas te dbugs 'byung rngub byed /
NK117(she)001:29868: thur sel ro smad na gnas te 'gro 'dug dang
NK117(she)001:29869: gshang gci 'dor ba'i las byed pas phyi'i rlung lnga'o
NK117(she)001:29870: // nang rlung ni sa rlung ser /
NK117(she)001:29881: de dag gis nang phung khams skye mched gnas pa'i rten byed /
NK117(she)001:29882: de yang ma dag pa'i dus na dug lnga mched pa'i gzhi byed la /
NK117(she)001:29883: lam dus su zad par gyi ting 'dzin la brten
NK117(she)001:29884: nas rdzu 'phrul 'grub pa dang dag pa'i tshe ye
NK117(she)001:29885: shes lnga mched pa'i rten byed do //
NK117(she)001:29886: de'ang las rlung gis 'khor ba'i rgyu byed cing sems
NK117(she)001:29887: kyi bzhon par gyur pas rnam rtog sna tshogs pa
NK117(she)001:29889: bying rgod rmug gsum sogs bskyed /
NK117(she)001:29890: gnas mal 'phyugs pas 'khrul snang 'char zhing dus bzhi'i rlung 'gyur ba tshe'i dus byed /
NK117(she)001:29891: mdor na rlung gi bye brag bcu gnyis las nang du lus kyi 'phel grib byed /
NK117(she)001:29893: gsang bar dus sbyor bcu gnyis su byas nas 'khor ba smin par byed do //
NK117(she)001:29894: spyir las rlung srog rtsar zhugs na smyon par 'gyur zhing /
NK117(she)001:29895: de mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i ye shes kyi dbu mar
NK117(she)001:29896: zhugs na sangs rgyas kyi sa dang 'bras bu'i yon
NK117(she)001:29898: khyad par dwangs ma'i rlung lnga d+au tir chud //
NK117(she)001:29899: zad par sa chu me rlung nam mkha' yi //
NK117(she)001:29900: ting nge 'dzin dang yon tan rdzu 'phrul 'grub //
NK117(she)001:29901: gsang ba'i rlung ni ye shes rnam pa lnga //
NK117(she)001:29902: rags pa'i chos dang rnam par 'gal ba yin //
NK117(she)001:29903: zhes pa ni de la srog gi sbyor ba rlung
NK117(she)001:29904: la ma bslabs na khams las su mi rung zhing
NK117(she)001:29906: de las skyes pa'i rdzu 'phrul kyang mi 'grub pas
NK117(she)001:29907: dang po zad par gyi ting 'dzin la dmigs nas
NK117(she)001:29909: de yang srog thur kha sbyar nas nang du thub
NK117(she)001:29910: thang du bzung ba'i mthar dal gyis btang bas phyi
NK117(she)001:29911: nang gi 'byung ba gnyis med du bzung nas 'byung
NK117(she)001:29912: ba so so'i kha dog dbyibs 'khor lo so so'i
NK117(she)001:29913: dbus la sogs par bsgoms pa cung zad brtan dus
NK117(she)001:29917: lte bar me rlung rnams kyi kha dog dang rnam
NK117(she)001:29918: pa can rlung sems gcig tu bcings pas rlung lnga
NK117(she)001:29919: las su rung ba'i rtags su rlung lnga'i kha dog
NK117(she)001:29921: gsal la mi rtog pa'i nyams dang /
NK117(she)001:29922: stong gzugs kyi rnam pa mang du mthong /
NK117(she)001:29923: de yang g.yas rlung dbu mar tshud na du ba /
NK117(she)001:29924: g.yon rlung tshud pas smig rgyu /
NK117(she)001:29925: me rlung las mar me dang 'od /
NK117(she)001:29928: sa rlung las gser mdog dang /
NK117(she)001:29930: mkha' rlung las sngon du mthing ga de nas 'od lnga'i thig le /
NK117(she)001:29931: dbu mar las su rung ba las 'od lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:29938: mdor na lus gnad kyi khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:29939: rlung sems kyi 'du ba ngan pas 'gro drug gi
NK117(she)001:29940: 'khor lo drug tu rlung sems 'dus na bde 'gro
NK117(she)001:29941: dang ngan song gi gnas rigs so so'i yul dang
NK117(she)001:29942: bde sdug gi snang ba 'char ro //
NK117(she)001:29943: de ltar byung na de dag la snying rje chen
NK117(she)001:29944: po bsgoms shing gnas sbyong gi gdams pas 'khrul gzhi'i
NK117(she)001:29945: rtsa ba bcad / khyad par sa chu me rlung
NK117(she)001:29946: nam mkha' dang bcas pa'i rlung dbu mar chud pas
NK117(she)001:29947: zad par sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dang bcas
NK117(she)001:29948: pa'i ting nge 'dzin la dbang bsgyur zhing rdzu 'phrul
NK117(she)001:29949: rtsa ba bcad / 'grub / nang du sems gnas
NK117(she)001:29950: khyad par can dang phyi rol du rigs lnga'i ngo
NK117(she)001:29951: bo 'od kha dog rang mdog gsal zhing dug lnga
NK117(she)001:29952: dag ye shes lnga la spyod /
NK117(she)001:29953: rigs lnga'i zhing du 'gro bar gsungs so //
NK117(she)001:29955: gsum pa bkod pa byang chub sems kyi khams //
NK117(she)001:29956: ro ma las ni zla ba'i bdud rtsi dang //
NK117(she)001:29957: rkyang ma las ni nyi ma'i rdul 'bab cing //
NK117(she)001:29958: pho yi rkyang ma mo yi ro ma'i sna //
NK117(she)001:29959: mdud par gyur pas khams gnyis 'dzag pa bsrung //
NK117(she)001:29960: de las gzhan du ga nyis po las mched pa'i //
NK117(she)001:29961: rtsa mdud kun na dwangs ma dkar dmar gnyis //
NK117(she)001:29962: dpa' bo dang ni rnal 'byor ma'i tshul du //
NK117(she)001:29963: 'khril zhing sbyor bas bde stong mchod pa len //
NK117(she)001:29964: zhes pa ni de la rnam shes kyi rten du
NK117(she)001:29965: gyur pa khams dwangs ma chen po yang khu rdul
NK117(she)001:29966: gnyis kyi rnam par yod pas khu ba ni ro
NK117(she)001:29967: ma'i yas sna nas spyi bo'i ham las 'bab la
NK117(she)001:29968: rdul ni rkyang ma'i mar sna gsang gnas kyi a
NK117(she)001:29969: las 'bab cing / de'ang skyes pa'i rkyang ma dang
NK117(she)001:29970: bud med kyi ro ma'i mdud pa las khu rdul
NK117(she)001:29972: de ltar gnyis po las tsakra'i rtsa 'dab tha dad
NK117(she)001:29973: par gyes pa'i dwangs ma dkar dmar gnyis rtsa mdud
NK117(she)001:29974: kun na dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor ma'i bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:29975: du bzhugs nas zhu bde'i rnal 'byor bsgoms pa las
NK117(she)001:29976: bde stong gi mchod pa len pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:29978: mdor na gnas pa rtsa ni yur ba 'dra //
NK117(she)001:29979: g.yo ba rlung ni 'gro 'ong kha lo pa //
NK117(she)001:29980: byang chub sems ni chu 'dra khrid sar 'du //
NK117(she)001:29981: 'khor lo drug tu brtsegs pa'i sgra gcan dbyings //
NK117(she)001:29982: srog dang rtsol ba'i shing rtas drangs pa las //
NK117(she)001:29983: dbu ma'i mdud pa gnyis gnyis grol ba dang //
NK117(she)001:29984: rlung dang khams kyi dwangs ma rnam gnyis te //
NK117(she)001:29985: sgra gcan ltor zhugs dang po'i sa nas bzung //
NK117(she)001:29986: sa bcu'i yon tan gong 'phel gtsug tor 'gro //
NK117(she)001:29987: zhes pa ni de yang rtsa gnad du 'gro ba la lus gnad /
NK117(she)001:29989: thig le la rtsol ba gal che'o //
NK117(she)001:29990: bye brag tu lus rten rtsa ni yur ba dang
NK117(she)001:29991: 'dra ste rlung rgyu ba'i lam yin pas srog rtsol
NK117(she)001:29992: brten nas rtsa lam sbyang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29993: ngag gi rten rlung ni 'khor 'das gnyis kar 'gro
NK117(she)001:29994: ba'i kha lo pa lta bu yin pas 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:29995: byed pa bcing ba'i gnad la mkhas par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:29996: yid kyi rten thig le ni don dam byang chub
NK117(she)001:29997: sems kyi rten yin pas rlung gnad la brten nas
NK117(she)001:29998: khrid sar 'du bar byas te rnam par 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:29999: med pa ye shes kyi rlung dang lhan cig gtsug
NK117(she)001:30000: tor gyi rtse mor bcing bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:30001: ji ltar bcing na lus bsrangs pas rtsa bsrangs /
NK117(she)001:30003: rlung gis chos nyid mthong ba yin pas lus gnad chos bdun nam /
NK117(she)001:30004: gtsug tor mkha' la drang por gtad pas ltag pa
NK117(she)001:30005: thang zhing mgrin pa sgur ba tsam yong bas des
NK117(she)001:30007: 'dan pa drang por bsrangs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30008: dpung pa mthong bar byas pa /
NK117(she)001:30009: gru mo rtsib mar sbyar ba /
NK117(she)001:30010: sgal tshigs drang por bsrang ba /
NK117(she)001:30011: lag ngar dpyi 'go'i rus par bcar bar barla steng du bzhag pa /
NK117(she)001:30012: mtshang ra gnad la bzhag cing rkang pa skyil krung
NK117(she)001:30013: g.yo 'gul med par bca' ba sogs kyis de rnams
NK117(she)001:30014: dang der 'brel gyi rtsa rnams 'ching ngo //
NK117(she)001:30015: de ltar rtsa'i gtso bo rnams dang de las gyes
NK117(she)001:30016: pa'i rtsa bdun khri nyis stong rnams 'chings shing der
NK117(she)001:30017: rgyu ba'i rlung chings pas der zhon pa'i rnam rtog
NK117(she)001:30019: de la chos nyid kyi dbu ma ni rdzas su grub pa ma yin pas sgra gcan te /
NK117(she)001:30020: phyi ltar de'i gdong mjug gnyis kyis nyi zla bza'
NK117(she)001:30021: bas nang ltar a ham gnyis dbu ma'i yas mas
NK117(she)001:30022: kyi snar gnas pa'i 'bar 'dzag gi ting 'dzin goms
NK117(she)001:30023: pa las dbu mar rlung zhugs gnas thim gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:30025: nyi zla'i rang bzhin khu rdul gnyis dbu ma'i nang
NK117(she)001:30026: du rgyun du 'bab par bsgoms pas byed pa 'ching
NK117(she)001:30027: ba la nus pa thob na phyi rol du nyi
NK117(she)001:30029: rtod la gnon pa sogs nus pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30030: de yang yum gyi bdag nyid can a shad las
NK117(she)001:30031: byung ba'i mes phung khams ma lus za bar byed
NK117(she)001:30032: pas gtum mo zhes bya ste /
NK117(she)001:30033: de nyid 'khor lo drug tu brtsegs pa'i srog shing
NK117(she)001:30034: dbu ma sgra gcan gyi dbyings srog rtsol gyi shing
NK117(she)001:30035: rtas 'khor lo so so'i gnas nas rim gyis drangs
NK117(she)001:30036: pas spyi bo'i ham yig dang reg pa 'phrod pa
NK117(she)001:30037: las dwangs ma dkar por bab pas bde ba skyes
NK117(she)001:30038: pa'i ngang las dar cig glod /
NK117(she)001:30039: de nas ro ma'i dkar cha dang rkyang ma'i dmar
NK117(she)001:30040: cha gnyis dbu ma'i yas mas kyi sna gnyis nas
NK117(she)001:30041: zhugs pa snying gar 'dres pa'i bde gsal zung 'jug
NK117(she)001:30042: gi e wam gyi nyams bskyang ba yin no //
NK117(she)001:30043: de'ang rtsa gnas kyi 'khor lo so sor rlung zin pas thig le zin /
NK117(she)001:30044: de zin pas bde ba zin zhing 'phel ba rlung sems las su rung /
NK117(she)001:30045: dus sbyor bcu gnyis kyi rlung dag pas tshogs sbyor
NK117(she)001:30046: mthong bsgom bzhi'i lam rdzogs pa'i yon tan 'thob cing
NK117(she)001:30047: dbu mar ro rkyang gi mdud pa nyer gcig byas
NK117(she)001:30048: pa grol ba las sa bcu po rim bzhin bgrod
NK117(she)001:30049: cing so so'i yon tan kyang rim bzhin mngon pa'o
NK117(she)001:30050: // dbye na tshogs lam chung ngu la dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi /
NK117(she)001:30051: 'bring por yang dag par spong ba bzhi rnams bshad de /
NK117(she)001:30052: skabs 'dir nye bar len pa'i lha bzhi mchod dgos par bshad de /
NK117(she)001:30053: de yang bsod nams nyer len gyi lha mchog gsum rin po cher /
NK117(she)001:30054: de bzhin du dngos grub nyer len yi dam /
NK117(she)001:30055: 'bras bu nyer len slob dpon dang mched lcam /
NK117(she)001:30056: lus nyer len gyi lha dus gsum gyi pha ma'o //
NK117(she)001:30057: tshogs lam chen por rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi yang bskyed rdzogs kyi don la gcig tu dran /
NK117(she)001:30059: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis dpyod /
NK117(she)001:30060: brjed pa med par sems pas rlung sems las rung gi ting 'dzin dang rdzu 'phrul thob /
NK117(she)001:30061: rmi lam sprul bsgyur sogs las sprul zhing dag par
NK117(she)001:30062: bgrod de chos nyan nas khams kyi dri ma sbyong
NK117(she)001:30063: zhing lha zhal mthong ba'i lung bstan thob pa sogs
NK117(she)001:30064: sbyor lam dang mthong sgom sogs dang rtsa rlung thig
NK117(she)001:30065: le'i yon tan don mthun du brtsi tshul sogs rgyas
NK117(she)001:30068: khyad par sgyu 'phrul dra ba gsang thig lugs //
NK117(she)001:30069: snod bcud rang la rdzogs pa phung po'i grong //
NK117(she)001:30070: dus gsum lung du ma bstan bde gshegs snying //
NK117(she)001:30071: mtha' dag mngon 'tshang rgya ba rdo rje'i gdan //
NK117(she)001:30072: snying ga dpal gyi be'u'i khong seng na //
NK117(she)001:30073: rtsa yi dwangs ma brgyad du gnas pa las //
NK117(she)001:30074: dbus ma gsum ni sku gsum chos nyid rten //
NK117(she)001:30075: mdun ma gcig ni ye shes 'char ba'i rtsa //
NK117(she)001:30076: rgyab na yon tan rtsa las zhing khams 'char //
NK117(she)001:30077: g.yon na rang rgyud rtsa gsum 'khrul snang rten //
NK117(she)001:30078: so so'i dbus na 'khor 'das yig 'bru ni //
NK117(she)001:30079: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed tshul du gnas pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:30080: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ges dag par byed //
NK117(she)001:30081: kun gyi dbus na dwangs ma'i rtsa dkar po //
NK117(she)001:30082: rta rnga'i bcu cha tsam du phra ba'i nang //
NK117(she)001:30083: rdul dang dbugs kyi dwangs ma 'dres pa'i 'od //
NK117(she)001:30084: kha dog lnga pa shin tu phra ba nyid //
NK117(she)001:30085: rang bzhin 'od gsal byang chub sems kyi rten //
NK117(she)001:30086: kun bzang rigs lnga bzhugs pa'i gzhal med khang //
NK117(she)001:30087: gang du rlung sems dwangs ma 'dus pa'i tshe //
NK117(she)001:30088: mya ngan 'das pa'i zhing snang mtha' dag 'char //
NK117(she)001:30089: snang cha'i 'od lnga stong cha'i chos sku gnyis //
NK117(she)001:30090: ro gcig 'dres pa lam gyis tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:30091: 'og min rnam dag stug po bkod pa zhes //
NK117(she)001:30092: gzhan du mi gnas sgrib pa mtha' dag pa //
NK117(she)001:30093: nam zhig spangs pa'i dus der lhun gyis grub //
NK117(she)001:30094: ces pa ni de la phyi snod kyi dang po rlung /
NK117(she)001:30096: sa rnams 'og mas gong ma brten tshul gyis chags shing /
NK117(she)001:30097: de'ang sa las drod 'byung zhing shing lcags sogs me'i
NK117(she)001:30098: rgyur song ba las 'byung bzhi'i rang bzhin du grub
NK117(she)001:30099: pa ltar / rlung sems dwangs mar 'dus pa khrag
NK117(she)001:30100: chu'i rang bzhin gyis gcig tu bsdus pa las nang
NK117(she)001:30102: de yang sa'i rang bzhin sha ste mnyen sha dang
NK117(she)001:30103: grims sha sogs sha sna tshogs pa snying nas mched
NK117(she)001:30104: cing de las me'i rang bzhin lus drod skyes nas
NK117(she)001:30105: dbang po dang kha dog bskyed /
NK117(she)001:30106: me'i rlung bskyed pas dbugs dang bkrag mdangs rgyas par
NK117(she)001:30107: byed cing phyi nang gi 'byung ba de dag bag
NK117(she)001:30108: la nyal dang kun nas ldang ba'i las kyis brtan
NK117(she)001:30109: g.yo chags gnas 'jig stongs byed pa dang mthun par
NK117(she)001:30110: nang lus sems kyi tshogs pa'ang 'byung ba so so'i
NK117(she)001:30111: byed las 'khrugs pas skye rga na 'chi'i rkyen byed
NK117(she)001:30112: pas na snod bcud kyi rang bzhin ni rang gi
NK117(she)001:30114: de'ang dus gsum char lung ma bstan pa'i sems kyi
NK117(she)001:30115: chos nyid bde gshegs snying po can 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK117(she)001:30116: gnas snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo'i rdo rje'i gdan
NK117(she)001:30118: de nyid dbyings zab pas dpal gyi be'u zhes smos
NK117(she)001:30119: nas de'i nang nas 'khrul snang dang ye shes skyed
NK117(she)001:30120: byed dwangs ma'i rtsa phran brgyad du gnas pa'i dbus
NK117(she)001:30121: na sbyang gzhi sbyong byed ltar gnas pa'i sa bon
NK117(she)001:30122: la gnad du bsnun pa'i tshul bi ma las gsungs
NK117(she)001:30123: pa bzhin no // 'di ltar snying khong stong nang
NK117(she)001:30124: na rtsa'i dwangs ma rtsa phran rgyus pa ldad pa
NK117(she)001:30130: de la dbus ma gsum ni sku gsum gyi yi
NK117(she)001:30131: ge chos nyid mi 'gyur ba'i rten yin la 'od
NK117(she)001:30132: snang ser la zlum pa'i dkyil du sbyang gzhi lha
NK117(she)001:30133: min gyi sa bon su dang byol song gi tri'i
NK117(she)001:30134: steng du sbyong byed rgyal ba'i sku rdo rje'i ngo
NK117(she)001:30135: bo dkar po / de'i mdun na ye shes bzhi'i rten las me long ye shes kyi rtsa mthing /
NK117(she)001:30136: gru bzhi pa'i sbubs na sbyang bya lha mi'i sa
NK117(she)001:30137: bon a n+ri dkar dmar gyi steng na sbyong byed
NK117(she)001:30138: thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin h+aum mthing ga'o //
NK117(she)001:30139: g.yon na dug gsum dang khams gsum rang mtshan pa'i
NK117(she)001:30140: 'khrul snang bskyed pa'i rten rtsa zla gam gyi dbyibs
NK117(she)001:30141: can dmar po'i sbubs na sbyang gzhi dmyal ba dang
NK117(she)001:30142: yi dwags kyi sa bon pre du'i steng du sbyong
NK117(she)001:30143: byed gsung rdo rje'i rang bzhin +aahyiga dmar 'od 'tsher
NK117(she)001:30144: ba'o // rgyab rtsa las zhing khams dang gzhal yas sogs dag pa'i snang ba 'char ba ste /
NK117(she)001:30145: gnas tshul la brgyad yod kyang byed las ni bzhi po nyid do //
NK117(she)001:30146: bye brag 'od ser la kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK117(she)001:30149: dmar nag la sgo lnga'i rnam shes gnas so //
NK117(she)001:30150: dwangs ma rgyu tshul ltar na 'od ser rtsa'i dwangs
NK117(she)001:30151: ma dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba la rgyu
NK117(she)001:30152: / mthing ga dbugs kyi dwangs ma la /
NK117(she)001:30154: dmar nag gi sgo lnga'i rtsa 'dab la'o //
NK117(she)001:30155: de'ang rigs drug gi sa bon drug dang 'bru gsum ni 'od ser po dang /
NK117(she)001:30158: dmar nag sogs kyi sgab na gnas so //
NK117(she)001:30159: de la a n+ri su tri pre du rnams dbugs dang rtsa dang khrag gi snyigs ma la rgyu'o //
NK117(she)001:30160: de'ang lha mi gnyis dang byol song dang lha min
NK117(she)001:30161: yi dwags dang dmyal ba rnams su skye ba'i kha
NK117(she)001:30162: zin ni rim bzhin yid shes dang kun gzhi'i rnam
NK117(she)001:30163: shes dang sgo lnga'i rnam shes dang nyon yid rnams
NK117(she)001:30164: kyis byas / sa bon so so la las bsog go //
NK117(she)001:30165: de bas na ma dag pa'i dus las nyon gyis
NK117(she)001:30166: byas pa'i bag chags mtha' dag yi ge drug po'i
NK117(she)001:30168: rtogs pa'i dus na dge ba'i cha dang ye shes
NK117(she)001:30169: kyi rang rtsal rnam par dag pa rnams gsang ba
NK117(she)001:30170: gsum gyi yi ge gsum gyi steng du bsog pas
NK117(she)001:30171: na 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i yi ge 'bru
NK117(she)001:30174: de phyir lus ni ye shes chen po'i rten //
NK117(she)001:30175: 'khor ba nyid na'ang ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul la //
NK117(she)001:30176: nyams dang dman par gyur pa gnyis ka med //
NK117(she)001:30177: 'gyur ba med pa'i don dam byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:30178: til la mar gyis khyab pa ji bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:30179: zhes pa ni 'di ltar sems nyid rang bzhin gyis
NK117(she)001:30180: 'od gsal ba'i khyab byed chen pos 'jag ma'i srin
NK117(she)001:30181: bu yan khyab pa'i phyir 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na'ang
NK117(she)001:30182: rang gi ngo bo nyid las gzhan du gyur pa'am
NK117(she)001:30183: / nyams pa dang dman par gyur pa rdul tsam
NK117(she)001:30184: yang med de dngul chu rdul khrod du lhungs kyang
NK117(she)001:30185: de dang ma 'dres pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:30186: de lta mod kyis bde gshegs snying po'i rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:30187: ni spros bral du yod pas re zhig 'gro khams
NK117(she)001:30188: la rnam shes tshogs kyi sgrib byed dang bcas pas
NK117(she)001:30189: ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang nas nyams 'og tu ma
NK117(she)001:30190: chud bar du rnam par rig pa dang bcas pa'i
NK117(she)001:30191: shes ngo na shin tu lkog tu gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30192: 'di ltar sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin ni sangs rgyas kho nas mkhyen gyis /
NK117(she)001:30194: byang chub sems dpa' sa bcu pas kyang bsam bya ma yin na /
NK117(she)001:30195: rtog ge rig pa la mtha' gcig tu gzhungs pas
NK117(she)001:30196: sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs tshul shes pa ma yin no
NK117(she)001:30197: // de yang lam gyi gnas skabs su blo dag par byed pa rigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30198: rigs pa dag par byed pa lung yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:30199: lung dag par byed pa'ang lung rnams la ltos pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30200: de ltar na 'khor lo tha ma ni 'khor gsum
NK117(she)001:30201: yongs dag gi rang bzhin du gnas pa'i phyir 'di
NK117(she)001:30204: snyam pa'ang gnyis su snang ba'i blo'i gzeb las ma thar ba'o //
NK117(she)001:30206: 'di ltar rdo rje lus kyi gnas lugs dang //
NK117(she)001:30207: gdod ma gzhi yi bzhugs tshul shes byas nas //
NK117(she)001:30208: gtum mo dang ni sgyu lus nying 'khrul lam //
NK117(she)001:30209: 'od gsal bar do 'pho ba rnam pa drug /
NK117(she)001:30210: skyes bu'i rtsol bas 'grub kyis gzhan rkyen la //
NK117(she)001:30211: rag ma lus phyir rang lus thabs kyi lam //
NK117(she)001:30212: zhes pa ni de la rdo rje'i lus kyi gnas
NK117(she)001:30213: lugs theg dman ltar mi gtsang ba'i rdzas so gnyis
NK117(she)001:30214: sogs su blta ba ma yin te /
NK117(she)001:30215: gzugs phung rnam snang sogs su shes pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30216: gdod ma gzhi'i bzhugs tshul kyang yod med yin min
NK117(she)001:30217: la sogs spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba
NK117(she)001:30218: shes par byas nas lam gyi rtsa ba gtum mo
NK117(she)001:30223: blo chod 'pho ba dang drug po ni rang gis
NK117(she)001:30224: rtsol ba'i mthus bsgrub pa kho na las gzhan rkyen
NK117(she)001:30225: la rag ma lus pas rang lus thabs ldan zhes
NK117(she)001:30226: bya'o // de ltar dmigs bcas kyi rdzogs rim drug
NK117(she)001:30227: po rgyas 'grel gyi gzhung du gsal ba dang phyag
NK117(she)001:30228: chen chos drug sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:30230: rtsa thig rlung la gnad du song nas slar //
NK117(she)001:30231: bde stong lam du byed pa gzhan lus te //
NK117(she)001:30232: kun kyang lam du 'gro ba thabs kyi lam //
NK117(she)001:30233: zhes pa ni de la gong du bstan pa'i chos
NK117(she)001:30234: drug po de rig ma la ma brten kyang rang
NK117(she)001:30235: lus la gnad du bsnun nas sbyang du rung bas
NK117(she)001:30236: na rang lus thabs ldan dang /
NK117(she)001:30237: dbang rnon ni lam gyi bogs 'byin du rig mar
NK117(she)001:30238: sbyor dgos par gsungs pa'ang srog rtsol gyi rlung la
NK117(she)001:30239: dbang thob cing 'pho med la gdengs su gyur pa
NK117(she)001:30240: dag gzhan lus la brten pa'i skabs yin pas bde
NK117(she)001:30241: stong gi rnal 'byor lam du byed pa sgyu 'phrul
NK117(she)001:30242: me long sogs las gsungs bzhin rig ma brtags 'gugs
NK117(she)001:30243: bsten tshul sogs rgyas 'grel gyis shes dgos so //
NK117(she)001:30244: de ltar snang bcas kyi rdzogs rim spyi dang phyi
NK117(she)001:30245: rkyen gzhan lus bsten pa la thabs lam du grags
NK117(she)001:30246: pa la sde snod rin po che gsum ka na
NK117(she)001:30247: nyon mongs pa thams cad kyi rtsa bar bstan pa
NK117(she)001:30248: bud med kyang 'dir stong nyid kyi 'byung gnas rgyal
NK117(she)001:30249: yum shes rab pha rol phyin ma'i rang bzhin du
NK117(she)001:30250: bltas nas thabs mkhas kyi cho gas lam du byas
NK117(she)001:30251: pa'o // de bas na nye rgyu de la brten
NK117(she)001:30252: nas rang rgyud ldan gyi gang zag /'phags par skad
NK117(she)001:30253: cig la btang nas bar chad med lam gcig car
NK117(she)001:30254: du skye bas na thabs kyi lam zhes bya ba'o
