NK117(she)001:30256: gnyis pa snang la med pa'i rdzogs rim nas //
NK117(she)001:30257: rnam par gyur pa'i bskyed rdzogs gang yin yang //
NK117(she)001:30258: dag pa'i snod bcud brtan g.yor snang ba kun //
NK117(she)001:30259: 'od du zhu nas snying ga'i sa bon nam //
NK117(she)001:30260: thig ler thim pa de yang mas rim ni //
NK117(she)001:30261: stong par gyur pa nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK117(she)001:30262: ye shes chen po'i spyod yul nyid la bzhag /
NK117(she)001:30263: bskyed rim gyis ni snang ba'i bden zhen 'gog /
NK117(she)001:30264: rdzogs rim gyis ni sgyu ma'i zhen rtog spong //
NK117(she)001:30265: bde gsal mi rtog lhan skyes ye shes 'char //
NK117(she)001:30266: zab pa'i rdzogs rim bla na med pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:30267: bla med rgyud las 'og mar gsungs pa med //
NK117(she)001:30268: dbang rnon tshe gcig rdo rje 'chang 'gro ba'i //
NK117(she)001:30269: nye lam sbas pa shin tu zab mo yin //
NK117(she)001:30270: zhes pa ni de'ang snang bcas rdzogs rim ni gong du bshad ma thag pa ltar yin zhing /
NK117(she)001:30271: gnyis pa snang ba med pa'i rdzogs rim ni gzugs
NK117(she)001:30272: la sogs pa'i rnam par gyur pa'i lha bskyed pa'i
NK117(she)001:30273: rim pa dang rdzogs zhes pa chos drug gang yin
NK117(she)001:30274: yang dag pa gzhan dbang lha'i snod bcud brtan pa
NK117(she)001:30275: gzhal yas khang dang g.yo ba tshogs drug gi yul
NK117(she)001:30276: du snang ba kun kyang 'od du zhu nas snying
NK117(she)001:30277: ga'i sa bon nam thig ler thim pa de yang
NK117(she)001:30278: mas nas rim bzhin yal nas sprin nam 'ja' tshon
NK117(she)001:30279: yal ba'i shul ltar stong par gyur pa ni nam
NK117(she)001:30280: mkha' la ngo bo nyid med pa dang don mthun
NK117(she)001:30281: du gsungs pa de yang ye shes chen po'i spyod
NK117(she)001:30282: yul 'gyur ba med pa la bzhag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30283: de lta bu'i bskyed rim gyis ni snang ba'i bden
NK117(she)001:30284: par zhen pa 'gog cing rdzogs rim gyis ni bskyed
NK117(she)001:30285: rim sgyu ma ltar bzung ba'i zhen rtog kyang spong
NK117(she)001:30286: nus pa'o // de ltar spangs pas bde gsal mi
NK117(she)001:30287: rtog lhan skyes ye shes rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK117(she)001:30288: chos nyid mngon du 'char zhing zab pa'am zab mo'i
NK117(she)001:30289: rdzogs rim stong rkyang ma yin pa'i bde stong bla
NK117(she)001:30290: na med pa rnams mngon du byed pa'i tshul bla
NK117(she)001:30291: na med pa dag rnal 'byor dang rnal 'byor chen
NK117(she)001:30292: po dang shin tu rnal 'byor dang rjes su rnal
NK117(she)001:30293: 'byor rnams las gsungs pa las phyi rgyud ste gsum
NK117(she)001:30294: sogs 'og mar gsungs pa med ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30295: dbang po tha 'bring rab yang rab sogs las dbang
NK117(she)001:30296: rnon tshe gcig rdo rje 'chang gi lam du 'gro
NK117(she)001:30297: ba'i nye lam sbas pa gzhan la ma grags pa'i
NK117(she)001:30298: myur lam shin tu zab mo yin zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30299: de la kha dang lag pa'i rnam par shar ba'i
NK117(she)001:30300: rim gnyis dmigs pa can ni mthar bsam gyis mi
NK117(she)001:30301: khyab pa'i rdzogs rim la bsdu dgos tshul yang bskyed
NK117(she)001:30302: rim skabs kyi dag pa'i snod bcud 'od du zhu
NK117(she)001:30303: nas snying kha'i sa bon la thim /
NK117(she)001:30304: de yang n+aa da'i bar du bsdus bzhin rdzogs rim
NK117(she)001:30305: gyi lhan skyes bde ba chen po'i lha sku yang
NK117(she)001:30306: dmigs bcas yin pas nam mkha' 'ja' tshon dengs pa
NK117(she)001:30307: bzhin bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngang la bzhag pa'o
NK117(she)001:30308: // de'ang n+aa da zhes pa shin tu phra ba'i
NK117(she)001:30309: rlung khams gsum pa'i bdag nyid can sangs ma rgyas
NK117(she)001:30310: bar du gzhom du med pa rnam bcas la brten
NK117(she)001:30311: nas dngos su 'jug pa'i phyi log pa nyid mchog
NK117(she)001:30312: tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po yin pa'i
NK117(she)001:30313: // phyir ro // des na sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK117(she)001:30314: ni spros bral yin pas de nyid la goms par
NK117(she)001:30315: byed pa'i skabs na pha rgyud pa la la bzhin
NK117(she)001:30316: rlung gi thabs las skyes pa'i shes pa gsal ba
NK117(she)001:30317: tsam dang ma rgyud pa kha cig ltar zhu ba'i
NK117(she)001:30318: thig le las skyes pa'i bde gsal tsam don dam
NK117(she)001:30319: pa'i bsgrub byar 'dod nas thabs las byung ba'i dpe'i
NK117(she)001:30320: lta ba kho na la mchog 'dzin byed pa ni
NK117(she)001:30321: gshis kyi bzhugs tshul gtan ma rtogs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30322: 'di ltar thabs las byung ba'i bde ba ni 'dus byas yin phyir don dam par mi rung ngo //
NK117(she)001:30323: de'ang sngags phyi pa gsum las bskyed rim tsam po ba sgyu ma lta bu dang rgyas gdab /
NK117(she)001:30324: dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi bsgom pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30325: thun rjes bsdu ba tsam las /
NK117(she)001:30326: zab pa'i rim pa rnams med do //
NK117(she)001:30328: gsum pa mthun pa'i grogs gyur dam tshig ni //
NK117(she)001:30329: sngags la zhugs pa'i brtul zhugs mi nyams bsrung //
NK117(she)001:30330: thabs dang gnyen po'i rten 'brel ma 'chol ba //
NK117(she)001:30331: rma bya'i mgrin par btsan dug zhugs ltar spyad //
NK117(she)001:30332: ces pa ni de'ang gsang sngags kyi smin grol gnyis
NK117(she)001:30333: dang mthun pa'i grogs su gyur pa'i dam tshig ni
NK117(she)001:30334: / gsang ba sngags kyi sgor zhugs phyin de'i mi
NK117(she)001:30335: mthun pa'i phyogs mtha' dag spang zhing mthun pa'i spyod
NK117(she)001:30336: pa'am brtul zhugs mi nyams par bsrung ba gang zhig
NK117(she)001:30337: gsar rnying gi sngags gzhung rnams na gsal ba'i thabs
NK117(she)001:30338: mang dka' ba med pa'i chos sna tshogs dang /
NK117(she)001:30339: de'i sngon du spang bya dug lnga sogs re zhig
NK117(she)001:30340: gnyen pos rten cing 'brel byung ma 'chol bas rang
NK117(she)001:30341: rgyud du ma shor ba'i thabs la ma rmongs pa
NK117(she)001:30342: rnams ni goms pa stobs su gyur tshe dug lnga
NK117(she)001:30343: sogs la spyod tshe dper na rma bya'i mgrin par
NK117(she)001:30344: btsan dug zhugs kyang de nyid de'i 'tsho ba'i zas
NK117(she)001:30345: mchog tu gyur nas kha dog bkrag mdangs sogs mdzes
NK117(she)001:30346: pa'i byed por gyur ltar spyad par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:30349: de la dam tshig dang ni sdom pa'i khyad //
NK117(she)001:30350: dam tshig 'da' bar bya ba ma yin la //
NK117(she)001:30351: sdom pa bya dang mi bya'i nges pa ste //
NK117(she)001:30352: ngo bo gcig la ldog chas dbye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:30353: de'ang sngags sdom yin na dam tshig 'dres //
NK117(she)001:30354: dam tshig yin na sdom pa 'dres mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:30355: zhes pa ni de la dam tshig dang sdom pa'i
NK117(she)001:30356: khyad par ni smon 'jug gtong ba sogs 'da' bar
NK117(she)001:30357: mi rung ba'i cha thams cad dam tshig dang /
NK117(she)001:30358: gnang bkag la dpyad nas 'jug ldog gnyis su byed dgos mtha' dag sdom par bzhag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30359: de'ang ngo bo gcig ste sems kyi steng na gnyis
NK117(she)001:30360: su grub pa'i gnas med kyang blos dam sdom gnyis
NK117(she)001:30363: kun gyi spyi don sngags sdom ma thob dang //
NK117(she)001:30364: smyo ba la sogs 'du shes rang bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:30365: mi gnas pa la ltung dang dngos grub med //
NK117(she)001:30366: sngags sdom ldan zhing ma nyams ma btang la //
NK117(she)001:30367: shes pa rang bzhin rnal du gnas pa de //
NK117(she)001:30368: ltung ba dang ni dngos grub gnyis ka'i snod //
NK117(she)001:30369: ces pa ni 'di ltar rten gyi gang zag sdom
NK117(she)001:30370: pas ma bsdams pa rnams la ni rang bzhin gyi
NK117(she)001:30371: nyams pa las bcas 'gal gyi cha nas dngos grub
NK117(she)001:30372: dang nyams pa gnyis ka med la /
NK117(she)001:30373: sngags gsar rnying kun gyi spyi don du sngags sdom
NK117(she)001:30374: ma thob pa rnams dang thob kyang smyo ba dang
NK117(she)001:30375: chang dbang la sogs kyis 'du shes rang bzhin du
NK117(she)001:30376: mi gnas pa rnams la ltung ba dang dngos grub
NK117(she)001:30378: dbang bzhi tshul bzhin du thob tshe sngags sdom thob pa yin la /
NK117(she)001:30379: thob pa de nyid ji bzhin du ldan zhing ma nyams pa dang blos ma btang ba rnams la /
NK117(she)001:30380: shes pa rang bzhin rnal du gnas shing skyon gyis
NK117(she)001:30381: ma bslad pa de ni nyams pa'i ltung ba dang
NK117(she)001:30382: bsrungs ba'i dngos grub gnyis ka'i snod du 'gyur zhes
NK117(she)001:30384: byang chub sems las gzhan pa'i rtsa ltung la //
NK117(she)001:30385: kun dkris zhes bya da dung bya ba de //
NK117(she)001:30386: byed 'dod ma log de la 'gyod pa med //
NK117(she)001:30387: rang ngor ltos pa'i ngo tsha shes pa dang //
NK117(she)001:30388: gzhan ngor ltos pa'i khrel yod med pa ste //
NK117(she)001:30389: chos gsum tshang ba'i kun slong bya ba'i mthar //
NK117(she)001:30390: gtugs pa de srid rgyun chags yod gyur na //
NK117(she)001:30391: kun dkris tshang ba'i pham par gyur pa yin //
NK117(she)001:30392: dus kyi bar chad rgyun chags med pa'am //
NK117(she)001:30393: chos gsum gang las cig shos ma tshang na //
NK117(she)001:30394: bya ba'i yan lag ma tshang sbom por 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:30395: zhes pa ni de la byang sems kyi rtsa ltung
NK117(she)001:30396: de'i sde snod du gtan la phab zin bzhin dang
NK117(she)001:30397: / 'dir sngags kyi ltung ba'i yan lag tu sbyor
NK117(she)001:30398: tshul ni lnga pa byang chub kyi sems spong ba
NK117(she)001:30399: kun dkris la mi ltos shing de ma yin pa'i
NK117(she)001:30400: bcu gsum po gang yin kyang nyes spyod de dang
NK117(she)001:30401: de byed cing de las ldog mi 'dod pa dang
NK117(she)001:30403: rang ngor ltos pa'i ngo tsha dang gzhan ngor ltos pa'i khrel yod med pa /
NK117(she)001:30404: de'i steng du nyes spyod gang yin la dga' zhing
NK117(she)001:30405: mgu ba ste chos bzhir dbye ba'ang yod pa'i kun
NK117(she)001:30406: slong bya ba'i mthar gtugs pa de'i srid du rgyun
NK117(she)001:30407: chags su yod par gyur na kun dkris tshang ba'i
NK117(she)001:30408: pham pa zhes shin tu lci ba yin zhing dus
NK117(she)001:30409: kyi bar zhes nyes spyod gang yin de mthar ma
NK117(she)001:30410: thug gong du de la 'gyod pa skye ba'am /
NK117(she)001:30411: rang ngor ltos pa'i ngo tsha gzhan ngor ltos pa'i
NK117(she)001:30412: khrel yod gsum gang rung skyes nas nyes spyod bshol
NK117(she)001:30413: na nyes pa'i bya ba'i yan lag ma tshang bas
NK117(she)001:30415: 'di ltar sngags kyi rtsa ltung ni grangs mang la
NK117(she)001:30416: 'byung nye bas bsrung daka'o snyam pa spangs nas bshags
NK117(she)001:30419: de yis shes bya'i rtsa ba yan lag kun //
NK117(she)001:30420: yid kyis mi spong lus kyis dor mi bya //
NK117(she)001:30421: nyin dang mtshan mo cha drug bgos pa la //
NK117(she)001:30422: cha re'i nang du rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po'i //
NK117(she)001:30423: nyes pa byung ngam ma byung sngo bgrang bya //
NK117(she)001:30424: gos na 'gyod pa bskyed cing phyir 'chos sems //
NK117(she)001:30425: gos pa med na dga' ba sgom zhing bsngo //
NK117(she)001:30426: sngon chad gos sam ma gos gang yin kyang //
NK117(she)001:30427: phyin chad srog la bab kyang nyes byas kyi //
NK117(she)001:30428: gos par mi bya'i sdom sems shin tu bsten //
NK117(she)001:30429: gang tshe cha drug gang yang rung ba'i nang //
NK117(she)001:30430: sngo bgrang byed pa'i 'du shes rmongs gyur na //
NK117(she)001:30431: kha na ma tho sbom po zhes pa 'byung //
NK117(she)001:30432: drug ka 'das na sbom po drug tu 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:30433: zhag de'i khong du phyir bcos ma grub na //
NK117(she)001:30434: phyi ma'i skya rengs dang po 'char ba dang //
NK117(she)001:30435: sbom po bcu gnyis dag tu 'gyur bar bshad //
NK117(she)001:30436: yan lag dam tshig la yang de yis 'gre //
NK117(she)001:30437: zhes pa ni de'i shes par bya dgos pa'i rtsa
NK117(she)001:30438: ba dang yan lag gi dam sdom rnams yid kyis
NK117(she)001:30439: mi spang // lus kyis mi dor bar bya ste /
NK117(she)001:30440: de ltar mi shes pa ni ltung ba'i sgo yin
NK117(she)001:30441: pas dus dang rnam pa thams cad du dran pa
NK117(she)001:30442: nye bar bzhag pa'i sems kyis blta zhing /
NK117(she)001:30443: de yang lus dang 'brel ba'i nyes byas tshar ba dang ltung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK117(she)001:30444: ngag gi yang pha rol po'i go ba dang ltung bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:30445: yid kyi nyes byas ni thun mtshams so so'i nang
NK117(she)001:30446: du gnyen pos ma slebs na rtsa ltung du 'gyur
NK117(she)001:30447: ro // spyir lus ngag gi grogs su yid 'gro
NK117(she)001:30448: ba'i phyir zhag gcig la nyin mtshan cha drug bgos
NK117(she)001:30449: ro // pa la / cha re'i nang du rtsa
NK117(she)001:30450: ltung bcu bzhi po'i bshags tshig 'don pa dang sbrags
NK117(she)001:30451: te nyes pa byung ngam ma byung ha kyang tsam
NK117(she)001:30452: ma yin par zhib tu sngo bgrang ste 'di dang
NK117(she)001:30454: nyes ltung gis gos na 'gyod pa bskyed cing phyir
NK117(she)001:30455: bcos kyi thabs la brtson pa dang gos pa med
NK117(she)001:30456: na dga' ba bsgom zhing de'i dge rtsa 'gro la
NK117(she)001:30457: bsngo zhing sngon chad gos sam ma gos pa gang
NK117(she)001:30459: da phyin chad srog la babs kyang nyes byas phra
NK117(she)001:30460: rags gang gis kyang gos par mi bya ba'i sdom
NK117(she)001:30461: sems shin tu brtan po bsten par bya dgos so
NK117(she)001:30462: // gang gi tshe zhag gcig gi nyin mtshan cha
NK117(she)001:30463: drug tu bgos pa gang yang rung ba'i nang du
NK117(she)001:30464: nyes ltung gis gos min gyi sngo bgrang byed pa'i
NK117(she)001:30465: 'du shes rmongs nas shol 'gyangs su gyur na kha
NK117(she)001:30466: na ma tho ba ste nyes byas sbom po zhes
NK117(she)001:30468: zhag gcig de'i nyin mtshan cha drug ka 'dus par
NK117(she)001:30469: gyur na sbom po drug tu 'gyur ba'i skyon yod
NK117(she)001:30470: phyir zhag de'i khong du phyir bcos kyi cho ga
NK117(she)001:30471: ma grub na zhag de'i phyi ma'i skya rengs dang
NK117(she)001:30472: po 'char ba dang ltung ba de nyid cher 'phel
NK117(she)001:30473: nas sbom po bcu gnyis dag tu 'gyur bar bshad
NK117(she)001:30474: cing yan lag gi dam tshig rnams la yang de'i
NK117(she)001:30477: thog mar bla med spyi la gces pa'i chings //
NK117(she)001:30478: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'i rab dbye 'di ltar brtag /
NK117(she)001:30479: dang po dbang thob slob dpon smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:30480: sngags rgyud tshigs bcad gcig pa yan chad bkral //
NK117(she)001:30481: lam gyi man ngag zab mo ston gsum la //
NK117(she)001:30482: chos kyi 'brel ba'i bsnyen bkur khur bor brnyas //
NK117(she)001:30483: de la sngags kyi dngos grub yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:30484: zhes pa ni thog mar bla med sngags gsar rnying
NK117(she)001:30485: spyi la gces pa'i chings chen po rtsa ba'i ltung
NK117(she)001:30486: ba bcu bzhi'i rab tu dbye ba 'di ltar brtag
NK117(she)001:30487: par bya ste / bcu bzhi po'i rtsa ltung dang
NK117(she)001:30488: po smin byed dbang bzhi thob pa'i slob dpon smos
NK117(she)001:30489: ci dgos sngags kyi rgyud tshigs su bcad pa gcig
NK117(she)001:30490: yan chad kyi don bkrol nas bshad pa'am /
NK117(she)001:30491: lam bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi man ngag zab mo ston
NK117(she)001:30492: pa dang gsum po gang rung la chos kyi 'brel
NK117(she)001:30493: ba'i don gyis bsnyen bkur sogs kyi khur mi blangs
NK117(she)001:30494: shing ci dgar bor nas brnyas par byas na de
NK117(she)001:30495: nyid la sngags kyi dngos grub yod pa ma yin
NK117(she)001:30497: gnyis pa sdom pa gsum dang bslab pa'i gnas //
NK117(she)001:30498: bde bar gshegs pa'i gnang bkag mtshams las 'das //
NK117(she)001:30499: de bzhin mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla ma yi //
NK117(she)001:30500: yul dus la dgongs bka' la khyad bsad yin //
NK117(she)001:30501: zhes pa ni gnyis pa so thar byang sems sngags
NK117(she)001:30502: sdom gsum ka dang de'i bslab gnas rnams la ston
NK117(she)001:30503: pa bde bar gshegs pas gnang ba dang bkag pa
NK117(she)001:30504: ngo ma shes pa'am khyad du bsad nas bsrung mtshams
NK117(she)001:30506: de bzhin du thos bsam sgom gsum gyis rang rgyud
NK117(she)001:30507: btul zhing lta sgom spyod gsum la yi dam byed
NK117(she)001:30508: pa dang 'chad spel sogs bstan pa 'dzin skyong spel
NK117(she)001:30509: gsum la brtson pa ni mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla
NK117(she)001:30510: ma yin te / de yis yul dbang po'i rim
NK117(she)001:30511: pa dang dus skabs su bab min la dgongs nas
NK117(she)001:30512: spang blang ji bzhin nam ma yin gang yang rung
NK117(she)001:30513: ste bka' gnang ba la khyad gsod byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30515: gsum pa dbang gral gcig tu 'dres pa'i mched //
NK117(she)001:30516: bskur zhing brnyas byas dmigs kyis bsal na'ang //
NK117(she)001:30517: mtha' yas sems can bde gshegs snying po'i spun //
NK117(she)001:30518: yin phyir ring dang nye ba'i mched la'ang mtshungs //
NK117(she)001:30519: zhes pa ni gsum pa ni gsang ba sngags kyi
NK117(she)001:30520: dbang gral gcig tu 'tshogs pa la 'dres pa'i mched
NK117(she)001:30521: ces de'ang pho mo'i dbye bas rdo rje spun sring
NK117(she)001:30522: su la'ang skur ba 'debs shing brnyas pa byed pa
NK117(she)001:30523: dmigs kyis bsal na'ang de tsam du ma zad mtha'
NK117(she)001:30524: yas sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po'i spun
NK117(she)001:30525: yin pa dang / de las yang rgyal bstan la
NK117(she)001:30526: zhugs so cog ring ba'i spun dang khyad par sngags
NK117(she)001:30527: la zhugs tshad nye ba'i mched yin phyir nyes ltung
NK117(she)001:30528: spang dgos pa kun la mtshungs so //
NK117(she)001:30530: bzhi pa sbyor ba rtsub pa'i sems can zhig /
NK117(she)001:30531: mthong ba'i chos la las kyis mnar gyur pa //
NK117(she)001:30532: de la dga' ba bsgoms nas byams pa'i sems //
NK117(she)001:30533: gtong ba byang chub sems dpar rab lci na //
NK117(she)001:30534: gzhan bde bral bar 'dod la smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:30535: zhes pa ni de la rtsa ltung bzhi pa ni
NK117(she)001:30536: de'ang bsam sbyor rtsub pa'i sems can bstan 'gror rtag
NK117(she)001:30537: tu gnod cing 'tshe ba can zhig mthong ba'i chos
NK117(she)001:30538: la gsod pa'am brdung brdeg byed pa mer bsreg chur
NK117(she)001:30539: bskyur byed pa sogs rang gis byas pa'i las kyis
NK117(she)001:30540: mnar bar gyur pa mthong ba dag la dga' ba
NK117(she)001:30541: bsgoms nas byams pa'i sems gtong ba byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:30542: dpa' la rab tu lci na /
NK117(she)001:30543: gzhan dag bde ba dang bral bar 'dod pa rnams
NK117(she)001:30544: la nyes pa shin tu lci ba smos ci dgos
NK117(she)001:30547: lnga pa gzhan don gnyer ba'i byang chub sems //
NK117(she)001:30548: spangs pa'i mod la smon sems gtong ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:30549: kun dkris tshang ba'i pham par gyur pa dang //
NK117(she)001:30550: gnang ba'i skabs bdun min par khu ba phyung //
NK117(she)001:30551: zhes pa ni 'di ltar 'gro ba'i don du byang
NK117(she)001:30552: chub bsgrub par bya'o snyam du dam bcas pa ni
NK117(she)001:30553: gzhan don gnyer ba'i byang chub kyi sems yin pa
NK117(she)001:30554: la de spangs nas sems can gyi don du sangs
NK117(she)001:30555: rgyas sgrub pa daka'o snyam pa'i smon sems gtong ba'i
NK117(she)001:30556: phyir dang / kun dkris tshang ba'i pham par 'gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:30557: gsang dbang dang sher dbang ro mnyam par lha mchod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30558: rigs rgyud spel don dang ril bu dang 'chi ltas
NK117(she)001:30559: brtag pa'i dus rnams su gnang ba'i skabs bdun yin
NK117(she)001:30560: pas dbyung du rung zhing de min par nam yang
NK117(she)001:30561: khu ba phyung bar mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:30563: drug pa theg pa gsum ltos rgyal ba'i bka' //
NK117(she)001:30564: dpyas shing ston pas ma gsungs zhes smra dang //
NK117(she)001:30565: las dang dngos grub rgyur rung bstan bcos gzhan //
NK117(she)001:30566: rjes gnang byin rlabs bka' ru ma bltas brnyas //
NK117(she)001:30567: zhes pa ni drug pa theg pa gsum ltos te nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30569: theg pa chen po sogs rgyal ba'i zhal nas gsungs
NK117(she)001:30570: pa'i bka' dang byin gyis brlabs pa'i bka' rjes su
NK117(she)001:30571: gnang ba'i bka' rnams la dpyas btab cing ston pas
NK117(she)001:30572: ma gsungs zhes smra ba dang /
NK117(she)001:30573: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las dang mchog dang thun
NK117(she)001:30574: mong gi dngos grub 'grub pa'i rgyur rung ba'i bstan
NK117(she)001:30575: bcos gzhan gang yang rung ba dag rjes su gnang
NK117(she)001:30576: ba dang byin gyis brlabs pa'i bkar ma bltas nas
NK117(she)001:30579: bdun pa dbang gi cho ga ma byas dang //
NK117(she)001:30580: ma rdzogs nyams dang snod ngan zab mos skrag /'dul ba'i dus skabs gnas kyis bskal pa la //
NK117(she)001:30581: gsang sngags zab mo'i don dang dgongs spyod bsgrags //
NK117(she)001:30582: dmigs bsal yin gyis rjes gnang bzlas lung yang //
NK117(she)001:30583: gsang sgrog ngos 'dzin 'dir ni snod la brtag /
NK117(she)001:30584: ces pa ni bdun pa smin byed dbang gi cho gas smin par ma byas pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30585: bum dbang tsam bskur yang mchog dbang gong ma gsum
NK117(she)001:30586: ma rdzogs pa dang dbang bzhi ka thob kyang dam
NK117(she)001:30587: tshig nyams pa sor ma chud pa dang nyan rang
NK117(she)001:30588: sogs snod ngan dang zab mo'i lta spyod la skrag
NK117(she)001:30589: pa skye ba'i skal dman dang /
NK117(she)001:30590: dus kyis bskal pa ste sngags kyi lta spyod zab mo ston ma ran pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30591: gnas kyis bskal pa ste dgag bya dmigs bsal yod
NK117(she)001:30592: pa rnams la gsang sngags zab mo'i thun mong ma
NK117(she)001:30593: yin pa'i dgongs spyod bsgrags pa rnams dmigs bsal yin
NK117(she)001:30594: gyis rjes gnang dang bzlas lung sogs kyang bum dbang
NK117(she)001:30595: ma thob pa la mi rung don gsang sgrog tu
NK117(she)001:30596: 'gro / ngos 'dzin yang 'dir ni snod brtag ste bya zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30598: brgyad pa gzugs phung rnam snang la sogs lnga //
NK117(she)001:30599: de bzhin skye mched lha skur mi shes pa //
NK117(she)001:30600: sdug bsngal bden par bsgrub pa'i rtog ge'i blos //
NK117(she)001:30601: brnyas dang dka' thub mthu yis lhag par gdung //
NK117(she)001:30602: zhes pa ni rtsa ltung brgyad pa ni gzugs phung
NK117(she)001:30603: rnam par snang mdzad sogs rgyal ba rigs lnga dang
NK117(she)001:30604: / de bzhin du dbang po dang yul sogs skye
NK117(she)001:30605: mched rnams sems pa sems ma sogs lha skur mi
NK117(she)001:30607: gzugs phung sdug bsngal gyi bden par bsgrubs nas dman
NK117(she)001:30608: pa'i rten tsam du bzung zhing rtog ge'i blos mi
NK117(she)001:30609: gtsang ba'i rdzas so gnyis su 'du shes bsgyur zhing
NK117(she)001:30610: brnyas pa dang dka' thub mthu yis lhag par gdungs
NK117(she)001:30613: dgu pa rang bzhin dag pa'i stong nyid don //
NK117(she)001:30614: sangs rgyas kho na'i spyod yul nyid las gzhan //
NK117(she)001:30615: sems can khams dang 'brel ba ldem dgongs su //
NK117(she)001:30616: the tshom zos nas dkri bar spangs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30617: zhes pa ni dgu pa ni rang bzhin dag pa'i
NK117(she)001:30618: stong pa nyid kyi don sangs rgyas kho nas mkhyen
NK117(she)001:30619: pa'i spyod yul nyid las gzhan pa'i sems can gyi
NK117(she)001:30620: khams dang 'brel bar ldem dgongs su gsungs par zad
NK117(she)001:30621: do snyams shing the tshom zos nas rang gi sems
NK117(she)001:30622: nyid stong pa nyid la dkri bar spangs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30624: bcu pa dkon mchog gsum dang bla ma dmod //
NK117(she)001:30625: bstan pa 'jig sogs drag shul cho ga yis //
NK117(she)001:30626: mngon du spyod pa'i yul la sran cing bzod //
NK117(she)001:30627: 'dris shing bshes nas byams par byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30628: zhes pa ni bcu pa ni dkon mchog gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:30629: dbu 'phang smad pa dang khyad par du rang nyid
NK117(she)001:30630: kyi bla ma la smod bskur 'debs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30631: rgyal bstan rin po che 'jig pa'i thabs la brtson
NK117(she)001:30632: pa sogs la mthu dang dmod pa'i las sbyor dang
NK117(she)001:30633: drag shul gyi cho gas mngon du spyod pa zhes
NK117(she)001:30634: tshar bcad pa'i thabs la mi brtson zhing /
NK117(she)001:30635: sdang yul gyis log sbyor la sran cing bzod pa
NK117(she)001:30636: tsam du ma zad 'dris shing bshes par byas nas
NK117(she)001:30637: dgra zla la byams par byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30639: bcu gcig ming bral chos la tshad mas gzhal //
NK117(she)001:30640: chos kyi bdag med blo dang rdzas 'gal bzhin //
NK117(she)001:30641: phung sogs stong par blta ba mchog 'dzin blos //
NK117(she)001:30642: skye med grub mtha' rtog pas 'jal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:30643: zhes pa ni bcu gcig pa ni ming dang bral
NK117(she)001:30644: ba'i chos ni spros bral de bzhin nyid de dag
NK117(she)001:30645: la yod med yin min sogs kyis tshad mas gzhal
NK117(she)001:30646: ba dang / chos kyi bdag med ni blo dang
NK117(she)001:30647: rdzas 'gal ba bzhin yin mod kyang rtog ge'i blos
NK117(she)001:30648: phung khams skye mched sogs stong par bsgrubs pa'i lta
NK117(she)001:30649: ba la mchog tu 'dzin pa'i blos skye med kyi
NK117(she)001:30652: bcu gnyis sngags kyi snod rung gdul bya'am //
NK117(she)001:30653: dad gsum ldan la don gnyer chos mi ston //
NK117(she)001:30654: kun slong ngan pas gzhan sems sun phyung nas //
NK117(she)001:30655: 'dun pa phyin ci log tu kyog pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30656: zhes pa ni bcu gnyis pa ni sngags kyi snod
NK117(she)001:30657: du rung ba'i gdul bya ste bla ma'i man ngag
NK117(she)001:30659: min kyang rang bzhin du dang ba dang 'dun pa
NK117(she)001:30660: dang yid ches kyi dad pa gsum dang ldan pa
NK117(she)001:30661: dag gis rang skal dang 'tshams pa'i smin grol sogs
NK117(she)001:30662: gdams pa don du gnyer ba la chos mi ston
NK117(she)001:30663: pa tsam du ma zad de nyid dad pa'i lam
NK117(she)001:30664: las 'dun pa ldog 'dod kyi bsam pas g.yo sgyu
NK117(she)001:30665: dang chos min la 'jug pa'i ched du bsam pa
NK117(she)001:30666: log par bsgyur te lam min la sbyar ba ni
NK117(she)001:30667: kun slong ngan pas gzhan sems sun phyung nas 'dun
NK117(she)001:30668: pa phyin ci log tu kyog pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30671: bcu gsum spyad bya'i dam rdzas rang rgyud du //
NK117(she)001:30672: bltas nas la la spong zhing la la sred //
NK117(she)001:30673: sngags kyi brtul zhugs ji bzhin nyams 'og tu //
NK117(she)001:30674: ma chud mtha' gnyis mal du 'khyams pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30675: zhes pa ni bcu gsum pa ni spyad bya'i dam
NK117(she)001:30676: rdzas sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga dang bro gar glu
NK117(she)001:30677: tshig rig ma sogs rang rgyud du bltas nas la
NK117(she)001:30678: la rtsog par bzung zhing spong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:30679: la la chags sred kyi spyod cing gsang ba sngags
NK117(she)001:30680: kyi brtul zhugs ji lta ba bzhin du nyams 'og
NK117(she)001:30681: tu ma chud par spang len gyi mtha' gnyis kyi
NK117(she)001:30684: bcu bzhi rnal 'byor ma sogs 'jig rten 'das //
NK117(she)001:30685: ma mo mkha' 'gro la sogs so mtshams 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:30686: 'byung ba lnga yi khams la rang rgyud bltas //
NK117(she)001:30687: dbang gi rten gyur bud med smod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30688: zhes pa ni bcu bzhi pa ni rnal 'byor ma
NK117(she)001:30689: la sogs pa'i ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma 'jig
NK117(she)001:30691: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma la sogs te 'das
NK117(she)001:30692: ma 'das kyi so mtshams 'dzin pa rnams dang 'byung
NK117(she)001:30693: ba lnga yang sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma ki
NK117(she)001:30694: me rlung gos dkar dam tshig sgrol sogs te khams
NK117(she)001:30695: lnga po'i rang bzhin nam dbyings nyid rigs lnga yum
NK117(she)001:30696: chen lnga'i rang bzhin yin kyang de ltar ma shes
NK117(she)001:30697: te rang rgyud du bltas nas 'byung lnga tha mal
NK117(she)001:30698: du bzung zhing brnyas par gyur pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30699: gsang dbang gi rten du gyur pa'i bud med la smod pa byas pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30700: gzhan yang bud med kyi rigs gang la smod kyang
NK117(she)001:30701: ltung bar 'gyur ba'i don rtsod pa'i dus su mi
NK117(she)001:30702: rnams bud med la rab tu zhen pa yin na
NK117(she)001:30703: de rnams 'dul phyir bud med du sprul pa'i lha
NK117(she)001:30704: rnams kyi sgyu 'phrul yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:30705: de ltar rtsa ltung bcu bzhi po ni bsrungs na
NK117(she)001:30706: phan yon dang nyams na nyes dmigs phar phyin theg
NK117(she)001:30707: pa man gyi rtsa ba bzhi las kyang nyes dmigs
NK117(she)001:30709: yan lag gi ltung ba ni /
NK117(she)001:30711: bcu bzhi'i yan lag sdom pa gtong byed kyi //
NK117(she)001:30712: pham pa min yang dngos grub thob pa la //
NK117(she)001:30713: gegs su che ba'i sbom po brgyad yod de //
NK117(she)001:30714: dbang dang dam tshig sdom pas ma sbyangs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:30715: tha mal bud med rig mar bsten pa dang //
NK117(she)001:30716: mtshan nyid 'gal ba'i dran pa'i khron pa nas //
NK117(she)001:30717: cho ga ma yin bzhin pas bdud rtsi len //
NK117(she)001:30718: dbang ma thob dang lhag par dad med la //
NK117(she)001:30719: sku gzugs glegs bam phyag mtshan phyag rgya ston //
NK117(she)001:30720: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus na 'thab rtsod dang //
NK117(she)001:30721: bab col kyal kas brtul zhugs tha mal sbyar //
NK117(she)001:30722: snod ldan dam chos 'dri la shes bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:30723: de las 'gal ba'i snyon dor lan du ldon //
NK117(she)001:30724: sngags kyi lta spyod bskur zhing nyams sad pa'i //
NK117(she)001:30725: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad //
NK117(she)001:30726: sngags rgyud de nyid cho ga mi shes bzhin //
NK117(she)001:30727: rdo rje 'dzin par nga rgyal rdzun dang 'grogs //
NK117(she)001:30728: dbang bskur thob kyang sngags la mi dad pa'i //
NK117(she)001:30729: the tshom can la slar yang gsang ba 'chad //
NK117(she)001:30730: ces pa ni de'ang sdom pa'i rtsa ba bcu bzhi
NK117(she)001:30731: de'i yan lag lta bu'i sdom pa gtong byed kyi
NK117(she)001:30732: rgyu pham pa min yang dngos grub thob pa la
NK117(she)001:30733: gegs su che ba'i sbom po brgyad yod de de
NK117(she)001:30734: dag ni / rang nyid las dbang dang dam tshig
NK117(she)001:30735: dang sdom pa ma thob cing rgyud ma sbyangs pa'i
NK117(she)001:30736: tha mal gyi bud med dad med log lta can
NK117(she)001:30737: dam tshig med pa rig mar bsten pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30738: bud med gang zhig mtshan nyid bzang po dang mi
NK117(she)001:30739: ldan pa'am mtshan ngan yon tan dang 'gal ba'i dran
NK117(she)001:30740: pa'i khron pa ste de'i b+ha ga nas bskyed rdzogs
NK117(she)001:30741: dang lag len mi ldan bzhin du bdud rtsi ste
NK117(she)001:30742: de'i rdul rang stobs kyis len pa la cho ga
NK117(she)001:30743: ma yin bzhin du bdud rtsi len zhes pa dang
NK117(she)001:30744: / spyir bum dbang nas bzung gong ma gsum bcas
NK117(she)001:30745: ma thob pa dang lhag par dad pa med pa
NK117(she)001:30746: dag la sku gzugs dang glegs bam dang phyag mtshan
NK117(she)001:30747: phyag rgya rnams mi gsang bar ston pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30748: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus na chos dang 'jig rten
NK117(she)001:30749: gang thad nas 'thab pa dang rtsod pa dang gal
NK117(she)001:30750: ma mchis lta'i bab col kyal kas brtul zhugs te
NK117(she)001:30751: rtsing spyod sogs kyi tha mal du sbyar ba /
NK117(she)001:30752: gsang ba sngags kyi snod ldan dam tshig thub nges
NK117(she)001:30753: kyis bskyed rdzogs sogs gnad khrol dka' ba dag ma
NK117(she)001:30754: shes nas snying nas dri ba la rang nyid kyis
NK117(she)001:30755: shes bzhin du mi shes par bardzusa nas gang dris
NK117(she)001:30756: pa de las 'gal ba'i snyon dor te dri ba
NK117(she)001:30757: por gshe skur dang 'phya smod sogs mi 'os pa'i
NK117(she)001:30758: lan ldon pa / sngags kyi lta spyod la mi
NK117(she)001:30759: dad cing sgro skur 'debs shing nyams sad pa'i nyan
NK117(she)001:30760: thos dang rang rgyal gyi rigs can nam lam der
NK117(she)001:30761: zhugs pa dag gi nang du zhag bdun du longs
NK117(she)001:30762: lan ldon pa / par bsdad pa / sngags rgyud
NK117(she)001:30763: zab mo'i lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi'i de kho na
NK117(she)001:30764: nyid dang cho ga'i phyag len sogs mi shes bzhin
NK117(she)001:30765: lan ldon pa / par bsdad pa / du /
NK117(she)001:30766: blun rmongs kyi gzhan dbang kho nas rdo rje 'dzin
NK117(she)001:30767: pa chen por rloms nas rang nyid go sa mthon
NK117(she)001:30768: por ma slebs kyang jo bardzusa zol gyis rdzun ris
NK117(she)001:30769: dang 'grogs nas gzhan dag bslu ba /
NK117(she)001:30770: yul dbang bskur thob pa yin kyang gsang sngags rdo
NK117(she)001:30771: rje theg pa la mi dad pa'i log lta dang
NK117(she)001:30772: the tshom can la slar yang gsang ba 'chad pa'o
NK117(she)001:30774: klu sgrub kyis bsdus de bzhin dpa' bo dang //
NK117(she)001:30775: lik+sham ka nas de las don gzhan pa //
NK117(she)001:30776: bsnyen pa dag par ma byas dbang bskur dang //
NK117(she)001:30777: rab gnas sbyin sreg slob ma bsdu bar rings //
NK117(she)001:30778: tshogs 'khor las gzhan phyi dro'i kha zas sogs //
NK117(she)001:30779: so byang bcas pa dgos med 'da' ba yis //
NK117(she)001:30780: bdag nyid sun 'byin dngos grub 'phrogs pa'i rgyur //
NK117(she)001:30781: gsungs pa'i sbom po rnams la'ang brtag par bya //
NK117(she)001:30782: zhes pa ni slob dpon chen po klu sgrub zhabs
NK117(she)001:30783: kyis bsdus don mdzad pa dang de bzhin du dpa'
NK117(she)001:30784: bo dang lik+sham ka ras kyang de dag las don
NK117(she)001:30785: gzhan pa lha gang yin gyi bsnyen pa dag par
NK117(she)001:30786: ma byas bzhin du dbang bskur ba'i rim pa dang
NK117(she)001:30787: de bzhin du rab gnas sbyin sreg bcas dang slob
NK117(she)001:30788: ma bsdu bar rings nas dbang bskur chos bshad sogs
NK117(she)001:30789: rang don ma 'grub gong nas gzhan don byed par
NK117(she)001:30790: rloms pa / sngags lugs kyi tshogs 'khor las gzhan
NK117(she)001:30791: pa'i phyi dro'i kha zas sogs la spyod pa so
NK117(she)001:30792: so thar pa dang byang sems kyi bcas pa'i khrims
NK117(she)001:30793: las dgos pa med bzhin 'da' ba de yis ni
NK117(she)001:30794: bdag nyid sun 'byin byas pa dang dngos grub mi
NK117(she)001:30795: thob cing 'phrogs pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba sogs gzhung chen
NK117(she)001:30796: du ma nas gsungs pa'i sbom po rnams la'ang zhib
NK117(she)001:30797: tu brtag par bya zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30798: de'ang dam zhes pa ni dam pa sangs rgyas kyi
NK117(she)001:30799: zhal nas gsungs pa dang tshig ni der 'brel zhing
NK117(she)001:30800: dam chos sgrog pa'i phrin las so //
NK117(she)001:30802: 'di ltar rnal 'byor bla med thun mong gi //
NK117(she)001:30803: rtsa ltung bcu bzhir b+ha wi lhas bsdus pa //
NK117(she)001:30804: kun la khyab cing yongs su grags pa ste //
NK117(she)001:30805: gzhan du rgyud sde bzhi po'i rang lugs kyi //
NK117(she)001:30806: bcu bzhi'i grangs nges dus kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK117(she)001:30807: spyi rgyud mngon byang sogs las gsal por gsungs //
NK117(she)001:30808: zhes pa ni de'ang phyi rgyud rnal 'byor rgyud dang
NK117(she)001:30809: nang rgyud bla med thun mong gi rtsa ltung thams
NK117(she)001:30810: cad bcu bzhir 'phags yul gyi slob dpon b+ha wi
NK117(she)001:30811: lhas bsdus pa 'phags bod kun la khyab cing yongs
NK117(she)001:30813: gzhan du na rgyud sde bzhi po so so'i rang
NK117(she)001:30814: lugs kyi bcu bzhi'i grangs nges pa dus kyi 'khor
NK117(she)001:30815: lo dang spyi'i rgyud mngon par byang chub pa sogs
NK117(she)001:30816: las gsal por gsungs yod pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:30819: rnal 'byor ldan pa 'achi'am srog gtong sla //
NK117(she)001:30820: rtag tu dam tshig bsrung bar ma byas na //
NK117(she)001:30821: sngags la spyod pa'i skyes bu ngan song dang //
NK117(she)001:30822: sangs rgyas gnyis las 'gro sa gsum pa med //
NK117(she)001:30823: ces pa ni de'ang rnal 'byor ldan pa ste sngags
NK117(she)001:30824: kyi sgor zhugs nas smin grol gnyis dang rim pa
NK117(she)001:30825: gnyis la brtson bzhin dam tshig bsrung ba la rang
NK117(she)001:30826: nyid 'chi ba'am srog gtong bar sla bar bslab dgos
NK117(she)001:30827: phyir rtag tu dam tshig bsrung bar ma byas na
NK117(she)001:30828: / sngags la spyod pa'i skyes bu mchog dman su
NK117(she)001:30829: yin kyang rung ste srid pa 'di nyid zhig pa'i
NK117(she)001:30830: 'og tu mar ngan song gsum dang /
NK117(she)001:30831: yar sangs rgyas kyi sa gnyis las 'gro sa gsum
NK117(she)001:30832: pa zhig med de dper na sbrul smyug dong du
NK117(she)001:30833: chud pa yar mar gnyis gang rung zhig las thad
NK117(she)001:30834: sor 'gro sa med pa ltar ro //
NK117(she)001:30835: des na 'bad pa chen pos dam tshig bsrung ba
NK117(she)001:30836: gal che zhing gal te bsrung ma shes pa'am shes
NK117(she)001:30837: kyang khyad gsod kyis sngags la 'phra yang de la
NK117(she)001:30838: dngos grub med cing des mchod pa phul yang lhas
NK117(she)001:30839: mi bzhes pa sogs skyon che bas spang blang mi
NK117(she)001:30842: de phyir ltung na bdag nyid sun phyung nas //
NK117(she)001:30843: phyir bcos thabs la de ma thag tu 'bad //
NK117(she)001:30844: khyad par rtsa ltung dang po shin tu lci //
NK117(she)001:30845: bla mar bsnyen bkur 'khor gsum yongs dag 'bul //
NK117(she)001:30846: dbang bskur bskyar nas sdom pa sor gzhug cing //
NK117(she)001:30847: nye bar mi gnas bdag 'jug lan mang blang //
NK117(she)001:30848: zhes pa ni 'di ltar sngags la zhugs pa dag
NK117(she)001:30849: phung 'tshengs gnyis ka'i rgyu ni de kho na ste
NK117(she)001:30850: de'i phyir na ltung ba'i nyams nyes byung na bdag
NK117(she)001:30851: nyid sun phyung ste rang gis rang la mtshang brus
NK117(she)001:30852: nas phyir bcos kyi thabs gzhung 'di las gsungs pa
NK117(she)001:30853: ltar la de ma thag tu 'bad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30854: sngags kyi rtsa ba dang yan lag kun las khyad
NK117(she)001:30855: par rtsa ltung dang po bla ma la bsten nas
NK117(she)001:30856: byung ba de lci bas na /
NK117(she)001:30857: bla ma mngon sum du bzhugs na de lugs dang
NK117(she)001:30858: min kyang de nyid kyi cho ga bzhin mchod pa'i
NK117(she)001:30859: tshogs kyis bsnyen bkur mchod yul bla ma mchod byed
NK117(she)001:30860: bdag mchod pa'i nor rdzas sogs dngos por 'dzin pa'i
NK117(she)001:30861: dug gis ma bslad par 'khor gsum yongs dag gis
NK117(she)001:30863: phyir zhing dbang bskur yang bskyar gyis zhus nas sdom pa gsor gzhug cing /
NK117(she)001:30864: nye bar mi gnas shing gzhan yul bgrod pa'am gshegs
NK117(she)001:30865: rjes lta bu yin na bla ma'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK117(she)001:30866: man ngag bzhin bdag 'jug lan mang blangs pas nyes
NK117(she)001:30869: bla ma med na sngags kyi sdom ldan mdun //
NK117(she)001:30870: phyag dang spyod lam dul bas rang gi ming //
NK117(she)001:30871: smos nas rdo rje theg pa'i 'dul ba dang //
NK117(she)001:30872: 'gal ba'i nongs pa 'di dang 'di byung bas //
NK117(she)001:30873: 'chab na bdag nyid bde bar gnas mi 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:30874: 'chab med legs par gsol nas bshags yul gyis //
NK117(she)001:30875: nyes par mthong ngam rang gis mthong lags brjod //
NK117(she)001:30876: yul gyis phyin chad bsdam par byed dam dri //
NK117(she)001:30877: chos bzhin 'dul ba bzhin du spyi bos nod //
NK117(she)001:30878: ces pa lan gsum brjod la thabs legs bya //
NK117(she)001:30879: zhes pa ni bshad ma thag pa ltar bla ma
NK117(she)001:30880: med par gyur na sngags kyi sdom pa dang ldan
NK117(she)001:30881: pa gang rung gi mdun du rang nyid kyi bla
NK117(she)001:30882: ma'i mos 'dun bzhag ste phyag dang spyod lam dul
NK117(she)001:30883: bzhin pas rang gi ming nas smos te rdo rje
NK117(she)001:30884: theg pa'i 'dul ba dang 'gal ba'i nongs pa 'di
NK117(she)001:30885: dang 'di byung bas zhes mi 'chab mi sbod pa
NK117(she)001:30886: gal che zhing gal te 'chab cing sbas na bdag
NK117(she)001:30887: nyid bde bar gnas par mi 'gyur zhing /
NK117(she)001:30888: 'chab pa med par legs par gsol nas slar bshags
NK117(she)001:30889: yul gyis nyes par mthong ngam brjod tshe rang gis
NK117(she)001:30890: mthong lags brjod mthar yul gyis phyin chad bsdam par
NK117(she)001:30891: byed dam dri bar chos bzhin 'dul ba bzhin du
NK117(she)001:30892: spyi bos nod par bgyi zhes pa de nyid lan
NK117(she)001:30893: gsum brjod pa'i rjes la thabs legs bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:30895: gal te phyir bcos 'gyangs na zhag re bzhin //
NK117(she)001:30896: gong 'phel 'gro 'gyur de yi gnyen po ru //
NK117(she)001:30897: stobs bzhi tshang ba'i yig brgyas rtag tu bshags //
NK117(she)001:30898: bcu bzhi'i sngo bgrang brjod pa'i bshags tshig gdon //
NK117(she)001:30899: zhes pa ni de'i phyir na ltung ba phyir bcos
NK117(she)001:30900: shol 'gyangs kyi mi 'gog pa gal shin tu che
NK117(she)001:30901: zhing gal te phyir bcos gal chung lta bus 'gyangs
NK117(she)001:30902: par gyur na zhag re song bzhin nyes byas kyi
NK117(she)001:30903: skyed gong 'phel du 'gro bar 'gyur ba de yi
NK117(she)001:30904: gnyen por / stobs bzhi tshang ba'i bshags pa dgos
NK117(she)001:30905: pa yang rdo rje sems dpa' spyi bor bsgoms pa
NK117(she)001:30906: gnyen por / rten gyi stobs / rang nyid kyi
NK117(she)001:30907: nyes byas kyi las ci bsags la sngo bgrangs byed
NK117(she)001:30908: cing 'gyod sems drag po bskyed pa rnam par sun
NK117(she)001:30909: gnyen por / rten gyi stobs / 'byin gyi stobs
NK117(she)001:30910: / sdig pa'i gnyen por dge ba kun dang khyad
NK117(she)001:30911: par rdo rje sems dpa' las lhag pa med pa
NK117(she)001:30912: shes bzhin du sgrub pa gnyen po kun tu spyod
NK117(she)001:30913: gnyen por / rten gyi stobs / 'byin gyi stobs
NK117(she)001:30914: / pa'i stobs / sngon byas kyi nyes byas la
NK117(she)001:30915: gting nas 'gyod cing phyin chad sdom sems la blo
NK117(she)001:30916: gzhol ba nyes pa la ldog pa'i stobs te bzhi
NK117(she)001:30917: po tshang ba'i sgo nas yig brgya la 'bungs dgos
NK117(she)001:30918: shing bye brag sarba sid+d+hi m+me rang nyid kyi ming
NK117(she)001:30919: smos pa pra yats+tsha zhes bzla bzhin rtag tu bshags
NK117(she)001:30920: gnyen por / rten gyi stobs / 'byin gyi stobs
NK117(she)001:30921: / pa'i stobs / pa dang / rtsa ltung bcu
NK117(she)001:30922: bzhi'i sngo bgrang brjod pa'i bshags tshig dang sbom po
NK117(she)001:30923: dang bcas pa dran shes dang ma bral bar gdon
NK117(she)001:30924: gnyen por / rten gyi stobs / 'byin gyi stobs
NK117(she)001:30925: / pa'i stobs / pa dang / to // zhes
NK117(she)001:30926: gnyen por / rten gyi stobs / 'byin gyi stobs
NK117(she)001:30929: khyad par mdo sgyu sems gsum ring lugs ni //
NK117(she)001:30930: spyi mdor sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK117(she)001:30931: bsrung dang spyad bya yid 'ong mi 'dor dang //
NK117(she)001:30932: shes bya bsgrub pa'i dbye bas nyi shu brgyad //
NK117(she)001:30933: ces pa ni khyad par du nang rgyud sde gsum
NK117(she)001:30934: las tshogs chen 'dus mdo dang sgyu 'phrul zhi khro
NK117(she)001:30935: sems sde ma bu bco brgyad kyi ring lugs ni
NK117(she)001:30936: / spyi mdor rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam
NK117(she)001:30937: tshig nas bsrung bya lnga bsgrub bya lnga dang du
NK117(she)001:30938: blang bya lnga shes par bya ba lnga bsgrub par
NK117(she)001:30939: bya ba lnga ste nyi shu rtsa brgyad po gzhung
NK117(she)001:30940: las shes par bya zhing bsrung dgos pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30941: de'ang bsrung ba'i yul lnga dang bla ma dbyer med pa gtso bor bzung dgos la /
NK117(she)001:30942: de yang brgyud pa'i bla ma spyi dang /
NK117(she)001:30943: rang 'khor ba'i gnas nas dang po chos sgor bcug mkhan la 'dren pa'i bla ma dang /
NK117(she)001:30944: dam tshig phog cing dbang bskur ba ni rdo rje theg pa'i bla ma /
NK117(she)001:30945: nyams chag bshags pa'i yul du gyur pa dam skong gi bla ma /
NK117(she)001:30946: thos bsam gyis shes rgyud bkrol ba ni shes rab rgyud kyi bla ma /
NK117(she)001:30947: bka' mdo rgyud kyi don rtogs par dka' ba sla bar byas pa man ngag ste /
NK117(she)001:30948: de lta bu mngon sum car phog tu shes thabs gnang ba man ngag lung gi bla ma'o //
NK117(she)001:30949: de lta bu'i slob dpon rnams rim gyis gnyan pa shes bzhin bkur dgos pa'i don yin no //
NK117(she)001:30951: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga dang //
NK117(she)001:30952: yan lag bcur bshad rtsa ba'i phyogs la ni //
NK117(she)001:30953: rdo rje slob dpon mi spong bkur stis bsnyen //
NK117(she)001:30954: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa dang //
NK117(she)001:30955: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams par byed //
NK117(she)001:30956: gsang ba'i don rnams gzhan mi bsgrag pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30957: zhes pa ni de yang sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i dam tshig rnam lnga ni /
NK117(she)001:30958: rdo rje slob dpon mi spong bar bkur stis bsnyen
NK117(she)001:30959: pa dang yi dam gang gi dbang thob pa de'i
NK117(she)001:30960: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:30961: spyir yang dag pa'i lta ba zhes rgyu 'bras mi
NK117(she)001:30962: 'gong pa dang khyad par sngags kyi lta sgom spyod
NK117(she)001:30963: pa'i lam du zhugs pa dag la byams shing brtse
NK117(she)001:30964: bar byed pa / gsang bar 'os pa dang gnyer
NK117(she)001:30965: gtad pa sogs kyi don rnams gzhan la mi smra
NK117(she)001:30966: bar byed pa / ba rnams so // rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:30967: yan lag dam tshig sde tshan gnyis su bsdu //
NK117(she)001:30968: dang po'i phyogs ni nyon mongs lnga mi spong //
NK117(she)001:30969: rang bzhin shes pa'i nyon mongs de bzhin nyid //
NK117(she)001:30970: thabs kyis zin pa rma bya dug zos 'dra //
NK117(she)001:30971: ye nas rigs lngar shes pas ye shes 'gyur //
NK117(she)001:30972: zhes pa ni de'ang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams
NK117(she)001:30973: sde tshan gnyis su bsdu ba dang po'i phyogs ni
NK117(she)001:30974: nyon mongs lnga mi spong zhes pa yang theg pa'i
NK117(she)001:30975: mchog dman gyi khyad par las nyan rang gi nyon
NK117(she)001:30976: mongs dngos su spyod pa smos ci yid la 'gyu
NK117(she)001:30978: phar phyin theg pa bas spang len gnyis su byas
NK117(she)001:30979: te spang bya'i nyon mongs 'dogs phyogs la'ang mi sdug
NK117(she)001:30980: pa dang mi gtsang ba'i rdzas so gnyis sogs su
NK117(she)001:30981: gnyen po stobs bskyed de bsgom pa sogs dug gsum
NK117(she)001:30982: po gang la'ang de dang de'i gnyen po bsgom pa
NK117(she)001:30983: yin kyang / sngags kyi sde snod las ni de
NK117(she)001:30984: kho na nyid mngon sum du rtogs pa'i bden pas
NK117(she)001:30985: nyon mongs rang rgyud kyi dngos po can du mi
NK117(she)001:30986: 'char bas rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pas spang
NK117(she)001:30987: yin kyang / du med cing / nyon mongs pa
NK117(she)001:30988: lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas kyi rigs dang rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:30989: dang phrin las yin pas nyon mongs pa spangs nas
NK117(she)001:30990: ye shes bsgrub tu med ces pa'o //
NK117(she)001:30992: gnyis pa'i phyogs ni bdud rtsi chen po lnga //
NK117(she)001:30993: blang bya nges pas chos nyid rol par blang //
NK117(she)001:30994: rigs lnga'i rang bzhin nyid du shes pas blang //
NK117(she)001:30995: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i dam rdzas yin pas blang //
NK117(she)001:30996: mkha' 'gro 'du zhing dngos grub nye bas blang //
NK117(she)001:30997: sangs rgyas kun gyi brtul zhugs yin pas blang //
NK117(she)001:30998: zhes pa ni yan lag gi dam tshig gnyis pa'i
NK117(she)001:30999: phyogs ni bdud rtsi chen po lnga ste dri chen
NK117(she)001:31000: dri chu mo'i rdul pho'i khams dkar po mam sa
NK117(she)001:31001: bcas blang byar nges pas chos nyid la chos nyid
NK117(she)001:31002: rol par blang rigs lnga'i rang bzhin nyid du shes
NK117(she)001:31003: pas blang dngos grub chen po bsgrub pa'i dam rdzas
NK117(she)001:31005: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs 'du zhing mchog thun gyi dngos grub nye bar byed pa'i rdzas yin pas blang /
NK117(she)001:31006: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi spyod pa'am brtul zhugs rdzas su blang dor med par spyod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31008: cha shas dbye ba nyis brgya'i grangs nges ni //
NK117(she)001:31009: nyi shur bsdu ba kun gzigs rong pa'i lugs //
NK117(she)001:31010: zhes pa ni cha shas dbye ba zhes pa gcig
NK117(she)001:31011: la'ang sum cu rtsa gnyis su phye bas drug cur
NK117(she)001:31012: 'gyur la / yan lag gcig nyid las nyi shur
NK117(she)001:31013: dbye bas nyis brgyar 'gyur te bsdoms na sum brgya
NK117(she)001:31014: 'gyur la / drug cu'o // de kun nyi shur
NK117(she)001:31015: bsdu ba 'di shes bya'i gnas kun gzigs pa rong
NK117(she)001:31016: pa chos kyi bzang po'i lugs so //
NK117(she)001:31018: sems kyi phyogs la med dang gcig pu dang //
NK117(she)001:31019: phyal ba dang ni lhun grub zhes grags pa //
NK117(she)001:31020: bsrung mtshams bral la 'da' bya mi dmigs pa'i //
NK117(she)001:31021: ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul dam tshig chings kyis bcings //
NK117(she)001:31022: ye nas nyams med rdo rje rgyal po'i lugs //
NK117(she)001:31023: zhes pa ni de la rdzogs pa chen po ni
NK117(she)001:31024: 'phags lam yin pas ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul la dam
NK117(she)001:31025: tshig chen po bzhi'i chings kyis bcings pa yang dang
NK117(she)001:31026: po ngo bo ka dag spros bral rang byung chen
NK117(she)001:31027: po'i dam tshig ni bsrung mtshams med pa'i chos nyid
NK117(she)001:31028: las mi g.yo ba byar med lhun rdzogs kyi ye
NK117(she)001:31029: shes chen po'i ngo bor gnas pa ni bsrung du
NK117(she)001:31030: med pa dang / gnyis pa ni de ltar phyi
NK117(she)001:31031: nang yul med du rtogs pa'i ngang nas sgo lnga
NK117(she)001:31032: rang yan gyi rig pa la snyam byed kyi blo
NK117(she)001:31033: zhen mi 'jug par chos can chos nyid du la
NK117(she)001:31034: bzla ba la ni phyal ba zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31036: de ltar ngo bo nyid med pa'i chos nyid ka dag gi gdangs la mkhyen cha dang /
NK117(she)001:31037: yon tan gyi tshogs rang bzhin lhun grub tu gnas
NK117(she)001:31038: pa chos can snang bzhi'i nyams len dang mi 'bral
NK117(she)001:31039: ba ni lhun grub kyi dam tshig go //
NK117(she)001:31041: 'di ltar dam sdom gnyis kar yin min gyi ris dang /
NK117(she)001:31044: bdag gzhan gyis rtogs min du 'dzin pa'i blo dang
NK117(she)001:31045: snyam byed gnyis kyi gzhal ba'i dgag bzhag dang pho
NK117(she)001:31046: tshod kyi yin blos rtogs pa thams cad chos nyid
NK117(she)001:31048: bltas pas ma mthong bas rang bzhin gcig tu gnas gyur /
NK117(she)001:31049: tshig gis mi mtshon pas ye shes gcig tu gnas gyur pa'i gcig pu zhes bya'o //
NK117(she)001:31050: bsrung mtshams bral ba'i dam tshig la 'da' bya mi
NK117(she)001:31051: dmigs pa'i ngo bo'i bzhugs tshul de lta bu ni
NK117(she)001:31052: dam tshig chings kyi bcings pa ste ye nas nyams
NK117(she)001:31053: pa med pa rdo rje rgyal po'i zhes theg rtse
NK117(she)001:31054: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi lugs so //
NK117(she)001:31055: de lta na'ang slob dpon chen pos /
NK117(she)001:31056: nga'i sngags sems phyogs 'di lta ba shas che ma
NK117(she)001:31057: 'ongs pa na tshig gi gdengs ni shes te lta
NK117(she)001:31058: ba'i gdengs ma rnyed pa mang po zhig ngan song
NK117(she)001:31059: du 'gro zhes gsungs pa'i dus la bab skabs 'dir
NK117(she)001:31060: sngon byon gyi mkhas grub seng+ge lta bu dag gi
NK117(she)001:31061: rjes su khyi mchong wa mchong mi byed pa'ang mi
NK117(she)001:31062: zlo kha med kyis thal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:31064: lam zhugs rnams kyi rang rgyud dag pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:31065: nyams na phyir bcos rin chen bum pa bzang //
NK117(she)001:31066: dam tshig rnam par bkod pa'i grub mtha' ni //
NK117(she)001:31067: rtsa ba'i bla ma'i sku gsung thugs gsum la //
NK117(she)001:31068: phyi nang gsang ba'i dam tshig gsum tshan gsum //
NK117(she)001:31069: srog gcod mi tshangs spyod dang brku ba spang //
NK117(she)001:31070: pha ma spun sring rang lus chos gang smod //
NK117(she)001:31071: bla ma'i grib 'gong yum gtse spun sring brdeg /
NK117(she)001:31072: gsung gi gsum la rdzun phra tshig rtsub spang //
NK117(she)001:31073: chos smra don sems gnas lugs sgom mi bkur //
NK117(she)001:31074: bla ma'i yum dang spun sring tshig mi brnyas //
NK117(she)001:31075: thugs kyi gsum la yid kyi rnam gsum dang //
NK117(she)001:31076: spyod dang bsgom dang lta ba log pa spang //
NK117(she)001:31077: bla ma lha mched blta bsgom mthun kun sems //
NK117(she)001:31078: zhes pa ni de yang gsang sngags la mos pa
NK117(she)001:31079: tsam gyis lam zhugs pa rnams kyi rang rgyud dag
NK117(she)001:31081: sngon gyi las smon dag pa 'ga' tsam las dam
NK117(she)001:31082: tshig ji bzhin bsrung ba dkon phyir nyams na phyir
NK117(she)001:31083: bcos ni gser sogs rin po che'i bum pa bzang
NK117(she)001:31084: po skyon gyis cung zad zhom yang rang stobs kyis
NK117(she)001:31085: gsor chog pa dam tshig rnam par bkod pa'i grub
NK117(she)001:31086: mtha' ni / rang gi sems kyi gnas lugs ji
NK117(she)001:31087: bzhin ngo sprad mkhan de ni yul mchog dman ci
NK117(she)001:31088: 'dra zhig yin kyang rtsa ba'i bla ma yin pa
NK117(she)001:31089: rgyud kyi dgongs pa tshad ma yin phyir de'i sku
NK117(she)001:31090: gsung thugs gsum la phyi nang gsang ba'i dam tshig
NK117(she)001:31091: gsum tshan gsum gsungs pa rtsa ba kho nas shes
NK117(she)001:31092: par nus phyir dang po sku'i phyi nang gsang gsum
NK117(she)001:31093: ni srog gcod pa phyi mi tshangs spyod nang brku
NK117(she)001:31094: mtha' ni / ba gsang ba'o // de'i 'gres kyi
NK117(she)001:31095: sku'i nang gsum rim bzhin pha ma dang spun sring
NK117(she)001:31096: dang rang lus kyi chos gang rung la smod pa
NK117(she)001:31097: mtha' ni / ba gsang ba'o // rnams so // sku'i gsang ba gsum ni /
NK117(she)001:31098: bla ma'i sku'i grib ma 'gong pa yum gtse ba spun sring la brdeg pa rnams so //
NK117(she)001:31099: gsung gi phyi nang gsang gsum rdzun phra ma tshig rtsub smra ba gsum phyi /
NK117(she)001:31100: chos smra ba don sems pa zhes thos bsam la
NK117(she)001:31101: brtson pa gnas lugs sgom pa gsum nang ste de
NK117(she)001:31102: dag la bkur sti mi byed pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31103: bla ma'i yum dang spun sring gsum gyi tshig la brnyas smod byed pa gsang ba'o //
NK117(she)001:31104: thugs kyi gsum la brnab sems gnod sems log lta gsum phyi /
NK117(she)001:31105: spyod pa dang bsgom pa lta ba gsum log pa ste tshul bzhin ma rtogs pa nang /
NK117(she)001:31106: bla ma dang lha dang mched lcam lta sgom mthun
NK117(she)001:31107: pa kun yid la mi byed bzhin log lta skye
NK117(she)001:31108: ba rnams so // de la lam zhugs pa rnams
NK117(she)001:31109: ni 'bras bu la reg pa ma yin pas gshis
NK117(she)001:31110: kyi bzhugs tshul dam tshig gi chings chen pos bcings
NK117(she)001:31111: pa'i tshig rnams 'khrul du mi gzhug par rang rgyud
NK117(she)001:31112: dag pa'i thabs la 'bad pa ni gal shin tu
NK117(she)001:31113: ba rnams so // che'o // de ltar rtsa ba
NK117(she)001:31114: nyi shu rtsa bdun po ni 'da' ba bya ba
NK117(she)001:31115: ma yin pas dam tshig tu bzhag la thabs kyis
NK117(she)001:31116: zin pa'i cha nas gzhan don du 'gyur min du
NK117(she)001:31117: dmigs nas gnang bkag gnyis su phye ba'o //
NK117(she)001:31119: thabs kyi dbang gyur yan lag nyi shu lnga //
NK117(she)001:31120: tan gan ma byin rdzun smra kyal pa'i tshig /
NK117(she)001:31121: spyad bya lnga ni gnang bkag shes pas spyod //
NK117(she)001:31122: ces pa ni 'di ltar lnga tshan lngar bshad pa
NK117(she)001:31123: rnams ni gsang sngags bla med kyi chos rnams gdod
NK117(she)001:31124: nas rgyal ba rnams kyi rdo rje gsum gyi dkyil
NK117(she)001:31125: 'khor chen por sangs rgyas pa yin na 'khor 'das
NK117(she)001:31126: gnyis ka kun tu bzang po phyag rgyas btab pa
NK117(she)001:31127: / nges pa dag gi dam tshig yin te /
NK117(she)001:31128: de ltar rtogs na chos rnams kun tu bzang po'i
NK117(she)001:31129: zhing khams su sbyor bas rang la nyes pa mi
NK117(she)001:31130: bskyed cing gzhan la phan chen po dang bcas pa'i
NK117(she)001:31131: spang gnyen med pa'i dam tshig la sgra ji bzhin
NK117(she)001:31132: par spyod du dbang zhing des las dang las 'bras
NK117(she)001:31133: dkar nag gnyis ka bskyed par mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:31134: de'ang spyad bya lnga yi sbyor ba ni rtsa rlung
NK117(she)001:31135: las su rung ba dag gi rgyud nas gsungs pa'i
NK117(she)001:31136: mu tra rgyud gzhung bzhin 'dzoms med kyis bsten pa
NK117(she)001:31137: dang sgrol ba yang nyams pa bdun dang zhing bcu
NK117(she)001:31138: tshang ba rnams dngos stobs dang mthu nus sogs kyi
NK117(she)001:31140: ngan song gsum sogs thugs rjes sgrol ba /
NK117(she)001:31141: ma byin len pa gsang sngags la 'os pa'i thod
NK117(she)001:31142: pa mtshan ldan sogs dang khyad par rig ma der
NK117(she)001:31143: mthun bcas thabs sna tshogs kyis blang ba /
NK117(she)001:31144: bstan 'gror gnod 'tshe ldog ched dang phan pa sgrub
NK117(she)001:31145: ched du rdzun smra ba dang ngag tshig rlangs po
NK117(she)001:31148: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nyon mongs lnga //
NK117(she)001:31149: mi spong lnga ni rang rgyud pa dang bral //
NK117(she)001:31150: zhes pa ni de'ang 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du
NK117(she)001:31151: rtogs nas 'byed pa med pa ni gti mug dang
NK117(she)001:31152: / de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la thugs rjes
NK117(she)001:31153: chags pas 'dod chags log rtog can snying rje'i rtsal
NK117(she)001:31154: gyis sgrol ba'i zhe sdang gzung 'dzin gyi chos rnams
NK117(she)001:31155: mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i lta ba sro ma shi
NK117(she)001:31156: ba ste ngar ma chags pa'i nga rgyal /
NK117(she)001:31157: gnyis 'dzin gyi lta spyod chos nyid kyi klong du mi 'dzud pa'i phrag dog ste lnga po ni /
NK117(she)001:31158: yang dag pa'i dug lnga ste sbas don yin no //
NK117(she)001:31161: nang sems can la zhen cing sred pa 'dod chags
NK117(she)001:31162: kun nas mnar bar sems pa zhe sdang khong khengs
NK117(she)001:31163: shing mnyen lcug med pa nga rgyal gzhan 'byor gyis
NK117(she)001:31164: yid la zug rngu bskyed cing phrag tu mi shong
NK117(she)001:31165: ba phrag dog /'di dag spang byar bzung na shes
NK117(she)001:31166: bya'i gnas lugs la nyon mongs pa rang rgyud du
NK117(she)001:31167: mi ldan pa'i don las ldog ste nyan rang gi
NK117(she)001:31168: lam du gol ba'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:31169: des na rgyud la dug lnga gang skyes pa'i rang ldog ma nyams pa lam du 'dod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:31170: gtan tshigs kyis gzhigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:31171: zhe sdang gi gnyen po byams pa bsgom pa sogs spang gnyen gnyis su byed pa /
NK117(she)001:31172: zhe sdang 'gag rjes kyi shes pa rtog med lam
NK117(she)001:31173: du 'dod pa de rnams gang yang theg rtse rdzogs
NK117(she)001:31174: pa chen po'i lam yang dag pa ma yin no
NK117(she)001:31176: shes bya'i gshis la nyon mongs pa rang rgyud ldan
NK117(she)001:31177: ma grub pas dug lnga gang rung skyes dus stong
NK117(she)001:31178: pa las ma 'das pas rang ldog can du mi
NK117(she)001:31179: gnas / gtan tshigs kyis gzhigs pas 'brel pa yang ma grub /
NK117(she)001:31180: spang bya'i gnyen po bsgom pa'i spros pa zhig /
NK117(she)001:31181: so so'i rang bzhin ma 'gags pa'i ngang de nyid
NK117(she)001:31182: chos nyid du shes na las gsog pa'i bya ba
NK117(she)001:31183: byed mi nus shing der brten pa'i bag chags kyang
NK117(she)001:31184: 'du mi byed pas spang du med do //
NK117(she)001:31185: de'ang 'khor ba'i rtsa ba nyon mongs pa yin kyang
NK117(she)001:31186: de spangs pa'i pha rol na ye shes bya ba'i
NK117(she)001:31187: bzang po zhig thob tu med kyang de'i gnas lugs
NK117(she)001:31188: ji bzhin ma shes skyon gyis /
NK117(she)001:31189: nyan thos kyis dug ltar du spong ba dang /
NK117(she)001:31190: rang rgyal gyis sems la skyer mi bcug 'dod nas 'gegs ci thub byed pa /
NK117(she)001:31191: byang chub sems dpa' dge ba'i rtsa ba dang mtshungs
NK117(she)001:31192: ldan du sbyor ba yang tshong dpon thabs la mkhas
NK117(she)001:31193: pas mi nag mdung thung can bsad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:31194: bram ze khye'u skar ma la dga' bas tshong dpon
NK117(she)001:31195: gyi bu mo chags pas gdung ba la phan pa
NK117(she)001:31196: bsgrubs pa / lha lung dpal rdor gyis glang dar ma bkrongs pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:31197: sngags phyi pa bya spyod rnal 'byor gsum gyis rang
NK117(she)001:31198: gi sgo gsum dag par bsgyur ba sogs kyang bla
NK117(she)001:31199: med theg pa'i gnas skabs 'dir chos mnyam pa chen
NK117(she)001:31200: po'i lta ba spros bral dang ting 'dzin gyi thabs
NK117(she)001:31201: la mkhas pa zung du 'jug pas nyon mongs pa'i
NK117(she)001:31202: tshogs rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i chos nyid kyis
NK117(she)001:31203: rgyas thebs pas rang ldog can du mi gnas par
NK117(she)001:31206: dri chen dri chu mam sa rak+ta zil //
NK117(she)001:31207: dang len lnga la gtsang sme'i gnyis rtog 'dral //
NK117(she)001:31208: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dri chen dang dri chu
NK117(she)001:31209: dang mam sa sha chen dang rak+ta mtshan ldan las
NK117(she)001:31210: byung ba 'di rnams gtsang rtsog gi rtog pa ldog
NK117(she)001:31211: pas chos nyid kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK117(she)001:31212: rang gi ngo bos sangs rgyas lngar bsgrub pa dang /
NK117(she)001:31213: nus mthus nad lnga bsal ba /
NK117(she)001:31214: byin rlabs kyi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i rdzas khyad par can yin pas dang du blang bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:31216: phung po 'byung yul dbang po kha dog lhar //
NK117(she)001:31217: shes bya lnga ni shes rab stobs kyis spyod //
NK117(she)001:31218: ces pa ni de la phung po lnga rgyal ba rigs lnga /
NK117(she)001:31220: dbang po dang dbang shes sems dpa'/
NK117(she)001:31222: kha dog lnga rigs lnga dang ye shes lngar shes par bya ba'o //
NK117(she)001:31224: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las de bzhin //
NK117(she)001:31225: bsgrub bya lnga ni rtogs goms mthu yis bsgrub //
NK117(she)001:31226: 'di dag dam tshig gsal bkra'i dgongs pa ste //
NK117(she)001:31227: de bzhin dus 'khor brtul zhugs nyi shu lnga //
NK117(she)001:31228: gsang 'dus sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor zla gsang sogs //
NK117(she)001:31229: zhes pa ni de'ang rdo rje'i rigs dang rin po
NK117(she)001:31230: che dang pad+ma dang las dang de bzhin gshegs pa
NK117(she)001:31231: ste bsgrub bya lnga ni rim gnyis la zhugs bzhin
NK117(she)001:31232: rtogs nas goms par gyur pa'i mthu yis bsgrub ces
NK117(she)001:31233: pa'o // de ltar shes bya lnga dang bsgrub bya
NK117(she)001:31234: lnga po ni phan tshun du ltos grub can yin
NK117(she)001:31235: te shes bya lta ba'i dam tshig de nyid rtogs
NK117(she)001:31236: na sgrub byed sgom pa'i dam tshig yin pas lta
NK117(she)001:31237: sgom zung 'jug tu nyams su blang la de'i ngang
NK117(she)001:31240: dang du blang ba gsum ni spyad bya'i dam tshig yin yang /
NK117(she)001:31241: las dang po pas yid kyis mi spong zhing lus
NK117(she)001:31242: kyis mi spyod la rang gis rang la mi khrel
NK117(she)001:31244: de yang thos nyung bdud kyis phyogs bslad pa kha
NK117(she)001:31245: cig stong nyid rtogs so snyam nas spyod pa 'dod
NK117(she)001:31246: rgyal du spyod pa dag yod kyang rtogs so snyam
NK117(she)001:31247: pa de nyid skyon yin pas rtsing spyod la brtson
NK117(she)001:31248: pa dag sngags lam du zhugs kyang phung 'tshengs shin
NK117(she)001:31250: nyams myong la drod cung zad thob nas gnang bkag
NK117(she)001:31251: gi rim pa ma brjed pas rtog dpyod dang bcas
NK117(she)001:31252: pas dam tshig dang 'gal na spang /
NK117(she)001:31253: mthun na bsgrub pa yin yang ji srid sems la
NK117(she)001:31254: khu 'phrig yod ring la las dang las kyi 'bras
NK117(she)001:31255: bu'ang yod par nges pas nyes spyod kyi mtshan nyid
NK117(she)001:31256: shes par byas nas kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa
NK117(she)001:31257: khrel bag yod pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK117(she)001:31258: gsum pa lhag pa'i dam tshig dang /
NK117(she)001:31259: dus 'khor gyi brtul zhugs nyi shu rtsa lnga sogs rgyas 'grel la blta bar bya'o //
NK117(she)001:31261: sngon dang phyin chad 'gyur ba'i rgyud sde yi //
NK117(she)001:31262: spyi don gyur pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa la //
NK117(she)001:31263: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor smon 'jug tshul khrims gsum //
NK117(she)001:31264: mi bskyod rdor dril phyag rgya bla ma gzung //
NK117(she)001:31265: rin 'byung chos nor mi 'jigs byams pa sbyin //
NK117(she)001:31266: snang mtha' theg pa gsum 'dzin chos rnams bshad //
NK117(she)001:31267: don grub mchod bstod phrin las kun la gus //
NK117(she)001:31268: zhes pa ni de yang sngon dang zhes pa rnying
NK117(she)001:31269: ma dang phyin chad 'gyur ba'i gsar ma'i rgyud sde'i
NK117(she)001:31270: spyi don du gyur pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa la
NK117(she)001:31271: / sangs rgyas rnal 'byor la smon pa dang 'jug
NK117(she)001:31272: pa dang so thar byang sems sngags sdom ste tshul
NK117(she)001:31273: khrims rnam pa gsum bsrung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:31274: mi bskyod par rdo rje dang dril bu phyag rgya bla ma bzung ba'o /
NK117(she)001:31275: rin 'byung la chos kyi sbyin pa dang nor te
NK117(she)001:31276: zang zing gi sbyin pa mi 'jigs byams pa ste
NK117(she)001:31277: bzhi'o // snang mtha' la nyan rang dang byang sems
NK117(she)001:31278: sngags te theg pa gsum 'dzin cing de dag gi
NK117(she)001:31279: chos rnams gzhan la bshad ces pa dang /
NK117(she)001:31280: don yod grub pa la mchod yul bkur zhing sbyin
NK117(she)001:31281: yul skyong ba sogs phrin las bzhi dang las rab
NK117(she)001:31282: 'byams kyi sgo nas kun la gus pa ste bstan
NK117(she)001:31283: 'gro'i don la 'jug pa mi lhod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31285: khyad par bla med rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni //
NK117(she)001:31286: rdo rje'i rigs gyur srog la 'tshe ba'ang //
NK117(she)001:31287: zhing bcu las gzhan dbu mar rlung rtog gsod //
NK117(she)001:31288: rin chen rigs la ma byin blang bya ni //
NK117(she)001:31289: mtshan ldan gzungs dang skal med skye bo'i nor //
NK117(she)001:31290: rdzogs pa'i byang chub rang stobs mthu yis blang //
NK117(she)001:31291: pad+ma'i rigs la ri dwags mig can mchod //
NK117(she)001:31292: stong pa nyid kyi bud med kun tu spyod //
NK117(she)001:31293: las chos dam tshig phyag rgya chen po bsten //
NK117(she)001:31294: 'khor lo'i rigs la sha chen lnga dang chang //
NK117(she)001:31295: las la brdzun tshig sgyu ma lta bur sgrog /
NK117(she)001:31296: ces pa ni khyad par sngags bla na med pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni /
NK117(she)001:31297: rdo rje'i rigs su gyur pa'i gzhan gyi srog la
NK117(she)001:31298: 'tshe ba'i dam tshig la'ang bsgral ba'i zhing bcu dang
NK117(she)001:31299: nyams pa bdun la gtogs pa rnams bsgral ba las
NK117(she)001:31300: / gzhan pa dbu mar las rlung dang rtog pa gsod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31301: rin po che rigs kyi dam tshig la ma byin
NK117(she)001:31302: pa blang bar bya ba ni mtshan ldan gyi gzungs
NK117(she)001:31303: ma dang skal med skye bos bdag gir byas pa'i
NK117(she)001:31304: thod pa mtshan ldan sogs sngags yo byad la 'os
NK117(she)001:31305: pa'i nor rdzas / rdzogs pa'i byang chub ste thar
NK117(she)001:31306: pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang rang stobs
NK117(she)001:31307: pa'i nor rdzas / mthu yis blang / pad+ma'i rigs
NK117(she)001:31308: kyi dam tshig la ri dwags mig can la sogs
NK117(she)001:31309: pa'i mtshan ldan gyi bud med dag dga' bder sbyor
NK117(she)001:31310: ba'i mchod pa dang stong pa nyid kyi bud med
NK117(she)001:31311: ces pa gnas lugs kyi don la mnyam par 'jog
NK117(she)001:31313: de'ang dngos kyi rig ma las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK117(she)001:31314: de'i yan lag gtum mo dam tshig gi phyag rgya
NK117(she)001:31315: yi da rig chos rgya phyag chen mchog tu mi
NK117(she)001:31316: 'gyur ba'o // 'khor lo'i rigs kyi dam tshig tu
NK117(she)001:31317: sha chang gnyis tha mal du ma shor bzhin du
NK117(she)001:31318: spyod cing dam tshig gi rdzas su dmigs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31319: las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig rdzun du smra ba
NK117(she)001:31320: yang gzhan phan gyi bsam pas rdzun tshig sgyu ma
NK117(she)001:31322: de yi yan lag tshig gis gab pa ni //
NK117(she)001:31323: ma bsgral bsgral sogs byang sa dang thun mong //
NK117(she)001:31324: lha dang lha min gsang ba pa mi brnyas //
NK117(she)001:31325: phyag rgya bzhon pa mtshon cha mtshan ma la //
NK117(she)001:31326: smad par mi bya'i gnyis ni dngos bstan te //
NK117(she)001:31327: gsang ba gnod sbyin phyag rgya sku gzugs rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:31328: bzhon pa bla ma'i stan dang chibs la sogs //
NK117(she)001:31329: mtshon cha lha yi ched du byas pa'i rigs //
NK117(she)001:31330: mtshan ma phyag mtshan lha dang bla ma dang //
NK117(she)001:31331: mchod rten grib ma 'gom la smad pa'i sgra //
NK117(she)001:31332: de bzhin mchod rdzas rnyings la dman mar grags //
NK117(she)001:31333: phyag mtshan rnam pa'ang bza' bar bkag pa yin //
NK117(she)001:31334: zhes pa ni de yi zhes pa rigs lnga'i dam
NK117(she)001:31335: tshig gi yan lag tshig gis gsal bar ma byas
NK117(she)001:31337: ma bsgral bsgral sogs byang chub sems dpa'i sa las
NK117(she)001:31338: bshad pa dang thun mong yin zhing de'ang ma bsgral
NK117(she)001:31339: ba ni shes sgrib kyi bag chags las ma bsgral
NK117(she)001:31340: ba'i nyan rang dgra bcom pa'i tshogs dang /
NK117(she)001:31341: ma grol ba ni sgrib gnyis kyi 'ching ba las
NK117(she)001:31342: ma grol ba'i tshangs pa la sogs so skye nas
NK117(she)001:31344: dbugs ma phyin pa dmyal ba sogs ngan song gsum
NK117(she)001:31345: sdug bsngal las dbugs 'byin ma thob pa dag dbugs
NK117(she)001:31346: dbyung ba / mdor na sems can thams cad myang 'das la 'god pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31347: lha dang lha min dang gsang ba pa gnod sbyin
NK117(she)001:31348: te dam la gnas shing bstan pa skyong bas mi
NK117(she)001:31349: brnyas pa dang / phyag rgya bzhi ka mi smad
NK117(she)001:31350: cing khyad par lha'i sku gzugs rdzogs pa ni mngon
NK117(she)001:31351: brnyas pa dang / gyur pa / bzhon pa bla ma'i chibs dang khri stan sogs /
NK117(she)001:31352: mtshon cha ni lha'i phyag mtshan gyi rigs /
NK117(she)001:31353: mtshan ma ni rigs lnga'i sa bon phyag mtshan dang /
NK117(she)001:31354: gzhan yang bla ma dang mchod rten gyi grib ma 'gong ba la smad pa'i sgrar bstan la /
NK117(she)001:31355: dman pa ni mchod ro gang rung 'gong ba'am bza' ba mi gtsang ba'i gnas su bsgyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:31356: phyag mtshan rdo rje ral gri sogs kyi gzugs bcos pa'ang bza' mi rung zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31358: khyad par gsod dang ma byin len pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:31359: dngos bstan nyid dam dgongs pa lung ston gyi //
NK117(she)001:31360: rnam dbye ma phyed sngags pa thur la ltung //
NK117(she)001:31361: zhes pa ni de la khyad par sngags kyi theg
NK117(she)001:31362: pa ldem por dgongs pa gzhan gyis mi shes pas
NK117(she)001:31364: gtsug lag khang gi zas nor ma byin par len
NK117(she)001:31365: pa sogs dngos bstan nyid dam dgongs pa lung ston
NK117(she)001:31366: gang yin gyi rnam dbye ma phyed pa'i sngags la
NK117(she)001:31367: spyod rloms la la thur la ltung zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31368: de lta na'ang gshis kyi bzhugs tshul mngon du gyur
NK117(she)001:31369: pa'i tshe bcas pa'i ltung ba ni chos can kun
NK117(she)001:31370: rdzob bden pa'i ngo bo gsog dang gsob dang rmi
NK117(she)001:31371: lam lta bu ya ma barla'i rang bzhin skye 'jig
NK117(she)001:31372: dang bcas pas rang mtshan 'dzin par mi nus pas
NK117(she)001:31373: chos kyi dbyings dge sdig las 'das pa'i ngang du
NK117(she)001:31376: mdor na gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs pa //
NK117(she)001:31377: sbas pa'i gsang bar mngon 'chal kun la gzur //
NK117(she)001:31378: zhes pa ni mdor bsdu na /
NK117(she)001:31379: gab pa'i gsang ba zhes sngags lam du gsungs shing
NK117(she)001:31380: gong 'og na gsal ba rnams ji bzhin ma rtogs
NK117(she)001:31381: pa la sbyor sgrol sogs sbas pa'i gsang rnams sgra
NK117(she)001:31382: ji bzhin par bsten nas gsang bar gdams pa'i rgya
NK117(she)001:31383: las 'das nas mngon par 'chal ba ste kun la
NK117(she)001:31384: spel zhing de'i dpang po rang nyid kyis byed pa
NK117(she)001:31385: lta bu la gzur zhes pa lags shing /
NK117(she)001:31386: de ltar ma yin pas rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK117(she)001:31387: la gnang bkag tshul bzhin du shes par spyad na
NK117(she)001:31388: lam gzhan pas khyad par 'phags shing myur zhes pa'o
NK117(she)001:31390: nyin bzhin bram ze gsod dang mtshams med spyod //
NK117(she)001:31391: sngags sdom skye ba'i rten du rung bas na //
NK117(she)001:31392: gsang sngags thabs kyis che ba smos ci dgos //
NK117(she)001:31393: zhes pa ni de yang gsang ba sngags kyi lta
NK117(she)001:31394: sgom spyod 'bras bzhi ston nus pa'i bla ma la
NK117(she)001:31395: bsten bzhin dam tshig la skyon ma bzhugs na /
NK117(she)001:31396: nyin re bzhin du bram ze gsod pa dang mtshams med pa lnga la spyod pa dag kyang /
NK117(she)001:31397: sngags kyi sdom pa skye ba'i rten du rung bas
NK117(she)001:31398: na gsang ba sngags zhes thabs kyi che ba yin
NK117(she)001:31399: pa smos ci dgos zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:31401: ltung mtshams mi shes bla mar mi gus dang //
NK117(she)001:31402: bag med la goms nyon mongs mthu che bzhi //
NK117(she)001:31403: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi de'i steng du //
NK117(she)001:31404: brjed ngas che dang dran pa mi gsal ba //
NK117(she)001:31405: bsnan pa dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu drug yin //
NK117(she)001:31406: de bas dran dang shes bzhin gnyen po yi //
NK117(she)001:31407: long ba dbye ba'i gnas skabs thob pa'i bag /
NK117(she)001:31408: bsrung ba ji bzhin nyin mtshan thun drug tu //
NK117(she)001:31409: spang blang gnas la bsgrims shing bsgrims shing dpyad //
NK117(she)001:31410: ces pa ni de la dam tshig gi blang dor
NK117(she)001:31411: gyi mtshams mi shes pa ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo
NK117(she)001:31412: dang po yin pa dang de'i steng du bla mar
NK117(she)001:31414: bag med pa ste dam tshig nyams chag la dogs
NK117(she)001:31415: zon med bzhin spyod pa la goms shing nyon mongs
NK117(she)001:31416: pa mthu che ba dang bzhi po 'di ni ltung
NK117(she)001:31417: ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi yin cing de'i steng du'ang
NK117(she)001:31418: spang blang sogs brjed ngas che ba dang dran pa
NK117(she)001:31419: mi gsal ba gnyis bsnan pa dam tshig nyams pa'i
NK117(she)001:31421: de bas na dran pa dang shes bzhin gyi gnyen
NK117(she)001:31422: po lhod med du bsten pa mig long ba dag
NK117(she)001:31423: mig 'byed mkhan gyis dbye ba'i skabs thob pa'i bag
NK117(she)001:31424: ste dogs zon byed pa ltar bsrung ba ji bzhin
NK117(she)001:31425: nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum thun drug tu spang
NK117(she)001:31426: rgyu dang blang rgyu'i gnas kun la bsgrims shing bsgrims
NK117(she)001:31427: shing ste zlos pa yang gal chen du gdams pa'o
NK117(she)001:31429: nyams na gso ba'ang 'og ma las 'phags te //
NK117(she)001:31430: nyan thos sdom khrims 'chab sems ma skyes na //
NK117(she)001:31431: lan bdun gsor yod 'chab bcas lan gcig kyang //
NK117(she)001:31432: gso ba'i yul med rdza be'u chag pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:31433: byang sdom rin chen nyer spyad chag dang 'dra //
NK117(she)001:31434: gzhan rkyen dge ba'i bshes la bsten nas gso //
NK117(she)001:31435: gsang sngags sdom pa rin chen snod zhom ltar //
NK117(she)001:31436: rang stobs mthu yis gso ru byar yod pas //
NK117(she)001:31437: bla ma spun brnyas 'phral du mnyes byas bskang //
NK117(she)001:31438: gsung gi tha tshig nyams na rdo rje chos //
NK117(she)001:31439: bsgoms la snying po'am yig brgya 'bum ther gdon //
NK117(she)001:31440: thugs las nyams na lo gsum smra ba bcad //
NK117(she)001:31441: gcig tu mnyam par gzhag pa gso ba'i thabs //
NK117(she)001:31442: zhes pa ni de'ang dam tshig nyams par gyur na
NK117(she)001:31443: gso ba'ang 'og ma rnams las 'phags pa yin te
NK117(she)001:31444: nyan thos sdom khrims 'chab pa'am sbas sems ma skyes
NK117(she)001:31445: na lan bdun gsor yod kyang /
NK117(she)001:31446: 'chab bcas te nyes pa gsang na lan gcig kyang
NK117(she)001:31447: gso ba'i yul med pa'i dpe rdza be'u chag pa
NK117(she)001:31448: bzhin dang / byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa ni
NK117(she)001:31449: rin po che'i nyer spyod de snod chag pa dang
NK117(she)001:31450: 'dra bas gzhan rkyen dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bsten
NK117(she)001:31452: gsang ba sngags kyi sdom pa'am dam tshig nyams na
NK117(she)001:31453: rin po che'i snod zhom pa ste rdib skyon byung
NK117(she)001:31454: na rang stobs mthu yis gso ru byar yod pa
NK117(she)001:31455: yang / bla ma dang rdo rje'i spun la brnyas
NK117(she)001:31456: pa ni 'phral du tshogs 'khor sogs kyis mnyes par
NK117(she)001:31458: gsung gi tha tshig ste bla ma smod pa sogs
NK117(she)001:31459: ngag gis nyams par gyur na rdo rje chos te
NK117(she)001:31460: rdo rje sems dpa' bsgoms la snying po yig drug
NK117(she)001:31461: gam yig brgya 'bum ther bton na bshags thub cing
NK117(she)001:31462: / thugs las nyams na zhes bla ma la lus
NK117(she)001:31463: ngag gis dam tshig bsrung bardzu byas kyang yid kyis
NK117(she)001:31464: log lta sogs shor na lo gsum smra ba bcad
NK117(she)001:31465: bzhin rtse gcig tu yengs pa med par mnyam par
NK117(she)001:31466: bzhag pa kho na gso ba'i thabs mchog tu gyur
NK117(she)001:31468: drug cha las thal thun tshod 'da' ba'i mtshams //
NK117(she)001:31469: 'gal dang nyams dang 'das dang ral ba zhes //
NK117(she)001:31470: zhag dang zla ba lo gcig lo gnyis 'das //
NK117(she)001:31471: gso bar rung ste phyi ma phyi ma lci //
NK117(she)001:31472: lo gsum 'das na gso bar rung ma yin //
NK117(she)001:31473: 'gal na tshogs 'khor nyams na bdog dgus bskang //
NK117(she)001:31474: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK117(she)001:31475: ral na srog gi gso ba'i rnam gzhag rnams //
NK117(she)001:31476: rdo rje nyi ma rnam par bkod las gsungs //
NK117(she)001:31477: zhes pa ni de la spyir ltung ba phal pa la yan lag bzhi dang ldan dgos te /
NK117(she)001:31478: ltung ba 'byung ba'i yul der 'du shes pa'i bsam pa /
NK117(she)001:31479: lus ngag dang 'brel na de'i sbyor ba sgo gsum
NK117(she)001:31480: gang gis bya ba rdzogs tshe mthar thug bzhi tshang
NK117(she)001:31481: na sngags sdom gtong ba'i pham par 'gyur ro //
NK117(she)001:31482: bye brag tu dbye na nyin thun gsum mtshan thun
NK117(she)001:31483: gsum la drug cha ste dam tshig nyams chag ci
NK117(she)001:31484: byung de'i khongs su ma bshags nas de las thal
NK117(she)001:31485: nas thun tshod las 'da' ba'i mtshams la /
NK117(she)001:31486: 'gal ba zhes nyams chag de ma bshags par zhag
NK117(she)001:31487: gis bar du chod pa dang de bzhin du nyams
NK117(she)001:31488: pa ni zla bas bar du chod pa /
NK117(she)001:31489: 'das pa ni nyams chag ma bshags par lo gcig
NK117(she)001:31490: dang gnyis 'das kyang gso bar rung ste gsungs kyang
NK117(she)001:31491: phyi ma phyi ma lci zhing lo gsum la zla
NK117(she)001:31492: ba phyed dang zhag po kha shas tsam ma tshang
NK117(she)001:31493: yang gso bar rung ba shugs la bstan pa las
NK117(she)001:31494: shes shing lo gsum tshang bar song na gso bar
NK117(she)001:31496: de dag rnams kyang rim pa bzhin du bshags thabs
NK117(she)001:31497: kyang 'gal na tshogs kyi 'khor lo rgya chen pos
NK117(she)001:31498: bskang ba dang / nyams na rang la gang yod kyi nor rdzas bdog dgus bskang zhing /
NK117(she)001:31499: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor rdzas gang yod
NK117(she)001:31500: dang dbyig ces rin po che'i rigs phul nus shing
NK117(she)001:31501: / ral na srog gis gso ba ni bla ma'i
NK117(she)001:31502: ched du rang gi lus srog gtong dgos kyang phangs
NK117(she)001:31503: sems mi skye ba ste dper na rgyal po'i chad
NK117(she)001:31504: pa'am dgra zla sogs kyi nyen la thug pa lta
NK117(she)001:31505: bu'i dus bla ma'i tshab tu rang lus gtong ba
NK117(she)001:31507: 'di lta bu'i rnam par bzhag pa'i thabs gang nas
NK117(she)001:31508: bshad na rdo rje nyi ma rnam par bkod pa
NK117(she)001:31510: gzhan yang dbang bzhi bskyar dang bdag 'jug blang //
NK117(she)001:31511: bskyed rdzogs bzlas brjod 'pho med tshul khrims dang //
NK117(she)001:31512: thig le'i rnal 'byor sbyin sreg gtor ma gtong //
NK117(she)001:31513: dral pa'i sngags rgyas bkru dang gtum mos sreg /
NK117(she)001:31514: tshogs sam rten gyi mdun du nyes pa bsgrags //
NK117(she)001:31515: srog bslu gsung rab bklag dang yig brgya bzla //
NK117(she)001:31516: man+dala yan lag bdun dang mchod rten bzhengs //
NK117(she)001:31517: la sogs thabs kyis gtugs pa ma yin la //
NK117(she)001:31518: khyad par dong sprug bshags pas mi 'dag med //
NK117(she)001:31519: dmigs bcas kun la 'gyod sems lhag par gces //
NK117(she)001:31520: zhes pa ni de'ang nyams chag byung nas lo gsum
NK117(she)001:31521: ma 'das pa dag gis sngon du bskang thabs bshad
NK117(she)001:31522: pa las gzhan pa yang bum dbang dang gsang dbang
NK117(she)001:31523: dang shes rab ye shes dang rig pa'i rtsal dbang
NK117(she)001:31524: ste bzhi po yang yang bskyar nas zhu ba dang
NK117(she)001:31525: / rang stobs kyis bdag 'jug yang yang blang zhing
NK117(she)001:31526: bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim bsgom pa gsang sngags kyi
NK117(she)001:31527: bzlas brjod sogs dang 'pho med kyi tshul khrims zhes
NK117(she)001:31528: khams 'dzag med du bsrung ba dang /
NK117(she)001:31529: thig le rnal 'byor ni 'dzin 'dren dgram gsum dang
NK117(she)001:31530: yum gyi mkhar lha tshogs bskyed cing 'bul ba'i thabs
NK117(she)001:31531: dang / sbyin sreg phyi nang gsang gsum gyi gtor ma gtong ba /
NK117(she)001:31532: dral ba'i sngags rgya zhes til la sdig pa bstims nas sngags rgyas bkru ba dang /
NK117(she)001:31533: za byed rdo rje mkha' 'gro la brten nas gtum mo'i mes bsreg pa dang /
NK117(she)001:31534: 'dus sde rgya mtsho 'tshogs pa'am rten gsum byin rlabs
NK117(she)001:31535: can gyi mdun du rang gi nyes pa bsgrags pa
NK117(she)001:31536: dang / 'chi nges pa'i sems can gyi srog bslu ba /
