NK117(she)001:32847: las ma g.yos na lha'i mig dang spyan lnga'i yon
NK117(she)001:32848: tan dang mngon par shes pa'i tshogs la sogs dbang
NK117(she)001:32849: po dwangs pa'i yon tan mtha' dag 'thob pa'o //
NK117(she)001:32851: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK117(she)001:32852: thams cad sems kyi rgyun du mkhyen pa dang /
NK117(she)001:32853: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis thams cad kun tu gzigs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:32854: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis kun tu gsan pa dang /
NK117(she)001:32855: rdzu 'phrul gyis tshogs kun tu don spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:32856: zag med kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yongs su rdzogs pa ste drug go //
NK117(she)001:32857: 'di ltar lhag mthong gi shes rab kyis ma zin na /
NK117(she)001:32858: zhi gnas rkyang pa ni bdag rtog bag la nyal
NK117(she)001:32859: yin phyir srid pa'i rtsa ba'i nyes dmigs drung nas
NK117(she)001:32860: mi 'byin zhing 'og mar yang mi lhung bas na
NK117(she)001:32861: mi g.yo ba'i las te bsam gtan gzugs med du
NK117(she)001:32862: 'phen pa tsam las don gzhan med do //
NK117(she)001:32863: spyi 'phags pa ni 'bras bu che ba'i bar mnyam du 'thob kyang /
NK117(she)001:32864: so so skye bo ni zhi gnas kho na'i bde
NK117(she)001:32865: ba la zhen te stong pa'i ngang du blo'i 'jug
NK117(she)001:32866: pa nub pa las gang du skye 'gyur gyi khams
NK117(she)001:32868: 'phags pa ni bdag dang bral ba'i lhag mthong gi
NK117(she)001:32869: ye shes so so rang rig gi khyad par byas
NK117(she)001:32870: pas bsam gtan gzugs med kyi ting 'dzin gyi yon
NK117(she)001:32871: tan tshang yang de dag gi sems rang mtshan par
NK117(she)001:32872: mi gnas pas khams gong mar mi skye yang /
NK117(she)001:32873: mi che ba'i sems thob nas 'og min gyi bar
NK117(she)001:32874: du mthong bsgom gyi ye shes gong ma thob nas
NK117(she)001:32876: de'ang mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu ni /
NK117(she)001:32881: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK117(she)001:32882: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK117(she)001:32883: ci yang med pa'i skye mched dang /
NK117(she)001:32884: yod min med min gyi skye mched dang /
NK117(she)001:32885: de dag la goms pa brtas pas gzugs dang gzugs med du skye ba'i rgyu byed do //
NK117(she)001:32886: 'gog pa ni 'jig rten pa'i tshor ba dang 'du
NK117(she)001:32887: shes 'gog pa'i ting 'dzin thob pa ste sems kyi
NK117(she)001:32888: spros pa 'gags nas rig cha'i yon tan yang bag
NK117(she)001:32889: la zha ba'o // de'ang blos dpyad cing brtags nas 'gog pa ni sems kyi spros pa 'gog pa'o //
NK117(she)001:32890: ma brtags pa rtog bral 'gog pa ni chos nyid
NK117(she)001:32891: rnam par mi rtog kyang ye shes kyi cha nas
NK117(she)001:32892: dmigs med kyi snying rje rgyun mi 'chad pas sems
NK117(she)001:32894: mdor na 'phags pa rnams kyis rtogs pa'i shes rab dang /
NK117(she)001:32895: so so'i skye bo'i bsgom pa'i bsam gtan gnyis rnam shes kyis gzhal na 'dra ba ltar snang yang /
NK117(she)001:32896: ye shes kyi ngo na khyad che ste bsam gtan
NK117(she)001:32897: gyi skabs na gzhi bzhag gi gnas lugs sems kyi
NK117(she)001:32899: shes rab kyi gnas skabs na rig thog tu spros
NK117(she)001:32900: pa rang zhig la song ba'i khyad par phyed dgos
NK117(she)001:32902: rtog pa yul dang 'brel na tha mal te //
NK117(she)001:32903: me long lta bu dwangs pa'i shes pa la //
NK117(she)001:32904: snang yul ma 'gags gza' skar bzhin bkra yang //
NK117(she)001:32905: rnam pa'i blo yis gos par ma gyur na //
NK117(she)001:32906: gzung ba'i yul dang 'dzin sems 'brel chad pas //
NK117(she)001:32907: so so rang rig rnam par mi rtog pa'i //
NK117(she)001:32908: ye shes bla ma'i sa la da lta phyin //
NK117(she)001:32909: zhes pa ni de'ang rtog pa ste snang ba'i yul
NK117(she)001:32910: 'di dang 'adi'o zhes pa bdag gir bzung na phan
NK117(she)001:32912: de ltar gyur na tha mal gyi 'gro bas sems
NK117(she)001:32913: kyi gnas lugs la go myong rtogs gsum bral ba
NK117(she)001:32914: ste / de ltar ma yin pa'i sems nyid me
NK117(she)001:32915: long dwangs pa lta bu'i shes pa'am rig ngo la
NK117(she)001:32916: snang yul gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya ste lnga
NK117(she)001:32917: dang yid ngor shar ba'i chos te drug po ma
NK117(she)001:32918: 'gags par gza' skar bzhin du bkra bar gyur kyang
NK117(she)001:32919: ste / / rnam pa'i ste so sor 'di dang
NK117(she)001:32920: 'adi'o snyam pa'i blo yis gos par ma gzung ba'i
NK117(she)001:32921: yul drug dang 'dzin pa'i sems 'brel thag chod pas
NK117(she)001:32922: so sor rang gi rig pa rnam par mi rtog
NK117(she)001:32923: par mthong bya mthong byed las 'das pa rtogs pas
NK117(she)001:32924: bcu drug ye shes bla ma ste rdzogs pa chen
NK117(she)001:32925: po sa bcu drug gi rgyal sar da lta nyid
NK117(she)001:32926: ste / / du phyin pa'o // zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:32928: mdor na dbyings kyi lam ni chos nyid gcig /
NK117(she)001:32929: rig pa'i lam ni shes rab khyad par can //
NK117(she)001:32930: 'od gsal lam ni sgron ma rnam pa gnyis //
NK117(she)001:32931: khregs chod lam ni shar grol dus mnyam ste //
NK117(she)001:32932: thod rgal lam ni dbyings dang rig pa yin //
NK117(she)001:32933: zhes pa ni de yang rgyu 'bras dag grol du
NK117(she)001:32934: 'dzin pa'i 'og ma'i lam lnga po rdzogs chen bden
NK117(she)001:32935: pa dbyer med kyi chos nyid yid dpyod las 'das
NK117(she)001:32936: par mdor bsdu na chos thams cad kyi dbyings stong
NK117(she)001:32937: pa nyid kyi lam ni chos nyid gcig las ma
NK117(she)001:32938: 'das shing / rig pa'i lam ni shes rab khyad par can te sor rtog ces so //
NK117(she)001:32939: 'od gsal lam thod rgal gyi lam ni sgron ma
NK117(she)001:32940: rnam pa gnyis te rgyangs zhags chu'i sgron ma dang
NK117(she)001:32941: / thig le stong pa'i sgron ma'o //
NK117(she)001:32942: khregs chod kyi lam ni shar grol dus mnyam ste
NK117(she)001:32943: thod rgal gyi lam ni dbyings zhes ngo bo stong
NK117(she)001:32944: pa dang rig pa ste thim la ma rmugs pa'i
NK117(she)001:32945: shes pa'o // 'di ltar kun gzhi la brten pa'i
NK117(she)001:32946: rnam shes tshogs brgyad pos rig pa'i cha la ma
NK117(she)001:32947: rig par sgro btags pas kun brtags zhes 'khor ba'i
NK117(she)001:32948: mtshan nyid du gnas pa de'ang rtogs pa rnams kyis
NK117(she)001:32949: 'khor 'das gnyis rig pa rang mal las g.yos pas
NK117(she)001:32950: gzung 'dzin gyi gzeb la thebs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:32951: gshis las ma 'khrul ba'i rang gsal rgya yan du
NK117(she)001:32952: grol ba'i khyad par las yod pa ma yin no
NK117(she)001:32954: 'di dag rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK117(she)001:32955: thun mong ma yin lam lngar mkhyen 'tshal nas //
NK117(she)001:32956: ma rig grogs dang 'khrul pa'i bslu brid kyis //
NK117(she)001:32957: mtha' med 'khor ba'i 'brog dgon 'jigs rung bar //
NK117(she)001:32958: las dang nyon mongs 'du byed lcags sgrog gis //
NK117(she)001:32959: de ring phan chad bcings la skyo ba'i sems //
NK117(she)001:32960: bskyed nas zhi ba dam pa'i grong khyer du //
NK117(she)001:32961: mya ngan 'da' ba'i lam mchog bsnyen par mdzod //
NK117(she)001:32962: ces pa ni de'ang 'di dag ste bshad ma thag
NK117(she)001:32963: pa'i lam lnga po de ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK117(she)001:32964: chen po'i thun mong ma yin pa'i lam lngar mkhyen
NK117(she)001:32965: par 'tshal zhes shes par byas nas ma rig pa
NK117(she)001:32966: ni rig pa'i ldog cha yin phyir de nyid grogs
NK117(she)001:32967: su gyur nas yengs shing 'khrul pa'i bslu brid kyis
NK117(she)001:32968: mtha' med pa'i 'khor ba'i dpe 'brog dgon pa chen
NK117(she)001:32969: po 'jigs su rung ba las mi dge ba'i tshogs
NK117(she)001:32970: dang nyon mongs brgyad khri 'du bar byed pa'i lcags
NK117(she)001:32971: sgrog gis dus de ring rig pa'i ngo bo 'khrul
NK117(she)001:32972: grol gnyis ka las 'das pa'i don 'di ma rtogs
NK117(she)001:32973: phan chad la bcings shing rmongs pa la skyo ba'i
NK117(she)001:32974: sems bskyed bzhin zhi ba dam pa'i grong khyer du
NK117(she)001:32975: zhes pa mya ngan las 'da' ba'i lam mchog tu
NK117(she)001:32976: gyur pa 'di la bsnyen par mdzod ces pa'ang dbang
NK117(she)001:32977: po dang skal ba rab tu gyur pa rnams kyis
NK117(she)001:32978: gzhi lta ba khregs chod dang /
NK117(she)001:32979: lam lhun grub 'od gsal thabs shes zung 'jug tu
NK117(she)001:32980: nyams su blangs pas rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i
NK117(she)001:32981: sa lam gyis 'jal ba la ma ltos par rdzogs
NK117(she)001:32982: pa chen po'i thun mong ma yin pa'i lam lngar
NK117(she)001:32983: sku gsum lam snang du rdzogs nas tshe lus gcig
NK117(she)001:32984: gis 'bras bu khyad chos drug ldan gyi gzhi thog
NK117(she)001:32986: de lta na'ang spangs rtogs phun sum tshogs pas phyi
NK117(she)001:32987: nang mthun pa'i rtags khyad par can med par rlung
NK117(she)001:32988: sems 'jug ldog gi rnam 'gyur las sems gnas cung
NK117(she)001:32989: zad thob pa'am / bdud sdig can gyis byin gyis
NK117(she)001:32990: brlabs pa'i grub rtags la dngos grub thob par bzung
NK117(she)001:32991: zad thob pa'am / nas / ngas chos nyid rnal ma'i don mthong bas las la re ba med /
NK117(she)001:32992: da phyin mgo la thod pa mi 'gel zhes rdzun
NK117(she)001:32993: rlabs chen pos rang gzhan gyi mgo bskor ba yod
NK117(she)001:32994: kyang de ni yid dpyod kyi lta sgom las ma
NK117(she)001:32995: grol bas da dung 'khor ba'i srog shing gcig tu
NK117(she)001:32996: yod pa'o // de'ang 'khor bar 'gro ba'i lam ni rgyud lnga ste /
NK117(she)001:33001: rgyu dang 'bras bu so sor ma nges pa'i lam mo //
NK117(she)001:33002: de ltar lam rgyud lnga'i sgrib pa ma spangs pa'i rang rgyud ldan rnams ni las dang /
NK117(she)001:33003: nyon mongs pa dang 'du byed kyi lcags sgrog dam
NK117(she)001:33004: po'i gzhan dbang du gyur nas 'gro ba rigs drug
NK117(she)001:33005: po las 'khor sa gzhan med pa'i gnas su bcings
NK117(she)001:33006: shing da dung yang 'ching ba las ma 'das pa
NK117(she)001:33007: 'di la bsam bzhin skyo ba tshad med par bskyed
NK117(she)001:33008: nas lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi po mthar phyin par
NK117(she)001:33009: bya'o // yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo
NK117(she)001:33010: lcags 'byed byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin
NK117(she)001:33011: po che'i lde mig las le'u bcu gnyis pa'i skabs
NK117(she)001:33013: de ltar gzhi lam mtshan nyid legs rtogs nas //
NK117(she)001:33014: mthar phyin 'bras bu sku dang ye shes ni //
NK117(she)001:33015: gzhan las ma byung kun gzhi'i rnyog pa dwangs //
NK117(she)001:33016: sems dang sems byung chos dbyings zhi ba yin //
NK117(she)001:33017: gang du gzhi las gzhi snang g.yos pa yi //
NK117(she)001:33018: bdag 'dzin bag chags shes bya'i cha 'dzin pa'i //
NK117(she)001:33019: tshogs brgyad nyer len sprin dang 'dra ba rnams //
NK117(she)001:33020: rnam par dag pa'i ye shes nyi ma ni //
NK117(she)001:33021: sgrib pa med par rang bzhin 'od du gsal //
NK117(she)001:33022: zhes pa ni de ltar gzhi'i gnas lugs shes bya'i
NK117(she)001:33023: chos thams cad kyi shes byed lam bden 'dus ma
NK117(she)001:33024: byas pa thams cad kyi mtshan nyid legs par rtogs
NK117(she)001:33025: par byas nas mthar phyin tshe 'bras bu sku lnga
NK117(she)001:33026: dang ye shes lnga la sogs pa ni gzhan gang
NK117(she)001:33027: las kyang ma byung zhing rang gi kun gzhi'i rnyog
NK117(she)001:33028: pa dwangs pa ste sems zhes 'khrul gzhi dang /
NK117(she)001:33029: sems byung ni 'khrul rtog kho na yin te /
NK117(she)001:33030: de nyid chos kyi dbyings su zhi ba'am rtogs par
NK117(she)001:33031: gyur pa la btags pa yin zhing gang du'ang ye
NK117(she)001:33032: gzhi lung ma bstan la gzhi snang ste yid cung
NK117(she)001:33033: zad g.yos pa mthu brtas nas bdag 'dzin dang bag
NK117(she)001:33034: chags sogs shes bya'i 'khrul rtog gi cha 'dzin pa'i
NK117(she)001:33035: sgo lnga'i rnam shes dang yid shes nyon yid kun
NK117(she)001:33036: gzhi ste tshogs brgyad nye bar len pa sprin phung
NK117(she)001:33038: rnam par dag pa'i ye shes te dpe nyi ma'i
NK117(she)001:33039: snying po la mun pa'i gzhi mi gnas pa lta
NK117(she)001:33040: bu ni / sgrib pa'i tshogs gang yang med par rang bzhin du 'od gsal ba'o //
NK117(she)001:33041: de'ang gzhi lam 'bras gsum rig pa ka dag gcig
NK117(she)001:33042: las 'gyur ba med pa'i ldog cha las sku lngar
NK117(she)001:33043: phye na / mi 'gyur rdo rje dang /
NK117(she)001:33045: chos longs sprul gsum ste lnga'o //
NK117(she)001:33047: glo bur dri ma cha dang bcas spangs pa //
NK117(she)001:33048: dag pa gnyis ldan byang chub mchog gi dngos //
NK117(she)001:33049: gdod ma'i sangs rgyas smon pa med pa'i dbyings //
NK117(she)001:33050: nya rgyas zla ba spros pa phyir gsal can //
NK117(she)001:33051: stong gi cha la dbyings su nub pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:33052: kun tu mi rtog chos nyid 'pho 'gyur med //
NK117(she)001:33053: dbyings kyi rtag pa mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku //
NK117(she)001:33054: zhes pa ni de yang gdod nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33055: glo bur gyi dri mas kyang ma gos pa la dag pa gnyis ldan te /
NK117(she)001:33056: de lta bu ni byang chub mchog gi dngos po
NK117(she)001:33057: gdod ma'i sangs rgyas smon pa med pa'i dbyings zhes
NK117(she)001:33058: bya'o // de'i dpe ni nya rgyas te tshes bco
NK117(she)001:33059: lnga'i zla ba 'od gsal gyi zer spros pa phyir
NK117(she)001:33060: gsal bzhin yul kun tu khyab pa can de nyid
NK117(she)001:33061: gnam stong gi nyin nub kyi cha la 'od dkar
NK117(she)001:33062: dbyings su nub pa ltar sems dang sems byung dbyings
NK117(she)001:33063: su nub tshe kun tu mi rtog ste rnam par
NK117(she)001:33064: mi rtog pa'i chos nyid 'di ni gzhan du 'pho
NK117(she)001:33065: ba dang ngo bo 'gyur ba'i rgyu dang bral yang
NK117(she)001:33066: dbyings kyi rtag pa ste chos nyid mi 'gyur ba
NK117(she)001:33067: gzhom gzhig dang bral ba'i rang bzhin ni rdo rje'i
NK117(she)001:33068: sku ste mi chod pa mi shigs pa bden pa
NK117(she)001:33069: sogs rdo rje'i chos bdun ldan gyi ngang du gnas
NK117(she)001:33070: bya'o // pa'o // 'di ni rnam par rtog bcas
NK117(she)001:33071: ma yin kyang dbyings kyi ngang na bltar mi mngon
NK117(she)001:33072: pa'i ye shes kyi 'char gzhi lhun grub tu yod
NK117(she)001:33073: bya'o // pa'o // pas / smon lam gyi rgyu
NK117(she)001:33074: la ma ltos par gzhan snang la thugs rje'i 'jug
NK117(she)001:33075: pa rgyun mi 'chad cing gzugs sku phrin las dang
NK117(she)001:33076: bcas pa rang du 'byung ba ni khyad par gyi
NK117(she)001:33077: bya'o // pa'o // pas / chos so // zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33079: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan zhi ba'i dbyings //
NK117(she)001:33080: stobs sogs yon tan rgya mtsho kun chub kyang //
NK117(she)001:33081: snang cha ngo bor ma 'dres spangs rtogs kyi //
NK117(she)001:33082: cha nas gzhal ba mngon par byang chub sku //
NK117(she)001:33083: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK117(she)001:33084: par dag pa dang glo bur gyi dri ma dag
NK117(she)001:33085: par byas pa'i rang bzhin ni rnam pa thams cad
NK117(she)001:33086: kyi mchog dang ldan pa'i zhi ba chen po'i dbyings
NK117(she)001:33087: yin / de nyid kyang stobs bcu dang /
NK117(she)001:33089: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad /
NK117(she)001:33091: byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun sogs
NK117(she)001:33092: yon tan rgya mtsho yod pa'i cha nas mngon par
NK117(she)001:33093: byang chub pa'i skur brjod kyang snang cha ngo bor
NK117(she)001:33094: ma 'dres shing dri ma'i tshogs spangs pa dang rtogs
NK117(she)001:33095: pa'i yon tan rgyas pa'i cha nas gzhal ba la
NK117(she)001:33096: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku zhes brjod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33098: shes bya'i yul la blo yi 'jug pa zhi //
NK117(she)001:33099: shes byed blo la 'dzin pa'i kun rdzob spangs //
NK117(she)001:33100: so so rang rig rtag chad mthar ma lhung //
NK117(she)001:33101: thim la ma rmugs phra ba'i ye shes ni //
NK117(she)001:33102: mkhyen cha 'gag med sku dang ye shes rten //
NK117(she)001:33103: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa rnams kyis mthong //
NK117(she)001:33104: gang la zhi ba chos kyi sku zhes brjod //
NK117(she)001:33105: ces pa ni de'ang shes par bya ba'i yul la blo'i 'jug pa zhi ba'i dbyings spros bral dang /
NK117(she)001:33106: shes byed kyi blo la 'dzin pa'i kun rdzob kyi
NK117(she)001:33107: chos thams cad spangs pa'i so so rang rtag pa
NK117(she)001:33108: dang chad pa'i mthar ma lhung zhing bco lnga'i zla
NK117(she)001:33109: ba'i dkar mdangs dbyings su 'khyil ba ltar thim la
NK117(she)001:33110: ma rmugs pa phra ba'i ye shes ni mkhyen cha
NK117(she)001:33111: 'gag pa med pa sku dang ye shes kyi rten
NK117(she)001:33112: du gyur pa de nyid shin tu mnyam par bzhag
NK117(she)001:33113: pa rnams kyis mthong ba gang la zhi ba chos
NK117(she)001:33115: de'ang stong chad nam mkha' lta bu ma yin pas
NK117(she)001:33116: chos sku'i dus na thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK117(she)001:33117: zab cing gting dpag dka' ba nang gsal thim la
NK117(she)001:33118: ma rmugs pas stong gi zla ba dbyings su nub
NK117(she)001:33119: pa ltar gzhan snang la mi mngon par bzhugs kyang
NK117(she)001:33120: de las gzugs nas rnam mkhyen bar mkhyen pas /
NK117(she)001:33121: phyir gsal du snang ba'i ye shes kyi gdangs nam yang rgyun chad med pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33124: so so rang gis rig bya rgyal ba'i khams //
NK117(she)001:33125: gcig dang du mar ma yin dngos po dang //
NK117(she)001:33126: dngos med las 'das mkha' ltar rnam mi rtog /
NK117(she)001:33127: gos pa med cing rnam 'gyur spros pa zhi //
NK117(she)001:33128: ngag gi yul 'das don dam bden pas bsdus //
NK117(she)001:33129: rtog dpyod tha snyad gtan tshigs kyis mi mtshon //
NK117(she)001:33130: blo dang snyam byed dpe dang 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:33131: sa bcu'i dbang phyug gis kyang spyod yul min //
NK117(she)001:33132: 'dren pa rnams la mngon sum gyur pa'i gnas //
NK117(she)001:33133: zab zhi gzhon nu bum pa'i khang mdzes nang //
NK117(she)001:33134: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams ni rtag bzhugs kyang //
NK117(she)001:33135: rnam pa'i cha nas gcig gis gcig mi gzigs //
NK117(she)001:33136: rang bzhin spros bral dbyings na dgongs klong gcig /
NK117(she)001:33137: ces pa ni de yang dus gsum du byon pa
NK117(she)001:33138: dang bzhugs pa dang 'byon 'gyur gyi 'dren pa rnams
NK117(she)001:33139: la mngon sum du gyur pa'i gnas zab zhi gzhon
NK117(she)001:33140: nu bum pa'i ste nang gsal thim la ma rmugs
NK117(she)001:33141: pa'i bde stong zung 'jug skye 'chi dang bgres rgud
NK117(she)001:33142: bral ba'i khang mdzes kyi nang na dus gsum gyi
NK117(she)001:33143: sangs rgyas rnams ni dus rtag par bzhugs kyang rang
NK117(she)001:33144: snang dbyings su thim pa'i zhi ba chen po la
NK117(she)001:33145: rnam pa'i chos med pas gcig gis gcig mi gzigs
NK117(she)001:33146: pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs kyang rang bzhin spros bral gyi
NK117(she)001:33147: dbyings nas dgongs pa'i klong gcig tu 'khyil ba chu
NK117(she)001:33148: phran sna tshogs rgya mtshor ro gcig tu 'dres pa
NK117(she)001:33151: mkhyen cha 'gag pa med pa'i rang gdangs las //
NK117(she)001:33152: thugs rje phyir gsal longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK117(she)001:33153: gnas dang dus dang ston pa chos dang 'khor //
NK117(she)001:33154: nges pa lnga ldan sku dang zhing khams dang //
NK117(she)001:33155: mtshan dpe yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid can //
NK117(she)001:33156: zhes pa ni de la nang dbyings spros bral chos
NK117(she)001:33157: nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang mkhyen cha 'gag
NK117(she)001:33158: pa med pa'i rang gdangs las thugs rje phyir gsal
NK117(she)001:33159: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku nges pa lnga ldan ni
NK117(she)001:33160: mtshan dpe rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid can te /
NK117(she)001:33161: de'i thugs kyis chos sku'i cha bzung la phrin las
NK117(she)001:33162: kyis sprul sku'i cha bzung bas sku gsum tha mi
NK117(she)001:33164: rig pa rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba longs sku dang /
NK117(she)001:33165: rig pa sna tshogs su 'char ba ni sprul sku /
NK117(she)001:33166: ji ltar snang yang don skye med las ma 'das pa chos sku'o //
NK117(she)001:33169: gnas ni lhun rdzogs 'og min stug po bkod //
NK117(she)001:33170: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer gsal 'tsher 'bar //
NK117(she)001:33171: mkha' dbyings dbang po'i mtshon chas bkab pa bzhin //
NK117(she)001:33172: mnan na nem zhing btegs na 'phar ba lta'i //
NK117(she)001:33173: gzhal med khang mdzes sgo 'phar rnam bzhir ldan //
NK117(she)001:33174: rta rkang brgyad ldan ye shes lnga'i brtsig pa //
NK117(she)001:33175: pha gu d+r+wa phyed mda' yab pu shud can //
NK117(she)001:33176: snam bur 'dod pa'i yon tan mig yangs ma //
NK117(she)001:33177: bde stong mchod sprin brtse dga' g.yo ba can //
NK117(she)001:33178: rnga yab 'phan gdugs rgyal mtshan nor bu'i tog /
NK117(she)001:33179: bla bre zar tshags gtsang khang phyur bur mdzes //
NK117(she)001:33180: chu zheng srid du mi mngon gang bltas gang //
NK117(she)001:33181: grangs kyis mi gtugs mkha' dbyings snod gyur bzhin //
NK117(she)001:33182: rten gzhi gzhal med khang pa re re'i nang //
NK117(she)001:33183: brten pa'i gtso bo lnga yi gdan khri ni //
NK117(she)001:33184: 'phrog byed gnyis 'thung cang shes zlos gar can //
NK117(she)001:33185: shang shang te'u chu skyes nyi zla'i steng //
NK117(she)001:33186: zhes pa ni de yang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i gnas
NK117(she)001:33187: ni lhun rdzogs 'og min stug po bkod pa ye
NK117(she)001:33188: shes lnga'i 'od zer gsal la 'tsher ba 'bar ba'i
NK117(she)001:33189: gzi 'od kyis nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad dbang po'i
NK117(she)001:33190: mtshon chas bkab pa bzhin du mdzes shing /
NK117(she)001:33191: mnan na nem zhing btegs na 'phar ba lta bu'i
NK117(she)001:33192: gzhal med khang chen po rab tu mdzes shing sgo
NK117(she)001:33193: 'phar rnam pa bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK117(she)001:33194: rta rkang dang rgyan sna tshogs ldan zhing ye shes lnga'i rtsig pas mdzes pa /
NK117(she)001:33195: pha gu dang dra phyed mda' yab pu shud sogs rgyan bkod ma tshang ba med pa /
NK117(she)001:33196: rtsig pa'i rtsa ba'i mtha' bskor du 'dod yon gyi
NK117(she)001:33197: snam bu la 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:33198: mig yangs ma ste lha mo rnams kyis bde stong
NK117(she)001:33199: gi mchod sprin spro ba'i brtse dgas g.yo ba can
NK117(she)001:33201: rnga yab dang 'phan gdugs dang rgyal mtshan nor bu'i
NK117(she)001:33202: tog ldan bla re dang zar tshags gtsang khang sogs
NK117(she)001:33204: chu zheng srid du mi mngon zhing gang bltas kyi
NK117(she)001:33205: yul gang dag grangs kyis mi gtugs shing mkha' dbyings
NK117(she)001:33206: snod du gyur pa bzhin du rten gzhi gzhal med
NK117(she)001:33207: khang pa re'i nang du brten pa'i lha rigs lnga
NK117(she)001:33208: gtso bo lnga'i gdan khri ni 'phrog byed seng+ge dang
NK117(she)001:33209: gnyis 'thung glang po che cang shes rta zlos gar
NK117(she)001:33210: can rma bya shang shang te'u ste lnga po'i steng
NK117(she)001:33211: du / chu skyes nyi zla brtsegs pa'i steng du bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK117(she)001:33215: don grub rnams rang rang gi 'khor dang bcas te bzhugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33218: dus gsum bzhir rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i dus //
NK117(she)001:33219: zhes pa ni dus gsum bzhir rdzogs ni 'das pa'i dus dang /
NK117(she)001:33221: da lta'i dus gsum ka mnyam pa nyid du bzhir
NK117(she)001:33222: rdzogs pa la kun tu bzang po'i dus zhes sgro
NK117(she)001:33225: 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i mtshan rdzogs ston pa lnga //
NK117(she)001:33226: rnam snang mi bskyod rdo rje rin chen 'byung //
NK117(she)001:33227: 'od mtshan stong 'bar don yod grub pa ni //
NK117(she)001:33228: rang rang rigs kyi yum dang bcas pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:33229: kha sbyor bdun gyi bdag nyid chen por bzhugs //
NK117(she)001:33230: zhes pa ni de yang ngo bo nyid las g.yo
NK117(she)001:33231: ba med pas 'pho 'gyur bral yang rang bzhin gyi
NK117(she)001:33232: gdangs 'gag med las mtshan dpe rdzogs pa'i ston pa
NK117(she)001:33234: mi bskyod rdo rje rin chen 'byung ldan 'od mtshan
NK117(she)001:33235: stong 'bar don yod grub pa rnams ni rang rang
NK117(she)001:33236: rigs kyi yum dang bcas shing kha sbyor bdun gyi
NK117(she)001:33237: bdag nyid chen por bzhugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33238: de'ang 'khor ba'i dus kyi phung po lnga po las
NK117(she)001:33239: 'phags pa'i ldan chos rgyal po'i sgras rgyal ba lnga
NK117(she)001:33240: dang / khams lnga po la dbyings kyi sgras 'phags
NK117(she)001:33241: chos ngos bzung nas yum lnga'i rang bzhin du mngon
NK117(she)001:33242: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa gang zhig rang rang
NK117(she)001:33243: gi rigs dang mtshungs pa'i lha mo snyoms par zhugs
NK117(she)001:33244: pas kha sbyor te phar phyin gyi longs sku tsam
NK117(she)001:33245: po ba las khyad par du byas pa ni bde
NK117(she)001:33246: stong gnyis med kyi khyad gzhir rang byung ba'o //
NK117(she)001:33247: de'ang 'dod khams pa ni lhag par rjes su chags
NK117(she)001:33248: pa gang zhig rjes su gzung phyir snyoms 'jug bstan
NK117(she)001:33249: pa'o // de ltar rnam pa longs spyod rdzogs kyang
NK117(she)001:33250: chos sku dang sprul skur yang bzung bas sku gsum
NK117(she)001:33251: yan lag bdun ldan du bzhugs te dmigs pa med
NK117(she)001:33252: pa'i thugs rgyud snying rje chen pos gang ba dang
NK117(she)001:33253: pa'o // / de'i 'phrin las thugs rje'i 'jug pa
NK117(she)001:33254: sems can gyi khams la rgyun mi 'chad pa dang
NK117(she)001:33255: pa'o // / / 'gog pa med pa ste sprul
NK117(she)001:33256: sku'i yan lag gsum ye shes kyi rang 'od kyi
NK117(she)001:33257: lha mo dang sbyor bas kha sbyor dang /
NK117(she)001:33258: de las zag med kyi bde chen rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33259: tshig dang yi ge med pa dgongs rgyud kyi chos 'khor la rtag par longs spyod pa ste /
NK117(she)001:33261: rnam pa de dag ldan kyang rang ngo spros pa
NK117(she)001:33262: kun dang bral bas rang bzhin med pa chos sku'i
NK117(she)001:33263: yan lag gcig ste yan lag bdun ldan gyi bdag
NK117(she)001:33266: nyid las mi gzhan sems dpa' sems ma'i 'khor //
NK117(she)001:33267: sgo ba bzhi dang de bzhin so so'i yum //
NK117(she)001:33268: zhes pa ni de'ang de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs lnga
NK117(she)001:33269: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i sems dpa' sems ma'i 'khor
NK117(she)001:33270: dang / sgo ba bzhi dang de bzhin du so
NK117(she)001:33271: so'i yum sgo ma bzhi dang bcas par bstan pa'o
NK117(she)001:33272: dang / // de ltar yang 'og ma rnams su
NK117(she)001:33273: ni rgyu 'bras spang gnyen can sbyang gzhi dang sbyong
NK117(she)001:33274: byed kyang dar ras tshos kyis bsgyur ba ltar 'khor
NK117(she)001:33275: ba nyid kyang myang 'das su grol ba'o //
NK117(she)001:33277: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i chos 'khor ni //
NK117(she)001:33278: sgra tshig mtshan ma'i yul las 'das par bskor //
NK117(she)001:33279: zhes pa ni de'i tshul yang ston pas gsungs pa
NK117(she)001:33280: med bzhin 'khor gyi sems dpa' rnams la rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:33281: rdzogs pa chen po'i chos kyi 'khor lo ni rang
NK117(she)001:33282: ngo'i shes rab kyi rtog dpyod las rmi lam gyi
NK117(she)001:33283: tshig ltar sgra tshig mtshan ma'i yul las 'das par
NK117(she)001:33284: bskor ba'o // de ltar sangs rgyas rnams kyi don
NK117(she)001:33285: dam pa'i chos 'khor ni skyes bu'i rnam rig dang
NK117(she)001:33286: 'brel pa ma grub pas sgra tshig mtshan ma'i spyod
NK117(she)001:33287: yul las 'das pa'i don rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK117(she)001:33288: po brjod bral blo 'das chen po'i ngo bor gnas
NK117(she)001:33290: steng khang zhi ba byang chub snying po'i gnas //
NK117(she)001:33291: dbang mdzad zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las //
NK117(she)001:33292: dam pa'i stangs dpyal gnyis ni sprul gzhi ste //
NK117(she)001:33293: kun la khyab par brdal bas chos kyi sku //
NK117(she)001:33294: 'gro drug so so'i gnas su don mdzad pa'i //
NK117(she)001:33295: rig pa'i skyes bu drug ni sprul par shar //
NK117(she)001:33296: rang snang longs sku'i zhing nang sum cu bzhi //
NK117(she)001:33297: gtso bo bcu la nyer bzhi 'khor gyi tshul //
NK117(she)001:33298: phung khams skye mched gnas su dag pa'i lha //
NK117(she)001:33299: gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po yin //
NK117(she)001:33300: zhes pa ni de'ang sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i lha bskyed
NK117(she)001:33301: dang bstun nas zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor steng khang na
NK117(she)001:33302: yod tshul zhi ba byang chub snying po'i gnas zhes
NK117(she)001:33303: smos nas don dbang mdzad zhi ba bzhi bcu rtsa
NK117(she)001:33304: gnyis las / dam pa'i stangs dpyal gnyis te kun
NK117(she)001:33305: bzang yab yum gnyis ni sprul gzhi yin te 'khor
NK117(she)001:33306: 'das kun la khyab par gdal bas chos kyi sku'o
NK117(she)001:33307: gnyis las / // de'i rtsal 'gro drug so so'i
NK117(she)001:33308: gnas su de dag gi don mdzad pa'i rig pa'i
NK117(she)001:33309: skyes bu drug ste lha dang lha min mi dang
NK117(she)001:33310: dud 'gro yi dwags dmyal ba'i thub pa rnams ni
NK117(she)001:33311: sprul gzhi'i sprul par shar ba yin la /
NK117(she)001:33312: rang snang longs sku ste dbyings snang longs sku'i zhing
NK117(she)001:33313: na gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum bcu la sems
NK117(she)001:33314: dpa' brgyad sems ma brgyad dang bcu drug /
NK117(she)001:33315: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de nyer bzhi 'khor gyi
NK117(she)001:33316: tshul yin cing de dag kyang phung khams skye mched
NK117(she)001:33317: gnas su dag pa'i lha gdan gsum tshang ba'i dkyil
NK117(she)001:33318: 'khor chen po rang gi sgo gsum la tshang ba
NK117(she)001:33319: yin zhes pa'o // de lta bu'i dal la rang bzhin gyi snang bar khyad dbye ba yang /
NK117(she)001:33321: 'di dag sgyu 'phrul dra ba mnyam sbyor sogs //
NK117(she)001:33322: bla med rgyud las lus grub dkyil 'khor ni //
NK117(she)001:33323: ji snyed bstan dang rnam dag mtshungs pa yin //
NK117(she)001:33324: zhes pa ni 'di ltar sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang
NK117(she)001:33325: sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gsang 'dus kyi rgyud snga phyi
NK117(she)001:33326: gnyis sogs bla med phal mo cher lus grub kyi
NK117(she)001:33327: dal ji snyed bstan pa rnams ni rang snang gis
NK117(she)001:33328: bsdus pa'i zhing khams yin pas rnam dag kyang mtshungs
NK117(she)001:33329: la / gzhan snang la shar ba'i zhi khro'i dal
NK117(she)001:33330: gang yang rung ste 'og min las gzhan du gyur
NK117(she)001:33331: pa ste dper na bsgrub ste las bgegs 'dul phyir
NK117(she)001:33332: rmi lam ltar 'jig rten pa'i 'khor gtso bor gyur
NK117(she)001:33333: pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum du sprul pa bzhin no //
NK117(she)001:33336: 'og khang tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK117(she)001:33337: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas phyi na rim pa dgu //
NK117(she)001:33338: sgo khyams dgu pa'i phyi mar rgyu 'bras kyi //
NK117(she)001:33339: rta babs gnyis ldan pho brang dbus ma'i nang //
NK117(she)001:33340: rdo rje'i brag chen pad+ma stong brdal la //
NK117(she)001:33341: thabs shes nyi zlar dbang phyug khyo shug ni //
NK117(she)001:33342: nyi shu rtsa gcig steng du dpa' gtum stag /'jigs byed seng ge gdug pa gzig dang ni //
NK117(she)001:33343: gtum pa dom dang stobs chen glang po dang //
NK117(she)001:33344: brjid pa'i ma he 'dzin pa'i chu srin dang //
NK117(she)001:33345: zhe sdang lto 'gro byol song gtso brgyad res //
NK117(she)001:33346: dregs pa pho mo bzung zhing bardzisa pa'i steng //
NK117(she)001:33347: 'khor 'das kun gyi spyi dpal bcom ldan 'das //
NK117(she)001:33348: che ba'i che mchog in+d+ra n+ai la'i gdangs //
NK117(she)001:33349: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od ldan bdun gsum zhal //
NK117(she)001:33350: zhabs brgyad phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK117(she)001:33351: zhi ba'i lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bsnams /
NK117(she)001:33352: gnam zhal yum mchog dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad //
NK117(she)001:33353: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis rdo rje dung khrag 'dzin //
NK117(she)001:33354: lhag ma gnas yul ma mo phra men bsnams //
NK117(she)001:33355: yab yum khro mkhar tshul lam mnyam par sbyor //
NK117(she)001:33356: srid dang zhi ba'i chos khams ma lus pa //
NK117(she)001:33357: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs kyi gdan khri nas //
NK117(she)001:33358: dbu brgyan 'khor lo'i bar la rang bzhin rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:33359: dbang mchog dang ni he ru ka dpal dgu //
NK117(she)001:33360: glo 'bur bzhi dang gru chad rnam bzhi la //
NK117(she)001:33361: rnam shes tshogs dag goo ri la sogs brgyad //
NK117(she)001:33362: dkyil 'khor dang po'i khyams la phra men brgyad //
NK117(she)001:33363: gnyis pa'i khyams la spor ma rnam pa brgyad //
NK117(she)001:33364: gsum pa'i khyams la dbang mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK117(she)001:33365: kun la rang rang sgo ba bzhi bzhir ldan //
NK117(she)001:33366: 'bar ba'i rnam rol gar dgu'i nyams kyis brjid //
NK117(she)001:33367: 'di dag rang snang longs sku'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK117(she)001:33368: gzhi snang lhun grub don gyi 'og min yin //
NK117(she)001:33369: bzhi pa'i khyams la mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis //
NK117(she)001:33370: lnga pa'i khyams la ma bdun sring mo bzhi //
NK117(she)001:33371: drug pa'i khyams la ging chen drug tshan gsum //
NK117(she)001:33372: bdun par khro bo yab yum bcu phrag drug /
NK117(she)001:33373: brgyad par pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu ste //
NK117(she)001:33374: dgu pa'i khyams la ma mo drug cu rnams //
NK117(she)001:33375: log 'dren gdul phyir sprul pas bsdus pa'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:33376: bgegs sogs gdul bya so so'i rang ngor snang //
NK117(she)001:33377: de phyir rang snang 'og min dkyil 'khor min //
NK117(she)001:33378: zhes pa ni de ltar zhi ba'i dal gyi 'og
NK117(she)001:33379: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor ni dur khrod 'bar
NK117(she)001:33380: ba'i gzhal yas khang phyi nang rim pa dgu yang
NK117(she)001:33381: khang chen nang du khang chung sbrag ma dgu yod
NK117(she)001:33382: pas sgo khyams yang dgu yod pa'i phyi rol gyi
NK117(she)001:33383: so so'i sgo 'degs pa'i them skas su gyur pa
NK117(she)001:33385: sgo steng so so'i khar them skas ltar yod pas
NK117(she)001:33386: 'bras bu'i rta babs rta las 'bab dus kyi rkang
NK117(she)001:33387: pa brkyang bskum dang mtshungs dpes sgro btags pa yin
NK117(she)001:33388: zhes pa'ang thos / de lta bu'i rta babs gnyis
NK117(she)001:33389: ldan gyi pho brang phyi nang rim dgu'i nang ma'i
NK117(she)001:33390: dbus su 'og gzhi rdo rje'i pha lam las grub
NK117(she)001:33391: pa'i brag ri chen po gzhom gzhig bral ba'i dbus
NK117(she)001:33392: su pad+ma 'dab ma stong brdal la thabs bde ba
NK117(she)001:33393: chen po'i ngo bo nya rgyas zla ba dang shes
NK117(she)001:33394: rab yum gyi mtshon byed nyi ma gnyis steng 'og
NK117(she)001:33395: tu brtsegs pa'i khar 'gro ba'i zhe sdang dang 'dod
NK117(she)001:33396: chags kyi rang gzugs dbang phyug la khyo ste pho
NK117(she)001:33397: zhes pa'ang thos / dang / u ma la shug
NK117(she)001:33398: ste mo ru byas pa'i stangs dpyal nyi shu rtsa
NK117(she)001:33399: gcig pho mo kha sbyor du bsgyel ba'i steng du
NK117(she)001:33400: dpa' la gtum pa'i stag dang /
NK117(she)001:33403: khro gtum ldan pa'i dom stobs chen glang po che dang /
NK117(she)001:33406: zhe sdang lto 'gro ste byol song gtso brgyad do //
NK117(she)001:33407: de'ang gzhal yas khang chen po phyi nang rim pa
NK117(she)001:33408: dgu po'i rgyan dang bkod pa sogs gzhi lam 'bras
NK117(she)001:33409: bu'i chos dang sbyor tshul rnams rgyas 'grel gzhung las
NK117(she)001:33410: rtogs par bya ba kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:33411: 'di ltar khyams bzhi pa nas dgu pa'i bar sprul
NK117(she)001:33412: pas bsdus pa'i tshul slob dpon gsang ba'i spyan 'grel
NK117(she)001:33414: don gyi 'og min chos dbyings dang /
NK117(she)001:33416: rig pa de dag gi don rtogs pa /
NK117(she)001:33419: 'jig rten gyi gtsang ma ris kyi lha lnga'i rtse mo'o //
NK117(she)001:33420: de ltar 'og min drug tu gsungs pa la 'di
NK117(she)001:33421: ni ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ram rtog pa'i
NK117(she)001:33422: 'og min yin phyir don spyi 'jal byed kyi rtog
NK117(she)001:33423: pa de'i gong na gzhan med pa'i phyir ro //
NK117(she)001:33424: de'ang khyams bzhi pa nas dgu pa'i bar gyi rten
NK117(she)001:33425: dang brten pa ni log par 'dren pa'i gnyen por
NK117(she)001:33426: sprul pas rang snang gi 'og min du mi bgrang
NK117(she)001:33427: ngo // de lta bu'i zhing khams kyang rang ngo'i
NK117(she)001:33428: sgrib pa las sgrol stobs kyi yon tan las byung
NK117(she)001:33429: ba'i rang snang chen por bkod pa yin no //
NK117(she)001:33432: chos sku'i ye shes phyi ru gsal ba'i mdangs //
NK117(she)001:33433: phun tshogs lnga ldan longs skur rdzogs pa'i gnas //
NK117(she)001:33434: gang du sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs gyur pa'i //
NK117(she)001:33435: sangs rgyas kho na'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa yi //
NK117(she)001:33436: rol pa nyid phyir gtso 'khor mchog dman mnyam //
NK117(she)001:33437: kun gyi thugs kyang rnam par mi rtog cing //
NK117(she)001:33438: gsung ni brjod bral sku ni mtshan dper rdzogs //
NK117(she)001:33439: rang snang ye shes mthong ba dag pa'i spyan //
NK117(she)001:33440: gcig gis gcig gzigs nam yang sgrib pa med //
NK117(she)001:33441: ces pa ni de'ang chos sku'i ye shes thim la
NK117(she)001:33442: ma rmugs pa'i skabs su gzhon nu bum pa'i skur
NK117(she)001:33443: gnas kyang ye shes phyi ru gsal ba'i tshe mdangs
NK117(she)001:33444: de nyid phun sum tshogs pa lnga ldan longs spyod
NK117(she)001:33445: rdzogs pa'i skur gnas pa ste /
NK117(she)001:33446: gang du sgrib pa mtha' dag spangs par gyur pa'i
NK117(she)001:33447: rnam par grol ba'i lam mthar thug pa de ni
NK117(she)001:33448: / sangs rgyas kho na'i rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i thugs
NK117(she)001:33449: rje'i rol pa'am rtsa las shar phyir gtso 'khor mchog
NK117(she)001:33450: dman kun gsang gsum mnyam zhing /
NK117(she)001:33451: kun gyi thugs kyang rnam pa ste mtshan mar mi rtog cing /
NK117(she)001:33452: gsung ni rlung gi 'phro 'du stongs pas brjod pa
NK117(she)001:33453: dang bral zhing sku ni snang stong spros pa dang
NK117(she)001:33454: bral bzhin mtshan dpe rdzogs shing rang snang ye shes
NK117(she)001:33455: te gzung 'dzin gyi mthong ba dag pa'i ste yul
NK117(she)001:33456: dang yul can gyi 'dzin pa bral ba'i spyan gyis
NK117(she)001:33457: gcig gis gcig gzigs pa la nam yang sgrib pa
NK117(she)001:33458: med cing chos sku ngo bo nyid kyis rtag pa'i
NK117(she)001:33459: gdangs las longs sku rgyun gyis rtag pa'i zhing khams
NK117(she)001:33460: su lhun gyis grub nas sprul sku rgyun mi 'chad
NK117(she)001:33464: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi spyod yul ni //
NK117(she)001:33465: bla na med phyir srid zhis ma bsdus phyir //
NK117(she)001:33466: dag pa'i sems can chen po rnams kyis kyang //
NK117(she)001:33467: mthong bar mi nus rgyal ba'i ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:33468: 'gal ba'i sgrib chad da dung ma spangs phyir //
NK117(she)001:33469: zhes pa ni de la dus gsum gyi rgyal ba
NK117(she)001:33470: rnams kyi khams dang yon tan gyi spyod yul ni
NK117(she)001:33471: nam mkhar ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa bla na
NK117(she)001:33473: srid zhi gnyis kas ma bsdus pa'i phyir na ngag gis brjod pa'i yul las 'das shing /
NK117(she)001:33474: don dam pa'i mthar thug pa /
NK117(she)001:33475: dpe dang tha snyad kyis mi thug pas sa bcu'i
NK117(she)001:33476: yon tan dang dbang bcu thob pa'i byang chub sems
NK117(she)001:33477: dpa' 'am / dag pa'i sems can chen po rnams
NK117(she)001:33478: kyis kyang sgra ji bzhin par mthong bar mi nus
NK117(she)001:33479: dpa' 'am / pa yang / rgyal ba'i ye shes
NK117(she)001:33480: dang 'gal ba'i sgrib chas da dung ma spangs pa'i
NK117(she)001:33481: phyir rgyal ba kho na'i spyod yul las gzhan ma
NK117(she)001:33482: dpa' 'am / pa yang / yin no // zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33484: 'das dang ma 'ongs da lta dus gsum gyi //
NK117(she)001:33485: nges pa las 'das 'og min chen po na //
NK117(she)001:33486: bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dus bzhi'i bdag nyid can //
NK117(she)001:33487: gtso 'khor ngo bo mthun pa'i rang snang ngo //
NK117(she)001:33488: zhes pa ni de la 'das ma 'ongs da ltar
NK117(she)001:33489: te 'dus byas kyi dus las 'das shing chos nyid
NK117(she)001:33490: 'dus ma byas pa yod med rtag chad sogs kyi
NK117(she)001:33491: nges pa las 'das pa'i rang snang don gyi 'og
NK117(she)001:33492: min chen po na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas 'das ma
NK117(she)001:33493: 'ongs da lta gsum dang dus gsum mnyam pa nyid
NK117(she)001:33494: la dus bzhi pa kun tu bzang po'i dus te
NK117(she)001:33495: dngos po dang mtshan ma las 'das pa'i bdag nyid
NK117(she)001:33496: can gtso zhes yar chad pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33497: 'khor zhes mar chad pa ma yin par thams cad ngo bo mthun pa'i rang snang kho na'o //
NK117(she)001:33500: de nyid ngang las sems can dag gdul ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:33501: 'dul byed ston pa gsum du bkod pa ni //
NK117(she)001:33502: rang bzhin sprul pa 'gro 'dul sprul pa dang //
NK117(she)001:33503: sna tshogs sprul pa gsum las rang bzhin ni //
NK117(she)001:33504: rgyal ba'i ye shes snang ba 'og min gyi //
NK117(she)001:33505: dbyings snang longs sku'i dpe byad dwangs shel nang //
NK117(she)001:33506: 'phos lta'i gzugs brnyan phyed sprul longs sku'i gnas //
NK117(she)001:33507: zhes pa ni de yang chos sku spros pa dang
NK117(she)001:33508: bral yang longs sku lhun grub kyi gdangs 'gag med
NK117(she)001:33509: de nyid kyi ngang las sems can rnams 'dul ba'i
NK117(she)001:33510: phyir du 'dul byed kyi ston pa rnam gsum du
NK117(she)001:33511: bkod pa ni gdul bya yang rnam pa gsum la
NK117(she)001:33512: dgongs te / dang po rgyal sras 'phags pa sogs
NK117(she)001:33513: gdul bya mchog la gzugs brnyan longs sku'am phyed sprul
NK117(she)001:33514: longs sku yang zer te dbyings kyi longs sku mkha'
NK117(she)001:33515: dgongs te / zla dang / 'di ni chu zla'i khyad par dang /
NK117(she)001:33516: gtso bo dbyings snang dang mtshungs kyang 'khor dman pa'i khyad par yod pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33517: 'gro 'dul dang sna tshogs sprul sku yang rim bzhin 'chad do //
NK117(she)001:33518: de la dang po ni gtsang ris kyi 'og min
NK117(she)001:33519: las 'phags pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa dbang phyug
NK117(she)001:33520: chen po'i 'og min bla na med pa 'di ltar
NK117(she)001:33522: dbus na 'og min shar na mngon par dga' //
NK117(she)001:33523: lho na dpal ldan nub na pad+ma brtsegs //
NK117(she)001:33524: byang na las rab grub pa rnam pa lngar //
NK117(she)001:33525: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dbus na 'og min chos dbyings dang /
NK117(she)001:33526: shar na mngon par dga' ba /
NK117(she)001:33527: lho na dpal dang ldan pa nub na pad+ma brtsegs
NK117(she)001:33528: pa byang na las rab grub pa dang rnam pa
NK117(she)001:33529: lnga'o // de lnga na brten pa'i lha ni /
NK117(she)001:33531: gzugs kyi rgyal po la sogs ston mchog lnga //
NK117(she)001:33532: mtshan dpe yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid can //
NK117(she)001:33533: zhi dang khro bo'i rnam 'gyur dpag med cing //
NK117(she)001:33534: zhes pa ni 'di ltar dbus na gzugs kyi rgyal po ste rnam snang dang /
NK117(she)001:33535: phyogs bzhir shar nas rim bzhin /
NK117(she)001:33536: mi bskyod pa rin 'byung snang mtha' don grub ste
NK117(she)001:33537: ston mchog lnga po rang rang gi 'khor nges pa
NK117(she)001:33538: mtshan dang dpe byad sogs yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag
NK117(she)001:33540: de dag kyang zhi ba dang khro bo'i rnam 'gyur dpag tu med pa dang bcas te bzhugs pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33541: rgyud gzhan las gtso bo mi bskyod pa 'byung yang
NK117(she)001:33542: 'dir ye shes rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo'i rgyud
NK117(she)001:33543: las dbus su rnam snang gsungs pa bzhin kun mkhyen
NK117(she)001:33544: klong chen pas rnam par shes pa'i rang bzhin so
NK117(she)001:33545: sor 'char zhing me long du gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa
NK117(she)001:33546: lta bu'i ye shes dang ldan pa rnam snang du
NK117(she)001:33550: ye shes rnam pa lnga po re re la'ang //
NK117(she)001:33551: bzhi bzhi'i 'khor dang bcas pa nyi shu lnga //
NK117(she)001:33552: chos dbyings ye shes g.yo ba med pa ni //
NK117(she)001:33553: nam mkha'i gzugs bzhin shes bya'i mtha' las 'das //
NK117(she)001:33554: me long ye shes gzung 'dzin rdul bral ni //
NK117(she)001:33555: mngon par 'du byed med bzhin mched pa'i gzhi //
NK117(she)001:33556: mnyam nyid ye shes chos kun mtshan nyid med //
NK117(she)001:33557: srid zhi dbyer med zhi ba'i dbyings su bzhugs //
NK117(she)001:33558: sor rtog ye shes chos nyid ji lta dang //
NK117(she)001:33559: chos can shes bya ji snyed rtag thogs med //
NK117(she)001:33560: bya grub ye shes phrin las gzhan phan can //
NK117(she)001:33561: chags thogs spangs pa'i mdzad pa lhun gyis grub //
NK117(she)001:33562: ces pa ni de ltar ston pa lnga po re
NK117(she)001:33563: re la'ang ye shes kyang rnam pa lnga ste de
NK117(she)001:33564: re re la'ang bzhi bzhi'i 'khor dang bcas pa'i nyi
NK117(she)001:33565: shu rtsa lnga yod pa las /
NK117(she)001:33566: chos dbyings ye shes g.yo ba med pa ni sems
NK117(she)001:33567: can thams cad la yod kyang brjod bya min te
NK117(she)001:33568: sna tshogs ma yin nam mkha'i gzugs bzhin shes bya'i
NK117(she)001:33570: me long ye shes ni gzung bya'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK117(she)001:33571: 'dzin byed kyi rtog pa med pa'i rdul bral ni
NK117(she)001:33572: mngon par 'du bya dang 'du byed med bzhin sna
NK117(she)001:33573: tshogs mched pa'i gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33574: mnyam nyid ye shes ni chos so cog kun mtshan nyid du grub pa med cing /
NK117(she)001:33575: srid pa zhes ngan pa dang zhi ba zhes bzang
NK117(she)001:33576: por dbyer med cing rtog tshogs thams cad zhi ba'i
NK117(she)001:33578: sor rtog ye shes chos nyid ji lta ba dang
NK117(she)001:33579: chos can shes bya ji snyed pa 'jig rten las
NK117(she)001:33580: 'das pa'i phun tshogs thams cad dang /
NK117(she)001:33582: nyan rang dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi yang
NK117(she)001:33583: dag grub pa thams cad rtag pa dang thogs pa
NK117(she)001:33585: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni /
NK117(she)001:33586: dper na sems can rnams kyi sgo gsum gyi bya
NK117(she)001:33587: ba byed bzhin du phrin las gzhan gyi sgo nas
NK117(she)001:33588: sems can gyi don lhun gyis grub par mdzad pa'o
NK117(she)001:33591: 'khor ni sa bcu'i sems dpa' 'ba' zhig la //
NK117(she)001:33592: sku yis chos rnams 'jal ba'i 'od bkye bas //
NK117(she)001:33593: byad kyi dri ma me long nang gsal ltar //
NK117(she)001:33594: da dung bdag dang ston pa'i khyad mthong nas //
NK117(she)001:33595: byang chub sgrib pa gting dpag dka' ba dag /
NK117(she)001:33596: sbyangs nas bcu gcig kun tu 'od la 'gro //
NK117(she)001:33597: zhes pa ni de'ang 'khor ni ston pa rang las
NK117(she)001:33598: rgyud gzhan gyis bsdus pa'i byang chub sems dpa' 'ba'
NK117(she)001:33599: zhig la sku'i chos rnams mjal ba'i 'od bkye ba'i
NK117(she)001:33600: mod la / byad kyi dri ma me long nang
NK117(she)001:33601: du gsal ba ltar da dung bdag ste 'khor dang
NK117(she)001:33602: ston pa'i khyad mthong nas byang chub sgrib pa shin
NK117(she)001:33603: tu phra ba gting dpag dka' ba dag sbyangs nas
NK117(she)001:33604: sa bcu gcig pa kun tu 'od la 'gro zhes
NK117(she)001:33606: dus ni sa bcu'i dbang phyug chen po rnams //
NK117(she)001:33607: 'jig rten mgon po ngo bo med pa'i dbyings //
NK117(she)001:33608: mi zad rgyan 'khor sku gsung thugs kyi ngang //
NK117(she)001:33609: ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig tu ma gyur bar //
NK117(she)001:33610: 'chi ba'i bdud bcom 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /
NK117(she)001:33611: ces pa ni de yang rang bzhin sprul pa'i ston
NK117(she)001:33612: 'khor rnam dus ni sa bcu'i dbang phyug 'phags pa
NK117(she)001:33613: chen po de rnams 'jig rten mgon po ston pa
NK117(she)001:33614: rigs lnga po ngo bo med pa'i dbyings mi zad
NK117(she)001:33615: pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i sku gsung thugs kyi ngang
NK117(she)001:33616: du ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig tu ma gyur bar
NK117(she)001:33617: du 'chi ba'i bdud bcom bzhin 'jig rten 'byor slad
NK117(she)001:33618: de ngo bo nyid med la sbyor phyir brtag pa'o
NK117(she)001:33621: gdul bya'i gti mug la sogs nyon mongs lnga //
NK117(she)001:33622: gang gis gnyen por che ba'i zhing khams dang //
NK117(she)001:33623: ston par bstan pa'i sku lnga chos rab lnga //
NK117(she)001:33624: gnas 'gyur ye shes rnam pa lnga po yang //
NK117(she)001:33625: mthong lam nas bzung sa bcu rgyun matha'i bar //
NK117(she)001:33626: rim rdzogs rdzogs pa'i byang chub snying por 'gro //
NK117(she)001:33627: zhes pa ni de la gdul bya'i gti mug la
NK117(she)001:33628: sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa lnga la sbyong byed 'og
NK117(she)001:33629: min la sogs pa'i zhing khams lnga ste gang gi
NK117(she)001:33630: gnyen por che ba'i zhing khams lngar rnam snang sogs
NK117(she)001:33631: ston par bstan pa'i sku lnga dang /
NK117(she)001:33632: chos dbyings ye shes sogs ye shes lngar snang bas
NK117(she)001:33633: gnas 'gyur lnga thob pa yang dug lnga'i dri ma
NK117(she)001:33634: sbyong dus rgyal ba rigs lnga dang bcas pa'i rten
NK117(she)001:33638: zhing 'di sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' las //
NK117(she)001:33639: gzhan gyi spyod pa'i yul du snang min zhing //
NK117(she)001:33640: de bzhin ston pa longs spyod rdzogs na'ang //
NK117(she)001:33641: 'khor sogs rang snang ma yin rgyud gzhan pas //
NK117(she)001:33642: bsdus phyir phyed snang rang bzhin sprul pa zhes //
NK117(she)001:33643: nyi zla kha sbyor chen po'i rgyud kyis bstan //
NK117(she)001:33644: zhes pa ni 'di zhes pa rang bzhin sprul pa'i
NK117(she)001:33645: zhing ste 'khor sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' las
NK117(she)001:33646: 'gro ba gzhan gyi spyod pa'i yul tha mal du
NK117(she)001:33647: snang ba ma yin zhing de bzhin du ston pa
NK117(she)001:33648: rigs lnga po dbyings snang longs spyod rdzogs sku ltar
NK117(she)001:33649: snang na'ang 'khor sogs te longs spyod dang ldan chos
NK117(she)001:33650: sogs rang snang ma yin cing rgyud gzhan pas bsdus
NK117(she)001:33651: phyir phyed snang rang bzhin sprul pa zhes gang du
NK117(she)001:33652: gsungs na nyi zla kha sbyor chen po'i rgyud kyis
NK117(she)001:33655: khyad par rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK117(she)001:33656: rang snang ye shes dkyil 'khor dam pa ru //
NK117(she)001:33657: mchog gzigs bla mas dbang bskur ma nyams la //
NK117(she)001:33658: nyin dus rang snang mngon sum 'od gsal dang //
NK117(she)001:33659: mtshan mo snying ga'i 'od mdangs goms pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:33660: rtogs pa'i rang bzhin tshad du ma phyin yang //
NK117(she)001:33661: chos nyid bden pa bla ma'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK117(she)001:33662: sa thob rnams dang skal ba mtshungs gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:33663: gzhi snang lhun grub phyogs bcu sprul par 'gro //
NK117(she)001:33664: zhes pa ni de yang theg pa kun las khyad
NK117(she)001:33665: par du gyur pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK117(she)001:33666: lugs ltar na rang snang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK117(she)001:33667: dam pa ru mchog gzigs te dngos grub gnyis las
NK117(she)001:33668: mchog thob pa'i bla mas spros bcas spros med rab
NK117(she)001:33669: tu spros med sogs thob bzhin ma nyams pa dag
NK117(she)001:33670: la nyin dus zer mdangs kyi 'od gsal dang /
NK117(she)001:33671: mtshan mo shes bya bum 'jug gis snying ga'i 'od
NK117(she)001:33672: gdangs la goms pa rnams ni rtogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK117(she)001:33673: tshad du ma phyin yang chos nyid 'gyur ba med
NK117(she)001:33674: pa dang / bla ma'i byin rlabs kyis lus kyi
NK117(she)001:33675: rgya las grol tshe sprul pa'i zhing yid la dran
NK117(she)001:33676: ma thag tu sa thob pa'i sems dpa' dang skal
NK117(she)001:33677: ba mtshungs par gyur nas gzhi snang lhun grub phyogs
NK117(she)001:33678: bcu sprul pa'i zhing mthong ba'i mod la bcu gcig
NK117(she)001:33679: kun tu 'od du dbugs 'byin thob pa yin la
NK117(she)001:33680: spyir zhing bcu dur khrod me ri 'bar ba dang
NK117(she)001:33681: bcu gcig yod kyang rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa
NK117(she)001:33682: pa dang / lnga ni / rtsa ba /
NK117(she)001:33683: khyad par rnam grol dbugs chen 'byin pa lnga //
NK117(she)001:33684: shar nas rin bzhin shel dang su war+na //
NK117(she)001:33685: pad rag in+d+ra n+ai la'i gzhal med khang //
NK117(she)001:33686: sgo khyams rta babs snang byed ba lang mig /
NK117(she)001:33687: zur bzhir mu tig mchod rten dril bu dang //
NK117(she)001:33688: g.yer khas sbrel ba'i dpyang thag rlung bskyod sgra //
NK117(she)001:33689: rnam thar gsum ldan chos dbyings dar dir sgrogs //
NK117(she)001:33690: phyogs bzhir spros sprin g.yo ba'i ba dan bzhi //
NK117(she)001:33691: phyi rim yan lag brgyad ldan rdzing bu'i 'gram //
NK117(she)001:33692: ta la'i ljon pa d+r+wa phyed 'phyang phrul can //
NK117(she)001:33693: shang shang te'u rma bya ka ta ri //
NK117(she)001:33694: ne tso mi skad smra dang ngang pa gzhon //
NK117(she)001:33695: ri skegs zer mo sbab dang kang+ka ri //
NK117(she)001:33696: lha'i bya dril bu'i sgra can khu byug dang //
NK117(she)001:33697: gser gyi rdo rje'i gzugs can kri ti pa //
NK117(she)001:33698: g.yu dang byi ru in+d+ra n+ai la dang //
NK117(she)001:33699: dung ltar kha dog phyed pa'i bya tshogs kyis //
NK117(she)001:33700: snyan sgrogs mgrin pa'i rgyud mngas kun tu 'khrol //
NK117(she)001:33701: de na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK117(she)001:33702: nyon mongs gnod pa zhi ba'i chu klung la //
NK117(she)001:33703: spyad pa tsam gyis 'du ba'i nad mi 'byung //
NK117(she)001:33704: yid la ci bsam dran pa'i mod la 'byung //
NK117(she)001:33705: sum cu rtsa gsum lha dang longs spyod mnyam //
NK117(she)001:33706: phyi rim rin chen sna bdun pha gu can //
NK117(she)001:33707: zhing mchog de na rigs bzhi'i ston pa yis //
NK117(she)001:33708: dus bzhir chos kyi sgra sgrogs rgyun mi chad //
NK117(she)001:33709: kun gyi bar snang he ru ka dpal zhing //
NK117(she)001:33710: dur khrod chen po me ri 'bar ba na //
NK117(she)001:33711: ston pa gzhon nu dpa' bo bcom ldan 'das //
NK117(she)001:33712: lag na rdo rje la sogs dpa' bo dang //
NK117(she)001:33713: mkha' 'gro'i sprin phung 'phro ba'i dbus nyid na //
NK117(she)001:33714: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i chos 'khor bskor //
NK117(she)001:33715: pad+ma las skyes rgyal sras dpag tu med //
NK117(she)001:33716: kun kyang lha dang lha mo khye'u dang //
NK117(she)001:33717: bu mo'i rnam pa drang srong grub pa can //
NK117(she)001:33718: rnam par rtog pa med cing sems gsum med //
NK117(she)001:33719: yid drug dang ni nyon mongs drug kyang med //
NK117(she)001:33720: ma rig pa med rkyen bzhi yod ma yin //
NK117(she)001:33721: de yang mtshungs par ldan pa rnams kyang med //
NK117(she)001:33722: ston pa rdo rje 'chang gi byin rlabs las //
NK117(she)001:33723: rang bzhin nyid du bkod phyir rang bzhin ni //
NK117(she)001:33724: sprul pa'i zhing zhes rgyal sras rnams la grags //
NK117(she)001:33725: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gsang lam du //
NK117(she)001:33726: rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud las bstan //
NK117(she)001:33727: zhes pa rgyud las bstan zhes pa rtsa ba nyid
NK117(she)001:33728: kyis shes par nus pas 'grel pa mi dgos so
NK117(she)001:33729: // tshul 'di ni gsang sngags thun mong du dag
NK117(she)001:33730: pa mkha' spyod dang sa spyod la sogs pa'i zhing
NK117(she)001:33731: du grub mtha' snyogs par grags pa dang rnam pa
NK117(she)001:33734: gzhan du bde chen mkha' la spyod pa dang //
NK117(she)001:33735: sa spyod zhes grags don gyi 'od gsal la //
NK117(she)001:33736: dbang thob lhan cig skyes pa'i d+aak+ki dang //
NK117(she)001:33737: yul chen nyer bzhir spyod pa'i zhing skyes ma //
NK117(she)001:33738: la sogs dpa' bo rnal 'byor ma tshogs dang //
NK117(she)001:33739: skal ba mnyam pa'i rig 'dzin gral gang du //
NK117(she)001:33740: lam gyi 'phro sbyong rig pa 'dzin pa yi //
NK117(she)001:33741: rdo rje bla ma rnams ni rab bzhugs nas //
NK117(she)001:33742: sngags kyi lta spyod rlabs po che la spyod //
NK117(she)001:33743: 'di dag rang snang dag pa'i sa bon dang //
NK117(she)001:33744: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i brtul zhugs mthar son pa'i //
NK117(she)001:33745: gsang sngags grub pa rnams la snang ba las //
NK117(she)001:33746: rtog 'dod can gyi phyin du yod pa yi //
NK117(she)001:33747: ris chad can du bsam par mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:33748: zhes pa ni de'ang sngags rgyud gzhan du na bde chen mkha' la spyod pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33749: sa spyod zhes grags pa yang /
NK117(she)001:33750: don gyi 'od gsal la dbang thob pa rnams ni lhan cig skyes ma dang /
NK117(she)001:33751: yul nyer bzhir sprul pa bzung ba'i zhing skyes ma
NK117(she)001:33752: sogs dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor ma rnams dang skal
NK117(she)001:33753: ba mnyam pa'i rig 'dzin gyi gral gang du lam
NK117(she)001:33754: gyi 'phro ma dag pa'i cha rnams sbyong zhing rig
NK117(she)001:33755: pa 'dzin pa'i rdo rje'i bla ma rnams ni rab
NK117(she)001:33756: tu bzhugs nas sngags kyi lta spyod rlabs po cher
NK117(she)001:33757: spyod nus pa'i go 'phang mchog la 'god pa yin
NK117(she)001:33758: cing / 'di dag rang snang dag par sbyangs pa'i sa bon dang /
NK117(she)001:33759: bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i brtul zhugs mthar son pa'i gsang sngags grub pa rnams la snang ba las /
NK117(she)001:33760: rtog 'dod can dag de ru e slebs kyi re
NK117(she)001:33761: bas phyin du yod pa lta bu'i ris su chad
NK117(she)001:33762: pa'i yul tha mal du bsam par mi bya'o //
NK117(she)001:33765: de nyid ngang las longs spyod rdzogs pa yi //
NK117(she)001:33766: yi ge'i sprin gyi 'od zer rab 'phros pas //
NK117(she)001:33767: 'jig rten 'dul byed sprul pa'i sku mchog ni //
NK117(she)001:33768: gnas rigs drug gi gdul bya'i snang ba la //
NK117(she)001:33769: rang rang ming gi mngon brjod rjes 'gro ba'i //
NK117(she)001:33770: 'dul byed rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK117(she)001:33771: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med stong gsum gyi //
NK117(she)001:33772: stong chen snyed dang mnyam par rab sprul nas //
NK117(she)001:33773: gdul ba bzhi yi 'gro don bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:33774: ces pa ni de nyid ngang las te dbyings nang
NK117(she)001:33775: gsal gyi gdangs 'gag med longs spyod rdzogs par shar
NK117(she)001:33776: ba'i yi ge'i sprin te rigs drug gi sa bon
NK117(she)001:33777: 'od zer gyi rnam par rab tu 'phros pas 'jig
NK117(she)001:33778: rten 'dul byed sprul pa'i sku mchog drug ni gnas
NK117(she)001:33779: rigs drug gi gdul bya'i snang ba la rang rang
NK117(she)001:33780: gi ming gi mngon brjod lha dang mi dang lha
NK117(she)001:33781: min sogs kyi rjes su 'gro ba'i /
NK117(she)001:33782: 'dul byed rigs pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug gi
NK117(she)001:33783: phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med stong gsum gyi stong
NK117(she)001:33784: chen po ji snyed dang mnyam par rab tu sprul
NK117(she)001:33785: nas gdul ba bzhi yi 'gro don bsam gyis mi
NK117(she)001:33786: khyab pa'ang 'gro ba so so gnas ris su de
NK117(she)001:33787: dang de'i snang ba dang mthun pa'i don mdzad pa
NK117(she)001:33790: de'ang bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba ni //
NK117(she)001:33791: sku yi mdzad pa chen po bcu gnyis yin //
NK117(she)001:33792: gsung gi mdzad pa theg pa gsum mam gcig /
NK117(she)001:33793: gang yang 'du shes rjes 'gro sems can gyi //
NK117(she)001:33794: nyon mongs gnyen por dgongs te gsungs pa la //
NK117(she)001:33795: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong grangs //
NK117(she)001:33796: gsung ltar snang yang sgra tshig rang mtshan pa //
NK117(she)001:33797: ma yin sems can khams la byin rlabs mthus //
NK117(she)001:33798: rnam par rig par nyid dang mthun par shar //
NK117(she)001:33799: thugs kyis gdul ba dus gsum mkhyen cing gzigs //
NK117(she)001:33800: dus kyang so sor mi rtog dus med dus //
NK117(she)001:33801: rang bzhin gdod ma'i gnas skabs kun tu bzang //
NK117(she)001:33802: gzhan gyi sems rgyud mkhyen dang de bzhin du //
NK117(she)001:33803: rdzu 'phrul chen po'i spyan dang snyan la sogs //
NK117(she)001:33804: mngon shes drug po dus las yol ba med //
NK117(she)001:33805: phrin las gdul ba kun tu sku dang ni //
NK117(she)001:33806: kun tu thugs dang de bzhin kun tu zhal //
NK117(she)001:33807: kun tu gsung gi gsang ba bsam mi khyab //
NK117(she)001:33808: sku gsung thugs dang dngos su don mdzad la //
NK117(she)001:33809: phrin las kyis ni dngos rgyud kun tu mdzad //
NK117(she)001:33810: de ltar dbyings las sprul pa'i sku mchog rnams //
NK117(she)001:33811: chos nyid la ltos ji lta'i ye shes dang //
NK117(she)001:33812: chos can la ltos ji snyed mkhyen pa yi //
NK117(she)001:33813: ye shes gnyis kyis gdul bya'i rgyud 'grol zhing //
NK117(she)001:33814: nye bar zhi dang ma 'dres chos tshul ston //
NK117(she)001:33815: zhes pa ni de la sku bsod nams chen pos
NK117(she)001:33816: 'dul ba ni sku yi mdzad pa chen po bcu
NK117(she)001:33817: gnyis yin la / gsung gi mdzad pa theg pa
NK117(she)001:33818: gsum mam gcig ste gang yang 'du shes kyi rjes
NK117(she)001:33820: sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa'i gnyen por
NK117(she)001:33821: dgongs te gsungs pa la chos kyi sgo mo brgyad
NK117(she)001:33822: khri bzhi stong gi grangs gsungs pa ltar snang yang
NK117(she)001:33823: sgra tshig rang mtshan pa ma yin zhing sems can
NK117(she)001:33824: gyi khams la byin rlabs zhugs pa'i mthus rnam par
NK117(she)001:33825: rig pa ste blo'i rtog dpyod nyid dang mthun par
NK117(she)001:33827: thugs kyi gdul ba 'das ma 'ongs da lta ste
NK117(she)001:33828: dus gsum mkhyen cing gzigs bzhin dus kyang so sor
NK117(she)001:33829: mi rtog pa la dus med kyi dus te rang
NK117(she)001:33830: bzhin gdod ma'i gnas skabs kun tu yin la gzhan
NK117(she)001:33831: gyi sems rgyud ji lta ba bzhin du mkhyen pa
NK117(she)001:33832: dang / de bzhin rdzu 'phrul chen po'i spyan dang
NK117(she)001:33833: snyan la sogs pa'i mngon shes drug po dus las
NK117(she)001:33834: yol ba med bzhin phrin las kyi gdul ba la
NK117(she)001:33835: kun tu sku 'dod dgur bsgyur ba dang /
NK117(she)001:33836: srid dang zhi ba'i khams kun tu thugs kyis khyab
NK117(she)001:33837: cing de bzhin du kun tu zhal te 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:33838: las dang skal bar ldan pa dag gi rang sems
NK117(she)001:33839: kyi gnas lugs rtogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33840: kun tu gsung gi gsang ba 'gro ba rigs drug
NK117(she)001:33841: gi sgra skad kyang de ltar snang ba'i byin rlabs
NK117(she)001:33842: kyi stobs bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK117(she)001:33843: de'ang sku gsung thugs kyis dngos su 'gro don mdzad
NK117(she)001:33844: cing phrin las kyis ni dngos brgyud kun tu bstan
NK117(she)001:33845: 'gro'i don mdzad la de ltar dbyings ka dag dang
NK117(she)001:33846: lhun grub las sprul pa'i sku mchog rnams ni /
NK117(she)001:33847: chos nyid don dam la ltos pa'i ji lta mkhyen
NK117(she)001:33848: pa'i ye shes dang chos can kun rdzob la ltos
NK117(she)001:33849: pa ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis gdul bya'i
NK117(she)001:33850: rgyud 'grol zhing nye bar zhi ba dang ma 'dres
NK117(she)001:33851: pa'i chos tshul ston zhes pa'o //
NK117(she)001:33853: de las yang sprul rnam pa brjod mi lang //
NK117(she)001:33854: 'gro ba drug gi gnas rigs de snyed du //
NK117(she)001:33855: lha rnams 'dul byed tshangs dbang bde 'byung sogs //
NK117(she)001:33856: mi la nyan rang byang sems 'khor los bsgyur //
NK117(she)001:33857: de bzhin lha ma yin la thags bzang ris //
NK117(she)001:33858: bya la shing rta mo dang ri dwags phyir //
NK117(she)001:33859: seng ge'i rgyal po yi dam brtan pa sogs //
NK117(she)001:33860: mdor na dmyal ba yi dwags gang dang gang //
NK117(she)001:33861: 'dul byed de dang de 'dra'i gzugs sprul nas //
NK117(she)001:33862: sems can don la nam yang g.yel ba med /
NK117(she)001:33863: 'di ni 'jig rten drug gi zhing rnams su //
NK117(she)001:33864: las dang bag chags dge sdig rgyu 'bras kyi //
NK117(she)001:33865: gnas rigs bde sdug mtho dman ltar snang ba'i //
NK117(she)001:33866: rang snang mthun pa'i ston pas don mdzad cing //
NK117(she)001:33867: chos kyang ma nges gdul bya'i blo rtog ltar //
NK117(she)001:33868: dus kyang rang rang skal ba'i rjes 'gro ba //
NK117(she)001:33869: ma dag zhing gi 'gro la de ltar snang //
NK117(she)001:33870: zhes pa ni de yang rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku
NK117(she)001:33871: de las kyang yang sprul gyi rnam pa brjod kyis
NK117(she)001:33872: mi lang 'byung ba yang 'gro ba drug gi gnas
NK117(she)001:33874: lha rnams 'dul bar byed pa la tshangs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33876: bde 'byung ste dbang phyug la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33877: mi la'ang nyan rang byang sems 'khor los bsgyur rgyal la sogs pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33878: de bzhin du lha ma yin la thags bzang ris /
NK117(she)001:33879: bya la shing rta mo dang /
NK117(she)001:33880: ri dwags 'dul phyir seng ge'i rgyal po yi dam
NK117(she)001:33881: brtan pa la sogs pa mdor na dmyal ba yi
NK117(she)001:33882: dwags sogs 'gro ba gang dang gang dul ba la
NK117(she)001:33883: 'dul byed kyang de dang de 'dra'i gzugs su sprul
NK117(she)001:33884: nas sems can gang gi don dgos pa de la
NK117(she)001:33885: nam yang g.yel ba med cing brtson pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33886: 'di nas 'jig rten drug gi zhing rnams su las
NK117(she)001:33887: dkar nag dang de'i bag chags dge sdig gnyis kyi
NK117(she)001:33888: rgyu 'bras kyis bskrun pa'i gnas ris drug por bde
NK117(she)001:33889: ba dang sdug bsngal dang mtho dman ltar snang ba'i
NK117(she)001:33890: rang snang dang mthun pa'i ston pas sems can gyi
NK117(she)001:33891: don mdzad cing / 'dul byed chos kyang ma nges
NK117(she)001:33892: te gdul bya'i mchog dman dang rtog pa mang nyung
NK117(she)001:33893: ltar dus kyang rang rang gi las bzang ngan gyi
NK117(she)001:33894: skal ba'i rjes su 'gro ba yin cing ma dag
NK117(she)001:33895: zhing gi 'gro ba yongs la de ltar snang ba'o
NK117(she)001:33898: gang zhig rmi lam nang du sangs rgyas mthong //
NK117(she)001:33899: rmi lam lta bur sprul pa'i chos bstan yang //
NK117(she)001:33900: ngo bo nyid med rang bzhin ma grub la //
NK117(she)001:33901: bdag med stong pa gsog tu rig bya zhes //
NK117(she)001:33902: zab mo'i mdo sde dag las gsungs pas na //
NK117(she)001:33903: 'khor 'das rmi lam lta bu'i rol pa la //
NK117(she)001:33904: snang ba'i sangs rgyas ngo bo dag na'ang //
NK117(she)001:33905: rnam pa gdul bya nyid ltar snang ba'i phyir //
NK117(she)001:33906: ma dag thugs rje'i rol pa'i sprul pa yang //
NK117(she)001:33907: ji srid 'khor ba'i rjes 'gro rgyun mi 'chad //
NK117(she)001:33908: ces pa ni 'di ltar gang zhig rmi lam nang
NK117(she)001:33909: du sangs rgyas mthong ba dang rmi lam lta bur
NK117(she)001:33910: sprul pa'i chos bstan pa rmis kyang ngo bo nyid
NK117(she)001:33911: med cing rang bzhin ma grub pa la bdag med
NK117(she)001:33912: pa'i stong pa dang gsog tu rig par bya zhes
NK117(she)001:33913: pa dang zab mo'i mdo sde dag las gsungs pas
NK117(she)001:33914: na 'khor ba dang myang 'das gnyis rmi lam lta
NK117(she)001:33915: bu'i rol pa la snang ba'i sangs rgyas kyi ngo
NK117(she)001:33916: bor dag na'ang rnam pa ni 'gog tu med pa
NK117(she)001:33917: gdul bya gang la gang 'dul ltar snang ba'i phyir
NK117(she)001:33918: na gdug pa 'dul phyir thugs rje rol pa'i sprul
NK117(she)001:33919: pa yang / ji srid 'khor ba ma stong bar
NK117(she)001:33920: gdul bya'i rjes su 'gro ba rgyun mi 'chad do
NK117(she)001:33923: de nyid ngang las sna tshogs sprul pa ni //
NK117(she)001:33924: rang bzhin byon dang 'du byed las byung ba //
NK117(she)001:33925: 'bur du byas dang ris su bris pa dang //
NK117(she)001:33926: gan+d+ho la dang khang bzang skyed mos tshal //
NK117(she)001:33927: mya ngam thang la sprul pa'i grong khyer dang //
NK117(she)001:33928: pad+ma dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin nor //
NK117(she)001:33929: gru gzings zam pa shing rta zas gos sogs //
NK117(she)001:33930: sems med bem po'i tshul du snang ba dang //
NK117(she)001:33931: skye ba mu ge'i tshe na nya bo che //
NK117(she)001:33932: nad kyis gdungs la srog chags des pa dang //
NK117(she)001:33933: srin mo'i gling du cang shes ba la ha //
NK117(she)001:33934: mi gtsang 'dam du gser gyi bung ba sogs //
NK117(she)001:33935: sprul pa sna tshogs rnam kun bde ba'i gzhir //
NK117(she)001:33936: rtog pa med cing g.yo ba med pa ltas //
NK117(she)001:33937: don chen gyis ni dpal du nye bar gnas //
NK117(she)001:33938: zhes pa ni de nyid kyi ngang las sna tshogs
NK117(she)001:33939: sprul pa zhes pa ni 'jig rten khams kyi 'khrul
NK117(she)001:33940: snang dang mtshungs par sangs rgyas kyi rnam sprul yang
NK117(she)001:33941: de snyed du 'char ba yang yid kyi byed pa
NK117(she)001:33942: po dang / chos su bya ba med bzhin du
NK117(she)001:33943: rang bzhin gyi ri brag yul ljongs sogs su sku
NK117(she)001:33944: gsung thugs rten rang byon du snang ba 'gro ba
NK117(she)001:33945: rnams kyis tshogs bsag gi yul du bzung nas lan
NK117(she)001:33946: cig tsam yang dad pa bskyed pa'i rten du bzung
NK117(she)001:33947: po dang / ba rnams dang / skyes bu'i rtsol
NK117(she)001:33948: ba dang 'du byed las byung ba'i sku gsung thugs
NK117(she)001:33949: po dang / ba rnams dang / rten rnams dang
NK117(she)001:33950: / gzhan yang sems med bem po'i tshul gyis 'gro
NK117(she)001:33951: ba rnams la phan cing bde ba cung zad ster
NK117(she)001:33952: nus pa'i tshogs drug gi yul du gyur pa thams
NK117(she)001:33953: cad rgyal ba'i phrin las su shes par bya ste
NK117(she)001:33954: po dang / ba rnams dang / rten rnams dang
NK117(she)001:33955: / // de'ang rten gsum 'bur du byas pa dang
NK117(she)001:33956: po dang / ba rnams dang / rten rnams dang
NK117(she)001:33957: / // / gyang logs dang thang sku sogs ris
NK117(she)001:33959: gan+d+ho la dang khang bzang skyed mos tshal rnams dang /
NK117(she)001:33960: mya ngam thang ste chu med pa'i sar sprul pa'i
NK117(she)001:33961: grong khyer dang pad+ma dang dpag bsam gyi shing dang
NK117(she)001:33962: yid bzhin nor bu gru gzings zam dang shing rta
NK117(she)001:33964: ston pa'i skyes rabs na gsal ba ltar mu ge'i tshe nya bo che dang /
NK117(she)001:33965: nad kyis gdungs pa la srog chags des pa dang /
NK117(she)001:33966: srin mo'i gling du cang shes rta mchog ba las
NK117(she)001:33967: tshong pa mang po srog skyob byas pa lta bu
NK117(she)001:33968: dang / mi gtsang ba'i 'dam rdzab tu gser gyi
NK117(she)001:33969: bung bar sprul nas de'i rigs kyi don byed pa
NK117(she)001:33970: sogs sprul pa sna tshogs nges med du bstan pa
NK117(she)001:33971: yang rnam pa kun tu bde ba'i gzhir 'gyur zhing
NK117(she)001:33972: dang / / de ltar phan btags so snyam pa'i
NK117(she)001:33973: rtog pa dang g.yo ba med pa lta bu'i sgo
NK117(she)001:33974: nas don gyis ni dpal du nye bar gnas so
NK117(she)001:33977: gal te gdul bar bya ba'i dus yol na //
NK117(she)001:33978: 'dul byed dbyings su nub pa'i mtshan dpe ni //
NK117(she)001:33979: ji ltar chu snod med tshe chu zla'i gzugs //
NK117(she)001:33980: sprul gzhi'i zla ba nyid la thim pa ltar //
NK117(she)001:33981: gdul bya'i snang bas bsdus pa'i sprul pa rnams //
NK117(she)001:33982: rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbyings su thim //
NK117(she)001:33983: de'ang gnam stong zla ba gcig shos nas //
NK117(she)001:33984: gcig tu thim pa med kyang phyir gsal mdangs //
NK117(she)001:33985: nang dbyings spros pa med pa'i ngang thim ltar //
NK117(she)001:33986: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i rang snang chos kyi sku'i //
NK117(she)001:33987: ye shes chen por 'khyil ba de nyid la //
NK117(she)001:33988: dbu ma pa rnams 'jug pa chos dbyings su //
NK117(she)001:33989: zhi ba'i 'gog pa dam pa zhes 'dod la //
NK117(she)001:33990: 'dir ni so so rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK117(she)001:33991: phra ba'i ye shes nang gsal chos kyi dbyings //
NK117(she)001:33992: thim la ma rmugs gzhon nu bum pa'i sku //
NK117(she)001:33993: gang du gdul bya snang ba'i mod nyid la //
NK117(she)001:33994: 'gag med thugs rje'i ye shes mched pa'i gzhi //
NK117(she)001:33995: shin tu mnyam par bzhag pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK117(she)001:33996: 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i go 'phang yin //
NK117(she)001:33997: zhes pa ni 'di ltar gal te gdul bar bya
NK117(she)001:33998: ba'i yul gang zhig dus yol nas sdug bsngal zad
NK117(she)001:33999: par gyur na 'dul byed mchog dman gang yang rung
NK117(she)001:34000: ste dbyings las byung zhing dbyings su nub pa'i mtshon
NK117(she)001:34001: dpe ni / ji ltar chus bkangs pa'i snod med
NK117(she)001:34002: tshe der snang ba'i zla gzugs sprul gzhi'i zla ba
NK117(she)001:34004: gdul bya so so'i snang bas bsdus pa'i sprul pa
NK117(she)001:34005: rnams kyang rang snang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbyings su
NK117(she)001:34006: thim pa'o // de'ang gnam stong gi zla ba de
NK117(she)001:34007: gcig shos nas gcig tu thim pa med kyang phyir
NK117(she)001:34008: gsal 'od dkar gyi mdangs nang dbyings spros pa med
NK117(she)001:34009: pa'i dbyings su thim pa ltar longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK117(she)001:34010: rang snang chos kyi sku'i ye shes chen po dang
NK117(she)001:34011: dbyer med du 'khyil ba de nyid la /
NK117(she)001:34012: dbu ma pa rnams kyis 'jug pa chos kyi dbyings
NK117(she)001:34013: su zhi ba'i 'gog pa dam pa zhes 'dod la
NK117(she)001:34014: / 'dir rang lugs ni so so rang rig pa'i
NK117(she)001:34015: ye shes de nyid kyang phra ba'i ye shes nang
NK117(she)001:34016: gsal chos kyi dbyings su zlum tshe thim la ma
NK117(she)001:34017: rmugs pa la gzhon nu bum pa'i sku zhes 'dod
NK117(she)001:34018: cing de nyid kyang gang du gdul bya snang ba'i
NK117(she)001:34019: mod de 'phral du 'gag pa med pa'i thugs rje'i
NK117(she)001:34020: ye shes mched pa'i gzhi las thugs rje'i rol rtsal
NK117(she)001:34022: de lta bu'i don mthar thug pa ni shin tu
NK117(she)001:34023: mnyam par bzhag pa'i chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa
NK117(she)001:34024: ste / de ni 'bras bu lhun grub chen po'i
NK117(she)001:34025: go 'phang ste gdod ma'i gnas lugs grol gzhi'i sar
NK117(she)001:34027: de'ang so so rang rig ye shes ni gtan 'gags ma yin te /
NK117(she)001:34028: de 'gags na myang 'das kyi yon tan rnams dang
NK117(she)001:34029: ye shes kyi chos nyid nyi ma dang zer ltar
NK117(she)001:34030: gnas pa'ang rgyun chad par 'gyur ba'o //
NK117(she)001:34031: 'di ltar kun gzhi dbyings su nub pa ni chos dbyings ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:34032: kun gzhi'i rnam shes nub pa ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:34033: yid shes nub pa ni mnyam nyid do //
NK117(she)001:34034: nyon mongs can gyi yid nub pa ni sor rtog ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:34035: sgo lnga'i rnam shes dbyings su nub pa ni bya grub ye shes so //
NK117(she)001:34036: de'ang chos dbyings dang mnyam nyid ji ltar mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK117(she)001:34037: me long dang sor rtog bya grub gsum ji snyed mkhyen par 'adu'o //
NK117(she)001:34038: des na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid ni
NK117(she)001:34039: chos sku dag pa gnyis ldan yin la de mthong
NK117(she)001:34040: ba'i thabs su sems kyi de kho na nyid la
NK117(she)001:34042: des spangs pa gnyis la brten nas nyon shes kyi
NK117(she)001:34043: sgrib pa bcom nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK117(she)001:34046: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:34047: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:34048: lde mig las le'u bcu gsum pa rdzogs pa'i skabs
NK117(she)001:34050: bdag rgyud snod kyi dpyad pa rdzogs gyur nas //
NK117(she)001:34051: 'jig rten mgon po dri med 'od zer gyi //
NK117(she)001:34052: zhal mthong thugs rje'i dbugs 'byin ma thob na //
NK117(she)001:34053: lam min g.yang sar dal rten stong log byas //
NK117(she)001:34054: de phyir 'di la legs par bshad pa'i cha //
NK117(she)001:34055: bla ma'i byin rlabs sgom byung shes rab las //
NK117(she)001:34056: thos bsam rtog ge'i rigs pas ma bskyed na //
NK117(she)001:34057: rang rang 'dod gzhung phyogs dang 'gal na 'chags //
NK117(she)001:34058: chos tshul rgya mtsho gting dpag dka' ba'i don //
NK117(she)001:34059: mnyam par bzhag pa kho na'i khyad chos las //
NK117(she)001:34060: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnas //
NK117(she)001:34061: yang dag mthong la nam yang bslu ba med //
NK117(she)001:34062: dge ba 'di yis bdag dang sems can rnams //
NK117(she)001:34063: rgyal ba'i ring lugs nor ba med pa'i lam //
NK117(she)001:34064: sgrib gnyis snyogs pa dwangs pa'i gzings zhugs nas //
NK117(she)001:34065: byang chub zhi ba rin chen gling phyin shog /
NK117(she)001:34066: nags mthong ri dwags dkyu ba'i sman ljongs na //
NK117(she)001:34067: dus bzhi'i mngon rtags ngom pa'i ljon pa ni //
NK117(she)001:34068: drang srong rnams la mi snyan sgrog mi byed //
NK117(she)001:34069: snying la 'bab par smra ba'i bya tshogs kyang //
NK117(she)001:34070: sbrul gdug 'khri shing lta bu'i 'khor ba 'dir //
NK117(she)001:34071: skyo ba'i nges 'byung shing rtas yid 'dren pa'i //
NK117(she)001:34072: ca co shin tu zhi ba sgrog thos nas //
NK117(she)001:34073: dbang po nye bar zhi ba'i dpal thob shog /
NK117(she)001:34074: lta ba yid byed rlung gis ma dkrugs la //
NK117(she)001:34075: spyod pa rgyal sras dam pa'i rjes 'gro bas //
NK117(she)001:34076: nam yang gzhan gyi khur du mi 'gro zhing //
NK117(she)001:34077: rlabs chen 'phrin las 'gro ba'i dpal du shog /
NK117(she)001:34078: ces pa ni yon tan rin po che'i mdzod rtsa ba'i sbyar byang ngo //
NK117(she)001:34080: lha mi'i theg pa rim dgu'i stegs nas bzung //
NK117(she)001:34081: nyan thos rang rgyal byang sems theg pa yan //
NK117(she)001:34082: kun gyi rtse gyur rgyud sde drug gi tog /
NK117(she)001:34083: nang rgyud sde gsum theg rim dgu las 'phags //
NK117(she)001:34084: de dag dgongs don rgya mtsho chen po'i mjing //
NK117(she)001:34085: rtog ge'i brgal brtag kho nas dpyad pa yis //
NK117(she)001:34086: dpag par nus rloms rang mgo rang bskor rgyu //
NK117(she)001:34087: de phyir rtsod pa'i rjes su mi 'brang gal //
NK117(she)001:34088: gzhung 'dir de lta'i skyon chags ma yin don //
NK117(she)001:34089: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab rnam gsum po //
NK117(she)001:34090: sngon goms mthu yis rdzogs dang chabs gcig par //
NK117(she)001:34091: 'chad rtsod rtsom pa'i blo gros mchog thob pas //
NK117(she)001:34092: sngon byon mkhas dang grub pa'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK117(she)001:34093: bden pa gnyis las brtsams pa'i gzhung mang don //
NK117(she)001:34094: nyung ngu'i gtam gyi sbyor bas 'dir btus bzhin //
NK117(she)001:34095: snying po gong bur dril 'di bla na med //
NK117(she)001:34096: 'dzam gling mdzes pa'i rgyan drug mchog gnyis dang //
NK117(she)001:34097: gangs ljongs 'dir byon mkhas dang mkhas rloms dag /
NK117(she)001:34098: ji snyed byon rnams bstan bcos mang brtsams mod //
NK117(she)001:34099: 'on kyang bstan la phan gnod mngon gyur bzhin //
NK117(she)001:34100: de phyir rgyal bstan nyid la rgyal ba bzhin //
NK117(she)001:34101: shing rta chen po gnyis kyi lam bzang mchog /
NK117(she)001:34102: zab mo lta ba rgya chen spyod pa zhes //
NK117(she)001:34103: yongs grags gzhung gnyis snying po'ang 'di nyid rang //
NK117(she)001:34104: da lta rgyal bstan nub rir nye ba'i skabs //
NK117(she)001:34105: rang rgyud gyong pos chos la khungs bcol nas //
NK117(she)001:34106: mar skog snum rtsis 'dul dka' mngon gyur tshe //
NK117(she)001:34107: rang rgyud kho na btul na ci ma rung //
NK117(she)001:34108: lar yang rdo rje'i theg par bshad sgrub gnyis //
NK117(she)001:34109: bstan mod de yang deng skabs bshad pa la //
NK117(she)001:34110: gtso bor 'dzin rnams dad dam snying rjer ring //
NK117(she)001:34111: sgrub brtson phal cher bstan 'gror phan la 'dun //
NK117(she)001:34112: 'on kyang de gnyis gang yang bstan dang 'gror //
NK117(she)001:34113: tshul 'chos tsam min phan sems mchog bskyed na //
NK117(she)001:34114: snyigs ma'i bstan 'dzin mchog tu gor ma chag /
NK117(she)001:34115: de phyir rang skyon sun 'byin chos kyi mchog /
NK117(she)001:34116: thos pa mang dgos rna dred ma song gal //
NK117(she)001:34117: bsam pas dpyod dgos 'khrul rtog ma spel gnad //
NK117(she)001:34118: sgom pa brtan dgos gzung 'dzin ma dam gal //
NK117(she)001:34119: 'chad rtsod rtsom gsum khengs pas ma bcom gces //
NK117(she)001:34120: de skad rang gzhan kun la smras nas slar //
NK117(she)001:34121: sems dge ba la nyes pa med gsungs phyir //
NK117(she)001:34122: yon tan rin chen mdzod kyi sa mu tra'i //
NK117(she)001:34123: tshig don chu thigs nor bu skra'i rtse mor //
NK117(she)001:34124: thob bzhin rang mnyam 'ga' la sman slad du //
NK117(she)001:34125: spel ba'i byed po rnam 'dren nyi shu'i zhabs //
NK117(she)001:34126: nam yang spyi bos mchod la mi ngal ba'i //
NK117(she)001:34127: rnal 'byor kun bzang gzhan phan zhes 'bod pas //
NK117(she)001:34128: ngal ba khyad bsad lci ba dang blangs nas //
NK117(she)001:34129: spel bzhin yi ge'i gzugs su ngom byed pa //
NK117(she)001:34130: rang slob dad ldan pun+ye rat+na dang //
NK117(she)001:34131: kun bzang 'chi med zung gis brtson pas bsgrubs //
NK117(she)001:34132: dge ba de yis bdag cag dpon slob la //
NK117(she)001:34133: bzang 'brel ngan 'brel thogs pa'i 'gro rnams gtsos //
NK117(she)001:34134: mtha' yas 'gro ba sems can ma lus kun //
NK117(she)001:34135: phyam gcig gdod ma'i mgon dang dbyer med shog /
NK117(she)001:34136: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi sgo lcags 'byed
NK117(she)001:34137: byed bsdus 'grel rgya mtsho'i chu thigs rin po che'i
NK117(she)001:34138: lde mig ces bya ba 'di nyid ris su ma
NK117(she)001:34139: chad pa'i dad pa dang ngos lkog bral ba'i dam
NK117(she)001:34140: tshig sogs 'phags nor bdun gces nor du 'dzin pa'i
NK117(she)001:34141: rnam 'dren dam pa pun+ye rat+na d+h+wa dza zhes pas
NK117(she)001:34142: bka' yis bskul ma byung ba thod du bcings te
NK117(she)001:34143: rje chos kyi rgyal po don gyi slad du mtshan
NK117(she)001:34144: nas smos te bdag cag gi byang chub ma thob
NK117(she)001:34145: bar rigs kyi bdag por 'du 'bral med pa 7dpal
NK117(she)001:34146: mkhyen brtse'i 'od zer ram rang byung rdo rje 'jigs
NK117(she)001:34147: med gling pa de nyid kyi bka' dri ma med
NK117(she)001:34148: pa rtsa ba yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga'
NK117(she)001:34149: ba'i char zhes bya ba'i le'u dgu pa yan gyis
NK117(she)001:34150: mdo lam gyi 'grel pa bden gnyis shing rta dang
NK117(she)001:34151: rjes kyi le'u bzhi yis sngags spyi dang khyad par
NK117(she)001:34152: rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhi lam 'bras bu'i don gtan
NK117(she)001:34153: la phab pa rnam mkhyen shing rta gnyis te /
NK117(she)001:34154: rgyas 'grel gnyis kyi glegs bam mthong bas 'jigs nas
NK117(she)001:34155: mjal ba las ldog pa'i gang zag rang 'dra 'ga'
NK117(she)001:34156: re la tshig don nyung ngu tsam sngon du bstan
NK117(she)001:34157: nas blo mi sun par byas rjes gdod rgyas 'grel
NK117(she)001:34158: la rim gyis 'dris par byas na lugs dang mthun
NK117(she)001:34159: pa zhig yong du re ba tsam las rnam dpyod
NK117(she)001:34160: dpyad gsum gyi blo gros kyi nyi mas zum pa'i
NK117(she)001:34161: kun+d+ha ltar gyur pa bdag ltas gzhung chen 'di 'dra'i
NK117(she)001:34162: 'grel pa 'bri ba'i spobs pa cung zad kyang thob
NK117(she)001:34163: pa min na'ang lhag bsam rab tu dkar ba zla
NK117(she)001:34164: ba'i 'od la 'gran nus pas bris pas nyes tshogs
NK117(she)001:34165: mkha' la ri mo bzhin stong zhing dge tshogs dbyar
NK117(she)001:34166: skyes kyi rgyun bzhin rgyas par gyur cig gu //
